NK025(ra)001:1: // 'dus pa mdo'i dbang gi cho ga khrigs su byas
NK025(ra)001:2: pa dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i 'jug ngogs las glegs bam
NK025(ra)001:4: bla ma dang bcom ldan 'das rgyal ba zhi khro
NK025(ra)001:5: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams
NK025(ra)001:8: bde chen chos dbyings 'og min zhing na dus gsum
NK025(ra)001:9: bzhugs pa'i rgyal ba sras bcas dkyil 'khor gcig tu
NK025(ra)001:10: lhun grub pa / bcom ldan bde gshegs rdo rje
NK025(ra)001:11: dbyings mchog dam pa rigs brgya zhi ba'i lha nyid
NK025(ra)001:12: ma 'gags rol pa khro bo'i lha //
NK025(ra)001:13: khrag 'thung tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor lhar bcas
NK025(ra)001:14: spro bsdu'i byed po khyab bdag dpal ldan bla mar
NK025(ra)001:15: rnams kun tu // rab btud yo ga gsum gyi
NK025(ra)001:16: dkyil 'khor cho ga'i rim pa 'chad par spro la
NK025(ra)001:17: bdag rgyud byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK025(ra)001:18: de ltar gsang sngags phyi rgyud kyi dbang rnams legs par grub nas /
NK025(ra)001:19: nang pa thabs kyi theg pa gsang sngags bla na med pa 'chad par byed pa la /
NK025(ra)001:20: spyir ma h+aa yo ga la dkyil 'khor bdun /
NK025(ra)001:21: a nu yo ga la dkyil 'khor bdun gsungs pa'i
NK025(ra)001:22: rgyud ma h+aa yo ga la rtsa rgyud gsang ba
NK025(ra)001:23: snying po'i rjes su 'brangs te nus dbang gtso che
NK025(ra)001:24: zhing / a nu yo ga la sgrub dbang gtso che ste /
NK025(ra)001:26: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga ni //
NK025(ra)001:27: nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bos bya //
NK025(ra)001:28: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga la //
NK025(ra)001:29: sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bos bya //
NK025(ra)001:31: ma h+aa a nu gnyis dbye tshul de ltar yang /
NK025(ra)001:32: zur thams cad mkhyen pa sh+aaka 'byung sogs a nu'i
NK025(ra)001:33: khongs nas ma h+aa zhor la thon yong bar dgongs
NK025(ra)001:34: nas / lha ngo bo gcig pas tsakli nyung zhing
NK025(ra)001:35: 'jug pa bde phyir lung a nu yo ga gtso
NK025(ra)001:37: kahthoga lugs su bar 'dir sgyu 'phrul zhi khro gnyis tshul bzhin du mdzad cing /
NK025(ra)001:38: a nu la tshogs chen 'dus pa sor gnas mdzad
NK025(ra)001:39: pa kahthoga rdor bzang gi chog khrigs su snang zhing
NK025(ra)001:40: / 'di'i slob rgyun gong ra ba phyogs su khams lugs sor gnas yin par grags kyang /
NK025(ra)001:41: bla ma sog zlog pa'i gsan yig dang zin bris /
NK025(ra)001:42: gong ra lo ts+aa ba gzhan phan rdo rjes bzhengs
NK025(ra)001:43: pa'i dbang tsaka sogs zur lugs kho nar snang zhing
NK025(ra)001:44: / khams lugs dang cha tsam las mi mthun par snang bas /
NK025(ra)001:45: kahthoga lugs yin no skad pa las don la zur
NK025(ra)001:46: lugs kho na khugs btsun par rtogs nas phugs bcol
NK025(ra)001:47: bar snang / zur lugs 'dir a nu'i khongs nas ma h+aa bton pas don mi 'gal yang /
NK025(ra)001:48: mdo sgyu gnyis ka tshang bar 'dod na yo ga yan song ba'i skabs 'dir /
NK025(ra)001:49: deng sang dbang rgyun ma chad bar yod pa bzhin /
NK025(ra)001:50: sgyu 'phrul zhi ba'i dbang byang blo gsal yid 'phrog
NK025(ra)001:51: mkhas grub g.yung ston rdo rje dpal gyis mdzad pa
NK025(ra)001:52: dang / khro bo'i dbang chog sgrol chen sangs rgyas
NK025(ra)001:53: rin chen gyis mdzad pa gnyis blangs te sgyu 'phrul
NK025(ra)001:54: zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor du tshul bzhin bzhengs te sgrub
NK025(ra)001:55: mchod dbang bskur sogs mdzad na 'thad par sems shing
NK025(ra)001:56: dang / / bla ma gong ma rnams tshogs chen
NK025(ra)001:57: gyi dus su dong sprug gi dkyil 'khor lha la
NK025(ra)001:59: 'gyod tshangs rgyal pa'i dkyil 'khor lnga zhes dbang don rgyas pa'i lugs /
NK025(ra)001:63: khro bo rkyang pa'i dkyil 'khor te lnga zur bka'i
NK025(ra)001:64: dkyil 'khor du mdzad srol 'dug pa de bzhin du
NK025(ra)001:67: zur nas sgyu 'phrul sbyor bar ma gsungs pas /
NK025(ra)001:68: rin chen phreng ba kho na ltar bya ba la /
NK025(ra)001:70: 'dir nub lnga pa nas bcu gcig gi bar gsang
NK025(ra)001:71: sngags bla na med pa theg pa rtsa ba'i dkyil
NK025(ra)001:72: 'khor bstan pa ni don bzhi ste /
NK025(ra)001:77: dang po la phyi nang gi bshags pa bya ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:79: dang po'i phyi'i bshags pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:80: dpang skong sngar byas pas ma byas kyang 'gal ba med /
NK025(ra)001:81: nang gi bshags pa dang na rag cho ga ci tsam 'grub pa bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:82: zhes gsungs pa'i don nub bzhi pa yan la yo
NK025(ra)001:83: ga phan rdzogs pa'i dbang du mdzad pa yin kyang
NK025(ra)001:91: yo ga ste zhag brgyad ni nges par dgos shing /
NK025(ra)001:92: de'i steng du spro na sngon 'gro'i cho ga rnams la zhag gcig dang /
NK025(ra)001:93: u pa ya'i sta gon zhag gis bar du chod
NK025(ra)001:94: par byed na zhag bcu tsam yang dgos par sems
NK025(ra)001:95: / lnga pa nas bcu gcig bar zhes tshogs chen yan la zhag bdun byed rtsis su mdzad pa /
NK025(ra)001:96: glan ston gyi chog khrigs su bzhi nas dgu'i bar
NK025(ra)001:97: zhes sa chog sta gon so sor phral ba'i lugs
NK025(ra)001:98: su bzhed / 'on kyang dngos gzhi sgrub pa'i long skabs che chung dang /
NK025(ra)001:99: slob ma'i grangs mang nyung sogs la ltos dgos pas
NK025(ra)001:100: zhag grangs dmigs bsal bzhin par bkab mi dgos la
NK025(ra)001:101: / de la'ang bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhis bstan pa'i dang po la gzhi'i bsnyen pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:102: kha gso ba'i bsnyen pa'i bya tshul chog khrigs 'di'i thog ma nyid du bshad zin /
NK025(ra)001:103: 'dir sta gon phan chad bsnyen pa /
NK025(ra)001:104: zhag ji tsam byed pa'i phyed nye bsnyen /
NK025(ra)001:106: dbang dang dngos grub len pa sgrub pa chen por byed pa 'di'i lugs su gda' bas /
NK025(ra)001:107: de'i dang po phyi nang gi bshags pa gnyis las /
NK025(ra)001:108: phyi'i bshags pa dpang skong sogs dang /
NK025(ra)001:109: nang gi bshags pa na rag dong sprug yin la /
NK025(ra)001:111: dang po gong du yan lag gi skabs su rgyas par byas pas chog /
NK025(ra)001:112: 'dir na rag brgya tshar tsam dang srid pa'i spyi mdos zur tsam byas kyang mi 'gal lo //
NK025(ra)001:114: gnyis pa dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga ni /
NK025(ra)001:116: gnyis pa dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga la don lnga ste /
NK025(ra)001:122: zhes gsungs pa'i don lnga'i dang po dkyil 'khor gyi sa gzhi byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:123: srung ba gnyis tshogs chen gyi skabs su rgyas par bshad par dam bcas pa yin te /
NK025(ra)001:124: thams ca da kyi sngon du sa chog bgyi ba
NK025(ra)001:125: la don brgyad du bshad pa'i dang po spyir brtag
NK025(ra)001:126: pa / gnyis pa bye brag tu brtag pa /
NK025(ra)001:128: bzhi pa dbang du bya ba /
NK025(ra)001:130: drug pa sa byin gyis brlab pa /
NK025(ra)001:132: brgyad pa sa bzung ba rnams las gzhan rnams rgyas par grub cing /
NK025(ra)001:133: drug pa dang bdun pa gnyis 'dir 'chad par khas blangs pa'i phyir /
NK025(ra)001:134: de la yo byad bsham tshul ni /
NK025(ra)001:137: stegs bu byi dor legs par byas la ba byung lnga byug /
NK025(ra)001:138: de nas yan lag rab gnas ni /
NK025(ra)001:139: stegs bu'i gra zhig tu man+dala pad+ma 'dab brgyad mdzes
NK025(ra)001:140: tshon du byas pa'i mtha' rdo rje'i ra bas bskor
NK025(ra)001:141: ba / de'i dbus su rin po che'i bum pa
NK025(ra)001:142: sna tshogs rdo rjes mtshan pa'i nang du chu gtsang
NK025(ra)001:143: ma snying po nyi shu rtsa lnga tshang bar blug
NK025(ra)001:144: ba / / kha rgyan mgul chings gzungs thag bya /
NK025(ra)001:145: shar du dam tshig gi thig skud dang gtor ma /
NK025(ra)001:149: pho brang gi dbus su rin po che'i snod du tshon lnga /
NK025(ra)001:151: dam rdzas bdud rtsi rnam pa gsum bzhag /
NK025(ra)001:152: rdo rje slob dpon gyi mdun du rigs kyi bum pa so so'i thugs phyag mtshan bri /
NK025(ra)001:153: phyi nang gi mchod pa lnga tshang bar bsham /
NK025(ra)001:155: gang du tshogs chen gyi dkyil 'khor chen po bri
NK025(ra)001:156: gzhi rgya che bar byas pa'i sar byi dor legs
NK025(ra)001:157: par byas / thog mar bshad pa ltar ba byung lnga byug /
NK025(ra)001:158: gzhung gzhan las thig tshon byin brlab lha sta gon gyi rjes su bshad kyang /
NK025(ra)001:159: 'dir yan lag rab gnas zhes skabs 'dir mdzad pas /
NK025(ra)001:160: sa gzhi'i dbus su rin po che'i snod lngar rdul tshon lnga blug ste /
NK025(ra)001:161: dbus su sngon po la h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:164: nub tu dmar po la +aamh byang du ljang gu
NK025(ra)001:165: la h+aam rnams slob dpon gyis rdo rje'i rtses bris
NK025(ra)001:166: pa dang / yang snod gcig tu ye shes lnga'i srad bu lnga yang bzhag /
NK025(ra)001:167: ka p+aa la gsum du dri chen /
NK025(ra)001:169: rak+ta gsum dngos sam yang na chang la bdud rtsi chos sman btab pa gsum tshar bkod /
NK025(ra)001:170: de'i shar du rin po che'i snod du dam tshig gi srad bu dkar dmar mthing gsum dang /
NK025(ra)001:171: lcog tse'i khar zhi ba'i gtor ma dpal bshos pad 'dab bzhi pa dkar po dang /
NK025(ra)001:172: khro bo'i gtor ma de dang 'dra ba 'bri smug gis byugs pa /
NK025(ra)001:174: phyi mchod mchod yon sngon du 'gro ba'i nyer spyod lnga /
NK025(ra)001:175: nang mchod sman raka sogs kyang bsham /
NK025(ra)001:176: lhor rdo rje dril bu rab rtse dgu pa'am rtse lngas kyang rung bas stegs la bkod /
NK025(ra)001:177: nub tu rdul tshon nam ras bris kyi pad+ma 'dab
NK025(ra)001:178: brgyad mdzes tshon gyi mu khyud rdo rje'i ra bas
NK025(ra)001:179: bskor ba'i steng rin po che'i bum pa chu gtsang
NK025(ra)001:180: la bum rdzas nyer lnga btab pa /
NK025(ra)001:181: mgul chings ljang gu rdo rje rgya gram gyi mtshan
NK025(ra)001:182: ma can gzungs rdor dang bcas pa la spro na
NK025(ra)001:183: sgos mchod nyer spyod lnga yang bsham /
NK025(ra)001:184: byang du ban+d+ha lcang lo can du bdud rtsi rlon sbyor ram /
NK025(ra)001:186: bdud rtsi ril bus bkang ba bsham /
NK025(ra)001:188: de nas slob dpon chas gos dkar po gyon la /
NK025(ra)001:191: glan ston gyis de nas slob dpon chas gos dkar por zhugs la phyag zhi thung lugs su btsal /
NK025(ra)001:193: ye nas mnyam nyid kyis bshags /
NK025(ra)001:194: kun tu bzang pos dam bca' /
NK025(ra)001:195: dus gsum sangs rgyas kyis byin dbab /
NK025(ra)001:196: mchod pa rnams rim par byin gyis brlab /
NK025(ra)001:197: zhi thung lugs su bstod pa yan chad bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:198: khro bo yang thung ngur gzhung bsrang /
NK025(ra)001:199: zhes gsungs pas thog mar zhi bshags bya ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:200: mdun gyi nam mkhar rigs lnga yab yum sems dpa'
NK025(ra)001:201: lcam dral thub drug sgo ba dang bcas pa badz+ra
NK025(ra)001:202: sa m+aa dzah zhes rdo rje bsdu ba'i phyag rgya
NK025(ra)001:203: spyan drangs te mngon sum lta bur bzhugs par dmigs
NK025(ra)001:204: la / kun bzang yab yum gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:205: yid dang chos ni ye nas mngon sangs rgyas //
NK025(ra)001:206: kun bzang yab yum dgongs spyod de 'dra yang //
NK025(ra)001:207: de ltar bdag gis ma rig ma rtogs te //
NK025(ra)001:208: kun bzang yab yum thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK025(ra)001:209: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK025(ra)001:210: rgyal ba rigs lnga gsan cing phung po lnga ni
NK025(ra)001:211: ye nas rgyal ba rigs lnga'i de ltar bdag gis
NK025(ra)001:212: rgyal ba'i rigs lnga'i thugs rje che mnga' rigs kyi
NK025(ra)001:213: yum lnga 'byung ba lnga ni rigs kyi yum lnga'i
NK025(ra)001:214: de ltar bdag gis rigs kyi yum lnga'i thugs rje
NK025(ra)001:215: che mnga' sems dpa' brgyad rnams rnam shes dbang po
NK025(ra)001:216: sems dpa' brgyad kyi de ltar bdag gis sems dpa'
NK025(ra)001:217: brgyad kyi thugs rje che mnga' sems ma brgyad rnams
NK025(ra)001:218: yul dang dus ni sems ma brgyad kyi de ltar
NK025(ra)001:219: bdag gis sems ma brgyad kyi thugs rje chen mnga'
NK025(ra)001:220: thub pa drug rnams nyon mongs drug ni thub pa
NK025(ra)001:221: drug gi de ltar bdag gis thub pa drug gi
NK025(ra)001:222: thugs rje che mnga' sgo ba bzhi rnams lus kyi
NK025(ra)001:223: rtog pa sgo ba bzhi yi de ltar bdag gis
NK025(ra)001:224: sgo ba bzhi yi thugs rje che mnga' sgo ma
NK025(ra)001:225: bzhi rnams rtag chad mu bzhi sgo ma bzhi yi
NK025(ra)001:226: de ltar bdag gis sgo ma bzhi yi thugs rje
NK025(ra)001:227: che mnga' bshags yul rnams rang la bstim mo //
NK025(ra)001:230: h+aum h+aum badz+ra d+h+rika ces pa tsam las med kyang /
NK025(ra)001:231: zhe sdang rdo rje bskyed tshul ni /
NK025(ra)001:232: zhes brjod pas rang nyid zhe sdang rdo rje badz+ra he ru ka sku mdog mthing nag /
NK025(ra)001:233: mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi dang
NK025(ra)001:234: po gnyis kyis rdo rje rtse dgu dang dril bu
NK025(ra)001:235: / bar pa gnyis kyis rtse lnga dang b+hany+dza /
NK025(ra)001:236: tha ma gnyis kyi zhing dbyug dang 'jig rten 'degs
NK025(ra)001:237: pa'i tshul can zhabs bzhi g.yon brkyang gis r+au tra
NK025(ra)001:239: yum khro mo dbang phyug ma sngon mo dril bu dang thod khrag 'dzin pas 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:240: yab yum gnyis ka dur khrod kyi chas kyis brgyan
NK025(ra)001:241: cing ye shes kyi me 'bar ba'i dbus su bzhugs
NK025(ra)001:242: pa'i thugs ka nas khro bo bcu steng 'og phyogs
NK025(ra)001:243: mtshams su spros te bgegs rnams bskrad cing bsrung bar
NK025(ra)001:245: de nas bgegs gtor btang bgegs bskrad gu gul gyi
NK025(ra)001:246: dud pas bdug cing zhes gsungs pa 'dir blangs te
NK025(ra)001:247: / bgegs gtor ram yam kham gis bsreg gtor bkrus /
NK025(ra)001:249: nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags rgya lan gsum gyi bgegs la bsngosa mthar /
NK025(ra)001:250: so lugs kyi phyag bzhes se lugs kyi dgongs pa ltar /
NK025(ra)001:253: gsang ba'i dam can so so nas //
NK025(ra)001:254: 'du ba'i lha ni ma gtogs pa //
NK025(ra)001:255: thams cad thugs rjes bskang zin gyis //
NK025(ra)001:256: da lta nyid du so sor dengs //
NK025(ra)001:258: rdo rje 'dzin rgyal khros nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:259: de ma thag tu bkas nas ni //
NK025(ra)001:260: bdun brgyud rigs kyang brlag par bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:261: h+aum h+aum h+aum zhes gu gul gyis bdug /
NK025(ra)001:265: badz+ra kro ta sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum a a h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:267: badz+ra kro ta h+aum k+aa ra h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:269: badz+ra kro ta bi dz+aa ya h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:270: ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:271: badz+ra kro ta n+ai la dan+da la h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:272: da ha da ha h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:273: badz+ra kro ta ya m+aan+ta ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:274: pa tsa pa tsa h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:275: badz+ra kro ta ar+ya a tsa la h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:277: badz+ra kro ta ha ya g+r+ai wa h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:278: hu lu hu lu h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:279: badz+ra kro ta a pa ra dz+ai ta h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:281: badz+ra kro ta a mri ta kun+da li h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:283: badz+ra kro ta tree lo kya bi dz+aa ya h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:285: badz+ra krod+d+ha ma h+aa ba la h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:286: s+pho ta s+pho ta h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:287: ces rol mo'i sgra dang bcas pas mtshams bcad do //
NK025(ra)001:289: slar yang badz+ra sa m+aa dza /
NK025(ra)001:290: zhes bshags yul spyan drangs te /
NK025(ra)001:293: ye nas mnyam nyid chos skur dag pa la //
NK025(ra)001:294: ma rig dbang gis sgro dang skur btab ste //
NK025(ra)001:295: bde dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs ngo bor smin //
NK025(ra)001:296: de zlog don du rgyal ba'i dam nos te //
NK025(ra)001:297: bdag cag ma rig lus dang ngag sems kyis //
NK025(ra)001:298: bag med tshul gyi dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK025(ra)001:299: rgyal ba 'khor bcas thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK025(ra)001:300: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK025(ra)001:303: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:304: byang chub mchog tu bdag gis sems bskyed de //
NK025(ra)001:305: don dam dang ni kun rdzob byang chub sems //
NK025(ra)001:306: deng nas tshul bzhin yongs su bzung bar bgyi //
NK025(ra)001:309: dus gsum sangs rgyas 'khor dang bcas //
NK025(ra)001:310: rang bzhin gnas nas sku bskyod de //
NK025(ra)001:311: mkhyen pa'i gnas mchog 'dir gshegs nas //
NK025(ra)001:312: brtse bas byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK025(ra)001:313: zhes pas bshags yul rnams bstim mo //
NK025(ra)001:315: zhes pas bshags pa dam bca' byin dbab byas la /
NK025(ra)001:316: yang dag zhi khro thung ba'i bstod pa yan chad bya /
NK025(ra)001:317: de nas bgegs gtor btang bgegs bskrad gu gul gyi dud pas bdug cing /
NK025(ra)001:318: zhes gsungs bar bgegs gtor btang ba gong du song /
NK025(ra)001:319: glan ston gyis mchod pa rnams rim par byin gyis brlab /
NK025(ra)001:320: zhes gsungs pa bdud rtsi dang gtor ma /
NK025(ra)001:322: nyer spyod rnams byin gyis brlab /
NK025(ra)001:324: gzhong pa rnam dag chos kyi dbyings //
NK025(ra)001:325: zhes sogs kyis sman gtor rak+ta dkyil 'khor du 'god pa'i tshig dang /
NK025(ra)001:326: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:327: sa ma ya tish+tha lhan gyi bar sgo 'byed phyag
NK025(ra)001:328: rdor gyi sa chog gi sngon du zhi thung gi
NK025(ra)001:329: skabs kyi mchod pa byin brlab ltar bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:332: mi dmigs chos nyid de bzhin nyid //
NK025(ra)001:333: ces ting 'dzin rnam gsum nas bzung rtsa rgyud las
NK025(ra)001:334: byung ba'i glu ye shes kyi mchod pa dang bstod
NK025(ra)001:335: pa'i bar gong du zhi thung gi cho ga khrigs
NK025(ra)001:336: su byas pa ltar bya zhing /
NK025(ra)001:337: rtsa bar bstod pa yan las ma bshad kyang /
NK025(ra)001:340: nyams chags bskang ba'i yig brgya'i bar dkyus bzhin bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:342: yang dag gi zhi khro thung ba'i bstod pa yan
NK025(ra)001:343: chad bya zhes gsungs pa'i khro thung gi rtsa ba
NK025(ra)001:344: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i rgya gzhung dri ma med pa
NK025(ra)001:345: yin cing / 'dir zhi thung gi las byang zin
NK025(ra)001:346: ma thag zhi ba rnams khro bor gnas bsgyur dgos
NK025(ra)001:347: yin cing / pas / mkhas grub se ston chen
NK025(ra)001:348: po rin cen rgyal mtshan gyis mdzad pa'i dong sprug
NK025(ra)001:349: rnams nges nyi ma'i 'od zer rab tu snang bar
NK025(ra)001:350: yin cing / pas / / zhi khro rab 'byams /
NK025(ra)001:352: zhi khro rigs bsdus gsum du bshad pa'i 'dir gnas 'gyur skabs yin la /
NK025(ra)001:354: gnas 'gyur ni slob dpon pad+ma'i gdams ngag gnubs sangs
NK025(ra)001:355: rgyas ye shes rin po ches phung po ri bo
NK025(ra)001:357: rgya zhang khrom gyis gter nas bton /
NK025(ra)001:359: khro thung gi rtsa ba la o rgyan rin po
NK025(ra)001:360: che'i man ngag ltar mngon rtogs sbyar te gong ma'i
NK025(ra)001:361: gsungs rgyun bzhin bri bar bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:363: spros pa med pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK025(ra)001:364: rang bzhin kun snang ye shes 'od //
NK025(ra)001:365: h+aum las rgyu yi ting nge 'dzin //
NK025(ra)001:366: de las dbang chen gzhal yas khang //
NK025(ra)001:377: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i nam mkha' la //
NK025(ra)001:378: 'thor byed rlung nag tshogs kyii rgya gram gtams //
NK025(ra)001:379: chags pa rak+ta'i tshogs kyi rba klong 'khyil //
NK025(ra)001:380: zhing chen gtams pa'i sa gzhi mtha' dbus gdal //
NK025(ra)001:381: keng rus chen pos brtsigs pa'i ri rab 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:382: ye shes 'bar ba'i me 'od kun tu 'phro //
NK025(ra)001:383: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he b+han+d+ha tsakra man+da la b+h+r+aum /
NK025(ra)001:384: zla gam smug nag dur khrod gzhal yas khang //
NK025(ra)001:385: dregs pa lha chen khyab 'jug dang //
NK025(ra)001:386: khyu mchog ma he gzig dang stag /
NK025(ra)001:387: gtum pa dom dang nyi zlar bcas //
NK025(ra)001:388: de steng rgyu yi yi ge las //
NK025(ra)001:389: thugs kyi phyag rgya rab tu 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:390: de las khrag 'thung he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:391: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:392: man ngag nas mngon rtogs kha bskang bas 'di man
NK025(ra)001:393: chod kyi tshig rnams slob dpon pad+ma'i man ngag tu
NK025(ra)001:394: shes par bya'o // dbus su bdag nyid bcom ldan
NK025(ra)001:395: 'das dpal chen po zhal gsum phyag drug pa g.yas
NK025(ra)001:396: dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing nag /
NK025(ra)001:397: spyan nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor du 'bar zhing /
NK025(ra)001:398: shangs nas h+aum 'byin cing zhal nas phata sgrog pa /
NK025(ra)001:399: phyag g.yas dang po rdo rje rtse dgu /
NK025(ra)001:400: bar pa na kha t+w+aam ga /
NK025(ra)001:402: g.yon dang po na dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:404: tha ma na rgyu zhags bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:405: bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na dur khrod kyi rgyan dang ldan zhing /
NK025(ra)001:406: badz+ra kro d+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:408: yum kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma rdo rje dung dmar
NK025(ra)001:409: 'dzin pa khro mo'i rgyan dang ldan pa sku la
NK025(ra)001:410: 'khril bar gyur / yum gyis mkha' pad+ma'i ge sar
NK025(ra)001:411: gyes pa 'dab ma brgyad pa'i dbus na am dmar
NK025(ra)001:412: 'khril bar gyur / po dang / yab kyi gsang
NK025(ra)001:413: pa rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i rtse mor dkar po
NK025(ra)001:414: 'khril bar gyur / po dang / gsal bar gyur
NK025(ra)001:415: / yab kyis sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya
NK025(ra)001:416: 'khril bar gyur / po dang / gsal bar gyur / s+t+wam / yum gyis r+aa ga ya mi /
NK025(ra)001:417: ra ho hamh snyoms par zhugs te dzahh+aum bam hoh
NK025(ra)001:418: byang chub kyi sems spros bo d+hi tsit+ta s+pha ra
NK025(ra)001:419: na phata / ye shes dam tshig chen po yi //
NK025(ra)001:420: pad+mo rdo rje ldan byas nas //
NK025(ra)001:421: gnyis su med pa'i brdas mtshon te //
NK025(ra)001:422: byang chub sems sprin spros pa las //
NK025(ra)001:424: ha ha ha ha ha ha ha ha /
NK025(ra)001:425: he he he he he he he he /
NK025(ra)001:427: sa bon de rnams mkha' gsang nas phyir 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:428: so so'i gdan gyi steng du rtsa sngags kyi sgras byung nas khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gsal bar bsgom /
NK025(ra)001:429: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:430: shar du bud+d+ha he ru ka sku mdog smug nag
NK025(ra)001:431: zhal gsum phyag drug pa g.yas ser g.yon dmar dbus
NK025(ra)001:432: smug nag / phyag g.yas gsum na 'khor lo dgra s+t+wa zhags pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:433: g.yon gsum na b+han+d+ha kha t+w+aam rnge'u chung bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:434: bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma dang gnyis su med par 'khril zhing /
NK025(ra)001:435: zhabs dri za pho mo'i gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:436: rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro d+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:437: lhor rat+na he ru ka sku mdog ser nag zhal
NK025(ra)001:438: gsum phyag drug zhal g.yas sngo g.yon dmar dbus ser
NK025(ra)001:439: nag / phyag g.yas gsum na rin chen thong gshol ral gri /
NK025(ra)001:440: g.yon gsum na b+han+d+ha dgra s+t+wa gtun shing can /
NK025(ra)001:441: rat+na kro d+hi shwa r+ai dang gnyis su med par 'khril zhing /
NK025(ra)001:442: zhabs gshin rje pho mo'i gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:443: pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro d+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:444: nub tu pad+ma he ru ka sku mdog dmar nag
NK025(ra)001:445: zhal gsum phyag drug pa g.yas dkar g.yon sngo dbus
NK025(ra)001:446: dmar nag / g.yas pa gsum na pad+ma rnge'u chung spu gri /
NK025(ra)001:447: g.yon pa gsum na b+han+d+ha rnge'u chung kha t+w+aam can /
NK025(ra)001:448: pad+ma kro d+hi shwa r+ai dang gnyis su med par 'khril zhing /
NK025(ra)001:449: zhabs gnyis klu pho mo'igadana la bzhugs pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:450: karma sh+r+ai he ru ka karma kro d+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:451: byang du karma he ru ka sku mdog ljang nag
NK025(ra)001:452: zhal gsum phyag drug pa g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus
NK025(ra)001:453: ljang nag / g.yas gsum na rgya gram zhags pa rnge'u chung /
NK025(ra)001:454: g.yon gsum na b+han+d+ha thod dbyug rnge'u chung can /
NK025(ra)001:455: karma kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma dang gnyis su med par 'khril zhing /
NK025(ra)001:456: zhabs gnyis gnod sbyin pho mo'i gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:458: nang gi khyams dang po'i shar du goo r+ai ma
NK025(ra)001:459: sku mdog sngon mo zhing dbyug dang b+han+d+ha rak+tasa bkang
NK025(ra)001:460: ba can / badz+ra tsoo r+ai ha /
NK025(ra)001:461: lhor tsoo r+ai ma sku mdog ser mo mda' gzhu 'geng ba /
NK025(ra)001:463: nub tu pra mo ha sku mdog dmar mo chu
NK025(ra)001:464: srin gyi rgyal mtshan dang b+han+d+ha rak+tasa bkang ba can
NK025(ra)001:466: byang du bet+ta l+ai sku mdog nag mo rdo rje rgya gram dang zhing gi dbyug pa can /
NK025(ra)001:468: shar lhor puk+ka s+ai dmar ser g.yon gyis zhing bzung nas g.yas kyis rgyu ma bzung ba'o //
NK025(ra)001:470: lho nub tu g+hasma r+ai ljang gu g.yas rdo rjes g.yon gyi b+han+d+ha dkrug pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:472: nub byang du sme sha n+ai mthing nag phyag g.yas
NK025(ra)001:473: g.yon gnyis kyis zhing bzung nas tshems kyis khong 'dral
NK025(ra)001:476: byang shar du tsan+da l+ai ser skya g.yon gyis zhing bzung nas g.yas kyis mgo bo gcod pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:477: khro mo de rnams kyang zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan gsum pa ral pa las me 'bar ba /
NK025(ra)001:478: dur khrod kyi rgyan dang ldan zhing zhabs gnyis nyi ma'i gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:479: phra men brgyad man chad kyi mngon rtogs gu ru
NK025(ra)001:480: pad+ma'i man ngag tu mi gsal ba khro bo dam
NK025(ra)001:481: pa rgyan las btus pa 'di ltar /
NK025(ra)001:482: nang khyams phyi ma'i phyogs mtshams rnams su rim pa bzhin /
NK025(ra)001:484: sid+ha kha ro bsnol ser seng //
NK025(ra)001:485: badz+ra bya g+h+ri mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:486: b+y+aa g+h+ri mnan stag bsnol mar stag /
NK025(ra)001:487: badz+ra sring+ga la mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:488: sri la nag mo byis ldag wa //
NK025(ra)001:489: badz+ra shwa na mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:490: shwa na 'dral lta mthing kha spyang //
NK025(ra)001:491: badz+ra gri d+ha mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:492: gri d+ha mgrin dmar rgyu 'dren rgod //
NK025(ra)001:494: kang+ka zhing phrag bsnar mgo ring //
NK025(ra)001:495: badz+ra k+aa ka mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:496: k+aa ka kha ro b+han gri nag /
NK025(ra)001:497: badz+ra u lu mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:498: u lu rdo rgyu mthing tshogs 'ug /
NK025(ra)001:499: badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dzah shar sgor rta gdong dkar mo lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK025(ra)001:501: lho sgor phag gdong nag mo mche zhags bsdom //
NK025(ra)001:503: nub sgor lcags sgrog dmar mo nyi zlas mtshan //
NK025(ra)001:504: badz+ra b+hasmi pa la ya ba to hoh byang sgor thal byed dril bu sna tshogs mdog /
NK025(ra)001:505: lcags ri la dbang phyug ma ni /
NK025(ra)001:506: shar du b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:507: srin mo smug nag thod rlon 'chang //
NK025(ra)001:509: lha chen dkar ljang tri sh+au la //
NK025(ra)001:511: gzhon nu dmar mo mdung thung 'phen //
NK025(ra)001:512: dbang mo dkar mo in+d+ra ka /
NK025(ra)001:513: lhor b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:515: bdud rtsi dmar mo pad+ma bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:516: zla ba dkar mo pun+da ri //
NK025(ra)001:517: be con ljang nag dbyug to 'phyar //
NK025(ra)001:518: srin mo dmar mo dung khrag 'thung //
NK025(ra)001:519: za ba ljang nag ba su 'dren //
NK025(ra)001:520: nub tu b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:521: dga' ba dmar mo ka tar 'phyar //
NK025(ra)001:522: stobs chen dkar mo gshol mda' 'dzin //
NK025(ra)001:523: rdo rje ser nag spu gris gcod //
NK025(ra)001:525: nor srung dkar mo bum pa 'dzin //
NK025(ra)001:526: rlung lha sngon mo ba dan 'phyar //
NK025(ra)001:527: byang du b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:528: gsod byed nag mo ral gri'i so //
NK025(ra)001:529: me mo dmar mo gsal shing 'phyar //
NK025(ra)001:530: phag mo nag mo mche zhags can //
NK025(ra)001:531: rgan byed dmar mo zhing chung za //
NK025(ra)001:532: sna chen dkar mo thod khrag 'thung //
NK025(ra)001:533: chu lha sngon mo sprul zhags 'dzin //
NK025(ra)001:534: khro thung rtsa bar sgo ma chad pas dbang mo
NK025(ra)001:535: nyer brgyad ma tshang ba 'dir kha bkang ba ni
NK025(ra)001:537: khu byug nag mo lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK025(ra)001:538: ra gdong sngon mo rgyu zhags 'dren //
NK025(ra)001:539: seng gdong dmar mo lcags sgrog 'dzin //
NK025(ra)001:540: skya ka ljang nag dril bu 'khrol //
NK025(ra)001:541: de ltar lha bskyed nas ye shes lnga'i dbang bskur ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:542: sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlab pa sogs zhi ba'i
NK025(ra)001:543: skabs su rgyas par song bas 'dir byin rlabs dran
NK025(ra)001:544: pa tsam gyis 'thus par dgongs te khro thung gi
NK025(ra)001:545: rtsa ba ltar / ahh+aum zhes sku gsung thugs dang /
NK025(ra)001:547: zhes rigs lngas dbang bskur ro //
NK025(ra)001:548: gu ru pad+ma'i man ngag las /
NK025(ra)001:549: bdag gi thugs ka nas yig 'bru las 'od zer 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:550: de las phyag rgya bzhi spro zhing /
NK025(ra)001:551: chos kyi sku las sprul pa'i skur /
NK025(ra)001:553: mdun gyi nam mkha' la me dpung 'dab 'dres tsam
NK025(ra)001:554: du bzhugs pa la snying pos bskul zhing phyag rgya
NK025(ra)001:555: bzhis spyan drangs / mi dmigs mkha' ltar dag pas khyab pa'i sku //
NK025(ra)001:556: spyan drangs gshegs su gsol bar mi dmigs kyang //
NK025(ra)001:557: thugs rje'i ngang nyid chos sku dag pa las //
NK025(ra)001:558: ye shes sgyu mar rol cing gshegs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:559: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:560: e h+ye hi +aa na ya hoh dzahh+aum bam hoh
NK025(ra)001:561: gzhal yas khang du byon nas lha rnams bdag nyid
NK025(ra)001:562: la thim pas chu dang 'o ma 'dres pa bzhin
NK025(ra)001:563: du gyur te / nam dngos grub ma thob kyi bar du brtan par bzhugs su gsol lo //
NK025(ra)001:565: sems can don phyir nan tan mchog bskyed cing //
NK025(ra)001:566: ye shes thugs rjes bdag la dgongs nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:567: mi gnyis don phyir dngos grub mchog gi rnams //
NK025(ra)001:568: bdag la stsal zhing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:570: ye shes sprul pa'i sku mngon du shar ba la
NK025(ra)001:571: gnyis su med pa'i rtogs pa'i sgo nas phyag btsal
NK025(ra)001:572: ba ni / bdag med phyogs bral don dam thugs chud cing //
NK025(ra)001:573: byams dang snying rje'i dgra zun mi mnga' yang //
NK025(ra)001:574: gdug pa 'dul phyir dus las mi 'da' ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:575: 'jigs byed khro bo tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:576: a ti pu hoh pra t+aits+tsha hoh mchod pa bya ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:577: bdag gi thugs ka nas lha mo ar+g+ha thogs pa mang po byung ste /
NK025(ra)001:578: bdag la khrus byed cing rang la thim mo //
NK025(ra)001:579: de bzhin du bdug spos ma shangs la thim /
NK025(ra)001:580: me tog mas gtor te dbu la thim /
NK025(ra)001:581: mar me ma spyan la thim /
NK025(ra)001:582: dri chab ma thugs la thim /
NK025(ra)001:583: lha bshos ma ljags la thim /
NK025(ra)001:584: sgra dbyangs ma snyan la thim /
NK025(ra)001:586: khrag 'thung rgyal po gar la dgyees //
NK025(ra)001:587: sku mdog zhal ni rnam par bsgyur //
NK025(ra)001:588: sku yi gar stabs glog 'gyu ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:589: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa bzhes //
NK025(ra)001:590: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:597: ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha hoh bdud rtsi'i mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:598: don skye 'chi med pa'i ngang du rtags lha rnams gnas pa'i phyir /
NK025(ra)001:599: ye shes kyi 'od zer sna lngas khyab par dmigs te mchod do //
NK025(ra)001:600: rang byung gdod nas rnam par dag /
NK025(ra)001:601: rtsa brgyad stong las sbyar ba'i sman //
NK025(ra)001:602: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK025(ra)001:603: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK025(ra)001:604: rgyud drug sems can kun sgrol ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:605: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK025(ra)001:606: rigs lnga khrag 'thung yab yum dang //
NK025(ra)001:607: koo sing sgo ma dbang phyug 'khor bcas la //
NK025(ra)001:608: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:609: thugs rje che dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK025(ra)001:610: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha hoh h+aum kha ram kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:611: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:612: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:613: rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro d+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:614: pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro d+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:615: karma sh+r+ai he ru ka karma kro d+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:616: h+aum kha ram kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:617: badz+ra goo r+ai ha sa ma ya de wi tsa kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:618: badz+ra tsoo r+ai ha sa ma ya badz+ra pra mo
NK025(ra)001:619: h+ae ha sa ma ya badz+ra bet+ta l+ai ha sa
NK025(ra)001:620: ma ya badz+ra puk+ka s+ai ha sa ma ya badz+ra
NK025(ra)001:621: g+hasma r+ai ha sa ma ya badz+ra sme sha n+ai
NK025(ra)001:622: ha sa ma ya badz+ra tsan+da l+ai ha sa ma
NK025(ra)001:623: ya h+aum kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:624: badz+ra sid+ha mu kha he kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:625: badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kha he badz+ra sring+ga la mu
NK025(ra)001:626: kha he badz+ra shwa na mu kha he badz+ra gri
NK025(ra)001:627: d+ha mu kha he badz+ra kam ka mu kha he
NK025(ra)001:628: badz+ra k+aa ka mu kha he badz+ra u lu ka
NK025(ra)001:629: mu kha he / h+aum kha ram kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:630: badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dzahkha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:631: badz+ra a mo ka h+aum badz+ra lo ka bam badz+ra
NK025(ra)001:632: b+hasmi pa la ya ba to ho h+aum kha ram
NK025(ra)001:635: shar gyi smug nag ma bdun gyi zhal du kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:637: lho'i ser nag ma bdun gyi zhal du b+h+yo bdun /
NK025(ra)001:638: nub kyi dmar nag ma bdun gyi zhal du b+h+yo bdun /
NK025(ra)001:639: byang gi ljang nag ma bdun gyi zhal du mkha' 'gro ma sum cu rtsa gnyis gyi zhal du /
NK025(ra)001:640: sman mchod kyi sham bu 'di yang dag me gcig gi dgongs pa ltar yin gsung /
NK025(ra)001:641: bdag cag ma rigs lus dang ngag sems kyis //
NK025(ra)001:642: bag med tshul gyi dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK025(ra)001:643: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK025(ra)001:644: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK025(ra)001:645: sman gyi sid+d+hi blang ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:647: ye shes lnga ldan b+han+d+ha'i snod nang du //
NK025(ra)001:648: yon tan brgyad ldan bdud rtsi bkang ba 'di //
NK025(ra)001:649: bde gshegs mchod nas dngos grub blang ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:650: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsal tu gsol //
NK025(ra)001:652: w+aa ka sid+d+hi +aah tsit+ta sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:654: sman raka bdud rtsi gsum 'bul ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:656: khyad par chen po grub pa rgyal ba'i bka' //
NK025(ra)001:657: snang srid snang ba chen por shar ba'i sku //
NK025(ra)001:658: rgyu gnyis rkyen gsum sbyar ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK025(ra)001:659: dpal chen khrag 'thung tshogs la mchod par 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:660: ma h+aa ba ling+ta kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:661: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:662: ma h+aa m+aam sa kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:665: ba su ta go ro tsa na kem ni ri ti kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:670: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor rnam par dag pa na
NK025(ra)001:671: bzhugs pa'i bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po badz+ra he
NK025(ra)001:672: ru ka yab yum 'khor dang bcas pas /
NK025(ra)001:673: bdag cag rnal 'byor pa'i dgra dang bgegs dang /
NK025(ra)001:674: bdud dang srin po ni bsgral /
NK025(ra)001:676: rnal 'byor gyi sa dam pa thob par mdzad du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:679: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:681: 'dzab dgongs mngon rtogs su shes so //
NK025(ra)001:682: zhes gsungs pa gu ru pad+ma'i man ngag gi mngon rtogs las /
NK025(ra)001:683: bdag badz+ra he ru kar gsal ba'i thugs kar ma las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor bsams /
NK025(ra)001:684: de'i steng du ye shes sems dpa' smug nag tshon gang ba zhig bsam la /
NK025(ra)001:685: de'i thugs kar nyi ma'i steng du rin po che zur brgyad kyi steng du h+aum bsam /
NK025(ra)001:686: zur brgyad la ru lu 'bru brgyad kyis bskor bar bsgom mo //
NK025(ra)001:687: yum gyi thugs kar yang de bzhin du bsgom mo //
NK025(ra)001:688: bdag gi thugs ka'i yig 'bru las 'od zer spros pas /
NK025(ra)001:689: bde bar gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud bskul te /
NK025(ra)001:690: 'gro ba sems can thams cad kyi sgriib pa sbyangs nas /
NK025(ra)001:691: de nas bdag la tshur 'dus pas bdag gi lus
NK025(ra)001:692: ngag yid gsum gyi sgrib pa bya sgro mes bcum
NK025(ra)001:693: pa bzhin song nas byang zhing dag par gyur nas
NK025(ra)001:694: / snang srid thams cad khro bo'i dkyil 'khor du ma gyur pa med par bsgom mo //
NK025(ra)001:696: 'di yan chod kyi tshigs bcad dang sngags rnams khro
NK025(ra)001:697: thung gi rtsa ba kho na la lhug pa'i mngon
NK025(ra)001:698: rtogs dang dmigs pa'i 'phro 'du bya tshul rnams gu
NK025(ra)001:699: ru pad+ma'i man ngag dri ma med pa bcos bslad
NK025(ra)001:700: dang bral nges pa dang phra men brgyad dang sgo
NK025(ra)001:701: ma dbang phyug gi mngon rtogs khro bo dam pa
NK025(ra)001:702: rgya che chung gnyis yod pa'i che ba'i rgya gzhung
NK025(ra)001:703: gi tshig bcos med yin pas phyogs 'di la spyan
NK025(ra)001:704: ras yangs pa rnams dgyes pa khyad par can bskyed
NK025(ra)001:705: du gsol / khro thung rtsa bar /
NK025(ra)001:706: bstod pa ni rgyud ltar gtum chen gyis bstod /
NK025(ra)001:707: ces gsungs pas rtsa rgyud gsang ba'i snying po'i le'u nyer gcig pa las gsungs pa 'di ltar /
NK025(ra)001:709: gtum chen dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:711: khro gnyer glog stong 'gyu ba bzhin //
NK025(ra)001:712: mche ba zangs yag za byed che hoh h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:713: rngam pa'i nga ro 'brug stong ldir //
NK025(ra)001:714: gtum chen ri rab 'bum bsnyil skad //
NK025(ra)001:715: a la ha la'i gad rgyangs che //
NK025(ra)001:716: spyugs pa'i 'thor rlung g.yeng ba che hoh h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:717: khro bo'i shes rab 'od po che //
NK025(ra)001:718: ye shes dkyil 'khor kun tu gsal //
NK025(ra)001:720: sna tshogs ye shes thig le che hoh h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:721: khro bo'i rgyal po sprin chen po //
NK025(ra)001:724: sna tshogs khros pa'i thig le che hoh h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:725: bdud kun gyi ni bdag chen po //
NK025(ra)001:726: bdud kyi bdud de bdud rnams 'joms //
NK025(ra)001:728: 'jigs byed chen po thig le che hoh h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:729: rdo rje brag chen sra ba po //
NK025(ra)001:730: rdo rje chu ste bdud chen po //
NK025(ra)001:731: rdo rje me ste kun 'bar che //
NK025(ra)001:732: rdo rje rlung ste 'thor rlung che hoh zhes bstod do //
NK025(ra)001:733: de nas khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gtso bo yab yum la bsdus te /
NK025(ra)001:734: rang nyid badz+ra he ru ka yab yum gyi nga rgyal la gnas par bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:735: de nas bum pa bskyed pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:736: bum pa gu gul gyi dud pas bdug /
NK025(ra)001:737: yungs thun gyis brab ste bgegs bskrad /
NK025(ra)001:740: las thams cad pa'i bum pa ram yam kham gis sbyang /
NK025(ra)001:741: sh+au nya t+aas stong pa'i ngang las phyi dur khrod 'bar ba /
NK025(ra)001:742: nang rin po che'i gzhal yas khang /
NK025(ra)001:743: de'i nang du ma s+au r+ya man+da las nyi ma'i
NK025(ra)001:744: steng du h+aum ljang gu'i 'phro 'du las bdud rtsi
NK025(ra)001:745: 'khyil ba ljang gu g.yas rgya gram /
NK025(ra)001:746: g.yon dril bu thogs pa stag gi pags pa'i sham
NK025(ra)001:747: thabs dar dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa
NK025(ra)001:751: karma he ru kas dbu brgyan par bsam /
NK025(ra)001:752: zhes gsungs pa'i don sgyu 'phrul lugs la dbang brlab dbab drang bstim brtan /
NK025(ra)001:753: zhes go rim du mdzad pa ye shes lngas dbang
NK025(ra)001:754: bskur zhing sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab pa
NK025(ra)001:756: zhi thung skabs su bshad pa'i phyag rgya rnams bca' zhing /
NK025(ra)001:757: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:758: ma h+aa +aa dar+sha dz+ny+aa na ma h+aa sa ma
NK025(ra)001:759: t+aa dz+ny+aa na ma h+aa pra t+ya be k+sha na
NK025(ra)001:760: dz+ny+aa na ma h+aa kri t+ya a nush+tha na dz+ny+aa
NK025(ra)001:761: na sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya
NK025(ra)001:762: badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:763: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aa ka badz+ra
NK025(ra)001:764: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra rigs
NK025(ra)001:766: yang na karma he ru kas dbu brgyan pa'i dbang gis sh+au nya t+aa dang /
NK025(ra)001:767: kri t+ya a nush+tha na go barjesa kyang btub bo //
NK025(ra)001:768: ru lu ru lu h+aum zhes snyan gsan dbab /
NK025(ra)001:769: e h+ye hi +aa na ya dzahh+aum bam hohzhesa spyan drangs /
NK025(ra)001:771: a big+h+n+aan+ta krita a mri ta kun+da li ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:774: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK025(ra)001:775: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i ye shes kyi //
NK025(ra)001:776: srid pa rgya mtsho mtha' yas kun //
NK025(ra)001:777: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK025(ra)001:778: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo bi shwa mu
NK025(ra)001:779: ke b+h+yahsarba tang+kham ung+ga te s+pha ra na hi mam
NK025(ra)001:780: ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:781: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au /
NK025(ra)001:782: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga push+pe pu /
NK025(ra)001:783: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga +aa lo ke h+r+aihsh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga gan+d+he gan /
NK025(ra)001:784: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:785: ma h+aa ba ling+ta kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:787: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:789: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le che ho'i bar zhi thung du rgyud drangs pa ltar dang /
NK025(ra)001:790: hoh rgyal ba rgya mtsho dgongs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:791: mchod pa rgya mtsho bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:792: nyams chag rgya mtsho bskang du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:793: dngos grub rgya mtsho stsal du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:794: phrin las rgya mtsho sgrub tu gsol //
NK025(ra)001:796: de nas mdzub mo gnyis bum par gtugs la /
NK025(ra)001:798: brgya rtsa bzlas pas bdud rtsi 'khyil ba 'od du zhu nas bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor bsam /
NK025(ra)001:799: slob dpon bzhengs te rdor dril 'dzin pas /
NK025(ra)001:800: sarba bi shud+d+he d+harma tha badz+ra sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:801: zhes pas bum pa'i chus dkyil 'khor gyi gzhi kun
NK025(ra)001:802: la gtor bas nyes skyon thams cad chos nyid stong
NK025(ra)001:804: de nas dam rdzas bdud rtsi gsum gyis chag chag gdab ste /
NK025(ra)001:805: gong gi b+han+d+ha gsum rim par blangs te chag chag gdab cing //
NK025(ra)001:806: bdud rtsi dri chen ye shes lnga ldan pas //
NK025(ra)001:807: de bzhin gsang mchog dngos grub dam pa'i mchog /
NK025(ra)001:808: bka' gsang sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor chen po ru //
NK025(ra)001:809: dam rdzas bdud rtsi dri chen chag chag 'debs //
NK025(ra)001:810: ma h+aa ba su ta man+da la h+aum //
NK025(ra)001:811: dam rdzas dam pa'i bdud rtsi dri chu 'dis //
NK025(ra)001:812: ye shes rang byung bdud rtsi bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:813: skye med byang chub sems su rtogs pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:814: gsang ba bdud rtsi chen pos chag chag 'debs //
NK025(ra)001:815: ma h+aa sa man+ta ku kus man+da la h+aum //
NK025(ra)001:816: bka' gsang rmad du byung ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK025(ra)001:817: 'khor ba rgyud gcod byang chub sems kyi ngang //
NK025(ra)001:818: mkha' dbyings rnam dag yum gyi gzhal yas su //
NK025(ra)001:819: rak+ta gsang ba mchog gis chag chag 'debs //
NK025(ra)001:820: ma h+aa rak+ta man+da la sogs /
NK025(ra)001:822: de nas thig gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:823: dang po stong pa'i ngang las s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra rat+na pad+ma e man+da la'i gdan lnga bsam /
NK025(ra)001:824: de dag gi steng du thugs ka nas h+aum s+w+aa +aamhh+aa /
NK025(ra)001:825: dam tshig gi thig la nyi zla pad+ma +aahh+aum gsum bsam /
NK025(ra)001:826: de nas rang gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:827: badz+ra sa ma ya dzahe h+ye hi lan gsum brjod pas /
NK025(ra)001:828: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas mdun gyi nam mkhar spyan drangs la /
NK025(ra)001:829: zhes 'byung bas gsang sngags gzhan la thig tshon byin
NK025(ra)001:830: rlabs lhan du byed kyang 'dir so sor 'byung bas
NK025(ra)001:831: dang po thig byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:832: ye shes lnga'i thig skud lnga dang dam tshig gi thig skud bsang sbyang /
NK025(ra)001:833: stong pa'i ngang las s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra rat+na pad+ma e man+da la zhes pas e las nam mkha' /
NK025(ra)001:834: rin po che'i khri pad+ma nyi zla ste gdan lnga brtsegs dang /
NK025(ra)001:835: dam tshig gi thig skud la nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan sum brtsegs su bsam mo //
NK025(ra)001:836: bdag gi thugs ka nas h+aum mthing dkar s+w+aa ser +aahdamara h+aa ljang gu ste sa bon lnga 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:839: gdan sum brtsegs kyi steng du 'khod par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:840: rang nyid badz+ra he ru ka yab yum du gsal ba'i thugs ka'i h+aum yig las 'od zer 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:841: badz+ra sa ma ya dzah e h+ye hi zhes lan gsum brjod pas /
NK025(ra)001:842: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyis sangs rgyas thams cad mdun gyi nam mkhar mngon sum du byon par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:844: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK025(ra)001:845: gzugs sku 'ja' tshon bzhin du so sor gsal //
NK025(ra)001:846: thabs dang shes rab mchog la mnga' brnyes pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:847: rigs lnga bde bar gshegs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:848: dmigs med chos kyi sku la longs spyod rdzogs pa'i
NK025(ra)001:849: sku la cir yang sprul pa'i sku la khams gsum
NK025(ra)001:850: zhing du sbyor la mdzes pa'i sku mchog sems can
NK025(ra)001:851: sgrol la mkhas // ngo mtshar pho brang bde bar gshegs pa'i yum //
NK025(ra)001:852: shes rab thabs kyi gtso la mnyes mdzad ma //
NK025(ra)001:853: rigs kyi yum gyur rnams la thabs mkhas thugs rje ye shes sprul pa'i ngang //
NK025(ra)001:854: rang rgyud rnal 'byor dag pas grub pa brnyes //
NK025(ra)001:855: thugs rje chen pos 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:856: sems dpa' sems ma rnams la byams dang snying rje dga' dang btang snyoms kyis //
NK025(ra)001:857: nyon mongs log par lta ba'i dgra rnams 'joms //
NK025(ra)001:858: gshin rje gshed po la sogs khro rgyal bzhi //
NK025(ra)001:859: sgo ba yab yum rnams la chos rnams ye nas gnyis med lhun grub pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:860: rtogs par bya ba'i yul du chos bzang mo //
NK025(ra)001:861: de nyid don rig byed pa rdo rje yid //
NK025(ra)001:862: gnyis med dkyil 'khor gtso la rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK025(ra)001:863: rtog pa rgyud drug so sor 'khor ba la //
NK025(ra)001:864: thabs mkha' thugs rjes ci 'dul der ston pa //
NK025(ra)001:865: thub pa chen po drug la a ti pu hoh pra t+aits+tsha hoh phyag btsal te /
NK025(ra)001:866: rtsa bar 'di las ma gsungs kyang /
NK025(ra)001:868: phyag nas phyogs bcu dus bzhi yan chad kyis bstod cing /
NK025(ra)001:869: zhes gsungs pas sgyu 'phrul zhi ba ltar /
NK025(ra)001:870: phyag gi rjes su mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:871: las bum sgrub mchod kyi skabs ltar /
NK025(ra)001:872: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK025(ra)001:873: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i srid pa rgya mtsho kun bzang
NK025(ra)001:874: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo yang dag don
NK025(ra)001:876: 'gro ba yongs kyi don slad du //
NK025(ra)001:877: phyag dang zhabs gnyis bsil nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:878: rdo rje'i gdan la bzhugs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:879: +aa ha ra +aa h+aa ra sarba bid+ya d+ha ra
NK025(ra)001:880: p+au dzi te na mahs man+ta bud+d+h+aa n+aam ga ga
NK025(ra)001:881: na kham sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:884: ti pu pa ra muh sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid d+hoo /
NK025(ra)001:885: sa ma yo ta muh sarba ma h+aa su kha sid+d+hoo /
NK025(ra)001:886: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au /
NK025(ra)001:889: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga push+pe pu /
NK025(ra)001:891: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga +aa lo ke h+r+aih pa na pem sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga gan+d+he gan /
NK025(ra)001:892: zhal zas dang rol mo sgyu 'phrul las dngos bstan
NK025(ra)001:893: ma gsungs kyang 'di ga'i rigs 'gre sbyar te spros
NK025(ra)001:895: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:896: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam tshig dam pa grub par mdzod /
NK025(ra)001:898: rab tu dga' de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam tshig dam pa dag cing grub par mdzad du gsol /
NK025(ra)001:900: rab tu de bzhin gshegs pa'i mchod pa chen po thams cad dag cing grub par mdzad du gsol /
NK025(ra)001:902: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:904: su ra ha u pa b+h+yo ka ma la m+aa
NK025(ra)001:905: badz+ra a mri te ha ra na pra t+aits+tsha b+ha
NK025(ra)001:906: ga wan dzahh+aum bam hoh a la la hoh ma
NK025(ra)001:907: h+aa ba lin+ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:909: h+aum p+aam badz+ra sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:910: sa ma ya hoh a nu r+aa ga ya mi /
NK025(ra)001:912: dzahh+aum bam hoh bo d+hi tsit+ta s+pha ra na phata /
NK025(ra)001:914: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu r+aa ga na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:915: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa p+au dza badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham //
NK025(ra)001:916: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:918: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le che ho'i bar zhi thung ltar ro //
NK025(ra)001:922: mi gnas pa'i ye shes chen po'i bdag nyid phyogs
NK025(ra)001:923: bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK025(ra)001:925: bdag rdo rje slob dpon gyis slob ma rnams kyi don du 'dus pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor /
NK025(ra)001:926: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las mi zad pa
NK025(ra)001:927: rgyan gyi 'khor lo gsang ba las kyang ches gsang
NK025(ra)001:929: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor du thig 'debs
NK025(ra)001:930: pas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis bdag la
NK025(ra)001:934: rdo rje ye shes kyi thig stsal tu gsol /
NK025(ra)001:935: badz+ra tish+tha tish+tha gu h+ya sa ma ya dz+ny+aa na am ku sha dzahdzah zhes lan gsum brjod pas /
NK025(ra)001:936: nam mkhar bzhugs pa'isangasa rgyas rnams kyi sbyor ba byang
NK025(ra)001:937: chub sems gyi chu rgyun ye shes kha dog lnga'i
NK025(ra)001:940: sku gsung thugs kyi 'od zer dkar dmar mthing gsum
NK025(ra)001:941: 'phros nas dam tshig gi thig skud gsum la thim
NK025(ra)001:942: pas sku gsung thugs su bsam mo //
NK025(ra)001:943: de nas slob dpon shar du blta /
NK025(ra)001:944: slob ma nub tu blta ba la thig sna gtad
NK025(ra)001:945: de dbyangs dang bcas pas thig skud sngon po brkyang
NK025(ra)001:946: ste / yi ge h+aum zhes bya ba ni //
NK025(ra)001:947: rdo rje rigs kyi rang bzhin te //
NK025(ra)001:948: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyis //
NK025(ra)001:949: zhe sdang dngos po sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:950: byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:951: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:952: zhes pas stong pa nyid kyi ye shes sngo breng nge byung bar bsam /
NK025(ra)001:953: de nas dkar po brkyang ste /
NK025(ra)001:954: yi ge zhes bya ba ni //
NK025(ra)001:955: de bzhin rigs kyi rang bzhin te //
NK025(ra)001:956: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyis //
NK025(ra)001:957: gti mug dngos po sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:958: byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:959: ma h+aa +aa dar+sha dz+ny+aa na me long lta bu'i ye shes dkar breng nge byung bar bsam /
NK025(ra)001:961: yi ge s+w+aa zhes bya ba ni //
NK025(ra)001:962: rin chen rigs kyi rang bzhin te //
NK025(ra)001:963: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyis //
NK025(ra)001:964: nga rgyal dngos po sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:965: byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:966: ma h+aa sa ma t+aa dz+ny+aa na mnyam pa nyid
NK025(ra)001:967: kyi ye shes ser breng nge byung dmar po brkyang
NK025(ra)001:968: ste / yi ge +aamhzhesa bya ba ni //
NK025(ra)001:969: pad+ma rigs kyi rang bzhin te //
NK025(ra)001:970: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK025(ra)001:971: 'dod chags dngos po sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:972: byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:973: ma h+aa pra t+ya bek+sha na dz+ny+aa na so sor
NK025(ra)001:974: rtog pa'i ye shes dmar breng nge ljang gu brkyang
NK025(ra)001:975: ste / yi ge h+aam zhes bya ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:976: las kyi rigs kyi rang bzhin te //
NK025(ra)001:977: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK025(ra)001:978: phrag dog dngos po sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:979: byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:980: ma h+aa kri t+ya +aa nush+tha na dz+ny+aa na zhes
NK025(ra)001:981: pas bya ba grub pa'i ye shes ljang breng nge
NK025(ra)001:983: de nas thig skud rnams gcig tu bsdoms la /
NK025(ra)001:985: 'dus pa chen po mdo yi dkyil 'khor du //
NK025(ra)001:986: gnyis med byang chub sems kyi 'phro 'du las //
NK025(ra)001:987: rdo rje ye shes thig chen 'di btab pas //
NK025(ra)001:988: pho brang dkyil 'khor yid bzhin lhun gyis grub //
NK025(ra)001:990: zhes bzlas shing thig skud bsgril nas sku gsung thugs
NK025(ra)001:991: yon tan phrin las nyi shu rtsa lnga'i ngo bor
NK025(ra)001:992: bsam mo // de nas dam tshig gi thig skud dkar po brkyang la /
NK025(ra)001:993: yi ge zhes bya ba ni //
NK025(ra)001:994: bde gshegs sku yi rang bzhin te //
NK025(ra)001:995: lus kyi dngos po sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:996: byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:997: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:1000: bde gshegs gsung gi rang bzhin te //
NK025(ra)001:1001: ngag gi dngos po sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:1002: byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:1003: sarba w+aa ka badz+ra mthing ga brkyang ste /
NK025(ra)001:1004: yi ge h+aum zhes bya ba ni //
NK025(ra)001:1005: bde gshegs thugs kyi rang bzhin te //
NK025(ra)001:1006: yid kyi dngos po sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:1007: byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:1008: tsit+ta badz+ra de nas gsum ka gcig tu bsdoms la /
NK025(ra)001:1010: mu mtha' g.yo 'gul med pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:1011: rnal 'byor mnyam nyid thod brgal du //
NK025(ra)001:1012: khro gtum rngam pa'i las mdzad pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:1013: gnas 'dir gzhal yas bri bar bya //
NK025(ra)001:1014: +aahh+aum badz+ra dz+ny+aa na ma ti kra ma h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1015: zhes brjod pas thig skud re re'ang gsum gsum ste dgu phrugs su ldan par bsam mo //
NK025(ra)001:1016: de nas thig skud lnga sgril dang gsum sgril gnyis ka gcig tu bsgril lo //
NK025(ra)001:1017: glan ston gyis kun bzang nas glu ye shes yan chod zhi thung lugs su lcogs na bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:1018: zhes gsungs kyang gong du grub pas ma byung kyang 'thus par sems /
NK025(ra)001:1019: bar 'dir ye shes kyi thig 'debs pa rigs par snang zhing /
NK025(ra)001:1020: kho bo'i bla ma sman lung pa chen po yang phyag len de ltar du mdzad pas /
NK025(ra)001:1021: ji ltar mdzad pa bzhin zin bris su btab pa 'di ltar ro //
NK025(ra)001:1022: slob dpon nub dang slob ma shar du gnas te /
NK025(ra)001:1023: g.yas pas thig skud bzung g.yon pa'i mtheb srin gyis
NK025(ra)001:1024: yas nas mas su bcus te gyen du nam mkhar
NK025(ra)001:1025: btab bo // de bzhin du slob dpon byang dang
NK025(ra)001:1026: slob ma lhor gnas pas tshangs thig gnyis pa gdab
NK025(ra)001:1027: btab bo // / logs thig la slob dpon shar
NK025(ra)001:1028: lho slob ma byang shar du gnas par slob mas
NK025(ra)001:1029: bskor te shar gyi logs thig gdab /
NK025(ra)001:1030: slob dpon nub byang slob ma lho nub tu gnas pas nub kyi logs thig gdab /
NK025(ra)001:1031: slob dpon de nyid dang slon ma byang shar du gnas pas byang gi logs thig gdab /
NK025(ra)001:1032: slob dpon shar lho dang slob ma lho nub tu gnas pas lho'i logs thig gdab /
NK025(ra)001:1033: slob dpon shar lho dang slob ma nub byang du gnas pas zur thig dang po gdab /
NK025(ra)001:1034: slob dpon lho nub dang slob ma dbang ldan du gnas pas zur thig gnyis pa gdab ste /
NK025(ra)001:1035: thig chen brgyad nam mkhar btab pa ni ye shes kyi thig go //
NK025(ra)001:1036: slob dpon shar dang slob ma nub tu gnas pas thig skud bsdu'o //
NK025(ra)001:1037: dkyus su rdor dril byin rlabs 'dug kyang /
NK025(ra)001:1038: glan ston gyi dgongs pa ltar 'dir tshon byin rlabs 'og nas len dgos pas 'di ltar /
NK025(ra)001:1040: de nas tshon byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:1041: tshon rigs mthun du bkod pa dpa' bo 'bru lnga 'god /
NK025(ra)001:1044: stong pa'i ngang las gdan lnga brtsegs su cho ga gsum gyis lhar bskyed /
NK025(ra)001:1051: kun bzang nas bstod pa'i bar du byas la /
NK025(ra)001:1053: sarba sam sho d+ha ni ye s+w+aa h+aa dang /
NK025(ra)001:1054: ram yam kham gis tshon lnga bsang sbyang /
NK025(ra)001:1055: stong pa'i ngang las s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra rat+na pad+ma e man+da la /
NK025(ra)001:1056: zhes gdan lnga brtsegs lnga'i steng du h+aum s+w+aa +aamhh+aa
NK025(ra)001:1057: lnga las rdo rje 'khor lo rin chen pad+ma rgya
NK025(ra)001:1058: gram 'bru lngas mtshan pa yongs su gyur pa las
NK025(ra)001:1059: / dbus su mi bskyod pa sngon po sa gnon mnyam bzhag rdo rje /
NK025(ra)001:1060: shar du rnam snang dkar po byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya'i rtser 'khor lo /
NK025(ra)001:1061: lhor rin 'byung ser po mchog sbyin mnyam bzhag gi steng na rin po che /
NK025(ra)001:1062: nub tu snang ba mtha' yas dmar po mnyam bzhag gi steng na pad+ma /
NK025(ra)001:1063: byang du don grub ljang gu skyabs sbyin dang mnyam
NK025(ra)001:1064: bzhag gi steng na rgya gram bsnams pa lnga ka'ang
NK025(ra)001:1065: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis mdzes par 'gyur
NK025(ra)001:1066: / 'dir rig lnga yab yum rigs par snang yang
NK025(ra)001:1067: glan ston gyis yab rkyang du bshad pa ltar ro
NK025(ra)001:1068: / // ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa sogs phyag rgya dang bcas te sngar bzhin dbang bskur /
NK025(ra)001:1069: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra
NK025(ra)001:1070: swa b+h+aa wa sogs sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlab
NK025(ra)001:1071: / badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum dzah zhes snyan gsan dbab /
NK025(ra)001:1072: e h+ye hi b+ha ga wan ma h+aa k+aa ru
NK025(ra)001:1073: ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh sa
NK025(ra)001:1074: ma ya s+t+wam / dzahh+aum bam hoh badz+ra am ku sha dzah badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1076: badz+ra g+han+de hoh zhes spyan drangs la bstim /
NK025(ra)001:1077: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+rasa brtan par byas /
NK025(ra)001:1078: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK025(ra)001:1079: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i srid pa rgya mtsho kun bzang
NK025(ra)001:1080: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo bi shwa yang
NK025(ra)001:1081: dag don du dag mod kyang //
NK025(ra)001:1082: 'gro ba phyag dang rdo rje'i +aa ha ra sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga gan+d+he gan /
NK025(ra)001:1084: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la +aahh+aum na mahsarba ta
NK025(ra)001:1085: th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha
NK025(ra)001:1086: ram kh+aa hi / ma h+aa ba lin+ta kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:1088: h+aum p+aam badz+ra sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu r+aa ga ma h+aa p+au dza badz+ra /
NK025(ra)001:1089: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:1091: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le che ho'i bar ro //
NK025(ra)001:1095: kun mkhyen ye shes dag pa la //
NK025(ra)001:1096: dug lnga'i sgrib pas ma mthong bas //
NK025(ra)001:1097: mtshon cing dag par bya ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:1098: byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:1100: zhes pas rigs lnga 'od du zhu rdul tshon la
NK025(ra)001:1101: thim pas ye shes re re'ang lnga lnga dang ldan
NK025(ra)001:1102: par bsam mo // mchan bur spung zhing bsnun pa ltar bya'o gsung /
NK025(ra)001:1103: de nas rdo rje dril bu'i rab gnas ni /
NK025(ra)001:1105: stong pa'i ngang las rdo rje'i lte bar che mchog he kur ka /
NK025(ra)001:1106: rtse lnga pa yin na yar gyi rwa lnga h+aum s+w+aa +aamhh+aa las mi bskyod sogs rigs lnga /
NK025(ra)001:1107: mar gyi rwa lnga m+aum l+aam m+aam b+aam t+aam las nam mkha' dbyings phyug ma sogs yum lngar bskyed /
NK025(ra)001:1108: rtse dgu pa las yar gyi mtshams kyi rwa bzhi lung gi he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:1113: yar pad brgyad la sa'i snying po sogs sems dpa' brgyad /
NK025(ra)001:1114: mar pad brgyad la la s+ye ma sogs sems ma brgyad /
NK025(ra)001:1115: bar gyi mtshams kyi rwa bzhir rak+sha kro d+hi shwa r+ai sogs lung gi yum bzhi'o //
NK025(ra)001:1116: ril po la 'dus pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha thams ca da rdzogs par bsam /
NK025(ra)001:1117: dril bu'i lte bar khro mo gnam zhal ma /
NK025(ra)001:1118: zhal la yum sher phyin ma /
NK025(ra)001:1119: rtse lnga pa la rwa lnga la mi bskyod pa sogs rigs lnga /
NK025(ra)001:1120: 'og gi pad+ma'i dbus dang phyogs mtshams su dbyings phyug ma sogs yum lnga /
NK025(ra)001:1121: sangs rgyas spyan ma sogs gsang yum bzhi /
NK025(ra)001:1122: gong ras la goo r+ai la sogs khro mo brgyad /
NK025(ra)001:1123: rdo ra la h+aum mdzad sgra 'byin ma sogs khro bo khro mo nyi shu /
NK025(ra)001:1124: lce la khro mo gar bsgyur ma /
NK025(ra)001:1125: rtse dgu pa la mtshams bzhi'i r+aa la las bzhi'i snying po dzahh+aum bam hohbaskyeda do //
NK025(ra)001:1127: de dag sngags sam ting nge 'dzin gyis gsal bar bskyed /
NK025(ra)001:1128: ces gsungs pa sngags kyis bskyed par spro na so so'i rtsa sngags brjod /
NK025(ra)001:1129: gang ltar yang ting nge 'dzin gsal bar bskyed do //
NK025(ra)001:1130: rtsa bar ye shes lngas dbang bskur /
NK025(ra)001:1131: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab /
NK025(ra)001:1132: kun bzang nas bstod pa'i bar bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:1133: zhes gsungs pa sngar bzhin sh+au nya t+aa sogs kyis dbang bskur /
NK025(ra)001:1134: k+aa ya badz+ra sogs kyis byin gyis brlabs /
NK025(ra)001:1135: badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum dzah zhes pa nas e h+ye hi sogs kyis drang /
NK025(ra)001:1136: am ku sha sogs kyis bstim /
NK025(ra)001:1138: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK025(ra)001:1139: zhes kun bzang gi mchod pa nas bzung phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i zhii bstod dang /
NK025(ra)001:1140: gtum chen dus mtha'i sogs khro bstod kyang bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:1142: de nas h+aum zhes brjod pas lha rnams 'od du zhu /
NK025(ra)001:1143: rdor dril la thim pas ye shes kyi ngo bor bsam zhing /
NK025(ra)001:1144: rdo rje lag g.yas par blangs te gsor zhing /
NK025(ra)001:1145: badz+ra d+ha ka dz+wa la ha na dz+wa la badz+ra pany+tsa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1146: dril bu lag g.yon pas dkrol zhing /
NK025(ra)001:1147: g+han+de p+aa sha d+har+m+aa b+ha ra h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1148: zhes brjod pas rdo rje la 'bras bu'i chos thams cad rdzogs te 'gro don mdzad par bsam /
NK025(ra)001:1149: dril bu stong pa nyid kyi ngang las chos sgra sgrog par bsam zhing lag tu bzung nas /
NK025(ra)001:1151: rdo rje dril bu rig pa 'dzin //
NK025(ra)001:1152: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:1154: chos la de bzhin dbang sgyur shog /
NK025(ra)001:1155: ces brjod cing rdo rje gsor bas khams gsum gyis mnan /
NK025(ra)001:1156: dril bu gsil bas srid gsum dbang du bsdu bar bsam mo //
NK025(ra)001:1157: de nas b+han+d+ha'i rab gnas ni /
NK025(ra)001:1158: bdud rtsi skam rlon gang rigs kyis bkang ba'i b+han+d+ha bsang sbyang /
NK025(ra)001:1159: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las 'dus pa chen po
NK025(ra)001:1160: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor thams cad yongs su rdzoogs par
NK025(ra)001:1161: bskyed la / sh+au nya t+aa sogs rigs lngas dbang bskur /
NK025(ra)001:1162: k+aa ya badz+ra sogs sku gsung thugs su brlab /
NK025(ra)001:1163: badz+ra sa ma ya dzahs snyan gsan dbab /
NK025(ra)001:1164: e h+ye hi b+ha ga wan sogs kyis drang /
NK025(ra)001:1165: badz+ra am ku sha sogs kyis bstim /
NK025(ra)001:1167: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK025(ra)001:1168: sogs kun bzang gis mchod la /
NK025(ra)001:1170: bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha dz+ny+aa na d+h+aa tu a dang /
NK025(ra)001:1171: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1172: zhes ci rigs bzlas pas lha rnams 'od du zhu
NK025(ra)001:1173: ba ye shes kyi bdud rtsis mer gyis gang bar
NK025(ra)001:1174: bsam mo // de nas dkyil 'khor gyi thog ma'i
NK025(ra)001:1175: sa chog gi drug pa sa bsrung ba dang bdun
NK025(ra)001:1176: pa byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:1178: de ltar yan lag rab gnas zin nas /
NK025(ra)001:1179: rdo rje slob dpon chas gos lngas brgyan te h+aum zhes rdo rje'i 'gros kyis dkyil 'khor bskor la /
NK025(ra)001:1180: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su phyin la shar du bltas te rnam rgyal gyi nga rgyal gyis 'dug la /
NK025(ra)001:1181: zhes gsungs pa g.yung ston gyi sgyu 'phrul dbang chog
NK025(ra)001:1182: tu rdo rje'i slob dpon rgyas pa'i chas su zhugs
NK025(ra)001:1183: la / zhes gsungs 'dug pa 'dir chas gos lngas
NK025(ra)001:1184: brgyan zhes gsungs pa de bzhin 'dra bar snang yang
NK025(ra)001:1185: la / / deng sang phyag bzhes su thang zhu
NK025(ra)001:1186: dang phod kha sogs mdzad 'dug pa rdo rje'i 'gros
NK025(ra)001:1187: sogs mdzad stabs bde bar snang bas /
NK025(ra)001:1188: bla mas chas zhugs byas te rdor dril 'dzin pas
NK025(ra)001:1189: h+aum h+aum rkang mthil gnyis su sna tshogs rdo rje
NK025(ra)001:1190: 'bar ba re res mtshan par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1191: zhes brjod cing h+aum sgra dang bcas te rdo rje'i
NK025(ra)001:1192: 'gros bya zhing rol mo dang bcas te dkyil 'khor
NK025(ra)001:1193: bskor la dbus su phyin te shar du bltas te
NK025(ra)001:1194: / rang nyid khro bo rnam par rgyal ba'i nga
NK025(ra)001:1195: rgyal zhes 'byung yang gtso bo mi bskyod pa'am badz+ra
NK025(ra)001:1196: he ru ka'i nga rgyal bzung ste stangs stabs sam
NK025(ra)001:1198: 'dus pa chen po'i lha tshogs mdun gyi nam mkhar
NK025(ra)001:1199: spyan drangs te phyi nang gsang ba'am lhag pa ting
NK025(ra)001:1201: yum bzhi po rigs bzhir byin gyis brlabs la dbang bskur dbab /
NK025(ra)001:1203: bstim brtan la zhes gsungs pas /
NK025(ra)001:1204: mdun gyi nam mkhar 'dus pa chen po mdo'i dkyil
NK025(ra)001:1205: 'khor lha tshogs thams cad mngon sum lta bur badz+ra
NK025(ra)001:1206: sa m+aa dzah phyi mchod kun bzang /
NK025(ra)001:1208: gsang ba sbyor sgrol rnams thig byin rlabs skabs ltar dbul /
NK025(ra)001:1209: yang na lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pas kyang rung ste /
NK025(ra)001:1211: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK025(ra)001:1212: sems kyi yid bzhin sprin tshogs kyis //
NK025(ra)001:1213: phyogs bcu thams cad sangs rgyas zhing //
NK025(ra)001:1214: mnyen 'jam reg na bde ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:1215: sna tshogs rin po che yi gzhi //
NK025(ra)001:1216: mdzes par bres shing spras pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:1218: dbyibs legs rdzing bu bro mchog bsil //
NK025(ra)001:1219: rin chen khang pa sna tshogs dang //
NK025(ra)001:1220: rgyan dang dpag bsam ljon pa'i tshal //
NK025(ra)001:1221: glu dbyangs tshigs su bcad pa'i sgra //
NK025(ra)001:1222: bla bre rgyal mtshan na bza' gdugs //
NK025(ra)001:1223: do shal dpung rgyan se mo do //
NK025(ra)001:1224: bza' dang btung ba'i mchog rnams dang //
NK025(ra)001:1225: rang la mdzes par brgyan pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:1226: lha dang lha mo rdul snyed kyis //
NK025(ra)001:1227: bro gar la sogs bsam yas kyis //
NK025(ra)001:1228: phyogs bcu nam mkha'i khams bkang nas //
NK025(ra)001:1230: skal ldan gsal ba'i khyad par gyis //
NK025(ra)001:1231: rim gyis yang na cig car du //
NK025(ra)001:1232: chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam sbyor zhing //
NK025(ra)001:1233: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen por bsgom //
NK025(ra)001:1234: a la la ste mchod par 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:1235: zhes mchod la phyogs bzhir slob ma bzhi grogs dang
NK025(ra)001:1236: bcas te chas su zhugs pa'am ma zhugs kyang rung
NK025(ra)001:1237: ste rol mor bcas te 'khod pa la /
NK025(ra)001:1238: rdo rje rin chen pad+ma las kyi rigs /
NK025(ra)001:1239: spyan ma sogs yum bzhir gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1241: k+aa ya badz+ra sogs kyis brlab /
NK025(ra)001:1242: badz+ra sa ma ya dzahs dbab /
NK025(ra)001:1243: e h+ye hi sogs kyis drangs /
NK025(ra)001:1244: am ku sha sogs kyis bstim /
NK025(ra)001:1247: gsang yum bzhis phyogs bzhi nas gsol ba gdab ste /
NK025(ra)001:1248: zhes pa las ma bshad kyang /
NK025(ra)001:1249: sgyu 'phrul las kun bzang yab yum la kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod /
NK025(ra)001:1252: bde bar gshegs so nas bzung sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga gan+d+he'i bar gyis mchod la /
NK025(ra)001:1253: dbyangs dang rol mor bcas pas /
NK025(ra)001:1255: sangs rgyas kun 'dus grong khyer nyid //
NK025(ra)001:1256: de ring shis par mdzad du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:1257: thams cad bdag nyid dgongs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:1258: de nas phyogs bzhi tha dad du /
NK025(ra)001:1260: zhi ba'i ye shes rang snang ba //
NK025(ra)001:1261: rgyan rnams kun gyis rab mdzes pa //
NK025(ra)001:1262: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku yi mchog /
NK025(ra)001:1263: dkyil 'khor chen po gsung du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:1265: yon tan rin chen rgyas pa'i gtso //
NK025(ra)001:1266: ma lus kun gyi re ba skong //
NK025(ra)001:1267: sangs rgyas kun gyi yon tan mchog /
NK025(ra)001:1268: dkyil 'khor chen po gsung du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:1270: rang bzhin dag pas gos pa med //
NK025(ra)001:1271: sangs rgyas kun gyi gsung gi mchog /
NK025(ra)001:1272: 'dod chags pha rol phyin pa brnyes //
NK025(ra)001:1273: dkyil 'khor chen po gsung du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:1275: bsam pa thams cad yongs rdzogs pa //
NK025(ra)001:1276: thams cad sgrol ba'i ded dpon mchog /
NK025(ra)001:1277: sangs rgyas kun gyi phrin las bdag /
NK025(ra)001:1278: dkyil 'khor chen po gsung du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:1280: bsam pa thams cad yongs rdzogs pa //
NK025(ra)001:1281: thams cad sgrol ba'i ded dpon mchog /
NK025(ra)001:1282: sangs rgyas kun gyi phrin las bdag /
NK025(ra)001:1283: dkyil 'khor chen po gsung du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:1284: yang bzhi po thams cad bsdoms nas /
NK025(ra)001:1285: bsod nams ye shes tshogs rdzogs pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:1286: rang rig mtha' dbus med pa'i dkyil //
NK025(ra)001:1287: ye shes pho brang 'khor lo'i tshul //
NK025(ra)001:1288: dkyil 'khor snying po bshad du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:1291: phyogs bcu ma lus thams cad kyi //
NK025(ra)001:1292: rgyal ba sras bcas dgongs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:1293: bdag nyid rdo rje rgyal po yis //
NK025(ra)001:1294: slob ma rnams kyi don phyir du //
NK025(ra)001:1295: dkyil 'khor chen po bdag bgyid pas //
NK025(ra)001:1296: bdag cag rjes su bzung ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:1297: sa 'di shis par byin rlabs pa //
NK025(ra)001:1298: bde bar gshegs pas mdzad du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:1299: zhes brjod la thugs ka'i 'od zer gyis nam mkhar
NK025(ra)001:1300: bzhugs pa'i lha tshogs rnams h+aum bzhis bsdus te thugs
NK025(ra)001:1304: h+aum zhes brjod pas nam mkha'i lha tshogs de rnams
NK025(ra)001:1305: kyi sku gsung thugs kyi byin rlabs thams cad 'od
NK025(ra)001:1307: yang h+aum zhes brjod pas 'od zer thams cad bdag la bsdu /
NK025(ra)001:1308: yang h+aum zhes brjod pas bdag gi sgo gsum gyi
NK025(ra)001:1309: sdig sgrib thams cad ba mo la nyi zer phog
NK025(ra)001:1310: pa ltar sbyangs / yang h+aum zhes brjod pas rang nyid gtso bo'i nga rgyal gnas 'gyur te /
NK025(ra)001:1311: zhe sdang rdo rje sku mdog mthing nag zhal gcig
NK025(ra)001:1312: phyag gnyis g.yas rdo rje rtse dgu dang g.yon dril
NK025(ra)001:1313: bu 'dzin pa / rkang mthil dang thugs kar nyi
NK025(ra)001:1314: ma'i steng du h+aum mthig nag 'bar ba res mtshan
NK025(ra)001:1315: bu 'dzin pa / par bsam mo // rtsa bar /
NK025(ra)001:1316: slob ma rnams yi dam gang yin sgom pa'i dbang
NK025(ra)001:1317: po'i sgo lnga nas 'od zer sna tshogs 'phro bar
NK025(ra)001:1318: bsam mo // zhes 'byung bas slob ma rnams kyang
NK025(ra)001:1319: yi dam gyi lha gang rigs su bsgoms pa'i dbang
NK025(ra)001:1320: po'i sgo nas 'od zer sna tshogs su 'phro bar
NK025(ra)001:1321: bsam la h+aum sgra stangs stabs dang bcas pas rdo
NK025(ra)001:1322: bsam mo // rje'i 'gros bya'o // rtsa bar /
NK025(ra)001:1323: de nas byang shar mtshams nas rdo rje'i 'gros kyis
NK025(ra)001:1324: bskor zhing sum+b+ha dang khro bcu'i sngags kyis bgegs bskrad
NK025(ra)001:1325: la / zhes gsungs pa mdo dbang zur lugs su gsal bar ma byung yang /
NK025(ra)001:1326: khams lugs su nang mtshams khro bcu'i phur gdab kyi rjes su khro bo bcu'i stangs stabs bshad cing /
NK025(ra)001:1327: sgyu 'phrul zhi khro'i dkyil chog rnams su yang de bzhin 'byung pas /
NK025(ra)001:1328: rdo rje slob dpon gyi chas su sogs kyi khyad
NK025(ra)001:1329: par la brten nas sbyor bar rigs par snang zhing
NK025(ra)001:1330: / khro bo bcu'i sngags kyiis bgegs bskrod par gsungs pa yang 'thus par sems te /
NK025(ra)001:1331: slob dpon gyis phyoogs mtshams so so dang /
NK025(ra)001:1332: steng shar stod dang 'og nub smad du 'gro zhing /
NK025(ra)001:1333: steng dang phyogs bzhi'i khro bor sngags kyi tshe g.yas bskor dang g.yas brkyang /
NK025(ra)001:1334: 'og dang mtshams bzhi'i khro bor g.yon bskor dang g.yon brkyang /
NK025(ra)001:1335: tshigs bcad rnams dang bstun te so so'i stangs stabs bya ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:1337: lag pa thal sbyar gyi spyi bor bzhag /
NK025(ra)001:1338: rkang pa phral te brkyang bskum bya //
NK025(ra)001:1339: tshigs chen bzhi yang bcag par bya //
NK025(ra)001:1340: h+aum k+aa ra yi phyag rgya yin //
NK025(ra)001:1341: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1343: rkang g.yon g.yas pa'i barla steng 'khyud //
NK025(ra)001:1344: lag gnyis thal mo bsdeb pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:1345: rnam par rgyal ba'i phyag rgya yin //
NK025(ra)001:1346: badz+ra kro d+ha bi dz+aa ya h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1347: ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:1348: mathe'u chung mthe bos mthil du mnan //
NK025(ra)001:1349: sor gsum bsgrengs te stabs byed pa //
NK025(ra)001:1350: dbyug pa sngon po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK025(ra)001:1351: badz+ra kro d+ha n+ai la dan+da h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1352: da ha da ha h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:1353: rkang g.yon brkyang la lag pa g.yon //
NK025(ra)001:1354: dkur brten lag g.yas nam mkhar 'phyar //
NK025(ra)001:1355: 'di ni gshin rje gshed kyi rgya //
NK025(ra)001:1356: badz+ra kro d+ha ya m+aan+ta ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1357: pa tsa pa tsa h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:1359: g.yon pas 'dzin pa ltar byed pa //
NK025(ra)001:1360: mi g.yo mgon po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK025(ra)001:1361: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1363: rta gdong phyag rgya bcas nas ni //
NK025(ra)001:1364: spyi bor bzhag nas 'gying ba'i tshul //
NK025(ra)001:1365: 'di ni rta mchog dpal gyi rgya //
NK025(ra)001:1366: badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai wa h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1367: hu lu hu lu h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:1368: rkang lag g.yon pa nam mkhar 'phyar //
NK025(ra)001:1369: lag pa gdengs pa'i tshul byas pa //
NK025(ra)001:1370: gzhan gyis mi thub phyag rgya yin //
NK025(ra)001:1371: badz+ra kro d+ha a p+aa ra dz+ai ta h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1373: lag pa gnyis kyis dkur brten nas //
NK025(ra)001:1374: rkang gnyis gshibs nas g.yas g.yon mchong //
NK025(ra)001:1376: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1378: lag gnyis mkhrig ma mthur du bsnol //
NK025(ra)001:1379: sdigs mdzub gnyis ni dpung bar bsgreng //
NK025(ra)001:1380: khams gsum rnam rgyal phyag rgya yin //
NK025(ra)001:1381: badz+ra kro d+ha tree lo kya bi dz+aa ya h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1383: rkang pa gom stabs g.yas g.yon mchong //
NK025(ra)001:1384: lag pa g.yas g.yon thal mo brdeg /
NK025(ra)001:1385: 'di ni stobs po che yi rgya //
NK025(ra)001:1386: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa b+aa la h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1387: s+pho ta ya s+pho ta ya h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:1389: gral du 'khod pa la sku gsung thugs kyis byin gyis brlab cing go bago'o //
NK025(ra)001:1390: zhes gsungs pa ni gong bzhin phyag rgya bcas te slob ma'i gnas gsum du gtugs la /
NK025(ra)001:1391: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya sogs /
NK025(ra)001:1392: rdo rje go cha'i phyag rgya bcas te /
NK025(ra)001:1393: badz+ra rak+sha ham zhes slob ma'i spyi por phyag rgya bzhag ste go bago'o //
NK025(ra)001:1395: de nas ji tsam 'os pa'i dkyil 'khor zur thig
NK025(ra)001:1396: nas 'debs pa'i bar cha lngar bgos pa'i nang ma
NK025(ra)001:1397: la 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad kyi dbus su shong na
NK025(ra)001:1398: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor me ri yan bri ba phyag
NK025(ra)001:1399: len / ma chud na sla nga'am ka to ra'i nang sas bkang la zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bri /
NK025(ra)001:1400: many+dzi'i kha la rtsibs brgyad kyi lte ba'i dbus su bzhag pa phyag len no //
NK025(ra)001:1401: de'i phyi ma cha lnga lngar bgos pa la bar khyams bcu /
NK025(ra)001:1402: de'i phyir ma la gzhal yas khang chen po'i sgo rta babs sogs /
NK025(ra)001:1403: de'i phyi ma la pad rdor me ri dug gsum gyi mtshan ma'o //
NK025(ra)001:1404: rdo rje'i 'chang gi dkyil 'khor 'dir gru bzhir byed
NK025(ra)001:1405: na'ang gab pa'i dbang drug nas khyams zla gam kha
NK025(ra)001:1406: sprod du bshad pas gru khyogs zlum por rigs so
NK025(ra)001:1407: // zhes gsungs pas bar 'dir lha sta gon gyi
NK025(ra)001:1408: lha gnas mi 'chol ba'i phyir las thig 'debs dgos
NK025(ra)001:1409: // pas / de yang khams lugs kyi thig rtsa
NK025(ra)001:1410: mi 'dra ba gnyis tsam zhig snang yang lag len
NK025(ra)001:1411: du khel mi khel sna tshogs shing /
NK025(ra)001:1412: dkyil 'khor gyi babs gnyis ka mthun par zhi ba'i
NK025(ra)001:1413: dkyil 'khor dbus su bri ba'am yang na steng du
NK025(ra)001:1414: bton la bri / khro bo'i dkyil 'khor dang po
NK025(ra)001:1415: rgyud lung gi khro bo gnas yul gyi khro mo
NK025(ra)001:1416: bton la bri / dang phra men / nang gi sgo ma dang bcas pa'i dkyil 'khor dang po /
NK025(ra)001:1417: khyams gnyis pa spor ma brgyad dang bar gyi sgo ma bzhi ste dkyil 'khor gnyis pa /
NK025(ra)001:1418: khyams gsum pa dbang mo nyer brgyad de dkyil 'khor gsum pa /
NK025(ra)001:1419: khyams bzhi pa la mkha' 'gro ma sum cu rtsa gnyis te dkyil 'khor bzhi pa /
NK025(ra)001:1420: khyams lnga pa ma bdun sring bzhi ste dkyil 'khor lnga pa /
NK025(ra)001:1421: khyams drug pa ging chen bco brgyad de dkyil 'khor drug pa /
NK025(ra)001:1422: khyams bdun pa khro bo khro mo drug cu ste dkyil 'khor bdun pa /
NK025(ra)001:1423: khyams brgyad pa pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu ste dkyil 'khor brgyad pa /
NK025(ra)001:1424: khyams dgu pa ma mo drug cu ste dkyil 'khor dgu pa /
NK025(ra)001:1425: khyams bcu pa la khams lugs su rig 'dzin bla ma dang /
NK025(ra)001:1426: zur lugs su bka' brgyad theg dgu yin pas 'dir
NK025(ra)001:1427: bcu pa la bka' brgyad theg dgu ste dkyil 'khor
NK025(ra)001:1428: bcu pa / bcu gcig pa rig 'dzin bla ma
NK025(ra)001:1429: la lugs gnyis ka la rnam pa gcig tu rta
NK025(ra)001:1430: babs kyi khyams la bzhugs par bzhed phyir /
NK025(ra)001:1431: phyi rol gyi nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor du bzhugs pa 'dra zhig snang yang zur lugs rtsa bar /
NK025(ra)001:1432: rdo rje 'chang gi dkyil 'khor 'dir gru bzhir byed
NK025(ra)001:1433: na'ang gab pa'i dbang drug nas khyams zla gam kha
NK025(ra)001:1434: sprod du bshad pas gru khyogs zlum por rigs so
NK025(ra)001:1436: kho bo'i bla ma sman lung pa chen pos /
NK025(ra)001:1437: 'di ni bde mchog mkha' 'gro rgya mtsho'i dkyil 'khor
NK025(ra)001:1438: dang dbyibs 'dra bar rtsig pa nas pu shu'i bar
NK025(ra)001:1439: sgor mor bris kyang 'thad ces gsungs pa /
NK025(ra)001:1440: gzhung dang shin tu mthun zhing rigs par snang /
NK025(ra)001:1441: bla ma gong ma phal cher rig 'dzin bla ma
NK025(ra)001:1442: phyi khyams su bkod pa las gzhal yas khang mi
NK025(ra)001:1444: 'dir rtsa ba las gzhal yas khang gsal por gsungs shing /
NK025(ra)001:1445: de yang gru bzhi dang zlum po 'dam khar bshad pas gzhal yas khang nges par dgos shing /
NK025(ra)001:1446: de yang zlum po bshad tshod du snang yang mdzes
NK025(ra)001:1447: cha'i dbang dang rta babs sogs 'jug pa bde phyir
NK025(ra)001:1448: gru bzhi phyag len du mdzad pas dkyil 'khor bcu
NK025(ra)001:1449: gcig ste phyogs rer sgo bcu gcig sbrag khyon bsdoms
NK025(ra)001:1450: pas sgo zhe bzhi mar 'gyur ba yin no //
NK025(ra)001:1451: de'i steng du zhi dkyil gyi sgo bzhi bsnan na zhe brgyad ma'o //
NK025(ra)001:1452: de ltar don nges par byas te /
NK025(ra)001:1453: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor logs su bri rtsis kyi khro
NK025(ra)001:1454: bo'i dkyil 'khor rnams kyi thig rtsa lag len du
NK025(ra)001:1455: phab ste gsal bar byas pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:1456: tshogs chen dkyil 'khor thig rtsa la //
NK025(ra)001:1457: tshangs zur bzhi po spyi ltar btab //
NK025(ra)001:1458: dkyil 'khor dang po'i lte ba la //
NK025(ra)001:1459: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad khyams dang bcas //
NK025(ra)001:1460: de nas cha chen gnyis btab pa //
NK025(ra)001:1461: gzhal yas khang pa dang po'o //
NK025(ra)001:1462: de nas che chung rig pas dpags //
NK025(ra)001:1463: dum bu dgur bgos dum bu res //
NK025(ra)001:1464: cha chen gsum rer bgos pa la //
NK025(ra)001:1465: dang po khyams dang de lhag gnyis //
NK025(ra)001:1466: gzhal yas khang du 'gyur mod de //
NK025(ra)001:1467: dbus nas mtha' yi bar dag tu //
NK025(ra)001:1468: sgo tshad che chung med pas na //
NK025(ra)001:1469: mi mdzes phyir du man ngag ni //
NK025(ra)001:1470: dkyil 'khor dang po nas bzung ste //
NK025(ra)001:1471: dkyil 'khor bcu pa'i bar dag tu //
NK025(ra)001:1472: sor re'i tshad kyis che bar bya //
NK025(ra)001:1473: de la dum bu gsum bcad pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:1474: dang po thams cad bar khyams la //
NK025(ra)001:1475: gnyis kun dbus dor mtha' gnyis btab //
NK025(ra)001:1477: gsum kun phyed gdab phyed phyi gdab //
NK025(ra)001:1478: d+r+wa phyed mda' yab pu shu'o //
NK025(ra)001:1479: kun la rta babs bya 'dod na //
NK025(ra)001:1480: dang po'i rta babs phyi ma'i khyams //
NK025(ra)001:1481: ka rgyan gnyis steng cha bzhir bgo //
NK025(ra)001:1482: glang rgyab pad chos gdugs tog can //
NK025(ra)001:1483: bka' brgyud theg dgu yan chod yin //
NK025(ra)001:1484: dkyil 'khor so so'i sgo tshad gnyis //
NK025(ra)001:1485: g.yas g.yon so sor phyin pa la //
NK025(ra)001:1486: dang po phyed gdab phyi ma bgo //
NK025(ra)001:1487: gnyis pa cha bzhi bgo bar bya //
