NK025(ra)001:1488: bcu gcig rig 'dzin bla ma'i khyams //
NK025(ra)001:1489: zla gam kha sbyor du bzhed kyang //
NK025(ra)001:1490: gru bzhi nyid mdzes de yi phyir //
NK025(ra)001:1491: nang ma kun las ches che ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:1492: cha chen gnyis la gzhal yas khang //
NK025(ra)001:1493: cha chen gnyis la rta babs so //
NK025(ra)001:1494: rta babs snam bu brgyad pa ste //
NK025(ra)001:1495: cha chen gnyis la cha phran bzhi //
NK025(ra)001:1497: nang du bgrod tshul 'di ltar ro //
NK025(ra)001:1498: dang po phyed drug gnyis gsum drug /
NK025(ra)001:1499: bzhi pa bzhi dang lnga phyed bzhi //
NK025(ra)001:1500: drug pa gsum bcad tshangs rtser sleb //
NK025(ra)001:1501: phyi yi rta babs ring thung ni //
NK025(ra)001:1502: dang po gcig gi rang sa la //
NK025(ra)001:1503: gnyis gsum cha phran gcig gis ring //
NK025(ra)001:1504: bzhi pa cha phran gcig gis bskum //
NK025(ra)001:1505: lnga pa dang po dag dang mnyam //
NK025(ra)001:1506: drug pa la ni gnyis phri zhing //
NK025(ra)001:1507: bdun pa la ni gcig phri ste //
NK025(ra)001:1508: brgyad pa gsum nas bcad pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:1509: pad gdan dbus rwa chos 'khor tog /
NK025(ra)001:1510: ci mdzes rig pas legs dpyad de //
NK025(ra)001:1511: cha chen gcig la tshang bar bya //
NK025(ra)001:1512: chu srin rwa yi skor tshad ni //
NK025(ra)001:1513: tshang thig g.yas nas dang po dang //
NK025(ra)001:1514: cha phran gcig gi bar mtshams su //
NK025(ra)001:1515: lag g.yon btsugs te g.yas pa yis //
NK025(ra)001:1516: rta babs dang po'i rtse mo la //
NK025(ra)001:1517: cha phran gcig gis ma reg par //
NK025(ra)001:1518: pu shu'i rtse nas dbus rwar then //
NK025(ra)001:1519: slar yang lag g.yon snga ma nas //
NK025(ra)001:1520: cha phran gnyis kyi phyir spos la //
NK025(ra)001:1521: g.yas pas sngar gyi gnas de nas //
NK025(ra)001:1522: phyir zlog pu shud reg pas bskor //
NK025(ra)001:1523: g.yon pa'i bskor tshul de yis shes //
NK025(ra)001:1524: de'i phyir pad+ma dur khrod dang //
NK025(ra)001:1525: rdo rje'i ra ba me ri sogs //
NK025(ra)001:1526: cha chen cha phran tshad rnams ni //
NK025(ra)001:1527: spyi ltar bskor bas las thig go //
NK025(ra)001:1528: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor sgo rdzogs kyi lte bar 'khor
NK025(ra)001:1529: lo rtsibs bzhi glo 'bur lha snam dang bcas pa'i
NK025(ra)001:1530: thig zur du man+dala che ba'am shing stegs che chung
NK025(ra)001:1531: ran pa zhig gi khar btab bo //
NK025(ra)001:1532: de ltar las thig btab pa'i steng du lha sta gon gyi tshom bu bkod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:1534: de nas kham por ram dung chos su chang phud la a mri ta /
NK025(ra)001:1540: bu ram rnams sbyar pa spe'usa lha gnas su dri'i thig le bya ste /
NK025(ra)001:1541: s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra man+da la gdan bsam /
NK025(ra)001:1543: chang phud la chos sman dang tsan+dana dkar dmar /
NK025(ra)001:1548: bu ram rnams sbyar te lha gnas rnams su pir gyis dri'i thig le bkod cing /
NK025(ra)001:1549: s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra man+da la zhes brjod la dang po zhi
NK025(ra)001:1550: ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su dri'i thig le'i steng
NK025(ra)001:1551: 'bras sam nas dkar gyi tshom bu bkod cing /
NK025(ra)001:1552: h'u h'u h'u badz+ra tsit+ta h'u /
NK025(ra)001:1553: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta a /
NK025(ra)001:1554: gtso bo kun bzang yab yum dbus su bkod /
NK025(ra)001:1556: de'i mdun du h'u badz+ra d+h+rika /
NK025(ra)001:1557: m+aum d+h+aa t+wi shwa r+ai mi bskyod pa sogs sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis po bkod de /
NK025(ra)001:1559: zhes gsungs pa de rnams kyi don ni /
NK025(ra)001:1560: thog mar tshom bu 'god pa dang bstun sngags rnams tshar gcig brjod par mdzad srol 'dug pas /
NK025(ra)001:1561: gtso bo kun bzang gi mdun du tshom bu bkod cing /
NK025(ra)001:1563: m+aum d+h+aa t+wi shwa r+ai mi bskyod pa yab yum mo //
NK025(ra)001:1564: shar rtsibs la dz+ai na dzika /
NK025(ra)001:1566: lho rtsibs la s+w+aa rat+na d+h+rika /
NK025(ra)001:1570: byang rtsibs la h+aa pradz+ny+aa d+h+rika /
NK025(ra)001:1572: shar lho'i gong ras la k+shi hi r+aa dza ya /
NK025(ra)001:1573: h+aum l+aa s+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:1574: lho nub kyi gong ras la tram a gar+b+ha ya /
NK025(ra)001:1575: tram m+aa le sa ma ya hoh nub byang gi gong ras la h+r+aihpad+ma pa da ma /
NK025(ra)001:1577: byang shar gyi gong ras la dz+rim ku ru pan+na h+r+aih a n+air+t+ya r+aa ga ya mi /
NK025(ra)001:1578: de'i phyir shar lho'i glo 'bur la mee d+ha ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:1580: lho nub kyi glo 'bur la th+l+him nis+sa ram pa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:1582: nub byang gi glo 'bur la h+aum sa r+aa dza ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:1583: bam d+ai pa su khi n+ai /
NK025(ra)001:1584: byang shar gyi glo 'bur la m+aum sh+r+ai a ram ga ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:1586: lha snam gyi shar lhor mu ne krem s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:1587: lha snam gyi byang du mu ne h'u trum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:1588: lhor mu ne srum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:1589: nub byang du mu ne bram s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:1590: lho nub tu mu ne k+sham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:1591: byang shar du mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:1592: shar sgor h+aum ya m+aan+ta krita phata /
NK025(ra)001:1593: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la ni h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:1594: lho sgor h+aum pradz+ny+aan+ta krita phata /
NK025(ra)001:1595: ma h+aa rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi nub sgor h+aum pad+m+aan+ta krita phata /
NK025(ra)001:1596: ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi byang sgor h+aum big+h+n+aan+ta krita phata /
NK025(ra)001:1597: ma h+aa karma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi zhi ba'i lha mtshan des rdzogs so //
NK025(ra)001:1599: dbus su a kra ma h+aa kro d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1600: ka ta ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1601: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1602: zhes che mchog yab yum dang /
NK025(ra)001:1603: de'i mdun du sarba ta th+aa ga ta sh+r+ai he
NK025(ra)001:1604: ru ka sarba ta th+aa ga ta kro d+hi shwa
NK025(ra)001:1605: r+ai h+aum / zhes dbang mchog dang /
NK025(ra)001:1606: de'i mdun du badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro
NK025(ra)001:1607: d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum zhes badz+ra he ru ka ste
NK025(ra)001:1608: gtso bo gsum gyi tshom bu bkod /
NK025(ra)001:1609: rtsibs brgyad kyi shar du bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1610: lhor rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1611: nub tu pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1612: byang du karma sh+r+ai he ru ka karma kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1613: zhes rgyud kyi khro bo bzhi dang /
NK025(ra)001:1614: mtshams bzhi'i shar lhor rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum rak+sha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1615: lho nub tu sa nu sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum sa nu kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1616: nub byang du gu h+ya sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum gu h+ya kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1617: byang shar du yak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum yak+sha
NK025(ra)001:1618: kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum zhes lung gi he ru
NK025(ra)001:1619: ka bzhi / glo 'bur gyi phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad du dang por phyogs bzhi /
NK025(ra)001:1620: de nas mtshams bzhi rim pa ltar /
NK025(ra)001:1629: khyams dang por phyogs mtshams su tshom bu gong bzhin bkod cing /
NK025(ra)001:1631: badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:1632: badz+ra sring+ga la mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:1633: badz+ra shwa na mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:1634: badz+ra gri d+ha mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:1636: badz+ra k+aa ka mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:1637: badz+ra u lu ka mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:1638: sgo bzhi'i shar du badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dzah lhor badz+ra a mu kh+aa h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1639: nub tu badz+ra lo ka bam /
NK025(ra)001:1640: byang du badz+ra b+hasmi pa la ya ba to hoh
NK025(ra)001:1641: dkyil 'khor gnyis pa'i khyams la phyogs mtshams brgyad du
NK025(ra)001:1643: sngags badz+ra a pra ti ha +aar+ya ni tsa tur ta ra phata /
NK025(ra)001:1645: sgo bzhi'i shar du sh+r+ai badz+ra mung+ga ra mu kha
NK025(ra)001:1646: shwa ra ya na mah lhor sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga
NK025(ra)001:1647: ma shwa ra ya y+aa na mah nub tu sh+r+ai
NK025(ra)001:1648: badz+ra kha t+w+aam ka pra dz+wa la ya y+aa na
NK025(ra)001:1649: mah byang du sh+r+ai badz+ra g+han+de pra dz+wa la ya
NK025(ra)001:1650: y+aa na mah dkyil 'khor gsum pa'i khyams phyogs bzhir
NK025(ra)001:1651: drug drug / sgo bzhir re re ste dbang mo
NK025(ra)001:1652: nyer brgyad kyi sngags spro na ma nu rak+sha s+ai
NK025(ra)001:1655: dkyil 'khor bzhi pa'i khyams la phyogs bzhir brgyad re 'god cing /
NK025(ra)001:1658: dkyil 'khor lnga pa'i khyams la shar lho nub gsum du gnyis gnyis /
NK025(ra)001:1660: sgo bzhir re re bkod cing /
NK025(ra)001:1663: dkyil 'khor drug pa'i khyams shar nub gnyis la bzhir re /
NK025(ra)001:1666: ging+kara ha ha ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1668: dkyil 'khor bdun pa'i khyams la shar nub tu bcu gnyis re /
NK025(ra)001:1670: shar nub kyi sgor drug re /
NK025(ra)001:1671: lho byang gi sgo bzhir re bkod cing /
NK025(ra)001:1674: dkyil 'khor brgyad pa'i khyams la phyogs rer drug cu re bkod cing /
NK025(ra)001:1675: shar pa rnams la b+ha na b+ha na am ku
NK025(ra)001:1676: sha dzah lho pa rnams la ha la ha la
NK025(ra)001:1677: p+aa sha h+aum / nub pa rnams la gardza gardza s+pho ta bam /
NK025(ra)001:1678: byang pa rnams la pa tsa pa tsa g+han+de hoh zhes so //
NK025(ra)001:1679: dkyil 'khor dgu pa'i khyams la phyogs rer bco lnga re bkod cing /
NK025(ra)001:1680: ma ma sha r+ai b+h+yoh zhes so //
NK025(ra)001:1681: dkyil 'khor bcu pa'i khyams la bka' brgyad theg dgu'i lha tshogs tshang ba yin pas /
NK025(ra)001:1682: dang po ni yang dag nas rim bzhin bka' brgyad gang rigs kyi sngags kyis bkod /
NK025(ra)001:1683: theg dgu ni spro na sgo 'byed phyag rdor nas
NK025(ra)001:1684: a ti'i bar gyi lha tshang bar bkod dgos pa
NK025(ra)001:1685: rig pas ci rigs su dpag go //
NK025(ra)001:1686: dkyil 'khor bcu gcig pa'i khyams la rig 'dzin bla
NK025(ra)001:1687: ma rnams bzhugs pas yo ga gsum gyi bla brgyud
NK025(ra)001:1688: grangs nges pa'i tshom bu bya ba'am /
NK025(ra)001:1689: yang na rig 'dzin la grangs nges med du bkod cing /
NK025(ra)001:1690: kun la ma h+aa gu ru sh+aa r+ai ram /
NK025(ra)001:1691: zhes pas rig 'a dzin rtsal 'chang bka' brgyud kyi bla ma rnams tshang ba'i tshom bu bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:1692: zhes gsungs pas ci rigs su byas pas chog /
NK025(ra)001:1693: de dag ni dkyil 'khor sta gon no //
NK025(ra)001:1694: dkyil 'khor mthar mtshams 'dzin sogs nyer spyod lnga dang /
NK025(ra)001:1695: yan lag rab gnas skabs su bshad pa ltar /
NK025(ra)001:1696: zhi khro'i gtor ma sman raka sogs phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa rnams rgya cher bsham mo //
NK025(ra)001:1697: de nas cho ga ji ltar bya ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:1699: de nas gnyis pa lha sta gon la gnas pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:1701: nang du rtsa ba dang yan lag gi mchod pa bsham mo //
NK025(ra)001:1704: ye na mnyam nyid kyis bshags /
NK025(ra)001:1707: mchod pa rnams byin gyis brlab /
NK025(ra)001:1709: dkyil 'khor khang pa'i phyi rol lam nang du yang rung ste /
NK025(ra)001:1710: cha gsum gyi cho ga snga ma ltar rgyas par btang /
NK025(ra)001:1711: rtsa ba yan lag gi mchod pa ni gong du bshags zin /
NK025(ra)001:1712: gral la 'khod de phyag bsdus pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:1713: thig byin rlabs kyi skabs ltar /
NK025(ra)001:1714: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK025(ra)001:1716: thub pa chen po drug la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:1717: a ti pu hoh pra t+aits+tsha hoh zhes pa'i bar dang /
NK025(ra)001:1718: khro bo bcu'i mtshams gcod ni /
NK025(ra)001:1719: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1721: ces pa nas stobs po che'i bar gyi sngags tsam brjod la mtshams bcad /
NK025(ra)001:1722: mdun gyi nam mkhar bshags yul 'dus pa mdo'i dkyil
NK025(ra)001:1723: 'khor gyi lha tshogs badz+ra sa ma ya dzah zhes
NK025(ra)001:1724: rdo rje bsdu ba'i sngags rgyas spyan drangs te yan
NK025(ra)001:1725: lag rab gnas kyi sngon 'gro'i skabs su bshad pa
NK025(ra)001:1726: ltar / ye nas mnyam nyid chos skur dag pa la //
NK025(ra)001:1728: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:1730: dus gsum sangs rgyas 'khor dang bcas //
NK025(ra)001:1731: zhes sogs kyis byin dbab bo //
NK025(ra)001:1733: zhi thung gi sngon 'gro'i skabs su rgyas par bshad pa ltar bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:1734: lha sta gon gyi cho ga dngos gzhi ni /
NK025(ra)001:1736: de nas rang nyid kun bzang du gsal ba'i thugs
NK025(ra)001:1737: ka'i h+aum las 'byung ba rim brtsegs dang bcas pa'i
NK025(ra)001:1739: yang bdag he ru kar gnas pa'i thugs kar 'byung
NK025(ra)001:1740: ba rim brtsegs dang bcas pa'i dkyil 'khor la khrag
NK025(ra)001:1751: steng gi khro bo khro mo drug cu /
NK025(ra)001:1752: shar du dung gi pho nya drug cu /
NK025(ra)001:1753: lhor lcags sam gser gyi pho nya drug cu /
NK025(ra)001:1754: nub tu bse'i pho nya drug cu /
NK025(ra)001:1755: byang du g.yu'i pho na drug cu /
NK025(ra)001:1756: 'og tu ma mo las byed drug cu /
NK025(ra)001:1757: rig 'dzin la sogs pa thams cad sngags kyis rdzogs tshul du bskyed /
NK025(ra)001:1759: swa b+h+aa wa zhes stong par sbyangs /
NK025(ra)001:1760: stong pa'i ngang las pad+ma dang nyi zla'i gdan gyi
NK025(ra)001:1761: steng du rang gi rig pa a mthing kha 'od
NK025(ra)001:1762: zer 'bar ba yongs su gyur pa las /
NK025(ra)001:1763: bdag nyid dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi spro bsdu'i byed
NK025(ra)001:1764: po bcom ldan 'das kun tu bzang po sku mdog
NK025(ra)001:1765: mthing kha zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK025(ra)001:1766: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing kha /
NK025(ra)001:1767: phyag dang po gnyis thugs kar byang chub mchog gi phyag rgyas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK025(ra)001:1768: bar pa gnyis rdo rje dang dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:1769: mtha' ma gnyis mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya mdzad pa rdo rje'i skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa /
NK025(ra)001:1770: rin po che'i dbu rgyanasogasa rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa /
NK025(ra)001:1771: dar sna tshogs kyi na bza' gsol ba /
NK025(ra)001:1772: yum kun tu bzang mo sngon mo pad+ma'i skyil krung can dang mnyam par sbyor ba'i skur gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1773: sh+au nya t+aa sogs kyis dbang bskur /
NK025(ra)001:1774: k+aa ya badz+ra sogs kyis brlab /
NK025(ra)001:1775: badz+ra sa ma ya dzahs dbab /
NK025(ra)001:1776: e h+ye hi sogs kyis drangs /
NK025(ra)001:1777: am ku sha sogs kyis bstim /
NK025(ra)001:1779: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK025(ra)001:1780: na mah sarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo sogs dang /
NK025(ra)001:1781: yang dag don du dag mod kyang //
NK025(ra)001:1782: bzhi bsnol gyis mchod la nga rgyal bzung /
NK025(ra)001:1783: de nas rang nyid kun bzang du gsal ba'i thugs ka'i h+aum las /
NK025(ra)001:1789: b+h+r+aum rnams 'phros pa las zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'og tu e las nam mkha' /
NK025(ra)001:1793: lam las ri rab ste 'byung ba rim brtsegs ri
NK025(ra)001:1794: rab dang bcas pa'i steng du b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi
NK025(ra)001:1795: shud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na man+da la /
NK025(ra)001:1797: b+h+r+aum las zhi ba'i gzhal yas khang lte ba zlum
NK025(ra)001:1798: po la 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud glo 'bur
NK025(ra)001:1799: gru chad dang lha snam sgo khyud rta babs 'dod
NK025(ra)001:1800: snam pha gu d+r+wa phyed pad+ma rdo rje me ri
NK025(ra)001:1801: dang bcas pa'i dbus su pad+ma s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra man+da la
NK025(ra)001:1802: / zhes brjod pas gdan pad+ma nyi zla'i gdan rnams su gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1803: bdag gi thugs ka nas lha sngags rnams rim par
NK025(ra)001:1804: thon te so so'i gdan la 'khod pa yongs su
NK025(ra)001:1805: gyur pa las lha rnams gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:1806: dbus su h+aum h+aum h+aum badz+ra tsit+ta /
NK025(ra)001:1807: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta a /
NK025(ra)001:1808: kun bzang yab yum du gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1811: gatsobo'i mdun du mi bskyod pa yab yum gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1812: shar rtsibs la dz+ai na dzika /
NK025(ra)001:1814: rnam snang yab yum du gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1815: lho rtsibs la s+w+aa rat+na d+h+rika /
NK025(ra)001:1817: rin 'byung yab yum du gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1820: snang mtha' yab yum du gasalabar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1821: byang rtsibs la h+aa pradz+ny+aa d+h+rika /
NK025(ra)001:1823: don grub yab yum du gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1824: shar lho'i gong ras la k+shi hi r+aa dza ya /
NK025(ra)001:1825: h+aum l+aa s+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:1826: sa snying yab yum du gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1827: lho nub kyi gong ras la tram a gar+b+ha ya /
NK025(ra)001:1828: tram m+aa le sa ma ya hoh nam mkha'i snying po yab yum du gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1829: nub byang gi gong ras la h+r+aihpad+ma pa da ma /
NK025(ra)001:1831: spyan ras gzigs yab yum du gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1832: byang shar kyi gong ras la dz+rim ku ru pan+na h+r+aih a nir+t+ya r+aa ga ya mi /
NK025(ra)001:1833: phyag rdor yab yum du gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1834: shar lho'i glo 'bur la mee d+h+aa ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:1836: byams pa yab yum du gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1837: lho nub kyi glo 'bur la th+l+him nis+sa ram pa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:1839: sgrib pa rnam sel yab yum du gsal bar /
NK025(ra)001:1840: nub byang gi glo 'bur la h+aum sa r+aa dza ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:1841: bam d+ai pa su shi n+ai /
NK025(ra)001:1842: kun bzang yab yum du gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1843: byang gi glo 'bur la m+aum sh+r+ai a ram ga ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:1845: 'jam dpal yab yum du gsal bar gyur //
NK025(ra)001:1846: lha snam gyi shar lho mu ne krem s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:1848: byang du mu ne h+aum trum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:1850: lhor mu ne srum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:1852: nub byang du mu ne bram s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:1854: lho nub tu mu ne k+sham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:1856: byang shar du mu ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:1857: dmyal ba'i thub pa rnams su gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1859: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta a /
NK025(ra)001:1860: khyams kyi nub tu byed pa po kun tu bzang po dang /
NK025(ra)001:1861: shar du bya ba mo kun tu bzang mo gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1862: shar sgor h+aum ya man+ta krita phata /
NK025(ra)001:1863: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dza la ni h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:1864: gshin rje yab yum gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1865: lho sgor h+aum pradz+ny+aan+ta krita phata /
NK025(ra)001:1866: ma h+aa rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:1867: stobs chen yab yum gsal bar sgyur /
NK025(ra)001:1868: nub sgor h+aum pad+m+aan+ta krita phata /
NK025(ra)001:1869: ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:1870: rta mgrin yab yum du gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1871: byang sgor h+aum big+h+n+aan+ta kri ta phata /
NK025(ra)001:1872: ma h+aa karma d+ha ra ma h+aa bdud rtsi 'khyil ba yab yum du gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1873: de nas bdag nyid du kun bzang yab yum gnas 'gyur te /
NK025(ra)001:1874: che mchog he ru ka dbu nyer gcig phyag zhe
NK025(ra)001:1875: gnyis pa zhi ba bzhi bcu'i lha tshogs bsnams pa
NK025(ra)001:1876: dur khrod kyi chas kyis 'jigs par byas pa ye
NK025(ra)001:1877: shes kyi me dpung 'bar ba'i dbus na gar dgu'i
NK025(ra)001:1878: nyams kyis rol pa'i skur gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1879: a kra ma h+aa kro d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1880: bdag gi thugs ka nas e /
NK025(ra)001:1885: b+h+r+aum rnams tshogs chen gyi dkyil 'khor 'og tu 'phros pas e las nam mkha' gru gsum /
NK025(ra)001:1886: yam las rlung rdo rje rgya gram /
NK025(ra)001:1887: ra las khrag gi rgya mtsho /
NK025(ra)001:1888: kem las keng rus kyi ri rab /
NK025(ra)001:1889: ram las bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar ba'i dbus su
NK025(ra)001:1890: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra tsakra dz+ny+aa na man+da
NK025(ra)001:1892: b+h+r+aum las khro bo'i gzhal yas khang mtshan nyid thams
NK025(ra)001:1893: cad yongs su rdzogs pa rim pa bcu gcig dang
NK025(ra)001:1894: ldan par gyur / s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra pad+ma man+da la de wa ti ra nan /
NK025(ra)001:1896: ti ra bam gyis pad+ma nyi zla ru tra pho mo'i gdan du gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1897: bdag nyid che mchog he ru kar gsal ba'i thugs
NK025(ra)001:1898: ka nas lha sngags rnams rim par thon te so
NK025(ra)001:1899: so'i gdan la 'khod de yongs su gyur pa las
NK025(ra)001:1900: lha rnams gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:1901: dkyil 'khor dang po'i dbus su a kra ma h+aa kro d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1902: ka ta ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1903: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1904: zhes che mchog yab yum dang /
NK025(ra)001:1905: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sh+r+ai he ru ka sarba ta th+aa ga ta kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1907: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1908: badz+ra he ru ka yab yum ste gtso bo gsum po gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1909: shar gyi rtsibs la bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1910: sangs rgyas khrag 'thung yab yum dang /
NK025(ra)001:1911: lho rtsibs la rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1912: rin chen khrag 'thung yab yum dang /
NK025(ra)001:1913: nub rtsibs la pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1915: byang rtsibs la karma sh+r+ai he ru ka karma kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1916: las kyi khrag 'thung yab yum te rgyud kyi he ru ka bzhi gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1917: shar lho'i rtsibs la rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka rak+sha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1919: lho nub tu sa nu sh+r+ai he ru ka sa nu kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1920: sa nu khrag 'thung yab yum dang /
NK025(ra)001:1921: nub byang du gu h+ya sh+r+ai he ru ka gu h+ya kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1922: gu h+ya khrag 'thung yab yum dang /
NK025(ra)001:1923: byang shar du yak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka yak+sha kro hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:1924: yak+sha khrag 'thung yab yum ste lung gi he ru ka bzhi gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1925: glo 'bur gyi shar du badz+ra goo r+ai ha /
NK025(ra)001:1927: nub tu badz+ra pra mo h+ae ha /
NK025(ra)001:1928: byang du badz+ra bet+ta l+ai ha /
NK025(ra)001:1929: shar lhor badz+ra puk+ka s+ai ha /
NK025(ra)001:1930: lho nub tu badz+ra g+hasma r+ai ha /
NK025(ra)001:1931: nub byang du badz+ra sme sha n+ai ha /
NK025(ra)001:1932: byang shar du badz+ra tsan+da l+ai ha /
NK025(ra)001:1933: zhes khro mo brgyad du gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1934: khyams dang por shar du badz+ra sing+ha mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:1935: lhor badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:1936: nub tu badz+ra sing+ga la mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:1937: byang du badz+ra shwa na mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:1938: shar lho badz+ra gri d+ha mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:1939: lho nub tu badz+ra kam ka mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:1940: nub byang du badz+ra k+aa ka mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:1941: byang shar du badz+ra u lu ka mu kha he las phra men brgyad du gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1942: shar sgor badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dzahrta gdong dkar mo dang /
NK025(ra)001:1943: lho sgor badz+ra a mu kha h+aum phag gdong ser mo dang /
NK025(ra)001:1944: nub sgor badz+ra lo ka bam seng gdong dmar mo dang /
NK025(ra)001:1945: byang sgor badz+ra b+hasmi pa la ya ba to hohspyanga
NK025(ra)001:1946: gdong ljang mo ste sgo ma bzhir gsal bar gyur
NK025(ra)001:1947: / dkyil 'khor gnyis pa'i khyams kyi phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad du /
NK025(ra)001:1948: badz+ra a pra ti ha +aar+ya ni tsa tu ra ta phata /
NK025(ra)001:1949: a rag+mo h+aum tshar brgyad brjod pas spor ma brgyad du gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1950: sgo bzhi'i shar sgor sh+r+ai badz+ra mu kha shwa ra
NK025(ra)001:1951: ya y+aa na mah dkar mo mig gcig rgyas 'debs
NK025(ra)001:1952: ma dang / lho sgor sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga ma
NK025(ra)001:1953: shwa ra ya y+aa na mah ser mo las mkhan
NK025(ra)001:1955: nub sgor sh+r+ai badz+ra kha t+w+aam ka pra dz+wa la
NK025(ra)001:1956: ya y+aa na mah dmar mo za byed dbang sdud
NK025(ra)001:1957: ma dang / byang sgor sh+r+ai badz+ra g+hen+de pra dz+wa
NK025(ra)001:1958: la ya y+aa na mah nag mo ral gcig rmongs
NK025(ra)001:1959: byed ma rnams gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1960: dkyil 'khor gsum pa'i khyams kyi phyogs bzhir drug drug las shar du ma nu rak+sha s+ai b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:1972: nub tu ra ti tam b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:1974: e ka tsa ra ma b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:1978: byang du m+aa ra na b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:1984: shar sgor ma h+aa k+aa li b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:1985: lho sgor tsa ka li b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:1986: nub sgor bum pa ka la ma b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:1987: byang sgor lam bo d+ha ra b+h+yo rnams las dbang phyug nyer brgyad du gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1988: dkyil 'khor bzhi pa'i khyams la e +aa ra li
NK025(ra)001:1989: h+aum so gnyis kyis mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis
NK025(ra)001:1990: phyogs rer brgyad brgyad du gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1991: dkyil 'khor lnga pa'i khyams la ma ma d+h+aa tu
NK025(ra)001:1992: h+aum bcu gcig gis ma bdun sring bzhi ste shar
NK025(ra)001:1993: lho nub gsum du gnyis gnyis /
NK025(ra)001:1995: sgo bzhir re re gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:1996: dkyil 'khor drug pa'i khyams su ging+ka ra ha ha
NK025(ra)001:1997: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum bco brgyad kyis
NK025(ra)001:1998: ging chen brgyad ni shar nub gnyis la bzhi re
NK025(ra)001:2000: sgo bzhir re re rnams gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:2001: dkyil 'khor bdun pa'i khyams la kro d+ha kro d+hi
NK025(ra)001:2002: h+aum drug cus khro bo khro mo drug cu ni
NK025(ra)001:2003: shar nub tu bcu gnyis re /
NK025(ra)001:2005: shar nub kyi sgor drug re /
NK025(ra)001:2006: lho byang gi sgor bzhi re gsal par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:2007: dkyil 'khor brgyad pa'i khyams la shar du b+ha na b+ha na am ku sha dzahdruga cu /
NK025(ra)001:2008: lhor ha la ha la p+aa sha h+aum drug cu /
NK025(ra)001:2009: nub tu gardza gardza s+pho ta bam drug cu /
NK025(ra)001:2010: byang du pa tsa pa tsa g+han+de hohdruga cu rnams
NK025(ra)001:2011: las pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcur gsal bar gyur
NK025(ra)001:2012: / dkyil 'khor dgu pa'i khyams la ma ma sha
NK025(ra)001:2013: r+ai b+h+yo drug cu las ma mo drug cu ni
NK025(ra)001:2014: phyogs rer bco lnga re gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:2015: dkyil 'khor bcu pa'i khyams la bka' brgyad ni /
NK025(ra)001:2016: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum yang dag dang /
NK025(ra)001:2017: a kro te ka ya m+aan+ta ka ha na ma tha b+ha ny+dza h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:2019: pad+m+aan+ta krita ma h+aa kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai wa hu lu hu lu h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:2021: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aana bam h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:2023: sh+r+ai he ru ka kro d+hi shwa r+ai s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:2024: h+aum ha ha phata ma ma yo g+ai n+ai ru lu b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:2026: +aahh+aum badz+ra sa ma ya ma h+aa gu ru sarba sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:2028: badz+ra tsash+ta sarba dush+tam h+r+aih myags h+r+ai da ya h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:2030: badz+ra sarba dush+tam a mu ka sha trum hri ga
NK025(ra)001:2031: nan myags thum ril hur thum dzahm+aa ra ya rbad
NK025(ra)001:2033: badz+ra ga ru da h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:2034: sarba d+aak+ki ni sa ma ya hring h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:2035: bka' sdod de sgrub chen bka' brgyad bdun brgya nyer lnga'i lha tshogs rnams dang /
NK025(ra)001:2036: gzhan yang 'jig rten lha dang mi'i theg pa /
NK025(ra)001:2041: u pa ya spyod pa'i rgyud /
NK025(ra)001:2042: yo ga rdo rje dbyings rnal 'byor gyi rgyud dang /
NK025(ra)001:2045: rdzogs pa a ti yo ga sogs kyi dkyil 'khor
NK025(ra)001:2046: gyi lha tshogs thams cad mgron thabs kyi tshul du
NK025(ra)001:2047: yongs su rdzogs par gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:2048: spro na de dag gi sngags sam ma brjod kyang rung ngo //
NK025(ra)001:2049: dkyil 'khor bcu gcig pa'i khyams la ma h+aa gu
NK025(ra)001:2050: ru sh+aa ri ram zhes lan mang du brjod pas
NK025(ra)001:2051: / rgyud lung man ngag gi bka' brgyud rig 'dzin
NK025(ra)001:2052: bla ma'i tshogs rnams mngon sum du zhal lam mer
NK025(ra)001:2054: zhi khro gnyis ka la dus gcig tu ye shes lngas dbang bskur /
NK025(ra)001:2055: sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlab /
NK025(ra)001:2056: sa ma dzahs snyan gsan dbab /
NK025(ra)001:2058: dzahh+aum bam hohs gnyis su med par bstim /
NK025(ra)001:2059: kun tu bzang po dang phyag dang zhabs bsil dang lha mo bzhi bsnol gyis mchod /
NK025(ra)001:2060: zhi ba'i lha rnams la su ra has gtor ma phul /
NK025(ra)001:2061: khro bo la dzahh+aum bam hohs dbul /
NK025(ra)001:2062: zhi ba la gsang nan gyi mchod /
NK025(ra)001:2063: khro bo la ra k+ta tshar gsum dbul /
NK025(ra)001:2064: phyogs bcu dus bzhi dang gtum chen gyis bstod /
NK025(ra)001:2065: 'di rnams kyi don zhi khro gnyis ka la thun
NK025(ra)001:2066: mong du ma h+aa shu nya t+aa sogs ye shes
NK025(ra)001:2067: lngas dbang bskur / sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma
NK025(ra)001:2068: h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham
NK025(ra)001:2069: sogs sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab /
NK025(ra)001:2070: badz+ra sa ma ya dzahzhesa snyan gsan dbab /
NK025(ra)001:2071: e h+ye hi b+ha ga wa na ma h+aa k+aa
NK025(ra)001:2072: ru ni ka d+r+ai sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh
NK025(ra)001:2074: zhes zhi khro rab 'byams kyi lha tshogs thams cad mdun gyi nam mkha' spyan drangs te /
NK025(ra)001:2075: dzahh+aum bam hohzhesa gnyis su med par bstim mo //
NK025(ra)001:2076: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK025(ra)001:2077: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i srid pa rgya mtsho kun bzang na mah yang dag don du dag mod kyang //
NK025(ra)001:2078: 'gro ba phyag dang rdo rje'i +aa ha sh+r+ai badz+ra
NK025(ra)001:2079: r+aa ga gan+d+he gan gyi bar zhi bsnol gyis mchod
NK025(ra)001:2080: / zhi ba rnams la gtor ma 'a bul ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:2081: +aahh+aum su ra ha u pa b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:2082: ka ma la m+aa la badz+ra a mri ta ha
NK025(ra)001:2083: ra na pra t+aits+tsha b+ha ga wan dzahh+aum bam hoh
NK025(ra)001:2084: a la la hoh ma h+aa ba ling+ta kha kha
NK025(ra)001:2086: khro bo rnams la dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra i dam d+h+au pe /
NK025(ra)001:2090: ba lin+ta pra t+aits+tsha hoh sh+r+ai ba na kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:2091: zhi ba la gsang nan gyis mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:2092: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam par sbyar ba ni //
NK025(ra)001:2093: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK025(ra)001:2094: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yi rab brgyan te //
NK025(ra)001:2095: dam tshig bzhin las ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:2096: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:2097: khro bo la rak+ta tshar gsum 'bul ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:2098: dzahh+aum bam hohsh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya /
NK025(ra)001:2102: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta /
NK025(ra)001:2103: ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha hoh kha kha kha /
NK025(ra)001:2105: h+aum b+h+yo h+aum b+h+yo h+aum b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:2106: bstod pa ni zhi ba rnams la /
NK025(ra)001:2107: phyogs bcu dus bzhir rdzogs pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:2110: gtum chen dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:2112: sta gon gnas par gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:2114: de nas dril bu gsil zhing /
NK025(ra)001:2115: mgon po thugs rje che ldan pa //
NK025(ra)001:2116: thams cad kun nas dgongs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:2117: deng gi gnas mchog dam pa 'dir //
NK025(ra)001:2118: slob ma rnams kyi don phyir du //
NK025(ra)001:2119: sang gi nang par gdugs bdal nas //
NK025(ra)001:2120: dkyil 'khor chen po bzhengs gsol pas //
NK025(ra)001:2121: sta gon la ni bzhugs nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:2122: byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:2123: zhes pa lha sta gon no //
NK025(ra)001:2124: bar 'dir bum pa sta gon bya ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:2126: de nas gsum pa bum pa sta gon ni bum
NK025(ra)001:2127: pa lnga dkar rtsis byugs pa la rigs lnga'i phyag
NK025(ra)001:2128: mtshan bris pa bla ma'i drung du ras gtsang ma'ikhara
NK025(ra)001:2130: khro bo gsang ba'i bum pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:2131: b+han+d+ha dkar po lcang lo can gnyis dar mthing dmar gyi khud du bzhag la /
NK025(ra)001:2132: de'i nang du rdo rje slob dpon gyis gtso byas
NK025(ra)001:2133: pa'i mched lcam rdo rje'i spun du yod kyi grangs
NK025(ra)001:2134: sman bzang po'i ril bu byas la gzhug go //
NK025(ra)001:2135: zhes gsungs pa'i don ji ltar bya ba ni zhi
NK025(ra)001:2136: bar rin po che'i bum pa lnga mgul chings mthing
NK025(ra)001:2137: dkar ser dmar ljang ba la rdo rje 'khor lo
NK025(ra)001:2138: rin chen pad+ma rgya gram gyis mtshan pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:2139: las bum bcud ldan rgya gram gyis mtshan ma can dar ljang dkris pa kha rgyan dang bcas pa /
NK025(ra)001:2140: khro bo gsang bum ni ka p+aa la kha sbyor lnga ste /
NK025(ra)001:2141: dar mthing dmar gyis rgya gram du bcings pa'i nang
NK025(ra)001:2142: du rtsa bar dpon slob du yod kyi grangs dang
NK025(ra)001:2143: mnyam pa'i sman gyi ril bu gzhug par gsungs shing
NK025(ra)001:2144: / glan ston gyis kyang de ltar gsungs pas /
NK025(ra)001:2145: deng sang phyag bzhes su chos sman rnying pa'i phab
NK025(ra)001:2146: rgyun can gyi bdud rtsi ril bu 'dab btags kyi
NK025(ra)001:2147: phyag len zhib mor byas pa'i ril bu ci 'byor
NK025(ra)001:2148: blugs par mdzad pas gong nas sta gon bya /
NK025(ra)001:2149: slob dpon gyi mdun du bum pa dang so so'i rdzas sogs nyer mkho rnams tshogs par byas te /
NK025(ra)001:2150: gong du lha sta gon gyi khro bo rnams spro
NK025(ra)001:2151: dus che mchog he ru ka'i nga rgyal la gnas
NK025(ra)001:2152: bzhin pas rdo rje dril bu dang bcas h'u mdzad
NK025(ra)001:2155: de nas bden pa bdar ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:2157: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa thams
NK025(ra)001:2158: cad kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las bkod
NK025(ra)001:2159: pa mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bka' bden
NK025(ra)001:2160: pa dang / bden pa yang dag pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:2161: bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs dang /
NK025(ra)001:2162: bcom ldan 'das zhi khro gsang ba mchog gi bka' bden pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:2163: bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK025(ra)001:2164: rnal 'byor pa bdag gi slob ma 'di rnams kyi
NK025(ra)001:2165: don du bum pa lha'i dkyil 'khor du bzhengs par
NK025(ra)001:2166: 'tshal bas / bar du gcod pa'i bgegs dang 'byung
NK025(ra)001:2167: po thams cad 'dir ma gnas par gzhan du dengs
NK025(ra)001:2168: 'tshal bas / shig / h+aum h+aum h+aum bi shwa
NK025(ra)001:2169: badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+da la phata phata phata
NK025(ra)001:2170: ha la ha la h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:2171: ces brjod cing rdo rje thogs te yungs kar gtor bas bgegs thams cad bskrad par bsam mo //
NK025(ra)001:2172: de'i rjes su'ang bgegs kyis mi tshugs pa'i phyir zhi khro'i bum pa thams cad gu gul gyis bdug /
NK025(ra)001:2173: bkra shis pa'i phyir dri zhim po'i spos kyis bdug /
NK025(ra)001:2174: zhi ba'i bum pa lnga'i sum gnyis dri bzang gi
NK025(ra)001:2175: chu la bum rdzas nyer lnga dang chos sman btab
NK025(ra)001:2176: / ku sha dang rma bya'i mdongs /
NK025(ra)001:2177: dbyar dus yin na 'bras bu can gyi shing lo 'bras me tog dang bcas pas kha brgyan /
NK025(ra)001:2178: gzungs thag rdo rje dang dung chos dri bzang gi chus bkang ba steng du bzhag /
NK025(ra)001:2180: gong du bshad pa'i rigs lnga'i mtshan mas brgyan te
NK025(ra)001:2181: slob dpon gyi mdun du stegs la bum gdan pad+ma
NK025(ra)001:2183: dbus su rdo rje dang mgul chings sngon po can /
NK025(ra)001:2184: de bzhin du shar dkar lho ser nub dmar byang ljang ba rnams dang /
NK025(ra)001:2185: byang shar du las bum bkod /
NK025(ra)001:2187: zhi ba'i bum pa'i mdun du stegs la bum gdan
NK025(ra)001:2188: pad+ma 'dab brgyad gong bzhin bris pa'i dbus dang phyogs
NK025(ra)001:2189: bzhir ma thod lnga po nang bum chu'i dod du
NK025(ra)001:2190: bdud rtsi ril bu dang bcas te bzhag /
NK025(ra)001:2191: de dag gi ya thod lnga po re zhig mi 'gebs pas logs su gsar /
NK025(ra)001:2192: zhi khro'i bum pa thun mong du nyer spyod lnga dang sman rag gtor gsum bsham mo //
NK025(ra)001:2193: de nas slob dpon gyis ram yam kham gis zhi khro'i bum pa rnams bsang sbyang /
NK025(ra)001:2194: bum pa bskyed tshul ni rtsa bar /
NK025(ra)001:2195: stong pa'i ngang las rdo rjes mtshan pa'i dbus kyi bum par b+h+r+aum gyi 'phro 'du dang /
NK025(ra)001:2196: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+hesa zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor gdan dang bcas pa bskyed la /
NK025(ra)001:2197: nas sam yungs kar blugs la kun bzang yab yum
NK025(ra)001:2198: dang mi bskyod pa yab yum gyis gtso byas pa'o
NK025(ra)001:2199: // shar du rnam snang gis gtso byas pa'i lha bzhi bcu /
NK025(ra)001:2203: bum rdzas nyer lnga tshang ba'i mgul chings kha rgyan gzungs thag rigs mthun bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:2204: zhes gsungs pas de'i tshul ni /
NK025(ra)001:2205: stong pa'i ngang las zhi ba'i bum pa lnga dang
NK025(ra)001:2206: las bum pad zla'i steng du b+h+r+aum drug las s+pha
NK025(ra)001:2207: ra na phata / sam ha ra na h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:2208: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra s+aur+ya
NK025(ra)001:2209: tsan+d+ra rat+na pad+ma man+dala b+h+aum las phyi bum pa'i rnam
NK025(ra)001:2210: pa la nang zhi ba'i gzhal yas khang gru bzhi
NK025(ra)001:2211: sgo bzhi rgyan rta babs mtshan nyid thams cad yongs
NK025(ra)001:2212: su rdzogs pa'i dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu
NK025(ra)001:2213: khyud glo 'bur lha snam dang bcas pa'i gzhal yas
NK025(ra)001:2214: khang lnga las bum dang bcas par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:2215: dbus kyi bum pa'i lte bar h+aum h+aum h+aum badz+ra tsit+ta /
NK025(ra)001:2216: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa ma n+ta a las kun bzang yab yum du gyur ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:2217: yab zhal gsum phyag drug g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing ba /
NK025(ra)001:2218: phyag dang po gnyis byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya
NK025(ra)001:2219: yum kun tu bzang mo sngon mo la 'khyud pa
NK025(ra)001:2220: / bar pa gnyis kyis rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2221: tha ma gnyis mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya mdzad pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:2223: shar gyi bum pa'i shar rtsibs /
NK025(ra)001:2224: lho yi bum pa'i lho rtsibs /
NK025(ra)001:2225: nub kyi bum pa'i nub rtsibs /
NK025(ra)001:2226: byang gi bum pa'i byang rtsibs rnams la h+aum badz+ra d+h+rika /
NK025(ra)001:2227: m+aum d+h+aa t+wi shwa r+ai las mi bskyod pa yab
NK025(ra)001:2228: yum zhal gsum phyag drug g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus
NK025(ra)001:2229: mthing ba / g.yas gsum rdo rje 'khor lo rin po che /
NK025(ra)001:2230: g.yon gsum dril bu pad+ma ral gri 'dzin pa yum dbyings phyug ma sngon mo dang sbyor ba'o //
NK025(ra)001:2235: byang gsum gyi shar rtsibs rnams la dz+ai na dzika /
NK025(ra)001:2236: l+aam dwe sha ra ti la rnam par snang mdzad
NK025(ra)001:2237: sku mdog dkar po zhal gsum phyag drug g.yas sngon
NK025(ra)001:2239: g.yas gsum na 'khor lo rdo rje rin chen /
NK025(ra)001:2240: g.yon gsum dril bu pad+ma rgya gram 'dzin pas yum
NK025(ra)001:2241: sangs rgyas spyan ma dkar mo dang gnyis su med
NK025(ra)001:2245: byang gsum gyi bum pa'i lho rtsibs dang /
NK025(ra)001:2246: lho'i bum pa'i dbus su s+w+aa rat+na d+h+rika /
NK025(ra)001:2247: m+aam mo ha ra ti las rin 'byung ser po
NK025(ra)001:2248: zhal gsum phyag drug g.yas sngo g.yon dmar dbus ser
NK025(ra)001:2249: ba / g.yas gsum rin po che /
NK025(ra)001:2252: g.yon gsum dril bu pad+ma rgya gram 'dzin pa yum m+aa ma k+ai dang gnyis su med pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:2253: nub kyi bum pa'i dbus dang /
NK025(ra)001:2257: byang bzhi'i nub rtsibs la +aamha ro lika /
NK025(ra)001:2258: p+y+aam r+aa ga ra ti las snang ba mtha' yas dmar po zhal gsum phyag drug /
NK025(ra)001:2259: g.yas ser g.yon ljang dbus dmar pa /
NK025(ra)001:2260: g.yas gsum pad+ma rdo rje 'khor lo /
NK025(ra)001:2261: g.yon gsum dril bu rin chen rgya gram 'dzin pa yum gos dkar mo dang gnyis su med pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:2265: nub bzhi'i bum pa'i byang rtsibs dang /
NK025(ra)001:2266: byang gi bum pa'i dbus su h+aa pra dz+ny+aa d+h+rika /
NK025(ra)001:2267: t+aam badz+ra ra ti las don yod grub pa ljang
NK025(ra)001:2268: gu zhal gsum phyag drug g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus
NK025(ra)001:2269: ljang ba / g.yas gsum ral gri rdo rje 'khor lo /
NK025(ra)001:2270: g.yon gsum dril bu rin chen pad+ma 'dzin pa yum dam tshig sgrol ma dang gnyis su med pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:2271: bum pa lnga ka'i shar lho'i gong ras la k+shi hi r+aa dza ya /
NK025(ra)001:2272: h+aum l+aa s+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam las sa snying dkar po g.yas rin po che'i myu gu /
NK025(ra)001:2273: g.yon dril bu da kur brten pa yum sgeg mo dkar mo me long 'dziin pa dang 'khril ba'o //
NK025(ra)001:2274: lho nub kyi gong ras la tram a gar+b+ha ya /
NK025(ra)001:2275: tram m+aa le sa ma ya hohls nam mkha'i snying po sngon po g.yas ral gri g.yon dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:2276: yum phreng ba ma sngon mo phreng ba 'dzin pa dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:2277: nub byang gi gong ras la h+r+aihpad+ma pa da ma /
NK025(ra)001:2278: h+r+aihg+ai ti ra ho ham las spyan ras gzigs dmar po g.yas pad+ma g.yon dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:2279: yum g+ai ti ma dmar mo pi wang 'dzin pa dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:2280: byang shar gyi gong ras la dz+rim ku ru pan+na
NK025(ra)001:2281: h+r+aih a n+air+t+ya r+aa ga ya mi las phyag rdor
NK025(ra)001:2282: ljang gu g.yas rdo rje dang g.yon dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:2283: yum gar ma ljang gu gar bsgyur ba dang 'khril ba'o //
NK025(ra)001:2284: shar lho'i glo 'bur la mee d+ha ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:2285: dzahd+h+au pe pra be sha las byams pa dkar ser g.yas glu shing dang g.yon dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:2286: yum spos ma dkar ser spos khang 'dzin pa dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:2287: lho nub kyi glo 'bur la th+l+him nis+sa ram pa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:2288: h+aum push+pe a be sha las sgrib pa rnam sel ljang gu g.yas ut+pala dang g.yon dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:2289: yum me tog ma ljang gu me tog 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:2290: nub byang gi glo 'bur la h+aum sa r+aa dza ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:2291: bam d+ai pa su khi n+ai las kun bzang dmar
NK025(ra)001:2292: skya g.yas rin po che'i snye ma g.yon dril bu
NK025(ra)001:2293: / yum mar me dmar skya mar me'i sdong bu 'dzin pa dang 'khril ba'o //
NK025(ra)001:2294: byang shar gyi glo 'bur la m+aum sh+r+ai a ram ga ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:2295: hohgan+d+he tsit+ta las 'jam dpal dmar ser g.yas ral gri dang g.yon dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:2296: yum dri chab ma dmar ser dri'i dung chos 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:2297: gtso 'khor thams cad longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dar
NK025(ra)001:2298: dang rin po che'i rgyan sna tshogs kyis brgyan pa'o
NK025(ra)001:2299: // bum pa lnga ka'i lha snam gyi shar lhor
NK025(ra)001:2300: mu ne krem s+w+aa h+aa las lha'i thub par brgya
NK025(ra)001:2301: byin dkar po pi wang bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:2302: lha snam gyi byang du mu ne h+aum trum s+w+aa
NK025(ra)001:2303: h+aa las lha min thub pa mthing kha go mtshon
NK025(ra)001:2304: bsnams pa / lha snam gyi lhor mu ne srum
NK025(ra)001:2305: s+w+aa h+aa las mi'i thub pa ser po gseg shang
NK025(ra)001:2307: lha snam gyi nub byang du mu ne bram s+w+aa
NK025(ra)001:2308: h+aa las byol song thub pa ser nag glegs bam
NK025(ra)001:2309: 'dzin pa / lha snam gyi lho nub tu mu
NK025(ra)001:2310: ne k+sham s+w+aa h+aa las yi dwags kyi thub pa
NK025(ra)001:2312: lha snam gyi byang shar du mu ne ye s+w+aa
NK025(ra)001:2313: h+aa las dmyal ba'i thub pa dud kha me chu
NK025(ra)001:2314: 'dzin pa ste drug ka yang sprul sku chags bral
NK025(ra)001:2315: gyi rnam pa can bzhengs pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:2316: shar sgor h+aum ya m+aan+ta krita phata /
NK025(ra)001:2317: ma h+aa badz+ra d+h+aa ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa
NK025(ra)001:2318: r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata las gshin rje gshed
NK025(ra)001:2319: smug nag thod dbyug dang sdigs mdzub can yum lcags
NK025(ra)001:2320: kyu ma smug nag lcags kyu dang thod khrag 'dzin
NK025(ra)001:2321: pa'o // lho sgor h+aum pradz+ny+aan+ta krota phata /
NK025(ra)001:2322: ma h+aa rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa las stobs po
NK025(ra)001:2323: che ser nag rdo rje dang sdigs mdzub can yum
NK025(ra)001:2324: zhags pa ma ser mo zhags pa dang thod khrag
NK025(ra)001:2325: 'dzin pa'o // nub sgor h+aum pad+m+aan+ta krita phata /
NK025(ra)001:2326: ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ra las rta mgrin dmar nag
NK025(ra)001:2327: rta mgo can thod dbyug sprul gyis dkris pa dang
NK025(ra)001:2328: sdigs mdzub can yum lcags sgrog ma dmar mo lcags
NK025(ra)001:2330: byang sgor h+aum big+h+n+aan+ta krita phata /
NK025(ra)001:2331: ma h+aa karma d+ha ra las bdud rtsi 'khyil pa
NK025(ra)001:2332: ljang nag rgya gram dang sdigs mdzad can yum dril
NK025(ra)001:2333: bu ma ljang gu dril bu dang thod khrag 'dzin
NK025(ra)001:2334: pa'o // de dag kyang khro bo'i rgyan gyis brgyan cing me dpung 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:2335: de nas gzhung gi dgongs pa ltar bum pa lnga
NK025(ra)001:2336: po'i nang du dbus kyi bum par kun bzang yab
NK025(ra)001:2337: yum gnyis bsnan te zhi ba zhe gnyis dang /
NK025(ra)001:2338: gzhan rnams la gtso bo go 'pho zhing kun bzang
NK025(ra)001:2339: yab yum gnyis med pa'i zhi ba bzhi bcu ste
NK025(ra)001:2340: / nas sam yungs kar dbus su 'bru zhe gnyis /
NK025(ra)001:2342: de dag 'bru re re bzhin so so'i sngags dang bcas bum par blug go //
NK025(ra)001:2343: 'dir nas sam yungs kar blug pa de rnams chus
NK025(ra)001:2344: bangs te mchu 'gags pa sogs kyi nyes dmigs 'dug
NK025(ra)001:2345: pas dar ram ras gtsang mar thum bu byas te
NK025(ra)001:2346: bum nang du bcug pa ni lag len gyi khyad
NK025(ra)001:2347: par 'jug pa bde ba'i gnad do //
NK025(ra)001:2348: de nas khro bo'i bum pa rnams sgrub tshul ni bsang sbyang thun mong du grub /
NK025(ra)001:2349: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum s+pha ra na phata /
NK025(ra)001:2351: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra tsakra dz+ny+aa na s+aur+ya
NK025(ra)001:2352: tsan+d+ra pad+ma man+da la de wa ti ra nan du
NK025(ra)001:2353: ti tsakra nan ti ra bam /
NK025(ra)001:2354: b+han+d+ha lnga po phyi b+han+d+ha la nang khro bo'i gzhal
NK025(ra)001:2355: yas khang mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa
NK025(ra)001:2356: lnga dang / khyad par dbus kyi b+han+d+ha khro bo'i
NK025(ra)001:2357: gzhal yas khang sgo sbrags bcu gcig dang ldan pa
NK025(ra)001:2359: khro bo gsang bum dbus ma'i lte bar a kra ma h+aa kro d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:2360: ka ta ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:2361: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum las che mchog
NK025(ra)001:2362: he ru ka dbu nyer gcig phyag zhe gnyis kyis
NK025(ra)001:2363: zhi ba zhe gnyis bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:2364: zhabs brgyad kyis yum gnam zhal ma'i dbu brgyad bardzisa shing /
NK025(ra)001:2365: dbus zhal la gsang rdor bcug pa /
NK025(ra)001:2366: phyag bco brgyad kyi g.yas brgyad khro mo brgyad g.yon
NK025(ra)001:2367: brgyad phra men brgyad bsnams pa zhabs brgyad dang bcas
NK025(ra)001:2368: pa dur khrod kyi chas brgyad dang dpal gyi chas
NK025(ra)001:2369: bcus brgyan te me dpung 'bar ba'i dbus na gar
NK025(ra)001:2371: de'i mdun du sarba ta th+aa ga ta sh+r+ai he
NK025(ra)001:2372: ru ka sarba ta th+aa ga ta kro d+hi shwa
NK025(ra)001:2373: r+ai h+aum zhes pas bcom ldan 'das dbang mchog he
NK025(ra)001:2374: ru ka dbu dgu'i dang po gsum g.yas dkar g.yon
NK025(ra)001:2376: bar pa gsum g.yas sngon g.yon ljang dbus mthing ba /
NK025(ra)001:2377: rtsa zhal 'og ma gsum dang sku mthing kha /
NK025(ra)001:2378: phyag bco brgyad kyi g.yas dgu na rdo rje /
NK025(ra)001:2386: lbu ba ste thod pa'i ga'u 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2395: ri rab rnams 'dzin zhing zhabs gnyis 'dor stabs su bgrad pa /
NK025(ra)001:2396: yum zhal gcig phyag gnyis rdo rje thod khrag 'dzin pa dang 'khril ba'o //
NK025(ra)001:2398: shar gyi khro bo gsang bum gyi shar rtsibs /
NK025(ra)001:2399: lho'i gsang bum gyi lho rtsibs /
NK025(ra)001:2400: nub kyi gsang bum gyi nub rtsibs /
NK025(ra)001:2401: byang gi gsang bum gyi byang rtsibs rnams la badz+ra
NK025(ra)001:2402: sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum
NK025(ra)001:2403: las rdo rje khrag 'thung mthing kha zhal gsum phyag
NK025(ra)001:2404: drug g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus sngo ba /
NK025(ra)001:2410: thong gshol 'dzin pa rdo rje khro mo dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba'o //
NK025(ra)001:2414: byang bzhi'i gsang bum gyi shar rtsibs dang /
NK025(ra)001:2415: shar gyi gsang bum gyi dbus su bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he
NK025(ra)001:2416: ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum las sangs
NK025(ra)001:2417: rgyas khrag 'thung smug nag smug dkar dmar ba'i zhal
NK025(ra)001:2418: gsum phyag drug g.yas gsum 'khor lo /
NK025(ra)001:2423: mi mgo 'dzin pa yum sangs rgyas khro mo dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba'o //
NK025(ra)001:2427: byang bzhi'i gsang bum gyi lho rtsibs dang /
NK025(ra)001:2428: lho'i gsang bum gyi dbus su rat+na sh+r+ai he ru
NK025(ra)001:2429: ka rat+na kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum las rin chen
NK025(ra)001:2430: las rin chen khrag 'thung ser sngo dmar ba'i zhal
NK025(ra)001:2431: gsum phyag drug g.yas gsum rin chen /
NK025(ra)001:2436: ri rab bsnams pa yum rin chen khro mo dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba'o //
NK025(ra)001:2440: byang bzhi'i gsang bum gyi nub rtsibs dang /
NK025(ra)001:2441: nub kyi gsang bum dbus su pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru
NK025(ra)001:2442: ka pad+ma kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum las pad+ma khrag
NK025(ra)001:2443: 'thung dmar dkar sngo ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi
NK025(ra)001:2449: 'jig rten 'degs pa yum pad+ma khro mo dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba'o //
NK025(ra)001:2454: byang gi bum pa'i dbus su karma sh+r+ai he ru
NK025(ra)001:2455: ka h+aum karma kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum las las
NK025(ra)001:2456: kyi khrag 'thung ljang dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag
NK025(ra)001:2457: drug gi g.yas gsum rgya gram /
NK025(ra)001:2462: zhags pa 'dzin pa yum las kyi khrag 'thung dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba'o //
NK025(ra)001:2463: khro bo gsang bum dbus ma'i shar lho'i rtsibs la
NK025(ra)001:2464: rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka rak+sha kro d+hi shwa r+ai
NK025(ra)001:2465: h+aum las srin po khrag 'thung mthing dkar dmar pa'i
NK025(ra)001:2466: zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas gsum rdo rje /
NK025(ra)001:2472: yum srin mo khro mo dang 'khril ba'o //
NK025(ra)001:2473: lho nub kyi rtsibs la sa nu sh+r+ai he ru
NK025(ra)001:2474: ka sa nu kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum las sa
NK025(ra)001:2475: nu khrag 'thung ser dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag
NK025(ra)001:2476: drug gi g.yas gsum rdo rje /
NK025(ra)001:2482: yum sa nu khro mo mthing nag dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba'o //
NK025(ra)001:2483: nub byang gi rtsibs la gu h+ya sh+r+ai he ru
NK025(ra)001:2484: ka gu h+ya kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum las gsang
NK025(ra)001:2485: ba'i khro bo dud kha dud dkar dmar ba'i zhal
NK025(ra)001:2486: gsum phyag drug gi g.yas gsum gri gug /
NK025(ra)001:2492: yum gsang ba'i khro mo dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba'o //
NK025(ra)001:2493: byang shar gyi rtsibs la yak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka
NK025(ra)001:2494: yak+sha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum las gnod sbyin khro
NK025(ra)001:2495: bo ljang dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi
NK025(ra)001:2502: yum gnod sbyin khro mo dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba'o //
NK025(ra)001:2503: gsang bum lnga ga'i 'khor lo'i phyir glo 'bur la badz+ra goo r+ai ha /
NK025(ra)001:2510: badz+ra tsan+da l+ai ha las shar du goo r+ai sngon mo zhing dbyug dang b+han+d+ha /
NK025(ra)001:2511: lhor tsoo r+ai ma ser mo mda' gzhu 'geng ba /
NK025(ra)001:2512: nub tu pra mo ha dmar mo chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan 'phyar ba /
NK025(ra)001:2513: byang du bet+ta l+ai nag mo rdo rje bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:2514: shar lhor puk+ka s+ai dmar ser byis pa'i rgyu ma 'dren pa /
NK025(ra)001:2515: lho nub tu g+hasma r+ai ljang nag b+han dmar /
NK025(ra)001:2516: nub byang du sma sha n+ai nag mo snying za ba /
NK025(ra)001:2517: byang shar du tsan+da l+ai ser skya bam ro'i mgo lus 'dral ba'o //
NK025(ra)001:2518: dbus kyi gsang bum khro bo'i gzhal yas khang sgo sbrags bcu gcig gi khyams dang po dang /
NK025(ra)001:2519: phyogs bzhi'i gsang bum gyi khyams la badz+ra sid+ha mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:2520: badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:2521: badz+ra sring+ga la mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:2522: badz+ra shwa na mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:2523: badz+ra gri d+ha mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:2524: badz+ra kam ka mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:2525: badz+ra k+aa ka mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:2526: badz+ra u lu ka mu kha he rnams las /
NK025(ra)001:2527: shar du seng gdong ser mo ro za ba /
NK025(ra)001:2528: lhor stag gdong dmar mo lag gnyis mthur du bsnol ba /
NK025(ra)001:2529: nub tu sri la nag mo byis pa'i ro bldag pa /
NK025(ra)001:2530: byang du shwa na sngon mo ro la 'bru tshugs su blta ba /
NK025(ra)001:2531: shar lhor gri d+ha dmar mo rgod mgo rgyu ma 'dren pa /
NK025(ra)001:2532: lho nub tu kam ka dmar nag mi ro phrag la bkal ba /
NK025(ra)001:2533: nub byang du k+aa ka nag mo bya rog gdong gri thod thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:2534: byang shar du u lu ma mthing nag 'ug gdong rdo rje'i dbyug pa thogs pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:2535: dbus kyi gsang bum gzhal yas khang bcu gcig gi sgo dang po bzhi dang /
NK025(ra)001:2536: phyogs bzhi'i gsang bum gyi sgo bzhir /
NK025(ra)001:2537: shar du badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dzahls rta gdong dkar mo lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2538: lho sgor badz+ra a mu kh+aa h+aum las phag gdog ser mo zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2539: nub sgor badz+ra lo ka bam las seng gdong dmar mo lcags sgrog thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:2540: byang sgor badz+ra b+hasmi pa la ya ba to hohls spyang gdong ljang nag dril bu 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:2541: khro bo gsang bum dbus ma'i gzhal yas khang gnyis
NK025(ra)001:2542: pa'i khyams kyi phyogs mtshams brgyad du badz+ra a pra
NK025(ra)001:2543: ti ha +aar+ya ni tsa tur ta ra phata /
NK025(ra)001:2545: shar du 'bar ma nyi zhags can dmar mo nyi zer gyi zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2546: shar lhor me khyer ma dmar mo glo zhags 'phen pa /
NK025(ra)001:2547: lhor skar mda' 'phen sngon mo g.yas mdung thung dang g.yon skar mda' 'phen pa /
NK025(ra)001:2548: lho nub tu ral gri'i skra can ma sngo nag khyung khra 'gyed pa /
NK025(ra)001:2549: nub tu lce 'bebs ma dkar mo thog 'bebs pa /
NK025(ra)001:2550: nub byang du khyung thogs ma sngoon mo khyung thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:2551: byang du ba lang gdong sngo nag glang chen gdong thog ser 'bebs pa /
NK025(ra)001:2552: byang shar du mig 'byin snying sreg ma thal kar klag+sha sdeb pa ste ral gri 'phyar ba'o //
NK025(ra)001:2553: gzhal yas khang gnyis pa'i shar sgor sh+r+ai badz+ra mung+ga
NK025(ra)001:2554: ra mu kha shwa ra ya na mahls dkar mo
NK025(ra)001:2555: mig gcig rgyas 'debs ma dkar mo rdo rje bsnams
NK025(ra)001:2556: pa / lho sgor sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga ma shwa
NK025(ra)001:2557: ra ya y+aa na mahls ser mo las mkhan tshe
NK025(ra)001:2558: 'phel ma ser mo mda' gzhu 'geng ba /
NK025(ra)001:2559: nub sgor sh+r+ai badz+ra kha t+w+aam ga pra dz+wa la
NK025(ra)001:2560: ya y+aa na mahls dmar mo za byed dbang sdud
NK025(ra)001:2561: ma dmar mo rgyal mtshan bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:2562: byang sgor badz+ra g+han+de pra dz+wa la ya y+aa na
NK025(ra)001:2563: mahls nag mo ral gcig rmongs byed ma ljang nag
NK025(ra)001:2565: khro bo gsang bum dbus ma'i dkyil 'khor gsum pa'i
NK025(ra)001:2566: khyams dang phyogs bzhi'i gsang bum gyi phyi khams la
NK025(ra)001:2567: b+h+yo nyer brgyad las dbang mo nyer brgyad ni /
NK025(ra)001:2568: shar du srin mo dmar ser g.yag gdong rtse gsum 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2569: tshangs ma dmar mo sprul gdong pad+ma 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2570: khro mo dmar ser gzig mgo dbyug to dang snying 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2571: khyab 'jug ma ser mo pha wang gdong 'khor lo dang dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2572: dbang mo dkar dmar sre mo'i gdong 'khor lo dang thod khrag 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2573: gzhon nu dmar mo dred mgo bam dbyug dang thod khrag 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:2574: lhor zhi ba dmar mo dom mgo rdo rje dang thod khrag 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2575: bdud rtsi ma sngon mo chu srin mgo bum pa 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2576: zhi ba mo sngo skya sdig pa'i mgo g.yas thod pa bam ril dang g.yon bam 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2577: be con nag mo khra mgo thod rlon 'chang ba /
NK025(ra)001:2578: srin mo dmar nag wa gdong zhing gi rgyu ma 'dren pa /
NK025(ra)001:2579: za byed nag mo stag mgo bam snying 'byin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2580: nub tu dga' ba dmar mo rgod mgo thod khrag 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2581: khrag 'thung dmar nag rta gdong rdor dbyug dang b+han+d+ha 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2582: rdo rje ser mo khyung gdong rdo rje dang b+han+d+ha 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2583: 'dod pa dmar ser khyi mgo zhing chen za ba /
NK025(ra)001:2584: nor srung dkar dmar pu shud mgo pad+ma 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2585: rlung mo sha ba'i mgo can dmar skya bam ro 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:2586: byang du gsod byed ma ljang nag spyang gdong thod rnga 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2587: me mo dmar mo skyin mgo ste 'brong gi mgo can me sgron 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2588: phag mo ljang ser phag gdong rtse gsum 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2589: rgan byed ljang sngon khra mgo bam gyi rgyu ma 'dren pa /
NK025(ra)001:2590: sna chen ljang dmar glang gdong bam ro 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2591: chu lha ljang nag sbrul gdong bum pa 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:2592: shar sgor khu byug gdong nag mo lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2593: lho sgor ra gdong sngon mo rgyu zhags bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:2594: nub sgor seng gdong dmar mo lcags sgrog 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:2595: byang sgor skya ka'i mgo can ljang nag dril bu 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:2596: 'di yan gyi phyoogs bzhi'i khro bo gsang bum gyi lha rdzogs pas shar du bud+d+ha he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:2598: nub tu pad+ma he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:2599: byang du karma he ru ka ste gtso bo rnams go 'pho zhing /
NK025(ra)001:2600: gzhan bzhi ka la lha tshogs kyi grangs ni khrag 'thung rigs lnga yab yum /
NK025(ra)001:2604: dbang mo nyer brgyad de khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa
NK025(ra)001:2605: brgyad tshang bar bzhed pas bum pa so sor yungs
NK025(ra)001:2606: kar 'bru nga brgyad la 'bru re re bzhin khrag
NK025(ra)001:2607: 'thung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad kyi so so'i snying po
NK025(ra)001:2608: bzlas te blugs dgos pa snga ma zhi ba'i skabs
NK025(ra)001:2609: ltar thum bu bcug pa legs so //
NK025(ra)001:2610: dbus kyi khro bo gsang bum gyi dkyil 'khor bzhi
NK025(ra)001:2611: ba'i khyams la e a ral+li h+aum las mkha' 'gro
NK025(ra)001:2613: dkyil 'khor lnga pa'i khyams la ma ma d+h+aa tu h+aum las ma bdun sring bzhi /
NK025(ra)001:2614: dkyil 'khor drug pa'i khyams la ging+ka ra ha ha
NK025(ra)001:2615: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum las ging chen
NK025(ra)001:2616: bco brgyad / dkyil 'khor bdun pa'i khyams la kro
NK025(ra)001:2617: d+ha kro d+hi h+aum las khro bo khro mo drug
NK025(ra)001:2618: bco brgyad / cu / dkyil 'khor brgyad pa'i khyams
NK025(ra)001:2619: la shar du b+ha na b+ha na am ku sha
NK025(ra)001:2620: dzahls dung gi mi mo drug cu /
NK025(ra)001:2621: lhor ha la ha la p+aa sha h+aum las lcags kyi mi mo drug cu /
NK025(ra)001:2622: nub tu gardza gardza s+pho ta bam las zangs kyi mi mo drug cu /
NK025(ra)001:2623: byang du pa tsa pa tsa g+han+de hohls g.yu'i mi
NK025(ra)001:2624: mo drug cu ste pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu
NK025(ra)001:2625: / dkyil 'khor dgu pa'i khyams la ma ma sha r+ai b+h+yo las ma mo drug cu /
NK025(ra)001:2626: dkyil 'khor bcu pa'i khyams la lha mi nyan rang
NK025(ra)001:2627: byang sems bya spyod rnal 'byor yo ga gsum gyi
NK025(ra)001:2628: lha tshogs te bka' brgyad theg dgu'i lha rnams dang
NK025(ra)001:2629: / dkyil 'khor bcu gcig pa'i khyams la ma h+aa
NK025(ra)001:2630: gu ru sh+aa r+ai ram las yo ga gsum gyi
NK025(ra)001:2631: rig 'dzin bla ma'i tshogs rnams gsal bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:2632: zhes khyams bzhi pa man chad mos bskyed kyis 'thus par sems /
NK025(ra)001:2633: mngon rtogs rgyas par spro na 'og gi mdun bskyed skabs nas blang ngo //
NK025(ra)001:2634: de ltar lha tshogs de rnams kyang dur khrod kyi
NK025(ra)001:2635: chas kyis brgyan cing gar dgu'i nyams ldan ye shes
NK025(ra)001:2636: kyi me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na brkyang bskum gar
NK025(ra)001:2637: gyis rol pa'o // las bum phyi dur khrod 'bar
NK025(ra)001:2638: ba nang rin po che'i gzhal yas khang gi nang
NK025(ra)001:2639: du ma s+aur+ya man+da las nyi ma'i steng du h+aum
NK025(ra)001:2640: ljang gu'i 'phro 'du las bdud rtsi 'khyil pa ljang
NK025(ra)001:2641: gu g.yas rgya gram dang g.yon dril bu thogs pa
NK025(ra)001:2642: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis brgyan par gyur
NK025(ra)001:2643: gyis rol pa'o // / khro bo gsang bum dbus
NK025(ra)001:2644: mar ma bdun sring bzhi yan nam lha lnga brgya
NK025(ra)001:2645: brgyad cu rtsa gnyis bskyed pa 'dam khar gsungs pa
NK025(ra)001:2646: gyis rol pa'o // / / 'dir phyir ma'i lugs
NK025(ra)001:2647: yin pas yungs kar lnga brgya brgyad cu rtsa gnyis
NK025(ra)001:2648: la 'bru re re bzhin lha so so'i snying po
NK025(ra)001:2650: khro bo gsang bum lnga por bdud rtsi ril bu
NK025(ra)001:2651: blugs pa'i dbang du byas na lha grangs kyi yungs
NK025(ra)001:2652: kar rnams thum bu ma byas kyang chog la /
NK025(ra)001:2653: yang na bdud rtsi chang phud kyis bkang ste kha
NK025(ra)001:2654: bcad par gsungs pa ltar na yungs kar rnams thum
NK025(ra)001:2656: de nas khro bo gsang bum lnga po bdud rtsi
NK025(ra)001:2657: skam rlon gang yin kyang thod kyis zhal bcad de
NK025(ra)001:2658: dar mthing dmar gyis rgya gram du bcings te bum
NK025(ra)001:2662: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las 'dus pa chen po'i
NK025(ra)001:2663: gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa bskyed la gtso
NK025(ra)001:2664: bo nas ma bdun sring bzhi yan chad bum pa'i
NK025(ra)001:2665: nang du yungs kar blug cing sngags kyis rdzogs par
NK025(ra)001:2666: bskyed / lnga tshan nyer lnga'i rdzas dang 'bru bcud
NK025(ra)001:2667: phud tshang bar blug pa'i khar rdo rje bzhag la
NK025(ra)001:2668: gzungs thag btags te thod pa gcig gis kha bcad
NK025(ra)001:2669: bskyed / / dar sna lngas bkab la bzhag go //
NK025(ra)001:2670: yang na zhi ba'i bum pa lnga po rigs lnga dang /
NK025(ra)001:2671: khro bo'i bum pa b+han+d+ha mtshan ldan la rigs lnga
NK025(ra)001:2672: so so'i thugs phyag mtshan bris la dbus su che
NK025(ra)001:2673: mchog gis gtso byas pa'i lha lnga brgya brgyad cu
NK025(ra)001:2674: rtsa gnyis dang / rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang thams cad tshang bar bskyed /
NK025(ra)001:2675: rigs bzhi'i bum pa la rigs rang rang gi gtso
NK025(ra)001:2676: byas pa'i lha lnga bcu rtsa brgyad po bskyed cing
NK025(ra)001:2677: rdzas tshangs bar blugs la phyogs bzhi'i dbus su dgod
NK025(ra)001:2678: / many+dzi'i khar ka p+aa la lngar bdud rtsi blug /
NK025(ra)001:2679: ces gsungs pa'i don yin no //
NK025(ra)001:2681: lha la ye shes lngas dbang bskur /
NK025(ra)001:2687: kun bzang gi mchod pa lnga dbul /
NK025(ra)001:2689: zhi khro'i bum pa thun mong du sh+au nya t+aa sogs rigs lngas dbang bskur /
NK025(ra)001:2690: k+aa ya badz+ra sogs kyis sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab /
NK025(ra)001:2691: badz+ra sa ma dzahs rdo rje bsdu ba'i phyag rgya dang bcas te snyan gsan dbab /
NK025(ra)001:2692: e h+ye hi b+ha ga wan ma h+aa k+aa ru
NK025(ra)001:2693: ni k+aa dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh sa
NK025(ra)001:2694: ma ya s+t+wam / zhes zhi ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:2695: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:2696: e h+ye hi +aa na ya zhes khro bo rnams spyan drangs /
NK025(ra)001:2697: thun mong du dzahh+aum bam hoh badz+ra am ku sha dzah badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:2700: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra gyis brtan par byas /
NK025(ra)001:2701: a ti pu hoh pra t+aits+tsha hohs phyag btsal /
NK025(ra)001:2702: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK025(ra)001:2703: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i srid pa rgya mtsho kun bzang na mah yang dag don du dag mod kyang //
NK025(ra)001:2704: 'gro ba phyag dang rdo rje'i +aa ha ra sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga gan+d+he'i bar gyis mchod /
NK025(ra)001:2706: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri tas sman mchod dbul /
NK025(ra)001:2707: ma h+aa ba ling+ta kh+aa his gtor ma dbul /
NK025(ra)001:2708: ma h+aa rak+ta kh+aa his khrag dbul /
NK025(ra)001:2709: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:2710: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK025(ra)001:2712: dkyil 'khor kun la rgyas par 'bul gyi bar dang /
NK025(ra)001:2713: skal ldan gsal ba'i khyad par gyis //
NK025(ra)001:2714: rim mam yang na cig car du //
NK025(ra)001:2715: chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam sbyor zhing //
NK025(ra)001:2716: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen por bsgom //
NK025(ra)001:2717: a la la ste mchod par 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:2718: a la la ste bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:2721: ri rab chen po'i gling bzhi na //
NK025(ra)001:2722: gnas pa'i sems can thams cad kun //
NK025(ra)001:2723: ye shes me chen bsgom byas te //
NK025(ra)001:2724: thams cad ma lus bsreg par bya //
NK025(ra)001:2726: srid gsum bsreg pa'i me chen te //
NK025(ra)001:2727: yid kyi ye shes me ru 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:2730: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:2731: pad+ma la ni rdo rje zhugs //
NK025(ra)001:2732: 'khril ba'i mchod chen mnyam sbyor bas //
NK025(ra)001:2733: bdag nyid mnyes pas mnyes par bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:2734: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:2735: a nu r+aa ga ya mi /
NK025(ra)001:2736: dzahh+aum bam hoh h+aum h+aum h+aum bo d+hi tsit+ta /
NK025(ra)001:2737: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa p+au dza badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:2738: zhes pas lhag pa ting nge 'dzin dang sbyor sgrol gyi mchod pa 'bul /
NK025(ra)001:2740: gtum chen gyis sngar bzhin bstod /
NK025(ra)001:2741: de nas zhi ba dang khro bo gsang bum gyi gzungs thag g.yon pas bzung /
NK025(ra)001:2743: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:2745: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:2747: las bum dang +aahbig+h+n+aan+ta krita a mri ta kun+da li ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:2748: ces sogs brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas shing /
NK025(ra)001:2750: bdag gi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros rdo rje la phog /
NK025(ra)001:2751: rdo rje las 'od 'phros bum pa'i nang gi lha la thim /
NK025(ra)001:2752: thugs rgyud bskul klad pa dung khang du song /
NK025(ra)001:2753: sgal tshigs nas brgyud rdo rjee nas yum gyi mkhar babs /
NK025(ra)001:2754: sbyor ba byas yum gyi zhal nas byung /
NK025(ra)001:2756: srog dag pa'i lam nas byung /
NK025(ra)001:2757: sgal tshigs nas brgyud de yum gyi mkhar babs sbyor
NK025(ra)001:2758: mtshams nas bdud rtsi'i rgyun babs pas bum pa gang
NK025(ra)001:2759: bar bsam zhing / ta pa la te ma ma he he pa ta la h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:2760: zhes brjod pas lha tshogs bdud rtsir zhu bum ba gang bas kyang /
NK025(ra)001:2761: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs
NK025(ra)001:2762: yon tan phrin las lnga'i ngo bor rdzogs par bsam
NK025(ra)001:2764: gsal ldan ma'am byin brlabs la //
NK025(ra)001:2765: stong gsum yungs 'brur gzhug tshul du //
NK025(ra)001:2766: dbyings nas dkyil 'khor spyan drangs mchod //
NK025(ra)001:2767: mnyes nas grub pa'i dam tshig mchog /
NK025(ra)001:2768: bdag nyid chen po mchod pa yis //
NK025(ra)001:2769: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor ma lus mnyes //
NK025(ra)001:2770: srid gsum 'gro ba thams cad la //
NK025(ra)001:2771: dga' ba chen pos khyab par 'gyur //
NK025(ra)001:2772: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba brtan pa yis //
NK025(ra)001:2773: phyogs bcu dus bzhir gshegs pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:2774: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor ma lus dang //
NK025(ra)001:2778: zhi ba'i bum pa dbus dang phyogs bzhir bzhag /
NK025(ra)001:2779: dbus kyi bum pa'i steng du thod pa dum bu
NK025(ra)001:2780: gcig pa'i nang du 'bru bcud kyi phud blug la
NK025(ra)001:2781: bdud rtsi btab pa'i khar rdo rje bzhag la zhi
NK025(ra)001:2783: bdag gi thugs ka nas 'od 'phros nas b+han+d+ha bdud rtsis gang ba'i bar gong bzhin byas la dbus /
NK025(ra)001:2788: bsang sbyang bskyed ba sogs byas la /
NK025(ra)001:2789: zhes gsungs pas rnam grangs su bshad pa las gong du rgyas par song /
NK025(ra)001:2790: 'dir bum pa 'god tshul gsungs pa 'og tu dkyil 'khor bris zin nas bkod dgos pas /
NK025(ra)001:2791: 'dir bum sgrub tshar ma thag tu dkyil 'khor gyi steng lding khri'i khar bzhag go //
NK025(ra)001:2794: de nas yo byad byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:2795: yo byad kyi phud bsags la ram yam kham gis bsang sbyang /
NK025(ra)001:2797: sam ha ra na h+aum gis 'phro 'dus /
NK025(ra)001:2798: tram rat+na tree lokya man+dala h+aum zhes pas yid bzhin
NK025(ra)001:2799: gyi nor bu rin po che mi zad pa'i gter
NK025(ra)001:2800: gyi phung po'i rtser +aahh+aum gi 'od las phyi nang
NK025(ra)001:2801: gsang ba'i longs spyod bsam gyis mi khyab pa byung
NK025(ra)001:2802: bar bsam mo // bye brag tu byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:2803: yo byad tsho gsum du bcad la tsho gcig bam
NK025(ra)001:2804: ser po'i 'phro 'du las dpa' bo 'bru lngar bskyed
NK025(ra)001:2805: la tshogs dang mchod par bya /
NK025(ra)001:2806: tsho gcig a dang ma'i 'phro 'du las 'dod yon
NK025(ra)001:2807: du byin gyis brlabs la sgrub pa po rnams rol
NK025(ra)001:2808: / tsho gcig nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags kyis rgya cher spel la mchod mgron la dgye /
NK025(ra)001:2809: der tshogs pa thams cad kyang lha dang lha mor bsam mo //
NK025(ra)001:2811: zhes gsungs pa ni sgrub pa'i skabs kyi yo byad
NK025(ra)001:2812: phun sum tshogs pa'i skabs su bshad pa ltar sman
NK025(ra)001:2813: raka gtor ma la sogs pa'i mchod rdzas dang 'tsho
NK025(ra)001:2814: ba zas kyi yo byad bsags pa rnams byin gyis
NK025(ra)001:2815: brlab pa'i dgongs pa yin par shes dgos so //
NK025(ra)001:2818: lnga pa slob ma sta gon ni nyer gnyis te /
NK025(ra)001:2821: spyi dang khyad par mchod par bsham /
NK025(ra)001:2822: mtshams nas 'dzab bstod kyi bar bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:2823: zhes gsungs pa'i ma chod pa bsham pa dang mtshams
NK025(ra)001:2824: nas 'dzab bstod kyi bar bya ba ni lha sta
NK025(ra)001:2825: gon dang bum sgrub rgyas par song ba des khyab
NK025(ra)001:2826: / slob ma sta gon dngos ni /
NK025(ra)001:2827: 'og tu dgos pa'i yo byad bdud rtsi ka p+aa la chos sman btab pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:2828: khyor chu'i dung chos dri bzang btab pa'i chus bkang ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:2829: so shing slob ma'i grangs dang mnyam pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:2830: de 'dor ba'i dkyil 'khor ras la bris pa'i pad+ma
NK025(ra)001:2831: 'dab brgyad mdzes tshon dri bzang gi thig le can
NK025(ra)001:2832: dang / bsrung skud lnga sgril 'dom gang ba gsum
NK025(ra)001:2833: lteb tu byas pa la rdo rje'i mdud pa sum
NK025(ra)001:2834: ldan slob ma dang grangs mnyam pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:2835: de bzhin du ku sha'i chun po che chung dang /
NK025(ra)001:2836: 'byor na slob ma'i grangs dang mnyam pa'i phur chung re re sogs legs par bsag go //
NK025(ra)001:2840: man+dala me tog dang bcas par yang nyer bsdogs bya /
NK025(ra)001:2841: lha sta gon du byas pa'i dkyil 'khor dang bum
NK025(ra)001:2842: pa sogs yol bas bsgribs la slob ma rnams sgo
NK025(ra)001:2844: slob dpon gyis bgegs gtor btang ba dkyil 'khor snga ma rnams dang 'dra la /
NK025(ra)001:2845: bden brdar gyi tshe khyad par du yang 'dus pa
NK025(ra)001:2846: chen po'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa
NK025(ra)001:2847: rnams kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:2849: bka' bsgor rnga dang rol mo sogs dbyangs dang bcas pa bya zhing /
NK025(ra)001:2853: slob ma rnams nang du bshar te yungs thun gyis brab /
NK025(ra)001:2854: gu gul gyi dud pas bdug /
NK025(ra)001:2855: spro na me thun chu thun khro bo dang ging
NK025(ra)001:2856: chas su zhugs pa mang pos mtshon cha sna tshogs
NK025(ra)001:2857: dang yungs kar rgyang zhag sogs brdeg cing bgegs bskrad
NK025(ra)001:2860: de nas slob ma rnams khrus bya zhes gsungs pas las bum gyi chus bkru zhing /
NK025(ra)001:2861: ji ltar bltams pa sogs sngags dang bcas pa brjod /
NK025(ra)001:2862: man+dala gyi me tog bgye bsdu byas te slob dpon gyis /
NK025(ra)001:2863: nam mkha' dang mnyam pa'i sems can thams cad khyab
NK025(ra)001:2864: bdag gdod ma'i mgon po kun bzang he ru ka'i
NK025(ra)001:2866: de'i ched du 'dir lung a nu yo ga dang
NK025(ra)001:2867: rjes su 'brel ba tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK025(ra)001:2868: du slob ma sta gon gyi chos rnams legs par
NK025(ra)001:2869: nyan te sems can gyi don bgyid snyam pa byang
NK025(ra)001:2870: chub kyi mchog tu thugs bskyed pa gsal btab ste
NK025(ra)001:2871: gsan 'tshal / gsan bya'i chos ni snga 'gyur rdo rje theg pa bka' gter gnyis las bka' ma /
NK025(ra)001:2872: de la yang mdo sgyu sems gsum du yod pa'i
NK025(ra)001:2873: don gsum ga tshang yang gtso che ba mdo'i skabs
NK025(ra)001:2874: yin / de yang rgyab brten gyi lung rtsa ba'i
NK025(ra)001:2875: rgyud rdo rje bkod pa kun 'dus rig pa'i mdo
NK025(ra)001:2876: yin / dang / dpal khrag 'thung 'dus pa'i rgyud /
NK025(ra)001:2877: sgyu 'phrul rtsa rgyud gsang ba'i snying po /
NK025(ra)001:2878: bshad pa'i rgyud dgongs pa 'dus pa /
NK025(ra)001:2881: rdo rje me long sogs kyi rgyud gzhung chen po rnams kyi don /
NK025(ra)001:2882: rgya gzhung pan+di ta chen po sangs rgyas gsang ba /
NK025(ra)001:2884: wa ra n+aa si'i pan+di ta +aa tsar+ya gsal ba'i rgyan /
NK025(ra)001:2887: rgya gar gtsug lag dpal dge sogs kyis rgyud lung gnyis la nye bar mkho ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:2888: khyad par lung a nu'i phyogs kyi bstan bcos chen po rnams mdzad cing /
NK025(ra)001:2889: a ti ltar na slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje /
NK025(ra)001:2891: o rgyan dus gsum mkhyen pa pad+ma 'byung gnas /
NK025(ra)001:2892: rgya gar pan chen mkhas pa nyer lnga sogs kyis
NK025(ra)001:2893: dbang gi las tho chen po sogs rgya gzhung du
NK025(ra)001:2894: ma mdzad / de yang rgyud dbang dang 'brel ba /
NK025(ra)001:2896: gdams ngag phyag bzhes dang 'brel ba /
NK025(ra)001:2897: phyag bzhes byin rlabs las byang dang 'brel dgos par gsungs pa bzhin /
NK025(ra)001:2898: rgya bod kyi pan grub rig 'dzin nam mkha'i skar tshogs ltar byon pa rnams kyis /
NK025(ra)001:2899: gnam la rdo rje'i ra ma zhig /
NK025(ra)001:2900: sa la dkyil 'khor gyi bkrag ma yal /
NK025(ra)001:2901: bar na sman raka gi mtsho ma skam pa zhal
NK025(ra)001:2902: nas snyan du brgyud pa'i phyag bzhes byin rlabs kyi
NK025(ra)001:2903: rgyun ma nyams par byon pa ltar /
NK025(ra)001:2904: kho bos kyang byar rung ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi sngon du 'gro ba'i las rnams dang /
NK025(ra)001:2905: khyad par du lha sta gon dang bum pa sta gon sogs legs par grub pa yin /
NK025(ra)001:2906: slob ma'i ngo skal du gyur pa la slob ma
NK025(ra)001:2907: sta gon du gnas pa 'dir bgyi ba skabs su
NK025(ra)001:2908: babs shing phyag bzhes su 'byung pas /
NK025(ra)001:2909: de ltar bgyid pa la zhes sogs kyi 'brel bkod
NK025(ra)001:2910: de drang don rgyu 'bras kyi chos bshad kyang ci
NK025(ra)001:2911: rigs byas rjes / de ltar gyi chos ston pa'i
NK025(ra)001:2912: rdo rje slob dpon bdag nyid la tha mal pa'i
NK025(ra)001:2913: 'du shes spangs te dkyil 'khor gyi khyab bdag kun
NK025(ra)001:2914: bzang he ru ka dang gnyis su med par mos
NK025(ra)001:2915: pa'i sgo nas sta gon gyi chos rnams zhu ba'i
NK025(ra)001:2917: gsol ba gdab pa ni snyim pa me tog dang bcas te thal mo sbyar nas /
NK025(ra)001:2920: hoh mi gnas pa'i ye shes chen po'i bdag nyid
NK025(ra)001:2921: 'dus pa chen po'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs 'khor
NK025(ra)001:2922: rgyal ba rgya mtsho zhing gi rdul snyed dang bcas
NK025(ra)001:2923: pa rnams gsan cing dgongs su gsol /
NK025(ra)001:2924: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba 'khor ba las nges
NK025(ra)001:2925: par byung nas 'gro ba sems can rnams kyi don
NK025(ra)001:2926: gyi slad du byang chub kyi mchog tu sems bskyed
NK025(ra)001:2927: nas bslab pa mthar phyin par stsal pas /
NK025(ra)001:2928: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis zhal bstan cing byin gyis brlab pa dang dbang bskur du gsol /
NK025(ra)001:2929: zhes zhu ba phul la sems bskyed pa 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod /
NK025(ra)001:2932: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK025(ra)001:2933: ye nas sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK025(ra)001:2934: rtog pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba las //
NK025(ra)001:2935: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK025(ra)001:2936: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK025(ra)001:2937: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK025(ra)001:2938: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK025(ra)001:2939: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK025(ra)001:2940: e ma ngo mtshar rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'gag pa med las thams cad 'gag /
NK025(ra)001:2942: e ma ngo mtshar rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas gnas pa med las thams cad gnas //
NK025(ra)001:2943: gnas pa nyid na gnas pa med //
NK025(ra)001:2944: e ma ngo mtshar rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dmigs pa med las thams cad dmigs //
NK025(ra)001:2945: dmigs pa nyid na dmigs pa med //
NK025(ra)001:2946: e ma ngo mtshar rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'gro 'ong med las 'gro dang 'ong //
NK025(ra)001:2950: de nas bla ma badz+ra he ru kar bsgoms la /
NK025(ra)001:2952: bla ma badz+ra he ru ka zhal gsum phyag drug
NK025(ra)001:2953: pa'i nga rgyal bzung ste slob ma la gnang ba
NK025(ra)001:2955: e ma bde gshegs snying po'i don //
NK025(ra)001:2956: theg chen gsang sngags snying po'i mchog /
NK025(ra)001:2957: ye nas lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas chos //
NK025(ra)001:2958: khyed la rab tu bstan par bya //
NK025(ra)001:2961: gzugs brnyan lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan dang //
NK025(ra)001:2963: byang chub sems dang tshogs mchog bstan //
NK025(ra)001:2965: de nas slar yang slob mas gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:2967: bcom ldan kun bzang he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:2969: thar pa chen po bdag 'dod de //
NK025(ra)001:2970: de yi dbang dang dam tshig dang //
NK025(ra)001:2971: mgon po dpa' bor skyabs song zhing //
NK025(ra)001:2972: theg chen khang par gzhug pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:2973: mkhyen rab ye shes bdag la stsol //
NK025(ra)001:2976: bu 'dir shog cig ci bde ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:2977: las spyod rim par 'gro ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:2978: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje bzung //
NK025(ra)001:2979: 'dus pa chen po'i dbang rdzogs sbyin //
NK025(ra)001:2981: slob ma rnams kyi klad pa dung khang du ma
NK025(ra)001:2982: las nyi ma'i 'phro 'du las 'od kyis lus mgo
NK025(ra)001:2983: mjug khyab / +aa yu h+aum dzah zhes pas tshe'i
NK025(ra)001:2984: rang bzhin mu tig ltar dkar po dri ma med
NK025(ra)001:2985: mjug khyab / par bsam / yang dung khang du
NK025(ra)001:2986: b+h+r+aum gyi 'phro 'du las zla gam dmar po sgo
NK025(ra)001:2987: gcig pa'i nang du badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra
NK025(ra)001:2988: h+aum gis h+aum k+aa ra sngo skya rdo rje dang
NK025(ra)001:2990: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h+aum gis mi
NK025(ra)001:2991: g.yo ba smug nag ral gri dang zhags pa can
NK025(ra)001:2993: bla mas rang nyid dpal chen po badz+ra he ru kar gsal ba'i g.yas g.yon gyi sor mo bcur /
NK025(ra)001:2995: g.yon lngar zla ba'i gdan la g.yas su h+aum s+w+aa +aamhh+aa /
NK025(ra)001:2996: g.yon du m+aum l+aam m+aam p+aam t+aam las rigs lnga
NK025(ra)001:2997: yab yum gyi lhar gsal ba'i sku gsung thugs las
NK025(ra)001:2998: 'od zer gyi 'phro 'dus slob ma rnams la thim
NK025(ra)001:2999: pas sgo gsum gyi sgrib pa dang bral bar bsam
NK025(ra)001:3000: zhing / bla mas phyag rdo rje nang bsdams kyi phyag rgya bcas te /
NK025(ra)001:3003: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK025(ra)001:3004: cad kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi
NK025(ra)001:3005: byin rlabs dang / bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs
NK025(ra)001:3006: kyis gang zag 'di rnams kyi rgyud la gnas pa'i
NK025(ra)001:3007: las dang nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:3008: lta ba dman zhing zhes shes rab zhan pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:3009: khyad par gsang sngags kyi sgor zhugs nas gsang ba
NK025(ra)001:3010: zab mo'i dbang nod pa la sgrib pa gangs kyi
NK025(ra)001:3011: rim pa bzhin du gnas pa thams cad skad cig
NK025(ra)001:3012: la byang zhing dag par gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:3013: badz+ra b+han+d+ha tra tha zhes brjod cing phyag rgya phral
NK025(ra)001:3014: te sprugs pas slob ma'i sgrib pa ma lus par
NK025(ra)001:3015: dag nas lus shel gang ltar gyur par bsam /
NK025(ra)001:3016: badz+ra a be sha ya a a /
NK025(ra)001:3017: zhes pas khro bo gnyis 'od zhu slob ma'i lus
NK025(ra)001:3018: la thim pas lus bkrags mdangs dang ldan par bsam
NK025(ra)001:3023: zhes gsungs pa'i don ni 'di ltar /
NK025(ra)001:3024: khyed rang rnams yi dam gang mos su bsgom mdzod /
NK025(ra)001:3025: de la slob dpon gyis badz+ra karma rak+sha ham /
NK025(ra)001:3026: zhes rdo rje go cha'i phyag rgya spyi bor bzhag
NK025(ra)001:3027: pas spyi bo'i ham ljang gu zhu ba las lus
NK025(ra)001:3028: mgo mjug rdo rje rgya gram gyi go khrab tu
NK025(ra)001:3029: gyur par bsam ste go bago'o //
NK025(ra)001:3030: lus bsrung ba ni slob dpon gyis gnas so sor
NK025(ra)001:3031: phyag rgya 'ching zhing sngags brjod pa gsang gnas su
NK025(ra)001:3032: khro bo rdo rje gnod sbyin mthing nag mche zhags
NK025(ra)001:3033: can dang / mi 'chi thal sbyor dmar po ral
NK025(ra)001:3034: gri dang sdigs mdzub can gnyis gshibs te zhal phyir
NK025(ra)001:3035: bstan bzhengs pa'i tshul du bskyed /
NK025(ra)001:3036: lte bar khro bo gnyis dbu sprad bcu drug mdor zhabs sprad de ske rags kyi tshul du bsrung /
