NK025(ra)001:3037: sgal tshigs bdun par dbu sprad snying gar phyag sprad de stod chings kyi tshul du bsrung /
NK025(ra)001:3038: mgrin par khro bo gnyis gshibs te bzhengs pa'i tshul du bsrung /
NK025(ra)001:3039: dpral bar dbu sprad ltag khung du zhabs sprad nas thod khyer gyi tshul du bsrung /
NK025(ra)001:3040: spyi bor khro bo gnyis bzhengs pa'i tshul du bsrung ba'i mos pa mdzod /
NK025(ra)001:3042: bla ma'i g.yas kyi mdzub mo h+aum las rdo rje
NK025(ra)001:3043: gnod sbyin dang g.yon pa'i mdzub mo h+aum las mi
NK025(ra)001:3044: 'chi thal sbyor du bsam la mdzub mo gnyis kyis
NK025(ra)001:3045: gnas de dag tu phyag rgya bca' zhing trum zhes
NK025(ra)001:3047: de nas slob ma rnams kyis phyag btsal thal mo sbyar te /
NK025(ra)001:3048: zhes gsungs pa sa phyag btsal ba'i mos pa dang
NK025(ra)001:3049: bcas te thal mo sbyar nas 'di'i rjes zlos mdzod
NK025(ra)001:3050: / dpa' bo rdo rje 'dzin pa khyod //
NK025(ra)001:3052: sdug bsngal chu bo rgyun zlog pa //
NK025(ra)001:3053: don gnyis bdag gis mngon bya'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:3054: thabs kyi las mtha' gang lags pa //
NK025(ra)001:3055: rim pa yang dag bstan bya'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:3056: thugs rjes nye bar bskyed mdzad de //
NK025(ra)001:3057: de ring gnas par mdzad du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:3059: bla mas bdud rtsi ka p+aa la thogs te /
NK025(ra)001:3060: dpal ldan rdo rje'i sku gsung thugs 'chang ba //
NK025(ra)001:3061: rdo rje mi phyed sku gsung thugs dang ldan //
NK025(ra)001:3062: deng nas bdag la byin gyis brlabs nas su //
NK025(ra)001:3063: rdo rje sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub sbyin //
NK025(ra)001:3067: w+aa k+aa sid+d+hi +aah tsit+ta sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:3070: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya w+aa k+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:3071: zhes lan gsum rdo rjes reg go //
NK025(ra)001:3072: de nas bla mas rdo rje phyed pa la 'dzin du bcug ste 'di'i rjes zlos byar gzhug go //
NK025(ra)001:3073: bdag ni las mchog skal bar ldan //
NK025(ra)001:3074: deng nas theg pa chen po la //
NK025(ra)001:3075: brten par bya phyir bdag la ni //
NK025(ra)001:3076: ye shes bsrung ba mdzad du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:3079: +aahbig+h+n+aan+ta krita a mri ta kun+da li h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:3080: ces pas khyor chu'i dri chab sbyin la /
NK025(ra)001:3081: kha bshal khong du yang btung ngo //
NK025(ra)001:3082: lhag ma rgyab tu bor ro //
NK025(ra)001:3084: badz+ra dzi ha sam b+ha ra pra ti ni h+aum
NK025(ra)001:3085: phata kyis so shing sbom pas lce gzhar phra mo
NK025(ra)001:3086: so brus la man+dala du mkha' dbyings ma'i phyag rgyas
NK025(ra)001:3087: dor / zhes gsungs pa bla mas so shing bum chus bsang sbyang /
NK025(ra)001:3088: stong pa'i ngang las h+aum las byung ba'i so shing
NK025(ra)001:3089: mtshan nyid ldan pa slob ma'i dngos grub kyi ltas
NK025(ra)001:3090: rtag cing sgrib pa sbyong ba'i nus ldan du gyur
NK025(ra)001:3091: / badz+ra dzi ha sam+b+ha ra pra ti ni h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:3092: ces brims te mkha' dbyings kyi phyag rgyas rtsa ba
NK025(ra)001:3093: 'cha' zhing rtses gzhar tshul byas pas sman pa mkhas
NK025(ra)001:3094: pas skyugs sman btang ba bzhin /
NK025(ra)001:3095: nad gdon sdig sgrib thams cad skyugs te dbang chen gser gyis gzhir thim /
NK025(ra)001:3096: rtse'i me tog bla mas byin gyis brlabs pa'i man+dala
NK025(ra)001:3097: du ltos med dor bas dngos grub kyi mtshan ma
NK025(ra)001:3098: gsal bar ston cig snyam pas sngags dang bcas te
NK025(ra)001:3100: ces mtshams sbyar la man+dala 'dab brgyad par 'dor du bcug ste /
NK025(ra)001:3103: phyogs bzhir rtse mo bstan na rigs bzhin 'grub /
NK025(ra)001:3104: byang shar du byung na bskyar ro //
NK025(ra)001:3105: zhes gsungs pa dang gsang sngags gzhan nas byung ba ltar rgyas bshad kyang bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:3108: de nas badz+ra rak+sha rak+sha h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:3109: ces pas srung skud pho'i g.yon /
NK025(ra)001:3110: mo'i g.yas su bcing zhes gsungs pa'i don ni srung skud sngar ltar las bum gyi chus bsang sbyang /
NK025(ra)001:3111: stong pa'i ngang las slob ma'i lus kyi bar chad
NK025(ra)001:3112: bsrung ba'i phyir lus dang tshad mnyam pa'i srung skud
NK025(ra)001:3113: ye shes lnga dang ldan phyir kha dog lnga ldan
NK025(ra)001:3114: / sku gsung thugs dang ldan pa'i mdud pa gsum btab pa /
NK025(ra)001:3115: nyin nub kyi bar chad bsrung phyir 'khor gnyis su
NK025(ra)001:3116: byas te rdo rje'i mdud pas bcing pas sgo gsum
NK025(ra)001:3117: gyis bar chad bsrung ba'i nus ldan du gyur zhes
NK025(ra)001:3118: badz+ra rak+sha'i sngags kyi btab la pho'i g.yon dang mo'i
NK025(ra)001:3119: g.yas su bcings te bum chu dang rdo rje rgyas
NK025(ra)001:3120: btab bo // ku sha sbyin pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:3122: badz+ra t+aik+sha na h+aum s+w+aa h+aas ku sha che chung sngas stan du sbyin /
NK025(ra)001:3123: zhes gsungs pa'i don ku sha che chung gnyis bum chus bsang /
NK025(ra)001:3124: d+h+aihls ku sha che ba dang h+aum las chung bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:3125: badz+ra t+aik+sha na h+aum zhes byin gyis brlabs te bsnol mar gtad do //
NK025(ra)001:3127: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la yas phur pa sras mchog tu byin gyis brlabs la sbyin no //
NK025(ra)001:3128: zhes gsungs pa'i don slob ma'i grangs sam yang na phur pa gcig bsang sbyang /
NK025(ra)001:3129: stong pa'i ngang las badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aana bam h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:3130: ces pas phur pa sras mchog stod khro bo la
NK025(ra)001:3131: smad phur pa'i dbal can dur khrod kyi chas dang
NK025(ra)001:3132: ldan par gyur / zhes sngags bzla zhing bsgril te
NK025(ra)001:3133: byin gyis brlabs la slob ma la sngags des sbyin
NK025(ra)001:3134: ldan par gyur / no // rtsa bar /
NK025(ra)001:3135: skabs 'dir dbang gi gleng gzhi dang gegs brgyad bshad do //
NK025(ra)001:3136: zhes gsungs pa sgo 'byed skabs ltar bram ze dung
NK025(ra)001:3137: phreng can gyi gleng gzhi dang gegs brgyad kyang bshad
NK025(ra)001:3139: de nas bla ma la phyag byas te sems rtse gcig tu 'dug go //
NK025(ra)001:3141: nyal ba'i rnal 'byor bshad pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:3143: de nas ku sha sngas stan du byas te pho g.yas mo g.yon 'og tu bcug la /
NK025(ra)001:3144: zhes gsungs pas che ba gdan dang chung ba sngas
NK025(ra)001:3145: su btab ste bla ma dang dkyil 'khor pa'i lha
NK025(ra)001:3146: tshogs yid la dran par byas nas ltas drang por
NK025(ra)001:3147: ston cig snyam pa las rtog pa gzhan gyis bar
NK025(ra)001:3150: rmi lam thun gsum du bcad de /
NK025(ra)001:3151: tho rengs kyi rmi lam bzang ngan brtag go //
NK025(ra)001:3152: zhes gsungs pas de yang gang byung drang por smos shig bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:3153: de yang gsang ba spyi rgyud las /
NK025(ra)001:3154: rmi lam sangs rgyas mthong ba ni //
NK025(ra)001:3155: yon tan rgya mtsho'i mngon sum bzhin //
NK025(ra)001:3156: mchod rten dang ni sku gzugs mthong //
NK025(ra)001:3157: de la mchod la sogs pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:3158: dge slong dag la chos nyan te //
NK025(ra)001:3159: yang na ma nyan na yang rung //
NK025(ra)001:3160: chos kyi rnal 'byor spyod pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:3161: de bzhin mdo sde klog pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:3162: rmi lam dge 'dun mthong ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:3163: yang na dge slong gcig pu mthong //
NK025(ra)001:3164: de dang 'grogs shig gtam zer dang //
NK025(ra)001:3165: yang na dge slong dngos por gyur //
NK025(ra)001:3166: gtsug lag khang dag mthong ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:3167: de bzhin dge slong ma dag mthong //
NK025(ra)001:3168: rgyal po'i sras dag mthong ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:3169: de bzhin bla ma pha ma dang //
NK025(ra)001:3170: mdza' bo rnam pa sna tshogs dang //
NK025(ra)001:3171: rmi lam du ni mthong na shis //
NK025(ra)001:3172: rig sngags dang ni dngos grub thob //
NK025(ra)001:3173: rgyal po dbang bskur slob ma 'dzin //
NK025(ra)001:3174: kun dga' rnam pa sna tshogs dang //
NK025(ra)001:3175: 'bab chu rnams dang rgya mtsho dang //
NK025(ra)001:3176: ri dang glang po che dag dang //
NK025(ra)001:3177: mthong na yang ni bzang por grags //
NK025(ra)001:3178: bzhon pa bzang la zhon pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:3179: nor bu 'bru dang zas mchog shis //
NK025(ra)001:3181: rgya skag ri la 'dzeg pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:3182: ka ra bi ra'i me tog 'thu //
NK025(ra)001:3183: mchod sdong bye ma thal phung la //
NK025(ra)001:3184: 'dzeg dang bong bu la zhon nas //
NK025(ra)001:3185: lho phyogs song nas ma log dang //
NK025(ra)001:3186: de bzhin spre'u zhon nas ni //
NK025(ra)001:3188: bud med nag mo khros ma'am //
NK025(ra)001:3189: de la 'dod chags spyod pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:3190: g.yang ngam shing las lhung ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:3191: ljon shing 'bras med skam po dang //
NK025(ra)001:3192: khyi dang khra dang srin po dang //
NK025(ra)001:3193: de las gzhan pas zos pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:3194: phag dang rnga mo ma he dang //
NK025(ra)001:3195: zhon nas dbyug pa thogs pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:3196: mi nag po yis sdigs pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:3197: til mar gyis byung phreng dmar thogs //
NK025(ra)001:3198: skra bregs phreng ba dmar po bcings //
NK025(ra)001:3199: de rnams ngan pa'i rmis ltas yin //
NK025(ra)001:3201: de dag bzang ngan brtags la ngan na slob ma bdud rtsi 'khyil bar bskyed la /
NK025(ra)001:3202: de'i sngags kyis bsrung ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:3204: zhes gsungs pa sang gi bya ba yin /
NK025(ra)001:3205: do nub kyi thugs dam gyi rim pa der gnang ba zhu zhes slob ma dagye'o //
NK025(ra)001:3206: de nas tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor la mchod bstod ci rigs bya /
NK025(ra)001:3207: lhag chad yig brgyas bskang la nam mkhar 'degs pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:3209: de nas rang chas gos ser pos mdzub mo smin
NK025(ra)001:3210: mtshams su bsnol la ha ha hi hi zhes pas
NK025(ra)001:3211: tshom bu'i lha tshogs dang thig nam mkhar bteg la
NK025(ra)001:3212: zhes gsungs pas lha sta gon du gnas pa rnams
NK025(ra)001:3213: nam mkhar bteg / tshom bu dang mchod gtor bsdu /
NK025(ra)001:3215: de nas bla mas byang shar nas re kh+aa mdzub
NK025(ra)001:3216: gang drangs te zangs gzhong ngam ting phor gyis bkab
NK025(ra)001:3217: pa rdo rjes mnan la bzhag go //
NK025(ra)001:3218: nub mo phrin las gzhung bsrang tshogs las bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:3219: 'grub na srid pa'i spyi mdos bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:3220: zhes gsungs pa'i don khyams bcu gcig pa'i byang shar nas nang nas phyir mthing /
NK025(ra)001:3224: ljang ba'i rtsig pa lnga mdzub gang drangs te ting phor bkab pa rdo rje mnan la bzhag /
NK025(ra)001:3225: nub mo zhi khro bka' gter gyi phrin las gang rigs gzhung srong ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:3227: mchod bskang tshogs las dang bcas pa bya /
NK025(ra)001:3228: srid pa'i spyi mdos sogs kyang btang ngo //
NK025(ra)001:3229: des nub mo'i bya ba grub /
NK025(ra)001:3230: nangs par snga bar langs te ltas brtag pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:3232: de nas zangs gzhong bsal te re kh+aa 'dres na nyams pa yod pas bshags pa bya /
NK025(ra)001:3234: zhes gsungs pa bri tshul ni /
NK025(ra)001:3236: dbus kyi lte ba slob dpon gyis bri /
NK025(ra)001:3237: de nas slob ma la bris zhes gnang ba sbyin te brir gzhug go //
NK025(ra)001:3238: ji ltar bri ba ni dbus kyi 'khor lo'i lte ba mthing /
NK025(ra)001:3241: glo 'bur gyi gru chad phyogs mdog /
NK025(ra)001:3242: lha snam bar khyams dang po ser /
NK025(ra)001:3243: rtsig pa mthing dkar ser dmar ljang ba'am ljang gu /
NK025(ra)001:3248: shar bu'am pu shu dkar po /
NK025(ra)001:3249: dkyil 'khor gnyis pa'i bar khyams dkar po /
NK025(ra)001:3250: rtsig pa dkar ser dmar ljang mthing ba'am ljang gu /
NK025(ra)001:3252: dkyil 'khor gsum pa'i khyams dmar po /
NK025(ra)001:3253: rtsig pa dmar ser ljang mthing dkar ba'am ljang gu /
NK025(ra)001:3255: dkyil 'khor bzhi pa'i khyams ser po /
NK025(ra)001:3256: rtsig pa ser dkar dmar ljang mthing ba'am ljang gu /
NK025(ra)001:3258: dkyil 'khor lnga pa'i khyams dmar po /
NK025(ra)001:3259: rtsig pa dmar ser ljang mthing dkar ba'am ljang gu /
NK025(ra)001:3261: dkyil 'khor drug pa'i khyams dkar po /
NK025(ra)001:3262: rtsig pa dkar ser dmar ljang mthing ba'am ljang gu /
NK025(ra)001:3264: dkyil 'khor bdun pa'i khyams nag po /
NK025(ra)001:3265: rtsig pa nag ljang dmar ser dkar ba'am ljang gu /
NK025(ra)001:3267: dkyil 'khor brgyad pa'i khyams shar dkar lho ser nub dmar byang ljang /
NK025(ra)001:3268: rtsig pa mthing dkar ser dmar ljang ba'am ljang gu /
NK025(ra)001:3270: dkyil 'khor dgu pa'i khyams ljang gu /
NK025(ra)001:3271: rtsig pa ljang dkar ser dmar mthing ba'am ljang gu /
NK025(ra)001:3273: dkyil 'khor bcu pa'i khyams dang bcu gcig pa'i khyams gnyis ka phyogs mdog /
NK025(ra)001:3274: rtsig pa gnyis ka mthing ser dmar ljang dkar pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:3275: nang ma rnams la rta babs yod na mas nas rim bzhin ser mthing dmar ljang ngo //
NK025(ra)001:3276: ka ba thams cad phyogs mdog /
NK025(ra)001:3278: dkyil 'khor phyi ma'i gu na ha ri bzhi ga sngon po /
NK025(ra)001:3280: phyi ma'i rta babs brgyad ni mas nas rim bzhin gser gdung ser /
NK025(ra)001:3288: dbus rwa dang chu srin rwa phyogs mdog /
NK025(ra)001:3292: nyi dkyil ljang gu la pa tra ris /
NK025(ra)001:3294: dur khrod gzhi nag po la mchod rten /
NK025(ra)001:3295: me chu sprin shing chu brgyad dang /
NK025(ra)001:3296: dur khrod kyi bkod pa sna tshogs /
NK025(ra)001:3297: rdor gdan mthing ga la rdo rje ser po /
NK025(ra)001:3298: me ri sna tshogs rnams bri zhing /
NK025(ra)001:3299: lha gnas so sor lha sta gon ltar lha'i sku mdog dang mthun pa'i tshon spungs bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:3300: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor ni lte ba mthing kha 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi ser po /
NK025(ra)001:3301: glo 'bur gyi gru chad ljang gu /
NK025(ra)001:3303: rtsig pa lnga nang nas rim bzhin mthing dkar ser dmar ljang ba /
NK025(ra)001:3304: 'dod snam dmar po phan spyi dang 'dra /
NK025(ra)001:3305: rta babs rim bzhi yang gong dang 'dra zhing pad rdor me ri gsum yang spyi ltar ro //
NK025(ra)001:3306: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor 'di bris zin nas khro bo tshogs chen gyi dbus su many+dzi'i khar bkod do //
NK025(ra)001:3308: bris zin nas nam mkhar bteg pa'i lha tshogs dkyil 'khor la bstim mo //
NK025(ra)001:3309: de nas dgong mo cha gsum btang ngo //
NK025(ra)001:3310: bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cu'i gtor ma btang la phyi mtshams bcad nas /
NK025(ra)001:3311: zhes gsungs pa dkyil 'khor bris zin pa'i nub mo'i bya ba yin /
NK025(ra)001:3312: 'dir gong du bshad pa ltar nangs par langs ma
NK025(ra)001:3313: thag mtshan ma brtags la slob ma 'ga' zhig dkyil
NK025(ra)001:3314: 'khor brir gzhug / slob dpon gyis sman raka gtor
NK025(ra)001:3315: gsum dang mchod pa lnga bshams te zhi khro'i phrin
NK025(ra)001:3316: las rgyas bsdus gang rigs gzhung bsrang /
NK025(ra)001:3317: bzlas pa ci rigs grub rjes phyi mtshams nas rim bzhin bya ba la /
NK025(ra)001:3319: phyi'i bar mtshams rgyal chen la tho'i phrin las bcol ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:3320: cha gsum gyi gtor ma dang po de las che ba bzhi /
NK025(ra)001:3322: bar pa dang tha ma'ang bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:3323: sha khrag gi brgyan pa'i gtor ma dang /
NK025(ra)001:3324: dza gad dang mchod pa rnam pa lnga yon chab dang bcas pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:3325: sgrub khang gi phyi'i sa bde bar phyogs mtshams su
NK025(ra)001:3326: man+dala pad+ma 'dab brgyad kyi lte ba phyogs mdog bya
NK025(ra)001:3327: / tho yang shar nas dkar ser dmar ljang brtsig go //
NK025(ra)001:3328: de la 'bras bu dang bcas pa'i shing dang rgyal chen bzhi'i gzugs bris pa gzug go //
NK025(ra)001:3329: zhes gsungs pa spro na rgyal tho bzhi dang phyogs skyong bcu'i tho brtsig pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:3330: bsdu na rgyal chen bzhis chog pas /
NK025(ra)001:3331: phyogs bzhir man+dala te dkyil 'khor pad+ma 'dab brgyad mdzes
NK025(ra)001:3332: tshon lte ba phyogs mdog tu bris pa'i steng tho
NK025(ra)001:3336: 'bras bu can gyi shing btsugs pa la /
NK025(ra)001:3337: rgyal chen bzhi'i sku gzugs bris pa gdags /
NK025(ra)001:3338: de'i mdun du gtor ma lcog zlum dkar dmar rgyan
NK025(ra)001:3339: gyis brgyan pa re dang bdud rtsi mchod pa lnga
NK025(ra)001:3340: breng tshar du bsham pa sogs nyer bsdogs byas la
NK025(ra)001:3341: 'dir thog mar bgegs gtor zhig bshams pa chab kyis
NK025(ra)001:3343: de nas rnal 'byor pas lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas tri
NK025(ra)001:3344: badz+ra am ku sha dzah lan gsum gyis bdag gi
NK025(ra)001:3345: thugs ka nas 'od zer lcags kyu'i rnam par 'phros
NK025(ra)001:3346: / bgegs rnams mdun du bkug la sngags drug phyag
NK025(ra)001:3347: rgya drug gis gtor ma 'og ma byin gyis brlabs
NK025(ra)001:3348: / la / bdag gi bsod nams stobs sogs bsdos la btang /
NK025(ra)001:3350: sngags drug phyag rgya drug gis bgegs gtor sbyangs spel
NK025(ra)001:3351: bsgyur thob tshim dbang du byas te spro na gang
NK025(ra)001:3352: gi cha gsum gyi tha ma /
NK025(ra)001:3353: bdag gi bsod nams stobs dang ni //
NK025(ra)001:3355: ya hi gats+tsha'i bar snga ma bzhin btang rjes /
NK025(ra)001:3356: gser skyems brtag pa gsum gyis byin gyis brlabs pa zhes gsungs pas /
NK025(ra)001:3357: sbyangs spel bsgyur gsum gyi sngags rgyas byin gyis brlabs te /
NK025(ra)001:3359: thams cad kyis bsngosa la chang phud rgyas par gtor la /
NK025(ra)001:3361: gong du sgo 'byed kyis cho ga skabs ltar /
NK025(ra)001:3363: lcags ri gser ri dngul gyi ri //
NK025(ra)001:3364: zhes pa nas nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags rgya dang /
NK025(ra)001:3365: gnod 'tshe ma byed par bka' bsgo ba'i bar byas la gser skyems phyogs bcur 'thor ro //
NK025(ra)001:3368: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal zhing skyabs su mchi'o //
NK025(ra)001:3369: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:3370: bden pa yang dag pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:3371: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis gsang sngags
NK025(ra)001:3372: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor gsang ba las kyang
NK025(ra)001:3373: ches gsang ba yang gsang rmad du byung ba'i dkyil
NK025(ra)001:3374: 'khor chen po 'dir bdag cag rnal 'byor pa 'dir
NK025(ra)001:3375: tshogs 'dus pa rnams la bar du gcod pa'i gdon
NK025(ra)001:3376: bgegs 'byung po'i ris su gtogs pa gnas 'dir ma
NK025(ra)001:3377: gnas par dpag tshad dang rgyang grags su ma nye
NK025(ra)001:3379: ces pa ltar khro bo'i nga rgyal gyis sngags dang bcas bgegs bskrad cing dmigs pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:3381: zhes mtshams gcod kyis bsdigs shing rang gi thugs ka
NK025(ra)001:3382: nas rdo rje gnod sbyin dpag tu med pa spros
NK025(ra)001:3383: pas thams cad gling gzhan du bskrad par bsam mo
NK025(ra)001:3385: rgyal tho 'dzugs pa shar nas rim bzhin bya ba yin kyang /
NK025(ra)001:3386: 'dir byang nas bya bar bshad pas /
NK025(ra)001:3388: de nas byang gi tho'i rtsar phyin la /
NK025(ra)001:3389: rang karma he ru kar bskyed pa'i thugs ka nas
NK025(ra)001:3390: b+h+r+aum gyi 'phro 'du las tho gzhal yas khang du
NK025(ra)001:3391: gyur pa'i nang nyi zla la /
NK025(ra)001:3392: bee sh+ra ba na ye yak+sha a ti pa ta
NK025(ra)001:3393: ye h+aum dzah zhes pas rnam thos sras g.yas rin
NK025(ra)001:3394: po ches mtshan pa'i rgyal mtshan /
NK025(ra)001:3396: gser khrab gser rmog can don grub kyi dbu brgyan pa bskyed /
NK025(ra)001:3397: sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlab bo //
NK025(ra)001:3399: slob dpon 'khor bcas rol mo dang dar gdugs ba
NK025(ra)001:3400: dan sogs spros pa rgya che bas sgrub khang nas
NK025(ra)001:3401: g.yas bskor gyis thon cing thog mar byang gi tho'i
NK025(ra)001:3402: rtsar byon te mchod gtor bdud rtsi rnams bsang sbyang
NK025(ra)001:3403: / stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i
NK025(ra)001:3404: snod du zhu ba las byung ba'i mchod yon bdug
NK025(ra)001:3405: spos me tog mar me dri chab zhal zas rol
NK025(ra)001:3406: mo sman phud gtor ma rnams 'dod pa'i yon tan
NK025(ra)001:3418: rang nyid karma he ru ka ljang dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas gsum dgra s+t+wa /
NK025(ra)001:3423: zhags pa 'dzin pa yum dang 'khril ba'i skur gyur
NK025(ra)001:3424: pa'i thugs ka nas b+h+r+aum 'phros pa tho la thim
NK025(ra)001:3425: te yongs su gyur pa las tho gzhal yas khang
NK025(ra)001:3426: du gyur pa'i nang du nyi zla'i gdan la bee
NK025(ra)001:3427: sh+ra ba na ye yak+sha a ti pa ta ye
NK025(ra)001:3428: h+aum dzahls rgyal po chen po rnam thos sras g.yas
NK025(ra)001:3429: rin po ches mtshan pa'i rgyal mtshan dang g.yon ne'u
NK025(ra)001:3431: gser khrab gser rmog dang rin po che'i rgyan gyis
NK025(ra)001:3432: brgyan pa don grub kyi dbu rgyan can du gyur
NK025(ra)001:3433: / sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:3434: de bzhin du w+aa ka tsit+ta sogs sngags rgyas gnas gsum byin gyis brlabs te /
NK025(ra)001:3435: rang karma he ru ka gnas 'gyur te rta mgrin
NK025(ra)001:3436: zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'am gang bder gnas bsgyur ro
NK025(ra)001:3438: de nas rang rta mgrin du bskyed nas pad+m+aan+ta krita badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai wa h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:3439: zhes bzlas nas spyan drangs te /
NK025(ra)001:3441: thugs ka'i 'od zer gyi 'phro 'dus spyan 'dren cing /
NK025(ra)001:3444: ri rgyal lhun po'i byang phyogs nas //
NK025(ra)001:3445: lcang lo can gyi pho brang nas //
NK025(ra)001:3446: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK025(ra)001:3447: tshur spyon rgyal chen rnam thos sras //
NK025(ra)001:3448: btsun mo sras dang blon por bcas //
NK025(ra)001:3449: g.yog 'khor bye ba stong ldan rnams //
NK025(ra)001:3450: 'dir sbyon mchod pa dam pa bzhes //
NK025(ra)001:3451: phrin las sgrub phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:3452: bee sh+ra ba na ye yak+sha a ti pa ta ye /
NK025(ra)001:3453: dzahh+aum bam hohs dgug gzhug bstim /
NK025(ra)001:3454: k+aa ya w+aak+ka tsit+ta badz+ra tish+thasa brtan par bzhugs su gsol /
NK025(ra)001:3455: mchod pa'i spos dang mar me spar te mchod yon
NK025(ra)001:3456: dang dri chab thun mong du bshad pas 'bul tshig
NK025(ra)001:3460: nags tshal bcud ni yi gar 'ong //
NK025(ra)001:3461: dri zhim rgyas pa lha yi rdzas //
NK025(ra)001:3462: lha rdzas dam pa'i bdug spos 'di //
NK025(ra)001:3463: rgyal chen 'khor dang bcas rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:3464: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags kyis //
NK025(ra)001:3465: thugs rjes dgongs la bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:3466: badz+ra d+h+au pe p+au tsa me g+ha sa mu dra s+pha ra na sa ma ye h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:3467: gtsang zhing gtsang mar skyes pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:3468: lha rdzas dam pa'i me tog 'di //
NK025(ra)001:3469: rgyal chen 'khor dang bdag cag dad pas thugs rjes
NK025(ra)001:3470: dgongs te badz+ra push+pe p+au tsa sdug bsngal 'joms shing
NK025(ra)001:3471: bkra shis pa // dge zhing mun sel mar me 'di //
NK025(ra)001:3472: rgyal chen 'khor dang bdag cag dad pas thugs rjes
NK025(ra)001:3473: dgongs te badz+ra +aa lo ke gtsang zhing gtsang mar
NK025(ra)001:3474: sbyar ba yi // lha rdzas dam pa'i dri chab 'di //
NK025(ra)001:3475: rgyal chen 'khor dang bdag cag dad pas thugs rje
NK025(ra)001:3476: dgongs te badz+ra gan+d+he sman rnams bcud ni yi gar
NK025(ra)001:3477: 'ong // sngags kyi zhal zas bshos 'di dag /
NK025(ra)001:3478: rgyal chen 'khor dang bdag cag dad pas thugs rjes
NK025(ra)001:3479: dgongs te badz+ra nee wi d+ya dri med yid du
NK025(ra)001:3480: 'ong ba yi // lha rdzas dam pa'i rol mo 'di //
NK025(ra)001:3481: rgyal chen 'khor dang bcas rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:3482: bdag cag dad bas 'bul lags kyi //
NK025(ra)001:3483: thugs rje dgongs la bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:3484: badz+ra shap+da p+au tsa me g+ha sa mu dra bee
NK025(ra)001:3485: sh+ra ba na ye ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri tas
NK025(ra)001:3486: sman 'bul / bee sh+ra ba na ye ma h+aa
NK025(ra)001:3487: ba lin+ta lan bdun nam gsum gyis gtor ma dbul
NK025(ra)001:3489: ri rgyal lhun po'i byang phyogs nas //
NK025(ra)001:3490: pho brang chen po lcang lo can //
NK025(ra)001:3491: zab cing rgya che gzigs 'phags po //
NK025(ra)001:3492: chos skyong rgyal po rnam thos sras //
NK025(ra)001:3493: btsun mo sras dang blon por bcas //
NK025(ra)001:3494: g.yog 'khor bye ba stong ldan la //
NK025(ra)001:3496: sngon gyi thugs dam rjes dgongs la //
NK025(ra)001:3497: gnas 'diir brtse zhing gshegs nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:3498: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK025(ra)001:3499: bdag cag dpon slob 'khor bcas kyi //
NK025(ra)001:3500: bar chad thams cad zhi ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:3501: bsam pa chos bzhin 'grub par mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:3502: bee sh+ra ba na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:3503: phyag rgya khu tshur gnyis bcangs mathe'u chung gnyis gdengs la phrin las bcol ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:3505: byang phyogs skyong ba'i rgyal po chen po /
NK025(ra)001:3508: gsang ba don yod grub pa khyod kyis ston pa'i spyan sngar bstan pa skyong bar dam bcas te /
NK025(ra)001:3509: mgon po mi 'gyur ba'i gdan la bzhugs nas khas blangs pa bzhin du /
NK025(ra)001:3510: rnal 'byor pa bdag cag sgrub pa la zhugs pa
NK025(ra)001:3511: rnams la byang phyogs gnod sbyin gyi bar chad thams
NK025(ra)001:3513: sgrub pa ma thon gyi bar du phyi'i dgra bgegs nang du ma btang /
NK025(ra)001:3514: nang gi dngos grub phyir ma btang /
NK025(ra)001:3515: phyi mtshams bskyang ba dang bsrung ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:3516: nang mtshams bskyang ba dang bar chad zhi ba'i phrin las mdzad du gsol /
NK025(ra)001:3517: zhes brjod de gtor ma dbul lo //
NK025(ra)001:3518: de nas shar du sngar ltar phyin la /
NK025(ra)001:3519: rang bud+d+ha he ru ka smug dkar dmar pa'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas gsum 'khor lo /
NK025(ra)001:3524: mi mgo 'dzin pa yum dang bcas par bsgoms la gong gi rigs 'gres sbyar te /
NK025(ra)001:3526: b+h+r+aum gyi 'phro 'du las tho gzhal yas khang gi nang du zla ba la /
NK025(ra)001:3527: d+hi ta rash+t+aa ye gan+d+har+b+ha a ti pa ta ye
NK025(ra)001:3528: h+aum dzahls yul 'khor srung dkar po g.yas pi wang
NK025(ra)001:3529: / g.yon ne'u le dung khrab dung rmog can rnam snang gis dbu brgyan pa bskyed /
NK025(ra)001:3530: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab /
NK025(ra)001:3531: rang bud+d+ha he ru ka rta mgrin du gnas bsgyur /
NK025(ra)001:3533: ri rgyal lhun po'i shar phyogs nas //
NK025(ra)001:3534: spos ngad ldan pa'i pho brang nas //
NK025(ra)001:3535: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK025(ra)001:3536: tshur spyon rgyal chen yul 'khor srung //
NK025(ra)001:3537: btsun mo sras dang blon por bcas //
NK025(ra)001:3538: g.yon 'khor bye ba stong ldan rnams //
NK025(ra)001:3539: 'dir spyon mchod pa dam pa bzhes //
NK025(ra)001:3540: phrin las sgrub phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:3541: d+hi ta rash+t+aa ye gan+d+har+b+ha a ti pa ta ye h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:3542: dzahh+aum bam hoh gzhan gong bzhin /
NK025(ra)001:3544: ri rgyal lhun po'i shar phyogs nas //
NK025(ra)001:3545: pho brang chen po spos ngad ldan /
NK025(ra)001:3546: zab cing rgya che gzigs 'phags po //
NK025(ra)001:3547: chos skyong rgyal po yul 'khor srung //
NK025(ra)001:3548: btsan mo sras dang blon por bcas //
NK025(ra)001:3549: g.yog 'khor bye ba stong ldan la //
NK025(ra)001:3551: sngon gyi thugs dam rjes dgongs la //
NK025(ra)001:3552: gnas 'dir brtse zhing gshegs nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:3553: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK025(ra)001:3554: bdag cag dpon slob 'khor bcas kyi //
NK025(ra)001:3555: bar chad thams cad zhi ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:3556: bsam pa chos bzhin 'grub par mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:3557: d+hi ta rash+t+aa ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:3559: hoh shar phyogs skyong ba'i rgyal po chen po phyi yul 'khor srung /
NK025(ra)001:3561: gsang ba rnam par snang mdzad khyod kyis ston pa'i spyan sngar bstan pa skyong bar dam bcas te /
NK025(ra)001:3562: shar gyi dri za'i bar chad zhi ba sogs /
NK025(ra)001:3563: de nas sngar bzhin lhor phyin te /
NK025(ra)001:3564: rang rat+na he ru ka ser sngo dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas gsum rin chen /
NK025(ra)001:3569: ri rab bsnams pa yum dang bcas par bskyed la /
NK025(ra)001:3570: b+h+r+aum gyi 'phro 'du las tho gzhal yas khang gi nang du zla ba la /
NK025(ra)001:3571: bi ru d+ha k+aa ku ra ban+d+he a ti pa
NK025(ra)001:3572: ta ye h+aum dzahls 'phags skyes po sngon po g.yas
NK025(ra)001:3574: lcags khrab lcags rmog can rin 'byung gi dbu rgyan can bskyed /
NK025(ra)001:3576: rang bud+d+ha he ru ka rta mgrin du bsgyur /
NK025(ra)001:3578: ri rgyal lhun po'i lho phyogs nas //
NK025(ra)001:3579: bee d+aur+ya yi pho brang nas //
NK025(ra)001:3580: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK025(ra)001:3581: tshur spyon rgyal che na 'phags skyes so //
NK025(ra)001:3582: btsun mo sras dang blon por bcas //
NK025(ra)001:3583: g.yog 'khor bye ba stong ldan rnams //
NK025(ra)001:3584: 'dir spyon mchod pa dam par bzhes //
NK025(ra)001:3585: phrin las sgrub phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:3586: bi ru d+ha k+aa ye ku ra ban+d+he a ti
NK025(ra)001:3587: pa ta ye h+aum dzah dzahh+aum bam hoh gzhan gong
NK025(ra)001:3589: ri rgyal lhun po'i lho phyogs nas //
NK025(ra)001:3590: pho brang chen po bee d+aur+ya //
NK025(ra)001:3591: zab cing rgya che gzigs 'phags po //
NK025(ra)001:3592: chos skyong rgyal po 'phags skyes po //
NK025(ra)001:3593: btsun mo sras dang blon por bcas //
NK025(ra)001:3594: g.yog 'khor bye ba stong ldan la //
NK025(ra)001:3596: sngon gyi thugs dam rjes dgongs la //
NK025(ra)001:3597: gnas 'dir brtse zhing gshegs nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:3598: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK025(ra)001:3599: bdag cag dpon slob 'khor bcas kyi //
NK025(ra)001:3600: bar chad thams cad zhi ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:3601: bsam pa chos bzhin 'grub par mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:3602: bi ru d+ha k+aa ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:3604: hoh lho phyoogs rgyal po chen po phyi 'phags skyes po /
NK025(ra)001:3606: gsang ba rin 'byung khyod kyis sogs /
NK025(ra)001:3607: grul bum gyi bar chad zhi ba sogs /
NK025(ra)001:3608: de nas nub tu phyin te /
NK025(ra)001:3609: pad+ma he ru ka dmar dkar sngo ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas gsum pad+ma /
NK025(ra)001:3614: 'jig rten 'degs pa yum dang bcas par bskyed /
NK025(ra)001:3615: b+h+r+aum gyi 'phro 'du las tho gzhal yas khang gi nang du zla ba la /
NK025(ra)001:3616: bi ru pak+sha ye n+aa ga a ti pa ta
NK025(ra)001:3617: ye h+aum dzahls spyan mi bzang dmar po g.yas sbrul
NK025(ra)001:3620: 'od dpag med kyis dbu brgyan pa bskyed la /
NK025(ra)001:3623: ri rgyal lhun po'i nub phyogs nas //
NK025(ra)001:3624: rgya mtsho'i chu yi pho brang nas //
NK025(ra)001:3625: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK025(ra)001:3626: tshur spyon rgyal po spyan mi bzang //
NK025(ra)001:3627: btsun mo sras dang blon por bcas //
NK025(ra)001:3628: g.yog 'khor bye ba stong ldan rnams //
NK025(ra)001:3629: 'dir spyon mchod pa dam pa bzhes //
NK025(ra)001:3630: phrin las sgrub phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:3631: bi ru bak+sha ye n+aa ga a ti pa ta ye h+aum dzah dzahh+aum bam hoh gzhan gong bzhin /
NK025(ra)001:3633: ri rgyal lhun po'i nub phyogs na //
NK025(ra)001:3634: pho brang chen po rgya mtsho'i gling //
NK025(ra)001:3635: zab cing rgya che gzigs 'phags po //
NK025(ra)001:3636: chos skyong rgyal po spyan mi bzang //
NK025(ra)001:3637: btsun mo sras dang blon por bcas //
NK025(ra)001:3638: 'khor g.yog bye ba stong ldan la //
NK025(ra)001:3640: sngon gyi thugs dam rjes dgongs la //
NK025(ra)001:3641: gnas 'dir brtse zhing gshegs nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:3642: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK025(ra)001:3643: bdag cag dpon slob 'khor bcas kyi //
NK025(ra)001:3644: bar chad thams cad zhi ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:3645: bsam pa chos bzhin 'grub par mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:3646: bi ru bak+sha ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:3648: hoh nub phyogs skyong ba'i rgyal po chen po phyi spyan mi bzang /
NK025(ra)001:3650: gsang ba snang ba mtha' yas khyod kyi sogs /
NK025(ra)001:3651: klu'i bar chad zhi ba sogs /
NK025(ra)001:3652: de nas rgyal tho tshar nas phyoogs skyong gi tho ni /
NK025(ra)001:3654: de nas phyogs skyong bcu la'ang spro na tho brtsigs la mchod pa gtor ma sngags tsam gyis dbul /
NK025(ra)001:3656: dbang po rdo rje 'chang ba la sogs pa bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:3658: phyogs skyong gi tho 'dzugs par 'dod na sgrub khang gi phyogs mtshams brgyad du tho re /
NK025(ra)001:3660: 'og gi tho nub smad du brtsig cing /
NK025(ra)001:3661: so so'i sku brnyan nam sngags byang gang bde ras sam shing byang la bris pa /
NK025(ra)001:3662: so so'i mdun du mchod pa dang zlum gtor re re bshams la /
NK025(ra)001:3663: thog mar steng gi tho nas brtsam tho so so'i rtsar phyin la /
NK025(ra)001:3664: rta mgrin gyi nga rgyal la gnas bzhin pas mchod
NK025(ra)001:3665: gtor rnams snga ma ltar bsang sbyang byin gyis brlab
NK025(ra)001:3666: / thugs ka'i b+h+r+aum gyi 'phro 'du las tho gzhal
NK025(ra)001:3667: yas khang du bskyed pa'i steng gi tho'i nang du
NK025(ra)001:3668: tshangs pa ser po gdong bzhi pa gun+d+he bsnams pa
NK025(ra)001:3670: shar gyi tho'i nang du brgya byin ser po rdo rje 'dzin pa glang po che la zhon pa /
NK025(ra)001:3671: shar lho'i tho'i nang du me lha dmar po me thab 'dzin pa ra skyes la zhon pa /
NK025(ra)001:3672: lho'i tho'i nang du gshin rje sngon po be con 'dzin pa ma he la zhon pa /
NK025(ra)001:3673: lho nub kyi tho'i nang du srin po smug nag ral gri 'dzin pa ro langs la zhon pa /
NK025(ra)001:3674: nub kyi tho'i nang du chu lha dkar po sbrul zhags 'dzin ba chu srin la zhon pa /
NK025(ra)001:3675: nub byang gi tho'i nang du rlung lha sngon po ba dan 'dzin pa sha ba la zhon pa /
NK025(ra)001:3676: byang gi tho'i nang du gnod sbyin ser po dbyug pa 'dzin pa rta la zhon pa /
NK025(ra)001:3677: byang shar gyi tho'i nang du dbang ldan dkar po rtse gsum 'dzin pa glang la zhon pa /
NK025(ra)001:3678: 'og gi tho'i nang du sa lha ser mo bum pa 'dzin pa phag la zhon pa rnams bskyed /
NK025(ra)001:3679: gong ltar gnas gsum byin gyis brlab /
NK025(ra)001:3680: tshangs pa la brah+ma ne s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:3681: brgya byin la in+d+ra ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:3682: me lhar ag+ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:3683: gshin rjer ya ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:3684: srin por n+air+t+ya ta ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:3685: chu lhar wa ru na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:3686: rlung lhar w+aa ya we ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:3687: gnod sbyin la ku be r+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:3688: dbang ldan la i sh+aa na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:3689: sa lhar pri thi wi de w+ai s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:3690: mtshan sngags de rnams la s+w+aa h+aa dor la h+aum dzahsbyara bas bkug la bstim /
NK025(ra)001:3691: s+w+aa h+aa dor la ar+g+ham sogs mchod sngags btags /
NK025(ra)001:3692: pany+tsa a mri tas bdud rtsi 'bul /
NK025(ra)001:3693: ba lin+ta bdun nam gsum gyis gtor ma phul /
NK025(ra)001:3694: dbang po rdo rje sogs so so'i bstod pa bya /
NK025(ra)001:3696: sngon lcang lo can gyi pho brang du ston pa zhal bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK025(ra)001:3697: chos kyi bstan tshogs chen po mdzad pa la thugs dgongs te /
NK025(ra)001:3698: mgon po mi 'gyur ba'i gdan la bzhugs nas phyi
NK025(ra)001:3699: mtshams skyong bar zhal gyis bzhes pa de bzhin du
NK025(ra)001:3700: / bdag gi gsang sgrub gnyan po 'di ma thon
NK025(ra)001:3701: gyi bar du phyi'i dgra bgegs nang du mi btang
NK025(ra)001:3702: zhing nang gi dngos grub phyir mi btang ba dang
NK025(ra)001:3703: / / dngos grub kyi stong grogs dang phyi mtshams
NK025(ra)001:3704: bsrung ba'i sngon gyi phrin las thugs dam las mi
NK025(ra)001:3707: 'dod gsol 'di zur lugs khams lugs gnyis kar cher mi gsal yang /
NK025(ra)001:3708: sngon gyi tho'i tsakli rnying pa'i rgyab byang las bris so //
NK025(ra)001:3709: rgyal tho dang phyogs skyong gi tho rnams la sgrub pa ma grol bar brtan bzhugs phrin bcol bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:3710: 'on kyang spros pa che na 'di bzhin bya zhing /
NK025(ra)001:3711: deng sang phyag bzhes su phyogs skyong bcu'i tho 'dzugs
NK025(ra)001:3712: mi mdzad pa shas che bas dbye bsdu skabs sbyar
NK025(ra)001:3713: bya'o // de ltar phyi'i bar mtshams rgyal chen bzhi'i tho 'dzugs ba sogs grub nas /
NK025(ra)001:3715: de nas nang du 'dus la gral phyag tshul phyag bya /
NK025(ra)001:3716: thun mong srung ba'i 'khor los mtshams bcad /
NK025(ra)001:3718: slob dpon thams cad 'dus te gral phyag dang tshul phyag bya ba la /
NK025(ra)001:3719: g.yung 'grel gyi zhi ba'i le'u bdun pa'i skabs su sngon 'gro ni tshul phyag dang /
NK025(ra)001:3725: nang dang phyi'i mchod pa byin gyis brlab ba rnams sgrub thabs kyi las byang ltar bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:3728: khro bo'i skabs su yang tshul phyag bya /
NK025(ra)001:3729: mtshams bcad ces sogs sngon 'gro'i yan lag tu bshad /
NK025(ra)001:3730: de yang zhi khro gnyis kyi sgrub thabs ni /
NK025(ra)001:3731: pan+di ta chen po sangs rgyas gsang ba'i zhi ba rin chen d+r+wa ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:3732: khro bo dam pa rgyan gnyis yin mod kyang /
NK025(ra)001:3733: rgya gzhung du song bas rgyud tshig lta bu'i don
NK025(ra)001:3734: bzang zhing tshig barlinga bas sgom don gsal 'debs tsam
NK025(ra)001:3735: las mtshams sbyor dang sa bcad sogs mi gsal bar
NK025(ra)001:3736: / bla ma gong ma rnams kyi chog khrigs mi gcig pa du ma 'byung bar zad /
NK025(ra)001:3737: 'on kyang khungs che ba par ma'i rgyun sogs 'dug
NK025(ra)001:3738: kyang tshul phyag bya zer ba tsam las 'di yin
NK025(ra)001:3739: gyi gsal kha mi snang zhing /
NK025(ra)001:3740: g.yung ston gyi zhi ba'i dbang byang dang /
NK025(ra)001:3741: sgrol ma ba sangs rgyas rin chen gyi khro bo'i
NK025(ra)001:3742: dbang byang sogs las kyang tshul phyag bya zer ba
NK025(ra)001:3743: tsam las gsal kha mi snang bas bya dka' bar
NK025(ra)001:3744: gyur kyang / zhi khro phur gsum dang bka' brgyad
NK025(ra)001:3745: dril ba'i chog khrigs yig rnying zhig las tshul phyag
NK025(ra)001:3746: skyabs 'gro drug skor la ngos bzung ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:3747: gral phyag ni bla ma nas bzung zhi khro chos
NK025(ra)001:3748: srung rnams kyi bar du phyag 'tshal ba la ngos
NK025(ra)001:3749: bzung ba dang / zhi ba rin chen d+r+wa ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:3750: khro bo dam pa rgyan gyi sgom khog mngon par rtogs pa'i man ngag las /
NK025(ra)001:3752: rnal 'byor ba rnams nang du 'dus la dkyil 'khor
NK025(ra)001:3753: gyi mthar 'khod de sa ma ya dzahzhesa dpang po'i
NK025(ra)001:3754: lha 'og nas 'byung ba bzhin spyan drangs la /
NK025(ra)001:3755: bdag gi lus rdul snyed du sprul nas /
NK025(ra)001:3756: grub na rnal 'byor rgyun bshags rgyas par bya /
NK025(ra)001:3757: de ma grub na bla ma dang mkha' 'gro la phyag gsum btsal /
NK025(ra)001:3758: yi dam gyi lha zhi khro la phyag gsum btsal /
NK025(ra)001:3760: de ni sngon gyi tshul bzang po'i rjes su zhugs pas tshul phyag ces bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:3761: de nas rdo rje slob dpon gdan la bzhugs la kun gyi phyag gsum gsum btsal lo //
NK025(ra)001:3762: de nas dbang gang snga ba nas rim pa bzhin du gsum gsum btsal lo //
NK025(ra)001:3763: des dbang gral gyi rim pa bzhin du thob pas na gral phyag ces bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:3765: rdo rje 'dus pa'i dbang gral du //
NK025(ra)001:3766: rdo rje don gyi stangs chen gsher //
NK025(ra)001:3768: des gral phyag dang tshul phyag bya ba de thal /
NK025(ra)001:3769: zhes 'byung bas shin tu khungs btsun zhing don gyi
NK025(ra)001:3770: 'brel chags pa lung dang bcas 'thad par snang bas
NK025(ra)001:3772: dpang po'i lha spyan 'dren 'og nas 'byung ba bzhin bya ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:3774: sa ma ya dzahzhesa rdo rje se gol g.yas su
NK025(ra)001:3775: gtogs pas bcom ldan 'das zhi ba'i lha tshogs thams
NK025(ra)001:3777: g.yon du gtogs pas khrag 'thung khro bo'i lha tshogs thams cad g.yon du spyan drangs /
NK025(ra)001:3778: dbus su gtogs pas bla ma dang mkha' 'gro rnams
NK025(ra)001:3779: mdun gyi nam mkha' la thibs kyi byon nas sprin
NK025(ra)001:3780: gtibs pa lta bur bzhugs par bsam zhes 'byung zhing
NK025(ra)001:3781: / se ston rin po che'i tshe bdag rnam nges
NK025(ra)001:3782: su yang de ltar bshad pa ltar tshogs zhing spyan
NK025(ra)001:3783: / drangs la / tshul phyag ni grub na rgyun bshags dang /
NK025(ra)001:3784: ma grub na rtsa ba gsum la phyag dgu phrugs su bya bar gsungs /
NK025(ra)001:3785: spyir dri med bshags rgyud nas 'byung ba'i /
NK025(ra)001:3786: ye shes sku mchog rang bzhin dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK025(ra)001:3787: zhes sogs la bshags rgyud du /
NK025(ra)001:3788: brjod med kyi bshags par grags shing /
NK025(ra)001:3789: yang phur gyi rdzogs rim mnyam med bsam gtan gling
NK025(ra)001:3790: ba'i a tir brjod med la lta ba'i klong bshags
NK025(ra)001:3791: su btags shing / gang ltar yang rung bas na /
NK025(ra)001:3792: de la bshad tshul gyi dbang du byas na /
NK025(ra)001:3793: bdag nyid chen po rigs lnga yab yum dang //
NK025(ra)001:3794: byang chub lcam dral khro bo khro mo'i tshogs //
NK025(ra)001:3796: phyi nang mkha' 'gro rnal 'byor ma yi tshogs //
NK025(ra)001:3797: zhes pa yan la rtsa ba gsum gyi lha tshogs tshang tshul dang /
NK025(ra)001:3799: brjod med shes rab mi g.yo chos kyi sku //
NK025(ra)001:3800: sogs sh+lo ka gcig la rtogs pa'i mjal phyag dang /
NK025(ra)001:3801: phyag bsdus pa tshang ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:3802: thugs rje'i gdung 'tshob rig 'dzin bdag cag gis //
NK025(ra)001:3803: zhes pa man chod la bshags pa rnams tshang tshul
NK025(ra)001:3804: gzhung du mar 'byung bas tshul phyag gi skabs 'dir
NK025(ra)001:3805: dpang po'i lha spyan drangs rjes dpon slob rnams lhan
NK025(ra)001:3806: cig tu phyag bya ba dang bstun ye shes sku
NK025(ra)001:3807: mchog gi bshags pa tshar gcig gsung na 'thad par
NK025(ra)001:3808: mthong / de nas slob dpon khrir bzhugs pa la /
NK025(ra)001:3809: sgrub mched thams cad kyis phyag gsum gsum btsal zhing /
NK025(ra)001:3810: dbang gang snga ba nas phyag gsum rim bzhin 'tshal bar gsungs pa /
NK025(ra)001:3811: 'dul bar rgan rim gyi phyag bya ba dang chos
NK025(ra)001:3812: mtshungs par dkyil 'khor du dbang thob pa snga rim
NK025(ra)001:3813: gyi phyag bya ba yin 'dug kyang /
NK025(ra)001:3814: sgrub mched rnams tshan gnyis su bcad de phan tshun
NK025(ra)001:3815: du phyag gsum re btsal bas 'jug pa bde zhing
NK025(ra)001:3817: des tshul phyag dang gral phyag 'tshal ba legs par grub /
NK025(ra)001:3818: thun mong srung ba'i 'khor los mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:3819: spyir rdo rje dang me ri la thun mong dang /
NK025(ra)001:3820: 'khor lo khro bo bcu dang bcas par thun mong ma yin par bshad kyang /
NK025(ra)001:3822: rdo rje gnod sbyin gyi mtshams /
NK025(ra)001:3825: khrag 'thung rigs lnga'i mtshams dang bzhir bshad pas /
NK025(ra)001:3827: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:3831: khro bo bcus g.yas skor du bgegs dang log 'dren tshar bcad /
NK025(ra)001:3832: g.yon skor du khro bo'i gur chen por gyur par bsam mo //
NK025(ra)001:3834: phyi'i nang mtshams dam sri mnan pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:3835: bar chad bgegs dang ye shes lha gnyis las /
NK025(ra)001:3837: rang ya m+aan+ta kar bskyed la /
NK025(ra)001:3838: rang bzhin dag pa'i ngo bo la //
NK025(ra)001:3839: zhes sogs kyi tshigs bcad rjes su sngags dang /
NK025(ra)001:3841: ling ga'i sker thag pa nag po btags pa la
NK025(ra)001:3842: 'gugs 'dren byas la mgo mthur du bstan la mnan
NK025(ra)001:3843: / zhes pa tsam las ma gsungs shing /
NK025(ra)001:3844: glan ston bsod nams mgon pos /
NK025(ra)001:3845: de nas them pa'i phyir rol tu dam sri rgyas par las mkhan gyis phur pa bzhin mnan la /
NK025(ra)001:3846: sgo byang gdags te bar chad bgegs dang ye shes lha gnyis las /
NK025(ra)001:3847: dang po ni dam sri'i 'gugs 'dren byas la dam sri bcug pa'i cho ga bya ste /
NK025(ra)001:3849: rang bzhin dag pa'i ngo bo la //
NK025(ra)001:3850: zhes sogs gong ltar bshad cing /
NK025(ra)001:3851: gzhung de nyid kyis dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi sngon 'gro bshad pa'i skabs su /
NK025(ra)001:3852: phur pa drug skor gyis dam sri'i mgo brdungs te /
NK025(ra)001:3853: de yang ngag nus dang ldan pa'i sngags pa gnyis
NK025(ra)001:3854: kyis rdo rje phur pa'i phrin chog tshang ba zhig
NK025(ra)001:3855: gyer nas / tshogs tha ma'i dus su bstan pa
NK025(ra)001:3856: la gnod pa'i dgra dang bgegs gang rung ba'i ling
NK025(ra)001:3857: ga bris la dgug gzhug bya ste /
NK025(ra)001:3858: them pa'i phyi rol du dong gru gsum pa brus par mnan la drag po'i bro bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:3861: rang ya m+aan+ta kar bskyed tshul gsungs pa ni ye
NK025(ra)001:3862: shes lha'i sgo byang gi dbang du mdzad pa yin
NK025(ra)001:3863: kyang / glan ston gyi dgongs pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:3864: snga 'gyur bka' gter gyi gzhung phal mo cher /
NK025(ra)001:3865: dam sri'i gnyen por phur pa basngagasa pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:3866: drag po'i las phal cher rdo rje gzhon nu la brten na shis par bshad pas /
NK025(ra)001:3867: skabs 'dir bka' gter gyi phur ba khyer bde ba zhig gi gzhung srong ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:3868: sman raka gtor gsum nyer spyod tsam la brten nas phrin las gyer /
NK025(ra)001:3870: tshogs thog ma dbul ba dang bar pa bshags pa'i bar du bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:3871: skabs 'dir zur lugs kyi brgyud pa rin po che 'di'i phyag bzhes su /
NK025(ra)001:3872: sngags 'chang chen po skyi ston tshe ring dbang po'i
NK025(ra)001:3873: phyag len bla chen bres gshongs pa chos rgyal rdo
NK025(ra)001:3874: rje zin bris su mdzad pa las /
NK025(ra)001:3875: ging pa dkar nag gi 'bag 'chams dang rdo rje slob dpon chas su zhugs /
NK025(ra)001:3877: spros pa'i yan lag tu 'dug pa spro na bya /
NK025(ra)001:3878: mi spro yang chad pa'i skyon med /
NK025(ra)001:3879: ling+ga bri ba ni rtsa bar gsal kha ma gsungs kyang zin bris de nyid las /
NK025(ra)001:3880: shog bu rang gi dri ma 'phog pa la dam
NK025(ra)001:3881: sri mi gzugs bya'i mgo can rkang lag lcags sgrog
NK025(ra)001:3882: gis bcings pa'i snying gar pho la tri tri dang
NK025(ra)001:3883: mo la sri sri bya ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:3884: lto bar sgrub pa la bar du gcod pa'i dam sri m+aa ra ya phata bya ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:3885: gzhan ling+ga spyi dang mthun par bris la /
NK025(ra)001:3886: mtha' ma rgya gram dza ram bskor zhes gsungs shing /
NK025(ra)001:3887: g.yung ston pa'i sgyu 'phrul zhi ba'i dbang byang du dam sri'i gzugs rid pa /
NK025(ra)001:3889: lag pas skra 'bal zhing brang brdung ba bri /
NK025(ra)001:3890: yang ra sog la bgegs kyi sgo byang dam sri'i gzugs zhig bris la /
NK025(ra)001:3891: de gnyis ka'i dpral bar rus /
NK025(ra)001:3893: 'doms su sgrub pa la bar du gcod pa'i dam sri m+aa ra ya phata /
NK025(ra)001:3896: zhes gsungs pa rnams kyi don /
NK025(ra)001:3898: dgra dang bgegs gang rung gi ling ga bris la /
NK025(ra)001:3899: zhes gsungs pa ltar na spyir btang gi dgra bgegs
NK025(ra)001:3900: las dam sri ngos ma zin pa'i skyon 'jug pa
NK025(ra)001:3901: dang / bla chen bres pa'i zin bris su /
NK025(ra)001:3902: dam sri mi lus bya mgo can bri bar bshad
NK025(ra)001:3903: na gnas yig bri ba'i skabs su pho la tri
NK025(ra)001:3904: tri dang mo la sri sri /
NK025(ra)001:3905: zhes gsungs pa phyogs gcig na dam sri la pho
NK025(ra)001:3906: mo gnyis ka bshad pa'i dbang gis mi 'gal yang
NK025(ra)001:3908: dam sri mo bya mchu can zhes snga 'gyur bka' gter spyir bshad pas bya mgo bris zin nas /
NK025(ra)001:3909: pho mo'i khyad par gyi srog yig bri ba mi rigs shing /
NK025(ra)001:3910: g.yung ston gyi dam sri dang bgegs gnyis su mdzad pa ni shin tu legs pas /
NK025(ra)001:3911: spyir dam sri yin na bgegs yin pas khyab mod kyang /
NK025(ra)001:3912: dam sri ni sgrub pa'i bar chod kho nar basngagasa
NK025(ra)001:3913: pa'i he ru ka gal po sogs las bshad pa'i
NK025(ra)001:3914: dus bcur rgyu ba'i nyul le dang /
NK025(ra)001:3915: phal la dus drug tu rgyu bar bshad pa'i nyil le'i rigs can gyi dam sri rnams yin la /
NK025(ra)001:3917: bgegs rigs stong phrag brgyad cus mtshon pa'i 'dre srin
NK025(ra)001:3918: phal la bshad pas shin tu 'chad tshul legs par
NK025(ra)001:3919: snang / 'on kyang phyag len 'jug pa bde phyir
NK025(ra)001:3920: bka' brgyad yongs rdzogs sogs las dam sri bya mchu
NK025(ra)001:3921: ma'i gzugs bri bar gsungs pa kho na legs pas
NK025(ra)001:3922: snang / / dug shog la mo gzugs bya mgo
NK025(ra)001:3923: can rkang lag lcags sgrog gis bsdams shing mchu bcings
NK025(ra)001:3924: pa nyam thag pa bris pa'i yan lag bzhi la
NK025(ra)001:3925: snang / / dzahh+aum bam hohdang / m+aa ra ya rbad /
NK025(ra)001:3926: lag nywa gnyis su chag chag /
NK025(ra)001:3927: rkang nywa gnyis su zha zha dang na tri rgad /
NK025(ra)001:3932: snying gar tri la dzahkha sprod /
NK025(ra)001:3933: de'i mthar yig mgo phyir bstan gyi ya ma dam
NK025(ra)001:3934: sri gam pa ri m+aa ra ya dzahdzahnana hri'u tri'u
NK025(ra)001:3935: ya na ma sh+aa dza khug nan /
NK025(ra)001:3936: sgrub pa la bar du gcod pa'i dam sri mo
NK025(ra)001:3937: bya mchu can gtso bor gyur pa'i dam sri rgyal
NK025(ra)001:3938: 'gong rgya 'dre sogs kyi bla srog rnam par shes
NK025(ra)001:3939: pa dmigs pa'i rten 'dir 'gugs chings sdom myos m+aa
NK025(ra)001:3940: ra ya phata / ces sogs lto ba che chung
NK025(ra)001:3941: dang bstun pa'i spel tshig rigs pas dpyad la bri
NK025(ra)001:3942: ra ya phata / / mgo nas brtsams yig mgo
NK025(ra)001:3943: nang bstan gyi log 'dren dam sri 'byung po ya
NK025(ra)001:3944: ma dam sri bgegs rigs rgyal 'gong rgya 'dre bsam
NK025(ra)001:3945: ngan sbyor rtsub 'chang ba rnams kyi lus ngag yid
NK025(ra)001:3946: gsum mthu stobs rdzu 'phrul bsod nams kha rje dbang
NK025(ra)001:3947: thang rlung rta nus pa thams cad gnon cig /
NK025(ra)001:3949: m+aa ra ya lam nan sogs gong bzhin rigs pas
NK025(ra)001:3950: dpyad de bris pa'i phyir dza khram nyer gcig bris
NK025(ra)001:3951: pa la / me chu sa rlung nam mkhas sbyang ba legs par byas te /
NK025(ra)001:3952: dug khrag gis byugs la sgo byang 'dogs pa'i sgo
NK025(ra)001:3953: them gyi 'og tu dong gru gsum brus pa'i khar
NK025(ra)001:3954: lcags slang gi nang du bkod de tshon skud kyis
NK025(ra)001:3955: bskor / lcags zangs rdo phye gsum dang yungs kar nag gi thun dang /
NK025(ra)001:3956: gu gul sol me dang bcas pa /
NK025(ra)001:3959: bla chen bres pa'i zin bris su /
NK025(ra)001:3960: gzu dpang gser skyems byas la bden pa brdar ba tsam las mi 'dug cing /
NK025(ra)001:3961: mkhas grub g.yung ston chen pos /
NK025(ra)001:3962: e ram gyis drag po'i dkyil 'khor bskyed /
NK025(ra)001:3963: ba hus lha las la gzud /
NK025(ra)001:3964: pho nya drug bskor btang la sprul pa spro /
NK025(ra)001:3969: lag sor dang phur pa byin gyis brlab /
NK025(ra)001:3970: g+ha ta ya'i sngags kyis ling+ga la phur pa gdab /
NK025(ra)001:3971: ces sogs rgyas par 'byung ba glan ston gyi dgongs pa dang yang mthun pas /
NK025(ra)001:3972: gzhung de rnams kyi don nyams su blang ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:3973: slob dpon rdo rje gzhon nu'i nga rgyal gyis drag
NK025(ra)001:3974: po'i chas su zhugs pa dang ging dkar nag gi
NK025(ra)001:3975: chas zhugs gnyis bcas rol mor bcas pas thon te
NK025(ra)001:3976: / dong khar gser skyems ram yam kham gis bsregs gtor bkrus /
NK025(ra)001:3977: +aahh+aum lan gsum gyis bdud rtsir byin gyis brlabs te /
NK025(ra)001:3978: bla ma rgyal ba zhi khro rab 'byams chos srung
NK025(ra)001:3979: dang bcas pa dmigs yul du byas te mkhyen par
NK025(ra)001:3980: gsol zhing gzu dpang bya ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:3982: mkhyen cig dgongs shig dus gsum bde gshegs rnams //
NK025(ra)001:3983: gdod ma'i mgon po kun tu bzang nas bzung //
NK025(ra)001:3984: tshig gsum bla ma ma lus snyan gson cig /
NK025(ra)001:3985: bdag gi rtse gcig dad pa'i sems kyis kyang //
NK025(ra)001:3986: 'phags pa mchod cing 'gro don bgyid snyam pas //
NK025(ra)001:3987: dam nyams dgra bo 'di yis ma ster ro //
NK025(ra)001:3988: ma gnod ye shes lha la mkhyen par gsol //
NK025(ra)001:3989: zhi ba rdor dbyings khrag 'thung lnga bcu sogs //
NK025(ra)001:3990: yi dam lha tshogs ma lus snyan bdag ni bskyed rdzogs zab mo'i ngang nyid nas //
NK025(ra)001:3991: bsnyen sgrub mtha' dbyung las bzhi spyod snyam pas //
NK025(ra)001:3992: las ngan dgra bo 'di ma gnod ye shes lha rdo rje phag mo ye shes mgon po'i tshogs //
NK025(ra)001:3993: mkha' 'gro chos skyong tshogs rnams snyan bdag ni khyed rnams bsgrub bsten mchod pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:3994: thugs dam bskang zhing las la bskul snyam pas //
NK025(ra)001:3995: dam nyams dgra bo 'di ma gnod ye shes lha zhes mkhyen par gsol lo //
NK025(ra)001:3998: 'gro ba'i dpal mgon bcom ldan sh+aaka thub la /
NK025(ra)001:3999: sdig can lha byin ngan pas brnyas btsugs so //
NK025(ra)001:4000: che rtags sku la ngur smrig gsol byas nas //
NK025(ra)001:4001: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas thob pa don ma chung //
NK025(ra)001:4002: su bden kun mkhyen mgon pos dpang mdzod cig /
NK025(ra)001:4003: yongs la dbang po'i sa bdag rgyal po la //
NK025(ra)001:4004: mtha' 'khob rgyal phran ngan pas brnyas btsugs so //
NK025(ra)001:4005: che rtags dbu la dar thod brgyan byas shing //
NK025(ra)001:4006: rgyal khrims tshul bzhin bskyangs pa don ma chung //
NK025(ra)001:4007: su bden kun mkhyen nam mkhar gnas pa'i bya khyung g+aa ru dar //
NK025(ra)001:4008: ltas ngan srin bya ngan pas brnyas che rtags dbu la nor bus brgyan byas shing //
NK025(ra)001:4009: 'dab gshog spu gris gtams pa don su bden kun
NK025(ra)001:4010: mkhyen bar snang gnas pa'i g.yu 'brug sngon po la
NK025(ra)001:4011: // ltas ngan bung ba ser pos brnyas che rtags lce la glog gis brgyan byas nas //
NK025(ra)001:4012: stong gsum sgra yis bkang ba don su bden kun
NK025(ra)001:4013: mkhyen gangs la gnas pa'i seng ge dkar mo la
NK025(ra)001:4014: // dur khrod wa skya ngan pas brnyas che rtags mgo la g.yu ral brgyan byas shing //
NK025(ra)001:4015: rtsal gsum lus la rdzoogs pa don su bden kun mkhyen rig 'dzin slob dpon pad+m+aa ka ra la //
NK025(ra)001:4016: mtha' 'khob lha srin ngan pas brnyas che rtags gser gyi rdo rje bsnams byas nas //
NK025(ra)001:4017: sgrub pa'i rig 'dzin brnyes pa don su bden kun
NK025(ra)001:4018: mkhyen chos bzhin byed pa'i rnal 'byor bdag cag la
NK025(ra)001:4019: // las ngan dgra bo rnams kyis brnyas che rtags bsnyen sgrub rnam bzhi mthar phyin zhing //
NK025(ra)001:4020: rim gnyis zab mo bsgoms pa don su bden kun mkhyen mgon pos dpang mdzod cig /
NK025(ra)001:4022: brub khung dong dang bcas bskyed pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:4023: e ram dz+wa la ram zhes brjod pas /
NK025(ra)001:4024: brub dong 'di nyid gnam lcags las grub pa'i e khang gru gsum 'jigs su rung ba /
NK025(ra)001:4025: phyi mthing nag gru gsum du 'dug pa /
NK025(ra)001:4026: nang dmar nag gru gsum du 'dug pa /
NK025(ra)001:4027: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa'i rtags su zur gsum dang ldan pa /
NK025(ra)001:4028: dug gsum dbyings su sgrol ba'i rtags su bang rim gsum dang ldan pa /
NK025(ra)001:4029: bdud dang gshin rje'i dpung gis mi tshugs pa'i phyir
NK025(ra)001:4030: phyi mkhar thabs su yod pa'i rtse la drag po
NK025(ra)001:4031: rtsang gi d+r+wa mig ris su btsugs pa /
NK025(ra)001:4032: phyi na zhe sdang gi me 'bar ba /
NK025(ra)001:4033: nang na 'dod chags kyi rlung 'khrug pa /
NK025(ra)001:4034: bar na gti mug gi mun pa 'thibs pa /
NK025(ra)001:4035: shar na shal ma ri'i sdong po /
NK025(ra)001:4036: lhor thal tshan gyi chu bo rab med /
NK025(ra)001:4038: byang du spu gri'i thang gis bskor ba /
NK025(ra)001:4039: bka'i lha ma srin sde brgyad kyi 'du sa /
NK025(ra)001:4040: phra men nyul le rnams kyi skos khang /
NK025(ra)001:4041: ma gshin sgrol ging rnams kyi tshogs khang /
NK025(ra)001:4042: 'chi bdag las kyi gshin rje'i bshas khang nag po 'jigs su rung ba zhig tu gyur /
NK025(ra)001:4043: n+ri tri dzah brub dong 'di nyid kyi nang du
NK025(ra)001:4044: yi ge tri yongs su gyur pa las gnod cing
NK025(ra)001:4045: 'tshe bar byed pa'i dam sri mo bya mchu can
NK025(ra)001:4046: dang / gzhan yang 'dre gzugs lus rid pa /
NK025(ra)001:4049: lag pa mya ngan gyi phyag rgya byas pa /
NK025(ra)001:4050: byang sems dkar dmar mthur du 'bab pa /
NK025(ra)001:4051: gcer bu byang thang la bton pa lta bu mgon
NK025(ra)001:4052: med skyabs dang bral ba 'dar yed yed pa zhig
NK025(ra)001:4053: tu gyur / pho nya btang ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:4054: g.yung gi dgongs pa ltar na /
NK025(ra)001:4055: ba hus lha las la gzud ces pa khro bo dam pa rgyan gyi tshogs tha ma'i dus ltar /
NK025(ra)001:4056: ba hus bi sogs kyi sngags bzla ba yin kyang
NK025(ra)001:4057: 'dir phur pa ltar rol mo dbyangs dang bcas te
NK025(ra)001:4059: dzah dam tshig chen po'i dus bab //
NK025(ra)001:4060: sprul pa chen po'i dus phyag brnyan chen po'i dus
NK025(ra)001:4061: shwa na mu kha'i dus bdag nyid chen po'i dus
NK025(ra)001:4062: khyod kyi phrin las dus sa bdag chen po'i dus
NK025(ra)001:4063: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus dgug 'dren ni /
NK025(ra)001:4064: h+aum mdzad kyi phyag rgya bcas la /
NK025(ra)001:4066: rgyal ba dgongs pa'i brgyud pa /
NK025(ra)001:4068: gang zag snyan khung gi brgyud pa /
NK025(ra)001:4070: smon lam dbang bskur gyi brgyud pa /
NK025(ra)001:4071: grub thob rnal 'byor gyi brgyud pa ste brgyud pa
NK025(ra)001:4072: drug ldan gyi dpal ldan bla ma dam pa rnams
NK025(ra)001:4074: sangs rgyas bka' chos kyi bka' dge 'dun gyi bka' phyi mtshan nyid kyi theg pa gsum /
NK025(ra)001:4075: nang gsang sngags kyi theg pa gsum /
NK025(ra)001:4076: gsang ba bla na med pa'i theg pa gsum ste
NK025(ra)001:4077: theg pa rim pa dgu dang 'brel ba yi dam
NK025(ra)001:4078: zhi khro rab 'byams kyi lha tshogs rnams kyi bka'
NK025(ra)001:4079: khyad par du yang 'jam dpal sku /
NK025(ra)001:4087: dmod pa drag sngags kyi lha tshogs rnams kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:4088: dpal ye shes kyi mgon po legs ldan nag po /
NK025(ra)001:4089: mnga' bdag dregs pa'i ded dpon bco brgyad /
NK025(ra)001:4090: dregs pa'i sde dpon sum cu la sogs te bka'
NK025(ra)001:4091: srung dam can rgya mtsho'i tshogs dang bcas pa'i bka'
NK025(ra)001:4092: rnal 'byor pa bdag gi sngags dang phyag rgya dang
NK025(ra)001:4094: chos kyi dbyings rang bzhin rnam par dag cing chos
NK025(ra)001:4095: can rgyu 'bras bslu ba med pa'i bka' bden pa
NK025(ra)001:4096: dang / bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK025(ra)001:4097: spyir sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa rin po che'i spyi dgra /
NK025(ra)001:4099: skye 'gro sems can yongs la gnod cing 'tshe ba /
NK025(ra)001:4100: khyad par bod khams 'phung bar byed pa'i rgya 'dre spun dgu /
NK025(ra)001:4104: gshin rje'i bu mo chu'i rgyal mtshan can ma dang /
NK025(ra)001:4105: pu tra nag mo hor mgo ma la sogs pa
NK025(ra)001:4106: sgrub pa'i bar chad rtsom pa'i ya ma dam sri'i
NK025(ra)001:4107: rigs su gyur ba thams cad rten 'di la skad
NK025(ra)001:4108: cig thang cig la myur du khug cig /
NK025(ra)001:4111: zhes rol mo drag po dang bcas lan gsum gyi rjes su dbyangs dang bcas te /
NK025(ra)001:4114: rang bzhin dag pa'i ngo bo la //
NK025(ra)001:4115: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis med de //
NK025(ra)001:4116: ma rtogs pa dang log par rtogs //
NK025(ra)001:4117: phyogs rtogs yang dag nyid ma rtogs //
NK025(ra)001:4118: sgrib pas sems dpangs dma' ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:4119: sems kyi rtog pas bcings pa yis //
NK025(ra)001:4120: gzhi stong ci la'ang bar chad byed //
NK025(ra)001:4121: rang gi dam tshig rang ma 'da' //
NK025(ra)001:4122: 'dzam bu'i gling gi lho phyogs na //
NK025(ra)001:4123: 'di nas dpag tshad brgyad khri na //
NK025(ra)001:4124: gshin rje'i rgyal po chos ston tshogs //
NK025(ra)001:4125: khyod kyi chos skal de ru nyon //
NK025(ra)001:4126: ma 'da' rang rang gnas su dengs //
NK025(ra)001:4127: sa ma ya ka pany+tsa rak+sha rak+sha h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4129: tshig 'di bgegs sprod 'dra ba zhig snang bas ha cang rigs pa ma mthong yang /
NK025(ra)001:4130: lugs 'di'i yig rnying phal cher la de ltar bshad
NK025(ra)001:4131: pas bsgyur bkod ma bde bas rang sor bzhag go
NK025(ra)001:4132: // 'on kyang g.yung ston chen pos gshin rje'i gnas su bskrad par bsam zhes gsungs pas /
NK025(ra)001:4133: 'og gi sa rim dgu'i mnan pa'i gnas kyang gshin rje'i gnas yin pas mi 'gal lam snyam /
NK025(ra)001:4134: de rjes phur pa'i gdab kha dngos ni /
NK025(ra)001:4135: phur pa drug skor ram gdab kha drug ste /
NK025(ra)001:4147: dmod pa ste drug tu dbye ba bka' gter gyi
NK025(ra)001:4148: man ngag rnams las 'byung yang 'dir mi 'grub pas
NK025(ra)001:4149: byang gter phur pa'i gdab khar de rnams don gyis
NK025(ra)001:4150: tshang bas 'jug pa bde zhing byin rlabs che bas
NK025(ra)001:4152: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed cing //
NK025(ra)001:4153: dus gsum rgyal ba'i gdung gsob pa //
NK025(ra)001:4154: rig 'dzin bdag cag rnams la ni //
NK025(ra)001:4155: gnod cing gdug pa'i dgra dang bgegs //
NK025(ra)001:4156: bdud dang bar du gcod pa rnams //
NK025(ra)001:4158: khro bo chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK025(ra)001:4159: yud tsam gyis ni 'dir bkug nas //
NK025(ra)001:4160: mngon spyod tshul bzhin bsgral ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:4161: lus ngag rdul du brlag nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:4162: sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:4163: badz+ra ad+gu sha dzah badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:4166: dngos grub bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK025(ra)001:4167: gdug cing sdang sems ldan pa rnams //
NK025(ra)001:4168: bzung zhig rgyob cig rnam par chings //
NK025(ra)001:4169: rtogs shig grogs dang bral bar gyis //
NK025(ra)001:4170: rings par khug la smyo ru chug /
NK025(ra)001:4171: phob cig rnam par gzir bar gyis //
NK025(ra)001:4172: nga yi dabangadu gyur nas ni //
NK025(ra)001:4173: bsgo ba'i bka' rnams nyan par byos //
NK025(ra)001:4174: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aana bam h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4175: lam h+aum lam s+t+wam b+ha ya nan /
NK025(ra)001:4176: mo ha g+ha ta ya b+ha ga w+aan /
NK025(ra)001:4177: hrihkri bi kri badz+ra h+aum k+aa ra h+aum h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4178: ma ra sa ni bra ma ya ti sarba big+h+n+aana pam h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4180: tshig dang bstun te phur thun rnams brdeg cing /
NK025(ra)001:4183: dam sri bya ba'i las ngan 'dis //
NK025(ra)001:4184: rdo rje slob dpon sku la bsdos //
NK025(ra)001:4185: rdo rje'i mched la bar chad byas //
NK025(ra)001:4186: rnal 'byor bdag la gnod byed cing //
NK025(ra)001:4187: rgyal khams yongs la gnod pa byas //
NK025(ra)001:4188: sbyor sgrol mang po'i sgo yang bkag /
NK025(ra)001:4189: bka' las 'da' byed dam sri rnams //
NK025(ra)001:4190: nam yang btang bar ma gsungs pas //
NK025(ra)001:4191: rdo rje khro bo'i phur pas btab //
NK025(ra)001:4192: lcags phye zangs phye rdo phyes brab //
NK025(ra)001:4193: gu gul sbyar ba'i dud pas bdug /
NK025(ra)001:4194: thun gyis brab cing mtshon chas gtub //
NK025(ra)001:4195: rdo rje srin po'i zhal du bstab //
NK025(ra)001:4196: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la sbyin //
NK025(ra)001:4197: ri rab brjid pa'i 'og tu mnan //
NK025(ra)001:4199: phur gdab ni g.yung gi dgongs pa ltar /
NK025(ra)001:4200: lag pa g.yas par ma s+aur+ya man+da la h+aum s+w+aa +aamhh+aa las rigs lnga yab lnga /
NK025(ra)001:4201: g.yon par a tsan+d+ra man+da la m+aum l+aam m+aam p+y+aam t+aam las yum lngar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:4205: rigs lnga yab yum snyoms par bzhugs pas sras mchog phur bu bskrun te /
NK025(ra)001:4206: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya phata dzah ha na
NK025(ra)001:4207: ha na dip+ta tsakra h+r+aih phur pa ta badz+ra sa
NK025(ra)001:4209: ces byin gyis brlabs te g+ha t+aa ya'i sngags bzla zhing ling+ga la gdab /
NK025(ra)001:4210: slar yang sngags de nyid kyis thun brab cing mtshon chas bsnun no //
NK025(ra)001:4212: yig rnying phal cher dang zur lugs glan lugs gnyis ka'i dgongs par /
NK025(ra)001:4213: bgegs kyi sgo byang ra sog la bris te them 'og tu spyi rting ldog ste gdags /
NK025(ra)001:4214: de'i thad kyi sgo gang du ye shes lha'i sgo byang 'dogs /
NK025(ra)001:4215: sgrub pa thon nas bgegs la phur gdab byas /
NK025(ra)001:4216: bdud rtsi stigs la dkyil 'khor gyi 'og tu mnan
NK025(ra)001:4217: par gsungs kyang lag len mi bde bas deng sang
NK025(ra)001:4218: phyag bzhes su dam sri gnon tshul spyi ltar mdzad
NK025(ra)001:4219: pas de lag len bde ba'i phyir na /
NK025(ra)001:4220: bla chen bres pa'i zin bris su /
NK025(ra)001:4221: shog ling blteb la tshon skud sna lnga gtsang mas bcings /
NK025(ra)001:4222: g.yag rur bcug la re ba nag pos kha dril /
NK025(ra)001:4223: them pa'i phyir dong gru gsum brus la sbas /
NK025(ra)001:4224: sa rim pa bcu dang rdo rje rgya gram gyi ri mo bcus mnan /
NK025(ra)001:4225: me dang chus mtshams bcad do //
NK025(ra)001:4226: zhes gsungs pa legs par snang bas ling+ga ro lteb byas tshon skud kyis bcings te /
NK025(ra)001:4227: g.yag ru ka lo mi bde bas glang 'og can gyi rwa me chus ma phog par bcug ste /
NK025(ra)001:4228: kha thun rdzas kyi lhag dang go thal gyis bcad
NK025(ra)001:4229: de re bas bstums pa slar yang tshon skud kyis
NK025(ra)001:4230: bcings / mtshams rnams su la thel gyi mnan te dong nang du bcug /
NK025(ra)001:4231: ro g.yam gyi phyogs gcig la ri rab gling bzhi
NK025(ra)001:4232: dang phyogs gcig la rdo rje rgya gram bris pas
NK025(ra)001:4233: mnan / sa rim pa bcu'am bdun g.yogs shing /
NK025(ra)001:4234: de rjes sa rdos bsubs te lag tshags dam par bya /
NK025(ra)001:4235: me chus rgyas btab ste bro brdung ni /
NK025(ra)001:4236: g.yung ston chen po'i dgongs pa ltar /
NK025(ra)001:4237: e b+h+r+aum zhes brjod pas nam mkha' rlung me chu
NK025(ra)001:4238: sa ri rab kyi steng drag po'i pho brang du
NK025(ra)001:4239: rdo rje gzhon nu'i dkyil 'khor bskyed la de'i nga
NK025(ra)001:4240: rgyal gyis rnal 'byor pa kun srin lag sbrel ba'i
NK025(ra)001:4241: bro ra gru gsum rtse mo lho bstan pa bcas
NK025(ra)001:4244: khro rgyal chen po sum+b+ha ni //
NK025(ra)001:4245: sum+b+ha ni yi nga rgyal gyis //
NK025(ra)001:4246: ri rab chen po'i sked nas gsor //
NK025(ra)001:4247: rgya mtsho chen po'i gting nas skem //
NK025(ra)001:4248: 'di la byang chub sems med kyi //
NK025(ra)001:4249: byang chub sems bskyed btang bar bya //
NK025(ra)001:4250: byang chub sems ni ma skyes par //
NK025(ra)001:4251: nam yang btang bar mi bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:4253: hoh bcom ldan 'das sum+b+ha ni dkyil dang 'khor du
NK025(ra)001:4254: bcas pa rnams la phrin las su gsol ba ni
NK025(ra)001:4255: / 'dir gsang sngags tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor chen po bzhengs su gsol bas /
NK025(ra)001:4256: bar du gcod pa'i ya ma dam sri la sogs
NK025(ra)001:4257: pa dgra bgegs gdug pa can thams cad thal ba'i
NK025(ra)001:4258: rdul du brlag par mdzad du gsol lo //
NK025(ra)001:4259: m+aa ra ya m+aa ra ya h+aum h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4260: su tri sa ma ya stram /
NK025(ra)001:4261: hoh khro bo chen po 'khor dang bcas pa thams cad gsan cing dgongs su gsol /
NK025(ra)001:4262: gsang sngags tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK025(ra)001:4263: tshogs rnams kyi sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub sgrub
NK025(ra)001:4264: pa'i phyir / sgrub pa po bdag cag gi bsam
NK025(ra)001:4265: pa yid bzhin du ma rdzogs kyi bar du sgrub
NK025(ra)001:4266: pa la bar du gcod par byed pa'i ya ma
NK025(ra)001:4267: dam sri la sogs pa gdug pa'i dgra bgegs thams
NK025(ra)001:4268: cad 'dul zhing bsgral du gsol lo //
NK025(ra)001:4269: sgrub pa'i dngos grub thams cad kyang yid bzhin du thob par mdzad du gsol lo //
NK025(ra)001:4270: des dam sri mnan pa tshar /
NK025(ra)001:4271: gnyis pa ye shes lha'i sgo byang ni /
NK025(ra)001:4273: de'i steng du khro bo'i gzugs lug sogs bris la sgo klad du gdags /
NK025(ra)001:4276: lug gam rkyang gi sog pa g.yon pa la khro bo gshin rje gshed po'i gzugs bri /
NK025(ra)001:4278: gnyis ka la mngon rtogs gsal bar ma byung yang /
NK025(ra)001:4280: rkyang ngam lug gi sog pa g.yon pa la khro
NK025(ra)001:4281: bo gshin rje gshed kyi gzugs nyi ma'i gdan la
NK025(ra)001:4282: gyad kyi dor stabs kyis bzhugs pa /
NK025(ra)001:4283: sku mdog smug nag be con dang 'khor lo bsnams pa khro bo'i cha byad can bris la /
NK025(ra)001:4285: pad nyi'i steng du ma he yod pa phyag len
NK025(ra)001:4286: ltar bris pa 'og gi dam sri'i mnan pa yod
NK025(ra)001:4287: pa'i thad kyi phyi'i sgo gong du btags pa'i mdun
NK025(ra)001:4288: du mchod gtor bshams pa rgyal tho'i skabs ltar byin
NK025(ra)001:4290: de ram yam kham gis sbyang /
NK025(ra)001:4291: sh+r+ai ya m+aan+ta ka h+aum sa ma ya dzahs snyan gsan bya /
NK025(ra)001:4292: zhes pa tsam las mi 'byung zhing /
NK025(ra)001:4293: glan ston dang g.yung ston gyis dam tshig pa bskyed par gsungs phyir lag len du 'di ltar /
NK025(ra)001:4294: bris sku ram yam kham dang sh+au nya t+aas sbyang /
NK025(ra)001:4295: stong pa'i ngang las h+aum s+pha ra na phata /
NK025(ra)001:4298: h+aum dang rtsa ba'i sngags kyi 'phro 'du las pad
NK025(ra)001:4299: nyi'i steng du gshin rje smug nag be con dang
NK025(ra)001:4300: 'khor lo can ma he'i steng du gyad kyi dor
NK025(ra)001:4301: stabs su bzhugs pa dur khrod kyi chas kyis brgyan
NK025(ra)001:4302: cing ye shes kyi me 'bar ba'i skur gyur /
NK025(ra)001:4304: dbang bskur byin rlabs bsdus pa bya zhes gsungs pas /
NK025(ra)001:4306: sh+r+ai ya m+aan+ta ka h+aum sa m+aa dzah bsdu ba'i phyag rgyas se gol gtogs /
NK025(ra)001:4310: khro bo'i rgyal po chen po gshin rje'i gshed //
NK025(ra)001:4311: dam tshig gnas mchog dam pa 'dir //
NK025(ra)001:4312: dam sri ma lus 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:4313: thugs rje'i dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:4316: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan nas /
NK025(ra)001:4317: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga gan+d+he'i bar gyi lha mo bzhi bsnol gyis mchod la /
NK025(ra)001:4319: sum cu rtsa gsum lha yi gnas mchog nas //
NK025(ra)001:4320: bcom ldan che mchog 'od kyi bka' stsal pa //
NK025(ra)001:4321: lha srin sde brgyad 'byung po'i dpon rnams kun //
NK025(ra)001:4322: sgrub pa mchog la deng 'dir bdag 'jug gi //
NK025(ra)001:4323: bla med byang chub 'bras bu ma thob par //
NK025(ra)001:4324: sgo 'di yan chad su yang ma 'da' zhig /
NK025(ra)001:4325: khro bo'i rgyal po gshin rje gshed la phrin las su gsol ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:4326: bdag cag la dngos grub kyi stong grogs dang phyi mtshams bsrung zhing nang mtshams bskyang ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:4327: khyad par sgrub pa ma tshar gyi bar du phyi'i dgra bgegs nang du ma btang /
NK025(ra)001:4328: nang gi dngos grub phyir ma btang /
NK025(ra)001:4329: rdo rje ya ma dam sri la sogs pa'i bar chad thams cad bsrung du gsol /
NK025(ra)001:4331: sgyu 'phrul dang 'dir gshin rje'i sgo byang ma gtogs gsal bar ma gsungs kyang /
NK025(ra)001:4332: da lta phyag bzhes su bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i sgo
NK025(ra)001:4333: byang yang 'dogs srol 'dug pas bka' brgyad sogs kyi
NK025(ra)001:4334: shan shor ba 'dra yang skyon du mi 'gyur zhing
NK025(ra)001:4335: / khyad par 'og tu sgrub dbang gi mtha' rten dus /
NK025(ra)001:4337: sgo byang phyi nang dgra bgegs skrod //
NK025(ra)001:4339: shin tu 'thad cing phun sum tshogs pa'i yan lag tu 'dug pas bya /
NK025(ra)001:4340: bla chen bres pa'i zin bris su phyi la bdud rtsi 'khyil ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:4341: nang du gshin rje 'dug kyang yig nor byung ba 'dra bas /
NK025(ra)001:4342: spyi ltar phyir gshin rjes bar chod bsrung zhing nang du 'khyil bas dngos grub ster ba 'thad pas /
NK025(ra)001:4343: ra sog la bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ljang gu rgya
NK025(ra)001:4344: gram dang thod khrag can khro tshul pad nyir brkyang
NK025(ra)001:4345: bskum gyis bzhengs pa bris te nang sgor btags /
NK025(ra)001:4346: mchod gtor bshams pa sngar ltar byin gyis brlabs te /
NK025(ra)001:4348: de nas gsang mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:4349: kun gyis langs la rdo rje thugs kar la mi rtog pa'i ngang la thugs kar h+aum bsam ste /
NK025(ra)001:4350: 'phro 'du las rdo rje rtse lnga pa /
NK025(ra)001:4352: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4353: ces pas bdag nyid bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ljang gu rdo rje rtse gsum thogs par bskyed la /
NK025(ra)001:4354: zhes gsungs pa ltar bdag bskyed gsal btab /
NK025(ra)001:4355: bris sku ram yam kham dang /
NK025(ra)001:4357: stong pa'i ngang las h+aum s+pha ra na phata /
NK025(ra)001:4359: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4360: sa bon dang sngags kyi 'phro 'du las khro bo
NK025(ra)001:4361: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ljang gu rgya gram dang thod
NK025(ra)001:4362: khrag 'dzin pa dur khrod kyi chas ldan ye shes
NK025(ra)001:4364: h+aum tram h+r+aih+aah +aahh+aum badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs snyan gsan dbab /
NK025(ra)001:4366: dzahh+aum bam hohs bstim la brtan par bya /
NK025(ra)001:4367: sngar bzhin kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod la /
NK025(ra)001:4368: khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil ba rten dang gnyis su
NK025(ra)001:4369: med par bzhugs nas gsang mtshams bsrung zhing dngos grub
NK025(ra)001:4370: ster ba'i phrin las mdzad du gsol /
NK025(ra)001:4375: gsang ba'i dam ldan so so nas //
NK025(ra)001:4376: 'du ba las ni ma gtogs pa //
NK025(ra)001:4377: thams cad thugs rje bskangs zin gyis //
NK025(ra)001:4378: da lta nyid du so sor dengs //
NK025(ra)001:4379: ci ste bka' las 'das gyur na //
NK025(ra)001:4380: rdo rje 'dzin rgyal khros nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:4381: rdo rje mtshon chen 'bar ba yis //
NK025(ra)001:4382: de ma thag tu bkas nas gshog /
NK025(ra)001:4383: bdun brgyud rigs kyang brlag par bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:4385: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK025(ra)001:4386: na mash+tsan+da badz+ra p+aa na ye /
NK025(ra)001:4387: ma h+aa yak+sha se na pa ta ye /
NK025(ra)001:4395: d+h+aa ra ya d+h+aa ra ya badz+ra /
NK025(ra)001:4396: d+h+aa ru na d+h+aa ru na badz+ra /
NK025(ra)001:4399: na mash+tsan+da badz+ra kro d+ha ya /
NK025(ra)001:4407: rang 'dra ba'i sprul pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK025(ra)001:4408: 'phros nas bgegs thams cad bskrad ces gsungs pa ltar
NK025(ra)001:4409: dmigs pa bya'o // h+aum zhes pa khro bo'i gur
NK025(ra)001:4410: du gyur nas bskal ba'i rlung yang mi thar bar
NK025(ra)001:4411: dmigs pa bya'o // bsam mo // rtsa ba las /
NK025(ra)001:4412: skabs 'dir gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la rdzas dgod pa bshad kyang /
NK025(ra)001:4413: phyag len du bar mtshams bcad pa 'dir blang ba yin pas /
NK025(ra)001:4415: de nas bar mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:4416: mi rtog pa'i ngang las bee ro tsa na /
NK025(ra)001:4417: zhes pas bdag nyid rnam par snang mdzad dkar po zhal gsum phyag drug pa /
NK025(ra)001:4418: zhal dbus dkar g.yas sngon g.yon dmar /
NK025(ra)001:4419: phyag dang po gnyis 'khor lo dang pad+ma /
NK025(ra)001:4420: bar ba gnyis rdo rje dang dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:4421: tha ma gnyis rin chen ral gri bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:4422: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan la bzhugs par bsam /
NK025(ra)001:4423: de'i thugs ka nas badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4424: ces pas mi g.yo ba zhal gsum phyag drug dbus sngo skya g.yas dkar g.yon dmar ba /
NK025(ra)001:4425: g.yas gsum rdo rje ral gri mda' /
NK025(ra)001:4426: g.yon gsum dgra s+t+wa zhags pa gzhu bsnams pa gcig phyungs nas mdun du bka' non du bsam /
NK025(ra)001:4429: na mahs man+ta'i sngags brjod cing /
NK025(ra)001:4431: me dpung zer ba rdo rje me'i sngags yin nam snyam yang /
NK025(ra)001:4432: glan ston gyis me'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK025(ra)001:4434: me'i dkyil 'khor gyis phyogs mtshams steng 'og thams cad
NK025(ra)001:4435: gang bar bsam pa yin nam snyam pa sogs som
NK025(ra)001:4436: nyi mang yang / skabs 'dir khams lugs su /
NK025(ra)001:4437: me yi dkyil 'khor la gnas snang mdzad kyis //
NK025(ra)001:4438: zhabs drung dbral dbyes nas phyung mi g.yo bran //
NK025(ra)001:4439: bdud las rnam rgyal phyag drug mda' gzhu dang //
NK025(ra)001:4440: ral gri zhags bsnams rdo rje'i char 'bebs pa //
NK025(ra)001:4441: khro bo grangs 'das pas ni rab bskor te //
NK025(ra)001:4442: bgegs rnams skrag mdzad h+aum gi sgras bkang nas //
NK025(ra)001:4443: 'jig rten gsum po gang bas rnam par 'jigs //
NK025(ra)001:4444: thams cad ma lus rdul du brlag par byos //
NK025(ra)001:4446: na mahs man+ta b+hu te nan /
NK025(ra)001:4447: a tsa la tsan+da ma h+aa ro sha na s+pho ta ya kham kham zhes gsungs pas /
NK025(ra)001:4448: me dpung gi dbus na bzhugs pa'i mi g.yo bas
NK025(ra)001:4449: sprul pa spros te bgegs skrod dmigs sngags dang bcas
NK025(ra)001:4450: gsal bar 'dug pas legs bshad du snang ba bzhin
NK025(ra)001:4453: ral gri'i phyag rgya g.yas nas klad la bskor bas bgegs thams cad bskrad /
NK025(ra)001:4454: g.yon nas bskor bas ral gri'i gur du bsam mo //
NK025(ra)001:4455: zhes gsungs pa ltar phyag rgya bca' zhing dmigs pas gsal btab bo //
NK025(ra)001:4456: gzhung du skabs 'dir bsnyen dbang byung yang /
NK025(ra)001:4457: phyag bzhes dang man ngag tu skabs 'dir ma tram bsgral bar mdzad pas rgyu mtshan ci'i phyir na /
NK025(ra)001:4458: 'og tu spyi don bzhi pa dkyil 'khor sgrub zhag gi cho ga bstan pa'i skabs su /
NK025(ra)001:4459: ma tram mnan cing gsang mtshams bcad /
NK025(ra)001:4460: khro bo bcu'i stangs stabs kyis dam sri brdung /
NK025(ra)001:4463: dam sri mnan nas ma tram bsgral zhes kyang 'byung bas /
NK025(ra)001:4464: dam sri mnan pa dang sgo byang gdags pa gnyis 'brel mtshungs su bshad phyir gong du grub pas /
NK025(ra)001:4465: gsang mtshams ma tram sgrol ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:4467: nye bar bsnyen pa'i yan lag tu bshad pas /
NK025(ra)001:4468: rnam pa gcig tu da lta bsnyen dbang ma grub bas mi 'thad pa 'dra yang /
NK025(ra)001:4469: lag len 'jug pa bde zhing snga 'gyur spyi babs kyi chog khrigs su yang de bzhin 'byung bas /
NK025(ra)001:4470: de'i phyir 'dir blang du rung ngo //
NK025(ra)001:4472: spyi don gnyis pa nye ba'i bsnyen pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:4473: bshags pa dam bca' byin 'bebs gong bzhin byas te /
NK025(ra)001:4478: badz+ra he ru ka h+aum gis rang he ru kar bskyed la /
NK025(ra)001:4479: zhes sogs kyis cho ga dngos ston pas /
NK025(ra)001:4480: de yang dkyil 'khor gyi byang shar du hom khung
NK025(ra)001:4481: gru gsum me ri dang bcas bris pa'i dbus su
NK025(ra)001:4482: 'jim pa'am ngar zan las ma tram mgo gsum g.yas
NK025(ra)001:4483: dkar g.yon dmar dbus dang lus sngo skya lag pa
NK025(ra)001:4484: drug rkang pa bzhi yod pa g.yon gyis g.yas mnan
NK025(ra)001:4485: pa'i gzugs gan rgyal du mgo bo lho nub tu
NK025(ra)001:4486: bstan la bzhag / spro na slob dpon chas su
NK025(ra)001:4487: zhugs pa'am yang na gong bzhin ging dkar nag gi
NK025(ra)001:4490: rang nyid khrag 'thung badz+ra he ru ka mthing dkar
NK025(ra)001:4491: dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi dang po gnyis
NK025(ra)001:4492: kyis rdo rje rtse dgu dang dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:4493: bar pa gnyis kyis rtse lnga dang b+hany+dza /
NK025(ra)001:4494: tha ma gnyis kyis zhing dbyug dang 'jig rten 'degs tshul can /
NK025(ra)001:4495: zhabs bzhi g.yon brkyang pa'i gyad gyi dor stabs kyis
NK025(ra)001:4496: r+au tra pho mo pad nyi'i gdan la 'gying ba
NK025(ra)001:4497: dur khrod kyi chas ldan ye shes kyi me 'bar
NK025(ra)001:4498: ba'i dbus na yum khro mo dbang phyug ma sngon
NK025(ra)001:4499: mo dril bu dang thod khrag 'dzin pa dang gnyis
NK025(ra)001:4500: su med par 'khril ba'i bdag nyid du gyur /
NK025(ra)001:4503: ma tram kha ru tra am gu sha dzah zhes lan gsum gyi mdun du bkug la /
NK025(ra)001:4504: zhes 'byung bas sngags dang phyag rgya lan gsum byas
NK025(ra)001:4505: pas ma tram bkug par bsam la gzugs dang gnyis
NK025(ra)001:4508: badz+ra gu h+ye dri sh+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:4509: zhes thod pa'i phyag rgya lan gsum bstan pas sngon gyi dam bca' las mi 'da' bar bsam la /
NK025(ra)001:4510: zhes pas thod pa'i phyag rgya ni /
NK025(ra)001:4511: lag pa gnyis thal mo khong stong gi sor mo'i
NK025(ra)001:4512: rtse rnams bkug ste mgo bo lta bur byas pa'o
NK025(ra)001:4513: // kha t+w+aam gi phyag rgya bcas te /
NK025(ra)001:4515: lag pa g.yas kyi mathe'u chung nang du bkug pa
NK025(ra)001:4516: mtheb chen gyis mnan te sor mo gsum gshibs te
NK025(ra)001:4517: sgreng ba'i phyag rgya'am yang na kha t+w+aam ka lag
NK025(ra)001:4518: pa g.yas su khyer te ging pa dang lhan cig
NK025(ra)001:4519: par 'cham stabs dbyangs dang rol mor bcas te /
NK025(ra)001:4522: ma tram bya ba'i sdig can khyod //
NK025(ra)001:4523: sngon yang dpal chen he ru kas //
NK025(ra)001:4524: bsgral nas dur khrod gnas su byas //
NK025(ra)001:4525: shes pa bla med gnas su spar //
NK025(ra)001:4526: da yang rnal 'byor dbang phyug gis //
NK025(ra)001:4527: bsgral nas sgrub pa'i gnas su bya //
NK025(ra)001:4528: phung po khams sogs gnas sbyangs nas //
NK025(ra)001:4529: rang byung mchod rten brgyad bzhugs te //
NK025(ra)001:4530: ma mo brgyad kyis bsrung bar byed //
NK025(ra)001:4531: thugs dam chen po ji bzhin du //
NK025(ra)001:4532: byin chen rnams kyis byin phob la //
NK025(ra)001:4533: dngos grub chen po'i stong grogs mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:4534: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa sa ma ya
NK025(ra)001:4535: mu dra ma tram pra b+han tsakra ha na ha
NK025(ra)001:4536: na h+aum phata / ces kha t+w+aam gi phyag rgya
NK025(ra)001:4537: bsnun pas mgo bo lho nub rkang pa byang shar
NK025(ra)001:4538: du bstan la rkang pa g.yon gyis mnan nas 'gyel
NK025(ra)001:4539: na h+aum phata / bar bsam / bdag gi zhabs g.yas kyi mthe bong dzahls lcags kyur bsam la /
NK025(ra)001:4540: rkang pa g.yas bteg pa'i 'cham stabs dang bcas te /
NK025(ra)001:4541: gnas kyi sgo 'di su yis bcad //
NK025(ra)001:4542: sems kyi bdag pos bcad dam ci //
NK025(ra)001:4543: gzung 'dzin rkang lag bsnol ba yi //
NK025(ra)001:4544: yul las 'das par sgo phye zhig /
NK025(ra)001:4545: h+aum h+aum phata phata ma tram ka ru tra h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4546: sarba phye tam tsa bya phye tam tsa bya /
NK025(ra)001:4547: zhes pas rkang pa bsnol ba phral /
NK025(ra)001:4548: ral gri'i phyag rgyas zhes 'byung yang /
NK025(ra)001:4549: ral gri dngos thogs te kha t+w+aam kha bra be sha phata kyis khog pa dral /
NK025(ra)001:4550: hri h+aum gis kho'i shes pa h+aum dkar po bdag
NK025(ra)001:4551: gi thugs kar thim pas thugs ye shes dbyer med
NK025(ra)001:4552: par bsam / skabs 'dir mgo dang rkang lag rnams
NK025(ra)001:4553: so sor phral te dkyil 'khor gyi lho nub tu
