NK025(ra)001:4554: par bsam / mgo / byang shar du rkang pa /
NK025(ra)001:4556: nub byang lag g.yon rnams bkod la /
NK025(ra)001:4557: ma tram gi khog pa'i nang du gzhal yas khang
NK025(ra)001:4558: rten dang brten par bcas pa gnas pa snga 'gyur
NK025(ra)001:4561: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he b+han+d+ha dz+ny+aa na ram zhes
NK025(ra)001:4562: pas ma tram gi khog pa zla gam smug nag
NK025(ra)001:4563: tu bsam / b+h+r+aum kham pra be sha phata kyis
NK025(ra)001:4564: ma tram gi khog pa'i sgo phye ba'i nang du
NK025(ra)001:4565: h+aum h+aum gi sgra dang bcas te phyin ha ha
NK025(ra)001:4567: sam ha ra na h+aum gis sgo bcad par bsam la /
NK025(ra)001:4568: de'i nang du srung 'khor sgom pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:4570: steng yang rdo rje'i bla bre la //
NK025(ra)001:4571: 'og kyang rdo rje'i sa gzhi bcal //
NK025(ra)001:4572: phyogs mtshams rdo rjes gtams pa las //
NK025(ra)001:4573: rdo rje mtshams las ma 'da' zhig /
NK025(ra)001:4574: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4575: badz+ra badz+ra badz+ra ram yam kham zhes pas rdo rje'i
NK025(ra)001:4576: gur du gyur nas bskal pa'i rlung gis mi thar
NK025(ra)001:4577: bar bsam / zhes pa ni ma tram bsgral bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:4579: khro bcu'i stangs stabs bya zhes gsungs pa gong du grub //
NK025(ra)001:4581: dam sri mnan la skra mtshams su zhag gi zo ris /
NK025(ra)001:4582: dpral bar thal chen tshom bu /
NK025(ra)001:4583: smin mtshams su khrag gi thig le bya /
NK025(ra)001:4584: zhes gsungs pa bsnyen dbang gi skabs su 'byung ngo //
NK025(ra)001:4586: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi mchod pa byin gyis brlab /
NK025(ra)001:4587: zhi khro'i gzhung bsrang zhes pa yang 'og tu 'chad do //
NK025(ra)001:4588: zur lugs su gsal bar ma byung yang /
NK025(ra)001:4589: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'o sngon du
NK025(ra)001:4590: rang rdo rje gzhon nur bskyed de phur gdab bya
NK025(ra)001:4592: skabs 'dir khams lugs su nang mtshams la gsum ste /
NK025(ra)001:4593: nang gi phyi mtshams khro bcu'i phur pa bgegs la btab pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:4594: nang gi nang mtshams mtshon cha 'chol bas mtshon cha'i gur phub pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:4595: nang gi gsang mtshams khro bcu'i stangs stabs kyis bgegs
NK025(ra)001:4596: rigs zil gyis mnan pa dang gsum du gsum pa'i
NK025(ra)001:4597: phur gdab 'dir skabs su bab par 'dug cing /
NK025(ra)001:4598: de yang sgyu 'phrul zhi ba'i dbang byang dang /
NK025(ra)001:4599: mdo dbang khams lugs su phur gdab tshig sna shin tu ring bas ha cang dub par snang zhing /
NK025(ra)001:4600: sgyu 'phrul zhi khro'i dbang chog sgrol chen sangs rgyas
NK025(ra)001:4601: rin chen gyi gsung nyid rgyas bsdus 'tsham par snang
NK025(ra)001:4602: bas / de'i dgongs don bsdus pa ni 'di ltar /
NK025(ra)001:4603: lcags sam shing las byas pa'i phur bu dar mthing
NK025(ra)001:4604: dmar gyi cod pan bcu slob dpon gyi mdun du
NK025(ra)001:4605: gsar la / dbal la khrag chen nam tshil chen byug /
NK025(ra)001:4606: gu gul gyi dud pas bdug la /
NK025(ra)001:4607: slob dpon zhe sdang rdo rje'i nga rgyal bya bar gsungs pa la gnyis te /
NK025(ra)001:4608: spyir sgyu 'phrul pa'i lugs kyi zhe sdang rdo rje
NK025(ra)001:4609: zhal gcig phyag gnyis rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin
NK025(ra)001:4610: pa sa chog gi bka' bsgo'i skabs su gsungs pa
NK025(ra)001:4611: dang / 'dir zhe sdang rdo rje zhal gsum phyag
NK025(ra)001:4612: drug par gsungs pa skabs 'gar phur pa la zhe
NK025(ra)001:4613: sdang rdo rje gzhon nu'i tha snyad btags pa sogs
NK025(ra)001:4614: yod pas so so'i skabs thob ltar ma 'dres par
NK025(ra)001:4615: shes pa gal che bar yod pas go bar bya'o
NK025(ra)001:4616: dang / // rnam par mi rtog pa'i ngang las h+aum zhes brjod pas rang nyid h+aum du gyur /
NK025(ra)001:4620: de las 'od zer 'phro 'dus badz+ra d+h+rika zhes brjod pas /
NK025(ra)001:4621: rang nyid zhe sdang rdo rje sngo nag g.yas dkar
NK025(ra)001:4622: g.yon dmar dbus sngo ba zhal re re la spyan
NK025(ra)001:4624: phyag drug gi g.yas gsum rdo rje /
NK025(ra)001:4630: zhabs gnyis rdo rje'i skyil krung can /
NK025(ra)001:4631: zhal mche ba'i myu gu cung zad gtsigs pa zhi ma khro'i cha lugs su gyur /
NK025(ra)001:4632: bdag gi thugs ka nas yi ge b+h+r+aum ser po
NK025(ra)001:4633: phyogs bcur khyab par 'phro 'du 'od du zhu ba
NK025(ra)001:4634: las / badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra b+h+r+aum zhes pas 'khor
NK025(ra)001:4635: lo ser po rtsibs brgyad steng 'og gi cha gnyis
NK025(ra)001:4636: las / te bcur gyur / bdag gi thugs ka
NK025(ra)001:4637: nas ma bcu 'phros rtsibs bcu'i dbus su nyi gdan
NK025(ra)001:4638: las / te bcur gyur / bcur gyur / slar
NK025(ra)001:4639: yang bdag gi thugs ka nas khro bo ta ki
NK025(ra)001:4640: r+aa dza dmar ljang zhal gcig phyag gnyis tho ba
NK025(ra)001:4641: dang lcags kyu 'dzin pa 'phros te phyogs skyong bcu
NK025(ra)001:4642: bkug ste phyogs mtshams steng 'og gi nyi gdan bcu'i
NK025(ra)001:4645: yang bdag gi thugs ka'i h+aum las h+aum bcu 'phros te phur pa la thim pas /
NK025(ra)001:4646: phur ba bcu stod khro bor rang rtags kyi phyag rgya can /
NK025(ra)001:4647: smad phur pa'i rnam pa can bcur gyur /
NK025(ra)001:4648: slob dpon gyi phyag g.yon gyis phur pa bzung zhing
NK025(ra)001:4649: g.yas pas rdo rje'i tho bas phur pa'i spyi bo
NK025(ra)001:4650: nas bsdigs pa'i tshul bya zhing /
NK025(ra)001:4651: sgrub khang gi shar stod du steng gi khro bo'i phur pa btab la /
NK025(ra)001:4652: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:4654: ces rang sngags dang tho bas bsdigs shing g+ha g+ha
NK025(ra)001:4655: g+h+aa ta ya g+h+aa ta ya sarba dush+tam m+aa ra
NK025(ra)001:4656: ya phata phata / k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba p+aa pam h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4657: h+aum badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya badz+ra d+h+aa ra +aadz+ny+aa pa ya ti /
NK025(ra)001:4658: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra k+ai la ya h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4659: ces rang sngags dang sder mo'i sngags barjooda pa 'og ma kun la 'agre'o //
NK025(ra)001:4660: shar smad du rnam rgyal gyi phur pa btab la bsdigs shing /
NK025(ra)001:4661: badz+ra kro d+ha bi dza ya h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:4662: ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4663: de bzhin du shar lhor badz+ra kro d+ha n+ai la dan+da h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:4664: da ha da ha h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4665: lhor badz+ra kro d+ha ya m+aan+ta ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:4666: pa tsa pa tsa h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4667: lho nub tu badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:4669: nub stod du badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai wa h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:4670: hu lu hu lu h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4671: nub byang du badz+ra kro d+ha a pa ra dz+ai ta h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:4673: byang du badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:4675: byang shar du badz+ra kro d+ha tree lokya bi dz+aa ya h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:4677: nub smad du 'og gi khro bo stobs po che'i phur pa btab ste /
NK025(ra)001:4678: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa b+aa la h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:4679: s+pho ta ya s+pho ta ya h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4681: de ltar phyogs skyong bcu la phur bu btab pas phyogs skyong de dag gi lus thams cad bcom /
NK025(ra)001:4683: rnam shes mi bskyod pa'i zhing du sangs rgyas /
NK025(ra)001:4684: khro bo rnams 'khor lo'i rtsibs nang du 'khod pa
NK025(ra)001:4685: de nyid dkyil 'khor gyi bya ba ma rdzogs kyi
NK025(ra)001:4686: bar du bgegs thams cad bsrung ba'i las mdzad par
NK025(ra)001:4687: gyur / khro bo la bstod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:4690: phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhi steng 'og gnyis //
NK025(ra)001:4691: khro bo'i rgyal po bdud chen rnams //
NK025(ra)001:4692: kun kyang zhal gsum phyag drug ste //
NK025(ra)001:4693: ya mtshan che ba'i dbu rgyan can //
NK025(ra)001:4694: dbu skra kham nag ral pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:4696: spyan gsum glog stong 'gyu ba bzhin //
NK025(ra)001:4697: mche ba zangs yag 'bar ba gtsigs //
NK025(ra)001:4698: rkan sgra gtogs pas khams gsum 'khrug /
NK025(ra)001:4699: bdud tshogs rnams kyis zhabs la gtugs //
NK025(ra)001:4700: mdzes pa'i lha mo mang po yis //
NK025(ra)001:4701: snyan pa'i glu dbyangs du mas bstod //
NK025(ra)001:4702: bcom ldan 'das kyi sprul pa ste //
NK025(ra)001:4703: yang sprul grangs med phyogs bcur 'phro //
NK025(ra)001:4705: lho phyogs gshin rje zhabs kyis gnon //
NK025(ra)001:4706: nub phyogs klu yi gdon rnams gzir //
NK025(ra)001:4707: byang phyogs gnod sbyin kun gyi bla //
NK025(ra)001:4708: mtshams kyi bgegs rnams zhi mdzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:4709: ya mtshan che la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK025(ra)001:4710: phyogs mtshams phur pas btab nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:4711: steng 'og yang dag byin gyis brlabs //
NK025(ra)001:4712: de nas h+aum zhes brjod pas khro bo rnams kyi
NK025(ra)001:4713: sku las ye shes kyi me rab tu 'bar te
NK025(ra)001:4714: me'i gur du gyur pa'i nang du sgrub pa po
NK025(ra)001:4715: rnams bag yangs su spyod bar bsam mo //
NK025(ra)001:4716: rtsa bar dngos su ma gsungs kyang sgyu 'phrul las
NK025(ra)001:4717: skabs 'dir mtshon cha'i mtshams bshad pa skabs su babs
NK025(ra)001:4718: pa 'di ltar / bdag gi thugs kar nyi ma'i
NK025(ra)001:4719: gdan steng sa bon las rigs lnga yab yum bcu
NK025(ra)001:4720: bskyed pa sbyor ba mdzad pa'i sbyor mtshams nas phyag
NK025(ra)001:4721: mtshan rnam pa lnga 'phros te mtshon cha'i gur spro
NK025(ra)001:4722: pa 'di ltar / ba'i sngags ni / a tsan+d+ra man+da la /
NK025(ra)001:4738: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:4741: sum+b+ha ni man+ta dz+wa la badz+ra h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4747: mtshon cha rnams rim pa bzhin 'phros te gur khang gis gtams par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:4749: nga yi dkyil 'khor bstan bya'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:4750: khro rgyal byin rlabs las byung ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:4751: mtshon cha rnam pa sna tshogs kyis //
NK025(ra)001:4752: dkyil 'khor rim pa'i tshul bzhin bsrung //
NK025(ra)001:4753: rdo rje bsdoms pa'i mthe bong mathe'u chung gung mo rnams bsgreng /
NK025(ra)001:4754: mdzub mo gnyis bkug pa'i rtse gung mo'i tshigs gsum
NK025(ra)001:4755: par btsugs pa rdo rje rtse gsum gyi phyag rgya
NK025(ra)001:4756: bcas la / steng yang rdo rje'i bla bre la //
NK025(ra)001:4757: 'og kyang rdo rje'i sa gzhi ste //
NK025(ra)001:4758: phyogs mtshams rdo rjes gtams pa las //
NK025(ra)001:4759: rdo rje'i mtshams las bgegs ma 'da' //
NK025(ra)001:4761: thal mo sbyar te sor mo bsnol ba 'khor lo'i rgyas /
NK025(ra)001:4762: steng yang 'khor lo'i bla bre la //
NK025(ra)001:4764: phyogs mtshams 'khor los gtams pa las //
NK025(ra)001:4765: gsang ba 'khor lo'i mtshams las bgegs ma 'da' /
NK025(ra)001:4766: badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra ha na tsakra h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4767: lag pa gnyis mthe bos mdzub mo bkug nas mnan pa ral gri'i rgyas /
NK025(ra)001:4768: steng yang ral gri'i bla bre la //
NK025(ra)001:4769: 'og kyang ral gri'i sa gzhi ste //
NK025(ra)001:4770: phyogs mtshams ral gris gtams pa las //
NK025(ra)001:4771: gsang ba ral gri'i mtshams las bgegs ma 'da' //
NK025(ra)001:4772: badz+ra tik+sha na tshin+d+ha h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4773: tsan+da ro sha khat+ga h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4774: sor mo'i rtse rnams bkug ste mgo bo lta bu dbyug to'i rgyas /
NK025(ra)001:4775: steng yang dbyug to'i bla bre la //
NK025(ra)001:4776: 'og kyang dbyug to'i sa gzhi ste //
NK025(ra)001:4777: phyogs mtshams dbyug tos gtams pa las //
NK025(ra)001:4778: gsang ba dbyug to'i mtshams las bgegs ma 'da' //
NK025(ra)001:4779: a ko ta mat+ga ra h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4780: badz+ra k+aa la r+au pa sha ya h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4781: sor mo rnams rtse sprad srin lag gnyis nang du bkug pa rgya gram gyi rgyas /
NK025(ra)001:4782: steng yang rgya gram bla bre la //
NK025(ra)001:4783: 'og kyang rgya gram sa gzhi ste //
NK025(ra)001:4784: phyogs mtshams rgya gram gtams pa las //
NK025(ra)001:4785: gsang ba rgya gram mtshams las ma 'da' zhig /
NK025(ra)001:4786: badz+ra karma sat+wa ha ha h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4788: mtshams bcad nang ni tshul chad du //
NK025(ra)001:4789: su yang 'da' bar ma byed cig /
NK025(ra)001:4790: cis te bka' las 'das gyur na //
NK025(ra)001:4791: tho ba lcags kyu 'khrigs pa yis //
NK025(ra)001:4792: snying nas drangs shing brdung bar bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:4794: de yang bka' bsgo bgegs skrod khro mtshams mtshon cha'i mtshams te mtshams gcod bzhi'i rim pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:4795: 'dir phyag mtshan rnams thugs nas 'phro ba 'di ga'i lugs thun mong ma yin pa yin cing /
NK025(ra)001:4796: la la dag lag pa'i sor mo rnams rigs lnga yab yum du byin gyis brlab par bshad kyang /
NK025(ra)001:4797: phyag mtshan thugs nas spro ba gzhung nas gsungs phyin 'di ga legs par sems so //
NK025(ra)001:4798: 'di yan chod kyis phyi nang gsang ba'i mtshams dgu phrugs su bya ba tshang ba yin pas /
NK025(ra)001:4801: phyi nang gsang ba'i mtshams dgu phrugs kyis dkyil 'khor sa gzhi bsrung bar bya ste /
NK025(ra)001:4802: phyi'i phyi mtshams rgyal chen dang phyogs skyong gi tho gzug /
NK025(ra)001:4803: nang mtshams dam sri brdungs la mnan pa bya /
NK025(ra)001:4805: nang gi phyi mtshams khro bo bcus bgegs la phur pa gdab /
NK025(ra)001:4806: nang mtshams mtshon cha 'chol bas mtshon cha'i gur phub /
NK025(ra)001:4807: gsang mtshams khro bo bcu'i stangs stabs kyis bgegs rigs zil gyis mnan /
NK025(ra)001:4808: gsang ba'i phyi mtshams bdud rtsi 'khyil pa dang mi g.yo bas dam sri'i bar tshad tshar bcad /
NK025(ra)001:4809: nang mtshams lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs kyi ye shes su sgom /
NK025(ra)001:4810: gsang mtshams gsang ba'i dam sri bdud rtsi gsang gtor gyis rdul phran bzhin du brlag par bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:4811: zhes gsungs pa ma h+aa dang a nu'i khyad par
NK025(ra)001:4812: gyis chog khrigs mi gcig pa'i dbang gis kha 'thor
NK025(ra)001:4813: ba ma gtogs don gyis tshang ba yin la /
NK025(ra)001:4814: 'on kyang gsang ba'i nang mtshams dang gsang mtshams gnyis las gzhung gi sngon 'gror 'byung /
NK025(ra)001:4817: zhe sdang rdo rje'i tshul bzung la //
NK025(ra)001:4818: 'bar ba'i spyan sogs bshad bzhin bya //
NK025(ra)001:4819: zhes sogs kyi don yin zhes bla ma rnams gsung ngo //
NK025(ra)001:4820: de ltar mtshams kyi rim pa yan lag dang bcas
NK025(ra)001:4821: pa grub nas gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la rdzas
NK025(ra)001:4823: de yang sngags gsar ma rnam snang mngon byang sogs
NK025(ra)001:4824: dang bla med kyi rgyud sde gzhan las kyang bshad
NK025(ra)001:4825: 'dug cing / rang lugs skabs 'dir sgo 'byed nas
NK025(ra)001:4826: a ti'i bar du rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor la
NK025(ra)001:4827: gzugs brnyan gyi rdzas dgod pa phyag bzhes dang bshad
NK025(ra)001:4829: rtsa ba'i rgyab rten gyi lung gi gtso bor gyur
NK025(ra)001:4830: pa sangs rgyas kun gyi dgongs pa 'dus pa'i mdo
NK025(ra)001:4831: chen po las / gser dngul zangs lcags la sogs pa //
NK025(ra)001:4832: gar lugs rgyal ba'i sku byas te //
NK025(ra)001:4833: phyag rgya ma nyams dang ldan na //
NK025(ra)001:4834: de yang mtshan ma'i rten du 'gyur //
NK025(ra)001:4835: shel rdo dung la sogs pa la //
NK025(ra)001:4836: 'bur las rgyal ba'i sku byas na //
NK025(ra)001:4837: de bzhin ma nyams rgyal mdzes na //
NK025(ra)001:4839: bla sha byang chub shing sogs la //
NK025(ra)001:4840: mkhas pas bzor bzhogs gzugs brnyan byas //
NK025(ra)001:4841: phyag rgya ma nyams kun rdzogs na //
NK025(ra)001:4843: sa la sogs pa phyag rgya bya //
NK025(ra)001:4844: kha dog mdzes dang ldan byas nas //
NK025(ra)001:4845: mtshan ma 'byung ba'i rten yin te //
NK025(ra)001:4846: mtshan mas mtshan ma rnams grol rig /
NK025(ra)001:4847: gang dag sa la rgyal ba'i dbyibs //
NK025(ra)001:4848: kun tu lham par byas pa la //
NK025(ra)001:4849: tshon rtsi lnga yis mdzes bkod na //
NK025(ra)001:4850: rnam grol rig pa'i rten du 'gyur //
NK025(ra)001:4851: gang gi gzugs brnyan gang yin dang //
NK025(ra)001:4852: de yi rang bzhin gcig pas na //
NK025(ra)001:4853: 'di la khyad par cung zad med //
NK025(ra)001:4856: gsang snying gi le'u dgu par /
NK025(ra)001:4857: sku gsung thugs ldan gzugs kyang dgod //
NK025(ra)001:4861: thugs phyag mtshan yang rung mod kyang 'dir ni khyad
NK025(ra)001:4862: par bris 'bur gyi sku gang yang rung ba'i rten
NK025(ra)001:4863: de nyid kyi gzugs brnyan la dmigs pa'i 'phro 'dus
NK025(ra)001:4864: dam ye bsres la dkyil 'khor du bkod par gsungs
NK025(ra)001:4865: pa'i phyir / de nyid lag len du ji ltar bya ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:4867: de nas gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la rdzas dgod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:4868: zhi ba'i gzhal yas khang du bdag nyid kun tu
NK025(ra)001:4869: bzang po yab yum du bskyed la mkha' gsang byin
NK025(ra)001:4870: gyis brlabs / sbyor ba mdzad pa'i byang chub sems kyi 'od zer las /
NK025(ra)001:4871: kun bzang yab yum bton nas tsakli la bstim zhing /
NK025(ra)001:4872: snying po brjod ces gsungs pa /
NK025(ra)001:4873: tshogs chen gyi dkyil 'khor legs par bris pa'i dbus
NK025(ra)001:4874: su many+dzi'i lta bu'i steeng zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bkod
NK025(ra)001:4875: / lha gnas so sor tsakli 'dzugs dgos pas /
NK025(ra)001:4876: lag len bde na 'di bzhin byed /
NK025(ra)001:4877: 'on te dkyil 'khor shin tu che zhing de la tsakli 'dzugs stabs mi bde na /
NK025(ra)001:4878: bkod bde ba rnams lha gnas so sor bkod cing /
NK025(ra)001:4879: de lhag rnams dkyil 'khor dbus kyi lding khri'i khar sbams te bzhugs kyang chog /
NK025(ra)001:4881: slob dpon dkyil 'khor la phyogs te bzhugs pa'i mdun du tsakli rnams stan la bkod la /
NK025(ra)001:4882: las bum gyi chu 'thor zhing +aahbig+h+n+aan+ta krita a mri
NK025(ra)001:4883: ta kun+da li ha na ha na h+aum phata kyis
NK025(ra)001:4884: bsang / swa b+h+aa was sbyang ngo //
NK025(ra)001:4885: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ngang las ser ge'i khri
NK025(ra)001:4886: pad+ma nyi zla'i gdan la bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das
NK025(ra)001:4887: dpal kun tu bzang po sku mdog mthing nag /
NK025(ra)001:4888: mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi dang po gnyis byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya /
NK025(ra)001:4889: bar pa gnyis kyis rdo rje dang dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:4890: tha ma gnyis mnyam gzhag gi phyag rgya can /
NK025(ra)001:4891: zhabs gnyis rdo rje'i skyil krung gis bzhugs pa'i pang
NK025(ra)001:4892: du yum kun tu bzang mo sngon mo zhal gcig
NK025(ra)001:4893: phyag gnyis yab kyi 'gul nas 'khyud cing /
NK025(ra)001:4894: zhabs gnyis pad+ma'i skyil krung gis sku la 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:4895: yab yum gnyis ka longs spyod rdzogs sku dar dang
NK025(ra)001:4896: rin po che'i rgyan gyis mdzes par spras pa'i skur
NK025(ra)001:4897: gyur / steng gi zhi dkyil la dmigs te /
NK025(ra)001:4898: bdag gi thugs ka na e yam ram bam lam
NK025(ra)001:4899: gyi yig 'bru 'phros dkyil 'khor gyi 'og gzhir rim
NK025(ra)001:4901: sam ha ra na h+aum 'phros 'dus 'byung ba rang
NK025(ra)001:4902: kha ma'i rtog pa sbyangs nas khams lnga rnam par
NK025(ra)001:4903: dag pa'i 'byung ba rim brtsegs su gyur /
NK025(ra)001:4904: slar yang bdag gi thugs ka nas b+h+r+aum 'phros 'byung rim gyi steng du 'khod /
NK025(ra)001:4906: sam ha ra na h+aum 'phros 'dus pa las /
NK025(ra)001:4907: lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor rdul tshon du
NK025(ra)001:4908: snang ba de nyid lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK025(ra)001:4909: brten gyi dkyil 'khor gyi rten gzhal yas khang gru
NK025(ra)001:4910: bzhi sgo bzhi glo 'bur dang bcas pa'i rgyan rta
NK025(ra)001:4911: babs mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i rang
NK025(ra)001:4912: bzhin du gyur / bdag nyid kun bzang yab yum
NK025(ra)001:4913: du gsal ba'i yum gyi mkha' pad+ma dmar po 'dab
NK025(ra)001:4914: ma brgyad pa ze'u 'bru la as mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:4915: yab kyi gsang gnas h+aum la rdo rje sngon po rtse lnga pa bu gar gyis mtshan par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:4917: sa ma ya hoh a nu r+aa ga ya mih
NK025(ra)001:4918: a nu r+aa ga ya hoh dzahh+aum bam hoh bo
NK025(ra)001:4919: d+hi tsit+ta s+pha ra na phata /
NK025(ra)001:4920: zhes yab yum snyoms par bzhugs pa'i sbyor mtshams byang
NK025(ra)001:4921: chub sems kyi 'od zer las rang 'dra'i kun bzang
NK025(ra)001:4922: yab yum thon te tsakli la thim par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:4924: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta a /
NK025(ra)001:4925: zhes brjod cing zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su gzhi'i kun bzang yab yum gyi tsakli bkod de /
NK025(ra)001:4927: mi bskyod pa yab yum bton la h+aum badz+ra d+h+rika gis kun bzang gi mdun du dgod /
NK025(ra)001:4928: de bzhin du thub pa yan chad rang rang gi gnas su so so'i sngags brjod cing dgod do //
NK025(ra)001:4929: zhes gsungs pa'i don ni kun bzang yab yum snyoms
NK025(ra)001:4930: par zhugs pa'i byang chub sems kyi 'od zer las
NK025(ra)001:4931: sbyor mtshams su zhi ba'i lha tshogs rnams gsal ba
NK025(ra)001:4932: mkha' gsang nas thon te tsakli so sor thim par
NK025(ra)001:4935: kun bzang yab yum gyi mdun du mi bskyod pa
NK025(ra)001:4936: yab yum zhal gsum phyag drug pa'i tsakli bkod do
NK025(ra)001:4939: shar rtsibs la rnam snang yab yum bkod do //
NK025(ra)001:4942: lho rtsibs la rin 'byung yab yum bkod do //
NK025(ra)001:4945: nub rtsibs la snang mtha' yab yum bkod do //
NK025(ra)001:4948: byang rtsibs la don grub yab yum bkod do //
NK025(ra)001:4950: h+aum l+aa s+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:4951: shar lho'i rtsibs mchan la sa snying yab yum bkod do //
NK025(ra)001:4953: tram m+aa l+ya sa ma ya hoh lho nub kyi
NK025(ra)001:4954: rtsibs mchan la nam mkha'i snying po yab yum bkod
NK025(ra)001:4955: / h+r+aihha h+aum pad+ma pa da ma /
NK025(ra)001:4957: nub byang gi rtsibs mchan la spyan ras gzigs yab yum bkod /
NK025(ra)001:4958: dz+rim ku ru pan+na h+r+aih a n+air+t+ya r+aa ga ya mi /
NK025(ra)001:4959: byang shar gyi rtsibs mchan la phyag rdor yab yum bkod /
NK025(ra)001:4960: mee d+ha ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:4961: dzahd+h+au pe pra be sha ya /
NK025(ra)001:4962: shar lho'i gru chad la byams pa yab yum bkod /
NK025(ra)001:4963: th+l+him nis+sa ram p+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:4965: lho nub kyi gru chad la sgrib sel yab yum bkod /
NK025(ra)001:4966: h+aum sa r+aa dza ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:4967: bam d+ai pa su khi n+ai /
NK025(ra)001:4968: nub byang gi gru chad la kun bzang yab yum bkod /
NK025(ra)001:4969: m+aum sh+r+ai a ram ga ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:4971: byang shar gyi chad grub la 'jam dbyangs yab yum bkod /
NK025(ra)001:4973: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta a /
NK025(ra)001:4974: yid chos kyi kun bzang yab yum gnyis so sor
NK025(ra)001:4975: yod na khyams kyi shar du kun bzang yab dang
NK025(ra)001:4977: mnyam sbyor yin na khyams kyi shar du bkod /
NK025(ra)001:4979: khyams sam snam bu'i shar lho'i lha'i thub pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:4980: mu ne h+aum trum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:4981: byang du lha min thub pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:4985: nub byang du byol song gi thub pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:4987: lho nub tu yi dwags kyi thub pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:4989: byang shar du dmyal ba'i thub pa rnams bkod /
NK025(ra)001:4991: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4992: shar sgor gshin rje gshed yab yum dang /
NK025(ra)001:4994: ma h+aa rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4995: lho sgor stobs chen yab yum dang /
NK025(ra)001:4997: ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:4998: nub sgor rta mgrin yab yum dang /
NK025(ra)001:5000: ma h+aa karma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:5001: byang sgor 'khyil ba yab yum rnams bkod do //
NK025(ra)001:5002: rtsa bar gsal bar ma byung yang /
NK025(ra)001:5003: glan ston gyis zhi khro'i gtso bo dang zhi ba'i
NK025(ra)001:5004: 'khor rnams kun bzang yab yum gyi mkha' gsang na
NK025(ra)001:5005: bton cing bkod / khro bo gzhan rnams dkyil 'khor
NK025(ra)001:5006: bskyed tshar nas sngar bzhin mkha' gsang brlabs te sbyor
NK025(ra)001:5007: mtshams nas spro ba dang bkod tshul gsungs pa shin
NK025(ra)001:5008: tu 'thad pas dgongs don ji bzhin lag len du
NK025(ra)001:5009: bton cing bkod / sbyar ba ni / rang nyid
NK025(ra)001:5010: kun bzang yab yum gnas 'gyur te bcom ldan 'das
NK025(ra)001:5011: che mchog he ru sku mdog smug nag 'bar ba
NK025(ra)001:5013: phyag zhe gnyis kyis zhi ba zhe gnyis bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:5014: zhabs brgyad pad nyi ru tra'i gdan la bgrad pa /
NK025(ra)001:5015: yum gnam zhal ma dbu dgu pa phyag bco brgyad
NK025(ra)001:5016: kyis gnas yul gyi khro mo phra men dang bcas
NK025(ra)001:5018: gnyis ka'ang dur khrod kyi chas brgyad dang dpal chas bcus rnam par brgyan cing /
NK025(ra)001:5019: ye shes kyi me 'bar ba'i dbus na gar dgu'i nyams kyis rol pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:5020: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor la dmigs te /
NK025(ra)001:5021: bdag gi thugs ka nas e yam ra kem ram /
NK025(ra)001:5025: khams lnga dag pa'i 'byung rim brtsegs par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:5026: slar yang thugs ka nas b+h+r+aum 'phros 'byung rim gyi steng du 'khod /
NK025(ra)001:5029: 'phro 'dus pa las lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil
NK025(ra)001:5030: 'khor rdul tshon du snang ba de nyid lhag pa
NK025(ra)001:5031: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gyi rten gzhal yas
NK025(ra)001:5032: khang bcu gcig sbrag dur khrod kyi rdzas kyi rang
NK025(ra)001:5033: bzhin can gru bzhi sgo bzhi pa rgyan rta babs
NK025(ra)001:5034: dur khrod pad+ma rdo rje me ri'i phreng bas yongs
NK025(ra)001:5035: su bskor ba mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su rdzogs
NK025(ra)001:5036: par gyur / bdag nyid che mchog yab yum du
NK025(ra)001:5037: gsal ba'i yum gyi mkha' pad+ma dmar po 'dab ma
NK025(ra)001:5038: brgyad pa ze'u 'bru la as mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:5039: yab kyi gsang gnas h+aum las rdo rje sngon po rtse lnga pa bu gar gyis mtshan par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:5041: sa ma ya hoh a nu r+aa ga ya mi /
NK025(ra)001:5042: a nu r+aa ga ya hoh dzahh+aum bam hoh bo d+hi tsit+ta s+pha ra na phata /
NK025(ra)001:5043: ces yab yum snyoms par zhugs pa'i sbyor mtshams nas
NK025(ra)001:5044: byang chub sems kyi 'od zer las khro bo tshogs
NK025(ra)001:5045: chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams thon
NK025(ra)001:5046: te tsakli la thim par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:5047: a kra ma h+aa kro d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:5048: ka ta ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum phata
NK025(ra)001:5049: dzah tshogs chen dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su che mchog
NK025(ra)001:5051: sngags de nyid dang ru lus che mchog gi mdun du dbang mchog he ru ka yab yum bkod /
NK025(ra)001:5052: de yang zhi dkyil steng du 'don pa man ngag gi lugs dang /
NK025(ra)001:5054: zhi dkyil khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su 'jug par bshad pa bzhin /
NK025(ra)001:5059: badz+ra he ru ka yab yum rnams dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su bkod par bzhed mod kyang /
NK025(ra)001:5060: 'dir ni man ngag bzhin zhi dkyil steng du bton
NK025(ra)001:5061: pa rnam pa gsal zhing phyag len bde ba gong
NK025(ra)001:5063: de nas dbang chen khro bo'i dbus su badz+ra he ru ka phyungs la sngags kyis dgod //
NK025(ra)001:5065: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sh+r+ai he ru ka sarba ta th+aa ga ta kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:5066: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:5067: badz+ra kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum dang ru lu bzla zhing /
NK025(ra)001:5068: badz+ra he ru ka dbang mchog gi mdun du bkod /
NK025(ra)001:5070: phyogs kyi rtsibs bzhi la rigs bzhi he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:5071: mtshams bzhir lung gi he ru ka rtsa sngags kyis dgod /
NK025(ra)001:5073: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:5074: bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum gis shar rtsibs su bud+d+ha khrag 'thung yab yum /
NK025(ra)001:5075: rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:5076: rat+na kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum gis lho rtsibs la rin chen khrag 'thung yab yum bkod /
NK025(ra)001:5077: pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:5078: pad+ma kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum gis nub rtsibs la pad+ma khrag 'thung yab yum bkod /
NK025(ra)001:5079: karma sh+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:5080: karma kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum gis byang rtsibs la karma khrag 'thung yab yum bkod /
NK025(ra)001:5081: rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:5082: rak+sha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:5083: shar lhor rak+sha khrag 'thung yab yum dang /
NK025(ra)001:5084: sa nu sh+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:5085: sa nu kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:5086: lho nub tu sa nu khrag 'thung yab yum dang /
NK025(ra)001:5087: gu h+ya sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:5088: gu h+ya kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:5089: nub byang du gu h+ya khrag 'thung yab yum dang /
NK025(ra)001:5090: yak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:5091: yak+sha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum las byang shar du yak+sha khrag 'thung yab yum rnams bkod /
NK025(ra)001:5093: gra bzhi'i glo 'bur la goo r+ai brgyad kyis bkod /
NK025(ra)001:5094: ces gsungs pa'i don ni gru chad kyi shar nas brtsams te phyogs bzhi dang /
NK025(ra)001:5095: shar lho nas mtshams bzhir khro mo brgyad rim bzhin bkod cing /
NK025(ra)001:5106: khyams dang po ser po la he brgyad las sing+ha brgyad /
NK025(ra)001:5107: sgo bzhir phata bzhis sgo ma bzhi zhes pa'i don ni /
NK025(ra)001:5108: dkyil 'khor dang po'i khyams la phra men brgyad gong bzhin bkod cing /
NK025(ra)001:5110: badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:5111: badz+ra sring+ga la mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:5112: badz+ra shwa na mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:5113: badz+ra gri d+ha mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:5115: badz+ra k+aa ka mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:5116: badz+ra u lu ka mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:5118: sgo bzhi'i shar lhor badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dzahlho sgor badz+ra a mu kh+aa h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:5119: nub sgor badz+ra lo ka bam /
NK025(ra)001:5120: byang sgor badz+ra b+hasmi ba la ya ba to hoh zhes sgo ma bzhi bkod /
NK025(ra)001:5122: khyams gnyis pa dkar po la a brgyad las spor ma brgyad dang /
NK025(ra)001:5123: sgo bzhir dzahh+aum bam hohdagoda ces gsungs pa'i don ni /
NK025(ra)001:5124: dkyil 'khor gnyis pa'i khyams la spor ma brgyad ni phyogs mtshams brgyad du bkod cing /
NK025(ra)001:5125: badz+ra a pra ti ha ar+ya ni tsa tu ra ta ra phata /
NK025(ra)001:5126: a rak+mo h+aum zhes bkod do //
NK025(ra)001:5127: sgo bzhir gsang yum bzhi ni /
NK025(ra)001:5128: shar sgo sh+r+ai badz+ra mut+ga ra mu kha shwa ra
NK025(ra)001:5129: ya na mah lho sgor sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga ma
NK025(ra)001:5130: shwa ra ya y+aa na mah nub sgor sh+r+ai badz+ra
NK025(ra)001:5131: kha t+w+aam ga pra dz+wa la ya y+aa na mah
NK025(ra)001:5132: byang sgor sh+r+ai badz+ra g+han+de pra dz+wa la ya y+aa
NK025(ra)001:5134: khyams gsum pa dmar po la b+h+yo nyer brgyad las dbang mo nyer brgyad ces gsungs pa'i don ni /
NK025(ra)001:5135: dkyil 'khor gsum pa'i khyams la dbang mo nyer brgyad ni /
NK025(ra)001:5136: shar du ma nu rak+sha s+ai b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:5148: nub tu ra ti tam b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:5150: e ka tsa ra ma b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:5154: byang du m+aa ra na b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:5160: shar sgor ma h+aa k+aa li b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:5161: lho sgor tsa ka li b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:5162: nub sgor bum pa ka la ma b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:5163: byang sgor lam bo d+ha ra ma b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:5166: khyams bzhi pa ser po la e so gnyis las
NK025(ra)001:5167: mkha' 'gro so gnyis e a ra li h+aum gis
NK025(ra)001:5168: bkod / ces gsungs pa'i don ni /
NK025(ra)001:5169: dkyil 'khor bzhi pa'i khyams kyi phyogs bzhir bdun bdun /
NK025(ra)001:5170: sgo bzhir re re dgos cing /
NK025(ra)001:5171: e a ral+li h+aum zhes bkod do //
NK025(ra)001:5173: khyams lnga pa dmar po la h+aum dun+tinga bzhi las
NK025(ra)001:5174: sgo ma bzhi ma ma d+ha tu dang badz+ra dun+tinga
NK025(ra)001:5175: b+h+yos dgod / ces gsungs pa'i don /
NK025(ra)001:5176: dkyil 'khor lnga pa'i khyams shar lho nub gsum du gnyis gnyis /
NK025(ra)001:5178: sgo bzhir re re bkod cing /
NK025(ra)001:5179: ma ma d+ha tu h+aum badz+ra dun+tinga b+h+yo zhes bkod do //
NK025(ra)001:5181: khyams drug pa dkar po la h+aum bco brgyad las
NK025(ra)001:5182: ging bco brgyad ging+ka ra ha ha ru lu ru
NK025(ra)001:5185: dkyil 'khor drug pa'i khyams la ging chen po bco brgyad shar nub tu bzhi bzhi /
NK025(ra)001:5187: sgo bzhir re re rnams bkod cing /
NK025(ra)001:5188: ging+ka ra ha ha ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum zhes bkod do //
NK025(ra)001:5190: khyams bdun pa nag po la h+aum drug cu las
NK025(ra)001:5191: khro bo drug cu kro d+ha kro d+hi h+aum gis
NK025(ra)001:5192: bkod / ces gsungs pa'i don ni /
NK025(ra)001:5193: dkyil 'khor bdun pa'i khyams la khro bo khro mo drug cu ni /
NK025(ra)001:5194: shar nub tu bcu gnyis re /
NK025(ra)001:5196: shar nub kyi sgor drug drug /
NK025(ra)001:5197: lho byang gi sgor bzhi bzhi bkod cing /
NK025(ra)001:5198: kro d+ha kro d+hi h+aum zhes bkod do //
NK025(ra)001:5200: khyams brgyad pa phyogs mdog la shar du dzahdruga cu las dung gi pho nya drug cu dgod /
NK025(ra)001:5201: lho phyogs su ha la sogs /
NK025(ra)001:5202: nub phyogs su gardza gardza sogs /
NK025(ra)001:5203: byang phyogs su pa tsa pa tsa sogs dgod /
NK025(ra)001:5205: spyir gdul bya gdon rigs sum brgya drug cu 'dul
NK025(ra)001:5206: phyir 'dul byed pho nya sum brgya drug cu yin
NK025(ra)001:5207: par / khyams brgyad pa 'di pho nya sum brgya
NK025(ra)001:5208: drug cu'i khyams yin kyang khyams 'dir lha nyis brgya
NK025(ra)001:5210: bdun pa'i khro bo khro mo drug cu dang /
NK025(ra)001:5211: khyams dgu pa'i ma mo drug cu sogs khyon sdoms khyams gsum bsdoms pas tshang bar shes dgos pas /
NK025(ra)001:5212: 'dir dkyil 'khor brgyad pa'i khyams kyi lha rnams bkod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:5213: shar du b+ha na b+ha na am ku sha dzahs
NK025(ra)001:5214: rdo rje'i rigs dung gi pho nya drug cu dang
NK025(ra)001:5215: / lhor ha la ha la p+aa sha h+aum gis
NK025(ra)001:5216: rin chen rigs lcags sam gser gyi pho nya drug
NK025(ra)001:5217: / cu dang / nub tu gardza gardza s+pho ta
NK025(ra)001:5218: bam gyis pad+ma'i rigs bse'i pho nya drug cu dang
NK025(ra)001:5219: / cu dang / / byang du pa tsa pa
NK025(ra)001:5220: tsa g+han+d+he hohs las kyi rigs g.yu'i pho nya drug
NK025(ra)001:5223: khyams dgu pa ljang gu la ma drug cu las
NK025(ra)001:5224: 'og gi ma mo drug cu ma ma sha r+ai
NK025(ra)001:5225: h+aum gis dgod / ces gsungs pa'i don ni /
NK025(ra)001:5226: dkyil 'khor dgu pa'i khyams kyi phyogs bzhir bco lnga re bkod cing /
NK025(ra)001:5227: ma ma sha r+ai b+h+yo zhes brjod do //
NK025(ra)001:5229: khyams bcu pa sna tshogs mdog la theg dgu'i lha tshogs tshang ba dgod /
NK025(ra)001:5231: dkyil 'khor bcu pa'i khyams la spro na sgo 'byed nas rnal 'byor rgyud man dang /
NK025(ra)001:5232: bka' brgyad sogs yo ga gsum gyi lha thams cad
NK025(ra)001:5233: bkod cho ga kyang phyag bzhes su mi mdzad pas
NK025(ra)001:5234: / sa stongs su mi lus pa'i khyad nas lha
NK025(ra)001:5235: dbang dus 'byung ba'i khro bo bcu rnams so so'i
NK025(ra)001:5236: sngags kyis bkod na legs sam snyam pas gang bde
NK025(ra)001:5238: rta babs kyi khyams rdo rje 'chang gi dkyil 'khor
NK025(ra)001:5239: la shar stod nas ma h+aa gu ru sha r+ai
NK025(ra)001:5240: ram gyis rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang rnams rim pa bzhin
NK025(ra)001:5241: dgod par bya'o // zhes gsungs pa'i don ni /
NK025(ra)001:5242: dkyil 'khor bcu gcig pa'i khyams su rgyud ma h+aa yo ga /
NK025(ra)001:5244: rdzogs chen a ti yo ga sogs kyi bla ma
NK025(ra)001:5245: brgyud pa rnams bdag nyid che mchog yab yum gyi
NK025(ra)001:5246: mkha' gsang nas bton te tsaklira bstim pa shar stod
NK025(ra)001:5248: ma h+aa gu ru sha r+ai ram zhes brjod do //
NK025(ra)001:5249: des ni gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la rdzas dgod pa'i dngos gzhi grub /
NK025(ra)001:5251: de nas khro bo gsang ba'i bum pa dang rtags gsum bla ma'i drung du dgod /
NK025(ra)001:5252: zhi ba'i bum pa phyogs bzhi dbus sam dkyil 'khor gyi mthar dgod /
NK025(ra)001:5253: las bum las mkhan gyi mdun /
NK025(ra)001:5254: zhes gsungs pa gong du bum sgrub tshar dus bla mas khro bo gsang bum bzung /
NK025(ra)001:5255: zhi ba'i bum pa rgyal thebs sogs kyis bzung la
NK025(ra)001:5256: dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' bskor te dbyangs dang bcas pas
NK025(ra)001:5258: bla mas khro bo gsang bum gyi gtso bo bzung /
NK025(ra)001:5259: gzhan lhag ma bzhi dang zhi ba'i bum pa lnga
NK025(ra)001:5260: sogs slob ma rnams kyis bzung ste dkyil 'khor la
NK025(ra)001:5261: bskor zhing dbyangs dang bcas te /
NK025(ra)001:5264: bum pa ma lags rgyal po lags //
NK025(ra)001:5265: rgyal po'i sngags kyis btab nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:5266: rgyal po chen por mnga' gsol gyi //
NK025(ra)001:5267: rgyal po'i tshul du bzhugs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:5268: zhes brjod la bum pa rang gi mdun nam phyogs bzhi dbus lngar dgod /
NK025(ra)001:5269: las bum du bdud rtsi 'khyil ba bskyed /
NK025(ra)001:5270: byin gyis brlabs te rgyal thebs kyi mdun du dgod /
NK025(ra)001:5273: tshig dang sngags kyis dgod ces gsungs pa /
NK025(ra)001:5275: sngags kyi spro na so so'am /
NK025(ra)001:5276: yang na zhi ba rnams bo d+hi tsit+ta dang /
NK025(ra)001:5277: khro bo rnams ru lus bkod de /
NK025(ra)001:5278: khro bo gsang bum dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su bkod /
NK025(ra)001:5279: de'i mdun du zhi ba'i gtso bum bkod /
NK025(ra)001:5280: khro bo dang zhi ba'i shar gyi bum pa gnyis shar dang /
NK025(ra)001:5283: byang gnyis byang phyogs su ste thams cad kyang many+dzi'i stegs la bkod do //
NK025(ra)001:5284: las bum bsgrubs zin pa de nyid kyang bla ma'i mdun nam dkyil 'khor gyi byang shar du bkod /
NK025(ra)001:5285: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su lding khri'i khar dkyil 'khor la bkod mi bde pa'i sku rten tsakli dang /
NK025(ra)001:5286: gzhan yang rin po che'i dbu rgyan dar dpyangs gdu bu /
NK025(ra)001:5287: do shal sogs zhi chas dang /
NK025(ra)001:5288: khro bo'i thod skam rin po che'i rtse bran /
NK025(ra)001:5289: ral pa'i thor tshugs sogs khro chas dang bcas pa /
NK025(ra)001:5290: gzhan yang rigs lnga dang sku gsung thugs kyi lha tsaka /
NK025(ra)001:5293: rnam snang gi sku sogs nang dbang bcu gcig gi dbang rdzas /
NK025(ra)001:5294: zhi khro'i phyag mtshan dur khrod dang dpal chas sogs
NK025(ra)001:5295: sgrub dbang bcu gsum gyi chas rnams kyang lding khri'i
NK025(ra)001:5296: steng dang phyogs mtshams gang bder bsham /
NK025(ra)001:5297: lha dbang gi tsakli 'dir lung a nu yo ga gtso che yang /
NK025(ra)001:5298: lha dbang gi dus ngo bo gcig pa'i khyad par dang /
NK025(ra)001:5299: sgrub mchod kyang rgyud lung gnyis sdebs te bya dgos
NK025(ra)001:5300: pa sogs dgos pa'i khyad par ches mang bas rgyud
NK025(ra)001:5301: lung gnyis ka'i lha dbang mdzad 'dug par /
NK025(ra)001:5302: khro bo la khyad par med kyang zhi ba'i dus khyad par che zhing /
NK025(ra)001:5303: yo ga ltar lha tshogs mi 'dra ba du ma
NK025(ra)001:5304: yod pas de'i phyir lha dbang gi tsakli dkyil 'khor
NK025(ra)001:5305: du bkod pa'i dmigs bsal med pa rnams dkyil 'khor
NK025(ra)001:5306: dbus lding khri'i khar sbams te bzhugs su gsol dgos
NK025(ra)001:5307: pa yin te / lha dbang gi dus su /
NK025(ra)001:5309: dbang zhu'i tsakli dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su sbams te gsol ba'i rten du bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:5311: gzhan yang lugs 'dir bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhir gsungs pa'i da lta bsnyen pa'i skabs yin na'ang /
NK025(ra)001:5312: 'og tu dgos pa'i yo byad phal cher da lta
NK025(ra)001:5313: bsags na legs shing mi brel ba'i dgos pa yod
NK025(ra)001:5314: pas / bsnyen dbang bskur ba'i cha lag /
NK025(ra)001:5318: rnga rnga lcag dang bcas pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:5319: gong du rtags gsum bla ma'i drung du dgod /
NK025(ra)001:5323: thal chen gyi mtshan ma rnams bya ba'i khrag zhag thal ba'i snod gsum nyer bsdogs bya /
NK025(ra)001:5324: nye bar bsnyen pa'i dus ma tram bsgral dgos pa gong du grub /
NK025(ra)001:5325: sgrub pa'i rdzas sman gtor rak+ta phyi nang gi mchod
NK025(ra)001:5326: pa rnams ni bzang zhing mang bar bsham dgos shing
NK025(ra)001:5327: / sgrub pa'i sngon 'gro rab gnas kyi yo byad rnams bsham tshul 'og tu 'byung /
NK025(ra)001:5328: sgrub pa chen po'i dngos grub kyi rdzas bsham pa logs su ston cing /
NK025(ra)001:5333: zla gam la bkra shis kyi bya kha sprod /
NK025(ra)001:5334: gsol byang bdud rtsi rlon sbyor dza gad kyis bkang ba khur bas bkab pa bsham mo //
NK025(ra)001:5336: kho bos bla chen bres gshongs par dri ba zhus par /
NK025(ra)001:5337: dpal bshos bshos bu stod zur gsum can /
NK025(ra)001:5339: rdo rje tshe la zlum po ga'u kha sbyor 'og dmar po /
NK025(ra)001:5341: rdo rje rtse lnga phyed pas mtshan pa yin gsungs /
NK025(ra)001:5343: 'di rnams la byin rlabs dang bskyed chog tha dad
NK025(ra)001:5344: du 'byung bas 'og tu sgrub chen skabs su ston
NK025(ra)001:5345: / 'on kyang gsol byang gi bskyed tshul gsungs pa'i rjes su /
NK025(ra)001:5346: de ni che mchog glang po'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK025(ra)001:5349: che mchog glang po'i dkyil 'khor ni nges nges zhig med gsung yang /
NK025(ra)001:5350: kho bo'i rigs bdag mkhas grub sman lung pa chen por dri ba zhus bar 'di ltar gsungs te /
NK025(ra)001:5351: che mchog glang po'i dkyil 'khor gyi gzhi phye dang rdul tshon dmar po bsre /
NK025(ra)001:5352: zla gam kha sprod zer ba rang thag yas gzhi
NK025(ra)001:5353: mas gzhi brtsegs pa lta bu ji bzhin la dbyibs
NK025(ra)001:5356: rdo rje rgya gram gyis bsdams pa'i tshul la dbus rwa bzhis mas gzhi la slebs pa /
NK025(ra)001:5359: bkra shis kyi bya kha sprod sogs dkyus ltar /
NK025(ra)001:5361: gzhung don gsal bar mdzad pa'i tshul la rjes su yi rangs par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:5363: rdo rje tshe zer ba che 'brang dang /
NK025(ra)001:5364: zla gam la bkra shis kyi bya kha sprod du
NK025(ra)001:5365: byas pa gnyis tha dad du gsungs pa 'dra zhig
NK025(ra)001:5366: dang / de'i byin rlabs tshe lcam lugs su zhal 'phangs shing /
NK025(ra)001:5367: bdud rtsi rlon sbyor khur bas bkab pa de nyid
NK025(ra)001:5368: la che mchog glang po'i dkyil 'khor du ming btags
NK025(ra)001:5370: 'on kyang 'dir mthong brgyud dang sngon gyi dpe bris
NK025(ra)001:5371: rnying pa sogs go bstun te 'chad par bya ba
NK025(ra)001:5372: la / dpal bshos stod gshog pa can zur gsum gyi dbyibs la smad zlum po dang /
NK025(ra)001:5373: dbang bshos ni khyab bdag sman lung pa chen po'i
NK025(ra)001:5374: phyag bzhes su ri rab bang rim bzhi pa'i steng
NK025(ra)001:5375: zla gam gyen du slang ba'i bcad kha mdun du
NK025(ra)001:5376: bstan pa'i logs la tshe ril spungs pa gnyis 'bring
NK025(ra)001:5378: rdo rje tshe 'brang glang po'i dkyil 'khor sogs bzhed
NK025(ra)001:5379: tshul mang pa de nyid zla gam kha sprod zer
NK025(ra)001:5380: yang phyag bzhes mthong brgyud la nyi zla'i ga'u lta
NK025(ra)001:5381: bu'am rang 'thag brtsegs pa lta bu 'og ma dmar
NK025(ra)001:5383: de la mar tshon gyi rdo rje rgya gram lte ba dkar /
NK025(ra)001:5388: rdo rje dkar po rtse lnga phyed pa dbus su btsugs shing /
NK025(ra)001:5389: g.yas g.yon du bkra shis kyi bya kha sprod zer
NK025(ra)001:5390: ba phyag len du mar tshon gyi ne tso kha
NK025(ra)001:5392: bdud rtsi rlon sbyor la bdud rtsi'i dkyil 'khor zhes 'og tu 'byung ba ltar na /
NK025(ra)001:5393: kho bo'i bla ma'i gsung ltar che mchog glang po'i
NK025(ra)001:5394: dkyil 'khor dang rdo rje'i tshe gcig par mdzad pa
NK025(ra)001:5396: de ltar dpal bshos dang dbang bshos tshe rnams dkyil
NK025(ra)001:5397: 'khor gyi lding khri'i steng ngam rnam pa gang mdzes
NK025(ra)001:5398: su bsham / gzhan yang pan chen re zangs tog
NK025(ra)001:5399: pa'i zin bris dang gtor dpe pan chen sku mched
NK025(ra)001:5400: kyi phyag bzhes ltar bris pa las 'di ltar 'byung
NK025(ra)001:5401: su bsham / ste / shar lhor bla ma'i gtor
NK025(ra)001:5402: ma zlum po rtse rgyas shing rtsa ba phra ba
NK025(ra)001:5403: pad 'dab bzhis bskor zhing rtser nor bu mig gsum
NK025(ra)001:5405: shar du yi dam gyi gtor ma stod gshog pa
NK025(ra)001:5406: can zur gsum pa pad 'dab bzhis bskor pa nyi
NK025(ra)001:5407: zla can / byang shar du mkha' 'gro'i gtor ma zlum po pad 'dab bzhis bskor ba /
NK025(ra)001:5408: byang du mgon po'i gtor ma zur gsum pad 'dab bzhis bskor ba yi dam lta bu /
NK025(ra)001:5409: nub byang du lha mo'i gtor ma'ang de bzhin no //
NK025(ra)001:5410: nub tu rnam sras kyi gtor ma bla ma dang
NK025(ra)001:5411: 'dra ba bkod par bshad pa legs ldan nyid zur
NK025(ra)001:5412: lugs la rnam sras dang gcig par mdzad 'dug pas
NK025(ra)001:5413: byung kyang legs shing ma byung kyang 'gal ba med
NK025(ra)001:5414: / lho nub tu dam can gyi gtor ma mkhar
NK025(ra)001:5415: thabs gru bzhi kha bad srab mo'i steng 'thug po
NK025(ra)001:5416: gcig ste nyis brtsegs kyi rtse mor ra'i gzugs gdong
NK025(ra)001:5418: dam can ni sangs rgyas gsang bas sgyu 'phrul gyi
NK025(ra)001:5419: srung mar basngagasa pa yin ces kho bo'i bla ma
NK025(ra)001:5420: sman lung pa chen po gsung zhing /
NK025(ra)001:5422: lhor dmar gtor zur gsum pa chos skyong spyi gtor gyi dod /
NK025(ra)001:5423: 'di yan chod thams cad dmar rtsis byug /
NK025(ra)001:5424: khyad par du dpal mgon legs ldan nag po la
NK025(ra)001:5425: sgrub gtor gru gsum pa dkyil nag mtha' dmar gyi
NK025(ra)001:5426: mdun du yum zla gam dmar po mtheb kyus bskor
NK025(ra)001:5427: ba sha khrag gis brgyan cing me ri rgyan sprod
NK025(ra)001:5428: kyis mdzes par byas pa la gtor gdugs mthing nag
NK025(ra)001:5429: dang / sku rten tsakli mda' la btags te gzug
NK025(ra)001:5430: pa re zhig byang ngam byang shar du bzhag cing
NK025(ra)001:5431: dang / / slar 'og tu sgos dbang gi dus dkyil 'khor du bkod dgos shing /
NK025(ra)001:5432: yang na sgos dbang la gtor ma'i bzo rgyun mi gcig pa yod pa 'og tu 'chad /
NK025(ra)001:5433: gzhan yang zhi ba'i spyi gtor zlum po dkar po la ril bu zhe gnyis kyis bskor ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:5434: khro bo la dpal bshos zur gsum pa dmar po
NK025(ra)001:5435: la mtheb kyu bcad kha phyir bstan lnga bcu rtsa
NK025(ra)001:5437: zhi khro'i spyi gtor gnyis dkyus las che zhing so
NK025(ra)001:5438: so'i rgyan spros kyis mdzes par byas pa dkyil 'khor
NK025(ra)001:5439: gyi rgyab phyogs nub tu bkod /
NK025(ra)001:5440: dkyil 'khor gyi lho g.yas su ka p+aa la mtshan
NK025(ra)001:5441: ldan du bdud rtsi sman phud rgyu gnyis rkyen sbyar
NK025(ra)001:5442: gyi 'bru bcud bzang pos bkang ba la sgrub sman
NK025(ra)001:5443: btab pa dang / g.yon byang du b+han+d+ha rak+tasa gang
NK025(ra)001:5444: ba la pad khrag gri khrag sogs khrag sna tshogs
NK025(ra)001:5445: btab pa dang / btab pa bkod / gzhan yang
NK025(ra)001:5446: sgrub dbang gi mtha' rten dbang rdzas shar lhor mar
NK025(ra)001:5447: btab pa dang / btab pa bkod / me / lho'i sman phud ni bdud rtsis 'thus /
NK025(ra)001:5449: byang shar du mdos raka ces pa /
NK025(ra)001:5450: kho bo'i yongs 'dzin sman lung pa chen po'i gsung las /
NK025(ra)001:5451: mdos raka la 'byor na ri rab dang nam mkha' phyogs mdog 'dzugs /
NK025(ra)001:5452: zhes gsungs pa bsdu na ri rab phyogs mdog la nam mkha' phyogs mdog 'dzugs pa'am /
NK025(ra)001:5454: mchod pa mdos kyi dkyil 'khor bzhengs la /
NK025(ra)001:5455: phyi cha mthun sprul pa'i ma mo gzhung bzhin mchod la thugs dam bskul /
NK025(ra)001:5456: zhes pa'i 'bru gnon du snga rol nas bshad pa ltar /
NK025(ra)001:5457: srid pa'i bem mdos sam ma mo'i khrag mdos /
NK025(ra)001:5458: e ka dza ti'am re ma ti'i mdos sam /
NK025(ra)001:5459: yang na dbang po'i sde'i dag snang ma gtsug lag khang snang srid spyi skongs lta bu bsham zhing /
NK025(ra)001:5460: khyad par gzhung dang bskur tshig sogs bstun na ma
NK025(ra)001:5461: mo'i rigs kyi mdos zhig 'thad par snang bas gang
NK025(ra)001:5462: bde bsham / lho nub tu chos skyong gi gtor ma ni /
NK025(ra)001:5463: ma mgon dam can sogs spyir bshams pas 'thus /
NK025(ra)001:5464: byang shar du las bzhi'i rdzas dang zor gtor bsham dgos pa'i las bzhi'i rdzas ni /
NK025(ra)001:5465: zhi rgyas dbang drag bzhi'i 'brang rgyas dkar zlum /
NK025(ra)001:5468: nag po gru gsum rnams dang /
NK025(ra)001:5469: zor rdzas gtor zor khrag byugs zur gsum mtshe yungs btsugs pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:5470: kong zor zor rdzas tshang ba bsham /
NK025(ra)001:5471: tshe rdzas su tshe'i 'brang rgyas dmar po rgya bum gzugs rtsa bar tshe ril gyis bskor ba /
NK025(ra)001:5472: rtser mar dkar gyi rdo rje'i tog btsugs pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:5473: tshe ril tshe chang yang bkod /
NK025(ra)001:5474: 'di dag ni sangs rgyas ye shes rin po ches /
NK025(ra)001:5475: tshe ni spyi yi kha skong yin //
NK025(ra)001:5476: sgo byang phyi nang dgra bgegs skrod //
NK025(ra)001:5477: rdzas skongs mar me bdud rtsi sman //
NK025(ra)001:5478: mtshams phur gdab kha bsnyen phur rten //
NK025(ra)001:5479: dmar chen rak+tasa thugs dam skong //
NK025(ra)001:5480: 'jig rten mchod rten drag zor gtor //
NK025(ra)001:5481: rig 'dzin gtor phud tshe zan rdzas //
NK025(ra)001:5483: dbang gong ma rnams dang gtad rgya dngos grub mdo
NK025(ra)001:5484: mgon tshe'i dkyil 'khor rnams slar 'og tu 'chad pas
NK025(ra)001:5485: 'dir mi dgos / dkyil 'khor gyi mthar spyi ltar byang shar mtshams 'dzin /
NK025(ra)001:5492: byang du zhal zas rnams dang /
NK025(ra)001:5494: bdug spos me tog mar me dri chab bzhi phyogs bzhir spel ma'am sgor bshams gang bde bya /
NK025(ra)001:5495: khams lugs su nub phyogs su bkod par bshad 'dug /
NK025(ra)001:5496: gzhan yang gzugs sgra ru ro reg bya ste 'dod yon lnga /
NK025(ra)001:5498: bkra shis rdzas dang rtags brgyad zung /
NK025(ra)001:5499: mtha' bskor du 'byor na rnam lnga brgya phrag gam /
NK025(ra)001:5500: yang na lha bshos dang me mar brgya phrag /
NK025(ra)001:5501: tshogs kyi 'khor lo'i yo byad bza' bca' btung ba'i
NK025(ra)001:5502: dngos po bzang zhing gya nom pa rnams tshogs gnyis
NK025(ra)001:5503: spel ba'i don du rgya cher bsham zhing /
NK025(ra)001:5504: nyin re bzhin mchod gtor rnying pa rnams gso zhing gsar du spros te dbul lo //
NK025(ra)001:5505: da ni dkyus la 'jug par bya ste /
NK025(ra)001:5507: gzhan yang mda' brgyad dar sna dang bcas pa /
NK025(ra)001:5508: gri brgyad me long dang bcas pa /
NK025(ra)001:5509: phur bu 'brub khung dang bcas pa /
NK025(ra)001:5510: 'phan bla bre yol bas brgyan par bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:5512: dkyil 'khor gyi phyi'i phyogs mtshams brgyad du mda' dar me long dang bcas pa brgyad dang /
NK025(ra)001:5513: gri brgyad dam ma 'byor na phyogs bzhir re re bkod la /
NK025(ra)001:5514: de rnams tshon sna lnga'i srad bus phyag len ltar bres shing sbrel lo //
NK025(ra)001:5515: phur bu dang 'brub khung ling+ga dang bcas pa yang gdab kha'i phyir gang bder bzhag /
NK025(ra)001:5516: dkyil 'khor du gnam rgyan bla bres /
NK025(ra)001:5518: bar rgyan dar gyi lnga ldi dang /
NK025(ra)001:5521: phye phur sogs kyi bkod bas mdzes par bya /
NK025(ra)001:5522: dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' ma stag lpags sam mchod lha'i
NK025(ra)001:5523: shog skor gyis dkris te rdul mi 'byung bar bya'o
NK025(ra)001:5525: skabs 'dir byin dbab ste bsnyen dbang bskur zhing /
NK025(ra)001:5526: de'i rjes su nye bsnyen gyi sngon 'gro bshags pa /
NK025(ra)001:5528: byin dbab byas te ma tram bsgral bar bshad pas
NK025(ra)001:5529: phyag len bde phyir skabs 'dir bshags pa dang dam
NK025(ra)001:5530: bca' blangs / byin 'bebs gcig gis go bcad de
NK025(ra)001:5531: bsnyen dbang bskur ba bsnyen pa dang nye bsnyen zung
NK025(ra)001:5532: du 'jug cing don mi 'gal bar lag len bde
NK025(ra)001:5533: bca' blangs / bas / de'i tshul ni slob dpon
NK025(ra)001:5534: thams cad dkyil 'khor la phyogs te phyag 'tshal zhing
NK025(ra)001:5535: bca' blangs / bas / / ye shes sku mchog
NK025(ra)001:5536: gi bshags pa bya zhing gzhan yang 'di skad do
NK025(ra)001:5538: ye nas mnyam nyid chos skur dag pa la //
NK025(ra)001:5539: ma rig dbang gis sgro dang skur btab ste //
NK025(ra)001:5540: bde dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs ngo bor smin //
NK025(ra)001:5541: de zlog don du rgyal ba'i dam nos te //
NK025(ra)001:5542: bdag cag ma rig lus dang ngag sems kyis //
NK025(ra)001:5543: bag med tshul gyis dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK025(ra)001:5544: rgyal ba 'khor bcas thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK025(ra)001:5545: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK025(ra)001:5547: sgrub mched rnams phreng ba sbrel te dkyil 'khor bskor ba'am /
NK025(ra)001:5548: yang na lag gnyis rdo rje phyir bsdams kyi gung
NK025(ra)001:5549: mo gnyis bshibs te sgreng ba dam tshig rdo rje
NK025(ra)001:5550: rtse gcig pa'i phyag rgya bcas te //
NK025(ra)001:5551: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:5552: byang chub mchog tu bdag gis sems bskyed de //
NK025(ra)001:5553: don dam dang ni kun rdzob byang chub sems //
NK025(ra)001:5554: deng nas tshul bzhin yongs su bzung bar bgyi //
NK025(ra)001:5557: de nas byin dbab pa ni thams cad gos bzang po gyon /
NK025(ra)001:5558: spos dud dang rol mo bya /
NK025(ra)001:5559: pho rnams kyis ha sta dang /
NK025(ra)001:5560: mo rnams kyis phreng ba g.yab cing /
NK025(ra)001:5562: rdo rje slob dpon dbang gi chas su zhugs pa'am rus pa'i rgyan gyis brgyan /
NK025(ra)001:5563: hasta ste mi lag gi g.yab dar thogs /
NK025(ra)001:5564: de bzhin du pho thams cad hasta g.yab /
NK025(ra)001:5565: mo rnams kyis phreng ba g.yab /
NK025(ra)001:5566: spos dang rol mo'i bye brag rgya chen por bcas
NK025(ra)001:5567: te dkyil 'khor bskor zhing dbyangs dang bcas te 'di
NK025(ra)001:5570: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i 'jig rten nas //
NK025(ra)001:5571: rnal 'byor dbang phyug rigs kyi yum dang bcas //
NK025(ra)001:5572: rgyal ba'i srung mar gyur pa'i dam tshig can //
NK025(ra)001:5573: mchod bstod bla ma rnams la skyabs su mchi //
NK025(ra)001:5575: mi gnas ye shes thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK025(ra)001:5576: bcom ldan che mchog khro rgyal 'khor dang bcas //
NK025(ra)001:5577: sngags tshig bshug pa'i brda yis spyan 'dren gyi //
NK025(ra)001:5578: phyag rgya gar gyi brda yis g.yab dor na //
NK025(ra)001:5579: dpal chen yab yum thugs dam rjes dgongs la //
NK025(ra)001:5580: thugs dam brda la dgongs te gshegs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:5582: chos nyid bde ba chen po'i sku byung ba //
NK025(ra)001:5583: bcom ldan che mchog yab yum gshegs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:5584: dur khrod dregs pa'i tshogs rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:5585: rgyud lung khro rgyal yab yum ye shes 'bar ba brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK025(ra)001:5586: koo r+ai khro mo brgyad po chos nyid mkha' ltar dag pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK025(ra)001:5587: sing ha phra men brgyad po 'bar ba'i bar khyams dur khrod nang shed nas //
NK025(ra)001:5588: spor ma gsang yum tshogs rnams tshad med bzhi rdzogs gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK025(ra)001:5589: rta gdong sgo ma 'khor bcas dam tshig lhun gyis
NK025(ra)001:5590: grub pa'i dkyil dbang phyug ming sring 'khor bcas zhe
NK025(ra)001:5591: sdang 'bar ba thugs kyi dkyil khro rgyal srin po
NK025(ra)001:5592: 'khor bcas dur khrod 'bar ba chen po'i dkyil mkha'
NK025(ra)001:5593: 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis sgrol byed 'bar ba'i las
NK025(ra)001:5594: kyi dkyil rdo rje ging chen 'khor bcas ging gi
NK025(ra)001:5595: bka' nyan las byed dkyil pho nya sder mo 'khor
NK025(ra)001:5596: bcas las rnams yongs su grub pa'i dkyil ye shes
NK025(ra)001:5597: ma mo'i tshogs rnams sdom pa sa la gnas pa'i
NK025(ra)001:5598: dkyil rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang 'khor bcas deng gi gnas
NK025(ra)001:5600: b+han+d+ha gsar rnying tshogs ni rdza ltar lhags //
NK025(ra)001:5601: keng rus gsar rnying tshogs ni ri ltar spungs //
NK025(ra)001:5602: rak+ta gsar rnying tshogs ni mtsho ltar bskyil //
NK025(ra)001:5603: m+aam sa gsar rnying tshogs ni thang ltar gdal //
NK025(ra)001:5604: zhing chen gsar rnying tshogs ni bye ltar bkram //
NK025(ra)001:5605: tsit+ta gsar rnying tshogs ni rlung ltar spungs //
NK025(ra)001:5606: byang chub sems kyi tshogs ni gangs ltar chags //
NK025(ra)001:5607: rgyan cha gsar rnying tshogs ni sprin ltar gtibs //
NK025(ra)001:5608: ta na ga na'i tshogs ni dbyings na rol //
NK025(ra)001:5609: rdo rje mched lcam lha dang lha mor rol //
NK025(ra)001:5610: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs ni mkha' ltar 'thibs //
NK025(ra)001:5611: rnal 'byor longs spyod che la spyan 'dren na //
NK025(ra)001:5612: thugs dam brda la dgongs te gshegs nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:5613: dkyil 'khor chen po 'di la byin phob la //
NK025(ra)001:5614: sgrub pa'i rtags dang mtshan ma bstan nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:5615: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:5616: badz+ra sa ma ya sid+d+hi phem phem /
NK025(ra)001:5617: badz+ra yo gi ni sa ma ya dzah badz+ra a be sha ya a a /
NK025(ra)001:5618: zhes brjod pas lha tshogs byon /
NK025(ra)001:5619: pra be sha ya phata dkyil 'khor gyi sgo phye /
NK025(ra)001:5620: a be shas dkyil 'khor dang gnyis su med par thim pas /
NK025(ra)001:5621: dkyil 'khor lha rnams gzi brjid dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK025(ra)001:5624: lha dang 'khon gcugs bsal ba'i phyir bshags pa bya /
NK025(ra)001:5625: 'gro don mthar phyin par bya ba'i phyir dam bca' /
NK025(ra)001:5626: las byas don yod pa'am dam can dbang du 'du ba'i phyir byin dbab pa bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:5628: skabs 'dir bsnyen dbang bskur ba'i dgos pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:5629: gsang sngags gzhan ltar na sgrub mchod ma grub kyang
NK025(ra)001:5630: snga 'gyur la dkyil 'khor bdun sogs bshad gzhi yangs
NK025(ra)001:5631: shing / khyad par sta gon gyi lha nam mkhar
NK025(ra)001:5632: bteg pa yang dkyil 'khor bris zin ma thag bstim
NK025(ra)001:5633: shing / zin pa dang / gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil
NK025(ra)001:5634: 'khor la rdzas dgod pa yang rgyas par grub cing
NK025(ra)001:5635: shing / zin pa dang / / byin 'bebs kyang
NK025(ra)001:5636: grub ma thag yin pas sgrub mchod grub pa dang
NK025(ra)001:5638: slob ma rnams bsnyen sgrub la 'jug rung gi dbang gi cho ga /
NK025(ra)001:5639: don nus pa'i dbang lta bu yin pas 'dir shin tu 'thad /
NK025(ra)001:5640: dkyil 'khor du zhugs te bsnyen sgrub dang dbang bskur
NK025(ra)001:5641: ba'i bya ba la 'jug dgos pa'i yo byad rdor
NK025(ra)001:5642: dril rnga phreng phur pa sogs byin gyis brlabs pa'i
NK025(ra)001:5645: de nas bsnyen par gnang ba'i dbang bzhi bskur ba na /
NK025(ra)001:5647: slob ma thams cad gral la 'khod de slob dpon gyis rdo rje dril bu thogs te /
NK025(ra)001:5649: h+aum dang a'i 'phro 'du las ye shes kyi rdo rje dril bur bsam ste /
NK025(ra)001:5650: zhes 'byung bas h+aum las byung ba'i rdo rje dang /
NK025(ra)001:5651: a las byung ba'i dril bu lag tu gtad pa'i mos pa mdzod /
NK025(ra)001:5654: thabs dang shes rab dbang chen te //
NK025(ra)001:5655: rdo rje dril bu rig pa 'dzin //
NK025(ra)001:5657: chos la 'dod bzhin dbang bskur ro //
NK025(ra)001:5659: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK025(ra)001:5660: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las zhing khams
NK025(ra)001:5661: dag pa zad mi shes pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i
NK025(ra)001:5663: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis rigs kyi
NK025(ra)001:5664: bu skal ldan rgyal ba'i sras rnams la rdo rje
NK025(ra)001:5665: dril bu'i dbang bskur bas gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor chen
NK025(ra)001:5666: por zhugs te / bsnyen grub rnam pa bzhi'i sgo
NK025(ra)001:5667: nas phrin las rnam pa bzhi la longs spyod pa
NK025(ra)001:5668: la thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med par 'brel
NK025(ra)001:5669: ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:5670: badz+ra g+han+de tish+tha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:5672: dril bu dkrol zhing snying gar gtugs gtad do //
NK025(ra)001:5673: de nas phur pa badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h+aum phata kyis sras mchog tu bskyed /
NK025(ra)001:5674: k+aa ya badz+ra sogs kyis sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs pa lag tu gtad la /
NK025(ra)001:5676: mi g.yo chos sku yon tan mchog mnga' ba //
NK025(ra)001:5677: sdug bsngal log par 'khyams pa'i sems can rnams //
NK025(ra)001:5678: thugs rjes gnyis med dbyings su sgrol mdzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:5679: khro rgyal 'bar ba'i dbang 'di khyod la sbyin //
NK025(ra)001:5681: smon lam gong bzhin byas te /
NK025(ra)001:5684: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK025(ra)001:5685: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las zha nga
NK025(ra)001:5686: khams dag pa zad mi shes pa rgyan gyi 'khor
NK025(ra)001:5688: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis rigs kyi
NK025(ra)001:5689: bu skal ldan rgyal ba'i sras rnams la phur pas
NK025(ra)001:5690: dbang bskur bas bar du gcod pa'i bgegs dang log
NK025(ra)001:5691: 'dren ya ma dam sri 'dul ba'i dbang dam pa
NK025(ra)001:5693: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aana bam h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:5695: ces pas phur pa snying gar gtugs bgegs la bsgril lo //
NK025(ra)001:5696: de nas phreng ba tsan+d+ra las zla ba la tram
NK025(ra)001:5697: bcu'i 'phro 'du las phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas kyi byin
NK025(ra)001:5698: rlabs bsdus phreng ba la thim par bsam la /
NK025(ra)001:5700: rdo rje ru tra bzhad pa che //
NK025(ra)001:5701: khur ba dbugs kyi rlung 'byin pa //
NK025(ra)001:5702: 'brug gi sgra ltar zab pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:5703: ru lu ru lu'i sgra sgrogs bzhad //
NK025(ra)001:5704: phyag rgya 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK025(ra)001:5706: gong bzhin brjod la zhes gsungs pas /
NK025(ra)001:5708: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK025(ra)001:5709: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las zhing khams
NK025(ra)001:5710: dag pa zad mi shes pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i
NK025(ra)001:5712: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis rigs kyi
NK025(ra)001:5713: bu skal ldan rgyal ba'i sras rnams la phreng ba'i
NK025(ra)001:5714: dbang bskur bas ru lu 'bru brgyad kyi 'dzab kyi
NK025(ra)001:5715: dbang dang / sangs rgyas kyi gsung dngos grub kyi
NK025(ra)001:5716: sgra dbyangs mi zad pa'i dbang dam pa thob par
NK025(ra)001:5717: dbang dang / gyur cig / ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:5718: a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum gis phreng ba snying gar gtug cing ru lu'i 'dzab ci rigs bgrang ngo //
NK025(ra)001:5719: de nas rnga nyi ma'i ste du h+aum gi 'phro
NK025(ra)001:5720: 'du las badz+ra tsa ma r+aa dza m+aa ra ya
NK025(ra)001:5721: h+aum gis ye shes kyi rngar bsam la /
NK025(ra)001:5723: chos sku mchog mnga' ye shes tshul khrims ldan //
NK025(ra)001:5724: dpal gyi phyag rgya ye shes tsa m+aa ra //
NK025(ra)001:5725: rigs kyi bu mchog khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK025(ra)001:5726: ma mo mkha' 'gro thams cad dbang sdud cing //
NK025(ra)001:5727: thugs dam gnad nas bskul nas bran bzhin du //
NK025(ra)001:5728: 'khor ba'i dbang mchog dam pa thob gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:5729: badz+ra tsa m+aa ra dzahm+aa ra ya a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:5730: zhes pas snying gar gtugs la brdung ngo //
NK025(ra)001:5731: de nas brda sgo dbye ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:5732: dpon slob thams cad phyag rdo rje nang bsdams kyi
NK025(ra)001:5733: phyag rgya bcas te bla ma'i rjes zlos bya zhing
NK025(ra)001:5734: sgom don snod bcud tha mal du bzung ste lha
NK025(ra)001:5735: dang ye shes su ma shar ba deng nas lhar
NK025(ra)001:5739: ye nas mnyam nyid mi 'ad'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:5740: gzung 'dzin bsnol bas sgo bcad de //
NK025(ra)001:5741: bdag med mi gnas ye shes kyis //
NK025(ra)001:5742: yul las 'das pa'i sgo phye zhig /
NK025(ra)001:5743: man+da la tsak+shu pra be sha phata /
NK025(ra)001:5744: phyag rgya bkrol bas snod bcud thams cad lha dang
NK025(ra)001:5745: ye shes su bsam zhing khyad par dkyil 'khor gyi
NK025(ra)001:5746: sgo bye ba'i nang du zhug te dkyil 'khor gyi
NK025(ra)001:5747: lha rnams la phyag 'tshal bar bsam zhing thal mo
NK025(ra)001:5752: shar lho nub byang sgo bzhi nas //
NK025(ra)001:5753: ye shes bzhi yi sgo phye ste //
NK025(ra)001:5754: zhi khro gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK025(ra)001:5755: rnal 'byor mchog gi phyag bgyid do //
NK025(ra)001:5756: zhes phyag btsal pas lha dang dbyer med du bsam mo //
NK025(ra)001:5757: de yan chad bsnyen pa'i cho ga'o //
NK025(ra)001:5758: skabs 'dir rtags gdab pa rigs par snang ste /
NK025(ra)001:5759: 'og gi spyi don gsum pa dkyil 'khor sgrub zhag
NK025(ra)001:5760: gi cho ga'i skabs na yod pa bzhin 'dir yang
NK025(ra)001:5761: blangs te / thog mar zhag gi zo ris lkog ma dang snying gar byug cing /
NK025(ra)001:5763: chos rnams ye nas gnyis su med par yi //
NK025(ra)001:5764: byang chub sems su gcig pa'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:5765: zhag gi za ris mtshan pa 'di //
NK025(ra)001:5766: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK025(ra)001:5767: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad dang //
NK025(ra)001:5768: sangs rgyas kun dang gcig pa'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:5769: 'di yang sngon gyi dam tshig lags //
NK025(ra)001:5771: ma h+aa mri te man+da la h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:5772: de nas dpral bar thal chen gyi tshom bu gsum btab cing /
NK025(ra)001:5774: chos rnams ye nas byang chub sems su thal chen
NK025(ra)001:5775: tshom bus he ru ka yi dur khrod chen po'i
NK025(ra)001:5776: ging chen kun dang 'di yang sngon gyi 'di yang
NK025(ra)001:5777: rtag kyi ma h+aa kem ni ri ti dz+wa la
NK025(ra)001:5778: man+da la h+aum / mkhur tshos dang sna rtser rak+ta'i thig le bkod cing /
NK025(ra)001:5780: chos rnams ye nas byang chub sems su rak+ta'i thig
NK025(ra)001:5781: les he ru ka yi dur khrod chen po'i mkha'
NK025(ra)001:5782: 'gro kun dang 'di yang sngon gyi 'di yang rtags
NK025(ra)001:5783: kyi ma h+aa rak+ta t+ai la ka man+da la h+aum
NK025(ra)001:5785: rtags 'di rnams gdab tshul ni glan ston gyis /
NK025(ra)001:5786: zhag gi zo ris skra mtshams su gdab /
NK025(ra)001:5787: thal chen gyi tshom bu dpral ba'i dbyibs su tri shu la rtse gsum gyi dbyibs su gdab /
NK025(ra)001:5788: rak+ta'i thig le b+han+d+ha zlum po'i dbyibs su smin mtshams su gdab /
NK025(ra)001:5789: ces gsungs pa ltar btab kyang chog /
NK025(ra)001:5790: 'di'i dgos pa ni sgrol ging rnams kyi 'gugs bsgral
NK025(ra)001:5791: gyi tshe rtag gdab pa rnams sgrub mched du ngo
NK025(ra)001:5792: shes pas bar chad bsrung zhing mi sgrol ba'i dgos
NK025(ra)001:5793: pa yod pas nangs re re bzhin du rtags gdab
NK025(ra)001:5795: de nas nub mo zhi khro'i phrin las gzhung bsrang zhing 'dzab khang dbye ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:5796: spyir sgyu 'phrul gyi cho ga'i phyag bzhes mang yang /
NK025(ra)001:5797: sngon 'gro'i skabs kyi byin 'bebs yan 'dir khams lugs ltar rgyas bsdus 'tshams par snang bas /
NK025(ra)001:5798: kahthoga pa rdor bzang gi chog khrigs las 'byung ba bzhin 'di ltar /
NK025(ra)001:5800: rol mo'i byin dbab pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK025(ra)001:5801: badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs rtsa ba'i bla ma rdo rje
NK025(ra)001:5802: sems dpa'i rnam pa la phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i skyabs
NK025(ra)001:5803: yul ma tshang ba med pa mkha' khyab kyi 'khor
NK025(ra)001:5804: lor bzhugs pa thams cad mngon sum du sad pa
NK025(ra)001:5805: la / bdag dang mkha' mnyam sems can rnams //
NK025(ra)001:5806: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK025(ra)001:5807: dus gsum bzhugs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:5808: mchog gsum bsten pa'i zhing gyur la //
NK025(ra)001:5809: gnyis med yid kyis skyabs su mchi //
NK025(ra)001:5810: dngos 'byor yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:5811: dag pa'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:5812: dngos grub chu bo gcod pa'i gegs //
NK025(ra)001:5813: nyes byas ma lus bshags par bgyi //
NK025(ra)001:5814: phyogs bcu 'khor gsum dag pa'i chos //
NK025(ra)001:5815: ma chags spyod la rjes yi rang //
NK025(ra)001:5816: dag pa'i mtha' bzhi dri ma med //
NK025(ra)001:5817: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed do //
NK025(ra)001:5818: bde gshegs dbang phyug sems can la //
NK025(ra)001:5819: dgos pa gsum phyir lus 'bul lo //
NK025(ra)001:5820: tshe rabs bgrangs pa'i las rnams kun //
NK025(ra)001:5821: bsdus te byang chub chen por bsngo //
NK025(ra)001:5822: zhes lan gsum la sogs par brjod la /
NK025(ra)001:5823: skyabs yul rnams rang la bsdus te ka dag gnyis su med pa'i klong du rang babs su bzhag /
NK025(ra)001:5824: gnyis pa mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:5825: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:5826: bdag nyid skad cig gi rdo rje he ru ka
NK025(ra)001:5827: sku mdog mthing nag mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum
NK025(ra)001:5828: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis kyis rdo rje rtse
NK025(ra)001:5830: bar pa gnyis kyis rtse lnga dang b+hany+dza /
NK025(ra)001:5831: tha ma gnyis kyis zhing dbyug dang 'jig rten 'degs pa'i tshul can /
NK025(ra)001:5832: zhabs bzhi g.yon brkyang pa'i gyad kyi dor stabs kyis
NK025(ra)001:5833: ru tra pho mo byi chings su bsnol ba mnan
NK025(ra)001:5834: pa / yum rdo rje'i khro mo dbang phyug ma
NK025(ra)001:5835: sngon mo g.yas dril bu 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud
NK025(ra)001:5836: pa / cing / g.yon dung khrag zhal du stob pa zhing gi g.yang gzhi /
NK025(ra)001:5840: thod pa skam rlon tshal bu'i cod pan /
NK025(ra)001:5841: se ral dpung rgyan dang bcas pa /
NK025(ra)001:5842: dpral bar thal chen gyi tshom bu /
NK025(ra)001:5843: smin dbus su rak+ta'i thig le /
NK025(ra)001:5844: os ko la zhag gi zo ris te /
NK025(ra)001:5845: dur khrod chas brgyad kyis brgyan pa /
NK025(ra)001:5846: khyad par yum la gzig gi pags pa'i sham thabs can cher gtum zhing khros pa /
NK025(ra)001:5847: bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:5849: bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+dala phata phata phata /
NK025(ra)001:5850: ha la ha la h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:5851: ces brjod pas yab yum gnyis kyi sbyor mtshams nas
NK025(ra)001:5852: khro bo 'chol ba mtshon cha'i char 'bebs pa dpag
NK025(ra)001:5854: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad gang /
NK025(ra)001:5855: bdud bgegs log par 'dren pa thams cad zil gyis mnan pas bag khums te 'dus pa la /
NK025(ra)001:5858: gsang ba'i dam bcas so so nas //
NK025(ra)001:5859: 'du ba'i lha ni ma gtogs pa //
NK025(ra)001:5860: thams cad thugs rjes bskangs zin gyis //
NK025(ra)001:5861: da lta nyid du so sor dengs //
NK025(ra)001:5863: rdo rje khro bo'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK025(ra)001:5864: de ma thag tu bkas nas ni //
NK025(ra)001:5865: gdon gyur rigs rnams brlag par 'gyur //
NK025(ra)001:5866: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da
NK025(ra)001:5867: sarba dush+tan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum
NK025(ra)001:5868: h+aum h+aum phata / ces brjod cing bskul bas khro
NK025(ra)001:5869: bo'i tshogs rnams kyis gsang spyod lta bar mi dbang
NK025(ra)001:5870: ba'i bgegs thams cad bsdigs bskrad brlag par byas /
NK025(ra)001:5872: khro bo'i tshogs rnams slar 'dus te /
NK025(ra)001:5873: khro bo'i rang bzhin gyis rdo rje'i gur khang chen
NK025(ra)001:5874: por gtams pa'i phyi rol kun nas bskal pa'i me
NK025(ra)001:5876: rgya mtsho'i rba rlabs 'khrug pa'i ra ba sum rim
NK025(ra)001:5877: nam mkha'i mtha' klas par gang bas mtshams bcad par
NK025(ra)001:5878: gyur / gsum pa bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:5879: badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs bla ma rig 'dzin zhi khro
NK025(ra)001:5880: rgyal ba rab 'byams sngon du sad pa'i spyan sngar
NK025(ra)001:5881: / sems can gyi don du mchog gi byang chub tshe 'di nyid kyis mngon du bya snyam pas /
NK025(ra)001:5882: tshe rabs 'khor ba thog ma med pa nas ma 'tshal te /
NK025(ra)001:5883: sdig pa mi dge ba'i las ci bgyis pa thams cad gnong zhing 'gyod /
NK025(ra)001:5884: phyin chad srog la bab kyang mi bgyid /
NK025(ra)001:5885: sngar byas kyi gnyen por rnal 'byor gyi rim pa
NK025(ra)001:5886: la 'jug snyam pa'i sems brtan por mngon sum du
NK025(ra)001:5888: ye shes sku mchog rang bzhin dkyil 'khor ni //
NK025(ra)001:5889: zla rgyas bzhin du spros pa mi mnga' yang //
NK025(ra)001:5890: thugs rje nyi gsal 'od bzhin snyoms mdzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:5891: 'dir gshegs bdag la dgongs shing bzhugs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:5892: brjod med shes rab mi g.yo chos kyi sku //
NK025(ra)001:5893: bde chen longs spyod rdzogs sku rigs lnga gtso //
NK025(ra)001:5894: thugs rje thabs mkhas rgya che rol pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:5895: zhi khro sprul pa'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:5896: dngos su 'byor dang yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:5897: kun tu bzang po bla med mchod sprin gyis //
NK025(ra)001:5898: mkha' dbyings rnam dag rgya che yongs bkod de //
NK025(ra)001:5899: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa rgya mtshos mchod //
NK025(ra)001:5900: kun tu bzang mo gsang ba'i b+ha ga la //
NK025(ra)001:5901: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor rab 'byams ma lus kun //
NK025(ra)001:5902: 'du 'bral med pa'i ngang du ro gcig pa //
NK025(ra)001:5903: gnyis med byang chub sems kyis mnyes gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:5904: sems kyi rang bzhin chos dbyings nam mkha' che //
NK025(ra)001:5905: chos rnams rnam dag ye nas 'od gsal zhing //
NK025(ra)001:5906: rnal 'byor nyid dbyings smra bsam las 'das pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:5907: mnyam nyid byang chub sems la rtag tu 'dud //
NK025(ra)001:5908: kun bzang rdzogs chen ye nas brdal ba la //
NK025(ra)001:5909: phyi nang gsang ba bkod pa'i dkyil 'khor ni //
NK025(ra)001:5910: snang srid rnam dag lha dang lha mo'i dbyings //
NK025(ra)001:5911: 'byung dang 'byung 'gyur yab yum lhun rdzogs rnams //
NK025(ra)001:5912: gsang chen rab dgyes gzugs can bdag nyid ma //
NK025(ra)001:5913: mkha' dbyings klong yangs pad+mo 'khyil ba la //
NK025(ra)001:5914: gnyis med thig le chen por 'od gsal zhing //
NK025(ra)001:5915: ma bcos spros med byang chub snying po'i sku //
NK025(ra)001:5916: cir yang snang ba bde chen g.yung drung lha //
NK025(ra)001:5918: bdag nyid chen po rigs lnga yab yum dang //
NK025(ra)001:5919: byang chub lcam dral khro bo khro mo'i tshogs //
NK025(ra)001:5920: rdo rje lha mo tshogs rje tshogs kyi bdag /
NK025(ra)001:5921: rigs lnga dpal chen khro rgyal yab yum bcu //
NK025(ra)001:5922: gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya sgo ma bzhi //
NK025(ra)001:5923: ye shes sprul pa'i lha tshogs mang po dang //
NK025(ra)001:5924: ma ltar byams shing sring ltar gdung la sogs //
NK025(ra)001:5925: legs nyes stangs 'dzin dam tshig rjes spyod ma //
NK025(ra)001:5926: phyi nang mkha' 'gro rnal 'byor ma yi tshogs //
NK025(ra)001:5927: dpang gyur rdo rje dam can dgongs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:5929: thugs rje'i gdung 'tshob rig 'dzin bdag cag gis //
NK025(ra)001:5930: 'gro ba'i don du byang chub sems bskyed de //
NK025(ra)001:5931: bla med go 'phang bgrod par bya ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:5932: bstan pa rgya mtsho'i so so'i 'dul khrims dang //
NK025(ra)001:5933: sku gsung thugs dang mnyam sbyor sdom pa'i mchog /
NK025(ra)001:5934: rdo rje 'da' dka' dam tshig gnyan gyi gter //
NK025(ra)001:5935: spyi dang khyad par lhag pa'i dam tshig rnams //
NK025(ra)001:5936: snga phyir mnos shing gnyer du smras so 'tshal //
NK025(ra)001:5937: yun du mi gtong 'da' bar mi bgyid cing //
NK025(ra)001:5938: don las gol zhing ldog sems ma mchis kyang //
NK025(ra)001:5939: gdod bya long yod snyam pa'i le lo yis //
NK025(ra)001:5940: klong du ma gyur rtsal shugs chung ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:5941: shes bzhin mi ldan bag med dbang gyur te //
NK025(ra)001:5942: sgom la mi brtson bsnyen sgrub g.yel la sogs //
NK025(ra)001:5943: tshor dang ma tshor ma rig dbang gis na //
NK025(ra)001:5944: ston pa'i bka' dang dam las 'das gyur te //
NK025(ra)001:5945: rnal 'byor gang zhing dam tshig nyams pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:5946: skad cig tsam yang 'phrad par mi bya zhes //
NK025(ra)001:5947: bka' las byung zhing de ltar ma lcogs te //
NK025(ra)001:5948: gsang sgo 'chol bas dbye bsal dka' ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:5949: mngon shes chung bas skyon can ma rtogs te //
NK025(ra)001:5950: nyams dang tshogs 'dres nyams pa bskang ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:5951: nyams dang snod min rnams la chos bshad dang //
NK025(ra)001:5952: nyams la mi 'dzem nyams pa'i skyon la sogs //
NK025(ra)001:5953: nyams dang 'grogs shing nyams pa de dag gis //
NK025(ra)001:5954: nyams grib skyon gyis gos bar gyur to 'tshal //
NK025(ra)001:5955: tshe 'dir rkyen dang yun gyi sgrib gyur rnams //
NK025(ra)001:5956: rab gnong 'gyod pa'i sems kyis mthol lo bshags //
NK025(ra)001:5957: byams pa'i thugs rjes bdag la dgongs nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:5958: gnyis med dbyings las mi 'gyur bdag bkod de //
NK025(ra)001:5959: dmigs med btang snyoms ngang la bzhugs nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:5960: gnyis med don gyi tshangs pa stsal du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:5961: don dam brjod med spros las 'das pa la //
NK025(ra)001:5962: rnam rtog gang yang dmigs par mi 'gyur zhing //
NK025(ra)001:5963: kun rdzob sgyu ma tsam gyi dbang gis na //
NK025(ra)001:5964: nongs pa mchis na rab nongs bzod par gsol //
NK025(ra)001:5965: bzhi pa dam bca' ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:5966: lhag pa'i bsam pa brtan pos //
NK025(ra)001:5967: rnal 'byor dbang po ye shes mthar phyin pa //
NK025(ra)001:5968: 'gro la phan mdzad thugs rje dbang sgyur zhing //
NK025(ra)001:5969: srid pa gsum gyi gnyen gyur gcig pu ba //
NK025(ra)001:5970: lha yi lha khyod bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:5971: bde bar gshegs pa'i sprul pa rgya mtsho dang //
NK025(ra)001:5972: rnal 'byor dbang phyug grub pa'i tshogs chen po //
NK025(ra)001:5973: lha dang lha min sngags 'chang dam tshig can //
NK025(ra)001:5974: kun nas 'dus pa rnams kyang dgongs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:5975: bdag ni rgyal srid mtho ris longs spyod dang //
NK025(ra)001:5976: 'dod pa'i yon tan bdag sgrub ma lags te //
NK025(ra)001:5977: 'gro la snying rje kho nas don brtson pa //
NK025(ra)001:5978: 'di la kun mkhyen khyed ni dpang du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:5979: mgon po ye shes sgrib pa mi mnga' bas //
NK025(ra)001:5980: bdag gi lhag pa'i bsam pa khyed kyis mkhyen //
NK025(ra)001:5981: 'phags mchog spyan sngar ji ltar dam bcas pas //
NK025(ra)001:5982: sun par mi bgyid mgon khyod bslu ma lags //
NK025(ra)001:5983: snying nas bdag ni khe dang grags la sogs //
NK025(ra)001:5984: g.yo dang zang zing sems ni gtan spangs nas //
NK025(ra)001:5985: gzhan don sgrub pa gcig pu'i sems bzhag ste //
NK025(ra)001:5986: rnal 'byor spyod pa chen po bdag gis spyad //
NK025(ra)001:5987: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:5988: byang chub mchog tu bdag gi sems bskyed de //
NK025(ra)001:5989: don dam dang ni kun rdzob byang chub sems //
NK025(ra)001:5990: deng nas tshul bzhin yongs su bzung bar bgyi //
NK025(ra)001:5991: srog chags thams cad gal te bdud gyur nas //
NK025(ra)001:5992: dum bu stong du bdag gi lus gtubs kyang //
NK025(ra)001:5993: byang chub sems mchog shes rab snying rje dang //
NK025(ra)001:5994: yi dam rgyal ba khyed ni yongs mi spong //
NK025(ra)001:5995: rdo rje dam tshig chen po rnams dang ni //
NK025(ra)001:5996: rdo rje slob dpon rdo rje mched lcam dang //
NK025(ra)001:5997: gzhan yang theg pa mchog la zhugs pa rnams //
NK025(ra)001:5998: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong ci nus bsrung //
NK025(ra)001:5999: 'khor ba bdag med sgyu ma'i rang bzhin la //
NK025(ra)001:6000: bdag ni 'jigs pa ci yang ma mchis te //
NK025(ra)001:6001: ma rig skye bo rnams kyi don slad du //
NK025(ra)001:6002: phyi mthar thug gi bar du gnas par spro //
NK025(ra)001:6003: gzhan don 'khor ba rnams su spyod pa na //
NK025(ra)001:6004: byang chub spyod pa rlabs chen bdag gis spyad //
NK025(ra)001:6005: 'gro drug sems can rnams la phan gdags phyir //
NK025(ra)001:6006: rang dbang du ni skye ba blang bar bgyi //
NK025(ra)001:6007: bdag ni yongs su bzung ba'i 'jig rten nam //
NK025(ra)001:6008: mya ngan 'das la spro ba ma mchis te //
NK025(ra)001:6009: gang dang gang du sdug bsngal gnas rnams su //
NK025(ra)001:6010: bskal pa rgya mtshor gnas shing phan par bgyi //
NK025(ra)001:6011: srid pa yun ring dus su brtson pa gang //
NK025(ra)001:6012: byang chub sems dpa'i yi dam lags bas na //
NK025(ra)001:6013: ji srid ngan song stongs par ma gyur ba //
NK025(ra)001:6014: de srid bdag gis skyo ba'i sems mi bskyed //
NK025(ra)001:6015: shes rab thabs kyis 'gro ba'i don bgyid pa //
NK025(ra)001:6016: snying rjes longs spyod de las ma mchis pas //
NK025(ra)001:6017: sems dmyal yi dwags gshin rje'i 'jig rten yang //
NK025(ra)001:6018: lha yi dga' tshal lta bur blta bar bgyi //
NK025(ra)001:6019: 'gro la thugs brtses dpal gyi mgur nas gsungs //
NK025(ra)001:6020: rnal 'byor dam chos bdud rtsi mchog rnams ni //
NK025(ra)001:6021: bdag gis 'jig rten thug pa ma mchis par //
NK025(ra)001:6022: ji ltar 'tshams par bzhin du rgyas par bgyi //
NK025(ra)001:6023: srid par las dang rkyen gyi dbang gyur te //
NK025(ra)001:6024: gang dang gang du dam chos 'jig pa der //
NK025(ra)001:6025: me tshogs spu gri'i so yang brgal nas ni //
NK025(ra)001:6026: phyi mthar thug gi bar du dam chos bzung //
NK025(ra)001:6027: bla med byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed de //
NK025(ra)001:6028: sgrub pa mchog la zhugs pa'i skye bo la //
NK025(ra)001:6029: tshe rabs rnams su mthu rtsal ci mchis kyis //
NK025(ra)001:6030: skyes chen rnams kyi dgongs pa rtag tu bskang //
NK025(ra)001:6031: dam pa'i chos dang sgrub pa'i gegs gyur ba //
NK025(ra)001:6032: mi dang mi min gdug pa gang yang rung //
NK025(ra)001:6033: bdag gis zhi dang khro bo'i phrin las kyis //
NK025(ra)001:6034: yongs su zhi zhing rnam par gzhom par bgyi //
NK025(ra)001:6035: rnal 'byor mchog gi theg chen bla med dang //
NK025(ra)001:6036: rdo rje rgyal po khyed la brten nas ni //
NK025(ra)001:6037: sangs rgyas zhing sbyang 'gro la sman slad du //
NK025(ra)001:6038: byang chub snying po bdag gis rtogs par bgyi //
NK025(ra)001:6039: bdag gi 'phags mchog phyag rgyas mngon sprul te //
NK025(ra)001:6040: gal te skabs med 'chi ba'i dus byung tshe //
NK025(ra)001:6041: gsang sngags mgon po ye shes dkyil 'khor can //
NK025(ra)001:6042: khyed kyi zhabs kyi drung du mchi bar bgyi //
NK025(ra)001:6043: srid gsum sdug bsngal ci 'dra khyed kyis mkhyen //
NK025(ra)001:6044: dmyal sogs med dpung zhi bar bgyid la sogs //
NK025(ra)001:6045: sems can don la myur du bdag brtson na //
NK025(ra)001:6046: dam pa rnams kyi nus mthu stsal du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:6047: lnga pa byin dbab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:6048: +aahh+aum a la la hoh b+ha ga w+aa na sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
