NK025(ra)001:6049: 'phags mchog thugs rje'i dus la bab //
NK025(ra)001:6050: khyad par bstan pa'i dus mthu rtsal 'byung ba'i dus
NK025(ra)001:6051: byin gyis brlab pa'i dus dbang mchog bskur ba'i dus
NK025(ra)001:6052: dngos grub stsol ba'i dus mthu chen bdud 'dul bcom
NK025(ra)001:6053: ldan 'das // byin chen byin phob bcom dbang chen
NK025(ra)001:6054: dbang bskur bcom dngos grub mchog stsol bcom bdag cag
NK025(ra)001:6056: h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum gis byin bsdus pas /
NK025(ra)001:6057: nam mkha' gang ba'i lha tshogs thams cad rang la thim ste /
NK025(ra)001:6058: sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lor byin gyis brlab par bsam mo //
NK025(ra)001:6059: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi mchod pa byin gyis brlab pa ni sa lugs bzhin 'di ltar /
NK025(ra)001:6060: dang po rtsa ba'i mchod pa sman gtor rak+ta gsum las /
NK025(ra)001:6061: bdud rtsi byin brlab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:6062: a mri ta kun+da li badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha h+aum phata kyis bsang /
NK025(ra)001:6063: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+dala
NK025(ra)001:6064: b+h+r+aum zhes bdud rtsi'i snod gzhal yas khang 'khor lo
NK025(ra)001:6068: zhes bcud sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga'i steng rigs lnga yab yum bcur bsam /
NK025(ra)001:6069: h+r+aihpad+m+aan+ta krita badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai wa h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:6070: +aahh+aum zhes kha gcod la bdud rtsi srung ma rta mgrin yum bzhis bskor bar bsam /
NK025(ra)001:6071: rigs lnga yab yum gyi sbyor mtshams nas bdud rtsi 'bab par bsam zhing /
NK025(ra)001:6072: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK025(ra)001:6073: zhes lan bdun nam gsum gyis byin gyis brlab /
NK025(ra)001:6074: dpal ldan rdo rje'i sku 'chang ba //
NK025(ra)001:6075: rdo rje mi phyed sku dang ldan //
NK025(ra)001:6076: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:6077: rdo rjee sku yi dngos grub stsol //
NK025(ra)001:6078: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:6079: nang mtshams lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs ye shes su bsgom pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:6080: bdud rtsi'i phud gtor zhing lhag ma smin mtshams su bzhag la /
NK025(ra)001:6081: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya sid+d+hi /
NK025(ra)001:6084: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:6086: ces brjod pas smin mtshams su zla ba'i gdan la
NK025(ra)001:6087: dkar po'i 'phro 'du las sku rdo rje dkar po
NK025(ra)001:6088: zhal gcig phyag gnyis 'khor lo dang dril bu 'dzin
NK025(ra)001:6089: par gyur / dpal ldan rdo rje'i gsung 'chang ba //
NK025(ra)001:6090: rdo rje mi phyed gsung dang ldan //
NK025(ra)001:6091: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:6092: rdo rje gsang gi dngos grub stsol //
NK025(ra)001:6093: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:6094: phud gtor zhing lhag ma mgrin par bzhag la /
NK025(ra)001:6095: w+aa ka sid+d+hi +aah s+pha ra na phata /
NK025(ra)001:6097: sarba ta th+aa ga ta w+aa ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:6099: mgrin par pad+ma'i gdan la +aahdamara po'i 'phro 'du las
NK025(ra)001:6100: gsung rdo rje dmar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pad+ma
NK025(ra)001:6102: dpal ldan rdo rje'i thugs 'chang ba //
NK025(ra)001:6103: rdo rje mi phyed thugs dang ldan //
NK025(ra)001:6104: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:6105: rdo rje thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK025(ra)001:6106: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:6107: phud gtor zhing lhag ma snying gar bzhag la tsit+ta sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:6110: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:6112: snying gar nyi ma'i gdan la h+aum sngon po'i 'phro
NK025(ra)001:6113: 'du las thugs rdo rje mthing ga zhal gcig phyag
NK025(ra)001:6114: gnyis rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:6115: sku gsung thugs sra zhing mkhregs pa'i dbang dang dngos grub dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:6116: gsang mtshams bdud rtsi gsang gtor ni /
NK025(ra)001:6117: bdud rtsi'i zegs ma las khro bo spros te bgegs bskrad par bsam zhing /
NK025(ra)001:6118: bi shud+d+he a mri te h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:6119: d+harma a mri te h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:6120: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:6121: phog pa tsam gyis brgyal bar gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:6122: reg pa tsam gyis tshig par gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:6123: rtogs pa rnams kyi bdud rtsi yin /
NK025(ra)001:6124: ma rtogs pa rnams kyi dug yin no //
NK025(ra)001:6125: gsang ba bdud rtsi'i mtshams las ma 'da' bar dengs shig /
NK025(ra)001:6127: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:6129: ram yam kham gis bsregs gtor bkrus /
NK025(ra)001:6130: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he b+han+d+ha dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+dala b+h+r+aum /
NK025(ra)001:6131: snod b+han+d+ha'i gzhal yas khang du bsam /
NK025(ra)001:6133: ba lin+ta te dz+wa ba lin+ta ba la b+aa d+ya gu h+ya sa ma ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:6134: zhes bdun nam gsum brjod pas bcud lha tshogs rnams
NK025(ra)001:6135: dgyes bzhad tshim par nus pa'i 'dod yon gyi phung
NK025(ra)001:6136: por bsam / rak+ta byin brlab ni /
NK025(ra)001:6137: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:6140: b+h+r+aum b+han+d+ha zhes brjod pas snod b+han+d+ha'i gzhal yas khang /
NK025(ra)001:6141: +aahh+aum rak+ta m+aum la rak+ta h+aum h+r+aihth+aa zhes bdun nam
NK025(ra)001:6142: gsum brjod pas rak+ta'i rgya mtsho bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin
NK025(ra)001:6143: du brlab bo // gnyis pa yan lag gi mchod pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:6144: phyi mchod rnams a mri tas bsang /
NK025(ra)001:6146: b+h+r+aum zhes snod rin po cher bsam /
NK025(ra)001:6149: ti pu pa ra muh sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid d+hoo /
NK025(ra)001:6150: sa ma yo ta muh sarba ma h+aa su kha sid+d+hi /
NK025(ra)001:6151: +aahh+aum zhes brjod pas nyer spyod dwangs shing thogs pa med pa nam mkha' dang mnyam par bsam mo //
NK025(ra)001:6152: de yang snga 'gyur lugs la mchod gtor thams cad
NK025(ra)001:6153: slob dpon gyi mdun du byin gyis brlabs nas dkyil
NK025(ra)001:6154: 'khor la 'god pa'i phyag len yod pa tshig dang
NK025(ra)001:6158: gzhong pa rnam dag chos kyi dbyings //
NK025(ra)001:6159: gtor ma ye shes phyag rgya'i tshogs //
NK025(ra)001:6160: rak+ta dmar gyi thig bkye zhing //
NK025(ra)001:6161: dkyil 'khor zla gam dbyibs dang bstun lags shing //
NK025(ra)001:6162: tshe dang gal gnyis mthun bsdebs nas //
NK025(ra)001:6164: mchod ni gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor mchod //
NK025(ra)001:6165: bla med dpal la 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:6166: ma h+aa ba lin+ta sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:6169: gtsang zhing gtsang mar sbyar ba phud kyi phud //
NK025(ra)001:6170: 'bru bcud stong sbyar dza gad dpa' bo ni //
NK025(ra)001:6171: mthu dang gzi brjid che bas 'gro ba 'dul //
NK025(ra)001:6172: dus gsum rgyal ba'i yum mchog m+aa ma k+ai //
NK025(ra)001:6173: skal med rnams kyi rkyen dang mi 'tshams te //
NK025(ra)001:6174: skal ldan thugs rje can gyis bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:6175: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:6178: bka' gsang rmad du byung ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK025(ra)001:6179: mkha' dbyings rnam dag yum gyi rang bzhin las //
NK025(ra)001:6180: rten 'brel bcu gnyis m+au la rak+ta dang //
NK025(ra)001:6181: dug gsum bsgral ba bam gyi rak+ta dang //
NK025(ra)001:6182: khams gsum bsgral ba rtsa ba'i rak+ta dang //
NK025(ra)001:6183: chags pa 'khor ba'i gnas nas drang ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:6184: bla med dpal gyi mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:6185: ma h+aa rak+ta sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:6187: thun mong gi mchod pa bkod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:6190: ti pu pa ra muh sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid d+hoo /
NK025(ra)001:6191: sa ma yo ta muh sarba ma h+aa su kha sid d+hoo /
NK025(ra)001:6192: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga push+pe pu /
NK025(ra)001:6196: g+ai ti h+r+aih sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:6198: dngos gzhi'i skabs 'dir zhi khro gnyis sgyu 'phrul ltar
NK025(ra)001:6199: gzhung bsrang dgos par spyir snga 'gyur skabs su bdag
NK025(ra)001:6200: mdun tha mi dad du bzhed cing /
NK025(ra)001:6201: phyogs 'dir yang bla ma 'ga' zhig bdag bskyed gtso che bar bzhed mod kyang /
NK025(ra)001:6202: lugs 'di'i khyad chos 'dzab khang dbye ba gsal por
NK025(ra)001:6203: 'byung bas bdag mdun tha dad du shugs kyis grub
NK025(ra)001:6204: cing / de ltar 'dzab khang dbye ba yang bdag
NK025(ra)001:6205: nyid dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo dang gnyis su med
NK025(ra)001:6206: par byas te 'dzab khang mdun du dbye ba'i tshul
NK025(ra)001:6208: 'dir ni bdag bskyed sgyu 'phrul ltar la 'dzab khang
NK025(ra)001:6209: mdun bskyed du byed pa gzhung las kyang shin tu
NK025(ra)001:6211: 'on kyang rnal 'byor pa blo rab dang rgan po rnams kyi don du lung gi phrin las dang /
NK025(ra)001:6212: rnal 'byor pa rtog pa phra zhing blo dman pa
NK025(ra)001:6213: gzhon pa rnams kyi don du rgyud kyi phrin las
NK025(ra)001:6214: yin ces dang / rgyud ltar bskyed la lung gi
NK025(ra)001:6215: gsal 'debs pa sogs kyang bshad pas dbye ba legs
NK025(ra)001:6216: yin ces dang / par phyes dgos / 'dir ni
NK025(ra)001:6217: sang nying dkyil 'khor la rab tu gnas par bya
NK025(ra)001:6218: yin ces dang / par phyes dgos / ba'i phyir
NK025(ra)001:6219: dang / lhag pa ting nge 'dzin dang gzugs brnyan
NK025(ra)001:6220: gyi dkyil 'khor la rdzas dgos pa de nyid byin
NK025(ra)001:6221: gyis brlab cing 'dzab khang dbye ba sogs la dgongs
NK025(ra)001:6222: yin ces dang / par phyes dgos / ba'i phyir
NK025(ra)001:6223: dang / pas / de'i phyir slob dpon gyis rgyud
NK025(ra)001:6224: bzhin bdag bskyed gsal btab la mdun bskyed 'dzab khang
NK025(ra)001:6225: dbye ba dang sbyor dgos pa la rgya gzhung kho
NK025(ra)001:6226: na'i tshig tsam brjod pas ting nge 'dzin gsal thebs
NK025(ra)001:6227: dka' phyir tshigs bcad rnams zhi ba rin che'i d+r+wa
NK025(ra)001:6228: yin ces dang / par phyes dgos / ba'i phyir
NK025(ra)001:6229: dang / pas / ba'i gzhung dang / lhug pa
NK025(ra)001:6230: rnams man ngag bzhin kho bos bsdebs par shes dgos
NK025(ra)001:6231: yin ces dang / par phyes dgos / ba'i phyir
NK025(ra)001:6232: dang / pas / ba'i gzhung dang / pas 'di
NK025(ra)001:6233: ltar / dngos gzhi la bdun gyi /
NK025(ra)001:6235: dang po kun rdzob sems bskyed ni /
NK025(ra)001:6236: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK025(ra)001:6237: ye nas sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK025(ra)001:6238: rtog pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba las //
NK025(ra)001:6239: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK025(ra)001:6240: gnyis pa don dam sems bskyed ni /
NK025(ra)001:6241: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK025(ra)001:6242: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK025(ra)001:6243: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK025(ra)001:6244: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK025(ra)001:6245: e ma ngo mtshar rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'gag pa med las thams cad 'gag /
NK025(ra)001:6247: e ma ngo mtshar rdzogs pa'i sangs gnas pa med las thams cad gnas //
NK025(ra)001:6248: gnas pa nyid na gnas pa med //
NK025(ra)001:6249: e ma ngo mtshar rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dmigs pa med las thams cad dmigs //
NK025(ra)001:6250: dmigs pa nyid na dmigs pa med //
NK025(ra)001:6251: e ma ngo mtshar rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'gro 'ong med las 'gro dang 'ong //
NK025(ra)001:6253: bsgrub pa'i gtsor ni ting 'dzin pas //
NK025(ra)001:6255: mun las snang byung ji bzhin du //
NK025(ra)001:6257: rtog pa'i dbang gyur ting 'dzin yin //
NK025(ra)001:6258: de ltar ting 'dzin rim bzhin sgom //
NK025(ra)001:6259: rtsa ba'i sa bcad gnyis pa ting 'dzin gsum gyi de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK025(ra)001:6260: dngos rnams nyid na dngos med pas //
NK025(ra)001:6261: rtog pa'i smra bsam yul las 'das //
NK025(ra)001:6262: de bzhin nyid dbyings ye shes te //
NK025(ra)001:6263: de phyir dngos po dngos med pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6265: de bzhin nyid ni spros med de //
NK025(ra)001:6266: rang bzhin kun tu snang ba'i dbyings //
NK025(ra)001:6267: sems can rnams la snying brtse'i phyir /
NK025(ra)001:6268: nam mkha' la ni nam mkha' bsgom //
NK025(ra)001:6270: dngos po med las dngos po'i sprin //
NK025(ra)001:6272: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid ni //
NK025(ra)001:6273: chos rnams kun gyi rtsa ba yin //
NK025(ra)001:6274: sems nyid yi ge'i rang bzhin te //
NK025(ra)001:6275: yi ge yid bzhin rin chen sprin //
NK025(ra)001:6276: yi ge'i mchog ni bsgom par bya //
NK025(ra)001:6280: rab tu brtan gyur a dkar las //
NK025(ra)001:6281: shin tu phra ba'i a rnams 'phro //
NK025(ra)001:6282: phyogs bcu gang bar gsal gyur nas //
NK025(ra)001:6283: byang chub sems su byin brlabs nas //
NK025(ra)001:6292: sha sha sa ha k+shah a +aa /
NK025(ra)001:6299: de las ming tshogs gsal 'bar kun //
NK025(ra)001:6300: spro zhing bsdu ba'ang de bzhin te //
NK025(ra)001:6301: 'di ni rdo rje dngos grub kyi //
NK025(ra)001:6302: brtan 'byung ye shes rgyu yin no //
NK025(ra)001:6303: gsum pa rten gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:6304: de las rgyal ba'i bzhugs gnas rten //
NK025(ra)001:6305: dbang chen dkyil 'khor rim bzhin bsgom //
NK025(ra)001:6314: bam u da ka man+da la /
NK025(ra)001:6317: ram badz+ra dz+wa la ram b+h+r+aum /
NK025(ra)001:6318: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsa kra s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra rat+na pad+ma man+da la b+h+r+aum /
NK025(ra)001:6319: ye shes phyogs bzhi dbus brtags te //
NK025(ra)001:6320: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub //
NK025(ra)001:6321: lhag pa'i ye shes glo 'bur can //
NK025(ra)001:6322: rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK025(ra)001:6324: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud bcas //
NK025(ra)001:6325: gru chad bzhis brgyan bar khyams dang //
NK025(ra)001:6326: kun tu gru bzhi sgo khyud ldan //
NK025(ra)001:6327: rol mo sna tshogs sprin phung bzhin //
NK025(ra)001:6328: dkyil 'khor bzhi bcu gnyis kyis brgyan //
NK025(ra)001:6329: seng ge glang chen rta dang khyung /
NK025(ra)001:6330: nam mkha' lding gi khri chen la //
NK025(ra)001:6331: nyi zla pad+ma rin po che'i //
NK025(ra)001:6332: gdan la ma s+aur+ya man+da la h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:6335: gzhal yas khang dang gdan bskyed pa'i steng lha bskyed pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:6346: shar lho'i gru chad la pa ya /
NK025(ra)001:6363: a nyid sna tshogs par snang ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:6364: ka la sogs pa'i bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK025(ra)001:6365: sgra yi ming gis thams cad bsdus //
NK025(ra)001:6366: mngon rdzogs rgyal por de nyid nges //
NK025(ra)001:6367: badz+ra tsakra rat+na pad+ma khat+ga g+han+de /
NK025(ra)001:6368: phyag mtshan bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su gyur /
NK025(ra)001:6369: de las spro dang bsdu ba yis //
NK025(ra)001:6370: so so'i phyag mtshan 'bar bar gyur //
NK025(ra)001:6371: dbus su rdo rje dang dril bu cha gnyis /
NK025(ra)001:6372: shar du 'khor lo dang dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:6373: lhor rin po che dang dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:6374: nub tu pad+ma da nga dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:6375: byang du ral gri dang dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:6376: shar lhor rin po che'i myu gu dang me long /
NK025(ra)001:6377: lho nub tu ral gri dang rin po che'i phreng ba /
NK025(ra)001:6378: nub byang du pad dkar dang pi wa /
NK025(ra)001:6379: byang shar du rdo rje dang gar lag /
NK025(ra)001:6380: shar lho'i gru chad la klu shing dang bdug spos /
NK025(ra)001:6381: lho nub tu 'khor lo dang me tog /
NK025(ra)001:6382: nub byang du rin po che'i snye ma dang me tog /
NK025(ra)001:6383: byang shar du ut+pala dang dri chab /
NK025(ra)001:6384: shar du rdo rje rtse lnga pa /
NK025(ra)001:6390: lho nub tu rin po che /
NK025(ra)001:6392: shar sgor thod dbyug dang lcags kyu /
NK025(ra)001:6393: lho sgor rdor dbyug dang zhags pa /
NK025(ra)001:6394: nub sgor pad dbyug dang lcags sgrog /
NK025(ra)001:6395: byang sgor rgya gram gyi dbyug pa dang dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:6398: de las phyogs bcur rab spros te //
NK025(ra)001:6399: rgyal ba rnams kyi thugs dam bskul //
NK025(ra)001:6400: de las slar ni bsdus pa las //
NK025(ra)001:6401: sgyu 'phrul 'bring po ltar mngon par rtogs pa sgom tshul ni /
NK025(ra)001:6403: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta a /
NK025(ra)001:6404: dbus su rang nyid bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu
NK025(ra)001:6405: bzang po mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug
NK025(ra)001:6406: gi dang po gnyis byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya
NK025(ra)001:6407: / bar pa gnyiis rdo rje dang dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:6408: tha ma gnyis mnyam bzhag gi phyag rgya mdzad pa
NK025(ra)001:6409: yum kun tu bzang mo sngon mo dang mnyam par
NK025(ra)001:6412: gtso bo'i mdun du mi bskyod pa mthing dkar dmar
NK025(ra)001:6413: ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi dang po gnyis kyis
NK025(ra)001:6414: rdo rje dang dril bu bsnams te yum la 'khyud
NK025(ra)001:6415: pa / bar ma gnyis kyi 'khor lo dang pad+ma /
NK025(ra)001:6416: tha ma gnyis kyi rin po che dang ral gri /
NK025(ra)001:6417: yum dbyings phyug ma sngon mo rdor dril 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6420: shar rtsibs la rnam par snang mdzad dkar sngo dmar
NK025(ra)001:6421: ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas gsum 'khor lo
NK025(ra)001:6423: g.yon gsum dril bu pad+ma ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:6424: yum spyan ma dkar mo 'khor lo dang dril bu 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6426: m+aam mo ha ra ti las lho rtsibs la rin
NK025(ra)001:6427: chen 'byung ldan ser sngo dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag
NK025(ra)001:6428: drug gi g.yas gsum rin chen rdo rje 'khor lo
NK025(ra)001:6429: // g.yon gsum dril bu pad+ma ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:6430: yum m+aa ma k+ai ser mo rin po che dang dril bu 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6433: nub rtsibs la snang ba mtha' yas dmar dkar sngo
NK025(ra)001:6434: ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas gsum pad+ma rdo
NK025(ra)001:6435: rje 'khor lo // g.yon gsum dril bu rin chen ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:6436: yum na bza' dkar mo pad+ma dang dril bu 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6439: byang rtsibs la don yod grub pa ljang dkar dmar
NK025(ra)001:6440: ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas gsum ral gri
NK025(ra)001:6442: g.yon gsum dril bu rin chen pad+ma 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:6443: yum dam tshig sgrol ma ral gri dang dril bu 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6444: gtso bo drug ka mtshan dpes spras pa longs spyod
NK025(ra)001:6445: rdzogs sku dar dang rin po che'i rgyan du mas
NK025(ra)001:6446: spras shing yab rnams rdo rje'i skyil krung dang /
NK025(ra)001:6447: yum rnams pad+ma'i skyil krung gis bzhugs pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6449: h+aum l+aa s+ya ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:6450: shar lho'i rtsibs mchan la sa snying dkar po zhal
NK025(ra)001:6451: gcig phyag gnyis g.yas rin po che'i myu gu dang
NK025(ra)001:6453: yum l+aa se dkar mo me long bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:6455: tram m+aa le sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:6456: lho nub kyi rtsibs mchan la nam mkha'i snying po ser po ral gri dang dril bu can /
NK025(ra)001:6457: yum phreng ba ma ser mo rin po che'i phreng ba 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6458: h+r+aihha h+aum pad+ma pa da ma /
NK025(ra)001:6460: nub byang gi rtsibs mchan la spyan ras gzigs dmar po pad+ma dang dril bu can /
NK025(ra)001:6461: yum glu ma dmar mo pi wam bsnams pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6462: dz+rim ku tu pan+na h+r+aih a n+air+t+ya r+aa ga ya mi /
NK025(ra)001:6463: byang shar gyi rtsibs mchan la phyag rdor ljang gu rdo rje dang dril bu can /
NK025(ra)001:6464: yum gar ma ljang gu gar bsgyur zhing ro brgya'i zhal zas stob pa'i tshul lo //
NK025(ra)001:6465: mee d+ha r+aa ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:6467: shar lho'i gru chad la byams pa dkar ser klu shing dang spyi blugs bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:6468: yum bdug spos ma dkar ser bdug spos bsnams pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6469: th+l+him nis+sa ram pa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:6471: lho nub gyi gru chad la sgrib sel dmar ser 'khor lo dang dril bu bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:6472: yum me tog ma ser mo me tog gi phreng ba bsnams pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6473: h+aum sa r+aa dza ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:6474: bam d+ai pa su khi n+ai /
NK025(ra)001:6475: nub byang gi gru chad la kun bzang dmar ljang
NK025(ra)001:6476: rin po che'i snye ma dang dril bu bsnams pa
NK025(ra)001:6477: / yum mar me ma dmar mo mar me bsnams pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6478: m+aum sh+r+ai a ram ga ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:6480: byang shar gyi gru chad la 'jam dbyangs dkar ljang ut+pala dang dril bu bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:6481: yum dri chab ma ljang gu dri'i dung chos bsnams pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6482: sems dpa' sems ma brgyad po yang longs spyod rdzogs sku dar dang rin po che'i rgyan can no //
NK025(ra)001:6484: khyams kyi shar du byed pa po kun bzang sngon po mnyam bzhag mnyam pa'i skyil krung can /
NK025(ra)001:6485: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta a /
NK025(ra)001:6486: khyams kyi nub tu bya ba mo kun tu bzang
NK025(ra)001:6487: mo dkar mo chos 'byung gi phyag rgya can mnyam
NK025(ra)001:6488: pa'i skyil krung gis bzhugs te rgyan spangs pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6490: snam bu'i shar lhor lha'i thub pa dkar po pi wang 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:6491: mu ne h+aum trum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:6492: snam bu'i byang du lha min thub pa sngon po g.yas ral gri dang g.yon go khrab can /
NK025(ra)001:6494: snam bu'i lhor mi'i thub pa ser po g.yas bseg shang dang g.yon lhung bzed 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6496: snam bu'i nub byang du byol song thub pa ljang gu glegs bam 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:6498: snam bu'i lho nub tu yi dwags kyi thub pa ser nag rin po che'i sgrom bu 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:6500: snam bu'i byang shar du dmyal ba'i thub pa dud kha me chu 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6501: thub pa drug ni sangs rgyas sprul sku mtshan dpe
NK025(ra)001:6502: can chos gos gsum ldan 'gro ba'i don la bzhengs
NK025(ra)001:6503: pa'o // h+aum ya m+aan+ta krita phata /
NK025(ra)001:6504: ma h+aa badz+ra d+h+aa ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:6505: shar sgor khro bo gshin rje gshed mthing nag thod dbyug dang sdigs mdzub can /
NK025(ra)001:6506: yum khro mo lcags kyu ma mthing nag lcags kyu dang thod khrag 'dzin pa 'khril ba'o //
NK025(ra)001:6508: ma h+aa rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:6509: lho sgor stobs chen ser nag rdo rje'i dbyug pa dang thod khrag can /
NK025(ra)001:6510: yum zhags pa ma ser nag zhags pa dang thod khrag 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6512: ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:6513: nub sgor rta mgrin dmar po pad+ma'i thod dbyug sbrul gyi dkris pa dang thod khrag can /
NK025(ra)001:6514: yum lcags sgrog ma dmar mo lcags sgrog dang thod khrag 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6516: ma h+aa karma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:6517: byang sgor bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ljang nag rgya gram gyi dbyug pa dang thod khrag can /
NK025(ra)001:6518: yum dril bu ma ljang gu dril bu dang thod khrag can no //
NK025(ra)001:6519: sgo ba yab yum brgyad khro bo dang khro mo'i
NK025(ra)001:6520: chas ldan ye shes kyi me 'bar ba'i dbus na
NK025(ra)001:6521: bzhugs pa'o // gdan la rdzogs dang sems dpa'i tshul //
NK025(ra)001:6522: 'khor lo rgyal po rgyal mo dang //
NK025(ra)001:6523: g.yas nas mthong thos snom pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:6524: myong dang btsun mo'i tshogs su bcas //
NK025(ra)001:6525: gru chad la ni mthong byed dang //
NK025(ra)001:6526: thos byed snom byed myong byed rnams //
NK025(ra)001:6527: btsun mo'i tshogs dang ldan par gnas //
NK025(ra)001:6528: bar khyams la ni thub drug dang //
NK025(ra)001:6529: mdun dang rgyab tu byed pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:6530: bya ba dag ni gnas par bstan //
NK025(ra)001:6531: sgo khyud bzhi la 'joms pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:6532: btsun mo'i tshogs dang ldan par gnas //
NK025(ra)001:6533: rdo rje 'khor lo rin po che //
NK025(ra)001:6535: ut+pala klu shing la sogs mtshan //
NK025(ra)001:6536: rin chen myu gu ral gri 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:6538: chos kyi 'khor lo rin chen snye //
NK025(ra)001:6539: gzugs mdzes rin chen phreng ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:6540: pi wang gar mkhan mchog nyid de //
NK025(ra)001:6541: me tog phreng dang spos mchog ma //
NK025(ra)001:6542: mar me byug pa la sogs mtshan //
NK025(ra)001:6543: las la 'khril zhing chos la brten //
NK025(ra)001:6545: gong gi phyag rgya chen po bzhin //
NK025(ra)001:6546: gnyis med dbyings kyi ngang du 'khril //
NK025(ra)001:6547: sgo bzhi khro ba'i phyag rgya ni //
NK025(ra)001:6548: n+ri mgo gdengs dang rdo rje gnon //
NK025(ra)001:6549: thod sbrul chen pos gnon pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:6550: rdo rje rgya gram las kyis gnon //
NK025(ra)001:6551: lcags kyu zhags pa s+pho ta hoh sgo bzhir gnas pa de dag kyang //
NK025(ra)001:6553: thub drug phyag rgya sna tshogs te //
NK025(ra)001:6554: mdor bsdus phyag rgya drug yin no //
NK025(ra)001:6555: bseg par dang ni pi wang dang //
NK025(ra)001:6556: go cha po ti rin chen sgrom //
NK025(ra)001:6557: me dang chu ni rab tu bstan //
NK025(ra)001:6558: yum ni dmigs med chos kyi dbyings //
NK025(ra)001:6559: kun bzang mnyam gzhag ye shes 'phro //
NK025(ra)001:6561: gzhan yang phyag rgya sna tshogs te //
NK025(ra)001:6562: yang na de bzhin gshegs nyid dam //
NK025(ra)001:6563: yang na rdo rje thal mo nyid //
NK025(ra)001:6564: mthing ga dkar po ser le brgan //
NK025(ra)001:6565: ljang gu la sogs sna tshogs pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:6566: gnyen lcug 'khril ldem gzhon tshul can //
NK025(ra)001:6567: gsal 'tsher lhun stug gzi byin ldan //
NK025(ra)001:6570: mtha' dbus med par khyab pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:6571: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub //
NK025(ra)001:6572: phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor gsal ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:6573: dbang bskur byin rlabs tshul bzhin bya //
NK025(ra)001:6574: de ltar bdag bskyed kyi dkyil 'khor rten dang brten par bcas pa bskyed nas /
NK025(ra)001:6575: 'di man chod bdag mdun bum gsum lhan cig tu bya bar bshad de /
NK025(ra)001:6576: khams lugs las bdag bskyed bshad rjes su dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:6579: brtan par bzhugs su gsol ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:6583: bzlas pa byed pa rnams 'og tu bum bskyed dang mdun bskyed dang thun mong du shes par bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:6585: 'on kyang bum bskyed dngos gong du bum pa sta
NK025(ra)001:6586: gon gyi tshe zhi khro'i bum pa gnyis ka rgyas
NK025(ra)001:6588: 'di man chod du logs su sgrub mi dgos shing /
NK025(ra)001:6589: zhi khro'i bdag mdun gyi cho ga so so'i tshe /
NK025(ra)001:6590: zhi khro gang yin gyi bum pa'i lha rnams kyang
NK025(ra)001:6591: sngar yod gsal 'debs kyi tshul du dran par byas
NK025(ra)001:6592: te mchod bstod dang 'dzab bzlas rnams lhan cig tu
NK025(ra)001:6593: bgyis pas 'thus / de nas 'dzab khang dbye zhing mdun bskyed gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:6595: de nas 'dzab zhi khro rig 'dzin gsum las /
NK025(ra)001:6596: dang po zhi ba'i 'dzab khang dbye ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:6597: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor gsal gdab pa spyir
NK025(ra)001:6598: 'byung ba rim brtsegs kyi steng du b+h+r+aum gyi 'phro
NK025(ra)001:6599: 'du las / b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa
NK025(ra)001:6600: na tsakra rat+na pad+ma karma g+han+de s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra pad+ma man+da
NK025(ra)001:6601: la zhes pa ni lha'i gzhal yas khang lte ba
NK025(ra)001:6602: zlum po mu khyud glo 'bur gru chad dang lha
NK025(ra)001:6603: snam sgo khyud rta babs 'dod snam pha gu d+r+wa
NK025(ra)001:6604: phyed pad+ma rdo ra me ri dang bcas pa'i dbus
NK025(ra)001:6605: su h+aum h+aum h+aum badz+ra tsit+ta /
NK025(ra)001:6606: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta as kun bzang bskyed /
NK025(ra)001:6607: de nas mi bskyod pa sogs zhi ba'i lha tshogs thams cad bskyed nas /
NK025(ra)001:6609: de ltar zhi ba bskyed tshul yang khams lugs su
NK025(ra)001:6610: ma h+aa a nu gnyis tha dad du byas te
NK025(ra)001:6611: / ma h+aa'i skabs su zhi ba yang bsdus pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:6614: yang zhi ba tshom bu gcig pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:6616: tshom bu lnga pa dang gsum ste zhi ba la dkyil 'khor drug /
NK025(ra)001:6617: de bzhin du khro bo la yang rgyas 'bring bsdus gsum dang /
NK025(ra)001:6620: lnga pa ste drug tu phye /
NK025(ra)001:6621: de dag so sor mngon rtogs sogs rgyas par bshad 'dug cing /
NK025(ra)001:6622: zur lugs su yang spros pa'i yan lag tu de
NK025(ra)001:6623: bzhin mdzad pa yang byung 'dug pas rig 'dzin rje'i
NK025(ra)001:6624: phyag dpe'i rgyun gyi dpe bris su yang snang zhing
NK025(ra)001:6625: / de dag gi rtsa ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:6626: rtsa rgyud gsang snying gi le'u bcu gcig pa las ji ltar gsungs pa'i tshul yin /
NK025(ra)001:6627: 'on kyang 'dir gtso bo a nu yin phyir sgyu 'phrul 'bring po ltar 'thad par sems pas /
NK025(ra)001:6628: de'i tshul ni zhi dkyil la dmigs te rtsa ba'i
NK025(ra)001:6629: sa bcad gsum pa rten gzhal yas khang bskyed pa
NK025(ra)001:6630: ni / bdag gi thugs ka nas e yam bam sum lam ram rnams chad /
NK025(ra)001:6635: e las nam mkha'i chos 'byung 'byams klas pa /
NK025(ra)001:6636: de'i steng du yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor ljang gu gzhu'i dbyibs can /
NK025(ra)001:6637: de'i steng du bam las chu'i dkyil 'khor dkar po zlum po /
NK025(ra)001:6638: de'i steng du sum las sa'i dkyil 'khor gru bzhi ser po /
NK025(ra)001:6639: de'i steng du lam las ri rab rin po che sna bzhi'i rang bzhin zur bzhi pa /
NK025(ra)001:6640: ram las me'i khor yug nam mkha'i mtha' klas pa 'bar ba /
NK025(ra)001:6641: ri rab kyi steng du b+h+r+aum 'phros te 'khod /
NK025(ra)001:6644: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra rat+na pad+ma man+da la /
NK025(ra)001:6645: ye shes rin po che 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang rgya phyogs bcur yongs su ma chad pa /
NK025(ra)001:6646: yon tan dpag med pa rgyas pa'i phyir gru bzhir gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:6647: lte ba zlum po rtsibs bzhi mu khyud dang bcas
NK025(ra)001:6648: pa'i phyir lhag pa'i ye shes rin po che'i glo
NK025(ra)001:6650: rtse mo phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas kyi dkyil
NK025(ra)001:6651: 'khor ma lus pa thams cad so sor ma yin
NK025(ra)001:6652: zhing / ngoo bo nyid gcig pa'i ye shes kun tu 'khyil ba /
NK025(ra)001:6653: ye shes bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i ye shes rin po che'i dbyibs dang /
NK025(ra)001:6654: kha dog la sogs pa rnam pa tha dad pa'i bye brag dang khyad par du gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:6657: ye shes rin po che sna tshogs kyi phreng ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:6664: reg bya sna tshogs kyis phyogs bcur 'khrigs par rang byung la /
NK025(ra)001:6665: mi sgrib par gsal pa'i rgyan bsam gyis mi khyab pas bklubs pa /
NK025(ra)001:6666: rnam par thar pa bzhi'i sgo nas 'jug pa'i sgo khyud can /
NK025(ra)001:6667: rnam par thar pa brgyad kyi rta babs dang ldan pa /
NK025(ra)001:6668: phyi dang nang med pa kun tu yang nang du gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:6669: pad+ma la gnas pa'i sna tshogs rdo rje'i lte bar
NK025(ra)001:6670: rdzogs shing phyi rol rdo rje'i ra bas steng 'og
NK025(ra)001:6671: phyogs mtshams kun tu dkrigs pa las /
NK025(ra)001:6672: ye shes kyi me 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang gi lte ba dang rtsibs bzhir /
NK025(ra)001:6673: dbus su mi 'jigs pa seng+ge'i khri cha gnyis /
NK025(ra)001:6674: shar du stobs glang po che'i khri /
NK025(ra)001:6676: nub tu dbang rma bya'i khri /
NK025(ra)001:6677: byang du thog pa med pa nam mkha' lding gi khri rnams kyi steng du pam pad+ma man+da la /
NK025(ra)001:6680: pad nyi zla ba'i gdan cha shas yongs su rdzogs par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:6689: byang shar rnams su pad zla'i gdan /
NK025(ra)001:6690: sgo bzhir brag dang nyi ma'i gdan rnams su gyur /
NK025(ra)001:6691: bzhi pa brten pa lha'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:6692: gdan de rnams kyi steng du dbus su a /
NK025(ra)001:6698: shar lho nas rtsibs mchan bzhir rim pa bzhin /
NK025(ra)001:6703: shar lho nas gru chad bzhir rim pa bzhin /
NK025(ra)001:6722: 'phro 'dus pas phyag mtshan bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su gyur pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:6723: dbus su rdo rje dang dril bu cha gnyis /
NK025(ra)001:6724: lhor rin po che dang dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:6725: nub tu pad+ma dang dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:6726: byang du ral gri dang dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:6727: shar lho nas rtsibs mchan bzhir rim bzhin myu gu dang me long /
NK025(ra)001:6728: ral gri dang rin po che'i phreng ba /
NK025(ra)001:6730: rdo rje dang gar gyi lag pa /
NK025(ra)001:6731: shar lho nas gru chad bzhir rim bzhin klu shing dang bdug spos /
NK025(ra)001:6733: rin po che'i snye ma dang me tog /
NK025(ra)001:6735: khyams kyi shar du rdoo rje rtse lnga pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:6737: snam bu'i shar lhor pi wang /
NK025(ra)001:6741: lho nub tu rin po che /
NK025(ra)001:6743: shar lhor thod dbyug dang lcags kyu /
NK025(ra)001:6744: lho sgor rdor dbyug dang zhags pa /
NK025(ra)001:6745: nub sgor pad dbyug dang lcags sgrog /
NK025(ra)001:6746: byang sgor rgya gram gyi dbyug pa dang dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:6752: tshur 'dus h+aum h+aum h+aum badz+ra tsit+ta /
NK025(ra)001:6753: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta a /
NK025(ra)001:6754: dbus su bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po
NK025(ra)001:6755: mthing dkar dmar pa'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi dang
NK025(ra)001:6756: po gnyis byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya /
NK025(ra)001:6757: bar pa gnyis rdo rje dang dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:6758: tha ma gnyis mnyam gzhag gi phyag rgya mdzad pa
NK025(ra)001:6759: yum kun tu bzang mo sngon mo dang mnyam par
NK025(ra)001:6762: gtso bo'i mdun gyi seng+ge'i khrir bcom ldan 'das mi
NK025(ra)001:6763: bskyod pa mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug
NK025(ra)001:6764: gi dang po gnyis kyis rdo rje dang dril bu
NK025(ra)001:6766: bar pa gnyis kyis 'khor lo dang pad+ma /
NK025(ra)001:6767: tha ma gnyis kyis rin po che dang ral gri /
NK025(ra)001:6768: yum dbyings phyug ma sngon mo rdor dril 'dzin pas yab la 'khyud pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6771: shar rtsibs la rnam par snang mdzad dkar sngo dmar
NK025(ra)001:6772: pa'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas gsum 'khor lo
NK025(ra)001:6774: mngon gsum dril bu pad+ma ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:6775: yum spyan ma dkar mo 'khor lo dang /
NK025(ra)001:6778: m+aam mo ha ra ti las lho rtsibs la rin
NK025(ra)001:6779: chen 'byung ldan ser sngo dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag
NK025(ra)001:6780: drug gi g.yas gsum rin chen rdo rje 'a khor
NK025(ra)001:6781: lo // g.yon gsum dril bu pad+ma ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:6782: yum m+aa ma k+ai ser mo rin po che dang dril bu 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6785: nub rtsibs la snang ba mtha' yas dmar dkar sngo
NK025(ra)001:6786: ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas gsum pad+ma rdo
NK025(ra)001:6787: rje 'khor lo / g.yon gsum dril bu rin chen ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:6788: yum na bza' dkar mo pad+ma dang dril bu 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6791: byang rtsibs la don yod grub pa ljang dkar dmar
NK025(ra)001:6792: ba'i zhal gsum phyag dug gi g.yas gsum ral gri
NK025(ra)001:6794: g.yon gsum dril bu rin chen pad+ma 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:6795: yum dam tshig sgrol ma ral gri dang dril bu 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6796: gtso bo drug ka mtshan dpes spras shing longs spyod
NK025(ra)001:6797: rdzogs sku dar dang rin po che'i rgyan du mas
NK025(ra)001:6798: spras shing yab rnams rdo rje'i skyil krung dang /
NK025(ra)001:6799: yum rnams pad+ma'i skyil krung gis bzhugs pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6801: h+aum l+aa s+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:6802: shar lho'i rtsibs mchan la sa snying dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK025(ra)001:6803: g.yas rin po che'i myu gu dang g.yon dril bu can /
NK025(ra)001:6804: yum l+aa s+ya dkar mo me long bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:6806: tram m+aa le sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:6807: lho nub kyi rtsibs mchan la nam mkha'i snying po ser po ral gri dang dril bu can /
NK025(ra)001:6808: yum phreng ba ma ser mo rin po che'i phreng ba 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6809: h+r+aihha h+aum pad+ma pa da ma /
NK025(ra)001:6811: nub byang gi rtsibs mchan la spyan ras gzigs dmar por pad+ma dang dril bu can /
NK025(ra)001:6812: yum glu ma dmar po pi wang bsnams pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6813: dz+rim ku ru pan+na h+r+aih a nir+t+ya r+aa ga ya mi /
NK025(ra)001:6814: byang shar gyi rtsibs mchan la phyag rdor ljang gu rdo rje dang dril bu can /
NK025(ra)001:6815: yum gar ma ljang gu gar bsgyur zhing ro brgya'i zhal zas stob pa'i tshul lo //
NK025(ra)001:6816: mee d+h+aa ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:6818: shar lho'i gru chad la byams pa dkar ser klu shing dang spyi blugs bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:6819: yum bdug spos ma dkar ser bdug spos bsnams pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6820: th+l+him nis+sa ram pa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:6822: lho nub kyi gru chad la sgrib sel dmar ser 'khor lo dang dril bu bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:6823: yum me tog ma ser mo me tog gi phreng ba bsnams pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6824: h+aum sa r+aa dza ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:6825: bam d+ai pa su khi n+ai /
NK025(ra)001:6826: nub byang gi gru chad la kun bzang dmar ljang
NK025(ra)001:6827: rin po che'i snye ma dang dril bu bsnams pa
NK025(ra)001:6828: / yum mar me ma dmar mo mar me bsnams pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6829: m+aum sh+r+ai a ram ga ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:6831: byang shar gyi gru chad la 'jam dbyangs dkar ljang ut+pala dang dril bu bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:6832: yum dri chab ma ljang gu dri'i dung chos bsnams pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6833: sems dpa' sems ma brgyad po yang longs spyod rdzogs sku dar dang rin po che'i rgyan can no //
NK025(ra)001:6835: khyams kyi shar du byed pa po kun bzang sngon po mnyam gzhag mnyam pa'i skyil krung can /
NK025(ra)001:6836: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta a /
NK025(ra)001:6837: khyams kyi nub tu bya ba mo kun tu bzang
NK025(ra)001:6838: mo dkar mo chos 'byung gi phyag rgya can mnyam
NK025(ra)001:6839: pa'i skyil krung gis bzhugs te rgyan spangs pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6841: snam bu'i shar lhor lha'i thub pa dkar po pi wang 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:6842: mu ne h+aum trum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:6843: snam bu'i byang du lha min thub pa sngon po g.yas ral gri dang g.yon go khrab can /
NK025(ra)001:6845: snam bu'i lhor mi'i thub pa ser po g.yas bseg shang dang g.yon lhung bzed 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6847: snam bu'i nub byang du byol song gi thub pa ljang gu glegs bam 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:6849: snam bu'i lho nub tu yi dwags kyi thub pa ser nag rin po che'i sgrom bu 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:6851: snam bu'i byang shar du dmyal ba'i thub pa dud kha me chu 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6852: thub pa drug ni sangs rgyas sprul sku mtshan dpe
NK025(ra)001:6853: can chos gos gsum ldan 'gro ba'i don la bzhengs
NK025(ra)001:6854: pa'o // h+aum ya m+aan+ta krita phata /
NK025(ra)001:6855: ma h+aa badz+ra d+h+aa ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:6856: shar sgor khro bo gshin rje gshed mthing nag thod
NK025(ra)001:6857: dbyug dang sdig mdzub can yum khro mo lcags kyu
NK025(ra)001:6858: ma mthing nag lcags kyu dang thod khrag 'dzin pa
NK025(ra)001:6860: ma h+aa rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:6861: lho sgor stobs chen ser nag rdo rje'i dbyug pa dang thod khrag can /
NK025(ra)001:6862: yum zhags pa ma ser nag zhags pa dang thod khrag 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6864: ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:6865: nub sgor rta mgrin dmar po pad+ma'i thod dbyug sbrul gyis dkris pa dang thod khrag can /
NK025(ra)001:6866: yum lcags sgrog ma dmar mo lcags sgrog dang thod khrag 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:6868: ma h+aa karma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:6869: byang sgor bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ljang nag rgya gram gyi dbyug pa dang thod khrag can /
NK025(ra)001:6870: yum dril bu ma ljang gu dril bu dang thod khrag can no //
NK025(ra)001:6871: sgo ba yab yum brgyad khro bo dang khro mo'i
NK025(ra)001:6872: chas ldan ye shes kyi me 'bar ba'i dbus na
NK025(ra)001:6878: brtan par bzhugs su gsol nas zhes 'byung ba'i don /
NK025(ra)001:6879: 'di man chod bdag mdun bum gsum thun mong du bya ba yin par /
NK025(ra)001:6880: bdag mdun gnyis bskyed ma thag dang /
NK025(ra)001:6881: zhi ba'i bum pa'i lha rnams kyang mngon sum lta bur bzhugs bzhin par gsal gdab ste /
NK025(ra)001:6882: bdag mdun bum gsum ka la dmigs te dbang bskur ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:6883: lnga pa la gnyis te dbang bskur ba dang byin gyis brlab pa'i dang po ni /
NK025(ra)001:6884: lag gnyis rdo rje phyi bsdams las gung mo gnyis
NK025(ra)001:6885: sbyar te sgreng ba rdo rje'i phyag rgya rang gi
NK025(ra)001:6886: spyi bor bzhag cing dkyil 'khor phyogs su yang btud
NK025(ra)001:6887: la / ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra
NK025(ra)001:6888: s+aa b+h+aa rdo rje bsdams pa las mdzub mo gnyis
NK025(ra)001:6889: brkyang pa dpral ba dang dkyil 'khor phyogs ma h+aa
NK025(ra)001:6890: +aa dar+sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa rdo rje bsdams
NK025(ra)001:6891: pa las srin lag gnyis brkyang pa rna ltag g.yas
NK025(ra)001:6892: dang dkyil 'khor phyogs ma h+aa sa ma t+aa dz+nya
NK025(ra)001:6893: na badz+ra swa b+h+aa rdo rje bsdams pa las mthe
NK025(ra)001:6894: bong gnyis brkyang ba ltag pa dang dkyil 'khor phyogs
NK025(ra)001:6895: ma h+aa pra t+ya bek+sha na dz+nya na badz+ra swa
NK025(ra)001:6896: b+h+aa rdo rje bsdams pa las mathe'u chung brkyang pa
NK025(ra)001:6897: rna ltag g.yon dang dkyil 'khor phyogs ma h+aa kri
NK025(ra)001:6898: t+y+aa nush+tha na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa bdag mdun
NK025(ra)001:6899: bum gsum gyi lha tshogs rnams kyi spyi gtsug tu
NK025(ra)001:6901: dpral bar rnam snang dkar po /
NK025(ra)001:6902: rna ltag g.yas su rin chen 'byung ldan ser po /
NK025(ra)001:6903: ltag par snang ba mtha' yas dmar po /
NK025(ra)001:6904: rna ltag g.yon du don yod grub pa ljang gu
NK025(ra)001:6905: rnams kyis dbu brgyan pa ni rtags kyi dbang dang
NK025(ra)001:6906: / ye shes lnga'i don thugs rgyud la gnas pa ni don gyi dbang ngo //
NK025(ra)001:6907: sangs rgyas lnga yi cod pan can //
NK025(ra)001:6908: dbu rgyan rin chen phreng ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:6909: dpung rgyan se mo do la sogs //
NK025(ra)001:6910: mdzes pa'i rgyan rnam sna tshogs kyis //
NK025(ra)001:6911: dbang mchog tu ni dbang bskur ro //
NK025(ra)001:6912: gnyis pa sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:6913: bshad ma thag pa'i rdo rje'i phyag rgya de nyid
NK025(ra)001:6914: rang gi gnas gsum dang sngags dang bstun gtug tshul
NK025(ra)001:6915: dang / dkyil 'khor du yang de bzhin du byas la /
NK025(ra)001:6916: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:6917: bdag bdun bum gsum gyi lha tshogs rnams kyi spyi bor zla ba la gnas pa'i dkar po /
NK025(ra)001:6919: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK025(ra)001:6920: sku rdo rje'i lha tshogs spyan drangs /
NK025(ra)001:6921: la thim pas sangs rgyas rnams kyi sku'i rang bzhin
NK025(ra)001:6922: las rnam snang dkar po 'khor lo dang dril bu
NK025(ra)001:6923: 'dzin par gyur / sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma
NK025(ra)001:6924: h+aa w+aa ka mgrin par pad+ma la gnas pa'i +aahdamara
NK025(ra)001:6925: 'dzin par gyur / po / de las 'od zer 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:6926: sangs rgyas gsung rdo rje'i lha tshogs +aahl thim pa
NK025(ra)001:6927: sangs rgyas rnams kyi gsung gi rang bzhin +aahls snang
NK025(ra)001:6928: mtha' dmar mo pad+ma dang dril bu 'dzin par gyur
NK025(ra)001:6929: / sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta thugs kar nyi ma la gnas pa'i h+aum sngon po /
NK025(ra)001:6931: sangs rgyas thugs rdo rje'i lha tshogs spyan drangs /
NK025(ra)001:6932: h+aum la thim pas sangs rgyas rnams kyi thugs kyi
NK025(ra)001:6933: rang bzhin h+aum las mi bskyod pa mthing ga rdo
NK025(ra)001:6934: rje dang dril bu 'dzin par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:6935: drug pa spyan drang ba la gsum gyi dang po snyan gsan dbab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:6936: bdag mdun bum gsum gyi lha tshogs rnams kyi thugs
NK025(ra)001:6937: kar rang 'dra ba'i ye shes sems dpa'i thugs kar
NK025(ra)001:6938: dwangs ma'i srog h+aum mthing ga ye shes lnga'i rang
NK025(ra)001:6939: bzhin can las 'od zer gyi phreng ba phyogs bcur
NK025(ra)001:6940: 'bar zhing 'phros pas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rgyal ba
NK025(ra)001:6941: sras dang bcas pa rang bzhin sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i
NK025(ra)001:6942: dkyil 'khor 'khor lo'i bdag nyid can du gyur te
NK025(ra)001:6943: 'gro ba'i don la chas bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:6944: stong pa shin tu yod med rnal 'byor mthu //
NK025(ra)001:6945: nam mkha' bzhin las dam tshig nye bar gnas //
NK025(ra)001:6946: bde gshegs bde bar gshegs mdzad gshegs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:6947: rdo rje sems dpa' skal bzang dpa' khyod bdag /
NK025(ra)001:6948: badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum dzah gnyis pa spyan drangs pa dngos ni /
NK025(ra)001:6949: lha tshogs de rnams mdun gyi nam mkha'i khams nas spyan drangs pa ste /
NK025(ra)001:6950: thugs rje'i lcags kyus thugs dam rgyud bskul zhing //
NK025(ra)001:6951: byams pa'i zhags pas gnas nas spyan yang 'dren //
NK025(ra)001:6952: lcags sgrog bka' yi pho nyas gnas bskyod de //
NK025(ra)001:6953: bde gshegs bzhugs shing rnam grol dgyes pa bskyed //
NK025(ra)001:6954: e h+ye hi b+ha ga wan ma h+aa k+aa ru
NK025(ra)001:6955: ni ka d+r+ai sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh sa
NK025(ra)001:6956: ma ya s+t+wam / dam tshig pa'i thugs ka nas
NK025(ra)001:6957: 'a phros pa'i phyag rgya bzhis bdag mdun bum gsum
NK025(ra)001:6958: gyi dam tshig pa rnams dang ye shes kyi dkyil
NK025(ra)001:6959: 'khor dgug bcings bsdams dgyes pa bskyed par bsam la
NK025(ra)001:6960: ma ya s+t+wam / / dzahh+aum bam hoh badz+ra am ku sha dzah badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:6962: badz+ra g+han+de hoh gsum pa brtan par bzhugs su gsol ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:6963: rin chen seng ge'i khri la yang dag nges bzhugs shing //
NK025(ra)001:6964: rang gi lha mo dag dang sras dang g.yog 'khor bcas pa rnams //
NK025(ra)001:6965: kun tu bzang po'i smon lam rjes su dgongs mdzad de //
NK025(ra)001:6966: 'jig rten lha dang bcas la sman slad bzhugs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:6967: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK025(ra)001:6968: bdun pa sdig sgrib sbyang ba'i phyir phrin las la
NK025(ra)001:6969: sbyar ba ni 'og tu 'dzab kyi dgongs pas 'thus
NK025(ra)001:6971: lhag pa ting nge 'dzin bsdus pas mchod la zhes 'byung yang /
NK025(ra)001:6972: phyag dang mchod phreng rgyas pas mi 'gal bas /
NK025(ra)001:6973: zhi ba rin chen d+r+wa ba bzhin 'di ltar phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:6974: mchod pa la bcu bzhi'i dang po phyag gi mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:6976: ma skyes rdo rje thabs kyi ye shes ni //
NK025(ra)001:6977: dmigs med shes rab yum gyi ngang du rtogs //
NK025(ra)001:6978: thugs rje'i bye brag sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK025(ra)001:6979: rdo rje sems dpa' che la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:6980: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK025(ra)001:6981: gzugs sku 'ja' tshon bzhin du so sor gsal //
NK025(ra)001:6982: thabs dang shes rab mchog la mnga' brnyes pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:6983: rigs lnga bde bar gshegs la dmigs med chos kyi
NK025(ra)001:6984: sku la longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la cir yang
NK025(ra)001:6985: sprul pa'i sku la khams gsum zhing du sbyor la
NK025(ra)001:6986: mdzes pa'i sku mchog sems can sgrol la mkhas //
NK025(ra)001:6987: ngo mtshar pho brang bde bar gshegs pa'i yum //
NK025(ra)001:6988: shes rab thabs kyi gtso la mnyes mdzad ma //
NK025(ra)001:6989: rigs kyi yum chen lnga la thabs mkhas thugs rje ye shes sprul pa yis //
NK025(ra)001:6990: rang rgyud rnal 'byor dag pas sgrub pa'i sa brnyes shing //
NK025(ra)001:6991: thugs rje chen po 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:6992: sems dpa' sems ma rnams la chos rnams rnam dag ye nas lhun grub pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:6993: rtog par bya ba'i yul ni chos bzang mo //
NK025(ra)001:6994: de nyid don rigs byed pa rdo rje yid //
NK025(ra)001:6995: kun bzang yab yum gnyis la rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK025(ra)001:6996: rtog pas rgyud drug so sor 'khor ba las //
NK025(ra)001:6997: thabs mkhas thugs rje cis 'dul der ston pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:6998: thub pa chen po drug la byams dang snying rje dga' dang btang snyoms kyis //
NK025(ra)001:6999: nyon mongs log pa ra lta ba'i dgra rnams 'joms //
NK025(ra)001:7000: gshin rje gshed po la sogs khro rgyal bzhi //
NK025(ra)001:7001: sgo ba yab yum rnams la a ti pu hoh pra t+aits+tsha hoh de nas dam bca' ste /
NK025(ra)001:7002: bde bar gshegs pa khyed ci 'dra //
NK025(ra)001:7003: de 'dra kho nar bdag gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:7004: spyod pa rmad byung bsam yas pa //
NK025(ra)001:7005: 'gro la phan phyir bdag gis spyad //
NK025(ra)001:7006: byang chub sems mchog dam pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:7007: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya 'di //
NK025(ra)001:7008: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong na //
NK025(ra)001:7009: rdo rje rgyal por byin brlabs mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:7011: sangs rgyas mdzad dka' bdag gis bsgrub //
NK025(ra)001:7012: byang chub spyad dka' bdag gis spyad //
NK025(ra)001:7014: bdag cag bsam pa 'grub gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:7015: gnyis pa phyag rgya'i mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7016: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:7017: dbang po'i yul du gar bsgyur ba //
NK025(ra)001:7018: thabs dang shes rab ldan gyur cing //
NK025(ra)001:7019: mnyam pa'i ngang nyid rtogs gsal nas //
NK025(ra)001:7020: thams cad byang chub mchog gi rgya //
NK025(ra)001:7021: bskyod chen 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su //
NK025(ra)001:7022: thabs dang shes rab thams cad kun //
NK025(ra)001:7024: bsgul bskyod thams cad phyag rgya yin //
NK025(ra)001:7025: 'di ni spyi rgya chen po ste //
NK025(ra)001:7026: bla med chen po 'di skad gsungs //
NK025(ra)001:7027: gsang ba de nyid nges pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:7033: mi bskyod nyi ma'i dkyil yi ge //
NK025(ra)001:7034: rin chen zla ba'i dkyil yi ge //
NK025(ra)001:7035: lnga gnyis zung du spros pa las //
NK025(ra)001:7036: sbyar bas phyag rgya 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK025(ra)001:7037: dang m+aum gnyis rtse sbyar te //
NK025(ra)001:7038: 'bru brgyad bsnol nas rtse sprad pa //
NK025(ra)001:7039: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:7040: bde ba chen po sbyin pa'i rgya //
NK025(ra)001:7041: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs kar bkan //
NK025(ra)001:7042: h+aum sgreng rtse mor rdo rje 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:7043: zla brtul 'bru sbas dril gsil zhing //
NK025(ra)001:7044: 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos la brten //
NK025(ra)001:7046: 'bru bzhi sbas nas m+aum sgreng rtse mor dril gsil 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:7048: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis blta //
NK025(ra)001:7050: 'bru bzhi sbas nas sgreng rtse mor 'khor lo 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:7051: zla brtul 'bru sbas 'khril ba'i tshul gyis dz+ai na dzika /
NK025(ra)001:7052: 'bru bzhi sbas nas l+aam sgreng rtse mor dril nyi
NK025(ra)001:7053: ma 'bru lnga las btud de 'dzub pa'i mdangs l+aam
NK025(ra)001:7055: 'bru bzhi sbas nas s+w+aa sgreng rtse mor rin chen 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:7056: zla brtul 'bru sbas 'khril ba'i tshul gyis s+w+aa rat+na d+h+rika /
NK025(ra)001:7057: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs m+aam sgreng rtse mor dril
NK025(ra)001:7058: nyi ma 'bru lnga las btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs
NK025(ra)001:7060: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs +aam sgreng rtse mor pad+ma 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:7061: zla brtul 'bru sbas dril 'khril ba'i tshul gyis +aamha ro lika /
NK025(ra)001:7062: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs p+y+aam sgreng rtse mor dril nyi ma 'bru lnga las su 'khril //
NK025(ra)001:7063: btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs p+y+aam r+aa ga ra ti /
NK025(ra)001:7064: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs h+aa sgreng rtse mor ral gri 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:7065: zla brtul 'bru sbas dril 'khril ba'i tshul gyis chos h+aa pradz+ny+aa d+h+rika /
NK025(ra)001:7066: 'bru bzhi sbas nas thugs t+aam sgreng rtse mor dril
NK025(ra)001:7067: nyi ma 'bru lnga las btud de 'dzum pa'i mdangs
NK025(ra)001:7069: 'di ni rgyal ba thams cad kyi //
NK025(ra)001:7070: dgyes pa chen po bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:7071: phyag rgya'i mchod pa dam pa yin //
NK025(ra)001:7072: a la la ste mchod par 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:7073: a la la ste dgyes par mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:7074: gsum pa kun tu bzang po'i mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7075: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK025(ra)001:7076: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i ye shes kyi //
NK025(ra)001:7077: srid pa'i rgya mtsho mtha' yas kun //
NK025(ra)001:7078: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK025(ra)001:7079: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo bi shwa mu
NK025(ra)001:7080: khe b+h+yahsarba th+aa kham ut+ga te s+pha ra na hi
NK025(ra)001:7081: mam ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:7082: bzhi pa phyag zhabs bsil ba'i mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7083: yang dag don du dag mod kyang //
NK025(ra)001:7084: 'gro ba yongs kyi don slad du //
NK025(ra)001:7085: phyag dang zhabs gnyis bsil nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:7086: rdo rje'i gdan la bzhugs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:7087: +aa ha ra +aa ha ra sarba bid+y+aa d+h+aa ra
NK025(ra)001:7088: p+au dz+ai te na mahs man+ta bud+d+ha nam ga ga
NK025(ra)001:7089: na kham sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:7090: lnga pa lha mo bzhi bsnol gyi mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7093: ti pu pa ra muh sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid d+hoo /
NK025(ra)001:7094: sa ma yo ta muh sarba ma h+aa su kha sid d+hoo /
NK025(ra)001:7095: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au /
NK025(ra)001:7096: pa na pem sh+ai badz+ra r+aa ga push+pe p+au /
NK025(ra)001:7097: pa na pem sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga +aa lo ke
NK025(ra)001:7098: h+r+aih pa na pem sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga gan+d+he gan
NK025(ra)001:7100: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:7101: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam tshig dam pa grub par mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:7103: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:7104: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam tshig dam pa dag cing grub par mdzad du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:7106: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:7107: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mchod pa chen po thams cad dag cing grub par mdzad du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:7108: drug pa bdud rtsi sman gyi mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7111: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:7112: rang byung gdod nas rnam par dag /
NK025(ra)001:7113: rtsa brgyad stong las sbyar ba'i sman //
NK025(ra)001:7114: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK025(ra)001:7115: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK025(ra)001:7116: rgyud lnga sems can kun sgrol ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:7117: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi mchog /
NK025(ra)001:7118: thams cad rnal 'byor bdud rtsi che //
NK025(ra)001:7119: byang chub sems ni rdo rje ste //
NK025(ra)001:7120: sha chen mchod pa rin po che //
NK025(ra)001:7121: pad+ma me tog yang dag ldan //
NK025(ra)001:7122: rdo rje chu ste las kyi mchog /
NK025(ra)001:7123: zas mchog tshe yi dri chen po //
NK025(ra)001:7124: ga bur shel gyi spos phor dri //
NK025(ra)001:7125: rin chen me ltar 'bar ba'i tshogs //
NK025(ra)001:7126: ma lus 'dus pa'i thig le che //
NK025(ra)001:7127: gcig tu dpa' ba'i ro rnams dang //
NK025(ra)001:7128: gnyis su med par mnyam sbyar nas //
NK025(ra)001:7129: bdud rtsi dam pa'i rin chen bcud //
NK025(ra)001:7130: bde gshegs rnams kyi thugs dam nyid //
NK025(ra)001:7131: rgyal pa rgyal mtsho'i dngos grub mchog /
NK025(ra)001:7133: bdag cag dad pa 'bul lags kyi //
NK025(ra)001:7134: thugs rjes dgongs nas bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:7135: bzhes nas rab tu dgyes mdzod la //
NK025(ra)001:7136: bla med dngos grub bdag la stsol //
NK025(ra)001:7137: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:7138: mi bskyod rnam snang rin 'a byung mtha' yas grub //
NK025(ra)001:7139: dus gsum bde gshegs rgyal mchog yab rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:7140: rnam dag bdag rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:7141: thugs rjes cher dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK025(ra)001:7142: ma h+aa bzang mo spyan dang m+aa ma gos dkar sgrol //
NK025(ra)001:7143: dus gsum bde gshegs rgyal mchog yum rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:7144: rnam dag thugs rjes ma h+aa 'gro ba'i dpal du gyur pa'i byang chub sems //
NK025(ra)001:7145: sa snying la sogs sems dpa' brgyad rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:7146: rnam dag thugs rjes ma h+aa sgeg mo phreng dang dbyangs dang gar ma sogs //
NK025(ra)001:7147: mdzes pa'i sku mchog lha mo brgyad rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:7148: rnam dag thugs rjes ma h+aa gshin rje stobs chen rta mgrin bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK025(ra)001:7149: rig pa'i rgyal po khro bo bzhi rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:7150: rnam dag thugs rjes ma h+aa lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dril bu ma //
NK025(ra)001:7151: ye shes gzhal yas sgo ma bzhi rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:7152: rnam dag thugs rjes ma h+aa dus gsum rgyal ba'i rang bzhin mkhyen pa'i dpal //
NK025(ra)001:7153: bya ba byeed dang gnyis med chos sku la //
NK025(ra)001:7154: rnam dag thugs rjes ma h+aa 'gro ba'i don phyir sprul pa'i skur ston pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:7155: 'jig rten 'dul ba'i thub pa drug rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:7156: rnam dag thugs rjes ma h+aa sdom la gnas shing rig 'dzin grub pa'i sa //
NK025(ra)001:7157: mkha' dang lha min phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor la //
NK025(ra)001:7158: rnam dag thugs rjes ma h+aa dam tshig dbang dang shes rgyud gab sbas pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:7159: nges pa'i lung ston rdo rje slob dpon la //
NK025(ra)001:7160: rnam dag thugs rjes ma h+aa shes pa'i khyad par rim par dbang bskur ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:7161: rgyal thebs spyan dang karma ging rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:7162: rnam dag thugs rjes ma h+aa tshe rabs sngon nas smon lam 'phro 'thud pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:7163: rgyal ba'i gdung gsob mched dang lcam dral la //
NK025(ra)001:7164: rnam dag thugs rjes ma h+aa yun ring dus nas bsnyen cing bsgrubs pa'i lha //
NK025(ra)001:7165: dam can rgya mtsho chos skyong srung ma la //
NK025(ra)001:7166: rnam dag thugs rjes ma h+aa 'jig rten 'di dang snga phyi gnyis ka ru //
NK025(ra)001:7167: lus srog bskyed pa'i dus gsum pha ma la //
NK025(ra)001:7168: rnam dag thugs rjes ma h+aa +aahh+aum /
NK025(ra)001:7169: lce yi dam tshig rdo rje ste //
NK025(ra)001:7170: rdo rje can gyi 'bru gsum bsgoms //
NK025(ra)001:7171: bdud rtsi lnga dang sbyar ba'i sman //
NK025(ra)001:7172: zos na byang chub mchog thob 'gyur //
NK025(ra)001:7174: w+aa ka sid+d+hi +aah tsit+ta sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:7177: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:7178: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aa ka sarba
NK025(ra)001:7179: ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta k+aa ya w+aa
NK025(ra)001:7181: bdun pa ba lim gtor ma'i mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7185: ka ma la m+aa la badz+ra a mri ta ha
NK025(ra)001:7186: ra na pra t+aits+tsha b+ha ga w+aa na dzahh+aum bam
NK025(ra)001:7187: hoh a la la hoh pa na pem /
NK025(ra)001:7189: ti pu pa ra muh sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid d+hoo /
NK025(ra)001:7190: sa ma yo ta muh sarba ma h+aa su kha sid d+ho /
NK025(ra)001:7192: brgyad pa gsang nan dbul ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:7194: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam pa sbyar ba ni //
NK025(ra)001:7195: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK025(ra)001:7196: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan te //
NK025(ra)001:7197: dam tshig gsang ba'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:7198: mi skye ye shes bde ba'i mchog dang ldan pa'i ro la bsnams su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:7199: a la la hoh byang chub sems dpa'i bde mchog de ni 'gog pa rnams las blang ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:7200: chags pa med pa'i bde mchog kun tu myong mdzad bzhes shing bsnams su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:7201: mchog tu gsang ba'i bde la rol zhing dam bcas 'jig rten sgrol //
NK025(ra)001:7202: byang chub skye gnas bde mchog dbyings las mi nyams dga' ba'i gar mdzod cig /
NK025(ra)001:7203: a la la hoh hoh sngon gyi zhen pa'i mtha' dang nyon mongs sngo skams gzir ba yi //
NK025(ra)001:7204: rmongs byed bde mchog rgyan dang ldan pas thabs kyis bskur te go bar mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:7205: 'gro kun mtshungs par spyod pa'i byang chub sgo mor lam ston cig /
NK025(ra)001:7206: bde mchog bdud rtsi khyad par med pa 'dus pa'i tshogs la bka' stsol cig /
NK025(ra)001:7207: a la la hoh dgu pa lhag pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:7208: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK025(ra)001:7209: sems kyi yid bzhin sprin tshogs kyis //
NK025(ra)001:7210: phyogs bcu thams cad sangs rgyas zhing //
NK025(ra)001:7211: mnyen 'jam reg na bde ba yi //
NK025(ra)001:7212: sna tshogs rin po che yi gzhi //
NK025(ra)001:7213: mdzes par bres shing spras pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:7215: dbyibs legs rdzing bu bro mchog bsil //
NK025(ra)001:7216: rin chen khang pa sna tshogs dang //
NK025(ra)001:7217: rgyan dang dpag bsam ljon pa'i tshal //
NK025(ra)001:7218: glu dbyangs tshigs su bcad pa'i sgra //
NK025(ra)001:7219: bla bre rgyal mtshan na bza' gdugs //
NK025(ra)001:7220: do shal dpung rgyan se mo do //
NK025(ra)001:7221: bza' dang btung ba'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK025(ra)001:7222: rang la mdzes par brgyan pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:7223: lha dang lha mo rdul snyed kyis //
NK025(ra)001:7224: bro gar la sogs bsam yas kyis //
NK025(ra)001:7225: phyogs bcu nam mkha'i khams bkang nas //
NK025(ra)001:7226: dkyil 'khor kun la rgyas par dbul //
NK025(ra)001:7227: skal ldan gsal ba'i khyad par gyis //
NK025(ra)001:7228: rim gyis yang na cig car du //
NK025(ra)001:7229: chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam sbyor zhing //
NK025(ra)001:7230: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen por sgom //
NK025(ra)001:7231: a la la ste mchod pa 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:7232: rtsa bar 'di nas 'dzab la 'jug par bshad kyang mchod phreng rnams tshang ba legs pas /
NK025(ra)001:7233: bcu pa ta na sgrol ba'i mchod pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:7234: ri rab chen po'i gling bzhi la //
NK025(ra)001:7235: gnas pa'i sems can ma lus kun //
NK025(ra)001:7236: ye shes me chen bsgom bya ste //
NK025(ra)001:7237: thams cad ma lus bsreg par bya //
NK025(ra)001:7238: srid gsum bsreg pa'i me yin te //
NK025(ra)001:7239: yid kyi ye shes me ru 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:7240: thog mar bdag nyid rtogs goms bsgral //
NK025(ra)001:7241: de nas gnyis med blo yis ni //
NK025(ra)001:7242: blo ngan 'jig rten snying re rje //
NK025(ra)001:7243: gnyis su med par bsgral bar bya //
NK025(ra)001:7244: bcu gcig pa ga na sbyor ba'i mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7245: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med par //
NK025(ra)001:7246: pad+mo la ni rdo rjee zhugs //
NK025(ra)001:7247: 'khril ba'i mchod chen mnyam sbyor bas //
NK025(ra)001:7248: bdag nyid mnyes pas mnyes par bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:7249: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:7250: a nu r+aa ga ya mi /
NK025(ra)001:7251: a nu r+aa ga ya ham /
NK025(ra)001:7252: dzahh+aum bam hoh h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:7253: bo d+hi tsit+ta s+pha ra na phata /
NK025(ra)001:7255: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa p+au dza badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:7256: bcu gnyis pa 'dod yon lnga'i mchod pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:7257: bza' dang bca' dang btung dang bgo //
NK025(ra)001:7258: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad ni //
NK025(ra)001:7260: chos nyid la ni chos nyid rol //
NK025(ra)001:7261: a la la hoh bcu gsum pa glu ye shes kyi mchod pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:7262: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:7263: ye shes dkyil 'khor thig le che //
NK025(ra)001:7264: bsod nams dkyil 'khor sku yi tshogs //
NK025(ra)001:7265: snang stong thig le kun tu rdzogs hoh /
NK025(ra)001:7266: rdo rje bsod nams thig le che //
NK025(ra)001:7267: rdo rje ye shes dkyil 'khor ldan //
NK025(ra)001:7268: rdo rje sgra chen mtha' yas pa //
NK025(ra)001:7269: rdo rje rgyal po thig le che hoh /
NK025(ra)001:7270: sku gsung thugs kyi rdzogs pa che //
NK025(ra)001:7271: yon tan phrin las kun tu rdzogs //
NK025(ra)001:7272: ye nas lhun rdzogs kun tu bzang //
NK025(ra)001:7273: 'dus pa'i tshogs chen thig le che hoh /
NK025(ra)001:7274: mi dmigs sgyu 'phrul mnyam pa'i dbyings //
NK025(ra)001:7275: mtha' yas kun nas sna tshogs 'phro //
NK025(ra)001:7276: mtha' yas kun nas lhun gyis thim //
NK025(ra)001:7277: sna tshogs sku gsung thugs chen po hoh /
NK025(ra)001:7278: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten rdul snyed du //
NK025(ra)001:7279: rgyal ba'i don ni rdul phran snyed //
NK025(ra)001:7280: sprul pa'i rdul phran grangs snyed kyis //
NK025(ra)001:7281: skad cig yud la lhum gyis grub hoh thams cad ma lus sku gsung thugs //
NK025(ra)001:7282: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag nyid che //
NK025(ra)001:7283: sku gsung thugs kyis kun tu khyab //
NK025(ra)001:7284: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le che hoh bcu bzhi pa rol mo sgra'i mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7285: dbang po'i spyod yul rang bzhin dngos po med //
NK025(ra)001:7286: rnam dag bdud rtsis rang bzhin dug lnga sel //
NK025(ra)001:7287: dam rdzas dag pa lnga dang zhal zas lnga //
NK025(ra)001:7288: sku lnga chos lnga dbyer med rang bzhin mnyam //
NK025(ra)001:7289: de phyir dag pas dag pa nyid mchod cing //
NK025(ra)001:7290: chos nyid la ni chos nyid thim par dbul //
NK025(ra)001:7291: dri med rnam dag nam mkha'i rang bzhin las //
NK025(ra)001:7292: lo rtog mtshan ma mang po'i sprin spungs te //
NK025(ra)001:7293: ye shes nyi zer 'od kyis rab brgyan te //
NK025(ra)001:7294: dag pa'i don phyir rtogs nas mchod par bgyi //
NK025(ra)001:7295: mnyam nyid blang dor med par snyoms par 'jug pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:7296: bde mchog longs spyod rdzogs pa sku yis rab brgyan te //
NK025(ra)001:7297: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yi lha mor gyur pa 'di //
NK025(ra)001:7298: dam tshig bzhin la ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:7302: dzahh+aum bam hoh pra t+aits+tsha hoh hoh spros pa med
NK025(ra)001:7303: pa'i dbyings las rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor rnam par
NK025(ra)001:7304: dag pa na / dus gsum du gshegs shing bzhugs
NK025(ra)001:7305: pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnam pa thams cad
NK025(ra)001:7306: mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi bye brag dang ldan pa
NK025(ra)001:7307: dag pa na / / bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo
NK025(ra)001:7308: rje sems dpa' la sogs pa rigs lnga'i bde bar
NK025(ra)001:7309: gshegs pa rigs mchog yum gyi gzungs dang bcas pa
NK025(ra)001:7310: dag pa na / / sems dpa'i tshogs / sems ma'i 'khor /
NK025(ra)001:7311: ye shes chen po'i dbang phyug /
NK025(ra)001:7312: thabs la mkhas pa'i bdag nyid /
NK025(ra)001:7316: ma lus mi lus lus pa med pa thams cad dang /
NK025(ra)001:7317: so so'i bzhugs gnas dang gzhal yas khang khyad par
NK025(ra)001:7318: can nas sku bskyod de mchod pa'i gnas dam pa
NK025(ra)001:7319: 'dir gshegs shing byin gyis brlab par mdzad du gsol
NK025(ra)001:7320: / hoh gzhan yang rnal 'byor gyi mchod yon dam pa sku gsung thugs rdo rje las byung ba /
NK025(ra)001:7321: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che /
NK025(ra)001:7322: yon tan dpag bsam gyi ljon shing /
NK025(ra)001:7323: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i lha mo gyur pa 'di byin gyis brlabs te phul bas /
NK025(ra)001:7324: ye shes rgya mtsho dus gsum du bzhugs pa rnams
NK025(ra)001:7325: kyi spyan lam du mngon sum du 'bab par gyur
NK025(ra)001:7326: cig / de ltar mngon sum du babs nas kyang rig pa mchog gi thugs rjes bzhes te /
NK025(ra)001:7327: bde ba mchog gi dgyes pa la longs spyad du gsol /
NK025(ra)001:7328: hoh mthol bshags bzod par gsol ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:7329: bdag gis dang po gsang ba rdo rje theg pa'i sgor khas 'ches te /
NK025(ra)001:7330: dam tshig gnyan po mngon par nos pa las /
NK025(ra)001:7331: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig nyams pa 'gal 'khrul du gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:7332: lha nye bar ma bsgom pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:7333: snying po yang dag par ma bgrangs pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:7334: sbyor ba mang po'i bar bskums pa /
NK025(ra)001:7335: dad pa can gyi tshogs bcag pa /
NK025(ra)001:7336: dge ba can gyi thugs dkrugs pa /
NK025(ra)001:7337: mchod pa lo zla las 'das pa /
NK025(ra)001:7338: dam rdzas dang du len rngo ma thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:7340: 'dzab dang bzlas brjod grangs nyung ba /
NK025(ra)001:7341: ting nge 'dzin thang lhod du gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:7342: le lo dang btang snyoms kyi dbang du gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:7343: mdor na de bzhin gshegs pa'i mdzad spyod klong du ma gyur cing /
NK025(ra)001:7344: sems can gyi rang bzhin du gyur bas snga slad
NK025(ra)001:7345: du dam tshig chag nyams su gyur pa thams cad
NK025(ra)001:7346: ni shin tu gnong zhing 'gyod pa'i sems kyis mthol
NK025(ra)001:7348: thugs rje chen pos bzod pa dang du bzhes te
NK025(ra)001:7349: tshangs pa yid bzhin du thob par stsal du gsol
NK025(ra)001:7350: / hoh dngos grub tu gsol ba'i mdo ni /
NK025(ra)001:7351: shes bya thams cad la thogs pa med pa'i shes rab /
NK025(ra)001:7357: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sku gsung thugs man chad /
NK025(ra)001:7358: dngos grub kyi rgyu dang skal pa gang lags pa dus phyi mar bsdad mi 'tshal bar /
NK025(ra)001:7359: dus da lta nyid du thob par mdzad du gsol /
NK025(ra)001:7360: hoh phrin las su gsol ba'i mdo ni /
NK025(ra)001:7361: bdag la sdang bar byed pa'i dgra /
NK025(ra)001:7363: gdug pa'i dpal du gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:7366: ye 'brog sum brgya drug cu la sogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:7367: mi shis pa de dag thams cad phyir bzlog cing zhi ba chen po mdzad du gsol /
NK025(ra)001:7368: hoh 'dod don du gsol ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:7369: bdag cag dam tshig 'di la mngon du zhugs pa rnams //
NK025(ra)001:7370: bcad gtubs sdug bsngal lus la 'byung bar mi 'gyur zhing //
NK025(ra)001:7371: grib ma phog pa'i sdug bsngal shin tu mi bzod pa //
NK025(ra)001:7372: sku yi phyogs tsam mthong bas mod la 'tsho ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:7373: gzi mdangs lus la 'jug pa'i nyi ma stong phrag gi //
NK025(ra)001:7374: 'od bzhin 'jig rten khams 'dir rtag tu 'char ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:7375: lus gang sems la tshe 'dir rdo rje rab snang ste //
NK025(ra)001:7376: re smon thams cad dus 'dir thob par mdzad du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:7377: sgyu 'phrul zhi ba rin chen d+r+wa ba'i las byang chog khrigs bar ma'i rgyun la skabs 'dir /
NK025(ra)001:7378: de nas rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal gdab /
NK025(ra)001:7380: lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi 'dzab bzlas shing /
NK025(ra)001:7382: zhes gsungs par 'di yan chod sgyu 'phrul dang ma
NK025(ra)001:7383: sbyar ba'i thabs med phyir zur nas kha bkang ba
NK025(ra)001:7384: yin la / dang po 'dzab khang dbye ba ni
NK025(ra)001:7385: bdag mdun gyi sgrub mchod dngos la ngos 'dzin pa
NK025(ra)001:7388: zhi ba'i 'dzab khang dbye ba ni rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor gsal gdab pa /
NK025(ra)001:7389: zhes sogs nas mchod bstod kyi bar grub rjes /
NK025(ra)001:7394: gnyis pa 'dzab dngos la lha bskul ba /
NK025(ra)001:7395: rtog pa'i gnas gsal gdab cing 'dzab bya ba /
NK025(ra)001:7397: dang po lha bskul ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:7398: kun bzang gong ltar bskyed la zhes gsungs pa bskyed
NK025(ra)001:7399: tshul rgyas par grub pa de gsal btab la 'dzab
NK025(ra)001:7402: rang gi thugs ka nas 'od gtso bo'i thugs kar
NK025(ra)001:7403: 'phros pas mnyes te gtso bo'i thugs ka nas 'od
NK025(ra)001:7405: rang gi bag chags dri ma dag /
NK025(ra)001:7406: gtso bo mnyes pa'i zhal 'dzum pa dang bcas bas rang la thim /
NK025(ra)001:7407: mchog thun mong gi dngos grub ster bar bsam la zhi ba'i bum pa'i gzugs thag nas bzung ste /
NK025(ra)001:7409: rig pa gsung gi byin rlabs kyis //
NK025(ra)001:7410: ljags kyi rtse la bkram nas ni //
NK025(ra)001:7411: du ma nyid du so sor go //
NK025(ra)001:7413: seng chen bsnol ba'i khri steng na //
NK025(ra)001:7414: rin chen nyi zla pad gdan la //
NK025(ra)001:7415: e ma kun bzang rdo rje nyid //
NK025(ra)001:7416: rig pa'i tshul snang sangs rgyas pa //
NK025(ra)001:7417: sangs rgyas thams cad bskyed pa'i yab //
NK025(ra)001:7419: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK025(ra)001:7420: dang po byang chub mchog gi rgya //
NK025(ra)001:7421: bar pa rdo rje dril bu 'dzin //
NK025(ra)001:7422: tha ma mnyam gzhag ye shes 'phro //
NK025(ra)001:7423: yum gyi dam par mtshan gsol ba //
NK025(ra)001:7424: phyi yi yul la sangs rgyas pa //
NK025(ra)001:7425: snang srid thams cad chos kyi dbyings //
NK025(ra)001:7426: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i yum //
NK025(ra)001:7427: bya ba mo dang gnyis su med //
NK025(ra)001:7428: bdag gi yi dam lha lags kyi //
NK025(ra)001:7429: yi dam lha la mchod par 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:7430: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK025(ra)001:7431: gnyis pa rtog pa'i gnas gsal gdab cing 'dzab bya ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:7434: yid shes rang rig ma skyes sems //
NK025(ra)001:7435: kun bzang yab kyi rang bzhin las //
NK025(ra)001:7436: ting 'dzin byed par dbang bskur nas //
NK025(ra)001:7437: ma lus kun gyis byed por shog /
NK025(ra)001:7438: chos kyi skye med ma skyes sems //
NK025(ra)001:7439: kun bzang yum gyi rang bzhin las //
NK025(ra)001:7440: ting 'dzin bya bar dbang bskur nas //
NK025(ra)001:7441: chos rnams kun gyi bya bar shog /
NK025(ra)001:7443: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta a /
NK025(ra)001:7448: byang chub sems mchog ye shes rdo rje'i thugs //
NK025(ra)001:7449: srid gsum dbang sdud thams cad mkhyen pa'i dpal //
NK025(ra)001:7450: bsnyel ba mi mnga' 'gro ba'i skyabs mdzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:7451: kun bzang rdo rje yid la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:7453: gdod nas ma byung ma skyes chos kyi dbyings //
NK025(ra)001:7454: ma skyes mi 'gag dngos por 'dzin dang bral //
NK025(ra)001:7455: 'byung byed thams cad bskyed pa yum gyi tshul //
NK025(ra)001:7456: bzang mo bya ba mo la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:7457: de bzhin du lha thams cad la dang por lha bskul ba /
NK025(ra)001:7458: gnyis pa rtog pa'i gnas gsal gdab cing 'dzab bya ba /
NK025(ra)001:7459: gsum pa bstod pa gsum kun la shes par bya ste /
NK025(ra)001:7461: de'i mdun du h+aum badz+ra d+h+rika /
NK025(ra)001:7463: mi bskyod pa yab yum bskyed tshar ba de nyid gsal gdab la /
NK025(ra)001:7464: 'od zer 'phro 'du gong ma ltar byas te /
NK025(ra)001:7466: rig pa gsung gi byin ljags kyi rtse la bkram
NK025(ra)001:7467: du ma nyid du so 'khor lo 'bar ba'i lte
NK025(ra)001:7468: seng chen bsnol ba'i khri rin chen nyi zla ston
NK025(ra)001:7469: pa rdo rje sems dpa'i gtso //
NK025(ra)001:7472: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK025(ra)001:7473: rdo rje 'khor lo rin chen g.yas //
NK025(ra)001:7474: dril bu pad+ma ral gri g.yon //
NK025(ra)001:7475: yum gyi dam par mtshan gsol ba //
NK025(ra)001:7476: kun tu bzang dang gnyis su med //
NK025(ra)001:7477: bdag gi yi dam lha yi dam lha la mchod sku gsung thugs kyi dngos gnyis pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7479: rnam shes nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK025(ra)001:7480: sems phyir mtshan nyid ma skyes pas //
NK025(ra)001:7481: mi bskyod yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK025(ra)001:7482: ting 'dzin thugs su dbang bskur nas //
NK025(ra)001:7483: dngos grub las rnams mngon byed shog /
NK025(ra)001:7488: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK025(ra)001:7489: gzugs sku stong pa nyid kyi tshul 'dzin cing //
NK025(ra)001:7490: yon tan ye shes lnga don thugs chud pa //
NK025(ra)001:7491: rgyal mchog mi bskyod pa la phyag don dam gnyis med dbyings su gsal //
NK025(ra)001:7492: dbyings phyug yum mchog tshul 'dzin cing //
NK025(ra)001:7493: yon tan rnam rtog mi mnga' ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:7494: rgyal yum kun tu bzang mo la'o //
NK025(ra)001:7495: shar du 'khor lo'i rtsibs la rnam snang bskyed pa gsal btab la /
NK025(ra)001:7496: gsum gyi dang po 'phro 'du byas te /
NK025(ra)001:7498: shar phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK025(ra)001:7499: glang chen bsnol ba'i khri steng du //
NK025(ra)001:7500: rin chen nyi zla bcom ldan rnam par snang mdzad gtso //
NK025(ra)001:7503: g.yas sngo g.yon dmar dbus dkar zhal //
NK025(ra)001:7504: 'khor lo rdo rje rin chen g.yas //
NK025(ra)001:7505: dril bu pad+ma rgya gram g.yon //
NK025(ra)001:7506: yum gyi dam par sangs rgyas spyan dang gnyis su med //
NK025(ra)001:7507: bdag gi yi dam yi dam lha la sku gsung thugs kyi gnyis pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7509: gzugs phung sa yi ngo sems phyir mtshan nyid ma
NK025(ra)001:7510: snang mdzad yab yum rang ting 'dzin sku ru dbang
NK025(ra)001:7516: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK025(ra)001:7517: gzugs sku me long lta bu'i tshul 'dzin cing //
NK025(ra)001:7518: yon tan chos kyi 'khor lo bskor mdzad pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:7519: rgyal mchog snang mdzad la phyag don dam gnyis med dbyings su gsal //
NK025(ra)001:7520: de bzhin dbyings phyug tshul 'dzin pa //
NK025(ra)001:7521: yon tan yod med stong pa'i cha //
NK025(ra)001:7522: sangs rgyas spyan la phyag lhor rin chen 'byung ldan bskyed pa gsal btab la /
NK025(ra)001:7523: gsum gyi dang po 'phro 'du byas te /
NK025(ra)001:7525: lho phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs rta mchog bsnol ba'i khri
NK025(ra)001:7526: rin chen nyi zla bcom ldan rin chen 'byung ldan
NK025(ra)001:7527: gtso // sku mdog ser po 'od du 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:7529: g.yas sngon g.yon dmar dbus ser zhal //
NK025(ra)001:7530: rin chen rdo rje 'khor lo g.yas //
NK025(ra)001:7531: dril bu pad+ma rgya gram g.yon //
NK025(ra)001:7532: yum gyi dam par mtshan m+aa ma k+ai dang gnyis
NK025(ra)001:7533: bdag gi yi dam lha yid dam lha la mchod
NK025(ra)001:7534: // sku gsung thugs kyi dngos gnyis pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7536: tshor ba chu yi ngo sems phyir mtshan nyid ma
NK025(ra)001:7537: 'byung ldan yab yum rang ting 'dzin yon tan dbang
NK025(ra)001:7538: dngos grub las rnams mngon s+w+aa rat+na d+h+rika /
NK025(ra)001:7542: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK025(ra)001:7543: gzugs sku mnyam pa nyid kyi tshul 'dzin cing //
NK025(ra)001:7544: yon tan yid bzhin re ba skong mdzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:7545: rgyal mchog rin chen 'byung ldan la don dam gnyis med dbyings su gsal //
NK025(ra)001:7546: m+aa ma k+ai yi rang bzhin la //
NK025(ra)001:7547: nga dang bdag med cha 'dzin ma //
NK025(ra)001:7548: m+aa ma k+ai la phyag nub tu snang ba mtha' yas bskyed pa gsal btab la //
NK025(ra)001:7549: gsum gyi dang po 'phro 'du byas te /
NK025(ra)001:7551: nub phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs rma bya bsnol ba'i khri
NK025(ra)001:7552: rin chen nyi zla bcom ldan snang ba mtha' yas
NK025(ra)001:7553: ni // sku mdog dmar po 'od du 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:7555: g.yas ser g.yon ljang dbus dmar zhal //
NK025(ra)001:7557: dril bu rin chen rgya gram g.yon //
NK025(ra)001:7558: yum gyi dam par mtshan na bza' dkar dang gnyis
NK025(ra)001:7559: bdag gi yi dam lha yi dam lha la mchod
NK025(ra)001:7560: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos gnyis pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7562: 'du shes me yi ngo sems phyir mtshan nyid ma
NK025(ra)001:7563: mtha' yas yab yum rang ting 'dzin gsung du dbang
NK025(ra)001:7564: dngos grub las rnams mngon +aamha ro lika /
NK025(ra)001:7568: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK025(ra)001:7569: gzugs sku so sor rtog pa'i tshul 'dzin cing //
NK025(ra)001:7570: yon tan mtha' gnyis skyon gyis ma gos pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:7571: rgyal mchog snang ba mtha' yas la don dam gnyis med dbyings su gsal //
NK025(ra)001:7572: pad+ma dbyings phyug rang bzhin la //
NK025(ra)001:7573: spyi dang rang gi cha 'dzin ma //
NK025(ra)001:7574: na bza' dkar la phyag byang du don yod grub pa bskyed pa gsal btab la /
NK025(ra)001:7575: gsum gyi dang po 'phro 'du byas te /
NK025(ra)001:7577: byang phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs shang shang bsnol ba'i khri
NK025(ra)001:7578: rin chen nyi zla bcom ldan don yod grub pa
NK025(ra)001:7579: ni // sku mdog ljang gu 'od du 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:7581: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus ljang zhal //
NK025(ra)001:7582: ral gri rdo rje 'khor lo g.yas //
NK025(ra)001:7583: dril bu rin chen pad+ma g.yon //
NK025(ra)001:7584: yum gyi dam par mtshan dam tshig sgrol dang gnyis
NK025(ra)001:7585: bdag gi yi dam lha yi dam lha la mchod
NK025(ra)001:7586: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos gnyis pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7588: 'du byed rlung gi ngo sems phyir mtshan nyid ma
NK025(ra)001:7589: don grub yab yum rang ting 'dzin phrin las dbang
NK025(ra)001:7590: dngos grub las rnams mngon h+aa pradz+ny+aa d+h+rika /
NK025(ra)001:7594: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK025(ra)001:7595: gzugs sku bya ba grub pa'i tshul 'dzin cing //
NK025(ra)001:7596: yon tan phrin las sna tshogs don mdzad pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:7597: rgyal mchog don yod grub pa la don dam gnyis med dbyings su gsal //
NK025(ra)001:7598: las kyi dbyings phyug tshul 'dzin cing //
NK025(ra)001:7599: bdag gzhan don grub cha 'dzin ma //
NK025(ra)001:7600: dam tshig sgrol la phyag de nas sems dpa'i 'dzab ni /
NK025(ra)001:7601: shar lho'i gong ras la sa snying yab yum bskyed
NK025(ra)001:7602: pa gsal btab la gsum gyi dang po 'phro 'du
NK025(ra)001:7604: shar lho 'khor lo'i gong ras la //
NK025(ra)001:7605: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan steng na //
NK025(ra)001:7606: byang sems sa yi snying po dang //
NK025(ra)001:7607: yum chen lha mo l+aa s+ya ma //
NK025(ra)001:7608: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK025(ra)001:7609: las nyon bag chags sbyang du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:7611: mig gzugs sems phyir ma skyes pa //
NK025(ra)001:7612: sa snying yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK025(ra)001:7613: ting 'dzin sems dpar dbang bskur nas //
NK025(ra)001:7614: spyod yul yongs su dag byed shog /
NK025(ra)001:7616: h+aum l+aa s+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:7620: me long ye shes khyad par las //
NK025(ra)001:7621: mtshan dpe sems dpa'i skur ston cing //
NK025(ra)001:7622: che ba'i yon tan bskyod mdzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:7623: sa yi snying por phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:7624: gnyis med chos dbyings khyad par las //
NK025(ra)001:7625: mtshan dpe lha mo'i skur ston cing //
NK025(ra)001:7626: rnam rtog zil gyis gnon mdzad ma //
NK025(ra)001:7627: l+aa s+ya ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:7628: lho nub kyi gong ras la nam snying yab yum bskyed pa gsal btab la /
