NK025(ra)001:7629: gsum gyi dang po 'phro 'du byas te /
NK025(ra)001:7631: lho nub 'khor lo'i gong nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan byang sems nam mkha'i snying po dang //
NK025(ra)001:7632: yum chen lha mo m+aa le gnyis //
NK025(ra)001:7633: gnyis med las nyon gnyis pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7634: sna dri sems phyir nam snying yab yum ting 'dzin
NK025(ra)001:7635: sems dpar spyod yul yongs su tram a gar+b+ha ya
NK025(ra)001:7636: / tram m+aa le sa ma ya hoh zhes bzlas so //
NK025(ra)001:7638: mnyam nyid ye shes khyad mtshan dpe sems dpa'i skur rnam rtog d+r+wa ba gcod mdzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:7639: nam mkha'i snying por phyag gnyis med chos dbyings khyad
NK025(ra)001:7640: mtshan dpe lha mo'i skur 'khor ba zil gyis non
NK025(ra)001:7641: mdzad ma // m+aa le ma la phyag nub byang
NK025(ra)001:7642: gi gong ras la spyan ras gzigs yab yum bskyed
NK025(ra)001:7644: gsum gyi dang po 'phro 'du byas te /
NK025(ra)001:7646: nub byang 'khor lo'i gong nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan byang sems spyan ras gzigs dbang dang //
NK025(ra)001:7647: yum chen lha mo g+ai ti ma //
NK025(ra)001:7650: lce ro sems phyir ma spyan ras gzigs dbang yab yum las //
NK025(ra)001:7651: ting 'dzin sems dpar spyod yul yongs su h+r+aihha h+aum pad+ma pa da ma /
NK025(ra)001:7656: sor rtog ye shes khyad mtshan dpe sems dpa'i skur mtha' yi dri mas ma gos pa //
NK025(ra)001:7657: spyan ras gzigs la phyag gnyis med chos dbyings khyad
NK025(ra)001:7658: mtshan dpe lha mo'i skur gnyis med don gyis tshim
NK025(ra)001:7659: mdzad ma // g+ai ti ma la phyag byang shar
NK025(ra)001:7660: gyi gong ras la phyag rdoor yab yub bskyed pa
NK025(ra)001:7661: mdzad ma // gsal btab la / gsum gyi dang po 'phro 'du byas te /
NK025(ra)001:7663: byang shar 'khor lo'i gong nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan byang sems phyag na rdo rje dang //
NK025(ra)001:7664: yum chen lha mo n+air+t+ya gnyis //
NK025(ra)001:7665: gnyis med las nyon gnyis pa na /
NK025(ra)001:7666: rna sgra sems phyir ma phyag rdor yab yum rang
NK025(ra)001:7667: ting 'dzin sems dpar spyod yul yongs su dz+rim ku
NK025(ra)001:7668: ru pan+na h+r+aih a n+ai r+t+ya r+aa ga ya mi
NK025(ra)001:7672: mtshan dpe sems dpa'i skur rnam rtog ma lusa'ajomasa mdzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:7673: phyag na rdo rjer phyag gnyis med chos dbyings khyad
NK025(ra)001:7674: mtshan dpe lha mo'i skur phrin las sna tshogs rdzogs
NK025(ra)001:7675: mdzad ma // n+air+t+ya ma la phyag phyi'i sems dpa' bzhi'i 'dzab ni /
NK025(ra)001:7676: shar lhoor byams pa yab yum bskyed pa gsal btab la /
NK025(ra)001:7677: gsum gyi dang po 'phro 'du byas te /
NK025(ra)001:7679: dkyil 'khor shar lho'i gru chad la //
NK025(ra)001:7680: nyi zla'i pad+ma'i gdan byang chub sems dpa' byams pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:7681: yum chen lha mo d+h+au pe gnyis //
NK025(ra)001:7682: gnyis med las nyon gnyis pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7683: mi dbang 'das dus ma byams pa yab yum rang
NK025(ra)001:7684: ting 'dzin sems dpar spyod yul yongs su me d+h+aa
NK025(ra)001:7685: ra ni s+w+aa h+aa dzahd+h+au pe pra be sha phata
NK025(ra)001:7689: thugs kyi ye shes khyad mtshan dpe sems dpa'i skur rgyal ba'i yon tan rgyas mdzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:7690: byams pa de la phyag h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:7691: skye med chos dbyings byin rlabs las //
NK025(ra)001:7692: mtshan dpe lha mo'i skur skye med don dam ston mdzad ma //
NK025(ra)001:7693: d+h+au pe ma la phyag lho nub kyi grar sgrib pa rnam sel bskyed pa gsal btab la /
NK025(ra)001:7694: gsum gyi dang po 'phro 'du byas te /
NK025(ra)001:7696: dkyil 'khor lho nub gru nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan byang sems sgrib pa rnam sel dang //
NK025(ra)001:7697: yum chen lha mo push+pe gnyis //
NK025(ra)001:7698: gnyis med las nyon gnyis pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7699: rna dbang da ltar ma skyes sems //
NK025(ra)001:7700: sgrib sel yab yum rang ting 'dzin sems dpar spyod
NK025(ra)001:7701: yul yongs su th+l+him nis+sa ram pa ye s+w+aa h+aa
NK025(ra)001:7702: / h+aum push+pe a be sha phata dzah zhes bzlas so //
NK025(ra)001:7705: ye shes rigs pa'i byin mtshan dpe sems dpa'i skur skye med chos sku ston mdzad ma //
NK025(ra)001:7706: sgrib pa rnam sel phyag h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:7707: skye med chos dbyings rang bzhin las //
NK025(ra)001:7708: mtshan dpe lha mo'i skur rig pa nyid las 'char mdzad ma //
NK025(ra)001:7709: push+pe ma la phyag nub byang du kun bzang yab yum bskyed pa gsal btab la /
NK025(ra)001:7710: gsum gyi dang po 'phro 'du byas te /
NK025(ra)001:7712: dkyil 'khor nub byang gru nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan byang sems kun tu bzang po dang //
NK025(ra)001:7713: yum chen lha mo +aa lo ke //
NK025(ra)001:7714: gnyis med las nyon gnyis pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7715: sna dbang ma 'ongs ma kun bzang yab yum rang
NK025(ra)001:7716: ting 'dzin sems dpar spyod yul yongs su h+aum sa
NK025(ra)001:7717: r+aa dza ya / bam d+ai pa su khi n+ai phata dzah zhes bzlas so //
NK025(ra)001:7720: ye shes rig pa'i byin mtshan dpe sems dpa'i skur 'bras bu'i chos rnams rdzogs mdzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:7721: kun tu bzang por phyag h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:7722: skye med chos kyi rang mtshan dpe lha mo'i skur rig pa nyid la gsal mdzad ma //
NK025(ra)001:7724: byang shar gyi grar 'jam dpal yab yum bskyed pa gsal btab pa la /
NK025(ra)001:7725: gsum gyi dang po 'phro 'du byas te /
NK025(ra)001:7727: dkyil 'khor byang shar gru nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan byang chub sems dpa' 'jam dpal dang //
NK025(ra)001:7728: yum chen lha mo gan+d+he ma //
NK025(ra)001:7729: gnyis med las nyon gnyis pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7730: lce dbang ma nges ma 'jam dpal yab yum rang
NK025(ra)001:7731: ting 'dzin sems dpar spyod yul yongs su m+aum sh+r+ai
NK025(ra)001:7733: hohgan+d+he tsit+ta phata dzah zhes bzlas so //
NK025(ra)001:7736: ye shes rig pa'i byin mtshan dpe sems dpa'i skur 'khor ba'i mtshan nyid rtogs mdzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:7738: skye med chos dbyings rang mtshan dpe lha mo'i skur mtha' yi skyon rnams dag mdzad ma //
NK025(ra)001:7739: gan+d+he ma la phyag de nas lha snam la thub pa bskyed pa de gsal btab pa la /
NK025(ra)001:7740: gsum gyi dang po 'phro 'du byas te /
NK025(ra)001:7742: gzhal yas snam bu'i shar lho na //
NK025(ra)001:7743: rnam dag pad+ma'i gdan steng du //
NK025(ra)001:7744: thub chen brgya byin pi wang bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:7745: sku mdog dkar po lha rnams 'dren //
NK025(ra)001:7746: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK025(ra)001:7750: nyon mongs dregs pa ma skyes sems //
NK025(ra)001:7751: lha yi thub pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK025(ra)001:7752: ting 'dzin thub par dbang bskur nas //
NK025(ra)001:7753: gdul bya ma lus 'dren byed shog /
NK025(ra)001:7758: mnyam nyid thugs kyi ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK025(ra)001:7759: nga rgyal 'joms phyir lha yi thub par sprul //
NK025(ra)001:7760: thugs rjes ltung ba'i sdug bsngal zhi mdzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:7761: bcom ldan lha yi thub la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:7762: byang du lha min thub pa bskyed pa gsal btab pa la /
NK025(ra)001:7763: gsum gyi dang po 'phro 'du byas te /
NK025(ra)001:7765: gzhal yas snam bu'i byang rnam dag pad+ma'i gdan thub pa thag bzang go cha 'dzin //
NK025(ra)001:7766: sku mdog mthing ga lha min 'dren //
NK025(ra)001:7767: thugs rje chen po'i 'thab rtsod sdug bsngal gnyis pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7768: nyon mongs khong khro ma lha min thub pa'i rang
NK025(ra)001:7769: ting 'dzin thub par gdul bya ma lus mu ne
NK025(ra)001:7774: mnyam nyid thugs kyi ngang las ma phrag dog 'dul
NK025(ra)001:7775: phyir lha min thub thugs rjes khong khro'i sdug bsngal
NK025(ra)001:7776: bcom ldan lha min thub la phyag lhor mi'i thub
NK025(ra)001:7777: pa bskyed pa gsal btab la /
NK025(ra)001:7778: gsum gyi dang po 'phro 'du byas te /
NK025(ra)001:7780: gzhal yas snam bu'i lho rnam dag pad+ma'i gdan //
NK025(ra)001:7781: thub pa bcom ldan sh+aakya thub //
NK025(ra)001:7782: bseg shang par bu'i tshul 'dzin cing //
NK025(ra)001:7783: sku mdog ser po mi rnams 'dren //
NK025(ra)001:7784: thugs rje 'gyur ba'i gnyis pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7785: nyon mongs 'dod chags ma mi yi thub pa'i rang
NK025(ra)001:7786: ting 'dzin thub par gdul bya ma lus mu ne
NK025(ra)001:7787: srum s+w+aa h+aa / zhes bzlas so //
NK025(ra)001:7790: mnyam nyid thugs kyi ngang las 'dod chags 'joms phyir
NK025(ra)001:7791: mi yi thub thugs rjes 'chi 'pho'i sdug bsngal bcom
NK025(ra)001:7792: ldan mi yi thub la nub byang du byol song
NK025(ra)001:7793: gi thub pa bskyed pa gsal btab la /
NK025(ra)001:7794: gsum gyi dang po 'phro 'du byas te /
NK025(ra)001:7796: gzhal yas snam bu'i nub byang na //
NK025(ra)001:7797: rnam dag pad+ma'i gdan thub pa dam ldan po ti 'dzin //
NK025(ra)001:7798: sku mdog ser nag byol song 'dren //
NK025(ra)001:7799: thugs rje bkol spyod gnyis pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7800: nyon mongs gti mug ma byol song thub pa'i rang
NK025(ra)001:7801: ting 'dzin thub par gdug bya ma lus mu ne
NK025(ra)001:7802: bram s+w+aa h+aa / zhes bzlas so //
NK025(ra)001:7805: mnyam nyid thugs rje'i ngang las gti mug 'joms mdzad
NK025(ra)001:7806: byol song thub thugs rjes glen lkugs sdug bsngal bcom
NK025(ra)001:7807: ldan byol song thub la lho nub tu yi dwags
NK025(ra)001:7808: kyi thub pa bskyed pa gsal btab la /
NK025(ra)001:7809: gsum gyi dang po 'phro 'du byas te /
NK025(ra)001:7811: gzhal yas snam bu'i lho nub nas //
NK025(ra)001:7812: rnam dag pad+ma'i gdan thub pa kha 'bar sgrom bu 'dzin //
NK025(ra)001:7813: sku mdog dmar nag yi dwags 'dren //
NK025(ra)001:7814: thugs rjes bkres skom gnyis pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7815: nyon mongs ser sna ma yi dwags thub pa'i ting
NK025(ra)001:7816: 'dzin thub par gdul bya ma lus mu ne k+sham
NK025(ra)001:7820: mnyam nyid thugs kyi ngang las ma ser sna 'joms
NK025(ra)001:7821: phyir yi dwags thub thugs rjes bkres skom sdug bsngal
NK025(ra)001:7822: bcom ldan yi dwags thub la byang shar du dmyal
NK025(ra)001:7823: ba'i thub pa bskyed pa gsal btab la /
NK025(ra)001:7824: gsum gyi dang po 'phro 'du byas te /
NK025(ra)001:7826: gzhal yas snam bu'i byang shar nas //
NK025(ra)001:7827: rnam dag pad+ma'i gdan thub pa gshin rje chos kyi rgyal //
NK025(ra)001:7828: sku mdog dud kha dmyal ba 'dren //
NK025(ra)001:7829: thugs rje tsha grang gnyis pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7831: nyon mongs zhe sdang ma dmyal ba'i thub pa'i rang
NK025(ra)001:7832: ting 'dzin thub par gdul bya ma lus mu ne
NK025(ra)001:7833: ye s+w+aa h+aa / zhes bzlas so //
NK025(ra)001:7836: mnyam nyid thugs kyi ngang las ma zhe sdang 'joms
NK025(ra)001:7837: phyir dmyal ba'i thub thugs rje tsha grang sdug bsngal
NK025(ra)001:7838: bcom ldan dmyal ba'i thub la de nas shar sgor
NK025(ra)001:7839: gshin rje gshed yab yum bskyed pa gsal btab la
NK025(ra)001:7840: / gsum gyi dang po 'phro 'du byas te /
NK025(ra)001:7841: gzhal yas khang gi shar sgo ru //
NK025(ra)001:7842: rdo rje brag gi khri steng du //
NK025(ra)001:7843: nyi ma gsal ba'i gdan steng na //
NK025(ra)001:7844: 'joms pa'i khro rgyal gshin rje gshed //
NK025(ra)001:7845: 'gugs pa'i lha mo lcags kyu gnyis //
NK025(ra)001:7846: gnyis med rol pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK025(ra)001:7847: dri za'i gdon rnams 'dul du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:7849: reg shes rtag par ma skyes sems //
NK025(ra)001:7850: gshed po yab yum rang bzhin las //
NK025(ra)001:7852: gdul bya ma lus mthar byed shog /
NK025(ra)001:7854: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:7858: me long lta bu'i ye shes byin rlabs las //
NK025(ra)001:7859: dri za 'dul ba'i khro bo'i skur ston cing //
NK025(ra)001:7860: thabs kyis lha yi bdud rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:7861: khro rgyal gshin rje gshed la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:7863: gnyis med chos kyi dbyings kyi byin rlabs las //
NK025(ra)001:7864: 'gro ba 'dul phyir khro mo'i skur ston cing //
NK025(ra)001:7865: thabs kyis 'khor ba'i gnas nas 'dren mdzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:7866: rdo rje lcags kyu ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:7867: lho sgor stobs po che yab yum bskyed pa gsal btab la /
NK025(ra)001:7868: gsum gyi dang po 'phro 'du byas te /
NK025(ra)001:7870: gzhal yas khang gi lho rdo rje brag gi khri
NK025(ra)001:7871: nyi ma gsal ba'i gdan 'joms pa'i khro rgyal stobs
NK025(ra)001:7872: po che // 'ching ba'i lha mo zhags pa gnyis //
NK025(ra)001:7873: gnyis med rol pa'i byin gshin rje'i gdon rnams 'dul gnyis pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7875: reg bya chad pa ma stobs chen yab yum rang
NK025(ra)001:7876: ting 'dzin 'joms par dbang gdul bya ma lus mthar
NK025(ra)001:7877: h'u pradz+ny+aan+ta kri ta h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:7878: ma h+aa rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la ni h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:7881: h+aum mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes byin gshin rje 'dul ba'i khro bo'i skur /
NK025(ra)001:7882: thabs kyis 'chi bdag bdud rnams 'joms khro rgyal stobs po che la phyag h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:7883: gnyis med chos kyi dbyings kyi byin 'gro ba 'dul phyir zhags pa ma ru sprul //
NK025(ra)001:7884: thabs kyis bla med gnas su 'dren rdo rje zhags
NK025(ra)001:7885: pa ma la phyag nub sgor rta mgrin yab yum
NK025(ra)001:7887: gsum gyi dang po 'phro 'du byas te /
NK025(ra)001:7889: gzhal yas khang gi nub rdo rje brag gi khri
NK025(ra)001:7890: nyi ma gsal ba'i gdan 'joms pa'i khro rgyal rta
NK025(ra)001:7891: mgrin dang // sdom byed lha mo lcags sgrog gnyis //
NK025(ra)001:7892: gnyis med rol pa'i byin klu yi gdon rnams 'dul gnyis pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7894: reg dbang bdag 'dzin ma rta mgrin yab yum rang
NK025(ra)001:7895: ting 'dzin 'joms par dbang gdul bya ma lus mthar
NK025(ra)001:7897: ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata //
NK025(ra)001:7901: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes byin klu chen 'dul
NK025(ra)001:7902: phyir khro bo'i skur thabs kyis phung po'i bdud rnams
NK025(ra)001:7903: 'joms khro rgyal rta mchog dpal la phyag h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:7904: gnyis med chos kyi dbyings kyi byin 'gro ba'i 'dul phyir lcags sgrog ma ru sprul //
NK025(ra)001:7905: thabs kyis nyon mongs gnas nas 'dren nyi zla lcags
NK025(ra)001:7906: sgrog ma la phyag byang sgor bdud rtsi 'khyil ba
NK025(ra)001:7907: yab yum bskyed pa gsal btab la /
NK025(ra)001:7908: gsum gyi dang po 'phro 'du byas la /
NK025(ra)001:7910: gzhal yas khang gi byang rdo rje brag gi khri
NK025(ra)001:7911: nyi ma gsal ba'i gdan 'joms pa'i khro rgyal bdud
NK025(ra)001:7912: rtsi 'khyil 'bebs pa'i lha mo dril bu ma //
NK025(ra)001:7913: gnyis med rol pa'i byin gnod sbyin gdon rnams 'dul gnyis pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7915: reg 'dul mtshan 'dzin ma 'khyil ba yab yum rang
NK025(ra)001:7916: ting 'dzin 'joms par dbang gdul bya ma lus mthar
NK025(ra)001:7918: ma h+aa karma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:7922: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes byin gnod sbyin 'dul
NK025(ra)001:7923: phyir khro bo'i skur thabs kyi nyon mongs bdud rnams
NK025(ra)001:7924: 'joms khro rgyal bdud rtsi 'khyil la phyag h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:7925: gnyis med chos kyi dbyings kyi byin 'gro ba 'dul phyir thos byed ma ru sprul //
NK025(ra)001:7926: thabs kyis 'gro ba ma lus 'dren mdzad ma //
NK025(ra)001:7927: rdo rje dril bu ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:7928: de nas zhi ba rin chen d+r+wa ba las gsungs pa'i 'dzab bskul 'di yang sbyar te /
NK025(ra)001:7929: yang dag don gyi snying po ni //
NK025(ra)001:7930: ji snyed brjod pa'i kha brgyud kyang //
NK025(ra)001:7931: gang nas btsal kyang mi rnyed de //
NK025(ra)001:7932: rang rig sgrib med dag pa yin //
NK025(ra)001:7933: de la rtag tu goms pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:7934: bsnyen po'i dam pa mchog yin no //
NK025(ra)001:7935: sems nyid theg par rab nges na //
NK025(ra)001:7937: d+r+wa ba'i dkyil 'khor mngon rdzogs pa //
NK025(ra)001:7938: da lta nyid du mngon gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:7940: bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha dz+ny+aa na d+h+aa tu a /
NK025(ra)001:7941: zhes ci nus su bzlas so //
NK025(ra)001:7944: ye nas mnyam nyid kyis bshags /
NK025(ra)001:7945: zhes gsungs pa'i phyogs bcu dus bzhi ni rtsa rgyud
NK025(ra)001:7946: kyi le'u bcu bzhi pa las gsungs pa gong du
NK025(ra)001:7947: glu ye shes kyi mchod pa'i skabs su bshad pa
NK025(ra)001:7948: ltar // phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:7950: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le che ho'i bar ro //
NK025(ra)001:7952: ye nas mnyam nyid chos skur dag pa la //
NK025(ra)001:7953: ma rig dbang gis sgro dang skur btab ste //
NK025(ra)001:7954: bde dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs ngo bor smin //
NK025(ra)001:7955: de zlog don du rgyal ba'i dam nos te //
NK025(ra)001:7956: bdag cag ma rig las dang ngag sems kyis //
NK025(ra)001:7957: bag med tshul gyis dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK025(ra)001:7958: rgyal ba 'khor bcas thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK025(ra)001:7959: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK025(ra)001:7960: rig pa'i me tog dor zhing dngos grub bskul pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:7961: dkyil 'khor du rdo rje'i phyag rgyas me tog 'thor zhing /
NK025(ra)001:7963: +aahbadz+ra sa ma ya +aah h+aum badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:7964: s+w+aa badz+ra sa ma ya s+w+aa /
NK025(ra)001:7965: h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya h+aa //
NK025(ra)001:7966: ye shes rgyal po sku gsung thugs //
NK025(ra)001:7967: yon tan phrin las rmad po che //
NK025(ra)001:7968: de nyid du ni mnyam sbyor bas //
NK025(ra)001:7969: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK025(ra)001:7972: badz+ra sa ma ya hoh dzahh+aum bam hohs dngos grub bskul /
NK025(ra)001:7974: de nas tshogs 'bul zhing rol lo //
NK025(ra)001:7975: zhes gsungs pas tshogs kyi yo byad bshams te /
NK025(ra)001:7976: tshogs sgyu 'phrul ltar bya ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:7977: ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai sarba dra byam sho d+ha ya h+aum phata kyis bsang /
NK025(ra)001:7978: ram yam kham gis bsreg gtor bkrus sbyang nas /
NK025(ra)001:7980: zhal zas kyi snod nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la dbus
NK025(ra)001:7981: dang phyogs bzhir h+aum tram +aahkham 'od du zhu ba
NK025(ra)001:7982: las byung ba'i bza' btung gi dngos po ye shes
NK025(ra)001:7983: lnga'i rang bzhin gyi bdud rtsi ro brgya dang 'dod
NK025(ra)001:7984: yon gyi rnam pa ma tshang ba med pas so
NK025(ra)001:7985: so'i lha mo'i rol pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa
NK025(ra)001:7986: dang bcas pa'i sprin 'phro bar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:7987: +aahh+aum lan gsum gyis byin gyis brlabs te /
NK025(ra)001:7989: bsod nams ye shes tshogs rdzoogs shing //
NK025(ra)001:7990: rang rig mtha' dbus med pa'i dkyil //
NK025(ra)001:7992: tshogs mchod dkyil 'khor gshegs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:7993: bcom ldan rdo rje sems dpa' nyid //
NK025(ra)001:7994: rigs bzhi'i lha dang lha mo dang //
NK025(ra)001:7995: kun bzang sprul pa'i tshogs rnams dang //
NK025(ra)001:7996: sgo ba la sogs gshegs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:7997: e h+ye hi b+ha ga wan ma h+aa k+aa ru
NK025(ra)001:7998: ni ka d+r+ai sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh sa
NK025(ra)001:7999: ma ya s+t+wam gyis snyan bsnan te /
NK025(ra)001:8001: dmigs med mkha' ltar dag pas khyab pa'i sku //
NK025(ra)001:8002: spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol bar mi dmigs kyang //
NK025(ra)001:8003: thugs rje'i ngang nyid chos skur dag pa las //
NK025(ra)001:8004: ye shes sgyu mar rol zhing gshegs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:8006: badz+ra am gu sha dzah badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8008: badz+ra g+han+de hoh thugs rje'i lcags kyus thugs dam rgyud bskul zhing //
NK025(ra)001:8009: byams pa'i zhags pas gnas nas spyan yang 'dren //
NK025(ra)001:8010: lcags sgrog bka' yi pho nyas gnas bskyod de //
NK025(ra)001:8011: bde gshegs bzhugs shing rnam grol dgyes pa bskyed //
NK025(ra)001:8012: ces bstim la lha mo bcu gnyis kyis mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:8013: pad skor sngon du 'gro bas so so'i phyag rgya dbyangs dang bcas te /
NK025(ra)001:8014: gsang ba'i mchod pa dam pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:8015: dga' ba bzhi dang mnyam par sbyor //
NK025(ra)001:8016: a la la ste mchod par 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:8017: a la la ste dgyes par mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:8020: sh+r+ai badz+ra g+ai ti h+r+aih sh+r+ai badz+ra n+air+t+ya +aah dung mdog sgeg mo rdo rje can //
NK025(ra)001:8021: sems dpa' sngon po'i ye shes 'bebs //
NK025(ra)001:8022: me long lta bu'i ye shes la //
NK025(ra)001:8023: badz+ra l+aa s+ya'i mchod par rol //
NK025(ra)001:8026: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye badz+ra m+aa le'i mchod pad+ma dbyangs mkhan rma bya'i mgrin //
NK025(ra)001:8027: spyan ras gzigs kyi dngos grub 'dzin //
NK025(ra)001:8028: so sor rtog pa'i ye badz+ra g+ai ti'i mchod gar mkhan 'gying ma gzi ldan ma //
NK025(ra)001:8030: bya ba nan tan ye badz+ra n+ai r+t+ya'i mchod nang
NK025(ra)001:8031: gi mchod pa dam ye shes bzhi dang mnyam a
NK025(ra)001:8032: la la ste mchod a la la ste dgyes sh+r+ai
NK025(ra)001:8035: sh+r+ai badz+ra a lo ke h+r+aih sh+r+ai badz+ra gan+d+he gan /
NK025(ra)001:8036: spos kyi sprin lding bdug pa mo //
NK025(ra)001:8038: byams pa thabs dang shes rab la //
NK025(ra)001:8039: badz+ra d+h+au pe'i mchod pa ut+pala mthing kha me tog 'thor //
NK025(ra)001:8041: snying rje thabs dang shes badz+ra push+pe'i mchod dbang gi phyag na sgron me bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:8043: dga' ba thabs dang shes badz+r+aa lo ke'i mchod tsan+dana bdud rtsi'i char 'bebs ma //
NK025(ra)001:8045: btang snyoms thabs dang shes badz+ra gan+d+he'i mchod phyi yi mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK025(ra)001:8046: tshad med bzhi dang mnyam par sbyor //
NK025(ra)001:8047: a la la ste mchod a la la ste dgyes tshogs spros la dbul te /
NK025(ra)001:8048: thabs dang shes rab ldan gyur cing //
NK025(ra)001:8049: byang chub sems dang ma chags pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:8050: gnyis su med par thim gyur nas //
NK025(ra)001:8051: tshogs chen gnyis kyang rdzogs par 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:8052: 'dod yon lnga po thams cad dang //
NK025(ra)001:8053: sna tshogs snang ba thams cad kun //
NK025(ra)001:8054: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dkyil 'khor dang //
NK025(ra)001:8055: gzugs mdzes lha dang lha mor brtag /
NK025(ra)001:8056: sna tshogs gzugs ni thams cad kun //
NK025(ra)001:8057: snang stong ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi //
NK025(ra)001:8058: chos dbyings dag pa'i ye shes te //
NK025(ra)001:8059: rdo rje lha mo gzugs mdzes ma //
NK025(ra)001:8060: 'dod yon phyag na bsnams pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:8061: rkang pas stabs byed lag gar bsgyur //
NK025(ra)001:8062: snyan pa'i glu dbyangs blangs nas ni //
NK025(ra)001:8064: a la la ste mchod a la la ste dgyes thams cad ma lus sgra rnams ni //
NK025(ra)001:8065: sgra stong ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi //
NK025(ra)001:8066: me long lta bu'i ye shes te //
NK025(ra)001:8067: rdo rje lha mo 'jam pa'i sgra //
NK025(ra)001:8068: 'dod yon phyag na rkang pas stabs byed snyan pa'i
NK025(ra)001:8069: glu dbyangs dkyil 'khor lha la a la la ste
NK025(ra)001:8070: a la la ste bde ba'i tshim byed bsod nams
NK025(ra)001:8071: te // tshim stong ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi //
NK025(ra)001:8072: brjod med mi gnas ye shes te //
NK025(ra)001:8073: rdo rje chags med pad+ma'i gsung //
NK025(ra)001:8074: 'dod yon phyag na rkang pas stabs byed snyan pa'i
NK025(ra)001:8075: glu dbyangs dkyil 'khor lha la a la la ste
NK025(ra)001:8076: a la la ste bde gshegs dkyil 'khor ma lus
NK025(ra)001:8077: la // bde ba ro yis tshim byed pa //
NK025(ra)001:8078: ro stong ngo bo nyid kyi gzhi //
NK025(ra)001:8079: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes te //
NK025(ra)001:8080: thams cad tshim byed ro yi lha //
NK025(ra)001:8081: 'dod yon phyag na rkang pas stabs byed snyan pa'i
NK025(ra)001:8082: glu dbyangs dkyil 'khor lha la a la la ste
NK025(ra)001:8083: a la la ste rdo rje reg bya myong byed
NK025(ra)001:8084: ma // dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun grub ni //
NK025(ra)001:8085: bde mchog dkyil 'khor yangs phyed ma //
NK025(ra)001:8086: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes te //
NK025(ra)001:8087: rdo rje reg bya'i lha mo ni //
NK025(ra)001:8088: 'dod yon phyag na rkang pas stabs byed snyan pa'i
NK025(ra)001:8089: glu dbyangs dkyil 'khor lha la a la la ste
NK025(ra)001:8090: a la la ste hoh bde bar gshegs pa'i dkyil
NK025(ra)001:8091: 'khor gyi lha rnams la tshogs kyi mchod pa phul
NK025(ra)001:8092: bas / bzhes shing rol nas mnyes te bdag cag gi dam tshig nyams pa thams cad skongs nas /
NK025(ra)001:8093: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob par mdzad du gsol /
NK025(ra)001:8094: rkang pa stabs byas lag pas gar bsgyur te phul na zhi bar 'gyur ro //
NK025(ra)001:8095: mkha' 'gro ma gsang ba'i rgyud na 'byung ngo //
NK025(ra)001:8096: tshogs kyi kha tshar rdzogs so //
NK025(ra)001:8097: sgyu 'phrul zhi ba'i las byang rnams su tshogs spros te 'bul ba tsam las /
NK025(ra)001:8098: thog mtha' bar gsum gyi tha snyad khro bo'i skabs su ma gtogs mi 'byung yang /
NK025(ra)001:8099: 'dir chog khrigs yig rnying gzhan nas kha bkang ba'i
NK025(ra)001:8100: tshogs thog mtha' bar gsum gyi sgo nas stob pa'i
NK025(ra)001:8101: tshul 'di ltar / dang po dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:8103: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam pa 'di //
NK025(ra)001:8104: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK025(ra)001:8105: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan te //
NK025(ra)001:8106: thugs dam bzhin las ci bder bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:8107: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya chos //
NK025(ra)001:8108: 'dod yon lha mos nam mkha' gang //
NK025(ra)001:8110: spyan sogs bde bas tshim gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:8112: u pa b+h+yoh k+aa ma ha h+ai pra t+aits+tsha hoh bar pa bshags pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:8114: dang po byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed nas //
NK025(ra)001:8115: rtsa ba yan lag bcas pa'i dam tshig la //
NK025(ra)001:8116: sems can dbang gi nor 'khrul ci mchis pa //
NK025(ra)001:8117: mi 'chab nongs pa'i sems kyis mthol lo bshags //
NK025(ra)001:8118: badz+ra sa t+wa sogs yi ge brgya pa brjod /
NK025(ra)001:8120: las dkyil lam thod pa mtshan ngan du ling+ga bcas la /
NK025(ra)001:8121: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:8122: bdag nyid kun bzang yab yum gdug pa can bsgral ba'i phyir badz+ra he ru kar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:8124: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:8125: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:8126: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i bka' bden pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:8127: chos can rgyu 'bras bslu ba med pa'i bka' bden pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:8128: zhi khro sgyu 'phrul rnam par rol pa'i lha tshogs rnams kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:8129: sprul pa yang sprul bka' nyan dang bcas pa rnams kyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:8130: rig sngags 'chang rnams kyi lhag pa'i bsam pa rnam par dag pa'i bden pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:8131: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK025(ra)001:8132: ma rungs pa'i sems can bsgral ba'i zhing bcur gtogs
NK025(ra)001:8133: pa thams cad mtshan ma rdzas kyi rten 'di la
NK025(ra)001:8134: skad cig tsam gyi mtshis par gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:8135: n+ri yam dzah n+ri badz+ra am ku dzah tri yam
NK025(ra)001:8136: dzah tri badz+ra am ku sha dzah zhes lcags kyu'i
NK025(ra)001:8138: dzahh+aum bam hohs bkug bstim myos par byas te gdug
NK025(ra)001:8139: pa'i snying gar dwangs ma ye shes kyi +aahdakara po
NK025(ra)001:8140: dang bcas pa / bdag dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs kyi thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:8142: gzas po'i snying ga'i sgo phye +aahdakara po la phog /
NK025(ra)001:8144: dug lnga ye shes su gnas 'gyur /
NK025(ra)001:8145: dwangs ma lnga sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba'i 'khor lor spar te sangs rgyas par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:8146: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka m+aa ra badz+ra sarba dush+tam sa ma ya mu tha /
NK025(ra)001:8147: ma tram kha kha kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:8148: hri da ya pi sa h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:8149: snyigs ma rang snang sgyu 'phrul gyi 'khor lo khro
NK025(ra)001:8150: tshogs su 'bar bas rdo rje bza' ba'i dam tshig
NK025(ra)001:8153: nga ni za byed chen po ste //
NK025(ra)001:8154: khams gsum ma lus bsgral ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:8155: gdul dka' ma lus 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:8156: sha rus la sogs bza' bar bya //
NK025(ra)001:8158: sarba dush+tam m+aa ra ya h+aum phata kyis ling+ga'i gnas lngar phur bu btab pas bsad /
NK025(ra)001:8159: yan lag thams cad dum bur gtub /
NK025(ra)001:8160: khog pa dral te stob cing /
NK025(ra)001:8161: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai badz+ra he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya /
NK025(ra)001:8166: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha kha kha le
NK025(ra)001:8167: le le h+aum b+h+yoh h+aum b+h+yoh h+aum b+h+yoh zhes brjod
NK025(ra)001:8169: sgeg pa dpa' ba 'jigs su rung ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:8170: rgod dang gshed dang 'jigs par ston pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:8171: snying rje rngams dang zhi ba la sogs pa //
NK025(ra)001:8172: sku yi dngos po shin tu bsgyur ba yin //
NK025(ra)001:8173: gar yang sgrub po rnal 'byor las //
NK025(ra)001:8174: gar gyi dbang phyug gtso bo che //
NK025(ra)001:8175: zla ba la sogs snying po can //
NK025(ra)001:8176: m+aam sa la sogs ro mchog bsil //
NK025(ra)001:8177: me tog la sogs tsan+d+rana dri //
NK025(ra)001:8178: bzang rgu 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:8179: mi mo rnams kyi reg bya'i mchog /
NK025(ra)001:8180: byin gyis rlobs shig rnal 'byor la //
NK025(ra)001:8181: sgrub pa'i rdzas 'di thams cad la //
NK025(ra)001:8182: h+aum dang phata kyis ldan par mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:8183: ces pas bsgral mtha' sbyor ba'i dam tshig chen por bsgrub pas lha thams cad tshim par byas la /
NK025(ra)001:8184: slar yang badz+ra he ru ka zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK025(ra)001:8185: gyi gtso bo kun bzang yab yum zhal gsum phyag
NK025(ra)001:8186: drug pa yum dang bcas par gnas su gyur par
NK025(ra)001:8187: bsam ste / bdud rtsi gsang nan 'bul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:8189: rnam dag sgrib spangs srid gsum skyon bral zhing //
NK025(ra)001:8190: ston ka'i zla gsal dri med zhal mnga' ba //
NK025(ra)001:8191: bcom ldan bde gshegs rdo rje dbyings dkyil 'khor //
NK025(ra)001:8192: dus gsum bde gshegs thams cad bskyed pa'i yab //
NK025(ra)001:8193: shes rab lha mo rigs kyi yum rnams dang //
NK025(ra)001:8194: phyag brnyan khro gtum rngams pa'i tshogs la sogs //
NK025(ra)001:8195: bsod nams ye shes tshogs kyi zhing rab rdzogs //
NK025(ra)001:8196: dgyes par rol cig mchod pa dam 'di //
NK025(ra)001:8197: bzhi te a la la yis dgyes par mdzad //
NK025(ra)001:8201: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8203: zhes pas 'khor gsum bde ba chen por ro mnyam mo //
NK025(ra)001:8204: bzhi pa gtsang lhag gi phyir du bzhag go //
NK025(ra)001:8207: bla ma la phyag sngon du 'gro bas /
NK025(ra)001:8208: dza gad dang m+aam sa bsnol mar stob cing /
NK025(ra)001:8209: mnyam nyid mi g.yo mnyam pa'i sangs rgyas dpal //
NK025(ra)001:8210: log rtog mtshan ma'i spros pa ngang gis zhi //
NK025(ra)001:8211: dam tshig bzhin las ci bder spyad nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:8212: mnyam rdzogs chen po'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:8214: bla mas pad skor bcas te /
NK025(ra)001:8215: a la la hoh zhes blangs shing nang dang gsang ba'i sbyin sreg gi tshul du rol lo //
NK025(ra)001:8216: mthar smon lam 'di skad gdab ste /
NK025(ra)001:8217: hoh bdag cag rdo rje'i slob dpon mched dang lcam
NK025(ra)001:8218: dral rnams kyis dza gad dpa' bo gsol bas 'gro
NK025(ra)001:8219: bas ma lus pa dbang du 'dus par gyur cig
NK025(ra)001:8220: / ma h+aa m+aam sa gsol pas rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen por gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:8221: rdo rje'i tshe gsol bas rdo rje sems dpa'i tshe dang lang tsho la mnga' brnyes par gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:8222: zhal zas kyi bye brag mang po gsol bas zhi
NK025(ra)001:8223: khro'i phrin las kyi rdzu 'phrul sna tshogs la dbang
NK025(ra)001:8226: lhag ma rnams gsog 'jog mi bya bar bsdus pa gong gi phud lhag dang bsres te bsag go //
NK025(ra)001:8227: des zhi ba'i 'dzab khang dbye ba grub bo //
NK025(ra)001:8228: skabs 'dir sgyu 'phrul khro bo'i bdag bskyed blangs te
NK025(ra)001:8229: skabs der mdun bskyed kyi 'dzab khang dbye ba sogs
NK025(ra)001:8231: bdag bskyed kyi zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor rten dang brten
NK025(ra)001:8232: par bcas pa gtso bo yab kyi bar du thim
NK025(ra)001:8233: / de thugs ka'i ye shes sems dpa' la /
NK025(ra)001:8235: h+aum yang n+aa da'i bar du bsdus te /
NK025(ra)001:8236: rang bzhin spros med ka dag gi dbyings su mi dmigs par yun ring du mnyam par bzhag go //
NK025(ra)001:8237: ting nge 'dzin de las langs te khro bo rol
NK025(ra)001:8238: pa'i dkyil 'khor du mngon par 'du bya ba ni
NK025(ra)001:8239: / khro bo dam pa rgyan las byung ba bzhin 'di ltar /
NK025(ra)001:8240: sngon 'gro rnams zhi ba'i skabs su grub pas 'dir ma dgos shing /
NK025(ra)001:8241: 'dir yang go nga bzhin tshigs bcad rnams khro bo
NK025(ra)001:8242: dam pa rgyan gyi gzhung dang lhug pa rnams kho
NK025(ra)001:8243: bo'i ngag tu shes dgos so //
NK025(ra)001:8244: dngos gzhi ting nge 'dzin gyi 'go 'dren pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:8246: 'dzin pa'i dbang gi sdug bsngal zhing //
NK025(ra)001:8247: gdug pa srid gsum 'du ba yi //
NK025(ra)001:8248: nga rgyal chen po brtan pa'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:8250: gong gi mnyam gzhag de nyid de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin du bltas te /
NK025(ra)001:8251: e ma ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK025(ra)001:8252: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK025(ra)001:8253: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK025(ra)001:8254: skyes tsam nyid na skye ba med //
NK025(ra)001:8256: e ma kun tu bzang po ni //
NK025(ra)001:8257: bde chen spros med thig le las //
NK025(ra)001:8258: stong pa'i nyid du rab gsal ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:8259: snying rje'i yul ni bsgom par bya //
NK025(ra)001:8261: mkha' mnyam dbyings nyid dag pa'i rang bzhin la //
NK025(ra)001:8262: bde gshegs thugs kyi snying po'i yi ge ni //
NK025(ra)001:8263: rang gi sems nyid yi ge h+aum du snang //
NK025(ra)001:8264: thams cad 'byung gnas ye shes chen po'i rgyu //
NK025(ra)001:8274: ra rak+ta dz+wa la sa mu dra h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8275: kem ni ri ti dz+wa la man+da la h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8279: dkyil 'khor gzhal yas rten gyur pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:8280: rgya gram dbang chen gtams pa la //
NK025(ra)001:8281: rlung nag rdo rje'i dkyil 'khor che //
NK025(ra)001:8282: thams cad 'degs pa'i stobs dang ldan //
NK025(ra)001:8283: dur khrod chen po rab 'jigs pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:8284: khrag gi rgya mtsho 'khrug pa'i dkyil //
NK025(ra)001:8285: keng rus chen po'i ri rab kyi //
NK025(ra)001:8286: steng gi 'bar ba'i klong dkyil na //
NK025(ra)001:8289: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na b+han+d+ha tsakra s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra pad+ma man+da la /
NK025(ra)001:8293: rten gzhal yas khang gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:8294: ye shes 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK025(ra)001:8295: phyogs bcur rgya yongs ma chad pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:8296: phyi dang nang med kun tu nang //
NK025(ra)001:8298: gru chad bzhi yis rnam par brgyan //
NK025(ra)001:8299: gru bzhi sgo khyud bzhi yis brgyan //
NK025(ra)001:8300: 'bar ba'i bar khyams gnyis kyis mdzes //
NK025(ra)001:8301: thod sbrul sna tshogs nyi zlas brjid //
NK025(ra)001:8303: khyu mchog ma he gzig dang stag /
NK025(ra)001:8304: gtum pa dom gyi spar bas ni //
NK025(ra)001:8305: dbang phyug lha chen la sogs bzung //
NK025(ra)001:8306: rgyu sngags kyi lha bskyed pa'i dang po gtso bo yab yum bskyed pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:8309: badz+ra kro d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8310: nges pa'i las ni rdo rje chen //
NK025(ra)001:8311: de las dpal chen he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:8312: 'bar ba chen po gar dgu yi //
NK025(ra)001:8313: 'jigs pa yi ni dus ltar drag /
NK025(ra)001:8314: badz+ra kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8315: bdag nyid sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK025(ra)001:8316: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje'i bdag /
NK025(ra)001:8317: khro rgyal ye nas yin pa'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:8318: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid nas //
NK025(ra)001:8319: khro mo dbang phyug mngon phyung ste //
NK025(ra)001:8320: hi hi dgyes pa'i gzi mdangs kyis //
NK025(ra)001:8321: rin chen pad+ma rgyas mdzad nas //
NK025(ra)001:8322: gnyis med 'khril bas dgyes par thim //
NK025(ra)001:8327: sa ma ya hoh a nu r+aa ga ya mi /
NK025(ra)001:8328: a nu r+aa ga ya ham /
NK025(ra)001:8329: dzahh+aum bam hoh snyoms par zhugs /
NK025(ra)001:8330: bo d+hi tsit+ta s+pha ra na phata /
NK025(ra)001:8331: byang chub sems sprin 'phros pa las //
NK025(ra)001:8332: stong gsum khro bo'i dkyil 'khor spro //
NK025(ra)001:8333: h+aum h+aum h+aum bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+da la h+aum phata phata phata /
NK025(ra)001:8335: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na //
NK025(ra)001:8336: mtha' yas khyab par khro bo yi //
NK025(ra)001:8338: phyogs bcu'i rdul snyed thon par gyur //
NK025(ra)001:8339: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8340: badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8341: de nas bcom ldan dgyes chen po //
NK025(ra)001:8342: dbu dang phyag zhabs stong khams kyi //
NK025(ra)001:8343: rdul snyed mtshon cha 'dzin pa ste //
NK025(ra)001:8344: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhir gyur //
NK025(ra)001:8346: dbang phyug che dang dur khrod kyi //
NK025(ra)001:8347: bdag po'i dregs pa khyo shug gi //
NK025(ra)001:8348: gdan la brkyang bskum tshul du bzhugs //
NK025(ra)001:8349: 'khor gyi khro bo bskyed pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:8350: bud+d+ha ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8351: bud+d+ha ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8352: rat+na ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8353: rat+na ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8354: pad+ma ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8355: pad+ma ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8356: karma ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8357: karma ma h+aa kro d+hishwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8358: dpal ni khrag 'thung chen po dang //
NK025(ra)001:8359: rin po che dang pad+ma dang //
NK025(ra)001:8360: las su gyur te phyogs bzhir bzhugs //
NK025(ra)001:8361: de kun 'jigs byed chen po yi //
NK025(ra)001:8362: cha lugs rngam pa'i nga ro yis //
NK025(ra)001:8363: 'bar ba'i klong na dbu gsum pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:8364: phyag drug zhabs bzhi dri za dang //
NK025(ra)001:8365: gnod sbyin gshin rje srin po sogs //
NK025(ra)001:8366: khyo shug dregs pa pho mo yi //
NK025(ra)001:8367: gdan la brkyang bskum tshul du bzhugs //
NK025(ra)001:8368: btsun mo khrag 'thung chen mo rnams //
NK025(ra)001:8370: sing ha brgyad bskyed pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:8371: ha ha ha ha ha ha ha ha /
NK025(ra)001:8372: de nas dgyes te ha brjod pas //
NK025(ra)001:8373: byang chub sems kyi sprin dag las //
NK025(ra)001:8374: dkar mo'i tshogs dang rkun mo dang //
NK025(ra)001:8375: rmongs byed dang ni thal byed ma //
NK025(ra)001:8376: sbos mo dang ni gtum mo dang //
NK025(ra)001:8377: rme sha can dang ma tshogs ma'i //
NK025(ra)001:8378: tshogs rnams rang gi lag cha dang //
NK025(ra)001:8379: ngo mtshar chas nas rngams thon te //
NK025(ra)001:8382: phra men brgyad bskyed pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:8383: he he he he he he he he /
NK025(ra)001:8384: de nas dgyes te he brjod pas //
NK025(ra)001:8385: byang chub sems kyi sprin dag las //
NK025(ra)001:8386: seng gdong chen mo'i tshogs dang ni //
NK025(ra)001:8387: stag dang wa dang khyi dang bzhad //
NK025(ra)001:8389: tshogs rnams rang gi lag cha dang //
NK025(ra)001:8390: ngo mtshar chas nas rngams thon te //
NK025(ra)001:8392: phyi rol shar gyi phyogs dag nas //
NK025(ra)001:8396: de nas dgyes te phata brjod pas //
NK025(ra)001:8397: byang chub sems kyi sprin dag las //
NK025(ra)001:8398: rdo rje sring 'gro ma tshogs dang //
NK025(ra)001:8399: gdong mo 'jig rten ro langs ma //
NK025(ra)001:8400: tshogs rnam rang gi lag cha dang //
NK025(ra)001:8401: ngo mtshar chas nas rngams thon te //
NK025(ra)001:8402: dkyil 'khor sgo bzhir rngam bzung nas //
NK025(ra)001:8403: dgyes pa'i phrin las phyogs bcu nas //
NK025(ra)001:8404: phata ces bsgrags pas thams cad khros //
NK025(ra)001:8406: / sngon gyi thugs dam chen po ni //
NK025(ra)001:8407: 'jig rten ma lus thams cad kun //
NK025(ra)001:8408: rgyal ba'i zhing du sbyor bas na //
NK025(ra)001:8409: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK025(ra)001:8410: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:8411: ye shes zer gyis lus rtog sbyangs //
NK025(ra)001:8412: gser zhun lta bu'i sems dag la //
NK025(ra)001:8413: gsung gi byin rlabs yid kyi 'bru //
NK025(ra)001:8414: thugs kar thim nas sku yi dbyibs //
NK025(ra)001:8415: rdo rje'i lam byung yum gyi mkha' //
NK025(ra)001:8416: chos kun byang chub sems su gnas //
NK025(ra)001:8417: lha rnams so so'i snying po ni //
NK025(ra)001:8418: h+aum ha he phata sgra byung bas //
NK025(ra)001:8419: byang chub sems su gcig par gnas //
NK025(ra)001:8420: h+aum h+aum badz+ra g+han+de s+pha ra na phata /
NK025(ra)001:8422: slar yang rkyen sngags kyi lha rnams gsal gdab pa /
NK025(ra)001:8423: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8424: badz+ra kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8428: sa ma ya hoh a nu r+aa ga ya mi /
NK025(ra)001:8429: a nu r+aa ga ya hamh bo d+hi tsit+ta s+pha ra na phata /
NK025(ra)001:8430: h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8431: ha ha ha ha ha ha ha ha /
NK025(ra)001:8432: he he he he he he he he /
NK025(ra)001:8434: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa sh+ai he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:8435: ma h+aa tsan+da sarba du sh+tan ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum h+aum h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:8436: badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa
NK025(ra)001:8437: la n+ai h+aum phata dzah +aahh+aum s+pha sam sarba ta
NK025(ra)001:8438: th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka ma
NK025(ra)001:8439: h+aa tsan+da sarba dush+tana ta ka ha na da ha
NK025(ra)001:8440: pa tsa h+aum h+aum h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:8441: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa
NK025(ra)001:8442: r+ai sarba dush+tana h+aum phata dzah s+pha sam rat+na ma
NK025(ra)001:8444: ma h+aa tsan+da sarba dush+tana ta ka ha na ha da ha pa tsa h+aum h+aum h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:8445: ma h+aa s+aur+ya rat+na ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai
NK025(ra)001:8446: bi da ma h+aum phata dzah s+pha sam pad+ma ma
NK025(ra)001:8448: ma h+aa tsan+da sarba dush+tana ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum h+aum h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:8449: h+r+aihshat+ta sa man+ta pad+ma ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai
NK025(ra)001:8450: kh+aa hi h+aum phata dzah s+pha sam karma ma h+aa
NK025(ra)001:8452: ma h+aa tsan+da sarba du sh+tan ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h+aum h+aum h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:8453: sarba a mo g+h+aa ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai
NK025(ra)001:8454: bi shwa h+aum phata dzah +aahh+aum s+pha sam badz+ra koo
NK025(ra)001:8455: r+ai ha / badz+ra tsoo r+ai ha /
NK025(ra)001:8461: badz+ra tsan+da l+ai ha phata dzah s+pha sam badz+ra sing+ha mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:8462: badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:8463: badz+ra srid+ga la mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:8464: badz+ra shwa na mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:8465: badz+ra gri d+ha mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:8467: badz+ra k+aa ka mu kha he /
NK025(ra)001:8468: badz+ra u lu ka mu kha he phata dzah s+pha
NK025(ra)001:8469: sam badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dzah badz+ra a
NK025(ra)001:8470: mu kh+aa h+aum / badz+ra lo ka bam /
NK025(ra)001:8471: badz+ra b+hasmi pa la ya ba to hohphata dzah +aahh+aum s+pha sam ma nu rak+sha s+ai b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:8473: roo tri ma b+h+yoh besh+na be b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:8484: e ka tsa ra ma b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:8488: ma h+aa m+aa ra na b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:8496: bum pa ka la ma b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:8498: lha rnams tshig gi mngon par rtog pa gsal gdab pa /
NK025(ra)001:8499: sa la sogs pas phyag rgyar byas //
NK025(ra)001:8500: rnam grol rim pa thob par 'gyur //
NK025(ra)001:8501: dag pa'i ye shes kyis sbyangs pas //
NK025(ra)001:8502: smos ci dgos te de nyid yin //
NK025(ra)001:8504: sngo nag smug nag ser nag dang //
NK025(ra)001:8505: dmar nag ljang nag 'jigs pa'i sku //
NK025(ra)001:8506: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhir bgrad //
NK025(ra)001:8507: ko rlon gos ni sna tshogs gyon //
NK025(ra)001:8508: rngam pa'i sgra chen 'jigs par sgrog /
NK025(ra)001:8509: sbrul dang thod phreng nyi zlar bcas //
NK025(ra)001:8510: stong gi 'jig rten khor yug bcas //
NK025(ra)001:8511: rdo rje dung chen gang ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:8512: ral gri dgra s+t+wa gshol la sogs //
NK025(ra)001:8513: rang gi lag cha sna tshogs bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:8515: gnas dang yul gyi phyag rgya dang //
NK025(ra)001:8516: sgo bzhi'i phyag rgya rab mdzes shing //
NK025(ra)001:8517: slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs //
NK025(ra)001:8518: bcu gnyis dang ni brgyad kyis mdzes //
NK025(ra)001:8519: rang gi stan dang lag cha dang //
NK025(ra)001:8520: ci bgyis zhes ni chas te gnas //
NK025(ra)001:8521: de ltar dkyil 'khor gsal bkod nas //
NK025(ra)001:8522: mtha' dbus med par khyab pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:8523: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na //
NK025(ra)001:8525: de ltar bdag bskyed kyi mngon rtogs tshar ma thag mdun bskyed bya ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:8527: de nas khro bo'i 'dzab khang dbye ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:8528: b+h+r+aum s+pha ra sam b+h+aum bi shu bi shud+d+he b+han+d+ha
NK025(ra)001:8529: dz+ny+aa na tsakra s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra pad+ma e man+dala de ba
NK025(ra)001:8530: ti ra nan / du ti tsikri nan /
NK025(ra)001:8531: ru tra kro d+hi ti ra ba bam /
NK025(ra)001:8532: a kra ma h+aa kro d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:8533: ka ta ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8534: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:8535: sarba ta th+aa ga ta kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8537: rak+sha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8539: bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8541: pad+ma kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8543: karma kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8545: rak+sha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8557: steng gi khro bo khro mo drug cu /
NK025(ra)001:8558: pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu /
NK025(ra)001:8560: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang rnams rim pas rtsa sngags kyis bskyed /
NK025(ra)001:8561: ces gsungs pa'i don mdun bskyed bsgrub pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:8562: khro bo tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor la dmigs te /
NK025(ra)001:8563: bdag gi thugs ka nas e /
NK025(ra)001:8568: ram rnams chad de dkyil 'khor gyi 'og gzhir brtsegs mar 'khod /
NK025(ra)001:8572: e las chos 'byung gru gsum pa mthing nag rgya khyon nam mkha' dang mnyam pa /
NK025(ra)001:8573: yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor sra zhing mkhregs pa
NK025(ra)001:8574: kha dog dud kha dbyibs rdo rje rgya gram gyi
NK025(ra)001:8576: ra las khrag gi rgya mtsho rba rlabs 'khrug pa dbyibs zlum po /
NK025(ra)001:8577: bam las sha chen gyi sa gzhi sra zhing 'thas pa gru bzhi pa /
NK025(ra)001:8578: kem las keng rus kyi ri rab bang rim bzhi pa /
NK025(ra)001:8579: ram las me'i dkyil 'khor nam mkha'i mtha' klas par 'khrug cing /
NK025(ra)001:8580: 'bar ba'i nang steng 'og phyogs mtshams thams cad rdo
NK025(ra)001:8581: rje'i sa gzhi ra ba d+r+wa ba gur bla bre
NK025(ra)001:8582: de dag las kyang ye shes kyi me rab tu
NK025(ra)001:8583: 'bar bar gyur / srung 'khor gyi nang du b+h+r+aum 'phros te 'khod /
NK025(ra)001:8586: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he b+han+d+ha dz+ny+aa na tsakra s+au
NK025(ra)001:8587: r+ya tsan+d+ra pad+ma e ka man+da la de wa ti
NK025(ra)001:8588: ra nan / du ti tsakra nan /
NK025(ra)001:8589: ru tra kro d+hi ti ra bam /
NK025(ra)001:8591: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams thams cad khyab /
NK025(ra)001:8592: de bzhin gshegs pas sras su dgongs /
NK025(ra)001:8593: byang chub sems dpas spun du dgongs /
NK025(ra)001:8594: ma mo dang mkha' 'gros rje bor dgongs /
NK025(ra)001:8595: gzhal yas khang gi che ba'i yon tan thams cad snang ba'i tshul gyis bsdus te b+h+r+aum la thim /
NK025(ra)001:8596: 'od du zhu ste gzhal yas khang sgom tshul gsar du bris pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:8597: ye shes 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang gru bzhi sgo bzhi pa /
NK025(ra)001:8598: phyi nang bcu gcig rim du yod pa /
NK025(ra)001:8599: lte ba zlum po 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad rtsibs mchan
NK025(ra)001:8600: dang bcas pa'i mtha' rdo rje'i ra bas bskor ba'i
NK025(ra)001:8601: phyir glo 'bur gyi gru chad bzhi dang ldan pa
NK025(ra)001:8605: nang mi mgo rlon pa ste sum rim la gnam lcags kyi gzer gyis bsdams pa /
NK025(ra)001:8606: thod pa de dag kyang dpral pa nas rdo rje'i thog 'phro ba /
NK025(ra)001:8610: sna nas rlung 'tshubs pa'i thod rtsig la zhing lpags kha sbyar gyi sgo dang /
NK025(ra)001:8614: zhing skam gyi sgo skyes can /
NK025(ra)001:8615: nang du zhi smug gi ka ba phyogs mtshams brgyad
NK025(ra)001:8616: du btsugs pa la gza' chen brgyad kyi gdung mig
NK025(ra)001:8618: rgyu skar nyer brgyad kyi phyam btang ba la sbrul
NK025(ra)001:8619: nag gi dra mas bkab pa'i steng bdud rtsi lngas
NK025(ra)001:8621: nang du zhing lpags kyi gdugs dang bla bre can /
NK025(ra)001:8622: thod pa'i pha gu phyir 'phyang ba la sbrug nag dang rgyu ma rlon pa /
NK025(ra)001:8623: glo snying nang khrol sogs kyi chun 'phyang /
NK025(ra)001:8624: d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pa 'phyang ba /
NK025(ra)001:8625: robs kyi mda' yab phyir 'phyar zhing /
NK025(ra)001:8626: thod pa'i pu shu gyen du bsgrigs pa'i rtse mor
NK025(ra)001:8627: zhing gi rgyal mtshan dang ba dan sna tshogs 'phyang
NK025(ra)001:8628: ba / nang dur khrod 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang
NK025(ra)001:8629: khrag zhag gi rgya mtsho 'khrug pa'i phyi rin po
NK025(ra)001:8630: che sna tshogs kyi rtsig pa dang pha gu la
NK025(ra)001:8631: rin po che dang me tog gi d+r+wa ba dang
NK025(ra)001:8633: rin po che'i mda' yab sngon po mthur du 'phyang zhing shar bu dkar po gyen du bsgrigs pa /
NK025(ra)001:8634: phyi rol du 'dod yon gyi snam bu dmar po dang /
NK025(ra)001:8635: nang nas rin po che'i gdung ma brgyad zla phyed
NK025(ra)001:8636: rdo rje'i gdung mgo can bsnol ba la rin po
NK025(ra)001:8637: che sna tshogs kyi dral phyam bkab cing /
NK025(ra)001:8638: nang du rin po che'i gdung zlum dang /
NK025(ra)001:8639: phyir mdzes gdung gru bzhi gser gyi ska rags kyi
NK025(ra)001:8640: tshul du gnas pa la ka thung bcu drug gis
NK025(ra)001:8642: phyi'i 'dod snam la gnas pa'i mchod pa'i lha mo
NK025(ra)001:8643: bcu drug gis mchod rdzas sna tshogs kyis sprin phung
NK025(ra)001:8645: gzhal yas khang de dag gi kha pad rnams la
NK025(ra)001:8646: gdugs dang 'phan dang dar dpyangs ba dan sna tshogs
NK025(ra)001:8647: 'phyar ba / phyi rol tu dpag bsam gyi shing
NK025(ra)001:8648: dang bkra shis pa'i rtags dang rdzas kyi khyad par
NK025(ra)001:8650: dbus phyur bur pad+ma dang bum gdan gyi bteg pa'i
NK025(ra)001:8651: bre chos kyi 'khor lo bcu gsum dang bcas pa
NK025(ra)001:8652: la rin po che'i gdugs rdo rje dang rin po
NK025(ra)001:8653: che'i tog dar dpyangs dang bcas pa /
NK025(ra)001:8654: chos 'khor gyi g.yas g.yon bre'i steng du ri dwags pho mo dang /
NK025(ra)001:8655: gser g.yu'i 'brug zung gis spras pa /
NK025(ra)001:8656: sgo khang gi steng du rta babs rim pa bzhi
NK025(ra)001:8657: pa glang gur dang bcas pa'i rgyan rta babs sgo
NK025(ra)001:8658: khang phyi'i rgyan dgus mdzes pa /
NK025(ra)001:8659: sgo thog tu bcu gcig rdo rjes mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:8660: de'i steng du pad+mas btegs pa'i bum pa bre chos 'khor gdugs tog dang bcas pa /
NK025(ra)001:8661: chos 'khor gyi g.yas g.yon du ri dwags pho mos mdzes par byas pa'i dkyil 'khor nang ma dang /
NK025(ra)001:8662: de lta bu'i dkyil 'khor gnyis pa nas bcu gcig
NK025(ra)001:8663: pa'i bar rtsig pa nas shar bu'i par thams cad
NK025(ra)001:8664: 'dra ba la nang du so so'i lha snam gyi
NK025(ra)001:8665: nang zur dang phyogs bzhir ka ba brgyad btsugs pa'i
NK025(ra)001:8666: steng gdung ma bres shing dral phyam dang thog bkab
NK025(ra)001:8667: pa / sgo'i phyi nang gi rgyan kun kyang nang ma dang dbyibs mtshungs shing /
NK025(ra)001:8668: de dag kyang phyi rim bzhin bang rim ltar dbus ma rnams mtho ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:8669: phyi rim pa ltar dma' ba'i rnam pa can /
NK025(ra)001:8670: thams cad kyang nang dur khrod 'bar ba'i gzhal yas
NK025(ra)001:8671: khang la phyi rin po che sna tshogs las grub
NK025(ra)001:8672: pa'i rang bzhin can dwangs gsal sgrib thogs med pas
NK025(ra)001:8673: / so so'i mos blor 'tshams pa bzhin bkod pa'i
NK025(ra)001:8674: bye brag sna tshogs su 'char ba 'gog pa med
NK025(ra)001:8675: / pa'o // dkyil 'khor bcu gcig pa'i sgo khang
NK025(ra)001:8676: gi steng du rta babs snam bu brgyad la 'og
NK025(ra)001:8677: nas rim pa bzhin du gser gdung /
NK025(ra)001:8683: mda' yab dang bcas pa'i glang gur /
NK025(ra)001:8688: g.yas g.yon du ri dwags pho mo /
NK025(ra)001:8689: zhing lpags dang rin po che'i gdugs /
NK025(ra)001:8690: nyi zla'i tog dang dar dpyangs dang bcas pa'i bkod pa phun sum tshogs pas mdzes par byas pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:8691: gzhal yas khang gi phyi rol na dur khrod chen po brgyad kyis bskor ba'o //
NK025(ra)001:8692: gzhal yas khang gi nang 'khor lo'i lte ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:8693: rtsibs brgyad la rin po che'i khri la sogs pa'i gdan drug brtsegs /
NK025(ra)001:8694: gzhan rnams la rang rang gi gdan du gyur /
NK025(ra)001:8695: de nas lha bskyed pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:8696: dbus kyi che mchog spyi ltar ram /
NK025(ra)001:8697: che mchog bdud rtsi la dgongs pa'i khro mkhar gnyis
NK025(ra)001:8698: gang bde mdzad srol 'dug pa las phyi ma rgyun
NK025(ra)001:8699: dkon par snang zhing ngo mtshar che bas don la
NK025(ra)001:8700: mi 'gal phyir phyi ma legs pas 'di ltar /
NK025(ra)001:8701: a kra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8702: ka ta ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:8703: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su che mchog sku mdog mthing nag dbu nyer gcig ste dang po'i dbus mthing /
NK025(ra)001:8714: steng zhal dmar po'i steng rta dbu ljang gus rta skad sgrog pa /
NK025(ra)001:8715: phyag zhe gnyis kyi dang po gnyis kun bzang yab yum thugs kar bsnol nas 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:8716: g.yas 'og ma nyi shu na rigs lnga /
NK025(ra)001:8721: lha min gyi thub pa dang nyi shu bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:8722: g.yon 'og ma nyi shu na yum lnga /
NK025(ra)001:8727: dmyal ba'i thub pa te nyi shu bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:8729: dpal chas brgyad kyis brgyan pa /
NK025(ra)001:8731: me ri me dpung gi klong na bzhugs pa /
NK025(ra)001:8732: byol song gtso brgyad kyi khri la dregs pa pad
NK025(ra)001:8733: zla nyi ma'i steng du yum khro mo gnam zhal
NK025(ra)001:8734: ma sku mdog mthing nag dbu dgu'i dbus ma mthing
NK025(ra)001:8735: ba'i zhal che mchog gi gsang ba'i rdo rje dang
NK025(ra)001:8736: sbyor ba / g.yas zhal bzhi ljang dmar mthing ser
NK025(ra)001:8737: po'i zhal bzhi che mchog gi zhabs g.yas pa bzhi
NK025(ra)001:8738: sbyor ba / dang sbyor ba / g.yon zhal bzhi
NK025(ra)001:8739: dmar ljang dkar dmar ba'i zhal bzhi che mchog gi
NK025(ra)001:8740: zhabs g.yon pa bzhi dang sbyor ba /
NK025(ra)001:8741: phyag bco brgyad kyi dang po gnyis rdo rje dang thod pa thugs kar bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:8742: g.yas kyi 'og ma brgyad kyis gnas ma brgyad kyi lha mo brgyad bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:8743: g.yon gyi 'og ma brgyad kyis yul ma phra men brgyad bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:8744: gnas ma brgyad dang yul ma brgyad thod pa bcu drug gi nang du bsnams pa'ang snang ngo //
NK025(ra)001:8745: zhabs bzhi nyi ma la sogs pa'i gdan la bzhengs pa /
NK025(ra)001:8746: dpal dang dur khrod kyi chas la sogs pa yab dang 'dra ba la /
NK025(ra)001:8747: gzig gi sham thabs can gsal bar bskyed do //
NK025(ra)001:8748: che mchog yab yum gyi mdun du dbang mchog bskyed pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:8749: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8750: sarba ta th+aa ga ta krod+hi shwa r+ai h+aum las
NK025(ra)001:8751: dbang mchog he ru ka sku mdog mthing nag dbu
NK025(ra)001:8752: dgu phyag bco brgyad zhabs bzhi pa /
NK025(ra)001:8753: rtsa zhal g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing ba /
NK025(ra)001:8754: bar zhal gsum g.yas sngo g.yon dmar dbus mthing ba /
NK025(ra)001:8755: steng zhal gsum ga mthing ba /
NK025(ra)001:8756: phyag g.yas dgu na rdo rje /
NK025(ra)001:8774: yum kro d+hi mthing nag rdo rje dang dung khrag 'dzin pa dang mnyam par sbyor ba /
NK025(ra)001:8776: pad+ma nyi zla ru tra'i gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:8777: dbang mchog yab yum gyi mdun du badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8778: badz+ra he ru ka mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum
NK025(ra)001:8779: phyag drug gi g.yas gsum rdo rje ral gri dgra
NK025(ra)001:8780: s+t+wa / g.yon gsum zhags pa lcags sgrog thong gshol can /
NK025(ra)001:8781: yum badz+ra kro d+hi dung khrag stob pa dom gyi gdan can me dpung gi klong na bzhengs pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:8782: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8783: shar rtsibs la bud+d+ha he tu ka yab yum smug
NK025(ra)001:8784: dkar dmar pa'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas gsum
NK025(ra)001:8786: g.yon gsum thod khrag zhags pa mi mgo 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:8787: yum bud+d+ha khrag 'thung dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril pa /
NK025(ra)001:8788: khyu mchog gi gdan la bzhengs pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:8789: rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8790: lho rtsibs la rat+na he ru ka yab yum ser
NK025(ra)001:8791: sngo dmar pa'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas gsum
NK025(ra)001:8792: rin chen dgra s+t+wa stong gi 'jig rten /
NK025(ra)001:8793: g.yon gsum b+han dmar rgyu zhags ri rab bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:8794: yum rin chen khrag 'thung dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba'i ma he'i gdan la bzhengs pa /
NK025(ra)001:8795: pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8796: nub rtsibs la pad+ma he ru ka yab yum dmar
NK025(ra)001:8797: dkar sngo ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas gsum
NK025(ra)001:8799: g.yon gsum b+han dmar thong gshol 'jig rten 'degs pa /
NK025(ra)001:8800: yum pad+ma khrag 'thung dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba stag gi gdan la bzhengs pa /
NK025(ra)001:8801: karma sh+r+ai he ru ka karma kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8802: byang rtsibs la karma he ru ka yab yum ljang
NK025(ra)001:8803: dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas gsum
NK025(ra)001:8804: rgya gram dgra s+t+wa ral gri /
NK025(ra)001:8805: g.yon gsum b+han dmar thong gshol zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:8806: yum las kyi khrag 'thung dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:8807: dregs pa khyo shug dang gzig gi gdan la bzhengs pa /
NK025(ra)001:8808: rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka rak+sha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8809: shar lho'i rtsibs la rak+sha he ru ka mthing dkar
NK025(ra)001:8810: dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas gsum rdo
NK025(ra)001:8812: g.yon gsum b+han dmar tho ba zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:8813: yum dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba dreg pa bsnol ba'i gdan la bzhengs pa /
NK025(ra)001:8814: sa nu sh+r+ai he ru ka sa nu kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8815: lho nub kyi rtsibs la sa nu he ru ka
NK025(ra)001:8816: ser dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas
NK025(ra)001:8819: g.yon gsum b+han+d+ha thod dbyug mi mgo 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:8820: yum dang khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:8821: gu h+ya sh+r+ai he ru ka gu h+ya kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8822: nub byang gi rtsibs la gu h+ye he ru ka
NK025(ra)001:8823: dud kha dung dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug
NK025(ra)001:8824: gi g.yas gsum gri gug kha t+w+aam dbyug to //
NK025(ra)001:8825: g.yon gsum b+han dmar mdung thung rnga yab can /
NK025(ra)001:8826: yum dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba'o //
NK025(ra)001:8827: yak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka yak+sha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:8828: byang shar gyi rtsibs la yak+sha he ru ka ljang
NK025(ra)001:8829: dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi g.yas gsum
NK025(ra)001:8830: rgya gram kha t+w+aam dgra s+t+wa /
NK025(ra)001:8831: g.yon gsum b+han dmar ral gri zhing dbyug 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:8832: yum dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba'o //
NK025(ra)001:8834: shar gyi glo 'bur la koo r+ai ma dkar mo phyag g.yas zhing dbyug /
NK025(ra)001:8836: zhing lpags kyi na bza' stod du g.yogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:8839: thod rlon gyi do shal phyag gdub zhabs gdub la sogs pa dang ldan pa zhing gdan no //
NK025(ra)001:8842: lho'i glo 'bur la tsoo r+ai ser mo mda' gzhu 'gengs pa /
NK025(ra)001:8844: nub kyi glo 'bur la pra mo ha dmar mo g.yas chu srin gyi rgyal ma tshan /
NK025(ra)001:8847: byang gi glo 'bur la bet+ta l+ai nag mo g.yas rdo rje /
NK025(ra)001:8848: g.yon zhing zhal du gsol ba /
NK025(ra)001:8850: shar lho'i gru chad la puk+ka dmar ser phyag g.yon pas zhing bsnams nas /
NK025(ra)001:8851: g.yas pas de'i rgyu ma zhags pas 'dren pa /
NK025(ra)001:8853: lho nub kyi gru chad la g+hasma r+ai ljang gu
NK025(ra)001:8854: g.yon pa'i thod khrag g.yas pa'i rdo rjes dkrug cing
NK025(ra)001:8855: gsol ba / badz+ra sme sha n+ai ha /
NK025(ra)001:8856: nub byang gi gru chad la sme sha n+ai mthing
NK025(ra)001:8857: nag phyag gnyis kyis zhing bzung la de'i glo snying
NK025(ra)001:8858: za ba'o // badz+ra tsan+da l+ai ha /
NK025(ra)001:8859: byang shar du gtum mo ser mo phyag gnyis kyis zhing bzung nas mgo lus 'dral ba'o //
NK025(ra)001:8861: khyams dang po'i lha snam gyi shar du sing+ha mu
NK025(ra)001:8862: kh+ai ser mo seng mgo dkar mo kha na ro
NK025(ra)001:8863: za ba / phyag gnyis kyis rdo rje rtse gsum pa'i phyag rgya thugs kar bsnol ba /
NK025(ra)001:8864: badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu khi he /
NK025(ra)001:8865: lhor b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kh+ai dmar mo stag mgo ser
NK025(ra)001:8866: mo phyag gnyis kyis rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i phyag
NK025(ra)001:8868: badz+ra sring+ga la mu kh+ai he /
NK025(ra)001:8869: nub tu sring+ga la mu kh+ai nag mo wa ser po'i mgo can /
NK025(ra)001:8870: phyag gnyis kyi zhing gi pags pa bsnams nas de'i chu ser ldag pa /
NK025(ra)001:8871: badz+ra shwa na mu kh+ai he /
NK025(ra)001:8872: byang du shwa na mu kh+ai mthing nag spyang ki'i
NK025(ra)001:8873: mgon can phyag gnyis kyi zhing bzung nas de'i glo
NK025(ra)001:8874: snying za ba'o // badz+ra gri d+ha mu kh+ai he /
NK025(ra)001:8875: shar lhor gri d+ha mu kh+ai dmar mo bya rgod dkar po'i mgo can mi'i rgyu ma 'dren pa /
NK025(ra)001:8877: lho nub tu kang+ka mu kh+ai sku mdog dmar mo //
NK025(ra)001:8878: phyag gnyis kyi zhing phrag pa la 'khur ba //
NK025(ra)001:8879: badz+ra k+aa ka mu kh+ai he /
NK025(ra)001:8880: nub byang du k+aa ka mu kh+ai nag mo g.yas gri /
NK025(ra)001:8883: badz+ra u lu ka mu kh+ai he /
NK025(ra)001:8884: byang shar du u lu mu kh+ai mthing ga 'ug
NK025(ra)001:8885: pa ser po'i mgo can rdo rje'i dbyug pa 'dzin
NK025(ra)001:8886: pa'o // badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dzah shar
NK025(ra)001:8887: sgor rta gdong lcags kyu ma dkar mo rta'i gdong
NK025(ra)001:8891: lho sgor phag gdong zhags pa ma ser mo zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:8893: nub sgor seng gdong dmar mo lcags sgrog bsnams pa'i
NK025(ra)001:8894: mdo mig smin mtshams su yod pa'i nang na nyi
NK025(ra)001:8895: zla ga'u'i nang du rnal 'byor pa'i tshe 'dzin pa
NK025(ra)001:8896: / badz+ra b+hasmi pa la ya ba to hoh byang sgor spyang gdong ma ljang gu g.yas dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:8898: rgyan cha lugs gong dang mthun pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:8899: dkyil 'khor gnyis pa'i khyams la badz+ra a pra ti ha +aar+ya ni tsa tu ra ta ra phata /
NK025(ra)001:8901: khyams kyi phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad du spor ma brgyad ni /
NK025(ra)001:8902: shar du 'bar ma nyi ma'i zer gyi zhags pa
NK025(ra)001:8903: can dmar mo nyi ma'i zer gyi zhags pa 'dzin
NK025(ra)001:8904: pa / badz+ra a pra ti ha +aar+ya sogs sngags gong bzhin no //
NK025(ra)001:8905: shar lhor me khyer glog ma sprin dmar mo glog gi zhabs pa 'phen pa /
NK025(ra)001:8906: badz+ra lhor skar mda' 'phen sngon mo g.yas mdung thung /
NK025(ra)001:8908: badz+ra lho nub tu srin mo rlung nag ral gri'i skra can ma sngo nag khyung khra 'gyed pa /
NK025(ra)001:8909: badz+ra nub tu klu mo lce 'bebs ma dkar mo thog 'bebs pa /
NK025(ra)001:8910: badz+ra nub byang du gnod sbyin khyung thogs ma sngon mo khyung 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:8911: badz+ra byang du ba lang sna glang po'i gdong can sngo nag thogs ser 'bebs pa /
NK025(ra)001:8912: badz+ra byang shar du mig 'byin snying sreg ma thal kar ral gri 'phyar ba /
NK025(ra)001:8913: de thams cad spyan gsum pa mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK025(ra)001:8915: dur khrod kyi chas brgyad rdzoogs pa khro mo'i cha lugs can no //
NK025(ra)001:8916: sh+r+ai he badz+ra mung+ga ra mu kha shwa ra ya
NK025(ra)001:8917: na mah shar sgor dkar mo mig gcig rgyas 'debs
NK025(ra)001:8918: ma dkar mo rdo rje thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:8919: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga ma shwa ra ya y+aa na
NK025(ra)001:8920: mah lho sgor ser mo las mkhan tshe 'phel ma
NK025(ra)001:8922: sh+r+ai badz+ra kha t+w+aam ga pra dz+wa la ya y+aa
NK025(ra)001:8923: na mah nub sgor dmar mo za byed dbang sdud
NK025(ra)001:8924: ma dmar mo rgyal mtshan 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:8925: sh+r+ai badz+ra g+han+de pra dz+wa la ya y+aa na mah
NK025(ra)001:8926: byang sgor nag mo ral gcig rmongs byed ma ljang
NK025(ra)001:8928: dkyil 'khor gsum pa'i khyams la dbang phyug ma nyer brgyad ni /
NK025(ra)001:8930: srin po'i chung ma gnas gyur pa //
NK025(ra)001:8931: dbang phyug chen mo mi srin mo //
NK025(ra)001:8934: mi srin mo 'di ni sngon srin po d+ha sha
NK025(ra)001:8935: g+r+ai wa'i chung ma byed pa'i dus su srin mo
NK025(ra)001:8936: dmar nag thod rlon 'dzin pa gcig yod par /
NK025(ra)001:8937: phyis ma tram gyis srin po'i lag nas phrogs te kho'i chung ma byas /
NK025(ra)001:8938: der kho mgo brnyan la dga' bas srin zhal g.yag gdong du bsgyur ba yin te /
NK025(ra)001:8939: ngo bo gcig la lus 'gyur ba ni dper na
NK025(ra)001:8940: ljong mo sbal par 'gyur ba lta bu yin gsungs
NK025(ra)001:8941: pas / dbang phyug ma 'di rnams la sprul gzhi dang sprul pa'i khyad par gnyis yod cing /
NK025(ra)001:8942: mngon par rtogs pa sgom pa'i tshe rgyu dang 'bras
NK025(ra)001:8943: bu'i tshul gyis gnas bsgyur ltar bsgom pa khams lugs
NK025(ra)001:8944: kyi srol la 'dug pa 'thad par mthong nas 'dir
NK025(ra)001:8946: khams lugs sprul pa rnams kyi phyag mtshan mi 'dra ba 'dug pa zur lug gtsang mar bgyis shing /
NK025(ra)001:8947: de la yang mi mthun pa re gnyis 'dug pa
NK025(ra)001:8948: lha dbang dus kyi bskur tshig btsan par bgyis pas
NK025(ra)001:8949: 'di ltar / dkyil 'khor gsum pa'i khyams kyi shar
NK025(ra)001:8950: du ma nu rak+sha s+ai b+h+yo las dbang phyug chen
NK025(ra)001:8951: mo mi'i srin mo sku mdog dmar nag rdo rje
NK025(ra)001:8953: de nyid gnas gyur pa las srin mo dmar ser
NK025(ra)001:8954: g.yag gdong ral pa gsig pa zhing g.yang dang rtse
NK025(ra)001:8955: gsum 'dzin pa / bra h+ma ni b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:8956: tshangs ma sku mdog dmar ser pad+ma bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:8957: de nyid gnas gyur pa las tshangs ma dmar ser sbrul gdong rtse lnga dang b+han dmar 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:8959: 'khrug mo sku mdog dkar mo rdo rje dang tri sh+au la bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:8960: de nyid gnas gyur pa khro mo dmar ser gzig mgo can dbyug to dang snying 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:8962: 'jug sred ma sngon mo rdo rje dang 'khor lo 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:8963: de nyid gnas gyur pas khyab 'jug ma ser mo
NK025(ra)001:8964: pha wang gdong 'khor lo dang ril pa spyi blugs
NK025(ra)001:8966: gzhon nu ma dmar mo rdo rje dang mdung bsnams pa de nyid gnas gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:8967: dbang mo dmar skya dred gdong bam dbyung 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:8969: dbang mo sku mdog dkar mo in+d+ra gdengs pa de nyid gnas gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:8970: brgya byin ma dkar dmar sre mong mgo dung dmar bsre ba /
NK025(ra)001:8972: zhi ba dmar mo rdo rje dang thod khrag 'dzin pa de nyid gnas gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:8973: zhi ba dmar mo dom gyi mgo can dung dmar dang rgyu zhags bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:8975: bdud rtsi ma sku mdog dmar mo pad+ma bsnams pa de nyid gnas gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:8976: bdud rtsi ma sngon mo chu srin mgo bum pa 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:8978: zhi ba dkar mo pun+d+ha ri bsnams pa de nyid gnas sgyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:8979: zhi ba mo sngo skya sdig pa'i mgo g.yas thod pa bum ril /
NK025(ra)001:8982: be con ma sngon mo dbyug to can de nyid gnas gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:8983: be con ma nag mo khra mgo can thod rlon bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:8985: srin mo sku mdog dmar ser thod khrag 'dzin pa de nyid gnas gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:8986: srin mo dmar nag wa gdong zhing gi rgyu ma 'dren pa /
NK025(ra)001:8988: za ba mo dmar nag sha khrag rol pa de nyid gnas gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:8989: za byed nag mo stag mgo bam gyi snying 'byin pa /
NK025(ra)001:8990: nub tu badz+ra ra ti tam b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:8991: dga' ba mo dmar mo ral gri 'dzin pa de nyid gnas gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:8992: dga' byed dmar mo bya rgod mgo ral gri dang 'khor lo thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:8993: badz+ra ru d+hi ra mat+t+aa b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:8994: khrag gis myos ma dkar mo gshol bsnams pa de nyid gnas gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:8995: khrag 'thung dmar nag rta gdong can rdo rje' dbyug pa dang dung dmar 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:8996: badz+ra e ka tsa ra ma b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:8997: gcig pu spyod ma ser mo spu gri bsnams pa de nyid gnas gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:8998: rdo rje ser mo khyung gdong rdo rje dang b+han+d+ha 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9000: yid 'phrog ma dmar mo mda' gzhu thogs pa de nyid gnas gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:9001: 'dod pa dmar ser khyi mgo zhing chen za ba /
NK025(ra)001:9003: grub mo dkar mo bum pa 'dzin pa de nyid gnas gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:9004: nor srung dkar dmar phu shud mgo pad+ma 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9006: rlung mo sngon mo ba dan 'phyar ba de nyid gnas gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:9007: rlung mo dmar skya sha ba'i mgo bam ro za ba /
NK025(ra)001:9008: byang du badz+ra ma h+aa m+aa ra na b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:9009: khyo med ma dmar nag ral gri 'dzin pa de nyid gnas gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:9010: gsod byed ma ljang nag spyang gdong bam chen dang rnge chung 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9012: me lha mo dmar mo gsal shing 'dzin pa de nyid gnas gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:9013: me mo ljang dmar lho 'brong gi mgo can me sgron dang rgyu ma 'dren pa /
NK025(ra)001:9015: phag mo dmar nag mche ba bsnams pa de nyid gnas gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:9016: phag mo ljang ser phag gdong rtse gsum 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9018: rgan byed ma dmar smug byis ro'i rgyu ma za ba de nyid gnas gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:9019: rgan byed ljang sngon rgya khra hor po'i mgo can bam gyi rgyu ma 'dren cing khrag 'thor ba /
NK025(ra)001:9021: sna chen mo dmar nag thod khrag 'thung ba de nyid gnas gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:9022: sna chen mo ljang dmar glang gdong bam chen 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9024: chu lha dkar sngo sbrul zhags bsnams pa de nyid gnas gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:9025: chu lha mo ljang nag sbrul gdong sbrul dang bum pa 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:9027: shar sgor nag mo chen mo lcags kyu can de nyid gnas gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:9028: khu byug gdong nag mo lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9030: lho sgor ra mgo dmar ser chen mo zhags pa can de nyid gnas gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:9031: ra gdong sngon mo rgyu zhags 'dren pa /
NK025(ra)001:9032: badz+ra bum pa ka la ma b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:9033: nub sgor bum sna sngo nag chen mo lcags sgrog can de nyid gnas gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:9034: seng gdong dmar mo lcags sgrog 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9035: badz+ra lam bo d+ha ra b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:9036: byang sgor gsus 'dzin ser nag chen mo ljang nag dril 'khrol de nyid gnas gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:9037: skye ka'i mgo can ljang nag dril bu 'dzin pa ste /
NK025(ra)001:9038: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad po de thams
NK025(ra)001:9039: cad kyang ral pa gsig pa zhing gi stod g.yogs
NK025(ra)001:9040: gzig gi sham thabs dang sbrul gyis brgyan pa /
NK025(ra)001:9041: zhing skam gyi gdan can no //
NK025(ra)001:9042: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'di yan chod kyi dkyil
NK025(ra)001:9043: 'khor gnyis bsdoms par khrag 'thung rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK025(ra)001:9044: ro // dkyil 'khor bzhi pa'i khyams la mkha' 'gro so gnyis ni /
NK025(ra)001:9045: shar du e a ra li h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:9046: dga' byed dkar mo rdo rje dang b+han+d+ha bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9047: e a 'dren byed dkar skya lcags kyu dang b+han+d+ha bsnams pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:9048: e a gsod byed dkar mo mda' gzhi 'gengs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9049: e a spor byed dkar skya spru gri thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9050: e a 'bar byed ma mthing nag rin chen bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9051: e a gzi brjid ma dmar ser nyi ma dang b+han+d+ha bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9052: e a khro gnyer ma mthing nag zhing lpags kyi ba dan dang b+han+d+ha bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9053: lhor e a 'joms byed ma dkar skya bam chen za tshul bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9054: e a chags byed ma dmar nag pad+ma e a
NK025(ra)001:9055: chags bral ma dmar nag ral gri e a 'khor
NK025(ra)001:9057: e a rgyas 'debs ma dmar nag lce dang lcags
NK025(ra)001:9058: kyu e a sna tshogs lus 'chang rdo rje rgya
NK025(ra)001:9059: gram e a bsrung ba mo ljang gu go khrab
NK025(ra)001:9060: nub tu e a gnod sbyin mo ljang nag mche
NK025(ra)001:9061: ba / e a yang dag 'phrog ma ljang gu mu tig gi dbyug pa 'phyar ba /
NK025(ra)001:9062: e a bya rog gdong nag mo gri dang 'khar gzhong thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9063: e a 'jigs byed ma dkar sngo mche ba gtsigs pa'i rin po che dang dung khrag /
NK025(ra)001:9064: e a bzhad mgo dkar mo snying 'byin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9065: e a 'ug gdong ma sngo skya keng rus 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9066: e a khyi mgo mthing nag keng rus 'cha' ba /
NK025(ra)001:9067: byang du e a phag gdong ma mthing nag tshil snying sha rus za ba /
NK025(ra)001:9068: e a rnga mo'i mgo sngo nag glo ba 'dren pa /
NK025(ra)001:9069: e a bong mgo ma sngon mo thod dbyugs dang dgra s+t+wa bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9070: e a 'joms gcod dmar nag ra mgo spu gri thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9071: e a rus 'cha' ma dmar nag byi la'i mgo keng rus 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9072: e a u sting mang sa dmar ljang seng gdong keng rus 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9073: e a dmar ser rus pa'i phreng can ma lce spyang gdong thod skam bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9074: shar sgor e a bum snam ser mo lcags kyu dang ral gri /
NK025(ra)001:9075: lho sgor e a gshin rje rnams 'joms ma sngon mo zhags pa dang ral gri /
NK025(ra)001:9076: nub sgor e a d+ha sha gri wa dmar mo lcags sgrog dang spu gri thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9077: byang sgor e a 'bod sgrog ma ljang gu dril
NK025(ra)001:9078: bu dang dgra ste thams cad kyang khro mo'i cha
NK025(ra)001:9079: byad / g.yon na phyag mtshan med pa rnams thod khrag 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:9080: dkyil 'khor lnga pa'i khyams la ma mo bdun ni /
NK025(ra)001:9082: shar du rdo rje kun grags ma nag mo dar nag gi gos can /
NK025(ra)001:9083: zhabs la sak+ti ste hor lhwam yu ba can gyon pa /
NK025(ra)001:9084: phyag g.yas ral gri dang g.yon thod khrag /
NK025(ra)001:9085: skra bardzesa pa la thod skam gyis brgyan cing /
NK025(ra)001:9086: rlon pa'i do shal can no //
NK025(ra)001:9087: ma ma kun bzang mo mthing nag gar mdzad pa /
NK025(ra)001:9088: lhor ma ma rdo rje kun gsal ma 'ja' tshon gyi gos can gri thod 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9089: ma ma rdo rje ye shes mthing nag snying dang thod khrag can /
NK025(ra)001:9090: nub tu ma ma rdo rje 'od chags ma sngon
NK025(ra)001:9091: nag rdo rje'i phreng ba thogs pa khrag gi mtsho
NK025(ra)001:9092: la gnas pa / ma ma rdo rje 'od 'phro
NK025(ra)001:9093: ma mthing nag zhags pa thogs pa me'i klong na
NK025(ra)001:9094: la gnas pa / bzhugs pa / byang du ma
NK025(ra)001:9095: ma rdo rje g.yu sgron ma mthing nag lcags kyu
NK025(ra)001:9096: 'dzin pa ste ma mo bdun rgyan cha lugs 'dra
NK025(ra)001:9097: la gnas pa / bzhugs pa / ba'o // badz+ra dun+tim b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:9098: shar sgor gling bzhi mgyogs ma lha'i sring mo dkar
NK025(ra)001:9099: mo bya rgod kyi thul pa gsol ba bya rgod
NK025(ra)001:9101: badz+ra lho sgor mkha' la khyung lding gshin rje'i sring
NK025(ra)001:9102: mo sngon mo stag gi thul pa gsol ba stag
NK025(ra)001:9104: badz+ra nub sgor dmar mo g.yag thod klu yi sring
NK025(ra)001:9105: mo dmar mo g.yag gi mgo can chu srin gyi
NK025(ra)001:9106: g.yang gzhi gsol ba chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan 'dzin
NK025(ra)001:9107: pa / badz+ra byang sgor nag mo sder chen gnod
NK025(ra)001:9108: sbyin sring nag mo rma bya'i thul pa gsol ba
NK025(ra)001:9110: bzhi ka'ang zhi ma khro skra thor tshugs can hor lhwam gyon pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:9111: dkyil 'khor drug pa'i khyams la ging chen bco brgyad ni /
NK025(ra)001:9112: ging+ga ra ha ha ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:9113: shar du khro bo ging+ka ra mthing nag spyan gsum
NK025(ra)001:9114: pa dur khrod kyii chas can ral gri dang b+han+d+ha
NK025(ra)001:9115: 'dzin pa / khro mo khams gsum dbugs sdud ma
NK025(ra)001:9116: sngo nag gri gug dang thod khrag 'dzin pa gzig
NK025(ra)001:9117: sham can dang mnyam par sbyor ba /
NK025(ra)001:9118: ging+ka ra rdo rje 'byung po dmar nag ral gri dang b+han+d+ha dmar gyis gang ba 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9119: ging+ka ra rdo rje gnod sbyin ljang nag gri dang sdigs mdzub 'phyar ba /
NK025(ra)001:9120: ging+ka ra rdo rje spyang ki dmar nag spyang mgo spu gri thod khrag /
NK025(ra)001:9122: rdo rje gshin rje mthing nag be con dang dgra s+t+wa /
NK025(ra)001:9123: ging+ka ra rdo rje rol pa dmar nag b+han+d+ha dang phal tshab ste gri bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9124: ging+ka ra rdo rje 'chi bdag ljang ser rdo rje gsor zhing brdeg pa /
NK025(ra)001:9125: nub tu ging+ka ra rdo rje dus mtshams ljang nag
NK025(ra)001:9126: shak+ti ste mdung so'i nang rma bya'i sgro chun gyis
NK025(ra)001:9127: bkang ba'i 'phang mdung dang mdung dar 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9128: ging+ka ra rdo rje ro langs ser nag zhing dbyug
NK025(ra)001:9129: 'phyar ba ging+ka ra rdo rje 'joms pa smug nag
NK025(ra)001:9130: rdo rje'i tho ba thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9131: ging+ka ra rdo rje ging lcam ljang nag rdo rje'i lcags kyus 'dren pa /
NK025(ra)001:9132: byang du ging+ka ra rdo rje dbang bsgyur ma dmar ser zhing gi g.yab mo 'debs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9133: ging+ka ra rdo rje 'phrul me che sngo skya gzugs
NK025(ra)001:9134: med rlung ltar rgyu ba mo mdung dar nag po
NK025(ra)001:9135: 'dzin pa / ging+ka ra rdo rje glog 'gyu ma dmar mo glog zhags 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9136: ging+ka ra rdo rje mthu mo che ljang nag lcags kyi tho ba thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9137: shar sgor ging+ka ra rdo rje rna nyan phra ma
NK025(ra)001:9138: mkhan mthing nag rdo rje dang dgra s+t+wa thogs pa
NK025(ra)001:9139: / lho sgor ging+ka ra rdo rje sgrol byed ma smug nag b+han+d+ha dang gri thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9140: nub sgor ging+ka ra rdo rje za byed chen mo
NK025(ra)001:9141: mthing nag longs spyod kyis gang ba'i gzhong pa bsnams
NK025(ra)001:9142: pa / byang sgor ging+ka ra rdo rje myong byed
NK025(ra)001:9143: ma smug nag longs spyod kyis gang ba'i gzhong pa
NK025(ra)001:9144: pa / bsnams pa / de dag thams cad stag
NK025(ra)001:9145: sham dang gzig sham la sogs khro bo dang khro
NK025(ra)001:9146: mo'i rgyan du mas brgyan pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:9147: dkyil 'khor bzhi pa dang drug pa gnyis mkha' 'gro las kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK025(ra)001:9148: dkyil 'khor bdun pa'i khyams la khro bo khro mo drug cu ni /
NK025(ra)001:9150: shar du khro bo rnam par rgyal ba dkar po
NK025(ra)001:9151: zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa rdo rje dang tho ba
NK025(ra)001:9152: / yum khro mo rdo rje snyems ma dkar mo
NK025(ra)001:9153: g.yas yab la 'khyud cing g.yon thod khrag stob pa
NK025(ra)001:9154: / / kro d+ha khro bo dbyug sngon can sngon po rin po che dang sdigs mdzub /
NK025(ra)001:9155: yum khro mo rdo rje sder mo dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9156: kro d+ha khro bo gshin rje gshed mthing nag dbyug to dang zhags pa /
NK025(ra)001:9157: yum khro mo rdo rje dur khrod ma dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9158: kro d+ha khro bo mi g.yo ba smug nag khu tshur dang ral gri /
NK025(ra)001:9159: yum khro mo rdo rje gtun khung ma dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9160: kro d+ha khro bo rta mgrin dmar po mda' gzhu dang pad+ma /
NK025(ra)001:9161: yum khro mo rdo rje gtum mo dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9162: kro d+ha khro bo gzhan gyis mi thub pa sngon po dgra s+t+wa dang gtun shing /
NK025(ra)001:9163: yum khro mo mda' snyems ma dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9164: lhor kro d+ha khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil ba ljang nag rgya gram 'phyar ba /
NK025(ra)001:9165: yum khro mo rlung 'byin ma dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9166: kro d+ha khro bo khams gsum rnam rgyal nag po rdo rje dang tho ba /
NK025(ra)001:9167: yum khro mo gsod byed ma dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9168: kro d+ha khro bo stobs po che dud kha dung dkar dang rnga yab /
NK025(ra)001:9169: yum khro mo bskyod byed ma dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9170: kro d+ha khro bo h+aum mdzad dmar skya rdo rje dang mda' gzhu 'geng ba /
NK025(ra)001:9171: yum khro mo sgra 'byin ma dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9172: nub tu kro d+ha khro bo badz+ra k+ai la ya mthing nag phur bu 'dril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9173: yum khro mo rgyas 'debs ma dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9174: kro d+ha khro bo rme brtsegs mthing nag phyag gnyis kar rdo rje thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9175: yum khro mo 'dam 'byin dung chen dam rdzas kyis gang ba bsnams pa dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9176: kro d+ha khro bo badz+ra yak+sha ljang nag phur pa sgreng pa /
NK025(ra)001:9177: yum khro mo yag+mo dung chen snying khrag gis bkang ba 'dzin pa dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9178: kro d+ha khro bo dmar nag rdo rje dang tho ba thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9179: yum khro mo dbang sgyur ma mgo bcad rak+tasa bkang ba 'dzin pa dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9180: kro d+ha khro bo za 'og sna tshogs mdog thod pa dang sbrul zhags /
NK025(ra)001:9181: yum khro mo za 'og ma rdo rje thod khrag thogs pa dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9182: kro d+ha khro bo rab 'khrug sngo nag ral gri can /
