NK025(ra)001:9183: yum khro mo rab 'jigs dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9184: byang du kro d+ha khro bo ma h+aa k+aa la dmar nag zhags pa can /
NK025(ra)001:9185: yum khro mo ral pa sgreng ma dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9186: kro d+ha khro bo mi 'chi thal sbyor sngo nag thal mo sdeb pa /
NK025(ra)001:9187: yum khro mo 'joms byed dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9188: kro d+ha khro chen gu lang smug nag gtun shing sdeb pa /
NK025(ra)001:9189: yum khro mo las grub ma dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9190: kro d+ha khro bo rab rngams ljang nag rdo rjes dung dmar dkrug cing gsol ba /
NK025(ra)001:9191: yum khro mo gtum chen tsit+ta dang thod khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9192: shar sgor kro d+ha khro bo 'jig rten gsum snang sngo nag be con dang sdigs mdzub can /
NK025(ra)001:9193: yum khro mo mi pham ma dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9194: kro d+ha khro bo 'jig rten gsum 'dul dmar nag tho ba 'phyar ba /
NK025(ra)001:9195: yum khro mo lcags kyu ma lcags kyu 'dzin pa dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9196: kro d+ha khro bo rngam chen smug nag be con dang sdigs mdzub /
NK025(ra)001:9197: yum khro mo dbang sdud ma dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9198: lho sgor kro d+ha khro bo 'jig rten gsum 'jigs dmar nag tho ba 'phyar ba /
NK025(ra)001:9199: yum khro gnyer can dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9200: kro d+ha khro bo 'jig rten gsum 'ching sngo nag dbyug to 'phyar ba /
NK025(ra)001:9201: yum khro mo zhags pa ma dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9202: nub sgor kro d+ha khro bo pad rgyal dmar nag ral gri 'phyar ba /
NK025(ra)001:9203: yum khro mo ro langs ma dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9204: kro d+ha khro bo be con sngon po rin po che dang be con 'phyar ba /
NK025(ra)001:9205: yum khro mo lcags sgrog ma dung chen 'bud pa dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9206: kro d+ha khro bo rdo rje tho ba dud kha tho ba bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9207: yum khro mo za byed ma dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9208: byang sgor kro d+ha khro bo badz+ra ka ti dmar nag gri gug dang sdigs mdzub can /
NK025(ra)001:9209: yum khro mo ral gcig ma dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9210: kro d+ha khro bo rdo rje go cha mthing nag go cha bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9211: yum khro mo dril 'khrol ma dril bu 'khrol zhing thod khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9212: khro bo de rnams thams cad kyang dpral bar thal chen gyi tshom bu /
NK025(ra)001:9213: mkhur tshos la rak+ta'i thig le /
NK025(ra)001:9214: mgrin par zhag gi zo ris te byug pa'i rdzas gsum /
NK025(ra)001:9216: thod pa tshar gsum gyi do shal /
NK025(ra)001:9217: sbrul chun te 'dogs pa'i rgyan gnyis /
NK025(ra)001:9218: glang chen ko rlon dang mi lpags kyi stod g.yogs
NK025(ra)001:9219: stag gi sham thabs de bgo ba'i gos gsum sogs
NK025(ra)001:9229: gzi mdangs mi lpags kyi chas /
NK025(ra)001:9230: dmar zal khrag gi chas te dpal chas bcus brgyan pa /
NK025(ra)001:9231: chas bcu 'di che mchog 'dus pa'i rgyud lugs ltar yin gsungs /
NK025(ra)001:9232: yum rnams kyang mi rus las byas pa'i spyi bo'i 'khor lo /
NK025(ra)001:9237: 'og pag ste rus pa'i phyag rgya lnga /
NK025(ra)001:9240: g.yas 'khyud g.yon thod khrag stob pa'i rnam pa can no //
NK025(ra)001:9241: 'di ni khro bo rol pa'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK025(ra)001:9242: dkyil 'khor brgyad pa'i khyams la pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu las /
NK025(ra)001:9243: shar du dung gi mi mo drug cu ni /
NK025(ra)001:9244: b+ha na b+ha na am ku sha dzah rdo rje
NK025(ra)001:9245: 'bar ba'i pho nya mthong byed ma dkar mo lcags
NK025(ra)001:9246: kyu bsnams pa / b+ha na rdo rje 'dzin byed ma dkar mo zhags pa 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9247: b+ha na rdo rje phur bu thogs med ma dkar mo snying brgyus pa'i zhags pa 'phen pa /
NK025(ra)001:9248: b+ha na rdo rje 'bigs pa mo dkar mo shel gyi mda' 'phen pa /
NK025(ra)001:9249: b+ha na rdo rje ro langs ma dkar mo ral gri thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9250: b+ha na rdo rje drag mo dkar mo mdung thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9251: b+ha na rdo rje mgyogs ma dkar mo mi lpags kyi g.yab mo 'debs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9252: b+ha na rdo rje gtum mo dkar mo mi snying 'byin cing cho nge 'debs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9253: b+ha na rdo rje 'bebs ma dkar mo glu len zhing gar bsgyur ba /
NK025(ra)001:9254: b+ha na rdo rje gsal ma dkar mo dung phreng klad la bskor ba /
NK025(ra)001:9255: b+ha na rdo rje stod ma dkar skya dar dkar gyi g.yab mo 'debs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9256: b+ha na rdo rje 'gugs ma dkar mo bdud kyi snying 'byin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9257: b+ha na rdo rje thogs med ma dkar mo zangs gri bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9258: b+ha na rdo rje bskyod ma dkar mo rlung gi zhags pa thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9259: b+ha na rdo rje 'chang bdag ma dkar dmar 'dzin byed zhags pa thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9260: b+ha na rdo rje phra men ma dkar dmar me sgron khyer ba /
NK025(ra)001:9261: b+ha na rdo rje myur byed ma dkar dmar glog gi zhags pa thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9262: b+ha na rdo rje bskul byed ma dkar dmar skar mda' 'phen pa /
NK025(ra)001:9263: b+ha na rdo rje gsal bkra mo dkar dmar rdo
NK025(ra)001:9264: rje'i zhags pa 'phen pa b+ha na rdo rje yang
NK025(ra)001:9265: dag ma dkar dmar phag gdong mi lpags kyi lcags
NK025(ra)001:9266: la dung dang byu ru'i phra btab pa'i lan phran
NK025(ra)001:9267: bsdeb pa / b+ha na rdo rje che ba mo dkar ser rdo rje rtse gcig pa 'phen pa /
NK025(ra)001:9268: b+ha na rdo rje gnon mdzad ma dkar ser rdo rje'i brag 'phen pa /
NK025(ra)001:9269: b+ha na rdo rje dbang phyug ma dmar ser tri sh+au la dang gze mo 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9270: b+ha na rdo rje sder mo dkar ser lcags kyu dmar po 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9271: b+ha na rdo rje kha 'bar ma dmar ser sprin pa'i go zu can kha nas me 'bar ba /
NK025(ra)001:9272: b+ha na rdo rje gsal byed ma dkar ser dung gi 'khor lo 'phen pa /
NK025(ra)001:9273: b+ha na rdo rje khro mo dkar ser mi lpags kyi g.yang gzhi bsdeb pa /
NK025(ra)001:9274: b+ha na rdo rje 'chang ma dkar ser rdo rje'i phur bu bsgril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9275: b+ha na rdo rje gtum mo dmar ser rdo rje'i tho ba thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9276: b+ha na rdo rje khros ma dmar ser rdo rje'i be con 'phyar ba /
NK025(ra)001:9277: b+ha na rdo rje las byed dmar ser ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9278: b+ha na rdo rje dus mtshan dmar ser shak+ti thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9279: b+ha na rdo rje thar pa mo dmar ser gtun shing thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9280: b+ha na rdo rje sku la mo dmar ser lcags kyu 'debs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9281: b+ha na rdo rje dpal 'bar ma dmar ser ras kyi zhags pa 'debs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9282: b+ha na rdo rje bskyod chen ma dmar ser rlung gi rkyal pa ste sbud pa thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9283: b+ha na rdo rje gso byed ma dkar sngo dung gi zhags pa can /
NK025(ra)001:9284: b+ha na rdo rje rlangs pa ma dkar sngo rlung gi zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9285: b+ha na rdo rje gsod pa mo dkar mo shel gyi gri thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9286: b+ha na rdo rje za ba mo dkar sngo sha chen za ba /
NK025(ra)001:9287: b+ha na rdo rje lus 'phrog ma dkar ser lcags kyi tsh+aa tsh+aa 'phro ba /
NK025(ra)001:9288: b+ha na rdo rje ngag 'phrog ma dmar ser lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9289: b+ha na rdo rje yid gtum ma dkar ser sen mos mi snying 'byin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9290: b+ha na rdo rje bde chen mo dmar ser ral pa'i g.yab mo 'debs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9291: b+ha na rdo rje khrag 'thung ma dkar sngo b+han+d+ha ra khrag 'thung ba /
NK025(ra)001:9292: b+ha na rdo rje 'cha' ba ma dkar sngo keng rus khral khrol du 'cha' ba /
NK025(ra)001:9293: b+ha na rdo rje tshe len ma dkar sngo dar gyi g.yab mo 'dor ba /
NK025(ra)001:9294: b+ha na rdo rje mdangs len ma dkar sngo dung gi par bu bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9295: b+ha na rdo rje srog 'phrog ma dkar mo tsit+ta 'byin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9296: b+ha na rdo rje snying 'byin ma dkar sngo snying gi phreng ba 'dren pa /
NK025(ra)001:9297: b+ha na rdo rje gcod byed ma dkar ljang shel rdo'i dgra s+t+wa 'phyar ba /
NK025(ra)001:9298: b+ha na rdo rje skul byed ma dkar mo lcags kyu bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9299: b+ha na rdo rje sna tshogs gzugs sku mdog sna
NK025(ra)001:9300: tshogs sam ljang gu zab slag gsol ba bse'i ldan
NK025(ra)001:9301: dkar te mdung la bse'i ba dan 'phyar ba /
NK025(ra)001:9302: b+ha na rdo rje smyon ma dkar ljang shel gyi rdo rje 'phen pa /
NK025(ra)001:9303: b+ha na rdo rje 'jug byed ma dkar ljang bya khra 'gyed pa /
NK025(ra)001:9304: b+ha na rdo rje yid 'phrog ma dkar ljang tshon
NK025(ra)001:9305: gyi gru gu ste srad bu sna lnga'i gru gu
NK025(ra)001:9306: thogs pa / b+ha na rdo rje ro rkun ma dkar ljang ro khur ba /
NK025(ra)001:9307: b+ha na rdo rje rdzu byed ma dkar ljang rlung gi zhags pa thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9308: b+ha na rdo rje 'jigs byed ma dkar ljang dug gi mche ba 'byin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9309: b+ha na rdo rje bcud len ma dkar ljang g.yu'i za ma tog bsnams pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:9310: lhor gser gyi mi mo drug cu ni /
NK025(ra)001:9311: ha la ha la p+aa sha h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:9312: rdo rje dbyings phyug ma ser nag me'i zhags pa thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9313: ha la rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma ser nag sdigs mdzub gyad kyi dor stabs can /
NK025(ra)001:9314: ha la rdo rje mthu 'bebs ma dmar ser ba dan gyi g.yab 'dor ba /
NK025(ra)001:9315: ha la rdo rje srab mo ser nag go gyon te gri phub 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9316: ha la rdo rje mchongs mo ser nag byan lag
NK025(ra)001:9317: ste bum pa dam pa lta bu'am bya ma bum
NK025(ra)001:9319: ha la rdo rje khro gtum can ser nag sdang
NK025(ra)001:9320: mig lta ba stag la zhon pa gri thod can
NK025(ra)001:9321: / ha la rdo rje brtson byed ma ser nag rlung gi zhags pa thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9322: ha la rdo rje 'jigs gdong ma ser nag kha bgrad mche gtsigs lag gnyis gdengs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9323: ha la rdo rje sha za ma ser nag ro dbyug klad la bskor zhing sha za ba /
NK025(ra)001:9324: ha la rdo rje khrag 'thor ma ser nag mi
NK025(ra)001:9325: mgo rlon pa'i phor par mi snying khrag zhag blug
NK025(ra)001:9326: cing 'thor ba / ha la rdo rje so gcig
NK025(ra)001:9327: ma ser mo kha mig so gcig ma rdo rje
NK025(ra)001:9329: ha la rdo rje ral gcig ma ser mo ral pa gos ltar gyon cing /
NK025(ra)001:9330: lcags kyu dang sdigs mdzub can /
NK025(ra)001:9331: ha la rdo rje 'khril byed ma ser mo sngo dmar gyi zhags pa 'phen pa /
NK025(ra)001:9332: ha la rdo rje 'dzul byed ma ser mo gser gyi ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9333: ha la rdo rje myur byed ma ser mo tshon gyi gru gu thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9334: ha la rdo rje mthu chen ma ser mo thog
NK025(ra)001:9335: gi char pa 'bebs shing ri klungs kun tu rgyug
NK025(ra)001:9336: pa / ha la rdo rje nag mo skra'i zhags pa 'phen pa /
NK025(ra)001:9337: ha la rdo rje rtog 'joms ma ser mo b+han+d+hara shar lnga dang bdud rtsi lnga za ba /
NK025(ra)001:9338: ha la rdo rje rtog med ma ser mo dung gi gzhong pa thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9339: ha la rdo rje yangs ma ser mo sprin gyi ga sha can glog zhags klad la bskor ba /
NK025(ra)001:9340: ha la rdo rje sna tshogs lus dmar skya za
NK025(ra)001:9341: 'og gi stod g.yogs can rnga mong du rdzu zhing
NK025(ra)001:9343: ha la rdo rje sdang mig ma dmar skya lcags kyu bya khra 'gyed pa /
NK025(ra)001:9344: ha la rdo rje dur khrod ma dmar skya zhing g.yang bsdeb pa /
NK025(ra)001:9345: ha la rdo rje mig 'gro ma dmar nag khyung zhon glog zhags 'debs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9346: ha la rdo rje bde 'gro ma ser mo mchong
NK025(ra)001:9347: gi bya glag dmar po zhon cing g.yu'i zor ba
NK025(ra)001:9348: 'debs pa / ha la rdo rje rgyas byed ma ser skya nyi zla'i 'khor lo 'phen pa /
NK025(ra)001:9349: ha la rdo rje 'dzum byed ma ser skya tshon
NK025(ra)001:9350: gyi gru gu brdog pa bu chung dang spre'ura rdzu
NK025(ra)001:9351: ba / ha la rdo rje khrag myos ma dmar
NK025(ra)001:9352: mo dur bya mchu ring gi gdong pa can thod
NK025(ra)001:9353: ba / khrag thogs pa / ha la rdo rje rngams 'tshig ma dmar mo spar mo gdengs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9354: ha la rdo rje mgyogs byed ma ser skya rlung la zhon pa lcags kyu can /
NK025(ra)001:9355: ha la rdo rje gtum pa mo dmar ser spu gri dang snying thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9356: ha la rdo rje mdung thung ma dkar ser g.yas mdung thung dang g.yon sder mo /
NK025(ra)001:9357: ha la rdo rje glog 'gyu ma dmar ser glog zhags 'phen cing nam mkhar rgyu ba /
NK025(ra)001:9358: ha la rdo rje thog 'bebs ma dmar ser thog gi tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro zhing rgya mtsho skems pa /
NK025(ra)001:9359: ha la rdo rje spor byed ma dmar ser zhing chen zhal du gsol ba /
NK025(ra)001:9360: ha la rdo rje 'khrug byed ma dmar ser rdo
NK025(ra)001:9361: rje thogs nas ri rab rtse nas 'joms shing rgya
NK025(ra)001:9363: ha la rdo rje dbang phyug ma smug nag ral gri dang snying thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9364: ha la rdo rje ka ma la smug nag mdzub
NK025(ra)001:9365: mos ri rab g.yeng zhing rkang pas rgya mtsho 'khrug
NK025(ra)001:9366: pa / ha la rdo rje gsal bkra ma dmar ser nyi zla'i zhags pa 'phen pa /
NK025(ra)001:9367: ha la rdo rje kha bsgyur ma dmar ser dung gi dgo ba zhon cing rgya gram 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9368: ha la rdo rje kun sgrol ma dmar ljang ral
NK025(ra)001:9369: gri klad la bskor zhing sram dang chu byar sprul
NK025(ra)001:9370: pa / ha la rdo rje myos byed ma dmar ljang ra ro smyo rdzu can snying 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9371: ha la rdo rje khrag 'thung ma dmar ljang thod khrag gsol ba /
NK025(ra)001:9372: ha la rdo rje 'bar ma dmar ljang rin po che 'bar ba thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9373: ha la rdo rje mi bzad ma dmar ljang gnam
NK025(ra)001:9374: sa gnyis thags su 'thag tshul gyis thags khri la
NK025(ra)001:9375: thags 'thag pa / ha la rdo rje 'phrog byed ma dmar ljang lcags kyu dang tsit+ta thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9376: ha la rdo rje sgrol byed ma ser ljang tsit+ta thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9377: ha la rdo rje sna tshogs stobs ser ljang zhing gi rkang lag 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9378: ha la rdo rje yid 'phrog ma ser ljang na
NK025(ra)001:9379: chung gi tshul du bardzu ba'i bu mo tha mal
NK025(ra)001:9381: ha la rdo rje srog len ma ser ljang snying brgyus pa'i zhags pa 'phen pa /
NK025(ra)001:9382: ha la rdo rje bcud len pa ma ser smug zangs mchu can phyag mtshan med pa /
NK025(ra)001:9383: ha la rdo rje tshe 'dzin ma ser mo bse'i ga'u dmar po 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9384: ha la rdo rje dbang mo che ser smug seng+ge
NK025(ra)001:9385: dkar mo zhon nas nyi zla brgyus pa'i zhags pa
NK025(ra)001:9386: 'phen pa / ha la rdo rje dregs 'joms ma ser mo go gyon zhing gi phub 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9387: ha la rdo rje sdud byed ma ser mo lcags kyu 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9388: ha la rdo rje bla 'dzin ma ser mo lcags kyu thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9389: ha la rdo rje srog 'dzin ma ser smug lcags kyu'i phyag rgya can /
NK025(ra)001:9390: ha la rdo rje rtsa 'gro ma ser nag rtsa la 'dzul ba'i phyag rgya can /
NK025(ra)001:9391: ha la rdo rje gnas 'byin ma ser smug 'brug
NK025(ra)001:9392: gi sgra 'byin pas sa dgu gting nas 'joms tshul
NK025(ra)001:9393: zhal gdangs shing phyag mtshan mi mnga' ba /
NK025(ra)001:9394: ha la rdo rje gnas gtod ma ser mo 'degs pa'i phyag rgya can no //
NK025(ra)001:9395: nub tu bse'i mi mo drug cu ni /
NK025(ra)001:9397: rdo rje thogs 'bebs ma dmar nag thog chen 'bebs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9398: gardza rdo rje 'brug sgrog ma dmar nag 'brug chen chibs pa phyag mtshan mi mnga' ba /
NK025(ra)001:9399: gardza rdo rje char 'bebs ma dmar nag sprin gyi
NK025(ra)001:9400: slog pa gsol zhing sprin las bdud rtsi'i char 'bebs
NK025(ra)001:9401: pa / gardza rdo rje 'od 'gyed ma dmar nag 'ja' 'od spro zhing 'gyed pa /
NK025(ra)001:9402: gardza rdo rje gsal bkra ma dmar nag g.yu'i lan phran can 'od 'phro zhing nyi ma 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9403: gardza rdo rje 'ja' tshon ma dmar nag 'ja' zhags thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9404: gardza rdo rje 'od 'phro ma dmar nag nyi zer 'phro ba /
NK025(ra)001:9405: gardza rdo rje 'od gsal ma dmar nag me dpung bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9406: gardza rdo rje khrag 'thung ma dmar nag thod khrag 'thung ba /
NK025(ra)001:9407: gardza rdo rje dbang phyug ma dmar nag rdo rje dang pad+ma bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9408: gardza rdo rje sa bdag ma dmar sngo lcags kyu phag mgo thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9409: gardza rdo rje 'gugs byed ma dmar sngo lcags kyu thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9410: gardza rdo rje dkar sham ma dkar sngo bse'i ga'u can /
NK025(ra)001:9411: gardza rdo rje sgra sgrog ma dmar sngo zhing gi rnge'u chung brdung ba /
NK025(ra)001:9412: gardza rdo rje yid gzhungs ma dmar sngo lag gnyis khu tshur 'chang ba /
NK025(ra)001:9413: gardza rdo rje lta na mdzes pa sngo dmar me tog gi chun 'phyang can /
NK025(ra)001:9414: gardza rdo rje sems 'phrog ma dmar sngo g.yu'i nyi ma bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9415: gardza rdo rje bdud 'bebs ma dmar sngo mi thod rta thod thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9416: gardza rdo rje mgyogs byed ma dmar sngo khyung chibs nyi ma bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9417: gardza rdo rje gsod rkyen ma dmar sngo seng zhon mdung thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9418: gardza rdo rje snying 'byin ma dmar ljang tsit+ta thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9419: gardza rdo rje dmar 'thung ma dmar ljang dung khrag 'thung ba /
NK025(ra)001:9420: gardza rdo rje rkang 'jib ma dmar ljang g.yi'i mgo can rkang dang bcud 'jibs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9421: gardza rdo rje las byed ma dmar ljang 'brug sngon chibs pa dung thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9422: gardza rdo rje zhags thogs ma sngon mo rlung la zhon pa zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9423: gardza rdo rje bla 'phrog ma dmar skya re ba'i
NK025(ra)001:9424: sham thabs can rlung la zhon pa b+han dmar thogs
NK025(ra)001:9425: pa / gardza rdo rje thogs med ma dmar ljang ral gri thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9426: gardza rdo rje za byed ma dmar ljang stag chen
NK025(ra)001:9427: sder mang la zhon pa thod khrag thogs shing gtsang
NK025(ra)001:9429: gardza rdo rje myos byed ma dmar ljang lcags kyi tho ba thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9430: gardza rdo rje rmugs byed ma dmar ljang lcags kyi d+r+wa ba thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9431: gardza rdo rje rdzu byed ma dmar ser ra skyes kham pa la zhon pa /
NK025(ra)001:9432: gardza rdo rje 'khrug byed ma dmar ser rgya mtsho hub kyis 'debs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9433: gardza rdo rje drag mo dmar ser dom la zhon pa /
NK025(ra)001:9434: gardza rdo rje skem ma dmar ser khrag gi lan phran can thod khrag /
NK025(ra)001:9435: gardza rdo rje dmar ser bya spang thi'i mgo can klad pa 'dral ba /
NK025(ra)001:9436: gardza rdo rje dmar ser zangs gri thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9437: gardza rdo rje 'dzin ma dmar ser sbrul nag gi zhags pa 'phen pa /
NK025(ra)001:9438: gardza rdo rje glog 'gyu ma dmar serardzu 'phrul gyi khra thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9439: gardza rdo rje g.yul 'joms ma dmar ser shak+ti thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9440: gardza rdo rje lha 'brel ma dmar ser rdo rje'i thog 'bebs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9441: gardza rdo rje srog 'brel ma dmar smug ka tar te ral gri 'phyar ba /
NK025(ra)001:9442: gardza rdo rje myur byed ma dmar smug glog gi ga sha can /
NK025(ra)001:9443: gardza rdo rje rengs byed ma mchong stabs can rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9444: gardza rdo rje srog byed ma dmar smug gri thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9445: gardza rdo rje glog byed ma dmar smug rdo rje'i be con 'phyar ba /
NK025(ra)001:9446: gardza rdo rje tho ba ma dmar smug rdo rje'i tho ba 'phyar ba /
NK025(ra)001:9447: gardza rdo rje gtum khung ma dmar smug gtun khung thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9448: gardza rdo rje zhags 'phen ma dmar smug bdud zhags thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9449: gardza rdo rje me khyer ma dmar smug dur khrod kyi me chen bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9450: gardza rdo rje sdud byed ma dmar smug gser gyi phreng ba thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9451: gardza rdo rje g.yengs byed ma dmar skya rlung gi 'khor lo thogs te ri rab g.yeng ba /
NK025(ra)001:9452: gardza rdo rje bdud 'joms ma dmar skya gtun shing dang tho ba thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9453: gardza rdo rje dpal mo dmar skya srid pa'i dpal
NK025(ra)001:9454: 'phrog par byed pa'i lcags kyu dang par bu bsnams
NK025(ra)001:9455: pa gser g.yu'i na bza' gsol ba /
NK025(ra)001:9456: gardza rdo rje dbang phyug ma dmar mo rdo rje rtse gsum dang thod khrag 'thung ba /
NK025(ra)001:9457: gardza rdo rje grags pa mo dmar skya mi mgo'i dung 'bud pa /
NK025(ra)001:9458: gardza rdo rje gtum bag can dmar nag mi snying bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9459: gardza rdo rje k+ai la ya dmar skya phur bu thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9460: gardza rdo rje bde tshogs ma dmar mo khrag char 'bebs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9461: gardza rdo rje ha la'i gdong dmar nag bdud rtsi bu ma pa 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9462: gardza rdo rje rab brjid ma dmar nag mi mgo
NK025(ra)001:9463: skam rlon rnying gsum gyi phreng ba bgrang zhing klad
NK025(ra)001:9464: la bskor ba'o // byang du g.yu'i mi mo drug cu ni /
NK025(ra)001:9465: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+de hoh rdo rje ma ljang sngon rgya gram 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9466: pa tsa rdo rje 'joms chen ma ljang sngon khyung khra thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9467: pa tsa rdo rje 'dul mdzad ma ljang sngon dred kyi g.yang gzhi rdeb pa /
NK025(ra)001:9468: pa tsa rdo rje dbang phyug ma ljang sngon thod rlon khrag bkang 'dzin pa g.yag la zhon pa /
NK025(ra)001:9469: pa tsa rdo rje grub byed ma ljang sngon mi mgo'i dung 'bud pa /
NK025(ra)001:9470: pa tsa rdo rje skul byed ma ljang sngon snyan pa'i glu len pa /
NK025(ra)001:9471: pa tsa rdo rje grub pa mo ljang sngon g.yu'i 'khor lo 'chang ba /
NK025(ra)001:9472: pa tsa rdo rje mthar phyin ma ljang smug g.yu'i thor tshugs can rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9473: pa tsa rdo rje mthar 'dod ma ljang smug rdo rje rgya gram thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9474: pa tsa rdo rje chud mi za ljang sngon dung gi mche ba 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9475: pa tsa rdo rje dbang sgyur ma ljang dmar chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9476: pa tsa rdo rje thogs med ma ljang dmar khyung zhon ral gri dang mdung dmar thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9477: pa tsa rdo rje grub pa mo dmar ljang shel gyi za ma tog bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9478: pa tsa rdo rje gsal byed ma dmar ljang me'i zhags pa 'phen pa /
NK025(ra)001:9479: pa tsa rdo rje dbang byed ma dmar ljang rdo
NK025(ra)001:9480: rje'i lcags kyu 'dzin pa spra dang byi la'i sprul
NK025(ra)001:9481: pa 'gyed pa / pa tsa rdo rje dam tshig
NK025(ra)001:9482: ma dmar ljang me'i zhags pa dang sdigs mdzub can
NK025(ra)001:9483: pa 'gyed pa / / pa tsa rdo rje bya
NK025(ra)001:9484: ra ma dmar ljang lcags kyi bya khra g.yu mig
NK025(ra)001:9485: can gyi mgo bya ra byed tshul /
NK025(ra)001:9486: pa tsa rdo rje stangs 'dzin ma dmar ljang rtsis kyi byang bu thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9487: pa tsa rdo rje stangs gcod ma dmar ljang rtsis kyi khram bam thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9488: pa tsa rdo rje gsal 'dzin ma dmar ljang rgyal 'pham 'byed pa'i sho rde'u 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9489: pa tsa rdo rje bskul byed ma ljang ser lcags kyi mda' 'phen pa /
NK025(ra)001:9490: pa tsa rdo rje dbang mo ljang ser khrag gi phor pa thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9491: pa tsa rdo rje phag mgo ma ljang ser phag mgo dang tho ba 'phyar ba /
NK025(ra)001:9492: pa tsa rdo rje spyan brgya ma ljang ser mgo
NK025(ra)001:9493: lus med par mig gis gang ba mda' gzhu 'geng
NK025(ra)001:9494: ba / pa tsa rdo rje pho nya mig stong
NK025(ra)001:9495: ldan ljang ser dbu stong phyag stong spyan stong can
NK025(ra)001:9497: pa tsa rdo rje 'od mgyogs ma ljang ser lus las 'ja' 'od 'gyed pa me long thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9498: pa tsa rdo rje rlung zhon ma ljang ser lag
NK025(ra)001:9499: na lcags kyi dgra s+t+wa bsnams pa rlung nag 'tshub
NK025(ra)001:9500: ma chibs pa / pa tsa rdo rje rdzu 'phrul
NK025(ra)001:9501: can ljang ser sbrul nag stong ga zhags pa 'phen
NK025(ra)001:9502: zhing rnga mo gwa pa la zhon pa /
NK025(ra)001:9503: pa tsa rdo rje rgyu ba mo chu srin gyi
NK025(ra)001:9504: mgo bo sbrul gyi lus can spu gri thogs pa
NK025(ra)001:9505: / pa tsa rdo rje dbang phyug rgyal ljang ser mdung rtse gsum 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9506: pa tsa rdo rje grags rgyal ma ljang nag dred mgo can stag la zhon pa gri thod /
NK025(ra)001:9507: pa tsa rdo rje dpal sham ma ljang nag dmar
NK025(ra)001:9508: gtor klad la bskor zhing zhags pa ltar 'phen pa
NK025(ra)001:9509: / pa tsa rdo rje yak+sha mo ljang nag gnod sbyin gyi mgo thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9510: pa tsa rdo rje khro bag can ljang gu bud
NK025(ra)001:9511: med kyi gzugs la skyes pa'i mgo bo can zhi
NK025(ra)001:9512: khro spel mar ston pa gri thod can /
NK025(ra)001:9513: pa tsa rdo rje mche ba mo ljang gu lag gnyis rdo rje'i mche ba 'debs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9514: pa tsa rdo rje dbang bskur ma ljang gu rda rje go cha'i phyag rgya can /
NK025(ra)001:9515: pa tsa rdo rje dngos grub bdag ljang nag 'dod yon lnga'i longs spyod kyi gzhong pa 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9516: pa tsa rdo rje sgrol byed ma ljang nag phal tshab ste gri bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9517: pa tsa rdo rje mnga' bdag mo ljang nag srid gsum du grags pa'i rnge'u chung brdung ba /
NK025(ra)001:9518: pa tsa rdo rje 'od 'phro ma ljang nag shak+ti thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9519: pa tsa rdo rje drag mo ljang smug gru gsum mthing nag thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9520: pa tsa rdo rje khro rkyen ma ljang smug ral pa sa la rdeb pa /
NK025(ra)001:9521: pa tsa rdo rje myur grub ma ljang smug ral gri thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9522: pa tsa rdo rje chud mi za ljang smug rin chen sgron me thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9523: pa tsa rdo rje 'dul byed ma ljang smug srin po'i thod pa thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9524: pa tsa rdo rje rgya mtsho ma sna tshogs lus can rgya mtsho skyom pa /
NK025(ra)001:9525: pa tsa rdo rje ltung 'dzin ma ljang smug zhing bcu dmyal ba nas 'dren pa'i lcags kyu can /
NK025(ra)001:9526: pa tsa rdo rje sgrol byed ma dmar smug ri rab 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9527: pa tsa rdo rje rang dbang mo ljang nag g.yu'i zhags pa 'debs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9528: pa tsa rdo rje 'dul mkhan ma ljang gu na chung chas bzang ste bu mo mdzes tshul /
NK025(ra)001:9529: pa tsa rdo rje goms pa mo ljang gu yungs kar mda' ltar 'phen pa /
NK025(ra)001:9530: pa tsa rdo rje las mkhan ma ljang skya mtshe zor 'phen pa /
NK025(ra)001:9531: pa tsa rdo rje dbang bsgyur ma ljang gu nyi
NK025(ra)001:9532: zla gza' skar slog par gyon zhing gling bzhi lag
NK025(ra)001:9533: par thogs pa / pa tsa rdo rje mchog sgrol ma ljang skya mi snying 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9534: pa tsa rdo rje rgyug 'dzin ma ljang skya shel dang lung thang gi phreng ba 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9535: pa tsa rdo rje rngams pa mo ljang skya sha khrag rlon par za ba /
NK025(ra)001:9536: pa tsa rdo rje spro rkyen ma ljang skya 'debs pa'i phyag rgya can /
NK025(ra)001:9537: pa tsa rdo rje gtum chen ma ljang skya nyi zla'i 'khor lo 'phen pa /
NK025(ra)001:9538: pa tsa rdo rje mig dmar ma ra gdong ljang skya khrag chang gi thod pa thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9539: pa tsa rdo rje sen mo can dmar smug sen mo lcags kyus gtams pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:9540: pho nya de dag thams cad kyang skra bardzesa pa /
NK025(ra)001:9544: rus pa'i phyag rgya lnga sogs khro mo'i chas thams cad dang ldan pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:9545: khyams 'di ni mgyogs 'gro yid kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK025(ra)001:9546: dkyil 'khor dgu pa'i khyams la ma mo drug cu ni /
NK025(ra)001:9547: shar du ma ma shwa ra h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:9548: ma mo ral gcig ma mthing nag zhal gcig phyag bzhi 'jigs gzugs can /
NK025(ra)001:9549: g.yas gnyis tri shu la dang ral gri /
NK025(ra)001:9550: g.yon gnyis gri gug dang nad rkyal can dre'u rta rkang gsum la zhon pa /
NK025(ra)001:9551: mi lpags dang glang chen gyi ko bas stod g.yogs
NK025(ra)001:9552: shing re lde'i sham thabs sogs lha mo spyi ltar
NK025(ra)001:9553: rgyan chas brjid pa ral pa can no //
NK025(ra)001:9554: ma ma ma mo thal mdog ma thod khrag 'thung
NK025(ra)001:9555: ba zhing g.yang sogs dur khrod kyi chas ldan no
NK025(ra)001:9556: // ma ma ma mo ral pa can mi thod
NK025(ra)001:9557: kyi phreng bas rgyan pa mi'i thod pa thogs pa
NK025(ra)001:9558: // / ma ma ma mo za byed rngam chen
NK025(ra)001:9559: mo mthing skya khrag ral gos su gyon pa tsit+ta
NK025(ra)001:9560: // / bzung ba / ma ma ma mo chen mo dmar mo thod khrag 'thung ba /
NK025(ra)001:9561: ma ma ma mo rgyud drug sgrol ba mo smug
NK025(ra)001:9562: nag me 'bar ba mi'i g.yang gzhi gyon zhing mi
NK025(ra)001:9563: snying brgyus pa'i phreng ba klad pa bskor ba /
NK025(ra)001:9564: ma ma ma mo srid gsum za byed dmar nag
NK025(ra)001:9565: gnam sa gnyis gos su gyon zhing thod khrag thogs
NK025(ra)001:9566: pa / ma ma ma mo srid gsum dbang sgyur
NK025(ra)001:9567: ma ser nag nyi zla'i thod can gri thod thogs
NK025(ra)001:9568: pa / pa / ma ma ma mo mthu bsnyems
NK025(ra)001:9569: ma ljang nag zhing gi go zu gsol ba g.yas
NK025(ra)001:9571: ma ma ma mo khros ma khrag 'thung ma dmar nag mi rta'i sha za zhing khrag 'thung ba /
NK025(ra)001:9572: ma ma ma mo sgrol byed ma mthing nag nang khrol dang glog snying thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9573: ma ma ma mo za byed tshe 'phrog ma sngo nag g.yu'i za ma tog bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9574: ma ma ma mo rngams byed 'phyo dga' ma dmar nag 'brug zhon snying thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9575: ma ma ma mo 'dzin byed ma ser nag lcags kyu dang thod khrag stob pa /
NK025(ra)001:9576: ma ma ma mo bgegs 'joms ma sngo nag spu gri dang tho ba thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9577: lhor ma ma shwa ra h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:9578: ma mo zhing bcu sgrol byed ma ljang nag gri dang b+han+d+ha thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9579: ma ma ma mo chad pa gcod pa mo sngo nag zhing g.yang sdeb pa /
NK025(ra)001:9580: ma ma ma mo 'byung po sgrol byed ma nag mo gri dang b+han+d+ha thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9581: ma ma ma mo gshin rje sgrol byed ma nag mo gri b+han thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9582: ma ma ma mo klu sgrol chen mo dmar mo gri b+han thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9583: ma ma ma mo gnod sbyin sgrol byed ma ljang nag gri b+han thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9584: ma ma ma mo srin mo sgrol byed ma sngo nag gri b+han thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9585: ma ma ma mo srin mo grol byed ma smug nag gri b+han thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9586: ma ma ma mo gzugs dbang ma dkar mo zhing dbyug bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9587: ma ma ma mo khrag dbang ma sngon mo thod khrag bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9588: ma ma ma mo drod dbang ma dmar mo tsit+ta thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9589: ma ma ma mo dbugs dbang ma ljang nag thod khrag dang zhags pa thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9590: ma ma ma mo bkrag dbang ma ser nag gri dang thod khrag thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9591: ma ma ma mo srog dbang ma smug nag gri dang thod khrag bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9592: ma ma ma mo khrang 'thung ma bya rgod mgo ser ljang ral gri dang thod khrag 'thung ba /
NK025(ra)001:9593: nub tu ma ma shwa ra h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:9594: ma mo za byed ma stag mgo dmar ser thod khrag 'thung ba /
NK025(ra)001:9595: ma ma ma mo 'jigs byed ma chu srin mgo ljang nag sha khrag gi gsur snod thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9596: ma ma ma mo dur khrod rgyan nag mo mi lpags rlon pa gsol zhing thod khrag thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9597: ma ma ma mo rdo rje gar dbang ma dmar
NK025(ra)001:9598: mo dbu brgya spyan stong ma thod khrag thogs pa
NK025(ra)001:9599: / ma ma ma mo pad+ma gar dbang ma dmar
NK025(ra)001:9600: mo mi mgo'i phor par mi snying dang tshil bu
NK025(ra)001:9601: / gsol ba / ma ma ma mo pad+ma phreng dmar nag b+han+d+ha khrag bkang bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9602: ma ma ma mo srid gsum mnga' bdag ma nag mo ri rab brnyil zhing rgya mtsho rnyog pa /
NK025(ra)001:9603: ma ma ma mo rgya mtsho gling dbang mo nag
NK025(ra)001:9604: mo chu srin gyi pags pa gsol zhing sbrul nag
NK025(ra)001:9605: stong gi gdengs ka can thod pa bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9606: ma ma ma mo tho ba mo sngo nag tho ba thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9607: ma ma ma mo rdo rje gtun khung ma mthing nag dgra bo gtun du brdung ba /
NK025(ra)001:9608: ma ma ma mo rdo rje dur khrod bdag sngo
NK025(ra)001:9609: nag mi mgos mtshan pa'i rdo rje'i dbyug pa gdengs
NK025(ra)001:9610: pa / ma ma ma mo rdo rje gdengs mo sngo nag rdo rje rtse gsum bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9611: ma ma ma mo rdo rje gsal bkra ma dmar nag rgyu zhags 'phen pa /
NK025(ra)001:9612: ma ma ma mo rdo rje khrag 'thung ma ljang ser b+han+d+ha rak+tasa bkang ba 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9613: ma ma ma mo nag mo drel zhon ma nad
NK025(ra)001:9614: rkyal gong du btags shing tshon gyi gru gu klad
NK025(ra)001:9615: la bskor ba / byang du ma ma shwa ra h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:9616: ma mo dus bzhi'i rgyal mo nag mo thod khrag thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9617: ma ma ma mo gnas myul ma nag mo spyang gdong mi sha za ba /
NK025(ra)001:9618: ma ma ma mo rdzu byed ma nag mo stag
NK025(ra)001:9619: mgo can thod khrag ma ma ma mo 'jums byed
NK025(ra)001:9620: ma khra mo 'jums par byed pa'i phyag rgya can
NK025(ra)001:9621: / ma ma ma mo gnam sa phyed bdag ma
NK025(ra)001:9622: nag mo ri klungs gzugs kyis khebs pa'i lag pa
NK025(ra)001:9624: ma ma ma mo rgyug byed ma dkar mo 'ja' gos can thod khrag thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9625: ma ma ma mo za byed ma ser mo stag
NK025(ra)001:9626: mgo can thod khrag thogs te gtsang rme med par
NK025(ra)001:9627: za tshul / ma ma ma mo rdo rje ya
NK025(ra)001:9628: byin dkar khra lcags kyu dang phur pa 'dzin pa
NK025(ra)001:9629: za tshul / / ma ma ma mo rdo rje
NK025(ra)001:9630: bse byin sngo nag zhags pa dang phur bu 'dzin
NK025(ra)001:9631: za tshul / / pa / ma ma ma mo
NK025(ra)001:9632: rdo rje phag byin dmar nag lcags sgrog dang phur
NK025(ra)001:9633: za tshul / / pa / bu thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9634: ma ma ma mo rdo rje de byin dbang grub
NK025(ra)001:9635: ma ljang nag dril bu dang phur bu 'phen pa
NK025(ra)001:9636: za tshul / / pa / bu thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9637: / ma ma ma mo sa bdag rgyal mo ser
NK025(ra)001:9638: nag gser gyi bum pa bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9639: ma ma ma mo phyi 'khor lo skyong ba'i bdag mo dkar mo rgyan cha mdzes tshul can /
NK025(ra)001:9640: ma ma ma mo 'phrog srin rgyal mo dmar nag
NK025(ra)001:9641: dar gos can prog zhu sogs rin po che'i rgyan
NK025(ra)001:9642: can / ma ma ma mo khro tshig myur ba'i
NK025(ra)001:9643: ma mo nag mo khrag ral can thod pa 'dzin
NK025(ra)001:9644: can / pa / de ltar ma mo drug cu
NK025(ra)001:9645: po thams cad kyang phyag rgya lnga dang thod skam
NK025(ra)001:9646: can / pa / gyi dbu rgyan / zhing g.yang gzig sham can rgyan dang ldan pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:9647: khyams 'di ni dam tshig chen po'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK025(ra)001:9648: dkyil 'khor bcu pa'i khyams la theg pa rim pa dgu'i lha tshogs thams cad rgyas par bskyed pa'am /
NK025(ra)001:9649: yang na 'dzab khang dbye ba'i don ltar bo d+hi
NK025(ra)001:9650: tsit+ta dang ru lu spel ma bzla zhing mos bskyed
NK025(ra)001:9651: bya / mtshams kyi khro bo rnams kyang don srung 'khor gyi mtshams mdzad pa'i lha yin kyang /
NK025(ra)001:9652: rdzas dgod dus 'dir bkod pa yin pas /
NK025(ra)001:9653: mngon rtogs bsgoms na legs te /
NK025(ra)001:9654: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:9656: shar stod du h+aum chen mthing skya 'khor lo dang thod dbyug thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9657: yum sgra 'byin ma sngon mo dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9658: badz+ra kro d+ha bi dz+aa ya h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:9659: ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:9660: shar smad du rnam rgyal dkar po rdo rje rtse lnga dang zhing dbyug bsnams pa /
NK025(ra)001:9661: yum snyems ma dkar mo dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9662: badz+ra kro d+ha n+ai la dan+da h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:9663: da ha da ha h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:9664: shar lhor dbyug sngon can mthing nag me dpung dang me lha'i spyi bo nas 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9665: yum sder mo mthing ga dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9666: badz+ra kro d+ha ya man+ta ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:9667: pa tsa pa tsa h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:9668: lhor gshin rje gshed ser nag be con dang gshin rje'i spyi bo nas 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9669: yum ro langs ma ser mo dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9670: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:9672: lho nub tu mi g.yo ba ljang nag ral gri dang srin po'i skra nas 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9673: yum gtun khung ma ljang nag dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9674: badz+ra kro d+ha h+ya g+r+ai ba h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:9675: hu lu hu lu h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:9676: nub stod du rta mgrin dmar nag zhing dbyug dang khyung gshog 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9677: yum gtum mo dmar mo dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9678: badz+ra kro d+ha +aa pa ra dz+ai ta h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:9680: nub byang du dpal ldan 'dod rgyal dmar ljang ba dan dang rlung lha'i skra nas 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9681: yum mda' snyems ma dmar ljang dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9682: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:9684: byang du bdud rtsi 'khyil pa ljang nag thod dbyug dang gnod sbyin gyi skra nas 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9685: yum rlung 'byin mo ljang nag dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9686: badz+ra kro d+ha tree lo kya bi dza ya h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:9688: byang shar du khams gsum rnam rgyal dkar po rdo rje dang 'byung po'i skra nas 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9689: yum gsod byed ma dkar mo dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba /
NK025(ra)001:9690: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa b+aa la h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:9691: s+pho ta ya s+pho ta ya h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:9692: nub smad du stobs po che dud kha thong gshol dang ti ra'i dbyug pa 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9693: yum bskyod byed ma dud kha dung khrag stob pa dang 'khril ba ste /
NK025(ra)001:9694: khro bo rnams dur khrod kyi chas brgyad dang /
NK025(ra)001:9695: yum rnams phyag rgya lngas brgyan cing ye shes kyi me 'bar ba'i 'bus na bzhugs pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:9696: dkyil 'khor bcu gcig pa'i khyams la rig 'dzin bla ma rnams bskyed pa ni gsum ste /
NK025(ra)001:9697: dang po rdzogs chen gyi brgyud pa ni shar stod nas rim pa bzhin /
NK025(ra)001:9698: ma h+aa gu ru sh+aa r+ai ram g+ai li h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:9699: kun tu bzang po yab yum sngon po skyil krung
NK025(ra)001:9700: mnyam bzhag can rus pa dang rin po che'i rgyan
NK025(ra)001:9701: thams cad kyis brgyan te rin po che'i khri pad+ma
NK025(ra)001:9702: dang nyi zla'i gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9703: ma h+aa rdo rje sems dpa' dkar po rdo rje dang dril bu can /
NK025(ra)001:9704: ma h+aa gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje sngon po rdo rje dang sdigs mdzub can /
NK025(ra)001:9705: ma h+aa sprul sku dga' rab rdo rje sangs rgyas sprul sku'i cha byad can dkar po /
NK025(ra)001:9706: ma h+aa slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen pan+di ta'i cha byad can /
NK025(ra)001:9707: ma h+aa rgyal po d+ha he na ta lo dang /
NK025(ra)001:9708: ma h+aa de'i sras r+aa dza hasti gnyis grub thob kyi cha lugs /
NK025(ra)001:9709: ma h+aa sras mo wa ra ni btsun mo'i cha lugs /
NK025(ra)001:9710: ma h+aa klu rgyal 'jog po ser po sbrul mgo bdun pa smad sbrul 'khyil phyag chos 'chad /
NK025(ra)001:9711: ma h+aa sras mo gnod sbyin mo byang chub lha
NK025(ra)001:9712: mo sngon mo dar dang rin po che'i rgyan ldan
NK025(ra)001:9713: phyag g.yas mchog sbyin dang g.yon chos 'chad /
NK025(ra)001:9714: ma h+aa gzungs ma a ra li btsun mo'i cha byad /
NK025(ra)001:9715: ma h+aa slob dpon ak+sho b+h+yahpan+di ta'i cha byad /
NK025(ra)001:9716: ma h+aa slob dpon ku ku r+aa dza grub thob kyi chas khyi mo kha dog lngas bskor ba /
NK025(ra)001:9717: ma h+aa smad 'tshong ma bud+d+ha sa ma dang /
NK025(ra)001:9718: ma h+aa bud+d+ha sa m+aa ti gnyis btsun mo'i cha byad /
NK025(ra)001:9719: ma h+aa ma h+aa r+aa dza rgyal po'i cha lugs /
NK025(ra)001:9720: ma h+aa sras mo go ma de wi btsun mo'i cha byad can /
NK025(ra)001:9721: ma h+aa kha che'i mkhan po rab snang pan+di ta'i cha lugs /
NK025(ra)001:9722: ma h+aa d+harma r+aa dza grub thob kyi cha lugs /
NK025(ra)001:9723: ma h+aa +aa tsar+ya +aa lo ka pan+di ta'i cha byad can /
NK025(ra)001:9724: ma h+aa o rgyan gyi mkhan po d+ha he na grub thob kyi cha lugs /
NK025(ra)001:9725: ma h+aa khyi'i mkhan po phyi ma grub thob kyi cha lugs khyi mo mchan khung du bcug pa /
NK025(ra)001:9726: ma h+aa slob dpon ma h+aa r+aa dza pan+di ta'i cha lugs /
NK025(ra)001:9727: ma h+aa drang srong b+ha shi ta drang srong bgres
NK025(ra)001:9728: po ril pa spyi blugs can ras dkar gyi na
NK025(ra)001:9729: bza' gsol ba / ma h+aa smad 'tshong ma bdag nyid ma btsun mo'i cha lugs /
NK025(ra)001:9730: ma h+aa slob dpon n+aa ga rdzu na sangs rgyas
NK025(ra)001:9731: sprul sku'i cha byad sbrul gyi rgyab yol dang gdengs
NK025(ra)001:9732: ka can / ma h+aa de wa r+aa dza rgyal po'i cha byad can /
NK025(ra)001:9733: ma h+aa 'jam dpal bshes gnyen phyi ma pan+di ta'i cha byad can /
NK025(ra)001:9734: ma h+aa dge bsnyen legs pa +aa tsar+ya gzhon tshul mdzes ldan /
NK025(ra)001:9735: ma h+aa slob dpon sangs rgyas gsang ba pan+di ta 'khar gsil lhung bzed can /
NK025(ra)001:9736: ma h+aa 'dir go rim sna tshogs su gyur kyang
NK025(ra)001:9737: rdo rje'i glu gsung ba po rig 'dzin bco brgyad
NK025(ra)001:9738: kyang tshang ngo // ma h+aa slob dpon sh+r+ai sid+ha pan chen gyi cha lugs /
NK025(ra)001:9739: ma h+aa dge slong ma kun dga' mo rab byung chas /
NK025(ra)001:9740: ma h+aa slob dpon bi ma la mi tra pan+di ta'i cha byad can /
NK025(ra)001:9741: ma h+aa bee ro tsa na bod btsun pan zhwa sne ring gsol ba /
NK025(ra)001:9742: ma h+aa g.yu sgra snying po rgya ban na bza' dur smrig bsnams pa rgya zhwa gsol ba /
NK025(ra)001:9743: ma h+aa gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra rab byung chos 'chad kyi phyag rgya can /
NK025(ra)001:9744: ma h+aa sog po dpal gyi ye shes sngags pa
NK025(ra)001:9745: lcang lo can rnams a ti bye brag gi brgyud
NK025(ra)001:9746: pa'o // gnyis pa lung a nu'i brgyud pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:9747: ma h+aa kun bzang yab yum dang /
NK025(ra)001:9748: ma h+aa rdo rje sems dpa' gong bzhin /
NK025(ra)001:9749: ma h+aa longs sku zhi ba rigs lnga dkar ser dmar ljang ba /
NK025(ra)001:9754: skyabs sbyin gyi phyag rgya can /
NK025(ra)001:9755: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan can /
NK025(ra)001:9756: ma h+aa 'bras bu sprul sku khrag 'thung che mchog
NK025(ra)001:9757: he ru ka khro bo mthing nag rdo rje dang
NK025(ra)001:9758: thod khrag can dur khrod kyi chas ldan /
NK025(ra)001:9759: ma h+aa dam pa tog dkar lha'i bu dar dang rin po ches brgyan pa /
NK025(ra)001:9760: ma h+aa 'jam dbyangs dmar ser ral gri dang glegs bam /
NK025(ra)001:9761: ma h+aa spyan ras gzigs dkar po zhal gcig phyag bzhi'i dang po thal sbyar /
NK025(ra)001:9762: 'og ma gnyis shel phreng dang pad dkar /
NK025(ra)001:9763: ma h+aa phyag rdor mthing kha khro bo rdo rje dang sdigs mdzub can /
NK025(ra)001:9764: ma h+aa lha grags ldan phyogs skyong lha'i bu'i cha byad can /
NK025(ra)001:9765: ma h+aa gnod sbyin skar mda' gdong dkar ser prog
NK025(ra)001:9766: zhu thor tshugs rin chen rgyan ldan nor bu 'dzin
NK025(ra)001:9767: pa / ma h+aa srin po blo gros thabs ldan dud kha mgo dgu phyag thal sbyor /
NK025(ra)001:9768: ma h+aa klu rgyal 'jog po klu'i cha byad can /
NK025(ra)001:9769: ma h+aa li tsa b+ai dri med grags pa dge bsnyen cha lugs sam rab byung gzhon nu /
NK025(ra)001:9770: ma h+aa skal ldan rgyal po dzahrgyala po'i cha byad chos 'chad can /
NK025(ra)001:9771: ma h+aa slob dpon u pa r+aa dza grub thob kyi cha lugs /
NK025(ra)001:9772: ma h+aa rgyal po in+d+ra b+hu ti rgyal po'i cha byad can /
NK025(ra)001:9773: ma h+aa klu rgyal n+aa ga pu tri /
NK025(ra)001:9774: ma h+aa rgyal po gu h+ya pu tri /
NK025(ra)001:9775: ma h+aa rgyal po sing+ha pu tra rnams rgyal po'i cha byad can /
NK025(ra)001:9776: ma h+aa ku ku r+aa dza phyi ma grub thob kyi cha lugs /
NK025(ra)001:9777: ma h+aa slob dpon ro langs bde ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:9778: ma h+aa slob dpon rdo rje bzhad pa gnyis pan+di ta'i chas ldan /
NK025(ra)001:9779: ma h+aa za hor rgyal po pra hasti rgyal chas can /
NK025(ra)001:9780: ma h+aa slob dpon sh+aakya seng+ge /
NK025(ra)001:9782: ma h+aa sh+aakya pra b+ha gsum rab byung /
NK025(ra)001:9783: ma h+aa slob dpon d+ha na rak+shi ta dang /
NK025(ra)001:9784: ma h+aa slob dpon h+aum k+aa ra gnyis grub thob kyi cha lugs /
NK025(ra)001:9785: ma h+aa s+thi ra ma ti /
NK025(ra)001:9786: ma h+aa +aa tsar+ya bde ba gsal mdzad /
NK025(ra)001:9787: ma h+aa mdo mkhan d+har+m+aa bo d+hi /
NK025(ra)001:9788: ma h+aa mkhan po chos rgyal skyong /
NK025(ra)001:9789: ma h+aa bal po ba su d+ha ra /
NK025(ra)001:9790: ma h+aa rgya gar gtsug lag dpal dge /
NK025(ra)001:9791: ma h+aa bru sha'i mkhan po che btsan skyes drug po pan+di ta'i cha lugs so //
NK025(ra)001:9792: gsum pa rgyud ma h+aa yo ga'i brgyud pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:9793: ma h+aa kun tu bzang po /
NK025(ra)001:9794: ma h+aa rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas /
NK025(ra)001:9795: ma h+aa rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK025(ra)001:9797: ma h+aa ku ku r+aa dza /
NK025(ra)001:9798: ma h+aa rgyal po dzahrnamasa gong dang 'dra ba /
NK025(ra)001:9799: ma h+aa rgyal po sha tra pu tri /
NK025(ra)001:9800: ma h+aa o rgyan rgyal po sid+ha r+aa dzah ma
NK025(ra)001:9801: h+aa rgyal po u pa r+aa dza gsum rgyal po'i
NK025(ra)001:9802: cha byad / ma h+aa sras mo go ma de wi gong mtshungs /
NK025(ra)001:9803: ma h+aa mee tri ka m+aa la grub thob chas /
NK025(ra)001:9804: ma h+aa +aa tsar+ya dzi na mi tra /
NK025(ra)001:9805: ma h+aa slob dpon rdo rje bzhad pa /
NK025(ra)001:9806: ma h+aa slob dpon nyin byed seng ge /
NK025(ra)001:9807: ma h+aa slob dpon bde ba gsal mdzad /
NK025(ra)001:9808: ma h+aa slob dpon sh+aakya bo d+hi /
NK025(ra)001:9809: ma h+aa dge slong so kya de wa /
NK025(ra)001:9810: ma h+aa slob dpon sgeg pa rdo rje /
NK025(ra)001:9811: ma h+aa chos blon bde ba /
NK025(ra)001:9812: ma h+aa mkhan po chos rgyal skyong ste dgu po pan+di ta /
NK025(ra)001:9813: ma h+aa rgyud lung man ngag gsum gyi bka' babs
NK025(ra)001:9814: kyi chu bo thams cad gcig tu 'dus pa gnubs
NK025(ra)001:9815: chen sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che sngags 'chang
NK025(ra)001:9816: chas dbu skra li rog bgres nyams can /
NK025(ra)001:9821: ma h+aa zur chen sh+aaka 'byung bzhi /
NK025(ra)001:9822: dge mched bco lnga'i dang po thugs sras bzhi ni /
NK025(ra)001:9823: ma h+aa so ye shes dbang phyug /
NK025(ra)001:9824: ma h+aa sru legs pa'i sgron ma /
NK025(ra)001:9825: ma h+aa spa gor blon rje 'phags /
NK025(ra)001:9826: ma h+aa dan yon tan mchog /
NK025(ra)001:9828: ma h+aa gnubs khu lung pa yon tan rgya mtsho /
NK025(ra)001:9829: gsum pa sru'i slob ma mchog bzhi ni /
NK025(ra)001:9830: ma h+aa dbyar ston gsal byang /
NK025(ra)001:9831: ma h+aa rgya ston blo gros gzhon nu /
NK025(ra)001:9832: ma h+aa rgya ston sh+aakya mchog rab /
NK025(ra)001:9833: ma h+aa zhu ston bsod sh+aaka /
NK025(ra)001:9834: ma h+aa bzhi pa spa gor beg ston ye shes /
NK025(ra)001:9836: ma h+aa rgya ston gzhon nu snying po /
NK025(ra)001:9837: ma h+aa skyo ston dar ma byang chub /
NK025(ra)001:9840: ma h+aa skyon ston dar rgyal /
NK025(ra)001:9841: ma h+aa lho pa ston snying ste bco lnga /
NK025(ra)001:9844: bu bzhi dang dge mched bco lnga sngags 'chang chas /
NK025(ra)001:9845: rin chen gsum sogs phal cher sngags chas so //
NK025(ra)001:9846: de rnams ni ngo mtshar brgyud pa yin la /
NK025(ra)001:9848: ma h+aa gnubs khu lung pa yon tan rgya mtsho /
NK025(ra)001:9849: ma h+aa sras ye shes rgya mtsho /
NK025(ra)001:9850: ma h+aa rgya ston blo gros byang chub /
NK025(ra)001:9851: ma h+aa mar pa yon tan byang chub /
NK025(ra)001:9852: ma h+aa sna nam tshul khrims byang chub ste byang chub rnam gsum /
NK025(ra)001:9854: rgya ston blo gros byang chub kyi brgyud 'dzin rnam gnyis kyi zhu ston gong du song /
NK025(ra)001:9856: ma h+aa tho gar nam mkha' lde dge bsnyen bgres
NK025(ra)001:9857: po na bza' dkar po ldum ma dang ber phyam
NK025(ra)001:9858: gsol ba / dbu skra sbom sog g.yu can /
NK025(ra)001:9859: ma h+aa bstan pa'i rtsa lag bde gshegs zur po
NK025(ra)001:9860: che sh+aakya 'byung gnas rab byung thang zhu gsol ba
NK025(ra)001:9861: / de'i slob ma rtse mo bzhi /
NK025(ra)001:9863: sgom chen brgya rtsa sogs sngags 'chang dang rab byung sna tshogs /
NK025(ra)001:9865: ma h+aa lha rje zur chung pa shes rab grags sngags 'chang chas /
NK025(ra)001:9866: de'i slob ma ka ba bzhi gdung ma brgyad gdung
NK025(ra)001:9867: phran sum cu rtsa gnyis sogs thams cad kyang sngags
NK025(ra)001:9868: chas dang rab byung chas sna tshogs /
NK025(ra)001:9870: gsang bdag sgro phug pa sh+aakya seng+ge sngags 'chang chas /
NK025(ra)001:9871: de'i dngos slong gdugs thogs stong dang /
NK025(ra)001:9873: ma h+aa mgar ston zung nge dang /
NK025(ra)001:9874: ma h+aa sreg ston rdo rje rgyal mtshan gnyis sngags 'chang chas /
NK025(ra)001:9875: ma h+aa glan ban nya tshal pa rdo rje 'od bgres tshul li rog phu thung can /
NK025(ra)001:9876: ma h+aa glan ston brtson 'grus seng+ge rab byung /
NK025(ra)001:9877: ma h+aa glan ston bsod nams rgyal po /
NK025(ra)001:9878: ma h+aa glan ston sangs rgyas dpal /
NK025(ra)001:9879: ma h+aa sprul sku lha rje lha 'bum /
NK025(ra)001:9880: ma h+aa glan ston bsod nams mgon po /
NK025(ra)001:9881: ma h+aa nyang chen shes rab dpal ldan /
NK025(ra)001:9882: ma h+aa gyer khang pa gzi ston sh+aakya bzang /
NK025(ra)001:9883: ma h+aa sgrol chen 'bro ston bsam 'grub rdo rje /
NK025(ra)001:9884: ma h+aa zur thams cad mkhyen pa sh+aakya 'byung gnas /
NK025(ra)001:9885: ma h+aa lang gro sprul sku tshe dbang rgyal po /
NK025(ra)001:9886: ma h+aa brgyud 'dzin legs pa dpal bzang /
NK025(ra)001:9887: ma h+aa mkhas grub chen po lha rigs 'jam dbyangs
NK025(ra)001:9888: rin chen rgyal mtshan dpal bzang po rnams sngags 'chang
NK025(ra)001:9890: ma h+aa rig 'dzin mnga' ris pa chen po legs
NK025(ra)001:9891: ldan bdud 'joms rdo rje sngags 'chang gos dkar can
NK025(ra)001:9892: dbu ral dkar po rgyab bsnyil bgres tshul dbang phod
NK025(ra)001:9893: pad zhwa chos gos rnams gsol ba chos 'chad dang
NK025(ra)001:9894: glegs bam can / ngo mtshar brgyud pa la rig 'dzin rje'i dngos slob /
NK025(ra)001:9895: ma h+aa thams cad mkhyen pa mkhyen brtse'i dbang phyug dang /
NK025(ra)001:9896: ma h+aa rdo rje 'chang dbang phyug rab brtan gnyis
NK025(ra)001:9897: dge slong rdo rje 'dzin pad zhu dang chos gos
NK025(ra)001:9898: rdor dril can / ma h+aa rig 'dzin rje'i dngos
NK025(ra)001:9899: slob chos 'di'i rgyun spel ba po skyi ston tshe
NK025(ra)001:9900: ring dbang po sngags 'chang gos dkar lcang lo can
NK025(ra)001:9901: rdor dril can / / ma h+aa bla chen chos
NK025(ra)001:9902: rgyal rdo rje rab byung chas la ral pa'i thor
NK025(ra)001:9903: rdor dril can / / tshugs can / ma h+aa
NK025(ra)001:9904: dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i khyab bdag sman lung pa chen
NK025(ra)001:9905: po mkhas grub blo gros mchog gi rdo rje dge
NK025(ra)001:9906: slong rdo rje 'dzin pa bgres tshul ag tshom can
NK025(ra)001:9907: pad zhu gsol ba rdor dril chos 'chad kyis 'dzin
NK025(ra)001:9908: rdor dril can / / tshugs can / pa /
NK025(ra)001:9909: gzhan yang brgyud tshul gcig la rje sgro phug pa
NK025(ra)001:9910: rdor dril can / / tshugs can / pa / nas / ma h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:9914: ma h+aa mkhas btsun bsod rgyal /
NK025(ra)001:9918: ma h+aa kun dga' bzang po /
NK025(ra)001:9920: ma h+aa zur sh+aakya sh+r+ai dpal bzang /
NK025(ra)001:9921: ma h+aa zur sh+aakya bshes gnyen /
NK025(ra)001:9922: ma h+aa brgyud 'dzin legs pa dpal bzang /
NK025(ra)001:9923: ma h+aa chos rje chos 'phags bzang po /
NK025(ra)001:9924: ma h+aa 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan /
NK025(ra)001:9925: gzhan yang sh+aakya bshes gnyen nas /
NK025(ra)001:9926: ma h+aa slob dpon dpal bzang ba /
NK025(ra)001:9927: ma h+aa zur ham rgyal ba dpal bzang /
NK025(ra)001:9928: ma h+aa mnyam med 'jam dbyangs chen po sogs mdor
NK025(ra)001:9929: na rgya gar gyi pan grub rnams phal cher phyag
NK025(ra)001:9930: na dbang rtags rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:9931: bod kyi bla ma rab tu byung ba rnams chos
NK025(ra)001:9932: gos gsum ldan glegs bam chos 'chad rdor dril sogs
NK025(ra)001:9934: sngags 'chang rnams kyang la la zhwa phod sogs drag po'i chas su zhugs pa /
NK025(ra)001:9935: la la ral pa'i thor tshugs bcings pa dang grol
NK025(ra)001:9936: ba sogs b+han phur rak+sha rdor dril d+aa ma ru
NK025(ra)001:9938: mdor na rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i tshogs de rnams dang /
NK025(ra)001:9939: gzhan yang mdo sgyu sems gsum rgyud lung man ngag dang 'brel ba'i dbang bskur /
NK025(ra)001:9941: man ngag ston pa'i dus gsum rig 'dzin bla ma'i
NK025(ra)001:9942: tshogs thams cad kyang zhal lam mer mngon sum du
NK025(ra)001:9943: bzhugs par gyur / de ltar mdun bskyed rgyas par bskyed zin nas /
NK025(ra)001:9944: khro bo gsang bum lnga po'i lha rnams kyang dran par bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:9950: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+tasa brtan par bzhugs su gsol /
NK025(ra)001:9952: bdag mdun bum gsum lhan cig tu dbang bskur /
NK025(ra)001:9953: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab /
NK025(ra)001:9955: ye shes pa spyan drangs la bstim zhing brtan par
NK025(ra)001:9956: bya ba rnams yin par gong gi 'phros khro bo
NK025(ra)001:9957: dam pa rgyan ltar bya ba yin te /
NK025(ra)001:9958: lag gnyis rdo rje phyi bsdams las gung mo gnyis
NK025(ra)001:9959: sbyar te sgreng ba rdo rje'i phyag rgya rang gi
NK025(ra)001:9960: spyi bor bzhag cing dkyil 'khor phyogs su yang btud
NK025(ra)001:9961: la / ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:9962: rdo rje bsdams pa las 'dzub mo gnyis brkyang ba
NK025(ra)001:9963: dpral ba dang dkyil 'khor phyogs ma h+aa +aa dar+sha
NK025(ra)001:9964: dz+ny+aa na badz+ra rdo rje bsdams pa las srin lag
NK025(ra)001:9965: gnyis brkyang ba rna ltag g.yas dang dkyil 'khor phyogs
NK025(ra)001:9966: ma h+aa sa ma t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra rdo rje
NK025(ra)001:9967: bsdams pa las mthe bong gnyis brkyang ba ltag pa
NK025(ra)001:9968: dang dkyil 'khor phyogs ma h+aa pra t+ya bek+sha na
NK025(ra)001:9969: dz+ny+aa na badz+ra rdo rje bsdams pa las mathe'u chung
NK025(ra)001:9970: brkyang pa rna ltag g.yon dang dkyil 'khor phyogs /
NK025(ra)001:9971: ma h+aa kri t+y+aa nush+tha na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra bdag
NK025(ra)001:9972: mdun bum gsum gyi lha tshogs rnams kyi spyi gtsug
NK025(ra)001:9973: tu mi bskyod pa mthing kha /
NK025(ra)001:9974: dpral bar rnam snang dkar po /
NK025(ra)001:9975: rna ltag g.yas su rin chen 'byung ldan ser po /
NK025(ra)001:9976: ltag par snang ba mtha' yas dmar po /
NK025(ra)001:9977: rna ltag g.yon du don yod grub pa ljang gu
NK025(ra)001:9978: rnams kyis dbu brgyan pa ni rtags kyi dbang dang
NK025(ra)001:9979: / ye shes lnga'i don thugs rgyud la gnas pa ni don gyi dbang ngo //
NK025(ra)001:9980: sangs rgyas lnga yi cod pan can //
NK025(ra)001:9981: dbu rgyan rin chen phreng ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:9982: dpung rgyan se mo do la sogs //
NK025(ra)001:9983: mdzes pa'i rgyan rnams sna tshogs kyis //
NK025(ra)001:9984: dbang mchog tu ni dbang bskur ro //
NK025(ra)001:9985: gnyis pa sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:9986: bshad ma thag pa'i rdo rje'i phyag rgya de nyid
NK025(ra)001:9987: rang gi gnas gsum du sngags dang bstun gtug tshul
NK025(ra)001:9988: dang / dkyil 'khor du yang de bzhin du byas la /
NK025(ra)001:9989: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:9990: bdag mdun bum gsum gyi lha tshogs rnams kyi spyi bor zla ba la gnas pa'i dkar po /
NK025(ra)001:9992: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK025(ra)001:9993: sku rdo rje'i lha tshogs spyan drangs /
NK025(ra)001:9994: la thim pas sangs rgyas rnams kyi sku'i rang bzhin
NK025(ra)001:9995: las rnam snang dkar po 'khor lo dang dril bu
NK025(ra)001:9996: 'dzin par gyur / sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma
NK025(ra)001:9997: h+aa w+aa ka badz+ra mgrin par pad+ma la gnas pa'i
NK025(ra)001:9999: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs gsung rdo rje'i lha
NK025(ra)001:10000: tshogs +aahl thim pas sangs rgyas rnams kyi gsung gi
NK025(ra)001:10001: rang bzhin +aahls snang mtha' dmar po pad+ma dang dril
NK025(ra)001:10003: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra thugs kar nyi ma la gnas pa'i h+aum sngon po /
NK025(ra)001:10004: de las 'od sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs /
NK025(ra)001:10005: thugs rdo rje'i lha tshogs h+aum la thim pas sangs
NK025(ra)001:10006: rgyas rnams kyi thugs kyi rang bzhin h+aum las mi
NK025(ra)001:10007: bskyod pa mthing kha rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin
NK025(ra)001:10008: par gyur / drug pa spyan drang ba la gsum gyi dang po snyan gsan dbab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:10009: bdag mdun bum gsum gyi lha tshogs rnams kyi thugs
NK025(ra)001:10010: kar rang 'dra ba'i ye shes sems dpa'i thugs kar
NK025(ra)001:10011: dwangs ma'i srog h+aum mthing kha ye shes lnga'i rang
NK025(ra)001:10012: bzhin can las 'od zer gyi phreng ba phyogs bcur
NK025(ra)001:10013: 'bar zhing 'phros pas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rgyal ba
NK025(ra)001:10014: sras dang bcas pa rang bzhin sgyu 'phrul khro bo'i
NK025(ra)001:10015: dkyil 'khor 'khor lo'i bdag nyid can du gyur te
NK025(ra)001:10016: 'gro ba'i don la chas par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:10017: sa la sogs las phyag rgya byas //
NK025(ra)001:10018: rnam grol rim pa thob par 'gyur //
NK025(ra)001:10019: dag pa'i ye shes kyis sbyangs pas //
NK025(ra)001:10020: smos ci dgos te de nyid yin //
NK025(ra)001:10022: phyogs dus dkyil 'khor bdag nyid che //
NK025(ra)001:10023: mi dmigs thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK025(ra)001:10024: dkyil 'khor thams cad spyan drang ngo //
NK025(ra)001:10025: rang snang dbyer med dkyil 'khor la //
NK025(ra)001:10026: 'jug pa'i mtshan nyid mnyam sbyor bas //
NK025(ra)001:10027: phyogs dus kun nas gshegs pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:10028: bsnyen pa'i dkyil 'khor rab tu rdzogs //
NK025(ra)001:10029: nye bar gyur pa'i dam tshig mchog /
NK025(ra)001:10030: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10031: gnyis pa spyan drang ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:10032: e h+ye hi a na ya hoh dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes nam mkhar dkyil 'khor spyan drangs te /
NK025(ra)001:10033: gsum pa rig pa'i me tog dor ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:10034: ram badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10035: bzhi pa dngos grub bskul ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:10036: khro la khros pas zhi mdzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:10037: thugs rje khro dpal rngam pa'i tshogs //
NK025(ra)001:10038: 'bar ba'i byin rlabs rmad po che //
NK025(ra)001:10039: de nyid du ni bdag la stsol //
NK025(ra)001:10040: badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:10041: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya hoh badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya phata /
NK025(ra)001:10042: lnga pa drin lan du mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:10043: a li u li t+aa li ta p+aa li /
NK025(ra)001:10044: damsh+ta goo na ro dri kha ram yo gi n+ai
NK025(ra)001:10045: kh+aa hi hoh drug pa gnyis med du bstim pa
NK025(ra)001:10046: ni / sems can don phyir nan tan mchog bskyed nas //
NK025(ra)001:10047: ye shes thugs rjes bdag la dgongs nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:10048: mi dmigs don phyir dngos grub mchog gi rnams //
NK025(ra)001:10049: bdag la stsal zhing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:10050: ka ya wa ka tsit+ta badz+ra h'u ha he phata /
NK025(ra)001:10052: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sarba dush+tam sa
NK025(ra)001:10053: ma ya su tra yu trang pra b+han tsakra h+aum
NK025(ra)001:10054: phata / bdun pa bzhugs su gsol ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:10055: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK025(ra)001:10056: brgyad pa gdug pa can za ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:10057: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sarba dush+tam sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:10058: am sa tam pa ka ya h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:10059: badz+ra gu h+ya dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:10061: dgu pa ma mo dang mkha' 'gro khyung gshog gis zil gyis mnan pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:10062: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra
NK025(ra)001:10063: sarba dush+tam sa ma ya mu dra ma tram pra
NK025(ra)001:10064: b+han tsakra bag+sha ya bag+sha ya /
NK025(ra)001:10067: bcu pa dbang du bsdu ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:10068: b+h+au ta k+she tri pra ti t+aam pa ka la h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:10069: mchod pa la bco lnga'i dang po phyag gi mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:10072: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor chen po ru //
NK025(ra)001:10073: bsgrub dang gdug pa 'dul ba yi //
NK025(ra)001:10074: 'bar ba khro bo'i lha tshogs la //
NK025(ra)001:10075: sgo gsum gus pas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:10083: glu ye shes rnams dbyangs dang bcas pas dbul /
NK025(ra)001:10084: rgya mtsho lnga'i smon lam gdab po //
NK025(ra)001:10085: zhes gsungs pa'i don phyag 'tshal 'dir ltar grub rjes /
NK025(ra)001:10086: bdag med phyogs bral don dam thugs chud cing //
NK025(ra)001:10087: byams dang snying rje dgra zun mi mnga' yang //
NK025(ra)001:10088: gdug pa 'dul phyir dus las mi 'da' ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:10089: 'jigs byed he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:10090: srid gsum 'joms pa'i lha la mnyam nyid ngang gis
NK025(ra)001:10091: khro la khro bo longs spyod mdzad la rdo rje
NK025(ra)001:10092: 'du 'phro khro la mi gnas mi dmigs chos skur
NK025(ra)001:10093: dag pa la // bdud 'dul khro bo mchog gi skur ston pa //
NK025(ra)001:10094: thugs rje gzi ldan gdug pa thabs kyis 'dul //
NK025(ra)001:10095: bcom ldan khro rgyal sku la thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK025(ra)001:10096: khro mo dbang phyug sku la 'khril mdzad cing //
NK025(ra)001:10097: mkha' 'gro mi zad 'bar ba'i sprin 'phro ma //
NK025(ra)001:10098: gdug pa 'dul mdzad yum la nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing //
NK025(ra)001:10099: 'dod rgur bsgyur pa'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK025(ra)001:10100: ma sring byams pa'i tshul gyis grogs mdzad ma //
NK025(ra)001:10101: phyi nang mkha' 'gro'i tshogs a ti pu hoh pra
NK025(ra)001:10102: ti pu hoh bde bar gshegs pa ci 'dra bar
NK025(ra)001:10103: // de 'dra kho nar bdag gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:10104: spyod pa rmad byung bsam yas pa //
NK025(ra)001:10105: 'gro la phan phyir bdag gis spyad //
NK025(ra)001:10106: byang chub sems mchog dam pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:10107: sku gsung thugs kyi phyag rgya 'di //
NK025(ra)001:10108: srog gi phyir yang mi gtong na //
NK025(ra)001:10109: rdo rje rgyal por byin brlabs mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:10111: sangs rgyas mdzad dka' bdag gis bsgrub //
NK025(ra)001:10112: byang chub spyad dka' bdag gis spyad //
NK025(ra)001:10114: bdag cag bsam pa 'grub gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:10115: gnyis pa phyag rgya'i mchod pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:10116: he ru ka yi gal po dang //
NK025(ra)001:10117: gsang ba snying po'i rgyud dag las //
NK025(ra)001:10118: rnam par grol ba mtshon pa'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:10119: dbus kyi khro bo'i phyag rgya ni //
NK025(ra)001:10120: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK025(ra)001:10121: rtse dgu rtse lnga ti ra g.yas //
NK025(ra)001:10122: dril bu dung dmar 'jig rten g.yon //
NK025(ra)001:10123: dpal chen badz+ra thabs kyi rgya //
NK025(ra)001:10124: shes rab yum gyi phyag rgya ni //
NK025(ra)001:10125: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog mthing //
NK025(ra)001:10126: g.yas pa shes rab thabs la 'khyud //
NK025(ra)001:10127: g.yon pa dung dmar gtso la stob //
NK025(ra)001:10128: kro d+hi shwa r+ai dbyings kyi rgya //
NK025(ra)001:10129: yab yum 'bar ba'i gdan la bzhengs nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:10130: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa 'di 'bul gyi //
NK025(ra)001:10131: mchod bzhes dam skongs mthu dbang dngos grub stsol //
NK025(ra)001:10132: shar gyi khro bo'i phyag rgya ni //
NK025(ra)001:10133: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus smug zhal //
NK025(ra)001:10134: 'khor lo rdo rje ti ra g.yas //
NK025(ra)001:10135: dril bu dung dmar tri sh+aul g.yon //
NK025(ra)001:10136: dpal chen bud+d+ha thabs shes rab yum ni sku mdog smug /
NK025(ra)001:10137: g.yas pa shes rab thabs la 'khyud //
NK025(ra)001:10138: g.yon pa dung badz+ra shwa r+ai yab yum phyag rgya
NK025(ra)001:10139: mchod bzhes lho yi khro bo'i phyag g.yas sngo g.yon
NK025(ra)001:10141: rin chen rdo rje ti ra g.yas //
NK025(ra)001:10142: dril bu dung dmar dgra s+t+wa g.yon //
NK025(ra)001:10143: dpal chen rat+na thabs shes rab yum gyi phyag rgya ni //
NK025(ra)001:10144: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog ser //
NK025(ra)001:10145: g.yas pa shes rab thabs g.yon pa dung rat+na shwa
NK025(ra)001:10146: r+ai yab yum phyag rgya mchod bzhes nub kyi khro
NK025(ra)001:10147: bo'i phyag g.yas dkar g.yon ser dbus dmar zhal //
NK025(ra)001:10148: pad+ma rdo rje ti ra g.yas //
NK025(ra)001:10149: dril bu dung ma rnga chung g.yon //
NK025(ra)001:10151: shes rab yum gyi phyag zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog dmar //
NK025(ra)001:10152: g.yas pa shes rab thabs g.yon pa dung pad+ma shwa
NK025(ra)001:10153: r+ai yab yum phyag rgya mchod bzhes byang gi khro
NK025(ra)001:10154: bo'i phyag g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus ljang zhal //
NK025(ra)001:10155: ral gri rdo rje ti ra g.yas //
NK025(ra)001:10156: dril bu dung dmar thong gshol g.yon //
NK025(ra)001:10157: dpal chen karma thabs shes rab yum gyi phyag zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog ljang //
NK025(ra)001:10158: g.yas pa shes rab thabs g.yon pa dung karma shwa
NK025(ra)001:10159: r+ai yab yum phyag rgya mchod bzhes dkyil 'khor de
NK025(ra)001:10161: bcom ldan dpal chen he ru la //
NK025(ra)001:10162: koo r+ai tshogs kyis bskor ba ni //
NK025(ra)001:10163: koo r+ai sngon mo byis dbyug sngo //
NK025(ra)001:10164: tsoo r+ai mda' gzhu 'gengs ma ser //
NK025(ra)001:10165: pra mo chu srin rgyal mtshan 'phyar //
NK025(ra)001:10166: be ta byis za rdor 'phyar nag /
NK025(ra)001:10169: sme sha mthing nag byis snying za //
NK025(ra)001:10171: khro mo goo r+ai ma brgyad rnams //
NK025(ra)001:10172: 'bar ba'i gdan las bzhengs nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:10173: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa 'di 'bul gyi //
NK025(ra)001:10174: mchod bzhes dam skongs mthu dbang dngos grub stsol //
NK025(ra)001:10175: dkyil 'khor de yi phyi bcom ldan dpal chen sing+ha'i tshogs kyi sid+ha kha ro snol ser seng //
NK025(ra)001:10176: b+y+aa g+h+ri mnan ltag snol mar stag /
NK025(ra)001:10177: sri la nag mo byis bldag wa //
NK025(ra)001:10178: shwa na 'dral s+t+wa mthing kha spyang //
NK025(ra)001:10179: g+r+ai d+ha mgrin dmar rgyu 'dren rgod //
NK025(ra)001:10180: kam ka zhing phrag snar mchu ring //
NK025(ra)001:10181: k+aa ka kha rog b+han gri nag /
NK025(ra)001:10182: u lu rdo rgyu mthing tshogs 'ug /
NK025(ra)001:10183: sing+ha chen po brgyad rnams kyang //
NK025(ra)001:10184: 'bar ba'i phyag rgya mchod bzhes dkyil 'khor de yi
NK025(ra)001:10185: bcom ldan dpal chen sgo ma'i tshogs kyis rta gdong
NK025(ra)001:10187: phag gdong nag mo mche zhags sdom //
NK025(ra)001:10188: lcags sgrog dmar mo nyi zla spyan //
NK025(ra)001:10189: thal byed dril bu sna tshogs mdog /
NK025(ra)001:10190: sgo ma chen mo bzhi rnams kyang //
NK025(ra)001:10191: 'bar ba'i phyag rgya mchod bzhes dkyil 'khor de yi
NK025(ra)001:10192: bcom ldan dpal chen dbang mo'i tshogs kyis 'jig rten
NK025(ra)001:10194: ci bgyi'i bka' nyan pho nya'i tshogs //
NK025(ra)001:10195: ma mo rnams kyi phyag rgya ni //
NK025(ra)001:10196: srin mo smug nag thod rlon 'chang //
NK025(ra)001:10198: lha chen dkar ljang tri sh+au la //
NK025(ra)001:10200: gzhon nu dmar mo mdung thung 'phen //
NK025(ra)001:10201: brgya byin dkar mo in+d+ra gdengs //
NK025(ra)001:10203: bdud rtsi dmar mo pad+ma bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:10204: zla ba dkar mo pun+d+ra ri //
NK025(ra)001:10205: be con ljang nag dbyug to 'phyar //
NK025(ra)001:10206: srin mo dmar mo dung khrag 'thung //
NK025(ra)001:10207: za ba ljang nag ba su 'dren //
NK025(ra)001:10208: dga' ba dmar mo ka tar 'phyar //
NK025(ra)001:10209: stobs chen dkar mo gshol mda' 'dzin //
NK025(ra)001:10210: rdo rje ser nag spu gris gcod //
NK025(ra)001:10212: nor srung dkar mo bum pa 'dzin //
NK025(ra)001:10213: rlung lha sngon mo ba dan 'phyar //
NK025(ra)001:10214: gsod byed nag mo ral gri'i so //
NK025(ra)001:10215: mi mo dmar mo gsal shing 'phyar //
NK025(ra)001:10216: phag mo nag mo mche zhags can //
NK025(ra)001:10217: rgan byed dmar mo zhing chung za //
NK025(ra)001:10218: sna chen dkar mo thod khrag 'thung //
NK025(ra)001:10219: chu lha sngon mo sbrul zhags 'dzin //
NK025(ra)001:10220: rdo rje nag mo lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK025(ra)001:10221: rdo rje ser mo ra mgo zhags //
NK025(ra)001:10222: rdo rje dmar mo lcags sgrog sdom //
NK025(ra)001:10223: rdo rje ljang nag dril 'khrol dgyes //
NK025(ra)001:10224: dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad rnams kyang //
NK025(ra)001:10225: 'bar ba'i phyag rgya mchod bzhes gsum pa kun tu bzang po'i mchod pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:10226: bde bar gshegs so khro rgyal gtso //
NK025(ra)001:10227: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i ye shes kyis //
NK025(ra)001:10228: srid pa'i rgya mtsho mtha' yas kun //
NK025(ra)001:10229: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK025(ra)001:10230: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi shwa mu
NK025(ra)001:10231: khe b+h+yahsarba th+aa kham ung+ga te s+pha ra na hi
NK025(ra)001:10232: mam ga ga na kham sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa
NK025(ra)001:10233: / bzhi pa phyag zhabs bsil ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:10234: yang dag don du dag mod kyang //
NK025(ra)001:10235: 'gro ba yongs kyi don slad du //
NK025(ra)001:10236: phyag dang zhabs gnyis bsil nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:10237: rdo rje gdan la bzhugs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:10238: +aa ha ra +aa ha ra sarba bid+ya d+h+aa ra
NK025(ra)001:10239: p+au dzi te na mahs man+ta bud+d+ha nam ga ga
NK025(ra)001:10240: na kham sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:10241: lnga pa lha mo bzhi bsnol gyi mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:10244: ti pu pa ra muh sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid d+hoo /
NK025(ra)001:10245: sa ma yo ta muh sarba ma h+aa su kha sid d+ho /
NK025(ra)001:10246: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au /
NK025(ra)001:10247: pa na pem sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga push+pe pu /
NK025(ra)001:10248: pa na pem sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga +aa lo ke
NK025(ra)001:10249: h+r+aih pa na pem sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga gan+d+he gan
NK025(ra)001:10251: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:10252: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam tshig dam pa grub par mdzod /
NK025(ra)001:10254: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:10255: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam tshig dam pa dag cing grub par mdzad du gsol /
NK025(ra)001:10257: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:10258: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mchod pa chen po dag par mdzod /
NK025(ra)001:10260: rab tu dga' ba'i bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:10261: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mchod pa chen po thams cad dag cing lhun gyis grub par mdzad du gsol /
NK025(ra)001:10262: drug pa bdud rtsi sman gyi mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:10264: rang byung gdod nas rnam par dag /
NK025(ra)001:10265: rtsa brgyad stong las sbyar ba'i sman //
NK025(ra)001:10266: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK025(ra)001:10267: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK025(ra)001:10268: rgyud lnga sems can kun sgrol ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:10269: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK025(ra)001:10270: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK025(ra)001:10271: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs chen gyi //
NK025(ra)001:10272: thugs dam dbyings nyid bskul ba'i mchog /
NK025(ra)001:10273: 'di ni sngon gyi dam tshig go //
NK025(ra)001:10274: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK025(ra)001:10275: thugs dam dbyings nyid bskang ba'i mchog /
NK025(ra)001:10276: sku gsung thugs kyi ngang nyid 'di //
NK025(ra)001:10277: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags kyi //
NK025(ra)001:10278: bzhes te kun tu dgyes mdzod las //
NK025(ra)001:10279: 'phrul gyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:10280: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:10281: spyi gtsug nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan steng du //
NK025(ra)001:10282: drin chen rtsa brgyud dpal ldan bla ma la //
NK025(ra)001:10283: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:10284: thugs rje che dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK025(ra)001:10285: sarba tshogs rje tshogs bdag dpal chen he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:10286: 'bar ba'i rgyal po khrag 'thung lnga rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:10287: rnam dag thugs rje sarba dpal chen sku la lhun grub mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:10288: kro d+hi shwa r+ai la sogs rigs kyi yum rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:10289: rnam dag thugs rje sarba mthing kha mchog rnams rdo rje gsang ba'i yum //
NK025(ra)001:10290: koo r+ai la sogs gnas kyi ma brgyad la //
NK025(ra)001:10291: rnam dag thugs rje sarba rdo rje gdong mo za byed mche gshog can //
NK025(ra)001:10292: sing+ha la sogs yul gyi phra men brgyad rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:10293: rnam dag thugs rje sarba sgo bzhir rab rngam rdo rje sring 'gro ma //
NK025(ra)001:10294: gdong mo ro langs 'jig rten ma tshogs la //
NK025(ra)001:10295: rnam dag thugs rje sarba dpal gyi 'khor tshogs badz+ra a ra li //
NK025(ra)001:10296: mkha' 'gro shugs 'gro ma tshogs rgya mtsho la //
NK025(ra)001:10297: rnam dag thugs rje sarba thugs rje'i shugs kyi 'dren pa'i las mdzad ma //
NK025(ra)001:10298: pho nya rgya mtsho 'bar ba'i tshogs rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:10299: rnam dag thugs rje sarba 'gro drug sems can ma lus sgrol ba yi //
NK025(ra)001:10300: ma gcig sngags kyi srung ma mthu mo che //
NK025(ra)001:10301: 'dod pa khams kyi bud med nyag gcig ma //
NK025(ra)001:10302: dpal ldan gnyan gyi re ma ti rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:10303: rnam dag thugs rje sarba dam tshig dbang dang shes rgyud gab sbas pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:10304: nges pa'i lung ston rdo rje slob dpon la //
NK025(ra)001:10305: rnam dag thugs rje sarba shes pa'i khyad par rim pas dbang bskur ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:10306: rgyal thebs la sogs karma ging rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:10307: rnam dag thugs rje sarba 'jig rten 'di dang phyi ma thams cad du //
NK025(ra)001:10308: dam tshig zung gis 'brel ba'i mched rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:10309: rnam dag thugs rje sarba dam la gnas shing rig 'dzin sgrub pa po //
NK025(ra)001:10310: lha dang lha min phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor la //
NK025(ra)001:10311: rnam dag thugs rje sarba tshe rabs sngon nas da lta yan chad du //
NK025(ra)001:10312: lus srog bskyed pa'i dus gsum pha ma la //
NK025(ra)001:10313: rnam dag thugs rje sarba +aa h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10314: lce yi dam tshig rdo rje ste //
NK025(ra)001:10315: rdo rje can gyi bsgoms nas //
NK025(ra)001:10316: bdud rtsi lnga la sbyar ba'i sman //
NK025(ra)001:10317: zos nas byang chub sku thob 'gyur //
NK025(ra)001:10321: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:10322: lce yi dam tshig rdo rje ni //
NK025(ra)001:10324: bdud rtsi lnga la sbyar ba'i sman //
NK025(ra)001:10325: zos na byang chub gsung thob 'gyur /
NK025(ra)001:10326: w+aa ka sid+d+hi +aamh s+pha sam sarba ta th+aa ga
NK025(ra)001:10327: ta ma h+aa wa ka lce yi dam tshig rdo
NK025(ra)001:10328: rje ste // rdo rje can gyi h+aum bsgoms nas //
NK025(ra)001:10329: bdud rtsi lnga la sbyor ba'i sman //
NK025(ra)001:10330: zos na byang chub thugs thob 'gyur //
NK025(ra)001:10332: s+pha sam sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK025(ra)001:10333: bdun pa gtor ma'i mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:10334: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka i dam d+h+au pam /
NK025(ra)001:10338: ba lim ta pra t+aits+tsha hoh sh+r+ai ban kha kha /
NK025(ra)001:10341: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam par sbyar ba 'di //
NK025(ra)001:10342: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK025(ra)001:10343: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan te //
NK025(ra)001:10344: dam tshig gsang ba'i mchod par bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:10345: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:10346: dgu pa ta na sgrol ba'i mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:10347: thog mar bdag nyid rtogs goms bsgral //
NK025(ra)001:10348: de nas gnyis med blo yis ni //
NK025(ra)001:10349: blo ngan 'jig rten snying re rje //
NK025(ra)001:10350: gnyis su med par bsgral bar bya //
NK025(ra)001:10351: bcu pa ga na sbyor ba'i mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:10353: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:10354: pad+mo la ni rdo rje zhugs //
NK025(ra)001:10355: 'khril ba'i mchod chen mnyam sbyor bas //
NK025(ra)001:10356: bdag nyid mnyes pas kun la mchod //
NK025(ra)001:10358: sa ma ya hoh a nu r+aa ga ya mi /
NK025(ra)001:10359: a nu r+aa ga ya ham /
NK025(ra)001:10361: bo d+hi tsit+ta s+pha ra na phata /
NK025(ra)001:10363: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa p+au dza badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:10364: bcu gcig pa dam rdzas kyi mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:10365: mnyam pa'i sgrub rdzas chen po 'di //
NK025(ra)001:10366: bdag dang mnyam pa'i tshogs la 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:10367: bza' dang bca' dang btung dang bgo //
NK025(ra)001:10368: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad kyis //
NK025(ra)001:10370: chos nyid la ni chos nyid thim //
NK025(ra)001:10371: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra a be sha ya a be sha ya /
NK025(ra)001:10372: pra be sha ya pra be sha ya /
NK025(ra)001:10373: pra t+aits+tsha hoh sh+r+ai ban kha kha /
NK025(ra)001:10375: bcu gnyis pa rak+ta tshar gsum gyis mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:10376: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK025(ra)001:10377: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK025(ra)001:10378: dpal chen 'khor bcas spyan drangs te //
NK025(ra)001:10379: dur khrod mchog gi gnas 'di ru //
NK025(ra)001:10380: zhing chen gsar rnying ti rar bcas //
NK025(ra)001:10381: dmar gyi ar+g+ham rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK025(ra)001:10383: ma lus par ni bsnams su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:10384: nga ni za byed chen po ste //
NK025(ra)001:10385: khams gsum ma lus bsgral ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:10386: gdul dka' ba dag 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:10387: sha rus la sogs za bar bya //
NK025(ra)001:10388: nga ni khrag 'thung chen po ste //
NK025(ra)001:10389: 'khor ba'i d+r+wa ba chags pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:10390: dmar chen po yi ar+g+ham la //
NK025(ra)001:10391: dmar gyi de ni rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK025(ra)001:10393: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa sa ma ya /
NK025(ra)001:10397: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta /
NK025(ra)001:10398: ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha hoh kha kha kha /
NK025(ra)001:10400: h+aum b+h+yo h+aum b+h+yo h+aum b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:10401: bcu gsum pa dpal la bstod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:10402: sgeg pa dpa' ba 'jigs su rung ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:10403: rgod dang gshe dang 'jigs par ston pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:10404: snying rje rngam dang zhi ba la sogs pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:10405: sku yi dngos po shin tu bsgyur ba yin //
NK025(ra)001:10406: gar byas sgrub po rnal 'byor pa //
NK025(ra)001:10407: gar gi dbang phyug gtso bo che //
NK025(ra)001:10408: zla ba la sogs snying po can //
NK025(ra)001:10409: m+aam sa la sogs bro mchog bsil //
NK025(ra)001:10410: me tog la sogs tsan+dana phreng //
NK025(ra)001:10411: bzang rgu 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:10412: mi mo rnams kyi reg bya'i mchog /
NK025(ra)001:10413: byin gyis rlobs shig rnal 'byor la //
NK025(ra)001:10414: grub pa'i rdzas ni thams cad la //
NK025(ra)001:10415: h+aum dang phata kyis ldan par mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:10416: bcu bzhi pa rol mo ye shes kyi mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:10417: rnam dag sgrib spangs srid gsum skyon bral zhing //
NK025(ra)001:10418: ston ka'i zla gsal dri med zhal mnga' ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:10419: bcom ldan bde gshegs ye shes dkyil 'khor dbyings //
NK025(ra)001:10420: khro bo'i tshogs chen ma lus thams cad dang //
NK025(ra)001:10421: dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa bskyed pa'i yab //
NK025(ra)001:10422: shes rab lha mo rigs kyi yum dang bcas //
NK025(ra)001:10423: phyag brnyan gtum chen rngam pa'i tshogs la sogs //
NK025(ra)001:10424: bsod nams ye shes tshogs kyi zhing rab rdzogs //
NK025(ra)001:10425: rnal 'byor dam tshig bdag cag rnams kyis 'tshal //
NK025(ra)001:10426: dgyes pa'i dus kyi mchod par sbyar ba 'di //
NK025(ra)001:10427: bzhes te a la la ste dgyes par mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:10431: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10432: dzahh+aum bam hoh badz+ra pra t+aits+tsha hoh hoh spros pa
NK025(ra)001:10433: med pa'i dbyings dang rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor rnam
NK025(ra)001:10435: dus gsum du rnam par gshegs shing bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das //
NK025(ra)001:10436: rnam pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi bye brag dang ldan pa /
NK025(ra)001:10437: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:10438: rigs lnga'i bde bar gshegs pa /
NK025(ra)001:10439: rigs mchog yun gyi dbyings na rtag tu rnam par bzhugs pa /
NK025(ra)001:10442: thun mong ma yin pa'i spyod pas shin tu khros shing ye shes chen po la rol ba /
NK025(ra)001:10443: rmad du byung ba drag shul /
NK025(ra)001:10444: bla na med pa'i thabs mkhas pa'i rgya mtsho dang
NK025(ra)001:10445: ldan pa'i rgyal po bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po
NK025(ra)001:10447: badz+ra d+aa ki ni yum kro d+hi shwa r+ai dang gnyis su med pa'i rol pa las byung ba'i /
NK025(ra)001:10448: rigs lnga'i dpal chen po yab yum /
NK025(ra)001:10452: phyi'i sgrub pa pho mo la sogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:10453: ye shes dang las las bskyed pa'i 'khor bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams cad /
NK025(ra)001:10454: mkhyen pa dang byin gyis brlab pa dam pa mdzad du gsol /
NK025(ra)001:10455: gzhan yang rnal 'byor pho mo dang /
NK025(ra)001:10457: ci bgyi dang bka' nyan thams cad dang /
NK025(ra)001:10458: phyogs bcu dus gsum na bzhugs pa'i rdo rje slob dpon /
NK025(ra)001:10459: mched lcam dral rnal 'byor gyi don la thugs dam rtse gcig tu mdzad pa rnams dgongs shing /
NK025(ra)001:10460: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i dgongs pa gzhung bzhin du mdzad pa rnams /
NK025(ra)001:10461: mkhyen pa dang byin gyis brlab pa mdzad du gsol /
