NK025(ra)001:10462: hoh rnal 'byor gyi mchod pa 'di la phud kyi mchod pa /
NK025(ra)001:10463: chos nyid la chos nyid 'byung ste 'byung ba chen
NK025(ra)001:10464: po kun rdzob kyi mtshan nyid tsam la bsdus nas
NK025(ra)001:10465: / deng sprul pa la sprul pa rol /
NK025(ra)001:10466: rnal 'byor gsang ba mchog gi mchod pa longs spyod
NK025(ra)001:10467: pa'i tshul du sbyar ba 'di bdag nyid chen po
NK025(ra)001:10468: 'khor dang bcas pa khyed rnams la /
NK025(ra)001:10469: dbang mi 'tshal bar phud gtsang bar dpags te /
NK025(ra)001:10470: dga' mgu rangs pa'i sems kyis /
NK025(ra)001:10471: mchod pa'i lha mo 'dod 'byor bstan pa'i tshul du gar gyi spyi gtsug gis blangs te /
NK025(ra)001:10472: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor rin po che gzhal yas khang
NK025(ra)001:10473: chos kyi dbyings kyi mtha' klas par phyur bur bkang
NK025(ra)001:10475: gnyis su med pa'i bde ba chen po'i ngang nas dgyes pa lhun grub tu dgongs te /
NK025(ra)001:10476: ye shes chen po chu zla lta bus sgyu ma la sgyu mar rol te /
NK025(ra)001:10477: sku gsung thugs kyi longs spyod mi zad pa'i gter chen po bzhes su gsol /
NK025(ra)001:10478: mthol bshags bzod par gsol ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:10479: deng yon gyi bdag po dang bdag rdo rje 'dzin pa 'khor dang bcas pa la sogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:10480: bdag cag gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir 'dus shing tshogs pa rnams kyis /
NK025(ra)001:10481: dang po gsang ba rdo rje theg pa'i sgor mchis te /
NK025(ra)001:10482: dam tshig chen po mngon par nos pa las /
NK025(ra)001:10483: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig chag nyams su gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:10484: lha nye bar ma bsgoms pa /
NK025(ra)001:10485: snying po dag par ma bzlas pa /
NK025(ra)001:10486: sbyor ba mang po'i bar bskum pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:10487: dad pa can gyi tshogs bcag pa /
NK025(ra)001:10488: dge ba can gyi thugs dkrugs pa /
NK025(ra)001:10489: dam rdzas dang du len rngo ma thogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:10490: mchod pa lo zla'i dus las 'das pa /
NK025(ra)001:10493: ting nge 'dzin thang lhod du gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:10494: le lo dang snyoms las kyi dbang du gyur pa /
NK025(ra)001:10495: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mdzad spyod dgongs spyod dam pa gdengs su ma gyur zhing /
NK025(ra)001:10496: sems can gyi shes pa rang thad du gyur pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:10497: khyad par du yang sgrub pa'i dam tshig dang khyad
NK025(ra)001:10498: par gyi dam tshig gnyan po nos pa las nyams
NK025(ra)001:10499: shing zhig ral du gyur pa ci mchis pa de
NK025(ra)001:10500: dag thams cad shin tu gnong zhing 'gyod pa'i sems
NK025(ra)001:10502: dbyings nyid nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang las sku ma chags pa bzod pa dang du bzhes te /
NK025(ra)001:10503: tshangs pa yid bzhin du rgyas par mdzad du gsol /
NK025(ra)001:10504: dngos grub tu gsol ba'i mdo ni /
NK025(ra)001:10505: shes bya thams cad la thogs pa med pa'i shes rab /
NK025(ra)001:10511: dpal chen po 'khor dang bcas pa'i sku gsung thugs man chad /
NK025(ra)001:10512: dngos grub kyi rgyu dang skal pa gang lags pa dus phyi mar mi thogs par /
NK025(ra)001:10513: deng 'phral du thob par stsal du gsol lo //
NK025(ra)001:10514: phrin las dang snyan snyun du gsol ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:10515: bdag cag rnams la sdang par byed pa'i dgra /
NK025(ra)001:10523: so so'i rmi lam ngan pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:10524: pra sogs rtsub pa la sogs te lo skeg dang zla skeg dang gshed bzhi la sogs pa /
NK025(ra)001:10525: mi mthun pa'i phyogs tshe rabs las kyi 'phro las gyur kyang rung /
NK025(ra)001:10526: 'phral gyi rkyen las gyur kyang rung /
NK025(ra)001:10527: mi dang mi ma yin pa la sogs pa'i gnod pa'i sbyor ba las gyur kyang rung ste /
NK025(ra)001:10528: de dag thams cad bzlog cing zhi bar mdzad du gsol lo //
NK025(ra)001:10529: gal te zhi bas mi 'dul na yang drag po'i phrin las kyis 'dul zhing tshar gcod pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:10533: phrin las drag dal rnam pa bzhi ji ltar 'dul zhing 'tshams pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:10534: yal bar mi mdor btang snyoms mi dgongs shing ming yang mi grags pa kho nar mdzad du gsol /
NK025(ra)001:10535: bdag cag dam tshig 'di la mngon du zhugs pa rnams //
NK025(ra)001:10536: bcad gtubs sdug bsngal lus la 'byung bar mi 'gyur zhing //
NK025(ra)001:10537: grib ma phog pa'i sdug bsngal shin du mi bzod pa //
NK025(ra)001:10538: sku yi phyogs tsam mthong bas mod la 'tsho ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:10539: gzi mdangs lus la 'jug pa'i nyi ma stong phrag gi //
NK025(ra)001:10540: 'od bzhin 'jig rten khams 'dir rtag tu 'char ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:10541: lus ngag sems la tshe 'dir rdo rje rab snang zhing //
NK025(ra)001:10542: re smon thams cad dus 'dir thob par mdzad du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:10543: bco lnga pa glu ye shes kyi mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:10545: gtum chen dus mtha'i me chen 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:10547: khro gnyer glog stong 'gyu ba bzhin //
NK025(ra)001:10548: mche ba zangs yag za byed che hoh h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10549: rngam pa'i nga ro 'bru stong ldir //
NK025(ra)001:10550: gtum chen ri rab 'bum bsnyil skad //
NK025(ra)001:10551: a la ha la'i gad rgyangs che //
NK025(ra)001:10552: spyugs pa'i 'thor rlung g.yeng ba che hoh h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10553: khro bo shes rab 'od po che //
NK025(ra)001:10554: ye shes dkyil 'khor kun tu gsal //
NK025(ra)001:10556: sna tshogs ye shes thig le che hoh h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10557: khro bo'i rgyal po'i sprin chen po //
NK025(ra)001:10560: sna tshogs khros pa'i thig le che hoh h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10561: bdud kun gyi ni bdud chen po //
NK025(ra)001:10562: bdud kyi bdud de bdud rnams 'joms //
NK025(ra)001:10564: 'jigs byeed chen po thig le che hoh h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10565: rdo rje brag chen sra ba po //
NK025(ra)001:10566: rdo rje chu bo sdud chen po //
NK025(ra)001:10567: rdo rje me ste kun 'bar che //
NK025(ra)001:10568: rdo rje rlung ste 'thor rlung che hoh rgya mtsho lnga'i smon lam gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:10569: hoh rgyal ba rgya mtsho dgongs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:10570: mchod pa rgya mtsho bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:10571: nyams chag rgya mtsho bskang du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:10572: dngos grub rgya mtsho stsal tu gsol //
NK025(ra)001:10573: phrin las rgya mtsho sgrub tu gsol //
NK025(ra)001:10576: a kra ma h+aa kro ta sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10577: ka ta ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum phata dzah ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10578: gtso bo gsal gdab cing bskul lam 'dzab bstod ni /
NK025(ra)001:10581: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK025(ra)001:10582: 'khor lo 'bar ba dbus kyi lte ba la //
NK025(ra)001:10583: bcom ldan che mchog dpal chen he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:10584: ston pa kun tu bzang po gnas 'gyur pa //
NK025(ra)001:10585: rgyal ba khro rgyal kun gyi rje btsun yab //
NK025(ra)001:10586: che ba'i nang nas che mchog bla na med //
NK025(ra)001:10587: che btsan 'gran zla bral ba kun gyi mchog /
NK025(ra)001:10588: sku gsung thugs kyi bdag la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:10589: 'bar ba'i dbu ni nyi shu rtsa gcig gis //
NK025(ra)001:10590: sa ni nyi shu rtsa gcig rim pas mnan //
NK025(ra)001:10591: g.yas g.yon phyag ni bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis na //
NK025(ra)001:10592: rgyal ba sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis bzhugs //
NK025(ra)001:10593: zhabs brgyad bgrad pas khro mo'i dbu brgyad bardzisa //
NK025(ra)001:10594: nyi ma stong gi 'od zer sku la brjid //
NK025(ra)001:10595: dpal gyi chas brgyad dur khrod rgyan rnams rdzogs //
NK025(ra)001:10596: che mchog he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:10597: kun tu bzang po'i chos nyid gnas 'gyur pas //
NK025(ra)001:10598: dpal 'bar khro mo kun gyi rje btsun yum //
NK025(ra)001:10599: shes rab dbyings nas sku bskyod thugs rjer ldan //
NK025(ra)001:10600: khro mo gnam zhal ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:10601: a kra ma h+aa kro ta sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10602: ka ta ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+au /
NK025(ra)001:10603: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10604: zhes khro bo gsang bum gyi gzungs thag nas bzung ste 'dzab bzlas so //
NK025(ra)001:10605: dmigs pa'i 'phro 'du rnams zhi ba ltar bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:10606: de nas dbang mchog gi 'dzab bskul te bstod cing gsal btab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:10608: bcom ldan dbang mchog he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:10610: dbu gsum dang por byung ba ni //
NK025(ra)001:10611: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK025(ra)001:10612: sku gsung thugs dang ldan pa'i dbu //
NK025(ra)001:10613: khams gsum mya ngan 'das pa'i zhal //
NK025(ra)001:10614: dbu gsum bar du rngams pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:10615: g.yas sngo g.yon ljang dbus mthing zhal //
NK025(ra)001:10616: thabs dang shes rab sems kyi dbu //
NK025(ra)001:10617: srid gsum dbyings su rdzogs pa'i zhal //
NK025(ra)001:10618: dbu gsum tha mar rngams pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:10619: g.yas g.yon dbus gsum mthing ba'i zhal //
NK025(ra)001:10620: lung dang man ngag sems kyi dbu //
NK025(ra)001:10621: khams gsum re ba skong ba'i zhal //
NK025(ra)001:10622: bco brgyad phyag rgya rol pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:10623: stong pa bco brgyad dbyings su thim //
NK025(ra)001:10624: bco brgyad phyag na bsnams pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:10625: rdo rje glo snying zhing chung g.yas //
NK025(ra)001:10626: b+han+d+ha zhing chung ti ra g.yon //
NK025(ra)001:10627: zhing zhags nyi ma khyung chen g.yas //
NK025(ra)001:10628: zhing chen zla ba 'ug pa g.yon //
NK025(ra)001:10629: me dang rgya mtsho lbu ba g.yas //
NK025(ra)001:10630: klu dang rin chen ri rab g.yon //
NK025(ra)001:10631: yon tan bco brgyad dbyings su rdzogs //
NK025(ra)001:10632: khro rgyal rgyan rnams sku la brjid //
NK025(ra)001:10633: rgyud rgyal che mchog he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:10634: dbang mchog sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK025(ra)001:10635: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sh+r+ai he ru ka sarba ta th+aa ga ta kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10636: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10638: badz+ra he ru ka gsal gdab cing 'dzab bstod ni /
NK025(ra)001:10641: dbang gi dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK025(ra)001:10643: dreg pa bsnol ba'i gdan steng du //
NK025(ra)001:10644: rdo rje mi bskyod gnas gyur pa //
NK025(ra)001:10646: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku bskyod pa //
NK025(ra)001:10647: mchod cing byin rlab gsal sgrub pa //
NK025(ra)001:10648: badz+ra he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:10649: nam mkha' kun bzang gnas gyur pa //
NK025(ra)001:10650: khro mo dbang phyug skur gsal bas //
NK025(ra)001:10651: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med //
NK025(ra)001:10652: kro d+hi shwa r+ai'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:10653: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10654: badz+ra kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10655: ru lu de bzhin du rim pa ltar 'dzab bskul
NK025(ra)001:10656: dang bstod pa gsal gdab cing sngags bzla ba sogs
NK025(ra)001:10658: dbang gi dkyil 'khor shar phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng na //
NK025(ra)001:10659: dri za bsnol ba'i rnam par snang mdzad khrag 'thung gti mug 'joms pa'i sku //
NK025(ra)001:10661: mchod cing bsgrubs te byin brlabs pas //
NK025(ra)001:10662: bud+d+ha he ru ka la sangs rgyas spyan ma khro
NK025(ra)001:10663: mo dbang phyug thabs dang shes rab byang chub sems
NK025(ra)001:10664: // spyan drangs mchod cing bsgrub pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:10665: bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma la bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10666: bud+d+ha kro d+hi ru lu h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10667: dbang gi dkyil 'khor lho phyogs 'khor lo'i gshin rje
NK025(ra)001:10668: bsnol ba'i rin chen 'byung ldan khrag 'thung chen po
NK025(ra)001:10669: nga rgyal 'joms // 'jigs byed ser nag 'bar bar gsal //
NK025(ra)001:10670: spyan drangs mchod cing bsgrub pa'i lha //
NK025(ra)001:10671: rat+na he ru ka la m+aa ma k+ai las 'jigs byed khro mo'i sku byung ba //
NK025(ra)001:10672: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK025(ra)001:10673: spyan drangs mchod nas bsnyen bsgrubs pas //
NK025(ra)001:10674: rat+na kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma la rat+na sh+r+ai he rat+na kro d+hi ru lu h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10675: dbang gi dkyil 'khor nub phyogs 'khor lo'i klu dbang
NK025(ra)001:10676: bsnol ba'i snang ba mtha' yas dbang chen khrag 'thung
NK025(ra)001:10677: 'dod chags 'joms // 'jigs byed dmar nag ral pa can //
NK025(ra)001:10678: sgom zhing mchod de bsgrubs pa'i lha //
NK025(ra)001:10679: pad+ma he ru ka la na bza' dkar mo 'jigs byed khro mo'i sku byung ba //
NK025(ra)001:10680: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK025(ra)001:10681: gnyis med byang chub sems bsgrubs pas //
NK025(ra)001:10682: pad+ma kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma la pad+ma kro d+hi ru lu h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10683: dbang gi dkyil byang phyogs 'khor lo'i gnod sbyin bsnol
NK025(ra)001:10684: ba'i don yod grub pa 'jigs byed khrag 'thung phrag
NK025(ra)001:10685: dog 'joms // ljang nag me 'bar 'jigs pa'i sku //
NK025(ra)001:10686: gsal bar bskyed cing mchod sgrub pa //
NK025(ra)001:10687: karma he ru ka la dam tshig sgrol ma 'jigs byed khro mo'i sku byung ba //
NK025(ra)001:10688: lhag pa byang chub sems 'phros pas //
NK025(ra)001:10689: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK025(ra)001:10690: gnyis med byang chub sems bsgrub pas //
NK025(ra)001:10691: karma kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma la karma sh+r+ai he karma kro d+hi ru lu h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10692: dbang gi dkyil 'khor shar lho 'khor lo'i mthu stobs mnga' bdag sgrol byed chen po bdud rnams 'joms //
NK025(ra)001:10693: bdud dang srin po sgrol la brtson //
NK025(ra)001:10694: mthing nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK025(ra)001:10695: rak+sha he ru ka la lha mo ral gcig khro mo yab kyi cha lugs can //
NK025(ra)001:10696: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK025(ra)001:10697: gnyis med byang chub sems bsgrub pas //
NK025(ra)001:10698: rak+sha kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma la rak+sha sh+r+ai he rak+sha kro d+hi ru lu h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10699: dbang gi dkyil 'khor lho nub 'khor lo'i dam tshig chen po dpal chen dam tshig mnga' mdzad ma //
NK025(ra)001:10700: ser nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK025(ra)001:10701: bskal pa brgyar yang dam tshig ldan //
NK025(ra)001:10702: sa nu he ru ka la yum chen dam tshig khro mo dam tshig bya ra mkhan //
NK025(ra)001:10703: sangs rgyas sems can 'da' mi byed //
NK025(ra)001:10704: dam tshig dbyings su bskul byed ma //
NK025(ra)001:10705: sa nu kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma la sa nu
NK025(ra)001:10706: sh+r+ai he ru sa nu kro d+hi ru lu h+aum
NK025(ra)001:10707: / dbang gi dkyil 'khor nub byang 'khor lo'i mkhyen
NK025(ra)001:10708: rab mnga' bdag sgrol byed chen po dregs pa 'dul
NK025(ra)001:10709: / // ljang nag 'jigs pa'i cha lugs can //
NK025(ra)001:10710: dus rnams rtag tu gsang ba'i lha //
NK025(ra)001:10711: zhe sdang 'khor ba sgrol la brtson //
NK025(ra)001:10712: gu h+ya he ru ka la rjes skyes 'a joms pa khro mo yab kyi cha lugs 'dzin //
NK025(ra)001:10713: yab yum thabs dang shes rab las //
NK025(ra)001:10714: dam tshig dbyings su bskul byed ma //
NK025(ra)001:10715: gu h+ya kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma la gu h+ya sh+r+ai he gu h+ya kro d+hi ru lu h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10716: dbang gi dkyil 'khor byang shar 'khor lo'i thugs rje'i mnga' bdag sgrol byed ma mo mkha' 'gro 'dul //
NK025(ra)001:10718: gang bsgrubs mthu dang dbang stsol pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:10719: yak+sha he ru ka la 'jig rten bdag mo khro mo dbang phyug kun gyi rje //
NK025(ra)001:10720: sprul pa kun gyi yang sprul pa //
NK025(ra)001:10721: thabs dang shes rab dbyer med pa //
NK025(ra)001:10722: yak+sha kro d+hi shwa r+ai ma la yak+sha sh+r+ai he yak+sha kro d+hi ru lu h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10723: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK025(ra)001:10724: 'bar ba'i glo 'bur gru chad bzhi po nas //
NK025(ra)001:10725: koo r+ai la sogs khro mo brgyad rnams ni //
NK025(ra)001:10726: gdug pa thabs kyis 'dul ba'i drag shul can //
NK025(ra)001:10727: sku mdog phyag mtshan sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK025(ra)001:10728: ye shes khro mo brgyad la badz+ra koo r+ai ha /
NK025(ra)001:10736: ru lu zhes khro mo brgyad kyi sngags dang ru lu spel ma bzlas /
NK025(ra)001:10738: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i bar khyams gser mdog na //
NK025(ra)001:10739: sid+ha la sogs phra men brgyad rnams ni //
NK025(ra)001:10740: ye shes las la 'gyed pa'i phra men ma //
NK025(ra)001:10741: rnam 'phrul las kyi 'gro ba'i don mdzad ma //
NK025(ra)001:10742: sing+ha phra men brgyad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:10744: badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kh+ai he /
NK025(ra)001:10745: badz+ra sring+ga la mu kh+ai he /
NK025(ra)001:10746: badz+ra shwa na mu kh+ai he /
NK025(ra)001:10747: badz+ra gri d+ha mu kh+ai he /
NK025(ra)001:10749: badz+ra k+aa ka mu kh+ai he /
NK025(ra)001:10750: badz+ra u lu ka mu kh+ai he /
NK025(ra)001:10752: bar khyams shar lho nub byang sgo bzhi ru //
NK025(ra)001:10753: tshad med bzhi yis 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:10754: rta gdong phag gdong seng gdong spyang gdong bzhi //
NK025(ra)001:10755: zhi rgyas dbang drag las la thogs med brtson //
NK025(ra)001:10756: rtag chad bdag 'dzin mtshan mar lta las grol //
NK025(ra)001:10757: ye shes sgo ma bzhi la badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dzah badz+ra a mu kha h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10759: badz+ra b+hasmi pa la ya ba to hoh ru lu h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10760: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK025(ra)001:10761: 'bar ba'i bar khyams gnyis pa dkar po nas //
NK025(ra)001:10762: chos dbyings rnam dag ngang las rang snang ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:10763: sna tshogs cir yang 'gyur ba'i sku mnga' ba //
NK025(ra)001:10764: srid gsum zhing du sbyor ba'i g.yang gzhi gsol //
NK025(ra)001:10765: spor ma chen mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:10766: badz+ra a pra ti ha +aar+ya ni tsa tu ra ta ra phata /
NK025(ra)001:10768: ru lu bar khyams shar lho nub byang sgo bzhi ru //
NK025(ra)001:10769: dgyes pa bskyed pa'i gsang ba'i yum chen bzhi //
NK025(ra)001:10770: gnyis med rol pas byin rlabs sna tshogs 'phro //
NK025(ra)001:10771: shes rab yum chen bzhi la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:10772: sh+r+ai badz+ra mut+ka ra mu kha shwa ra ya na
NK025(ra)001:10773: mah ru lu sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga ma shwa ra
NK025(ra)001:10774: ya y+aa na mah ru lu sh+r+ai badz+ra kha t+w+aam
NK025(ra)001:10775: ga pra dz+wa la ya y+aa na mah ru lu
NK025(ra)001:10776: sh+r+ai badz+ra g+han+de pra dz+wa la ya y+aa na mah
NK025(ra)001:10777: ru lu h+aum / tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK025(ra)001:10778: 'bar ba'i bar khyams dmar po gsum pa na //
NK025(ra)001:10779: mi srin la sogs dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad //
NK025(ra)001:10780: dregs pa lha chen rnams kyi chung ma ste //
NK025(ra)001:10781: dbang drag las la thogs pa med par spyod //
NK025(ra)001:10782: dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad la b+h+yo ma nu rak+sha
NK025(ra)001:10783: s+ai b+h+yo zhes pa la sogs pa'i dbang phyug ma
NK025(ra)001:10784: nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi sngags dang ru lu spel
NK025(ra)001:10785: ma bzlas so // zhes gsungs pa'i don /
NK025(ra)001:10799: badz+ra ru d+hi ra mat+t+aa b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:10800: badz+ra e ka tsa ra ma b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:10804: badz+ra ma h+aa m+aa ra na b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:10812: badz+ra bum pa ka la ma b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:10813: badz+ra lam bo d+ha ra ma b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:10815: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK025(ra)001:10816: 'bar ba'i bar khyams bzhi pa gser mdog na //
NK025(ra)001:10817: nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing //
NK025(ra)001:10818: 'dod rgur bsgyur ba'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK025(ra)001:10819: ma sring byams pa'i tshul gyis grogs mdzad ma //
NK025(ra)001:10820: mkha' 'gro sum cu gnyis la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:10822: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10824: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dbang gi 'bar ba'i bar khyams lnga pa dmar po na //
NK025(ra)001:10825: 'jig rten dregs pa 'dul ba'i ma mo'i tshogs //
NK025(ra)001:10826: phyi 'khor 'dul zhing nang 'khor skyong mdzad ma //
NK025(ra)001:10827: dur khrod ma bdun las kyi sring mo bzhi //
NK025(ra)001:10828: bgegs srung ma mo rnams la ma ma d+ha tu h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10829: zhes pa bdun dang ru lu spel ma bzlas so //
NK025(ra)001:10831: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dbang gi 'bar ba'i bar khyams drug pa dkar po na //
NK025(ra)001:10832: khams gsum sgrol ba'i ging chen bco brgyad ni //
NK025(ra)001:10833: srid gsum las la thogs med sgrol la brtson //
NK025(ra)001:10834: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu gtan nas brlag par byed //
NK025(ra)001:10835: ging chen ging lcam tshogs la ging ka ra ha ha ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10837: tshogs chen 'dus pa dbang gi 'bar ba'i bar khyams bdun pa nag po nas //
NK025(ra)001:10838: bcom ldan h+aum mdzad sa gsum brjid kyis gnon //
NK025(ra)001:10839: khams gsum 'dul mdzad ye shes lha yi lha //
NK025(ra)001:10840: 'jigs byed 'bar ba'i gdug pa'i tshogs rnams 'joms //
NK025(ra)001:10841: khro bo khro mo rnams la kro d+ha kro d+hi h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10843: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dbang gi 'bar ba'i bar khyams brgyad pa'i phyogs mdog na //
NK025(ra)001:10844: ye shes thugs rjes phyogs bcur khyab pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:10845: gdon tshogs 'dul ba'i las la thogs med pa //
NK025(ra)001:10846: ci bgyi bka' nyan las rnams myur mdzad pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:10847: phyogs bzhi pho nya'i tshogs la b+ha na b+ha na
NK025(ra)001:10848: am gu sha dzah ru lu ha la ha la
NK025(ra)001:10849: p+aa sha h+aum / ru lu gardza gardza s+pho ta bam /
NK025(ra)001:10850: ru lu pa tsa pa tsa g+han+de hoh ru lu h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10851: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dbang gi 'bar ba'i bar khyams dgu pa ljang gu na //
NK025(ra)001:10852: stong khams yongs su las la dbang byed pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:10853: ma chen rgyal mo srid pa gsum gyi bdag /
NK025(ra)001:10854: yum chen las la dbang ba'i dbang mo che //
NK025(ra)001:10855: ma mo drug cu'i tshogs la ma ma shwa ra h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10857: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dbang gi 'bar ba'i bar khyams bcu pa mdzes tshon na //
NK025(ra)001:10858: theg dgu'i lha tshogs rgyal ba zhi khro rnams //
NK025(ra)001:10859: dbyings dang ye shes dbyer med gdul bya la //
NK025(ra)001:10860: chu dang chu zla bzhin du ston mdzad pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:10861: 'gro ba'i don rnams sgrub la bo d+hi tsit+ta ma
NK025(ra)001:10862: h+aa su kha dz+ny+aa na d+h+aa tu +aah ru lu
NK025(ra)001:10863: h+aum / tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dbang gi gzhal yas khang chen rta babs khyams bzhi na //
NK025(ra)001:10864: rig 'dzin bla ma byin rlabs mthu rtsal can //
NK025(ra)001:10865: lhun grub phyag chen tshe dbang rnam smin gyi //
NK025(ra)001:10866: rgya bod mkhas grub rtsa brgyud bla ma rnams //
NK025(ra)001:10867: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi dngos grub 'dir stsol cig /
NK025(ra)001:10868: don gnyis grub par byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK025(ra)001:10869: ma h+aa gu ru sh+aa ri ram g+ai li h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10870: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10872: de ltar zhi khro'i 'dzab khang dbye ba sgom bzlas sogs grub nas /
NK025(ra)001:10873: khro bo dam pa rgyan las gsungs pa'i 'dzab rgyas pa rnams bya ma dgos shing /
NK025(ra)001:10876: yun ring dus nas bsnyen cing bsgrubs pa'i lha //
NK025(ra)001:10877: bcom ldan dpal chen badz+ra he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:10878: 'khor gyi gsang bdag yum chen mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK025(ra)001:10879: dam chos dngos grub gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK025(ra)001:10880: da lta nyid du mngon sum ltar gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:10881: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10882: zhes spyi 'dzab ci nus su bgrang ngo //
NK025(ra)001:10884: khro bo'i skabs 'dir gsal bar ma byung yang /
NK025(ra)001:10885: gong gi zhi ba'i rigs 'gre sbyar te /
NK025(ra)001:10887: gtum chen dus mtha'i me chen 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:10888: zhes sogs gong du song ba'i glu ye shes kyi mchod pa de nyid 'dir yang blangs te sbyar /
NK025(ra)001:10891: ye nas mnyam nyid chos skur dag pa las //
NK025(ra)001:10892: ma rig dbang gis sgro dang skur btab te //
NK025(ra)001:10893: bde dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs ngo bor smin //
NK025(ra)001:10894: de zlog don du rgyal ba'i dam nos te //
NK025(ra)001:10895: bdag cag ma rig lus dang ngag sems kyis //
NK025(ra)001:10896: bag med tshul gyi dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK025(ra)001:10897: rgyal ba 'khor bcas thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK025(ra)001:10898: thugs rje che mnga' khyod la bzod par gsol //
NK025(ra)001:10899: rig pa'i me tog dor zhing dngos grub bskul ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:10900: dkyil 'khor du rdo rje'i phyag rgyas me tog 'thor zhing /
NK025(ra)001:10902: +aahbadz+ra sa ma ya +aah h+aum badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10903: s+w+aa badz+ra sa ma ya s+w+aa /
NK025(ra)001:10904: h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya h+aa //
NK025(ra)001:10905: ye shes rgyal po'i sku gsung thugs //
NK025(ra)001:10906: yon tan phrin las rmad po che //
NK025(ra)001:10907: de nyid du ni mnyam sbyor bas //
NK025(ra)001:10908: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK025(ra)001:10911: badz+ra sa ma ya hoh dzahh+aum bam hohs dngos grub bskul /
NK025(ra)001:10912: rtsa bar gsal kha ma byung yang /
NK025(ra)001:10913: khro bo'i tshogs 'dir 'bul ba rigs par snang zhing /
NK025(ra)001:10914: skabs 'dir legs ldan sogs bka' srung rnams mchod bskang bya /
NK025(ra)001:10915: sha chang gtso bor gyur pa'i tshogs kyi yo byad
NK025(ra)001:10916: gtsang rme med pa zhing lpags sam gcan gzan gyi
NK025(ra)001:10917: pags pa'i gdan la bshams te bsang chu 'thor zhing
NK025(ra)001:10918: / bi shwa bi shud+d+he a mri ta h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:10919: d+harma a mri ta h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:10920: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:10921: ram yam kham gis bsreg gtor bkrus sbyang nas /
NK025(ra)001:10922: am pad+ma ba lin+ta bi shwa tsakra b+h+r+aum /
NK025(ra)001:10927: s+pha sam a tsan+d+ra man+da la /
NK025(ra)001:10928: s+pha sam tshogs kyi snod pad+ma nyi zla'i gdan gyi
NK025(ra)001:10929: steng du tshogs kyi yo byad sha lnga bdud rtsi
NK025(ra)001:10930: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i
NK025(ra)001:10931: rnam pa ma tshang ba med pa bdud rtsi'i rol
NK025(ra)001:10932: pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i bza' btung gi dngos
NK025(ra)001:10933: por gyur / bdud rtsi bran te /
NK025(ra)001:10934: ba lin+ta te dz+wa ba lin+ta gu h+ya sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:10935: lan gsum gyis byin gyis brlabs te /
NK025(ra)001:10936: tshogs zhing spyan drang ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:10938: dbang phyug chen po yab yum dang //
NK025(ra)001:10939: byang chub rdo rje lcam dral dang //
NK025(ra)001:10940: khro bo'i rgyal po mtha' yas dang //
NK025(ra)001:10941: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs chen po //
NK025(ra)001:10942: lha dang lha min rnal 'byor pa //
NK025(ra)001:10944: dam tshig tshul bzhin gshegs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:10945: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka e h+ye hi d+r+ai sh+ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:10946: e a ral+li hoh hrim hrim hrim /
NK025(ra)001:10948: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK025(ra)001:10949: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra a gat+ta ya a gat+ta ya /
NK025(ra)001:10950: pra be sha ya pra be sha ya /
NK025(ra)001:10952: to sha ya to sha ya /
NK025(ra)001:10953: sarba badz+ra d+aa ki na nan /
NK025(ra)001:10957: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sarba dush+tana sa ma ya /
NK025(ra)001:10958: mu dra pra ban tsakra h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:10959: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam par sbyar ba ni //
NK025(ra)001:10960: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer rnam par 'phro //
NK025(ra)001:10961: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga yis rab brgyan te //
NK025(ra)001:10962: dam tshig gsang ba'i mchod par bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:10963: tshogs mchod dam pa rgya cher bteg pa 'di //
NK025(ra)001:10964: mchod sprin sna tshogs nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NK025(ra)001:10965: 'dod yon lha mo sgeg mo bsam yas pas //
NK025(ra)001:10966: zhing khams khyab pa mchod pa'i sprin du 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:10968: su ra ha u pa b+h+yoh ka ma la m+aa
NK025(ra)001:10969: la badz+ra a mri ta ha ra na pra t+aits+tsha
NK025(ra)001:10970: b+ha ga wan dzahh+aum bam hoh a la la hoh
NK025(ra)001:10971: pa na pem / pu nu su ra to /
NK025(ra)001:10972: ti pu pa ra muh sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid d+hoo /
NK025(ra)001:10973: sa ma yo ta muh sarba ma h+aa su kha sid d+hoo /
NK025(ra)001:10974: de nas tshogs gsum du spros la dang po dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:10975: sgeg pa dpa' ba 'jigs su rung ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:10976: rgod dang gshe dang 'jigs par ston pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:10977: snying rje rngam dang zhi ba la sogs pa //
NK025(ra)001:10978: sku yi dngos po shin tu bsgyur ba yin //
NK025(ra)001:10979: gar byas sgrub po rnal 'byor pa //
NK025(ra)001:10980: gar gyi dbang phyug gtso bo che //
NK025(ra)001:10981: zla ba la sogs snying po can //
NK025(ra)001:10982: m+aam sa la sogs ro mchog bsil //
NK025(ra)001:10983: me tog la sogs tsan+dana dri //
NK025(ra)001:10984: bzang rgu 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:10985: mi mo rnams kyi reg bya'i mchog /
NK025(ra)001:10986: byin gyis rlobs shig rnal 'byor la //
NK025(ra)001:10987: sgrub pa'i rdzas 'di thams cad la //
NK025(ra)001:10988: h+aum dang phata kyis ldan par mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:10989: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra i dam d+h+au pam /
NK025(ra)001:10993: ba lin+ta pra t+aits+tsha hoh sh+r+ai ban kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:10994: tshogs par pa dbul zhing bshags pa bya ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:10996: tshe rabs thog mtha' med pa'i dus mtha' nas //
NK025(ra)001:10997: da lta'i lus 'di blangs pa yan chad du //
NK025(ra)001:10998: lus kyis sdig byas spyod pa ngan du byas //
NK025(ra)001:10999: ngag gis tshig 'khyal smras pa ngan du brjod //
NK025(ra)001:11000: sems kyi blo nor log par bsam la sogs //
NK025(ra)001:11001: 'dod khro gti mug dbang gis nongs bgyis na //
NK025(ra)001:11002: 'di 'dra'i dmyal tshogs shin tu mi bzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:11003: bkram pa'i lha tshogs khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK025(ra)001:11004: ye shes lha la rtog pa mi mnga' yang //
NK025(ra)001:11005: de yi 'khor du gtogs pa'i lha srin rnams //
NK025(ra)001:11006: mi yi skyon mthong tsam na chad pa gcod //
NK025(ra)001:11007: nyams chag 'gal 'khrul mchis pa mthol lo bshags //
NK025(ra)001:11008: bzod par bzhes nas tshangs pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK025(ra)001:11009: bdag cag rdo rje slob dpon mched lcam dral gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dus pa rnams kyi //
NK025(ra)001:11010: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig nyams chag tu gyur pa rnams mthol zhing bshags so //
NK025(ra)001:11011: de ltar mthol lo bshags pa bzod pa dang du
NK025(ra)001:11012: bzhes te nyams pa thams cad bskang bar mdzad du
NK025(ra)001:11013: gsol / tshogs tha ma ling+ga thod ngan nam hom khung du bcug ste /
NK025(ra)001:11014: 'brub khung du ling+ga dgra bgegs dngos su bsam /
NK025(ra)001:11015: rang dpal chen po'i nga rgyal gsal te /
NK025(ra)001:11017: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:11018: lha las la gzud pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11019: ba hu bi di ra ro'u tri /
NK025(ra)001:11021: she na bi na ya bi ta th+aa ga te /
NK025(ra)001:11022: tsa le pra tsa le gur pa gur pa sham pa ri /
NK025(ra)001:11026: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:11027: dkon mchog gsum gyi bka' bden pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:11028: bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:11029: bcom ldan 'das zhi khro tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil
NK025(ra)001:11030: 'khor lha tshogs 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyi bka'
NK025(ra)001:11031: bden pa dang / bden pa chen po'i byin gyis brlabs kyis /
NK025(ra)001:11033: gnod pa'i bgegs thams cad skad cig thang cig yud tsam la 'dir khug cig /
NK025(ra)001:11034: e yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor mchog /
NK025(ra)001:11035: 'bar ba gtum chen rngams pa las //
NK025(ra)001:11036: khros pas yid kyis mchod sbyin bya //
NK025(ra)001:11037: sangs rgyas bsod nams sku yang 'jig /
NK025(ra)001:11038: bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga la //
NK025(ra)001:11039: mtshan ma ming rus bcas par bya //
NK025(ra)001:11040: bkug nas rdo rje phur pas gdab //
NK025(ra)001:11041: rdul du byas nas tshogs la dbul //
NK025(ra)001:11042: zhe sdang rdo rje 'khor bcas pas //
NK025(ra)001:11044: skad cig yud la brlag mdzad de //
NK025(ra)001:11045: brlag par ma gyur gang yang med //
NK025(ra)001:11046: brlag mdzad khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:11047: lha mo slas can tshogs kyi bdag /
NK025(ra)001:11048: he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:11049: slob dpon la ni brnyas byed dang //
NK025(ra)001:11050: rnal 'byor bar du gcod pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:11051: dam tshig gnyan po 'dral ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:11052: rdo rje spun la 'khu byed rnams //
NK025(ra)001:11053: khyod kyis rdul du brlag nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:11054: gnod sems ma lus gtan nas phyungs //
NK025(ra)001:11055: gang la bya ba khyod shes kyis //
NK025(ra)001:11056: dmigs pa'i gnas nas khug la shog /
NK025(ra)001:11058: bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+da la phata phata phata /
NK025(ra)001:11059: ha la ha la h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:11060: tri yam dzah n+ri yam dzah badz+ra am gu sha dzah pra be sha phata /
NK025(ra)001:11062: badz+ra am gu sha dzah badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:11064: badz+ra g+han+de hoh spro na gong bzhin ba hus kyang pho nya btang /
NK025(ra)001:11065: h+aum dzah chos nyid kun tu bzang po'i rol pa las //
NK025(ra)001:11066: 'jig rten spyod pa'i tshul yang mi spong ste //
NK025(ra)001:11067: thabs la mkhas pas khro rgyal tshul ston pa //
NK025(ra)001:11068: ma chags dag pa yum gyi gzhal yas su //
NK025(ra)001:11069: dbang phyug rgyal po thabs kyi rol pa yis //
NK025(ra)001:11070: gnyis med byang chub sems kyi 'phro 'du las //
NK025(ra)001:11071: sku gsung thugs las sprul pa'i phra men ma //
NK025(ra)001:11072: rdo rje mkha' 'groo ye shes dam tshig can //
NK025(ra)001:11073: bka' bzhin rjes su sgrub pa'i mched lcam la //
NK025(ra)001:11074: sdang bar byed pa'i dgra dang gnod pa'i bgegs //
NK025(ra)001:11075: koo r+ai 'gugs pa'i tshogs kyis khug la shog /
NK025(ra)001:11076: tsoo r+ai rkun mo'i tshogasakyisa mthu stobs rkun //
NK025(ra)001:11077: pra mo rmongs byed tshogs kyis rmongs par mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:11078: bet+ta thal byed tshogs kyis thal bar rlog /
NK025(ra)001:11079: puk+ka g+hasma sme sha tsan+da l+ai //
NK025(ra)001:11080: gnod byed bzung la chings shig dbang du bsdus //
NK025(ra)001:11081: rab tu myos su chug la brgyal bar mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:11082: seng+ge stag dang wa dang spyang mo'i mgo //
NK025(ra)001:11083: gdug pa'i mgo la yum gyi chas can ma //
NK025(ra)001:11084: mgo nas gsol la sha rus lha rkang gzhibs //
NK025(ra)001:11085: gri d+ha kam ka pho rog 'ug po'i mgo //
NK025(ra)001:11086: mkha' la rlung ltar 'gyu ba'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK025(ra)001:11087: de yi glo snying nang khrol rkang tshil rnams //
NK025(ra)001:11088: chem chem gsol te drag po'i las rnams mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:11089: dkar mo rdo rje khyab pa'i sku //
NK025(ra)001:11090: ye shes nyi ma 'bum gyi gzi //
NK025(ra)001:11091: rdo rje gdong mo tshul bzhin spyon //
NK025(ra)001:11092: chings shig phag gdong zhags pa ma //
NK025(ra)001:11093: 'dod chags dmar mo dril byed sku //
NK025(ra)001:11094: rnam dag pad+ma'i dkyil na bzhugs //
NK025(ra)001:11095: rdo rje'i 'jig rten lcags sgrog ma //
NK025(ra)001:11096: dbang du sdus shig nyi zla'i spyan //
NK025(ra)001:11097: 'bar ba chen po thal byed ma //
NK025(ra)001:11098: sangs rgyas longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK025(ra)001:11099: sangs rgyas bden pa kun brten ma //
NK025(ra)001:11100: rol cig khams gsum slar 'tsho ma //
NK025(ra)001:11101: khyed kyi thugs dam dus la bab //
NK025(ra)001:11102: drongs shig khug cig dgra bgegs kyi //
NK025(ra)001:11103: tsit+ta dkar nag mtshams nas drongs //
NK025(ra)001:11104: go ro tsa na'i rgya nas drongs //
NK025(ra)001:11105: ba su ta yi mgul nas drongs //
NK025(ra)001:11106: dbang po rnam shes kun nas drongs //
NK025(ra)001:11107: dpal chen rngam pa'i zhal du stob //
NK025(ra)001:11108: rdul cha tsam yang med par gyis //
NK025(ra)001:11111: skabs 'dir yig rgyun gzhan la som nyi za ba'i bskul mang bar snang yang /
NK025(ra)001:11112: 'di ni 'jam dbyangs rin chen rgyal mtshan dang /
NK025(ra)001:11113: pan chen sku mched kyi bla dpe'i rgyun bzhin bris pas rgyas bsdus 'tshams shing khung che bar mngon /
NK025(ra)001:11114: gdab phur byugs bdug brab gsum gyis byin rlabs dang /
NK025(ra)001:11117: h+aum s+w+aa +aamhh+aa las lag g.yas nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la rigs lnga yab lnga /
NK025(ra)001:11119: m+aum l+aam m+aam p+y+aam t+aam las lag g.yon zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la rigs lnga yum lnga /
NK025(ra)001:11120: badz+ra any+dza lis sor mo bsnol /
NK025(ra)001:11122: badz+ra a be sha a h+aum a a /
NK025(ra)001:11123: byang chub kyi sems spros pas rdo rje gzhon nur gyur pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11124: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h+aum phata dzah yum bskyed pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11125: dip+ta tsakra ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:11127: phur bu gu gul gyis bdug cing khrag yungs byug cing brab ste ling+gara btab la /
NK025(ra)001:11128: badz+ra sa ta ra tsa h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:11129: na mahs man+ta k+aa ya w+aaka tsit+ta nam /
NK025(ra)001:11131: g+h+aa ta ya g+h+aa ta ya /
NK025(ra)001:11133: k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba p+aa pam phata phata /
NK025(ra)001:11134: h+aum h+aum h+aum badz+ra k+ai la ya badz+ra d+ha rod a dz+ny+aa pa ya ti /
NK025(ra)001:11135: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra k+ai la ya h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:11136: dgra bgegs kyi rnam shes a dkar po chos kyi dbyings su spar /
NK025(ra)001:11137: bkrag mdangs tshe dang gzi brjid sogs rnal 'byor par bstim la /
NK025(ra)001:11138: gri 'jam dpal du gsal bas gtub ste /
NK025(ra)001:11139: h+r+aish+ti bi kri ta na na /
NK025(ra)001:11140: sarba sha trun n+aa sha ya s+t+wam b+ha ya h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:11141: bdud rtsi bran te dbul zhing stob pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11142: dam nyams 'byung po'i sha ni zan las zhim //
NK025(ra)001:11143: sha yi rang bzhin gti mug che //
NK025(ra)001:11144: gti mug mchod pa 'di bzhes la //
NK025(ra)001:11145: bde gshegs sku yi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:11146: dam nyams 'byung po'i khrag ni chang las zhim //
NK025(ra)001:11147: khrag gi rang bzhin 'dod chags che //
NK025(ra)001:11148: 'dod chags mchod pa bde gshegs gsang gi dngos dam nyams 'byung po'i rus pa mar las zhim //
NK025(ra)001:11149: rus pa'i rang bzhin zhe sdang che //
NK025(ra)001:11150: zhe sdang mchod pa bde gshegs thugs kyi dngos h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:11151: bee d+aur sngon po'i rin chen ri rab las //
NK025(ra)001:11152: nyi ma stong gi 'od zer brdal ba ltar //
NK025(ra)001:11153: sems dpa' sngon po 'od kyi dkyil 'khor can //
NK025(ra)001:11154: dpal ldan gzi byin 'bar la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:11155: 'od phung stug po sprin ltar 'khrigs pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:11156: 'jigs byed rngams stobs brkyang bskum tshul du bzhugs //
NK025(ra)001:11157: za byed bskal pa'i me dpung bzhin du 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:11158: gdug pa thams cad rdo rje'i zhal du 'dren //
NK025(ra)001:11159: mi bzad mche ba gtsigs pa'i zhal gdangs shing //
NK025(ra)001:11160: srid gsum za bar byed pa'i rkan sgra can //
NK025(ra)001:11161: nyi zla 'bar ba'i spyan gyi sdang mig gis //
NK025(ra)001:11162: bgegs dpung sreg par mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:11164: badz+ra kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:11167: spro na dkyil 'khor gyi sngags thams cad kyi mthar kh+aa hi btags la dbul /
NK025(ra)001:11168: bsdu na khrag 'thung rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi sngags rnams la kh+aa hi btag la 'bul /
NK025(ra)001:11170: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum kh+aa hi kh+aa hi zhes 'bul lo //
NK025(ra)001:11176: skabs 'dir zhi ba ltar tshogs la rol pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11177: rdo rje las pas bla ma la phyag sngon du 'gro bas dza gad dang m+aam sa stob cing /
NK025(ra)001:11178: mnyam nyid mi g.yo sogs brjod cing /
NK025(ra)001:11179: bla mas a la la hoh zhes blangs te rol pa'i mthar /
NK025(ra)001:11180: tshogs kyi smon lam gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11181: hoh bdag cag rdo rje slob dpon mched dang lcam
NK025(ra)001:11182: dral rnams kyis rdo rje'i tshe gsol bas tshe dbang
NK025(ra)001:11183: phun sum tshogs pa thob par gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:11184: zhal zas sna tshogs gsol bas rdo rje sems dpa'i
NK025(ra)001:11185: sku tshe dang lang tshol mnga' brnyes par gyur cig
NK025(ra)001:11186: / dza gad dpa' bo gsol bas 'gro ba mang po dbang du bsdus par gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:11187: zhal zas sna tshogs gsol bas zhi khro'i rdzu 'phrul la mnga' brnyes par gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:11188: lhag ma rnams gsog 'jog mi bya bar bsdus la gong gi phud lhag dang bsres te gsog go //
NK025(ra)001:11190: 'di nas bzung tshogs chen gyi dkyil 'khor la 'dzab rgyun gsung mi 'chad /
NK025(ra)001:11191: spro na gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na dang /
NK025(ra)001:11193: par bkab ma byung yang 'thus pas dpon slob rnams
NK025(ra)001:11194: kyi dal brel gnas dus sogs dang bstun te bya'o
NK025(ra)001:11196: de nas nam lang pa dang rab tu gnas pa bya ba la don brgyad de /
NK025(ra)001:11197: sngon du bya ba'i cho ga dang /
NK025(ra)001:11198: ting nge 'dzin gyis dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:11199: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor spyan drangs bstim pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:11200: dbang po skyon bsal gyi chos bdun bya ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:11201: me long phul te chu bdun gyis khrus gsol zhing sku phyi ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:11202: che ba'i yon tan rgyan cha rnams kyis dbang bskur zhing mnga' gsol ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:11203: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa 'a bul ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:11204: brtan par bzhugs su gsol zhing smon lam btab pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:11205: zhes don brgyad kyis bstan pa las thog mar yo byad bsham pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11207: dang po sngon du bya ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:11208: dkyil 'khor gyi shar du man+dala 'dab brgyad mdzes tshon bya /
NK025(ra)001:11209: dbus su many+dzi'i khar rin po che'i snod du bzed zhal gyi me long bzhag /
NK025(ra)001:11210: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi mchod pa bshams /
NK025(ra)001:11211: shar du dbang po skyon bsal gyi thur ma sogs bsham /
NK025(ra)001:11212: lhor rgyas pa'i sbyin sreg bya /
NK025(ra)001:11216: 'khar ba'i snod du ba yi rnam lnga sogs sbyar ba'i chus /
NK025(ra)001:11217: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya bi sho d+ha ni h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:11218: zhes pas me long du sku gzugs shar ba la
NK025(ra)001:11219: khrus gsol bas dngos 'dzin gyi dri ma thams cad
NK025(ra)001:11220: bdag par bsam / til mar la +aahh+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK025(ra)001:11221: zhes byugs pas thugs byang chub kyi gzugs dang ldan par bsam /
NK025(ra)001:11222: shing shun lnga'i phye ma dang ba byung chu dang
NK025(ra)001:11223: gong gi sngags kyis khrus gsol bas khams lnga'i rtog
NK025(ra)001:11224: pa dag nas che ba'i yon tan thams cad phun
NK025(ra)001:11226: ras kha tshar can gyis phyis te /
NK025(ra)001:11227: rat+na pra ba na tsa ra ha s+w+aa h+aas lta ngan shes sgrib dag par bsam /
NK025(ra)001:11228: de nas spos dri bzang po phul bas sangs rgyas
NK025(ra)001:11229: kyi mdzad pa'i phrin las yongs su rdzogs par bsam
NK025(ra)001:11230: mo // zhes gsungs pa'i don dang po dkyil 'khor
NK025(ra)001:11231: chen po'i shar du rdul tshon nam chu tshon gyi
NK025(ra)001:11232: man+dala pad+ma 'dab brgyad mdzes tshon du byas pa'i khrus
NK025(ra)001:11233: stegs kyi dbus su many+dzi'i khar khrus gzhong rin po
NK025(ra)001:11234: che'i snod kyi bzed zhal me long dang bcas pa
NK025(ra)001:11235: mo // dang / 'khar ba'i khrus bum du ba'i
NK025(ra)001:11236: zho 'o ma mar lci ba dri chu ste rnam
NK025(ra)001:11237: lnga sbyar ba'i chu dri bzang btab pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:11238: til mar ram dngos su ma 'byor na 'bru mar te snum /
NK025(ra)001:11239: gzhan yang rdo rje las rim las /
NK025(ra)001:11241: nya gro d+ha dang par pa ta'i //
NK025(ra)001:11242: shing shun phyes mas phyi bar bya //
NK025(ra)001:11243: zhes gsungs pa'i don man ngag ltar /
NK025(ra)001:11248: par pa ste shing shun lnga'i phye ma sbyar ba'i
NK025(ra)001:11249: lde gu lcog rtse lta bu'i stegs la khrus bya
NK025(ra)001:11250: ba'i chu bdun tshan gnyis kyi dang po zhi ba'i
NK025(ra)001:11251: dkyil 'khor la khrus gsol ba'i chu bdun ni /
NK025(ra)001:11255: nas 'bras gro sran til sogs 'bru sna tshogs kyi phye ma btab pa'i chu /
NK025(ra)001:11258: sih+la sogs spos sna tshogs btab pa'i chu /
NK025(ra)001:11259: bzang drug sogs sman sna tshogs btab pa'i chu /
NK025(ra)001:11260: rin po che sna tshogs btab pa'i chu ste chu bdun dang /
NK025(ra)001:11261: ras dkar kha tshar ma nyams pa la rigs lnga'i
NK025(ra)001:11262: sa bon nam dri bzang gis thig le byas pa'i
NK025(ra)001:11264: yang stegs gcig tu khro bo'i dkyil 'khor la khrus gsol ba'i chu bdun ni /
NK025(ra)001:11266: de bzhin du thal chen gyi chu /
NK025(ra)001:11269: sha chen gyi chu ste dwangs ma klad pa la ngos 'dzin pas de dang bsres pa'i chu /
NK025(ra)001:11270: pad+ma rak+ta ste byang sems dmar po'i chu /
NK025(ra)001:11272: ro ras kha tshar ma nyams pa la rigs lnga'i sa bon can gyi sku phyi rnams bzhag go //
NK025(ra)001:11273: de bzhin du shar du dbang po skyon bsal gyi
NK025(ra)001:11274: thur ma yang zhi ba la rin po che las
NK025(ra)001:11281: rin po che'i spu gri rnams dang /
NK025(ra)001:11288: gser gyi chan pa rnams dang /
NK025(ra)001:11289: zhi bar chu gnyis sngon 'gro'i nyer spyod spyi ltar ram /
NK025(ra)001:11290: yang na chu bzhi'am gnyis sngon du 'gro ba'i bzhi
NK025(ra)001:11291: bsnol te bdug spos me tog mar me dri chab
NK025(ra)001:11292: bzhi / zhal zas sogs ji ltar rigs pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:11293: khro bor yang chu gnyis sam bzhi sngon du 'gro ba'i bzhi bsnol /
NK025(ra)001:11295: zhi khro thun mong du gtor ma dang bdud rtsi
NK025(ra)001:11296: sogs mchod pa'i yo byad bzang zhing mang ba bsham
NK025(ra)001:11297: / lhor rgyas pa'i sbyin sreg gi thab khung dang bsreg rdzas sogs bsham pa'am /
NK025(ra)001:11298: ma grub na rab gnas spyir rgyas pa'i sbyin sreg
NK025(ra)001:11299: gi don du ts+aa ru'i bza' ba bsham pa yin
NK025(ra)001:11300: cing / de la yang spyir sha chang ma 'dres pa'i bza' btung bsham pa yin kyang /
NK025(ra)001:11301: 'dir bla med kho na dang 'brel phyir sha chang btang ba mi 'gal 'dra yang /
NK025(ra)001:11302: tshogs 'khor zur du yod phyin sha chang ma 'dres
NK025(ra)001:11303: pa'i bza' bca' btung ba'i dngos po ci 'byor bsham
NK025(ra)001:11304: / nub tu cha gsum gtor ma dang de'i mchod pa bsham /
NK025(ra)001:11305: byang du sha chang gtso bor gyur pa'i tshogs kyi 'khor lo'i yo byad ci 'byor bsham /
NK025(ra)001:11306: dkyil 'khor rang gi rtsa ba dang yan lag gi
NK025(ra)001:11307: mchod pa rnams kyang nang re bzhin gsar du bsham
NK025(ra)001:11308: pa'am zhal bso / gzhan yang shar du mnga' dbul
NK025(ra)001:11309: gyi mchod stegs rgya che bar zhi khro'i mnga' dbul
NK025(ra)001:11310: gyi chas bris sam 'bar du byas pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11311: zhi ba dang khro bo'i dbu g.yas dkar g.yon dmar
NK025(ra)001:11312: dbu mthing du byas pa la +aahh+aum gsum gyis mtshan
NK025(ra)001:11313: pa / zhi ba dkar po phyag drug dang /
NK025(ra)001:11314: khro bo sngon po phyag drug +aahh+aum s+w+aa h+aa m+aum rnams kyis mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11315: zhi ba'i zhabs dkar po bzhi dang /
NK025(ra)001:11316: khro bo'i zhabs sngon po bzhi dzahbazhisa mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11317: zhi ba'i dbu skra thor tshugs mthon mthing dang /
NK025(ra)001:11318: khro bo'i ral pa kham ser dzahs mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11319: zhi khro'i smin ma ras mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11320: zhi khro'i spyan gnyis a dang h+r+aihs mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11322: zhi khro'i tshems mche ba'i myu gu cung bzad tsam k+shas mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11323: zhi khro'i sku mdog sna tshogs dang rgyan sna tshogs h+aum lnga dang +aahh+aum s+w+aa h+aas mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11329: dril bu drug h+aum drug gis mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11334: cod pan h+aum h+r+aihs mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11337: do shal tram gis mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11338: se mo do ste do shal phyed pa tram gis mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11339: dpung rgyan sa yig gis mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11340: phyag zhabs kyi gdu bu sa yig gis mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11341: seng ge glang chen rta rma bya shang shang ste
NK025(ra)001:11342: sems can lngas bteg pa'i gdan khri su yig gis
NK025(ra)001:11343: mtshan pa / nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan ma a pa gsum gyis mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11344: rin po che'i khri tram gis mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11345: 'od zer sna lnga ra yig gis mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11346: dar gyi stod g.yogs pa yig gis mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11347: dar gyi smad g.yogs pa yig gis mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11348: gsar phod de khro bo'i phod ka sa yig gis mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11349: zi ldir te rdo rje gong pa lta bus sa yig gis mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11350: gar gyi phu dung sa yig gis mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11351: gdugs sa yig gis mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11352: rgyal mtshan h+aum yig gis mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11353: bla bre sa yig gis mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11354: yol ba h+aum gis mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11356: gling bzhi'i man+dala sa yig gis mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11357: yul mkhar sa yig gis mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11358: bran pho mo h+r+aihs mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11359: bu bu mo h+r+aihs mtshan pa /
NK025(ra)001:11360: gzugs ma h+r+aihs mtshan pa rnams kyang bsham /
NK025(ra)001:11361: sa bon 'di rnams las yo byad 'di rnams bskyed
NK025(ra)001:11362: dgos phyir ma bris kyang chog pa 'dra yang sngar
NK025(ra)001:11363: gyi yig rnying gi tsakli rnying pa rnams la bris
NK025(ra)001:11364: 'dug pas bris kyang rnam par gsal ba 'dra zhig
NK025(ra)001:11365: 'dug cing ma bris kyang chog par sems /
NK025(ra)001:11366: de ni yo byad bsham pa'i rim pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:11367: de nas nam langs pa dang phrin las bya ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:11368: dkyil 'khor gyi nub phyogs su cha gsum gtor ma
NK025(ra)001:11369: bshams pa de nyid cha gsum gyi cho gas btang
NK025(ra)001:11370: / thog mar khrus bum pa'i rnam lnga sbyar ba'i
NK025(ra)001:11371: chu de nyid kyis dkyil 'khor phyogs su me long
NK025(ra)001:11373: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya bi sho d+ha ni h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:11374: zhes brjod pas dkyil 'khor dngos por 'dzin pa'i dri ma thams cad dag par bsam /
NK025(ra)001:11375: me long la til mar gyis byugs shing /
NK025(ra)001:11377: zhes byugs pas thugs byang chub kyi gzugs dang ldan par bsam /
NK025(ra)001:11378: shing shun lnga'i phye ma'i lde gu me long gi dngos la byugs pa khrus bum gyis bkru zhing /
NK025(ra)001:11379: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya bi sho d+ha na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:11380: zhes khrus gsol bas khams lnga'i rtog pa dag nas
NK025(ra)001:11381: che ba'i yon tan thams cad phun sum tshogs par
NK025(ra)001:11382: bsam / khrus ras kyis me long gi ngos phyi zhing /
NK025(ra)001:11383: rat+na bra ban tsa ra ha s+w+aa h+aas lta ngan dang shes sgrib dag par bsam /
NK025(ra)001:11384: de nas spos dri bzang pos bdug par bshad pa /
NK025(ra)001:11386: spos dkar sogs 'bul bar bshad kyang /
NK025(ra)001:11387: kahthoga rdor bzang gis dri lnga'i chus dri bskyed de /
NK025(ra)001:11388: zhes gsungs pa shin tu 'thad la /
NK025(ra)001:11389: chu bdun tshan du bshams pa'i spos chab de nyid me long gi ngos la dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:11390: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a b+hi she ka ta sa ma ya sh+r+ai ye h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:11391: brjod pas sangs rgyas kyis mdzad pa phrin las yongs su rdzoogs par bsam /
NK025(ra)001:11392: de nas sngon du 'gro ba'i phrin las lung gi zhi khro'i gzhung bsrang bar gsungs pas /
NK025(ra)001:11393: de'i sngon du bya ba ni rtsa bar lung gi zhi khro tshar ba'i rjes su bshad kyang /
NK025(ra)001:11394: glan ban gyis lung gi zhi khro'i sngon du bya bar gsungs pa 'thad par snang ste /
NK025(ra)001:11396: de nas phyag rgyas par btsal /
NK025(ra)001:11398: ye nas mnyam nyid kyis bshags /
NK025(ra)001:11401: mchod pa'i byin gyis brlab bo //
NK025(ra)001:11402: zhes gsungs pa'i don phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:11403: rgyas par spro na dri med bshags rgyud ltar /
NK025(ra)001:11404: hoh klong chen po stong gsum gyis stong chen po'i
NK025(ra)001:11405: 'jig rten gyi khams 'di ni don dam par chos
NK025(ra)001:11406: kyi dbyings yum gyi mkha' b+ha ga yangs pa'i klong
NK025(ra)001:11407: / rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor rnam par dag pa
NK025(ra)001:11408: na bzhugs pa'i bde bar gshegs pa 'khor rgyal ba
NK025(ra)001:11409: rgya mtsho dang bcas pa rnams la phyag 'tshal lo
NK025(ra)001:11410: / // zhes pa nas bzung zhi khro'i phyag 'tshal tshang bar byed pa dang bstun phyag bya zhing /
NK025(ra)001:11411: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa la lhun gyis grub par gyur to //
NK025(ra)001:11412: zhes pa'i bar brjod bsdu na gong du bshad pa ltar tshul phyag dang gral phyag bya /
NK025(ra)001:11413: khro bo'i bcu mtshams gcod ni rang badz+ra he ru kar dran par bya zhing /
NK025(ra)001:11414: khro mtshams kyi lha rnams kyang gsal btab ste /
NK025(ra)001:11416: dbang mchog sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK025(ra)001:11417: nga ni dkyil 'khor las byed kyis //
NK025(ra)001:11418: phyogs skyong bcu po mnan pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:11419: 'khor gyi gdon tshogs ma lus kun //
NK025(ra)001:11420: dus gsum sangs rgyas bka' byung gis //
NK025(ra)001:11422: badz+ra kro d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum a a a h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:11423: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:11425: ces sogs khro bcu'i sngags brjod do //
NK025(ra)001:11428: ye nas mnyam nyid chos skur dag pa la //
NK025(ra)001:11429: ma rig dbang gis sgro dang skur btab ste //
NK025(ra)001:11430: bde dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs ngo bor smin //
NK025(ra)001:11431: de zlog don du rgyal ba'i dam nos te //
NK025(ra)001:11432: bdag cag ma rig lus dang ngag sems kyis //
NK025(ra)001:11433: bag med tshul gyis dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK025(ra)001:11434: rgyal ba 'khor bcas thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK025(ra)001:11435: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK025(ra)001:11437: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:11438: byang chub mchog tu bdag gis sems bskyed de //
NK025(ra)001:11439: don dam dang ni kun rdzob byang chub sems //
NK025(ra)001:11440: deng nas tshul bzhin yongs su bzung bar bgyi //
NK025(ra)001:11442: spos dang rol mor bcas te /
NK025(ra)001:11444: dus gsum sangs rgyas 'khor dang bcas //
NK025(ra)001:11445: rang bzhin gnas nas sku bskyod de //
NK025(ra)001:11446: mkhyen pa'i gnas mchog 'dir gshegs nas //
NK025(ra)001:11447: brtse bas byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK025(ra)001:11450: rtsa ba dang yan lag gnyis las /
NK025(ra)001:11451: rtsa ba'i mchod pa sman gtor rak+ta dang /
NK025(ra)001:11452: yan lag gi mchod pa nyer spyod rnams yin par
NK025(ra)001:11453: rab gnas kyi phyir du bshams pa'i mchod pa dang
NK025(ra)001:11454: dkyil 'khor gyi mchod pa thun mong du byin gyis
NK025(ra)001:11456: dang po rtsa ba'i mchod pa sman gtor rak+ta gsum las /
NK025(ra)001:11457: bdud rtsi byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11458: a mri ta kun+da li badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha h+aum phata kyis bsang /
NK025(ra)001:11459: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+da la b+h+r+aum /
NK025(ra)001:11460: zhes bdud rtsi'i snod gzhal yas khang 'khor lo dang bcas par bsam /
NK025(ra)001:11463: zhes bcud sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga'i steng rigs lnga yab yum bcur bsam /
NK025(ra)001:11464: h+r+aihpad+m+aan+ta krita badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai wa h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:11466: zhes kha gcod la bdud rtsi'i srung ma rta mgrin yum bzhis bskor bar bsam /
NK025(ra)001:11467: rigs lnga yab yum gyi sbyor mtshams nas bdud rtsi 'bab par bsam zhing /
NK025(ra)001:11468: +aahh+aum sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK025(ra)001:11469: zhes lan bdun nam gsum gyi byin gyis brlab /
NK025(ra)001:11470: dpa' ldan rdo rje'i sku 'chang ba //
NK025(ra)001:11471: rdo rje mi phyed sku dang ldan //
NK025(ra)001:11472: deng bdag byin gyi brlabs nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:11473: rdo rje sku yi dngos grub stsol //
NK025(ra)001:11474: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:11475: nang mtsham lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs ye shes su bsgom pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11476: bdud rtsi'i phud gtor zhing lhag ma smin mtshams su bzhag la /
NK025(ra)001:11477: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya sid+d+hi /
NK025(ra)001:11480: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:11482: ces brjod pas smin mtshams su zla ba'i gdan la dkar po'i 'phro 'dus las /
NK025(ra)001:11483: sku rdo rje dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis 'khor lo dang dril bu 'dzin par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:11484: dpal ldan rdo rje'i gsung rdo rje mi phyed gsung
NK025(ra)001:11485: deng bdag byin gyis rdo rje gsung gi na mahsarba
NK025(ra)001:11486: ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta
NK025(ra)001:11487: phud gtor zhing lhag ma mgrin par bzhag la /
NK025(ra)001:11488: w+aa ka sid+d+hi +aah s+pha ra sam ha sarba ta
NK025(ra)001:11489: th+aa ga ta w+aak+ka badz+ra gsung rdo rjer mgrin par
NK025(ra)001:11491: gsung rdo rje dmar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pad+ma dang dril bu 'dzin par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:11492: dpal ldan rdo rje'i thugs rdo rje mi phyed thugs
NK025(ra)001:11493: deng bdag byin gyis rdo rje thugs kyi na mahsarba
NK025(ra)001:11494: ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta
NK025(ra)001:11495: phud gtor zhing lhag ma snying khar bzhag la /
NK025(ra)001:11497: s+pha ra na sam ha ra na mahsarba ta th+aa
NK025(ra)001:11498: ga ta tsit+ta badz+ra thugs rdo rjer snying gar nyi
NK025(ra)001:11499: ma'i gdan la h+aum sngon po'i 'phro 'du las /
NK025(ra)001:11500: thugs rdo rje mthing kha zhal gcig phyag gnyis rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:11501: sku gsung thugs sra zhing mkhregs pa'i dbang dang dngos grub dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:11502: gsang mtshams bdud rtsi gsang gtor ni /
NK025(ra)001:11503: bdud rtsi'i zegs ma la khro bo spros te bgegs bskrad par bsam zhing /
NK025(ra)001:11504: bi shud+d+he a mri te h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:11505: d+harma a mri te h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:11506: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:11507: phog pa tsam gyis brgyal bar gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:11508: reg pa tsam gyis tshim par gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:11509: rtogs pa rnams kyi bdud rtsi yin /
NK025(ra)001:11510: ma rtogs pa rnams kyi dug yin no //
NK025(ra)001:11511: gsang ba bdud rtsi'i mtshams las ma 'da' bar dengs shig /
NK025(ra)001:11513: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:11515: ram yam kham gyis bsreg gtor bkrus /
NK025(ra)001:11516: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he b+han+d+ha dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+da la b+h+r+aum /
NK025(ra)001:11517: snod b+han+d+ha'i gzhal yas khang du bsam /
NK025(ra)001:11519: ba lin+ta te dz+wa ba lin+ta ba la b+aa te gu h+ya sa ma ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:11520: zhes bdun nam gsum brjod pas bcud lha tshogs rnams
NK025(ra)001:11521: dgyes bzhad tshim par nus pa'i 'dod yon gyi phung
NK025(ra)001:11522: por bsam / rak+ta byin brlab ni /
NK025(ra)001:11523: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum gis bsang /
NK025(ra)001:11526: snod b+han+d+ha'i gzhal yas khang +aahh+aum rak+ta m+au la rak+ta h+aum h+r+aihth+aa /
NK025(ra)001:11527: zhes bdun nam gsum brjod pas rak+ta'i rgya mtsho bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin du brlab bo //
NK025(ra)001:11528: gnyis pa yan lag gi mchod pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11529: phyi mchod rnams a mri tas bsang /
NK025(ra)001:11531: b+h+r+aum zhes snod rin po cher bsam /
NK025(ra)001:11534: ti pu pa ra muh sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid d+hoo /
NK025(ra)001:11535: sa ma yo ta muh sarba ma h+aa su kha sid d+hoo /
NK025(ra)001:11537: zhes brjod pas nyer spyod dwangs shing thogs pa med pa nam mkha' dang mnyam par bsam mo //
NK025(ra)001:11539: de nas lung gi zhi khro bya ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:11540: rang lus kyi phyogs mtshams steng 'og bcur phyogs skyong bcu'i gdan la khro bo bcu bsam la /
NK025(ra)001:11541: zhes gsungs pa'i don rab gnas kyi sngon du bya ba'i bdag mdun gyi cho ga dang /
NK025(ra)001:11542: khyad par bdag bskyed gtso che ba'i dbang du byas pa yin kyang //
NK025(ra)001:11543: bdag mdun gnyis ka me long dang gzugs brnyan bzhin lhan cig tu gsal gdab ste /
NK025(ra)001:11547: gdod na ma skyes rnam dag chos kyi sku //
NK025(ra)001:11548: chos nyid byang chub sems su dbyer med kyang //
NK025(ra)001:11549: srid pa srog gis bsdus pa'i 'jig rten pa //
NK025(ra)001:11550: log rtog dngos por gol ba'i dbang gis ni //
NK025(ra)001:11551: sdug bsngal brgyad khri bzhi stong rang las byung //
NK025(ra)001:11552: sdug bsngal brgyad dang gsum gyi 'gro ba rnams //
NK025(ra)001:11553: rgyu 'bras theg pa gzhan gyis mi 'dul te //
NK025(ra)001:11554: gsang sngags gsang chen nges pa'i dus la bab //
NK025(ra)001:11557: srid gsum phyi nang snod bcud thams cad nas //
NK025(ra)001:11558: snyigs ma lnga dang skye 'gro ma lus kun //
NK025(ra)001:11559: thams cad sangs rgyas nyid kyi rang bzhin las //
NK025(ra)001:11560: thabs la mkhas pas 'di ltar brtag shing bsgom //
NK025(ra)001:11562: zhi khro'i mtshams bcad thun mong du byas la zhes
NK025(ra)001:11563: gsungs pa'i don gong du zhi khro'i gzhung bsrang ba'i
NK025(ra)001:11565: gnyis pa mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11566: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:11567: bdag nyid skad cig gis rdo rje he ru ka zhes sogs nas /
NK025(ra)001:11568: ra ba gsum rim nam mkha'i mtha' klas pa gang bas mtshams bcad par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:11569: zhes pa'i bar 'dir len cing mtshams gcod kyi don lung gis gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11572: steng 'og phyogs mtshams dngos po cir snang yang //
NK025(ra)001:11573: khro bcu yab yum sgom pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK025(ra)001:11574: phyogs bcur gnas pa'i bgegs rnams kun bsal nas //
NK025(ra)001:11575: bar chad med cing dngos grub thob par shog /
NK025(ra)001:11577: ye shes sku mchog dang bshags pa bya zhes gsungs
NK025(ra)001:11578: pas gong gi 'phros badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs bshags yul
NK025(ra)001:11582: ye nas mnyam nyid chos skur dag pa la //
NK025(ra)001:11583: ma rig dbang gis sgro dang skur btab ste //
NK025(ra)001:11584: bde dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs ngo bor smin //
NK025(ra)001:11585: de zlog don du rgyal ba'i dam nos te //
NK025(ra)001:11586: bdag cag ma rig lus dang ngag sems kyis //
NK025(ra)001:11587: bag med tshul gyis dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK025(ra)001:11588: rgyal ba 'khor bcas thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK025(ra)001:11589: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK025(ra)001:11592: rnal 'byor dbang po ye shes mthar phyin pa //
NK025(ra)001:11593: zhes sogs kyi dam bca' yang blangs te de'i don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11597: sgrib pa rnam gnyis dngos po cir yid kyis mngon du bshags pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK025(ra)001:11598: sgrib pa ye nas dag pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK025(ra)001:11599: sems nyid rang bzhin med pa'i don rtogs shog /
NK025(ra)001:11604: +aahh+aum a la la hoh zhes sogs dang /
NK025(ra)001:11605: 'phags mchog thugs rje'i dus la bab //
NK025(ra)001:11607: de'i don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11611: mthu dang bral ba'i sdug bsngal cir bde gshegs byin rlabs gsal bar rdzogs pa'i mthus //
NK025(ra)001:11612: rgyal ba'i sku ru lhun gyis grub nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:11613: thams cad byin rlabs mthu nyid lhun grub shog /
NK025(ra)001:11615: zhi khro'i byin rlabs byas la /
NK025(ra)001:11617: thog mar bdud rtsi byin brlab ni /
NK025(ra)001:11618: gong gi 'phros a mri tas bsang ba nas /
NK025(ra)001:11619: bdud rtsi'i gsang gtor gsang ba bdud rtsi'i mtshams las
NK025(ra)001:11620: ma 'da' bar dengs shig gi bar du byas te
NK025(ra)001:11625: bzhi brgya bzhi'i nad rnams cir snang yang //
NK025(ra)001:11626: bdud rtsis sman mchog bsgrubs shing mchod pa'i mthus //
NK025(ra)001:11627: yun du glags lta'i gnod pa kun bsal nas //
NK025(ra)001:11628: skye shi med par lhun gyis grub pa shog /
NK025(ra)001:11629: gtor ma byin brlab kyang gong gi 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:11630: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru kas bsang ba nas bzung gtor ma byin brlab dang /
NK025(ra)001:11631: rak+ta yang byin gyis brlabs te don gsal btab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11635: brgyad khri bzhi stong don rnams cir tshogs dang gtor mas mchod pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK025(ra)001:11636: 'phral du skabs 'tshol gnod pa kun bsal nas //
NK025(ra)001:11637: 'pho 'gyur med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK025(ra)001:11638: gong gi 'phros phyi mchod byin brlab byas te /
NK025(ra)001:11639: nam mkha' dang mnyam par bsam mo'i bar bya /
NK025(ra)001:11640: de'i don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11644: thun mong rdzas kyi dngos po cir mchod pa byin gyis brlabs pa'i nus mthu yis //
NK025(ra)001:11645: 'dod pa'i yon tan mngon du rdzogs gyur nas //
NK025(ra)001:11646: dus gsum bde gshegs ma lus mchod par shog /
NK025(ra)001:11649: bla mas rgyud lung zhi ba bya /
NK025(ra)001:11650: las slob gcig gis rgyud lung khro bo bya /
NK025(ra)001:11651: yang zhi ba'i sems bskyed dang ting nge 'dzin gsum byas la /
NK025(ra)001:11652: zhes 'byung yang phyag bzhes su bla ma rang gis zhi khro gnyis ka mdzad de /
NK025(ra)001:11653: zhi ba rin chen d+r+wa ba'i las gzhung gi thog ma kun rdzob sems bskyed kyi /
NK025(ra)001:11654: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK025(ra)001:11656: de phyir dngos po dngos med pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:11662: gnam sa dngos po ri brag cir de bzhin nyid kyi ting 'dzin bsgom pa'i mthus //
NK025(ra)001:11663: chos nyid stong pa nyid du rtogs nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:11664: spros pa med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK025(ra)001:11666: de bzhin nyid ni spros med de //
NK025(ra)001:11668: nam mkha' la ni nam mkha' bsgom //
NK025(ra)001:11674: ma rtogs sems can sdug bsngal cir kun tu snang ba'i ting 'dzin bsgoms pa'i mthus //
NK025(ra)001:11675: chos nyid skye ba med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK025(ra)001:11676: gnyis su med pa ra lhun gyis grub rgyu'i ting 'dzin ni /
NK025(ra)001:11678: dngos po med la dngos po'i sprin //
NK025(ra)001:11680: brtan 'byung ye shes rgyu yin no //
NK025(ra)001:11686: ma rig sems kyi dngos por cir rgyu yi ting 'dzin rtse gcig bsgoms pa'i mthus //
NK025(ra)001:11687: chos nyid byang chub sems kyi don rang byung ye shes lhun gyis grub rtsa bar /
NK025(ra)001:11688: zhi ba'i 'byung rim gzhal yas khang bskyed pa yan byas la /
NK025(ra)001:11690: zhi ba rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor bdag mdun lhan cig tu bsgom zhing gong gi 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:11691: de las rgyal ba'i bzhugs gnas rten //
NK025(ra)001:11692: dbang chen dkyil 'khor rim bzhin bsgom //
NK025(ra)001:11693: zhes tshig rkang gnyis rang mdun bskyed kyi rten bskyed
NK025(ra)001:11694: pa'i skabs kyi bdag gi thugs ka nas zhes pa
NK025(ra)001:11701: dkyil 'khor gyi 'og gzhi brtsegs mar 'khod ces pa nas /
NK025(ra)001:11702: sgo bzhir brag dang nyi ma'i gdan rnams su gyur /
NK025(ra)001:11705: ye shes phyogs bzhi dbus brtag te //
NK025(ra)001:11707: nyi zla pad+ma rin po che'i bar brjod cing don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11711: snod kyi 'jig rten 'a byung ba cir gzhal yas khang chen bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK025(ra)001:11712: chos nyid mtha' dbus med pa'i don 'og min gnas su lhun gyis grub rtsa bar /
NK025(ra)001:11713: zhi ba'i lha tshogs bskyed nas /
NK025(ra)001:11714: zhes gsungs pa'i don gong gi 'phros mdun bskyed kyi /
NK025(ra)001:11715: gdan de rnams kyi steng du dbus su a /
NK025(ra)001:11716: de'i mdun du tha tha zhes pa nas /
NK025(ra)001:11717: khro bo dang khro mo'i chas ldan ye shes kyi me 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa'i bar dang /
NK025(ra)001:11718: gdan la rdzogs dang sems dpa'i tshul //
NK025(ra)001:11720: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub //
NK025(ra)001:11721: ces pa'i bar brjod nas don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11725: phung po lnga dang 'byung ba cir rigs lnga yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK025(ra)001:11726: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK025(ra)001:11727: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med par shog /
NK025(ra)001:11729: dbang po yul dus rnam shes cir sems dpa' sems
NK025(ra)001:11730: ma bsgoms pa'i byin thams cad lha dang lha mo'i
NK025(ra)001:11731: don rgyal ba'i sras su lhun gyis grub na mo
NK025(ra)001:11732: h+aum / yan lag bzhi yi dngos po cir sgo
NK025(ra)001:11733: ba yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin yab yum 'du 'bral
NK025(ra)001:11734: med pa'i don phrin las rnam bzhi lhun gyis grub
NK025(ra)001:11735: h+aum / na mo h+aum / yid dang chos kyi
NK025(ra)001:11736: dngos po cir kun bzang yab yum bsgoms pa'i byin
NK025(ra)001:11737: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med don chos sku 'gyur
NK025(ra)001:11738: med lhun gyis grub na mo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:11739: 'gro ba rigs drug dngos po cir thub pa drug
NK025(ra)001:11740: tu bsgoms pa'i byin rol pa cir yang snang ba'i
NK025(ra)001:11741: don sangs rgyas mdzad pa lhun gyis grub //
NK025(ra)001:11743: yang zhi ba'i lha la sngags kyi dbu rgyan byin rlabs byas nas /
NK025(ra)001:11745: lag gnyis rdo rje phyi bsdams las zhes pa nas bzung /
NK025(ra)001:11746: mi bskyod pa mthing kha rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin par gyur gyi bar dang /
NK025(ra)001:11747: sangs rgyas lnga yi cod pan can //
NK025(ra)001:11749: dbang mchog tu ni dbang bskur ro //
NK025(ra)001:11750: zhes pa'i bar brjod na don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11753: lus ngag yid gsum dngos por cir dbang bskur byin
NK025(ra)001:11754: gyis brlabs pa'i byin las dang nyon mongs ma lus
NK025(ra)001:11755: kun byang nas // sku dang ye shes lhun gyis grub rtsa bar /
NK025(ra)001:11756: de nas ye shes pa spyan drangs te sa m+aa
NK025(ra)001:11757: dzahs spyan drangs zhes gsungs pa'i don gong gi 'phros
NK025(ra)001:11758: / dang po snyan gsan dbab pa ni zhes pa nas /
NK025(ra)001:11759: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra gyi bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11762: sangs rgyas sems can dngos po cir bde gshegs spyan
NK025(ra)001:11763: drangs bstim pa'i byin ye nas gnyis su med pa'i
NK025(ra)001:11764: don rtogs nas // gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub rtsa bar /
NK025(ra)001:11765: de nas lha tshogs mchod la zhes gsungs pa'i don
NK025(ra)001:11766: gong gi 'phros mchod pa bcu bzhi'i dang po phyag
NK025(ra)001:11769: ma skyes rdo rje thabs kyi ye shes ni //
NK025(ra)001:11771: sgo ba yab yum rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:11772: a ti pu hoh pra t+aits+tsha hoh zhes pa'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11775: bdag dang gzhan du dngos po cir ye nas 'dres
NK025(ra)001:11776: pa chen po'i byin gnyis 'dzin gcig tu go ba'i
NK025(ra)001:11777: don gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub rtsa bar
NK025(ra)001:11778: / de nas bde gshegs khyed sogs brjod nas zhes gsungs pa'i don gong gi 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:11779: bde bar gshegs pa khyed ci 'dra //
NK025(ra)001:11781: bdag cag bsam pa 'grub gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:11782: ces pa'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11785: 'gro drug sems can sdug bsngal cir dam bca' rnam
NK025(ra)001:11786: gsum byas pa'i byin bsam pa mtha' ru phyin pa'i
NK025(ra)001:11787: don bdag gzhan gnyis kyi don gnyis mthar phyin shog
NK025(ra)001:11789: de nas sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhes sogs brjod nas /
NK025(ra)001:11790: zhes gsungs pa'i don gong gi 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:11791: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba mngon rdzogs pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:11793: a la la te dgyes par mdzod kyi bar phyag
NK025(ra)001:11794: rgya gar mchod rdzogs par byas la don gsal gdab
NK025(ra)001:11797: gzung 'dzin rnam rtog dngos po cir phyag rgya'i mchod
NK025(ra)001:11798: pa phul ba'i byin phyag rgya rnam bzhi lhun gyis
NK025(ra)001:11799: grub nas kyang // thams cad phyag rgya chen por lhun grub shog /
NK025(ra)001:11801: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK025(ra)001:11803: zhes gsungs pa'i don gong gi 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:11804: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK025(ra)001:11805: zhes pa nas chu gnyis 'phul ba sngags dang bcas pa'i bar brjod nas don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11808: phyi nang gsang ba'i dngos po cir kun tu bzang po'i mchod pa phul ba yis //
NK025(ra)001:11809: dngos po thams cad mchod par gyur nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:11810: spyod yul thams cad yongs su dag par shog /
NK025(ra)001:11812: pa na pem zhes brjod la /
NK025(ra)001:11813: zhes gsungs pa'i don gong gi 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:11814: pa na pem zhes pa nas /
NK025(ra)001:11815: lha mo bzhi bsnol gyi mchod pa /
NK025(ra)001:11816: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mchod pa chen po thams cad dag cing lhun gyis grub par mdzad du gsol /
NK025(ra)001:11817: zhes pa'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11820: bdag gzhan dngos po khyad par cir mchod pa rnam
NK025(ra)001:11821: lnga phul ba'i byin thams cad 'gag pa med pa'i
NK025(ra)001:11822: don rtogs nas // 'khor gsum ma lus yongs su dag par shog /
NK025(ra)001:11824: rang byung gdod nas dag pa'i zhes sogs brjod la zhes gsungs pa'i don /
NK025(ra)001:11826: dngos grub blang ba k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha
NK025(ra)001:11827: badz+ra gyi bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni
NK025(ra)001:11830: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams cir bdud rtsi sman
NK025(ra)001:11831: mchod phul ba'i byin 'phral du skabs 'tshol dngos po
NK025(ra)001:11832: kun bsal nas // skye shi med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK025(ra)001:11834: yang su ra to pa po ka ma le zhes
NK025(ra)001:11835: brjod la zhes gsungs pa'i don gtor ma phul ba
NK025(ra)001:11837: u pa b+h+yoh zhes sogs nas /
NK025(ra)001:11838: gsang nan 'bul ba'i a la la ho'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11841: stong phrag brgyad cu'i bgegs rnams cir dam rdzas gtor
NK025(ra)001:11842: mas mchod pa'i byin yun du glags lta'i gnod pa
NK025(ra)001:11843: kun bsal nas // 'pho 'gyur med par lhun gyis grub rtsa bar /
NK025(ra)001:11844: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK025(ra)001:11845: zhes sogs brjod la zhes gsungs pa'i don lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa 'bul tshig /
NK025(ra)001:11846: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK025(ra)001:11848: a la la ste mchod par 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:11849: zhes pa'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11852: sems kyi rtog pa'i dngos por cir dngos po yo byad lnga ru grub nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:11853: rig pa cir yang snang ba'i don rtogs nas //
NK025(ra)001:11854: 'dod pa'i yon tan lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK025(ra)001:11856: ri rab chen po'i gling bzhi nas /
NK025(ra)001:11858: zhes gsungs pa sbyor sgrol gyi mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11860: +aat+ma ko&aham gi bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11863: chags sdang rnam gnyis dngos po cir tan gan rnam
NK025(ra)001:11864: gnyis mchod pa'i byin spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i
NK025(ra)001:11865: don bdag gzhan don gnyis lhun gyis grub 'dod yon
NK025(ra)001:11867: bza' dang bca' dang btung dang bgo //
NK025(ra)001:11869: chos nyid la ni chos nyid rol //
NK025(ra)001:11870: a la la ho'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11873: yul dang dbang po'i dngos po cir 'dod yon lnga yi mchod pa phul ba'i mthus //
NK025(ra)001:11874: yul sems gnyis su med pa'i don spyod yul ma lus yongs su dag par shog /
NK025(ra)001:11876: dbang po'i spyod yul la sogs zhes gsungs pa'i don ni /
NK025(ra)001:11877: rol mo sgra'i mchod pa kho na yin 'dug kyang /
NK025(ra)001:11878: gsang snying ltar glu ye shes kyi mchod pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:11879: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:11881: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le che ho'i bar dang /
NK025(ra)001:11882: rol mo sgra yi mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11883: dbang po'i spyod yul rang bzhin dngos po med //
NK025(ra)001:11885: dzahh+aum bam hoh pra t+aits+tsha hoh'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11888: nyon mongs sdug bsngal dngos po cir glu dang rol mo sgra snyan phul ba yis //
NK025(ra)001:11889: thams cad theg pa chen po'i sgrar gyur nas //
NK025(ra)001:11890: gsang sngags don nyid kun gyi rtogs par shog /
NK025(ra)001:11891: hoh phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i bde bar gshegs pa thams
NK025(ra)001:11892: cad kyi bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje
NK025(ra)001:11893: sems dpa' la sogs pa rigs lnga rgyal ba rgya
NK025(ra)001:11894: mtsho'i 'khor bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang bcas pa
NK025(ra)001:11895: thams cad gsan cing dgongs su gsol /
NK025(ra)001:11896: bdag cag rnal 'byor gyi mchod pa dam pa rig
NK025(ra)001:11897: pa'i khyad par phyi nang gsang ba gsum sbyar te
NK025(ra)001:11898: / phul bas sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud mnyes pa chen por gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:11899: de'i byin rlabs kyis ma tha' yas sems can thams
NK025(ra)001:11900: cad rdo rje 'chang gi gral thob par gyur cig
NK025(ra)001:11901: / bdag gi dam tshig nyams pa skongs te dngos grub kyi snod dam par gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:11902: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sar mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas par gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:11903: a la la hoh dam tshig gang 'dod zhu /
NK025(ra)001:11904: zhes gsungs pa ltar yid la gang 'dod kyi gsol ba gdab la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11907: yid la bsam pa'i dngos po cir smon lam sngon
NK025(ra)001:11908: du btab pa'i byin yid la ci bsam lhun grub
NK025(ra)001:11909: don 'gro don ma lus lhun gyis grub rtsa bar
NK025(ra)001:11910: / de nas khams gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor du byas la /
NK025(ra)001:11911: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he zhes pa nas /
NK025(ra)001:11912: +aa li k+aa li yan chad dang /
NK025(ra)001:11913: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su ka h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:11914: zhes bzlas la phyogs bcu dus bzhis bstod la /
NK025(ra)001:11915: zhes 'byung ba b+h+r+aum bi shwa sogs brjod pa 'dzab
NK025(ra)001:11916: khang dbye ba la dgongs pas gong ltar 'dzab khang
NK025(ra)001:11917: dbye bar bya ba'am yang na +aa li k+aa li
NK025(ra)001:11918: dz+ny+aa na pany+tsa sat+wa kro d+ha mu na ye s+w+aa
NK025(ra)001:11919: h+aa dang / gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na ci mang bzlas la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11922: rdul bral rtsol pa'i sdug bsngal cir bsnyen sgrub rnam bzhi'i 'dzab bsnyen byas pa'i mthus //
NK025(ra)001:11923: thams cad kun tu bzang po'i don dngos grub rnam
NK025(ra)001:11924: gsum lhun gyis ces khams gsum lha'i dkyil 'khor du
NK025(ra)001:11925: byas la / bo d+hi tsit+ta'i 'dzab bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:11926: zhes gsungs pas slar yang bod+hi tsit+ta bazla'o //
NK025(ra)001:11928: sngon 'gro zhi khro thun mong tshar nas ting 'dzin rnam gsum zhi ba dang mthun /
NK025(ra)001:11929: 'byung ba rim brtsegs lung gi gsal 'debs gong dang 'dra /
NK025(ra)001:11930: gtum pa dom zhes brjod la /
NK025(ra)001:11931: zhes gsungs pa'i don ni ting 'dzin gsum dang 'byung
NK025(ra)001:11932: rim rnams dag sbyor gong dang mtshungs pa 'dir len
NK025(ra)001:11933: pa la dgongs kyang nyis bldabs las dgos don lhag
NK025(ra)001:11934: po med cing / gtum pa dom gyi sbar bas ni //
NK025(ra)001:11935: zhes pa yan chad khro bo dam pa rgyan ltar bya bar gsungs pa yang spro na /
NK025(ra)001:11936: 'dzin pa'i dbang gis sdug bsngal zhing //
NK025(ra)001:11938: gtum pa dom gyi sbar ba ni //
NK025(ra)001:11939: dbang phyug lha chen la sogs bzung //
NK025(ra)001:11941: mi spro na mdun bskyed skabs ltar bdag gi thugs
NK025(ra)001:11942: ka nas e yam ra pam kem ram rnams chad
NK025(ra)001:11944: gzhan rnams la rang rang gi gdan du gyur /
NK025(ra)001:11945: zhes pa'i bar gyis bdag mdun gyi khro bo'i rten
NK025(ra)001:11946: gzhal yas khang me long dang gzugs brnyan bzhin gcig
NK025(ra)001:11947: char bskyed cing don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11950: dur khrod rdzas kyi dngos po cir 'bar ba'i gzhal
NK025(ra)001:11951: yas bsgoms pa'i byin rdzas su lta ba'i rtog pa
NK025(ra)001:11952: kun bsal nas // gnas mchog rab 'byams lhun gyis grub na mo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:11953: 'dod pa lnga yi yon tan cir tshogs kyi mchod
NK025(ra)001:11954: pa sbyar ba'i byin mtha' la zhen pa'i gdung ba
NK025(ra)001:11955: kun bral nas // bde ba chen por lhun gyis rtsa bar /
NK025(ra)001:11956: h+aum de babs pa las dur khrod chas brgyad skal pa'i klong nas bzhugs pa yan brjod /
NK025(ra)001:11957: ces gsungs pa'i don gong gi 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:11958: khro bo'i mdun bskyed skabs kyi a kra ma h+aa zhes sogs gtso bo che mchog bskyed pa nas /
NK025(ra)001:11959: rgyud lung gi khro bo dgu bskyed pa'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11962: ru tra rnam gsum dngos po cir he ru dgu
NK025(ra)001:11963: ru bsgoms pa'i byin bdud dang srin po'i bar chad
NK025(ra)001:11964: kun bral nas // ye shes dgu ru lhun gyis grub na mo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:11965: khams gsum sa dgu'i dngos po cir yum chen dgu
NK025(ra)001:11966: ru bsgoms pa'i byin ma bdun sring mo'i bar chad
NK025(ra)001:11967: kun bsal nas // thig le dgu ru lhun gyis grub rtsa bar /
NK025(ra)001:11968: yang dkyil 'khor gong ras bzhi la phra men gnas ma brgyad kyi sngags brjod la bsgom /
NK025(ra)001:11971: shar gyi glo 'bur la goo r+ai dkar mo zhes pa nas /
NK025(ra)001:11972: mgo lus phral ba'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11975: rnam shes brgyad kyi dngos po cir koo r+ai brgyad
NK025(ra)001:11976: du bsgoms pa'i byin yul la mngon par rtog pa
NK025(ra)001:11977: kun bcom nas // rnam par rtog pa'i 'du shes med par shog /
NK025(ra)001:11979: lha snam dang po'i phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhir phra men gyi sngags brjod la /
NK025(ra)001:11980: zhes gsungs pa'i don gong gi 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:11982: khyams dang po'i lha snam gyi shar du zhes pa nas /
NK025(ra)001:11983: 'ug pa'i mgo can rdo rje'i dbyug pa 'dzin pa /
NK025(ra)001:11984: zhes pa'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11987: dur khrod brgyad gyi dngos po cir phra men brgyad
NK025(ra)001:11988: du bsgoms pa'i byin mtshan mar snang ba'i dngos po
