NK025(ra)001:11989: kun bral nas // rnam par rtog pa'i bag chags med par shog /
NK025(ra)001:11991: de'i sgo bzhi ru sgo ma bzhi'i sngags brjod la /
NK025(ra)001:11992: zhes gsungs pa'i don gong gi 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:11993: badz+ra +aar+ya te dzahte nga dzah shar sgo rta gdong zhes pa nas /
NK025(ra)001:11994: rgyan cha lugs gong dang mthun pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:11995: zhes pa'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:11998: chu bo bzhi po'i dngos po cir sgo ma bzhi
NK025(ra)001:11999: ru bsgoms pa'i byin tshad me bzhi ru rdzogs pa'i
NK025(ra)001:12000: don rtogs nas // phrin las rnam bzhi 'du 'bral med par shog /
NK025(ra)001:12002: lha snam gnyis pa'i phyogs mtshams bzhir spor ma'i sngags
NK025(ra)001:12003: brjod la spor ma zhal gcig phyag gnyis spyan dang
NK025(ra)001:12004: bcas pa zhes gsungs pa'i don gong gi 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:12005: dkyil 'khor gnyis pa'i khyams la zhes pa nas /
NK025(ra)001:12007: zhes pa'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12010: phyogs mtshams brgyad kyi dngos po cir spor ma brgyad
NK025(ra)001:12011: du bsgoms pa'i byin snang srid sde brgyad bar chad
NK025(ra)001:12012: kun bsal nas // 'jig rten bar chad gang yang med par shog /
NK025(ra)001:12014: 'byung ba bzhi yi dngos po cir gsang ba'i yum
NK025(ra)001:12015: bzhi bsgoms pa'i byin chos nyid dwangs snyigs med pa'i
NK025(ra)001:12016: don rtogs nas // thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med par shog /
NK025(ra)001:12018: b+h+yo las dbang phyug ma'i sngags brjod la //
NK025(ra)001:12019: zhes gsungs pa'i don gong gi 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:12020: dkyil 'khor gsum pa'i khyams la zhes pa nas /
NK025(ra)001:12022: zhes pa'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12025: sgal tshigs rnams kyi dngos po cir dbang phyug nyer
NK025(ra)001:12026: brgyad bsgoms pa'i byin rnam par rtog pa'i bar chad
NK025(ra)001:12027: kun bsal nas // bar chad rkyen gyi sdug bsngal med pa shog /
NK025(ra)001:12029: lha snam bzhi par mkha' 'gro sum cu so gnyis
NK025(ra)001:12030: rang rang gi sku mdog phyag mtshan dang bcas pa
NK025(ra)001:12031: bskyed la / zhes gsungs pa'i don gong gi 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:12032: dkyil 'khor bzhi pa'i khyams la zhes pa nas /
NK025(ra)001:12033: phyag mtshan med pa rnams thod khrag 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:12034: zhes pa'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12037: so dang rus pa'i dngos po cir mkha' 'gro so
NK025(ra)001:12038: gnyis bsgoms pa'i bar du gcod pa ma lus kun
NK025(ra)001:12039: bsal nas // sgrub pa'i bar du gcod pa med par shog /
NK025(ra)001:12041: lha snam lnga par ma bdun sring bzhi'i sngags brjod pas zhal gcig phyag gnyis par bskyed /
NK025(ra)001:12042: ces gsungs pa'i don gong gi 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:12043: dkyil 'khor lnga pa'i khyams la zhes pa nas /
NK025(ra)001:12044: thor tshugs can hor lhwam gyon pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:12045: zhes pa'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12048: sha khrag rtsa yi dngos po cir ma dang sring
NK025(ra)001:12049: mo bsgoms pa'i byin tshe srog gnod pa'i bar chad
NK025(ra)001:12050: kun bsal nas / nyin mtshan rtag tu thams cad skyob par shog /
NK025(ra)001:12052: lha rnams drug par ging bco brgyad kyi sngags brjod la zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa bskyed /
NK025(ra)001:12053: ces gsungs pa'i don gong gi 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:12054: dkyil 'khor drug pa'i khyams la zhes pa nas /
NK025(ra)001:12056: zhes pa'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12058: lhu tshigs bco brgyad dngos po cir ging chen bco
NK025(ra)001:12059: brgyad bsgoms pa'i byin bsgral ba'i zhing bcu ma lus
NK025(ra)001:12060: kun bsgral nas // sangs rgyas zhing khams ma lus dag par shog /
NK025(ra)001:12062: lha snam bdun par kro d+ha kro d+hi la khro bo drug cu zhal gcig phyag gnyis so //
NK025(ra)001:12063: zhes gsungs pa'i don gong gi 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:12064: lha snam bdun par zhes pa nas /
NK025(ra)001:12065: 'di ni khro bo rol pa'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK025(ra)001:12066: zhes pa'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12069: rus mgo tshigs mgo'i dngos po cir khro bo drug
NK025(ra)001:12070: cu bsgoms pa'i byin khams gsum gdug ba ma lus
NK025(ra)001:12071: kun bsgral nas // sangs rgyas phrin las lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK025(ra)001:12073: lha snam brgyad par pho nya sum brgya drug cu
NK025(ra)001:12074: zhal gcig phyag gnyis phyag mtshan dang bcas pa bskyed
NK025(ra)001:12075: la / zhes gsungs pa'i don gong gi 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:12076: dkyil 'khor brgyad pa'i khyams la zhes pa nas /
NK025(ra)001:12077: khyams 'di ni mgyogs 'gro yid kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK025(ra)001:12079: khyams dgu pa'i ma mo drug cu yang zhor la bskyed dgos pas gong gi 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:12080: dkyil 'khor dgu pa'i khyams la zhes pa nas /
NK025(ra)001:12081: khyams 'di ni dam tshig chen po'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK025(ra)001:12082: zhes pa'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12085: rtsa bran mang po'i dngos po cir pho nya sum brgya drug cu bsgoms pa'i mthus /
NK025(ra)001:12086: dam tshig nyams dang dgra bgegs kun bsgral nas //
NK025(ra)001:12087: gnod pa'i bar chad ci yang med par shog /
NK025(ra)001:12089: lha snam dgu par rig 'dzin gyi sngags brjod la /
NK025(ra)001:12091: dkyil 'khor bcu pa'i khyams la badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra zhes pa nas /
NK025(ra)001:12092: ye shes kyi me 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa'o'i bar dang /
NK025(ra)001:12093: dkyil 'khor bcu gcig pa'i khyams la rig 'dzin bla ma zhes pa nas /
NK025(ra)001:12094: mngon sum du bzhugs par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:12095: zhes pa'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12098: skra dang ba spu'i rtog pa cir rig 'dzin khro tshogs yang sprul bsgoms pa'i mthus //
NK025(ra)001:12099: skra rtse ba spu thig les khyab gyur te //
NK025(ra)001:12100: sprul pa 'phro zhing rtog pa gar skyes pa //
NK025(ra)001:12101: der phung rang byung dkyil 'khor thob par shog /
NK025(ra)001:12103: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab /
NK025(ra)001:12105: he ru ka lngas dbu brgyan par bsam la /
NK025(ra)001:12106: badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs snyan gsan dbab /
NK025(ra)001:12108: zhes gsungs pa'i don gong gi 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:12109: lag gnyis rdo rje phyi bsdams las zhes pa nas /
NK025(ra)001:12110: mi bskyod pa mthing kha rdo rje dang dril bu
NK025(ra)001:12111: 'dzin par gyur gyi bar dbang bskur byin rlabs byas
NK025(ra)001:12112: la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12115: lus ngag yid gsum dngos po cir dbang bskur byin gyis brlabs pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK025(ra)001:12116: las dang nyon mongs ma lus kun byang nas //
NK025(ra)001:12117: sku dang ye shes lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK025(ra)001:12119: snyan gsan dbab pa ni zhes pa nas /
NK025(ra)001:12120: b+hu ta k+she tri pra ti tam pa ka ya h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:12121: zhes pa'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12124: sangs rgyas sems can dngos po cir bde gshegs spyan
NK025(ra)001:12125: drangs bstim pa'i byin ye nas gnyis su med pa'i
NK025(ra)001:12126: don rtogs nas // gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub yang gong gi 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:12127: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor chen po ru //
NK025(ra)001:12129: phyi nang mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:12130: a ti pu hoh pra t+aits+tsha hoh zhes pa'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12133: bdag dang gzhan du dngos po cir ye nas 'dres
NK025(ra)001:12134: pa chen po'i byin gnyis 'dzin gcig tu go ba'i
NK025(ra)001:12135: don gnyis su med par lhun gyis grub yang gong
NK025(ra)001:12136: gi 'phros / bde bar gshegs pa khyed ci 'dra //
NK025(ra)001:12138: bdag cag bsam pa 'grub gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:12139: ces pa'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12142: 'gro drug sems can sdug bsngal cir dam bca' rnam
NK025(ra)001:12143: gsum byas pa'i byin bsam pa mtha' ru phyin pa'i
NK025(ra)001:12144: don bdag gzhan gnyis kyi don gnyis mthar phyin shog
NK025(ra)001:12146: gnyis pa phyag rgya'i mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12148: dbang mo nyer brgyad kyi mthar /
NK025(ra)001:12149: mchod bzhes dam skong mthu dbang dngos grub stsol //
NK025(ra)001:12150: zhes pa'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12153: gzung 'dzin rnam rtog dngos po cir phyag rgya'i mchod
NK025(ra)001:12154: pa phul ba'i byin phyag rgya rnam bzhi lhun gyis
NK025(ra)001:12155: grub nas kyang // thams cad phyag rgya chen por lhun grub shog /
NK025(ra)001:12157: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK025(ra)001:12159: chu gnyis 'bul ba'i sngags sogs tshang bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12162: phyi nang gsang ba'i dngos po cir kun tu bzang po'i mchod pa phul ba yin //
NK025(ra)001:12163: dngos po thams cad mchod par gyur nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:12164: spyod yul thams cad yongs su dag par shog /
NK025(ra)001:12166: pa na pem zhes sogs lha mo bzhi bsnol gyi mchod pa /
NK025(ra)001:12167: thams cad dag cing lhun gyis grub par mdzad du gsol /
NK025(ra)001:12168: zhes pa'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12171: bdag gzhan dngos po khyad par cir mchod pa rnam
NK025(ra)001:12172: lnga phul ba'i byin thams cad 'gag pa med pa'i
NK025(ra)001:12173: don rtogs nas // 'khor gsum ma lus yongs su dag rtsa bar /
NK025(ra)001:12177: rang byung gdod nas rnam par dag /
NK025(ra)001:12179: gdod mo ro langs 'jig rten ma tshogs la //
NK025(ra)001:12180: rnam dag thugs rje de nas dkyus la zhugs te /
NK025(ra)001:12182: srin mo'i cha lugs shin tu 'jigs par ston //
NK025(ra)001:12183: phyogs mtshams 'dzin pa'i spor ma brgyad rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:12184: rnam dag thugs rje dpal chen sku la 'du 'bral med pa yis //
NK025(ra)001:12185: ye shes thugs kyi dgyes sde rnam bzhi la //
NK025(ra)001:12186: rnam dag thugs rje 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor chen po'i mtha' bsrung pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:12187: dam can dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad la //
NK025(ra)001:12188: rnam dag thugs rje khams gsum gdug pa ma lus 'dul mdzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:12189: khro bo khro mo rol pa'i tshogs rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:12190: rnam dag thugs rje phrin las ma lus myur du 'grub byeed pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:12191: rdo rje mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis la //
NK025(ra)001:12192: rnam dag thugs rje zhing bcu ma lus gnas nas 'dren byed pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:12193: rdo rje ka tar ging chen bco brgyad la //
NK025(ra)001:12194: rnam dag thugs rje ye shes rol pa'i phyag rgya cir snang ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:12195: mgyogs ma pho nya sum brgya drug cu la //
NK025(ra)001:12196: rnam dag thugs rje phyi 'khor bsrung zhing nang 'khor skyong mdzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:12197: dam can rgya mtsho ma mo'i tshogs rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:12198: rnam dag thugs rje rdo rje gral 'chang rim par ston mdzad pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:12199: rnal 'byor dbang phyug rig 'dzin tshogs rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:12200: rnam dag thugs rje yang gong gi 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:12201: dpal gyi 'khor tshogs badz+ra a ra li //
NK025(ra)001:12203: bdud rtsi dngos grub blang ba /
NK025(ra)001:12204: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha /
NK025(ra)001:12205: zhes pa'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12208: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams cir bdud rtsi sman
NK025(ra)001:12209: gyis mchod pa'i byin 'phral du skabs 'tshol gnod pa
NK025(ra)001:12210: kun bsal nas // skye shi med par lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK025(ra)001:12212: khyad par sgrub pa chen po nas /
NK025(ra)001:12213: pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi'i bar brjod la zhes gsungs pa'i don tshig ma gcig kyang gong 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:12214: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka i dam zhes pa nas /
NK025(ra)001:12215: pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:12216: zhes pa'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12219: stong phrag brgyad cu bgegs rnams cir dam rdzas gtor
NK025(ra)001:12220: ma 'bul ba'i byin yun du glags lta'i gnod pa
NK025(ra)001:12221: kun zhi nas // 'pho 'gyur med par lhun gyis grub rtsa bar /
NK025(ra)001:12222: yang bdag gi thugs ka nas ram la me 'phros zhes pa nas /
NK025(ra)001:12223: mchod pa yan chad brjod la zhes gsungs pa'i don yang gong gi 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:12224: thog mar bdag nyid rtogs goms bsgral //
NK025(ra)001:12226: b+au dza badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham gi bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12229: chags sdang rnam gnyis dngos po cir tan gan rnam
NK025(ra)001:12230: gnyis mchod pa'i byin spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i
NK025(ra)001:12231: don bdag gzhan don gnyis lhun gyis grub par shog
NK025(ra)001:12233: mnyam pa'i sgrub rdzas chen po 'di //
NK025(ra)001:12235: sh+r+ai ban kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:12236: zhes pa'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12239: yul dang dbang po'i dngos po cir 'dod yon lnga yi mchod pa phul pa'i mthus //
NK025(ra)001:12240: yul sems gnyis su med pa'i don spyod yul ma lus yongs su dag par shog /
NK025(ra)001:12242: rak+ta tshar gsum gyis mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12243: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK025(ra)001:12245: h+aum b+h+yo'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12248: chags sdang rnam gnyis dngos po cir khams gsum khrag gi rgya mtsho phul ba'i mthus //
NK025(ra)001:12249: nyon mongs sems su gsal ba'i don sems nyid dbye ba med pa'i don rtogs shog /
NK025(ra)001:12251: phyi snod b+han+d+ha zhes sogs dang /
NK025(ra)001:12252: skal bzang rmad byung zhes sogs gsungs pa'i don gong gi 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:12253: sgeg pa dpa' pa 'jigs su rung ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:12255: badz+ra pra t+aits+tsha hoh'i bar brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12258: zhen cing chags pa'i dngos po cir khams gsum khrag gi rgya mtshos mchod pa'i mthus //
NK025(ra)001:12259: dug lnga ma lus rtsad nas dag gyur nas //
NK025(ra)001:12260: gnyis med mchod pa lhun gyis grub na mo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:12261: nyon mongs sdug bsngal dngos po cir glu dang rol mo sgra snyan phul ba yis //
NK025(ra)001:12262: thams cad theg pa chen po'i sgrar gyur nas //
NK025(ra)001:12263: gsang sngags don nyid kun gyis rtogs phyogs bcu dus
NK025(ra)001:12264: bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag nyid
NK025(ra)001:12265: bcom ldan 'das dpal chen mchog he ru ka la
NK025(ra)001:12266: sogs pa he ru ka dgu klong 'bar ba'i 'khor
NK025(ra)001:12267: khro bo khro mo bsam gyis mi khyab pa thams
NK025(ra)001:12268: cad gsan cing bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK025(ra)001:12269: bdag cag rnal 'byor gyi mchod pa dam pa rig
NK025(ra)001:12270: pa'i khyad par phyi nang gsang ba gsum du phul
NK025(ra)001:12271: bas sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud mnyes pa chen pos
NK025(ra)001:12273: de'i byin rlabs kyis mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams
NK025(ra)001:12274: cad rdo rje 'chang gi gral thob par gyur cig
NK025(ra)001:12275: / bdag gi dam tshig nyams pa thams cad skong nas dngos grub kyi snod du gyur te /
NK025(ra)001:12276: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sar mngon par
NK025(ra)001:12277: rdzogs pas sangs rgyas nas 'khor ba kar dag par
NK025(ra)001:12278: gyur cig / a la la hoh dam tshig zhu
NK025(ra)001:12279: zhes gsungs pa'i don rang gang 'dod kyi gsol ba
NK025(ra)001:12280: gdab la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12283: yid la bsam pa'i dngos po cir smon lam sngon
NK025(ra)001:12284: du btab pa'i byin yid la ci bsam lhun grub
NK025(ra)001:12285: don 'gro don ma lus lhun gyis grub khams gsum
NK025(ra)001:12286: lha yi dkyil 'khor du bsams la 'dzab bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:12287: khro bo la lha mang nyung nges pa med pas gang mos bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:12288: zhes gsungs pa'i don spro na khro bo'i 'dzab khang dbye ba'i don ltar lha so so'i 'dzab bzla /
NK025(ra)001:12290: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:12295: rgyu 'bras rtsol ba'i sdug bsngal cir bsnyen sgrub rnam bzhi'i 'dzab bsnyen byas pa'i mthus //
NK025(ra)001:12296: thams cad kun du bzang po'i don dngos grub rnam
NK025(ra)001:12297: gsum lhun gyis grub de nas tshogs bya ba ni
NK025(ra)001:12298: / zhi khro gnyis la tshogs 'khor so sor bshams te /
NK025(ra)001:12299: thog mar zhi ba'i tshogs bsang ba /
NK025(ra)001:12300: ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai sarba dra byam zhes sogs nas bzung /
NK025(ra)001:12301: bdud rtsi gsang nan 'bul ba'i mthar /
NK025(ra)001:12303: zhes pa'i bar dang tshogs la rol pa'ang bya /
NK025(ra)001:12304: de bzhin du khro bo'i tshogs gsang ba /
NK025(ra)001:12305: h+r+aihbi shwa bi shud+d+he zhes sogs nas /
NK025(ra)001:12306: tshogs tha ma'i mtshan ma ston cig gi bar byas
NK025(ra)001:12307: la zhi khro gnyis kyi tshogs thog mtha' bar gsum
NK025(ra)001:12308: bgyis pa'i don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12311: 'dod yon lnga yi dngos po cir tshogs kyi mchod pa byas pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK025(ra)001:12312: mtha' la zhen pa'i gdung ba kun bral nas //
NK025(ra)001:12313: bde ba chen po'i longs spyod rdzogs par shog /
NK025(ra)001:12315: de nas zhi ba'i lhag ma dang khro bo'i lhag
NK025(ra)001:12316: ma byas la zhes gsungs pa snga 'gyur phyogs phal
NK025(ra)001:12317: cher lhag ma sgrub pa thon khar ma gtogs mi
NK025(ra)001:12318: mdzad kyang / bka' ma la gtong srol kyang 'dug
NK025(ra)001:12319: pas lhag ma zhi khro gnyis so so'i lugs sam
NK025(ra)001:12320: yang na 'og tu 'byung ba bzhin btang kyang chog
NK025(ra)001:12321: mdzad kyang / la / mi gtong na gtsang lhag
NK025(ra)001:12322: dang btsog lhag bsres pa la bdud rtsi bran te
NK025(ra)001:12323: bzhag la phyir mi gtong zhing don gsal gdab pa
NK025(ra)001:12324: mdzad kyang / la / ni / rtsa bar /
NK025(ra)001:12326: lo zur zla skeg gnod pa cir mkha' 'gro dbang phyug lhag ma phud kyis mchod pa yis //
NK025(ra)001:12327: mo ngan rmi lam ngan pa kun bsal nas //
NK025(ra)001:12328: bar chad rkyen gyi sdug bsngal med par shog /
NK025(ra)001:12330: brtan skyong byas la zhes gsungs pa snga 'gyur spyi
NK025(ra)001:12331: lugs ltar brtan ma bskyang zhing don gsal gdab pa
NK025(ra)001:12334: 'jig rten srin mo 'gro drug cir gtor ma phri bskol med par bsngosa pa yis //
NK025(ra)001:12335: 'jig rten srin mo 'gro drug kun tshim nas //
NK025(ra)001:12336: zhing bcu sgrol zhing 'gro don rdzogs par shog /
NK025(ra)001:12338: zhi khro rnam gnyis kyi rjes mchod byas la bsdus //
NK025(ra)001:12340: dkyil 'khor gnyis kar thun mong du /
NK025(ra)001:12341: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK025(ra)001:12342: zhes sogs kyi sgo nas kun bzang zhabs bsil dang /
NK025(ra)001:12343: pa na pem sogs lha mo bzhi bsnol gyis mchod /
NK025(ra)001:12345: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:12347: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le che ho'i bar dang /
NK025(ra)001:12350: gtum chen dus mtha'i me chen 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:12352: rdo rje rlung ste 'thor rlung che hoh'i bar gyis bstod /
NK025(ra)001:12353: yig brgya tshar gsum gyis lhag chad bkang la /
NK025(ra)001:12354: mdun bskyed dkyil 'khor ma bsdus kyi bar du brtan par bzhugs gsol bya ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:12355: 'dir ni gzugs dang lhan cig tu //
NK025(ra)001:12356: zhes sogs bya zhing su pra tish+thasa me tog gtor /
NK025(ra)001:12357: bdag bskyed du snang pa de nyid ka dag gi klong du mi dmigs par bzhag la /
NK025(ra)001:12358: slar yang rang thun mtshams kyi lha rdo rje sems
NK025(ra)001:12359: dpa'i rnam par bltas la don gsal gdab pa ni
NK025(ra)001:12362: gzung 'dzin rnam gnyis dngos por cir lha dang gzhal
NK025(ra)001:12363: yas bsdus pa'i byin rtag chad gnyis su 'dzin pa'i
NK025(ra)001:12364: mtha' bral nas // snang srid chos kyi sku ru rtogs rtsa bar /
NK025(ra)001:12365: de nas zhi khro so so'i lus gnas go bgo lus bsrung byas nas zhes gsungs pa'i don /
NK025(ra)001:12366: se ston rin chen rgyal mtshan gyi bzhed pa ltar
NK025(ra)001:12367: rang thun mtshams kyi rdo rje sems dpar gsal ba'i
NK025(ra)001:12368: spyi bor zla ba la gnas pa'i ham de las
NK025(ra)001:12369: 'phros 'dus lus rdo rje'i go khrab kyis gtams par
NK025(ra)001:12370: bsam / a tsan+d+ra man+da la ham /
NK025(ra)001:12373: rdo rje phyi bsdoms kyi sor mo bsnol /
NK025(ra)001:12374: mthe bong gnyis gshibs te bsgreng /
NK025(ra)001:12375: mthil gnyis phye ba rdo rje go cha'i phyag rgya dpral bar gtugs la /
NK025(ra)001:12376: badz+ra k+aa w+aa tsi rak+sha rak+sha /
NK025(ra)001:12378: lus bsrung ni khro bo rdo rje gnod sbyin dang
NK025(ra)001:12379: mi 'chi thal sbyor te gnyis kyis gsang gnas su
NK025(ra)001:12380: bzhengs / lte ba dang bcu drug mdor bcings /
NK025(ra)001:12381: snying ga dang tshigs pa bdun par bcings /
NK025(ra)001:12383: dpral ba dang ltag khung du 'ching ba'i tshul /
NK025(ra)001:12384: spyi bor bzhengs pa'i tshul gyis bsrung bar bsam la
NK025(ra)001:12385: lag gnyis rdo rje khu tshur gyis mdzub mo gnyis
NK025(ra)001:12386: gnas so sor bsnol pa rdo rje bsrung ba'i rgyas
NK025(ra)001:12388: dar dkar pos gnas dgur mdud par bsam la lag
NK025(ra)001:12389: gnyis spyi bor rtse sprad pa gsham brdab ste badz+ra
NK025(ra)001:12390: tu sh+ya hoh rat+na mu ka ta tram tram tram
NK025(ra)001:12391: tram tram +aar+ya lam bo d+ha ra badz+ra d+r+ai sh+ya
NK025(ra)001:12392: hoh zhes brjod la don gsal gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12395: rnam rtog chos kyi dngos por cir spyod lam rgyun gyi ting 'dzin byin rlabs pas //
NK025(ra)001:12396: bdag nyid yi dam lha ru gyur nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:12397: 'gro don ma lus rdzogs par byed par shog /
NK025(ra)001:12400: des lung gi las byang grub /
NK025(ra)001:12401: lung gi zhi khro'i las byang 'di la khams lugs
NK025(ra)001:12402: su glegs bam dang por lha sta gon gyi tshe
NK025(ra)001:12403: bdag mdun bum gsum ga la tshar gsum bldabs 'dug
NK025(ra)001:12404: pa bsgom bde rgyu med pa'i khar mgo nyog sum
NK025(ra)001:12405: brtsegs zhes pa sgra ji bzhin par snang /
NK025(ra)001:12406: glegs bam gsum par a nu yo ga dngos bstan
NK025(ra)001:12407: gyi tshe legs par bshad pa 'di ltar yang snang
NK025(ra)001:12408: ste / mtshams gcod kyi skabs bdag lus kyi phyogs
NK025(ra)001:12409: mtshams steng 'og tu khro bo bcu gsal 'debs pa
NK025(ra)001:12410: ste / dang / zhi ba'i lung gi dus spyi bo'i gnas lngar rigs lnga yab yum bcu /
NK025(ra)001:12411: mig la sa snying yab yum /
NK025(ra)001:12412: rna g.yas nam snying yab yum /
NK025(ra)001:12413: lce g.yas spyan ras gzigs yab yum /
NK025(ra)001:12414: mig g.yon byams pa yab yum /
NK025(ra)001:12415: rna ba g.yon sgrib sel yab yum /
NK025(ra)001:12416: sna g.yon kun bzang yab yum /
NK025(ra)001:12418: phrag gong g.yas g.yon dung ke mdun rgyab la sgo ba yab yum /
NK025(ra)001:12423: zhabs mthil gnyis rnams la thub drug /
NK025(ra)001:12424: de bzhin du khro bo'i skabs kyang bdag lus dur khrod kyi gzhal yas khang lhun grub /
NK025(ra)001:12429: rgyu ma rnam la rgyud lung gi he ru ka dgu /
NK025(ra)001:12430: lus kyi g.yon gyi char de dag gi yum dgu /
NK025(ra)001:12431: g.yas kyi rtsib ma brgyad la ma mo brgyad /
NK025(ra)001:12432: g.yon rtsib brgyad la phra men brgyad /
NK025(ra)001:12433: mdun rgyab phyogs mtshams rnams su spor ma brgyad /
NK025(ra)001:12434: sgal tshigs nyer brgyad la dbang mo nyer brgyad /
NK025(ra)001:12435: yan lag bzhi la sgo ma bzhi /
NK025(ra)001:12436: so sum cu rtsa gnyis la mkha' 'gro so gnyis /
NK025(ra)001:12437: gzugs drug mgo dang bdun la ma mo bdun /
NK025(ra)001:12438: ne'u bseg la sring mo bzhi /
NK025(ra)001:12439: lde'u rtsibs bco brgyad la ging bco brgyad /
NK025(ra)001:12440: rus mgo drug cu la khro bo drug cu /
NK025(ra)001:12441: rtsa sum brgyad drug cu la pho nya sum brgyad drug cu /
NK025(ra)001:12442: skra bzhi khri bzhi 'bum dang ba spu bye ba
NK025(ra)001:12443: bzhi khri bzhi 'bum gyi sprul pa'i pho nya rnams
NK025(ra)001:12445: spyir rgyud ma h+aa yo ga la phyi dkyil dang /
NK025(ra)001:12446: lung a nu yo ga la lus dkyil bshad pas shin du 'thad par mngon zhing /
NK025(ra)001:12447: lung gi las byang 'di rnal 'byor pa rgan po
NK025(ra)001:12448: rnams kyi don ched du lta ba che ba dang
NK025(ra)001:12452: 'bras bu mthar phyin par bya ba'i phyir rgyud las lung du bsgyur zhes dang /
NK025(ra)001:12453: lus la lha bkod de yid kyis gsal btab nas /
NK025(ra)001:12454: na mo h+aum gis gzi byin bskyed ces gsungs pa'i
NK025(ra)001:12455: don yin pas rgyud lung man ngag la shin tu
NK025(ra)001:12456: 'dris pa'i rnal 'byor pa rgan po rnams kyi rgyud
NK025(ra)001:12457: ltar mngon par rtogs pa nges pas /
NK025(ra)001:12458: phyi mtshon byed dpe'i dkyil 'khor la rag ma lus
NK025(ra)001:12459: par nang zab mo rdo rje lus kyi dkyil 'khor
NK025(ra)001:12460: gyi yid kyis gsal gdab cing don gnyis med a
NK025(ra)001:12461: ti yo ga'i rol par thag bcad de /
NK025(ra)001:12462: tshig rjes don dran gyi tshul du gsal btab pas
NK025(ra)001:12463: rgyud lung man ngag gi mdo don gcig tu 'dril
NK025(ra)001:12464: ba'i nyams len bzang po zhig 'byung la /
NK025(ra)001:12465: rgyud ltar mngon rtogs gsal mi thebs pa rnams kyis
NK025(ra)001:12466: lung gi phrin las nyams su len mi shes pas
NK025(ra)001:12467: / de ltar na zur lugs su gong ltar mdzad srol 'dug pa shin tu legs pas /
NK025(ra)001:12468: 'di lta bu'i go don rnams thos bsam sgom gsum
NK025(ra)001:12469: gyis gtan la phab ste gong ltar nyams su blang
NK025(ra)001:12470: ngo // 'di ni rab gnas kyi sngon du las gzhung bsrang ba'i dod yin no //
NK025(ra)001:12471: de ltar bdag mdun gyi sgrub mchod lung gi phrin las rgyud dang sbyar ba grub nas /
NK025(ra)001:12472: rtsa bar skabs 'dir lhag ma gtong ba 'dug kyang
NK025(ra)001:12473: lhag ma'i rgyu mtshan gong du smos zin pa ltar
NK025(ra)001:12474: / skabs 'dir bum bskyed gsungs pa rab gnas kyi
NK025(ra)001:12475: lha la dbang bskur ba'i bu ma pa yin te
NK025(ra)001:12477: de nas bum pa bskyed pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12478: sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na d+ha rma d+h+aa tu swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:12479: e yam bam sum lam ram s+pha ra /
NK025(ra)001:12481: e a ka sha man+da la /
NK025(ra)001:12482: yam ba yu ta man+da la /
NK025(ra)001:12483: bam a mri ta kun+da li man+da la /
NK025(ra)001:12485: lam rat+na pra b+h+aa wa man+da la /
NK025(ra)001:12486: ram badz+ra dz+wa la man+da la /
NK025(ra)001:12490: du ti rat+na s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra pad+ma man+da la /
NK025(ra)001:12492: badz+ra tsakra rat+na pad+ma khat+ga g+han+de s+pha ra /
NK025(ra)001:12504: bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha dz+ny+aa na d+h+aa tu +aahh+aum s+w+aa +aamhh+aa /
NK025(ra)001:12505: ma h+aa shu nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na +aa dar+sha sa
NK025(ra)001:12506: man+ta pra d+ya bek+sha kro t+ya nush+tha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra
NK025(ra)001:12510: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta
NK025(ra)001:12511: a nu r+aa ga p+au dza badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa
NK025(ra)001:12512: +aat+ma ko&a ham / zhes brjod bum rdzas tshang ba blug /
NK025(ra)001:12513: kha rgyan mgul chings gzungs thag can du dbang bskur /
NK025(ra)001:12518: a ti pu hoh pra ti dza hohs phyag rgya /
NK025(ra)001:12521: sngags kyis sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis la dbul /
NK025(ra)001:12527: rgya mtsho lnga'i smon lam btab la bum pa nub tu dgod /
NK025(ra)001:12528: ces gsungs pa'i don bum pa rdzas ldan kha rgyan
NK025(ra)001:12529: mgul chings gzungs thag dang bcas pa slob dpon gyi
NK025(ra)001:12531: slob dpon kun tu bzang po'i nga rgyal la gnas pas /
NK025(ra)001:12532: sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na d+harma d+ha tu swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:12535: e yam bam sum lam ram rnams bum pa'i 'og tu gnas pa las /
NK025(ra)001:12538: e a ka sha man+da la /
NK025(ra)001:12539: yam ba yu ta man+da la /
NK025(ra)001:12540: bam a mri ta kun+da li man+da la /
NK025(ra)001:12542: lam rat+na pra b+h+aa wa man+da la /
NK025(ra)001:12543: ram badz+ra dz+wa la man+da la /
NK025(ra)001:12544: zhes 'byung rim gyi steng du b+h+r+aum s+pha ra sam
NK025(ra)001:12545: ha bum pa zlum po tshad dang mtshan nyid thams
NK025(ra)001:12546: cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i nang du /
NK025(ra)001:12547: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he du ti rat+na s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra pad+ma man+da la /
NK025(ra)001:12548: rin po che sna tshogs las grub pa'i gzhal yas
NK025(ra)001:12549: khang mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i nang
NK025(ra)001:12550: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi'i lte ba dang rtsibs bzhir seng+ge
NK025(ra)001:12551: glang chen rta mchog rma bya shang shang gis bteg
NK025(ra)001:12552: pa'i rin po che'i khri pad+ma dang nyi zla'i gdan
NK025(ra)001:12553: lngar gyur / gdan lnga'i steng du h+aum t+r+aam h+r+aih+aah sa bon lngar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:12554: s+pha ra sam ha badz+ra tsakra rat+na pad+ma khat+ga g+han+de /
NK025(ra)001:12555: dbus su rdo rje dang dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:12556: shar du 'khor lo dang dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:12557: lhor rin po che dang dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:12558: nub tu pad+ma dang dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:12559: byang du ral gri dang dril bu te phyag mtshan lngar gyur /
NK025(ra)001:12560: s+pha ra sam ha h+aum badz+ra d+h+rika /
NK025(ra)001:12562: dbus su mi bskyod rdo rje sems dpa' mthing kha
NK025(ra)001:12563: zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas rdo rje thugs ka dang
NK025(ra)001:12564: g.yon dril bu dkur brten pa la yum dbyings phyug
NK025(ra)001:12565: ma sngon mo g.yas dril bu dang g.yon rdo rje
NK025(ra)001:12569: shar du rnam snang dkar po g.yas 'khor lo dang
NK025(ra)001:12570: g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa yum spyan ma dkar mo
NK025(ra)001:12574: lhor rin 'byung yab yum gnyis ka ser po rin po che dang dril bu 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:12577: nub tu snang ba mtha' yas yab yum gnyis ka dmar po pad+ma dang dril bu 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:12580: byang du don grub yab yum gnyis ka ljang gu ral gri dang dril bu 'dzin pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:12581: bum nang gi rigs lnga'i lha la dbang bskur ba
NK025(ra)001:12582: dang byin gyis brlabs pa'i dmigs pa dang bcas te
NK025(ra)001:12583: gong bzhin phyag rgya bcas te /
NK025(ra)001:12584: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:12591: tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:12592: zhes ye shes lngas dbang bskur zhing sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab bo //
NK025(ra)001:12593: badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum dzah zhes snyan bsnan te /
NK025(ra)001:12594: e h+ye hi b+ha ga w+aan ma h+aa k+aa ru
NK025(ra)001:12595: ni ka d+r+ai sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh sa
NK025(ra)001:12596: ma ya s+t+wam / zhes spyan drangs /
NK025(ra)001:12600: badz+ra g+han+de hoh zhes bum pa'i dam tshig pa rnams la bstim /
NK025(ra)001:12601: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+rasa brtan par byas /
NK025(ra)001:12602: a ti pu hoh pra t+aits+tsha hohs phyag bya /
NK025(ra)001:12603: kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyi mchod pa 'di ltar /
NK025(ra)001:12604: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK025(ra)001:12605: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i ye shes kyis //
NK025(ra)001:12606: srid pa rgya mtsho mtha' yas kun //
NK025(ra)001:12607: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK025(ra)001:12608: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yo bi shwa mu
NK025(ra)001:12609: khe b+h+yahsarba tat+kham ut+ga te s+pha ra na hi mam
NK025(ra)001:12610: ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:12611: yang dag don du dag mod kyang //
NK025(ra)001:12612: 'gro ba yongs kyi don slad du //
NK025(ra)001:12613: phyag dang zhabs gnyis bsil nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:12614: rdo rje'i gdan la bzhugs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:12615: +aa ha ra +aa ha ra sarba bid+y+aa d+h+aa ra
NK025(ra)001:12616: p+au dzi te na mahs man+ta bud+d+ha n+aam ga ga
NK025(ra)001:12617: na kham sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:12620: ti pu pa ra muh sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid d+hoo /
NK025(ra)001:12621: sa ma yo ta muh sarba ma h+aa su kha sid d+hoo /
NK025(ra)001:12622: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au /
NK025(ra)001:12623: pa na pem sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga push+pe pu /
NK025(ra)001:12624: pa na pem sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga +aa lo ke
NK025(ra)001:12625: h+r+aih pa na pem sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga gan+d+he gan
NK025(ra)001:12628: bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha dz+ny+aa na d+h+aa
NK025(ra)001:12629: tu +aah na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa
NK025(ra)001:12630: pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:12633: u pa b+h+yoh ka ma la m+aa la badz+ra a
NK025(ra)001:12634: mri ta ha ra na pra t+aits+tsha b+ha ga wan
NK025(ra)001:12635: dzahh+aum bam hoh a la la hoh pa na pem
NK025(ra)001:12637: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK025(ra)001:12639: a la la ste mchod par 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:12640: zhes lhag pa ting nge 'dzin dang //
NK025(ra)001:12641: ri rab chen po'i gling bzhi la //
NK025(ra)001:12643: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med par //
NK025(ra)001:12645: bza' dang bca' dang btung dang bgo //
NK025(ra)001:12647: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:12648: zhes sogs glu ye shes kyi mchod pa rnams phul /
NK025(ra)001:12649: rgya mtsho lnga'i smon lam gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12650: hoh rgyal ba rgya mtsho dgongs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:12651: mchod pa rgya mtsho bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:12652: nyams chag rgya mtsho bskang du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:12653: dngos grub rgya mtsho stsal du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:12654: phrin las rgya mtsho sgrub tu gsol //
NK025(ra)001:12656: bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha dz+nya na d+ha tu a /
NK025(ra)001:12657: zhes ci 'grub bzlas mthar bzhi bsnol gyis mchod /
NK025(ra)001:12659: yig brgyas lhag chad bskang ste lha rnams mi zhu bar dkyil 'khor gyi nub phyogs su bkod do //
NK025(ra)001:12661: de nas chu bdun tshan gnyis brtag pa gsum gyis byin gyis brlabs te /
NK025(ra)001:12662: zhes 'byung bas brtag pa gsum ni /
NK025(ra)001:12663: swa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ho sarba d+harma swa b+h+aa wa bi shud+d+ho&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:12665: spyi ltar chos nyid rnam dag gi phyag rgya bcas te /
NK025(ra)001:12666: zhi khro'i chu bdun tshan gnyis kyi ma dag pa sbyangs /
NK025(ra)001:12667: de dag kyang rnam pa so so'i byed las dang ldan par bsam la /
NK025(ra)001:12668: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga ta b+h+yohbi shwa mu khe
NK025(ra)001:12669: b+h+yahsarba th+aa kham ut+ga te s+pha ra na i mam
NK025(ra)001:12670: ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:12671: lan gsum dang nam mkha' mdzod kyi phyag rgyas cher spel /
NK025(ra)001:12672: ngo bo bdud rtsi'i khrus chas kyi rang bzhin du gyur pa bsam la /
NK025(ra)001:12673: badz+ra a mri ta kun+da li ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:12675: bdud rtsi'i thal sbyor gyi phyag rgyas bdud rtsir bsgyur zhing byin gyis brlabs te /
NK025(ra)001:12676: dkyil 'khor gyi byang du dgod par gsungs kyang shar
NK025(ra)001:12677: de nyid du bzhag pa khrus kyi tshe phyag len
NK025(ra)001:12679: de nas rgyal thebs kyi rtsa ba las kyi zhi khro'i gzhung bsrang /
NK025(ra)001:12680: zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor bskyed ye shes lngas dbang bskur /
NK025(ra)001:12681: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs /
NK025(ra)001:12682: 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab pa yan chad bya /
NK025(ra)001:12686: zhes gsungs pa'i don rgyas pa'i sbyin sreg dang 'brel
NK025(ra)001:12687: nas slar yang las gzhung bsrang dgos kyang ha cang
NK025(ra)001:12688: spros pas dub par snang bas re zhig bzhag go
NK025(ra)001:12689: // des rab gnas la spyi don brgyad kyis bstan pa'i dang po sngon 'gro bstan zin to //
NK025(ra)001:12690: rab gnas kyi spyi don gnyis pa ni rtsa bar /
NK025(ra)001:12691: gnyis pa teng 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12692: rang rdo rje gzhon nur bskyed la /
NK025(ra)001:12693: zhes gsungs pa'i don rang rdo rje gzhon nu zhal gsum phyag drug yum dang bcas par bltas la /
NK025(ra)001:12695: zhes pas phyogs bcur nyi ma'i gdan /
NK025(ra)001:12696: sgrub khang gi khro mtshams kyi phur pa gdab pa'i sar /
NK025(ra)001:12697: sum+b+ha lan bcus phyogs skyong bcu bkug te bsgyel ba'i
NK025(ra)001:12698: gdan la rang gi thugs ka nas h+aum bcus khro
NK025(ra)001:12699: bo bcu bskyed la bskul ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:12701: dbang mchog bsgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK025(ra)001:12702: nga ni dkyil 'khor las byed kyis //
NK025(ra)001:12703: phyogs skyong bcu po mnan pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:12704: 'khor gyi gdon tshogs ma lus kun //
NK025(ra)001:12705: dus gsum sangs rgyas bka' byung gis //
NK025(ra)001:12707: badz+ra kro d+hi sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:12709: rang rdo rje gzhon nur gsal bas khro bo bcu
NK025(ra)001:12710: spros zin nas gnas 'gyur te badz+ra he ru kar
NK025(ra)001:12711: bskyed la / badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:12713: ces khro bo bcu'i sngags brjod la phur pa phyogs bcur gdab bo //
NK025(ra)001:12714: zhes 'byung yang phur gdab gong du grub pas phur pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:12715: lha de rnams gnyis su med par bsam mo //
NK025(ra)001:12717: de nas gsang ba'i dris sbyang /
NK025(ra)001:12718: bdag nyid kun bzang yab yum sbyor ba'i mkha' nas rdo rje sems dpa' mdun du phyungs la /
NK025(ra)001:12719: rdor sems kyi thugs ka'i h+aum las ram yam kham gis dkyil 'khor gyi dngos mtshan sbyangs la /
NK025(ra)001:12720: zhes gsungs pa'i don dkyil 'khor gyi lha la rab tu gnas pa'i phyir /
NK025(ra)001:12722: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta a las
NK025(ra)001:12723: bdag nyid gzhi'i kun tu bzang po mthing dkar dmar
NK025(ra)001:12724: ba'i zhal gsum phyag drug gi dang po gnyis byang
NK025(ra)001:12726: bar pa gnyis rdo rje dang dril bu /
NK025(ra)001:12727: tha ma gnyis mnyam gzhag gi phyag rgya mdzad pa /
NK025(ra)001:12728: yum kun tu bzang mo sngon mo dang mnyam par sbyor ba mtshan dpes spras la /
NK025(ra)001:12729: dar dang rin po che'i rgyan can seng khri pad
NK025(ra)001:12730: zlar rdo rje'i skyil krung du bzhugs pa'i yab yum
NK025(ra)001:12731: snyoms par zhugs pa'i sbyor mtshams nas las kyi lha
NK025(ra)001:12732: rdo rje sems dpa' dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis
NK025(ra)001:12733: rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin pa zhig mdun du
NK025(ra)001:12734: 'phros / rdor sems de'i thugs ka'i h+aum las me
NK025(ra)001:12735: rlung chu gsum gyi sa bon ram yam kham 'phros
NK025(ra)001:12736: pa las me rlung chu gsum byung ste dkyil 'khor
NK025(ra)001:12737: gyi mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i dngos po rnams mes bsregs
NK025(ra)001:12739: chus bkrus par bsam la lag gnyis thal mo sbyar
NK025(ra)001:12740: ba'i bar du me tog gi phreng ba bzung ste
NK025(ra)001:12744: mi gnas pa'i ye shes chen po'i bdag nyid phyag
NK025(ra)001:12745: rgya'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs thams cad bdag la
NK025(ra)001:12747: da ltar yang bdag cag gis mtha' yas pa'i sems
NK025(ra)001:12748: can thams cad 'khor ba las bsgral ba'i lha tshogs
NK025(ra)001:12749: rnams la rab tu gnas pa'i phrin las bgyi bar
NK025(ra)001:12750: 'tshal bas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis bdag
NK025(ra)001:12754: rab gnas ye shes kyi snang ba thob par mdzad du gsol /
NK025(ra)001:12755: zhes pas phreng ba dkyil 'khor du dor /
NK025(ra)001:12756: zhes gsungs pa'i don me tog dkyil 'khor du dor /
NK025(ra)001:12757: dkyil 'khor pa rnams kyis slar yang me tog de rang gi mgo bor bcings par bsam ste /
NK025(ra)001:12758: rat+na m+aa le a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:12759: zhes dam tshig rdo rje'i phyag rgyas blangs te mgo bor bcing ngo //
NK025(ra)001:12761: de nas dkyil 'khor lha rnams rten bskyed bya ba'i
NK025(ra)001:12762: dod lta bu'i sngon du mi dmigs par sbyang ba
NK025(ra)001:12764: thal mo khong stong du sbyar /
NK025(ra)001:12765: sh+au nya t+aa bdun brjod pas /
NK025(ra)001:12766: gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i klong /
NK025(ra)001:12767: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes su bsgom zhes 'byung ba ltar bya /
NK025(ra)001:12769: yang rdor sems kyi thugs ka nas 'byung ba rim
NK025(ra)001:12770: brtsegs la b+h+r+aum smug nag las 'dus pa chen po'i
NK025(ra)001:12771: dkyil 'khor bskyed / yang thugs ka nas h+aum bco brgyad phyung la he ru ka dgu /
NK025(ra)001:12772: ha brgyad las goo r+ai brgyad /
NK025(ra)001:12774: phata bzhi las sgo ma bzhi /
NK025(ra)001:12775: a brgyad las spor ma brgyad /
NK025(ra)001:12776: dzahh+aum bam hohls gsang yum bzhi /
NK025(ra)001:12777: b+h+yo nyer brgyad las dbang phyug nyer brgyad de khrag 'thung rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor bskyed /
NK025(ra)001:12778: e so gnyis las phrin las myur mgyogs kyi dkyil 'khor bskyed /
NK025(ra)001:12779: h+aum drug cu las khro bo rol pa'i dkyil 'khor /
NK025(ra)001:12780: dzahh+aum bam hohdruga cu las mgyogs 'gro yid kyi dkyil 'khor bskyed /
NK025(ra)001:12781: ma drug cu las dam tshig rgya mtsho'i dkyil 'khor /
NK025(ra)001:12782: dzahbaco brgyad las sgrol ba ging gi dkyil 'khor /
NK025(ra)001:12783: b+h+yo bcu gcis las ma bdun sring bzhi dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor bskyed de /
NK025(ra)001:12784: de'i steng du yang rdor sems kyi thugs ka nas zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bskyed de /
NK025(ra)001:12785: zhes gsungs pa'i don sngar yod gsal 'debs kyi tshul
NK025(ra)001:12786: du bdag blo sbyang phyir rten dang brten par bcas
NK025(ra)001:12788: gong gi mdun bskyed skabs ltar thog mar khro bo bskyed de /
NK025(ra)001:12789: bdag gi thugs ka nas e yam ram bam kem
NK025(ra)001:12790: ram rnams chad de dkyil 'khor gyi 'og gzhi brtsegs
NK025(ra)001:12791: mar 'khod / ces 'byung rim bskyed ba nas bzung /
NK025(ra)001:12792: rten gzhal yas khang bcu gcig sbrag yongs su rdzogs
NK025(ra)001:12793: pa rten dang brten par bcas pa thams cad tshang
NK025(ra)001:12794: bar bskyed de / dkyil 'khor bcu gcig pa'i lha
NK025(ra)001:12795: bskyed pa'i mjug rig 'dzin bla ma'i tshogs thams cad
NK025(ra)001:12796: kyang zhal lam mer mngon sum du bzhugs par gyur
NK025(ra)001:12797: bar bskyed de / / zhes pa'i bar tshang bar gyer sgom mdun bskyed kyi tshul du gsal btab /
NK025(ra)001:12798: de nas zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12799: gong gi mdun bskyed skabs bzhin /
NK025(ra)001:12800: bdag gi thugs ka nas e yam bam sum lam
NK025(ra)001:12801: ram rnams chad de dkyil 'khor gyi 'og gzhir brtsegs
NK025(ra)001:12802: mar 'khod ces pa nas mthar sgo ba yab yum
NK025(ra)001:12803: brgyad khro bo dang khro mo'i chas ldan ye shes
NK025(ra)001:12804: kyi me 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:12805: zhes pa'i bar tshang bar brjod cing khro bo'i dkyil
NK025(ra)001:12806: 'khor gyi steng du rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor
NK025(ra)001:12807: chen po reg la ma 'byar ba me ri 'dab
NK025(ra)001:12810: zhi khro gnyis ka la dus gcig tu dbang bskur
NK025(ra)001:12811: la zhes gsungs pas gong du bsgrubs ma thag pa'i
NK025(ra)001:12812: rab gnas kyi dbang bum nub tu bkod pa de
NK025(ra)001:12813: / bla mas kun tu bzang po'i nga rgyal gyis bzung ste /
NK025(ra)001:12814: dkyil 'khor pa de rnams la dbang bskur bar mos te /
NK025(ra)001:12816: rin chen bum pas dbang bskur nas //
NK025(ra)001:12817: dbang chen rdo rje'i skur bsgoms te //
NK025(ra)001:12818: ye shes lnga yi rang bzhin gyis //
NK025(ra)001:12819: dbang bskur chos dbyings gsal bar shog /
NK025(ra)001:12820: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:12821: ma h+aa a dar+sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra ma h+aa sa
NK025(ra)001:12822: ma t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra ma h+aa pra t+ya bak+she
NK025(ra)001:12823: na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra ma h+aa kri t+y+aa nush+tha na
NK025(ra)001:12825: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK025(ra)001:12826: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las zhing khams
NK025(ra)001:12827: dag pa mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bka'
NK025(ra)001:12828: bden pa dang / bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK025(ra)001:12829: 'dus pa chen po'i lha rnams la ye shes lngas
NK025(ra)001:12830: dbang bskur bas rnam shes brgyad ye shes lngar lhun
NK025(ra)001:12831: gyis grub nas phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug
NK025(ra)001:12833: yon gyi bdag po dang srid pa gsum gyis bsdus
NK025(ra)001:12834: pa'i sems can thams cad kyi thob par gyur cig
NK025(ra)001:12835: / ces brjod pas bum nang gi rigs lnga'i sbyor
NK025(ra)001:12836: mtshams nas byang sems bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun gyis dkyil
NK025(ra)001:12839: chu zhabs gyen du 'khyil ba las zhi khro'i dkyil
NK025(ra)001:12840: 'khor gyi lha tshogs de rnams kyi spyi gtsug tu
NK025(ra)001:12842: dpral bar rnam snang dkar po /
NK025(ra)001:12843: rna ltag g.yas su rin chen 'byung ldan ser po /
NK025(ra)001:12844: ltag par snang ba mtha' yas dmar po /
NK025(ra)001:12845: rna ltag g.yon du don yod grub pa ljang gu rnams kyis dbu brgyan par bsam mo //
NK025(ra)001:12846: dbang bum gyi lha rnams kyi ye shes pa gshegs /
NK025(ra)001:12847: dam tshig pa chur bsam ste rang gzhan gyis longs spyad do //
NK025(ra)001:12848: dbang bum 'di gzhan du mi dgos so //
NK025(ra)001:12849: rtsa bar gsal bar ma byung yang sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab pa rigs par snang ste /
NK025(ra)001:12850: rdo rje'i phyag rgyas dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i gnas gsum du gtug tshul byas te /
NK025(ra)001:12851: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:12852: lha rnams kyi spyi bo'i dkar po las 'od zer 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:12853: sangs rgyas rnams kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK025(ra)001:12854: sku rdo rje'i lha tshogs spyan drangs te la thim
NK025(ra)001:12855: pas sangs rgyas rnams kyi sku'i rang bzhin las rnam
NK025(ra)001:12856: snang dkar po 'khor lo dang dril bu 'dzin par
NK025(ra)001:12857: gyur / sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aa
NK025(ra)001:12858: ka mgrin par pad+ma la gnas pa'i +aahdamara po las
NK025(ra)001:12859: sangs rgyas rnams kyi thugs gsung rdo rje'i lha tshogs
NK025(ra)001:12860: gyur / spyan drangs / +aahl thim pas sangs rgyas
NK025(ra)001:12861: rnams kyi gsu nga gi rang bzhin +aahls snang mtha'
NK025(ra)001:12862: dmar po pad+ma dang dril bu 'dzin par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:12863: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta thugs kar
NK025(ra)001:12864: nyi ma la gnas pa'i h+aum sngon po las sangs
NK025(ra)001:12865: rgyas rnams kyi thugs thugs rdo rje'i lha tshogs spyan
NK025(ra)001:12866: drangs / h+aum la thim pas sangs rgyas rnams kyi
NK025(ra)001:12867: thugs kyi rang bzhin h+aum las mi bskyod pa mthing
NK025(ra)001:12868: kha rdo rje dang dril bu 'dzin par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:12870: zhes pa yan chad ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:12874: de nas gsum pa rang bzhin ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:12876: rol mo'i sgra byas nas zhes gsungs pas /
NK025(ra)001:12877: rol mo sna tshogs dbyangs dang bcas pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:12878: spos btul zhing g.yab dar dang bcas te bsgoms pa
NK025(ra)001:12879: dang 'dra ba'i lha tshogs nam mkha'i khams gang bar
NK025(ra)001:12882: chos sku rig pa rang snang ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:12883: rdo rje dbyings kyi lha tshogs dang //
NK025(ra)001:12884: khams gsum ma lus brdal ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:12886: rdo rje 'chang gral rim bgrod pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:12888: smon lam dam tshig lugs bzhin du //
NK025(ra)001:12889: gnas 'dir ma lus gshegs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:12892: sprin phung bzhin du gshegs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:12893: chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang nas //
NK025(ra)001:12894: gzhal yas chen po'i gnas mchog nas //
NK025(ra)001:12895: rgyal ba 'khor bcas ma lus kun //
NK025(ra)001:12896: thugs rje'i dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:12897: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten thams cad nas //
NK025(ra)001:12898: rgyal ba gar bzhugs 'khor dang bcas //
NK025(ra)001:12899: rdo rje dam can ji snyed pa //
NK025(ra)001:12900: thams cad kun nas dgongs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:12901: rgyal ba'i thugs dam bskang ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:12902: 'khor ba yongs su sbyong ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:12904: thugs dam dbang gis gshegs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:12905: badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum dzah zhes snyan gsan dbab
NK025(ra)001:12906: te nam mkhar byon pa rnams mdun bskyed la bstim
NK025(ra)001:12907: pa ni so so'i phyag rgya dang bcas te /
NK025(ra)001:12909: thugs rje'i lcags kyus thugs dam rgyud bskul zhing //
NK025(ra)001:12910: byams pa'i zhags pas gnas nas spyan yang 'dren //
NK025(ra)001:12911: lcags sgrog bka' yi pho nyas gnas bskyod la //
NK025(ra)001:12912: bde gshegs bzhugs shing rnam grol dgyes pa bskyed //
NK025(ra)001:12913: e h+ye hi b+ha ga wa na ma h+aa k+aa
NK025(ra)001:12914: ru ni ka d+r+ai sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh
NK025(ra)001:12920: k+aa ya w+aa kas brtan par bzhugs su gsol nas /
NK025(ra)001:12922: sems can don phyir nan tan mchog bskyed nas //
NK025(ra)001:12923: ye shes thugs rje bdag la dgongs na sa kyang //
NK025(ra)001:12924: mi dmigs don phyir dngos grub mchog gi rnams //
NK025(ra)001:12925: bdag la stsal zhing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:12926: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK025(ra)001:12927: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sarba dush+tana sa
NK025(ra)001:12928: ma ya mu dra ma tram pra b+han tsakra h+aum
NK025(ra)001:12929: phata / k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK025(ra)001:12930: zhes brtan pa bzhugs su gsol /
NK025(ra)001:12931: skabs 'dir glan ston bsod nams mgon pos /
NK025(ra)001:12932: ting nge 'dzin 'og ma ni chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang nas /
NK025(ra)001:12933: rgyal ba zhi khro'i lha tshogs rnams byon nas pho
NK025(ra)001:12934: brang gi tsakli dkyil 'khor dang bcas pa la thim
NK025(ra)001:12935: pas / pho brang gi lha tshogs rnams 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa'i gzi byin dang ldan par bsam /
NK025(ra)001:12938: mdun gyi rdo rje sems dpa' rang la thim pas /
NK025(ra)001:12939: rang nyid kyang dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs de dag
NK025(ra)001:12940: la mnga' gsol ba'i gzi byin dang ldan par bsam
NK025(ra)001:12941: / zhes gsungs pa zab gnad du 'dug pas de bzhin du bya /
NK025(ra)001:12944: zhes pas rdo rje sems dpa' rang la bstim pas /
NK025(ra)001:12945: dkyil 'khor la mnga' gsol ba'i gzi brjid dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK025(ra)001:12946: zhes gsungs pa ltar las kyi lha ra nga la bsdu'o //
NK025(ra)001:12947: de nas khrus rnams kyi thog mar me long dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:12949: de nas me long dbul ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:12951: me long dag la gzugs brnyan snang ba ltar //
NK025(ra)001:12952: chos rnams rang bzhin gdod nas dag pa la //
NK025(ra)001:12953: che ba'i yon tan mang po 'byung 'gyur zhing //
NK025(ra)001:12954: rnam par byang ba'i chos nyid gsal bar shog /
NK025(ra)001:12956: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK025(ra)001:12957: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las zhing khams
NK025(ra)001:12958: dag pa mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bka'
NK025(ra)001:12959: bden pa dang / bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs
NK025(ra)001:12960: kyis 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs pa'i
NK025(ra)001:12961: sku la me long phul bas kun gzhi bag chags
NK025(ra)001:12962: kyi g.ya' dang bral nas chos sku brjod du med
NK025(ra)001:12963: pa 'i don bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can
NK025(ra)001:12964: thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:12965: ces brjod la 'khar ba'i khrus bum gyi chus gang bzhin du khrus bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:12966: spyi don bzhi pa dbang po skyon bsal gyi chos bdun bya ba la /
NK025(ra)001:12967: zhi khro gnyis kyi thog mar zhi ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:12969: de nas dbang po'i skyon bsal gyi chos bdun bya ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:12970: zhi ba'i rin po che'i gser gyi thur ma thogs la /
NK025(ra)001:12971: khyad par rgyu las byung ba yi //
NK025(ra)001:12972: rin po che yi thur ma yis //
NK025(ra)001:12973: spyan gyis dbang po'i skyon bsal na //
NK025(ra)001:12974: spyan lnga yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK025(ra)001:12976: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs
NK025(ra)001:12977: pa'i sku la rin po che'i thur mas spyan phye
NK025(ra)001:12978: bas thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi spyan dam
NK025(ra)001:12979: pa bdag dang snyan 'drud thogs la /
NK025(ra)001:12980: khyad par rgyu las rin po che yi thur ma yis //
NK025(ra)001:12981: dbang po snyan gyi skyon snyan lnga yongs su rdzogs na mo /
NK025(ra)001:12982: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs
NK025(ra)001:12983: pa'i sku la rin po che'i snyan sel gyi snyan
NK025(ra)001:12984: bsal bas / sangs rgyas kyi snyan yongs su gsan
NK025(ra)001:12985: pa ma 'gags pa bdag dang rmang gzer thogs la
NK025(ra)001:12986: bsal bas / / khyad par rgyu las rin po che yi rmang gzer gyis //
NK025(ra)001:12987: shangs kyi dbang po skyon sems kyi rnam grangs shes na mo /
NK025(ra)001:12988: phyogs bcu bde bar gshegs pa la rin po che'i
NK025(ra)001:12989: rmang gzer gyis shangs kyi spu gtogs pas gzhan sems
NK025(ra)001:12990: kyi rnam grangs shes pa'i don bdag dang ljags bzhar
NK025(ra)001:12991: thogs la / khyad par rgyu las rin po che yi ljangs bzhar gyis //
NK025(ra)001:12992: ljags kyi dbang po'i skyon gsung rab ma lus 'chad na mo /
NK025(ra)001:12993: phyogs bcu bde bar gshegs pa la rin po che'i
NK025(ra)001:12994: ljags bzhar gyis dri ma bsal bas gsung rab ma
NK025(ra)001:12995: lus pa 'chad pa'i don bdag dang tshems shing thogs
NK025(ra)001:12996: la / khyad par rgyu las rin po che yi tshems shing gis //
NK025(ra)001:12997: tshems kyi dri ma bsal ba yis //
NK025(ra)001:12998: mnyam par bzhag pa thob na mo /
NK025(ra)001:12999: phyogs bcu bde bar gshegs pa la rin po che'i
NK025(ra)001:13000: tshems shing gis tshems kyi dri ma bsal bas shin
NK025(ra)001:13001: tu mnyam pa'i don bdag dang so mang thogs la
NK025(ra)001:13002: / khyad par gyur las rin chen dung gi so mang gis //
NK025(ra)001:13003: dbu skra'i dri ma'i skyon mtshan nyid ma 'dres mkhyen na mo /
NK025(ra)001:13004: phyogs bcu bde bar gshegs pa la dung gi so
NK025(ra)001:13005: mang gis dbu skra bshad pas thabs shes ma 'dres
NK025(ra)001:13006: pas 'gro ba'i don byed pa bdag dang chan pa'am
NK025(ra)001:13008: khyad par rgyud las rin po che yi spu gri yis //
NK025(ra)001:13009: dbu yi skra rnams skyon nyon mongs rtsad nas gcod na mo /
NK025(ra)001:13010: phyogs bcu bde bar gshegs pa la spu gris sprul
NK025(ra)001:13011: sku'i dbu skra bzhar bas dug gsum rtsad nas bcad
NK025(ra)001:13012: te nyon mongs pa'i zug rngu dang bral pa bdag
NK025(ra)001:13013: dang don lnga pa dngos po skyon sbyang gi chos
NK025(ra)001:13014: dgu la / me long gong ltar dbul /
NK025(ra)001:13016: spyi don lnga pa dngos po skyon sbyang gi chos
NK025(ra)001:13017: dgu la zhi khro gnyis kyi dang po zhi ba
NK025(ra)001:13020: me long dag la gzugs brnyan snang ba ltar //
NK025(ra)001:13021: chos rnams rang bzhin gdod nas dag pa las //
NK025(ra)001:13022: che ba'i yon mang po 'byung 'gyur zhing //
NK025(ra)001:13023: rnam par byang ba'i chos nyid gsal bar shog /
NK025(ra)001:13025: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la me long phul bas /
NK025(ra)001:13026: kun gzhi bag chags kyi g.ya' dang bral nas chos
NK025(ra)001:13027: sku brjod du med pa'i don bdag dang ces brjod
NK025(ra)001:13028: la 'khar ba'i khrus bum gyi chus khrus gsol lo
NK025(ra)001:13030: chu bdun tshan gnyis kyi dang po chu gtsang thogs la /
NK025(ra)001:13031: rgyal ba'i sku la nyon mongs mi mnga' yang //
NK025(ra)001:13032: sems can nyon mongs bag chags sbyang slad du //
NK025(ra)001:13033: rgyal ba'i sku la chu gtsang khrus gsol bas //
NK025(ra)001:13034: las dang nyon mongs bag chags dag par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13036: phyogs bcu bde bar gshegs pa la chu gtsang gis
NK025(ra)001:13037: sku khrus gsol bas bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems
NK025(ra)001:13038: can thams cad kyi las dang nyon mongs pa'i dri
NK025(ra)001:13040: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya bi sho d+ha na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:13041: sbrul chab ste bul chu thogs la /
NK025(ra)001:13042: rgyal ba'i sku la rab rib mi sems can ma
NK025(ra)001:13043: rig mun pa bsal rgyal ba'i sku la sbrul chab
NK025(ra)001:13044: 'di gsol bas // rmongs pa'i rab rib ma lus dag na mo /
NK025(ra)001:13045: phyogs bcu bde bar gshegs pa la sbrul chab kyis
NK025(ra)001:13046: khrus gsol bas bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can
NK025(ra)001:13047: thams cad kyi shes bya'i dri ma dag par gyur
NK025(ra)001:13048: cig / sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya 'dag chal te sug chu thogs la /
NK025(ra)001:13049: rgyal ba'i sku la dri ma mi sems can sdug
NK025(ra)001:13050: bsngal dri ma bsal rgyal ba'i sku la 'dag chal
NK025(ra)001:13051: khrus gsol bas // tshul khrims mngon par byang chub sku thob shog /
NK025(ra)001:13053: phyogs bcu bde bar gshegs pa la 'dag chal gyi
NK025(ra)001:13054: khrus gsol bas tshul khrims kyi chu bo mngon par
NK025(ra)001:13055: byang chub pa'i sku bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems
NK025(ra)001:13056: can thams cad kyi thob par gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:13057: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya 'bru chab thogs la /
NK025(ra)001:13058: rgyal ba'i sku la bsnyel ba mi sems can mu
NK025(ra)001:13059: ge'i sdug bsngal bsal rgyal ba'i sku la 'bru chab
NK025(ra)001:13060: 'di gsol bas // ting 'dzin phung po chos sku dag par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13062: phyogs bcu bde bar gshegs pa la 'bru chab kyi
NK025(ra)001:13063: khrus gsol bas ting nge 'dzin gyi phung po dang
NK025(ra)001:13064: chos kyi sku bdag dang sarba ta th+aa ga ta
NK025(ra)001:13065: k+aa ya spos chab thogs la /
NK025(ra)001:13066: phrin las lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas sku gzugs las //
NK025(ra)001:13067: spos chen dri yi sku khrus 'di gsol bas //
NK025(ra)001:13068: dri mchog stong gsum kun tu 'byung ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:13069: shes rab phung po sprul sku thob par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13071: phyogs bcu bde bar gshegs pa la spos chab kyis
NK025(ra)001:13072: sku khrus gsol bas shes rab kyi phung po dang
NK025(ra)001:13073: / sprul pa'i sku bdag dang sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya sman chab thogs la /
NK025(ra)001:13074: rdo rje'i sku mchog nam mkha'i rang bzhin la //
NK025(ra)001:13075: dri med sman chab sku khrus 'di gsol bas //
NK025(ra)001:13076: nyon mongs sdug bsngal nad 'joms rgyal po yis //
NK025(ra)001:13077: rnam grol phung po rdo rje'i sku thob shog /
NK025(ra)001:13079: phyogs bcu bde bar gshegs pa la sman chab bram
NK025(ra)001:13080: ze'i sku khrus gsol bas rnam par grol ba'i phung
NK025(ra)001:13081: po dang rdo rje'i sku bdag dang sarba ta th+aa
NK025(ra)001:13082: ga ta k+aa ya rin po che'i chab thogs la
NK025(ra)001:13083: / chos rnams yongs su rdzogs pa'i sku mchog la //
NK025(ra)001:13084: rin chen chab kyi sku khrus 'di gsol bas //
NK025(ra)001:13085: yid bzhin nor ltar ma lus re skong ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:13086: ye shes phung po longs spyod rdzogs par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13088: phyogs bcu bde bar gshegs pa la rin po che'i
NK025(ra)001:13089: chab kyis sku khrus gsol bas rnam par grol ba'i
NK025(ra)001:13090: ye shes mthong ba'i phung po dang /
NK025(ra)001:13091: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku bdag dang sarba ta th+aa
NK025(ra)001:13092: ga ta k+aa ya de dag ni chu bdun gyi
NK025(ra)001:13093: sku khrus so // sku phyi ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:13094: ras dkar gyi sku phyi thogs la /
NK025(ra)001:13096: thugs rje lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas sku gzugs la //
NK025(ra)001:13097: sri zhu gus phyir ras kyis sku phyis pas //
NK025(ra)001:13098: las dang nyon mongs bag chags kun byang nas //
NK025(ra)001:13099: spyod lam rnam par dag pa'i sku thob shog /
NK025(ra)001:13101: phyogs bcu bde bar gshegs pa la ras kha tshar
NK025(ra)001:13102: ma nyams pas sku phyis pas gzung 'dzin las byung
NK025(ra)001:13103: ba'i dri ma thams cad dang bral nas spyod lam
NK025(ra)001:13104: rnam par dag pa'i sgo bdag dang sarba ta th+aa
NK025(ra)001:13105: ga ta k+aa spyi don bzhi pa'i gnyis pa khro
NK025(ra)001:13106: bo'i dbang po skyon bsal gyi chos bdun bya ba
NK025(ra)001:13108: de nas khro bo'i dbang po skyon bsal gyi chos bdun bya ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:13111: khrag 'thung spyan la sgrib pa mi mnga' yang //
NK025(ra)001:13112: rnal 'byor 'gro drug bag chags bsal ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:13113: gser gyi thur mas spyan gyi skyon bsal nas //
NK025(ra)001:13114: srid gsum ye shes spyan du gsal gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:13115: badz+ra tsak+shu sa man+ta bi sho d+ha na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:13117: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK025(ra)001:13118: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las zhing khams
NK025(ra)001:13119: dag pa mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bka'
NK025(ra)001:13120: bden pa dang / bden pa chen po'i byin gyis
NK025(ra)001:13121: brlabs kyis khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK025(ra)001:13122: tshogs kyi spyan gyi nyes pa bsal nas thams cad
NK025(ra)001:13123: mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi spyan bdag dang mtha' yas
NK025(ra)001:13124: pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig
NK025(ra)001:13125: bden pa dang / / snyan 'brud thogs la /
NK025(ra)001:13127: khrag 'thung snyan la 'gag pa mi rnal 'byor 'gro
NK025(ra)001:13128: drug bag chags bsal gser gyi thur mas snyan gyi
NK025(ra)001:13129: skyon khams gsum sgra rnams dus gcig gsal srog srum
NK025(ra)001:13130: pra be sha ga s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:13132: phyogs bcu khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs kyi snyan gyi nyes pa bsal bas /
NK025(ra)001:13133: srid gsum sems can thams cad kyi chos kyi sgra
NK025(ra)001:13134: chen po thos nas shes rgyud grol ba bdag dang
NK025(ra)001:13136: khrag 'thung shangs la nyes skyon mi rnal 'byor 'gro
NK025(ra)001:13137: drug bag chags bsal gser gyi rmang gzer shangs kyi
NK025(ra)001:13138: nyes khams gsum dri rnams dus gcig bsal pri yam
NK025(ra)001:13140: phyogs bcu khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs
NK025(ra)001:13141: la rmang gzer gyis shangs kyi spu btogs pa dug
NK025(ra)001:13142: lnga ye shes su grol nas chos kyi dri bdag
NK025(ra)001:13144: khrag 'thung ljags la nyes pa mi rnal 'byor 'gro
NK025(ra)001:13145: drug bag chags bsal gser gyi ljags bzhar ljags kyi
NK025(ra)001:13146: skyon khams gsum sems can chos kyi ro tshor shog
NK025(ra)001:13148: phyogs bcu khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs
NK025(ra)001:13149: kyi ljags kyi nyes pa bsal bas chos nyid kyi
NK025(ra)001:13150: ro tshor te rang sar grol ba bdag dang rus
NK025(ra)001:13152: khrag 'thung tshems la nyon mongs mi rnal 'byor 'gro
NK025(ra)001:13153: drug bag chags bsal rus pa'i thur la tshems kyi
NK025(ra)001:13154: nyes 'khor ba'i dug gsum rtsad nas chod gyur cig
NK025(ra)001:13157: phyogs bcu khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs
NK025(ra)001:13158: kyi tshems kyi nyes skyon bsal bas dug gsum rtsad
NK025(ra)001:13159: nas chod pa bdag dang dung gi so mang thogs
NK025(ra)001:13160: la / khrag 'thung skra la nyes pa mi rnal
NK025(ra)001:13161: 'byor 'gro drug bag chags bsal dung gi so mang
NK025(ra)001:13163: srid gsum longs spyod rdzogs sku thob par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13164: ma nu sam so s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:13166: phyogs bcu khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs
NK025(ra)001:13167: kyi dbu skra bshad pas thabs ma 'dres pas 'gro
NK025(ra)001:13168: ba'i don byed pa bdag dang chan pa thogs la
NK025(ra)001:13169: / khrag 'thung sku la nyes skyon mi rnal 'byor
NK025(ra)001:13170: 'gro drug bag chags bsal gser gyi chan pas zhal
NK025(ra)001:13172: sprul pa sku yi dbang po thob gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:13175: phyogs bcu khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs
NK025(ra)001:13176: kyi zhal gyi spu bregs pas bag chags rtsad nas
NK025(ra)001:13177: chod de rang byung ye shes bdag dang de dag
NK025(ra)001:13179: spyi don lnga pa'i gnyis pa khro bo'i dngos po skyon sbyong gi chos dgu bya ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:13181: dngos po skyon sbyang la chu bdun gyi khrus las zhes gsungs kyang chos dgu ni /
NK025(ra)001:13182: me long dbul zhing khrus bya ba /
NK025(ra)001:13183: chu bdun gyis khrus bya ba /
NK025(ra)001:13186: 'khar ba'i khrus bum gyi chus me long gi ngos la khrus bya zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13188: me long dag las gzugs brnyan snang ba ltar //
NK025(ra)001:13189: chos rnams rang bzhin gdod nas dag pa la //
NK025(ra)001:13190: che ba'i yon tan mang po 'byung 'gyur zhing //
NK025(ra)001:13191: rnam par byang ba'i chos nyid gsal bar shog /
NK025(ra)001:13193: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha khrag 'thung rol
NK025(ra)001:13194: pa'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs 'jigs byed chen po'i sku
NK025(ra)001:13195: la me long phul bas sku gzhi bag chags kyi
NK025(ra)001:13196: g.ya' dang bral nas chos sku brjod du med pa'i
NK025(ra)001:13198: dang po zhun chen yi chu thogs la /
NK025(ra)001:13200: don dam bcud kyi thig le chen po 'dis //
NK025(ra)001:13201: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus gsol pas //
NK025(ra)001:13202: lhan cig skyes pa'i dri ma kun dag nas //
NK025(ra)001:13203: byang chub sems kyi brlan dang ldan par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13204: bo d+hi tsit+ta dz+ny+aa na bi shud+d+he h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:13206: phyogs bcu khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs
NK025(ra)001:13207: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la zhun chen gyi khrus
NK025(ra)001:13208: gsol bas / lhan skyes kyi dri ma dag nas
NK025(ra)001:13209: bde chen byang chub kyi sems bdag dang thal chen
NK025(ra)001:13212: lhag pa'i thal bas phrin las rdzogs pa'i chus //
NK025(ra)001:13213: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus bdag gzhan gnyis 'dzin dri ma kun spangs nas //
NK025(ra)001:13214: gnyis su med pa'i don dang ldan badz+ra bi sa smi ti dz+ny+aa na bi shud+d+he h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:13216: phyogs bcu khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs
NK025(ra)001:13217: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la thal chen gyi chus
NK025(ra)001:13218: khrus gsol bas / kun btags kyi dri ma bsal
NK025(ra)001:13219: nas gnyis med kyi don bdag dang byang chub sems
NK025(ra)001:13222: skye med byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin 'di //
NK025(ra)001:13223: dkar la dag pa gnyis med ye shes chu //
NK025(ra)001:13224: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus rdo rje rigs
NK025(ra)001:13225: kyi dngos grub thob badz+ra bo d+hi tsit+ta dz+ny+aa na
NK025(ra)001:13227: phyogs bcu khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK025(ra)001:13228: tshogs 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la byang chub sems
NK025(ra)001:13230: rdo rje rigs kyi dngos grub dang me long lta
NK025(ra)001:13231: bu'i ye shes bdag dang dri chen gyi chu thogs
NK025(ra)001:13233: dri chen gsang ba'i rdzas chen dam rdzas mchog /
NK025(ra)001:13234: skye shi med pa ye shes rdo rje'i chu //
NK025(ra)001:13235: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus de bzhin rigs
NK025(ra)001:13236: kyi dngos grub thob badz+ra +aa yuhdz+ny+aa na bi shud+d+he
NK025(ra)001:13238: phyogs bcu khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs
NK025(ra)001:13239: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la dri chen gyi chus
NK025(ra)001:13240: khrus gsol bas / de bzhin gshegs pa'i dngos grub
NK025(ra)001:13241: dang yod med las 'das pa stong pa nyid kyi
NK025(ra)001:13242: ye shes bdag dang m+aam sa'i chu thogs la /
NK025(ra)001:13244: khams gsum rgyud drug 'khor ba'i sems can rnams //
NK025(ra)001:13245: dug gsum bsgral ba sha chen bcud kyi chus //
NK025(ra)001:13246: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus rin chen rigs
NK025(ra)001:13247: kyi dngos grub thob badz+ra ma h+aa m+aam sa bi
NK025(ra)001:13249: phyogs bcu khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK025(ra)001:13250: tshogs 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la sha chen gyi
NK025(ra)001:13252: rin chen rigs kyi dngos grub dang mnyam nyid ye shes bdag dang pad+ma rak+ta'i chu thogs la /
NK025(ra)001:13254: pad+ma rak+ta gsang ba dbang gi rdzas //
NK025(ra)001:13255: chags par byed pa dmar la dwangs pa'i chus //
NK025(ra)001:13256: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus pad+ma rigs kyi
NK025(ra)001:13257: dngos grub thob pad+ma rak+ta ti la ka bi shud+d+he
NK025(ra)001:13259: phyogs bcu khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK025(ra)001:13260: tshogs 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la pad+ma rak+tasa khrus
NK025(ra)001:13261: gsol bas / pad+ma rigs kyi dngos grub dang so
NK025(ra)001:13262: sor rtog pa'i ye shes bdag dang dri chu thogs
NK025(ra)001:13264: dri chu kun gyi sos byed las yi rigs //
NK025(ra)001:13265: thams cad dag byed bdud rtsi chen po'i chus //
NK025(ra)001:13266: 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la khrus las kyi rigs
NK025(ra)001:13267: kyi dngos grub thob badz+ra ma h+aa ma ma ku
NK025(ra)001:13268: ku dz+ny+aa na bi shud+d+he h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:13270: phyogs bcu khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK025(ra)001:13271: tshogs 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la dri chu'i khrus
NK025(ra)001:13272: gsol bas / las kyi rigs kyi dngos grub dang
NK025(ra)001:13273: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes bdag dang de nas
NK025(ra)001:13274: ro ras kyis sku phyi ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:13275: ro ras kyi sku phyi thogs la /
NK025(ra)001:13277: thugs rje lhun rdzogs khrag 'thung dkyil 'khor la //
NK025(ra)001:13278: dur khrod chen po'i ras kyis sku phyi pas //
NK025(ra)001:13279: shes bya'i las dang nyon mongs sgrib byang nas //
NK025(ra)001:13280: spyod lam rnam par dag pa'i sku thob shog /
NK025(ra)001:13281: badz+ra sarba ta th+aa ga ta dz+ny+aa na bi shud+d+he h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:13283: phyogs bcu khrag 'thung rol pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK025(ra)001:13284: tshogs 'jigs byed chen po'i sku la ro ras kyis
NK025(ra)001:13285: phyis bas shes bya'i sgrib pa dag nas spyod lam
NK025(ra)001:13286: rnam par dag pa bdag dang de dag gis zhi
NK025(ra)001:13287: khro'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams kyi dngos po'i
NK025(ra)001:13288: skyon sbyong ngo // spyi don drug pa mnga' dbul ni /
NK025(ra)001:13290: don drug pa che ba'i yon tan dang /
NK025(ra)001:13291: rgyan cha'i mnga' gsol ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:13292: spyi don bdun pa phyi nang gsang gsum gyi mchod pa dbul ba dril ba la don bzhi ste /
NK025(ra)001:13293: dang po gzugs bye brag tu mnga' gsol ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:13294: gnyis pa mdzes pa rgyan du mnga' gsol ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:13295: gsum pa che ba'i yon tan phun tshogs su mnga' gsol ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:13296: bzhi pa mnyes mchod bzhes par mnga' gsol ba'o //
NK025(ra)001:13297: dang po gzugs bye brag tu mnga' gsol ba la /
NK025(ra)001:13311: bde bar gshegs pa'i byin rlabs tshur 'dus pa las /
NK025(ra)001:13312: zhi ba dang khro bo rang rang gi spyod yul
NK025(ra)001:13313: dang 'tshams pa'i dbu gsum gyi rnam par gyur ces
NK025(ra)001:13314: dbu gsum gyi gzugs brnyan thogs te 'bul ba'i tshul
NK025(ra)001:13317: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK025(ra)001:13318: bde gshegs sku la dbu yis mnga' gsol bas //
NK025(ra)001:13319: rnam par thar pa'i dbu gsum thob na ni //
NK025(ra)001:13320: khams gsum yongs su dag par mdzad gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:13322: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK025(ra)001:13323: kyi sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las zhing khams
NK025(ra)001:13324: dag pa mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i bka'
NK025(ra)001:13325: bden pa dang / bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs
NK025(ra)001:13326: kyis 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs pa'i
NK025(ra)001:13327: sku la dbu gsum gyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK025(ra)001:13328: khams gsum dbang du sgyur zhing rnam par thar pa
NK025(ra)001:13329: dbu gsum bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams
NK025(ra)001:13330: cad kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:13332: +aahh+aum s+w+aa h+aa ste 'bru lnga'i 'phro 'du las bskyed
NK025(ra)001:13333: tshul gong ltar zhi khro'i phyag drug gi gzugs brnyan
NK025(ra)001:13335: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku la
NK025(ra)001:13336: phyag gis mnga' ye shes drug gis 'gro ba'i don
NK025(ra)001:13337: mdzad nas // khams gsum 'gro drug rtsad nas gcod par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13339: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs pa la phyag gis mnga' gsol bas /
NK025(ra)001:13340: ye shes drug gi don rtogs pa bdag dang dzahbazhi'i
NK025(ra)001:13341: 'phro 'du las zhi khro'i zhabs bzhi'i gzugs brnyan thogs
NK025(ra)001:13342: te dbul zhing / lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor
NK025(ra)001:13343: bde gshegs sku la zhabs kyis rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhis
NK025(ra)001:13345: bdud bzhi ma lus zil gyis gnon gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:13347: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs pa la zhabs kyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK025(ra)001:13348: rdzu 'phrul rkang pa bzhis bdud bzhi zil gyis gnon
NK025(ra)001:13349: pa bdag dang dbu skra dzah'i 'phro 'du las zhi
NK025(ra)001:13350: khro'i dbu skra'i gzugs thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13351: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs dbu la
NK025(ra)001:13352: skra yis khyab pa thugs rje chen po'i phrin las
NK025(ra)001:13353: kyis // lta ba mthar mi ltung dang ldan par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13355: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs
NK025(ra)001:13356: pa la dbu skra lcang lo la mthon mthing gis
NK025(ra)001:13357: mnga' gsol bas / khyab byed thugs rje'i phrin las
NK025(ra)001:13358: dang mtha' bral gyi lta ba bdag dang smin ma
NK025(ra)001:13359: la ra'i 'phro 'du las zhi khro'i smin ma'i gzugs
NK025(ra)001:13360: mnga' gsol bas / brnyan thogs te / lhag pa
NK025(ra)001:13361: gzugs brnyan dkyil bde gshegs sku la smin ma'i thabs
NK025(ra)001:13362: chen g.yang gzhi mkhas pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK025(ra)001:13363: gdul bya'i 'gro ba chud mi gson par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13365: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs pa la smin mas mnga' gsol bas /
NK025(ra)001:13366: thabs mkhas che mang gi gdul bya 'dren pa bdag
NK025(ra)001:13367: dang spyan la a hri'i 'phro 'du las zhi khro'i
NK025(ra)001:13368: spyan gyi gzugs brnyan thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13369: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku la
NK025(ra)001:13370: spyan gyis spyan lnga ma lus yongs su rdzogs nas
NK025(ra)001:13371: ni // rmongs pa'i rab rib thams cad dag par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13373: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs pa la spyan gyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK025(ra)001:13374: thams cad du gsal zhing rig pa ma 'gags par
NK025(ra)001:13375: mthong bar bdag dang ljags la a'i 'phro 'du las
NK025(ra)001:13376: zhi khro'i ljags kyi gzugs brnyan thogs te dbul zhing
NK025(ra)001:13377: / lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku
NK025(ra)001:13378: la ljags kyis sgra skad bsam gyis mi khyab bye
NK025(ra)001:13379: / brag gis // gdul bya'i sems can thams cad smin grol shog /
NK025(ra)001:13381: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs pa la khyab byed ljags kyi mnga' gsol bas /
NK025(ra)001:13382: sgra'i bye brag sna tshogs pas gdul bya thams cad
NK025(ra)001:13383: dus gcig la smin par mdzad pa bdag dang tshems
NK025(ra)001:13384: mche ba la k+sha'i 'phro 'du las zhi khro'i tshems
NK025(ra)001:13385: mche ba'i gzugs brnyan thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13386: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku la
NK025(ra)001:13387: mche bas skye shi sdug bsngal rtsad nas gcod mdzad
NK025(ra)001:13388: cing // sgrib pa ma lus thams cad zad byed shog /
NK025(ra)001:13390: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs pa la tshems mche bas mnga' gsol bas /
NK025(ra)001:13391: skye shi rtsad nas gcod sgrib pa ma lus dag pa bdag dang sku mdog la /
NK025(ra)001:13392: h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum +aahh+aum s+w+aa h+aa'i 'phro 'du
NK025(ra)001:13393: las zhi khro sku mdog gi gzugs brnyan thogs te
NK025(ra)001:13394: dbul zhing / lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku la sku mdog rgyan gsol bas //
NK025(ra)001:13395: mi 'gyur chos nyid skyon gyis ma gos dang //
NK025(ra)001:13396: che ba'i yon tan spyod cing ma 'gags pa //
NK025(ra)001:13397: sna tshogs rol pa'i rgyan du shar nas ni //
NK025(ra)001:13398: phrin las lnga po yongs su rdzogs gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:13400: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs pa'i sku la sku mdog gis mnga' gsol bas /
NK025(ra)001:13401: mi 'gyur ba'i chos de skyon gyis ma gos par spyod cing /
NK025(ra)001:13402: sna tshogs rol pas phrin las lnga yongs su rdzogs pa bdag dang phyag mtshan la /
NK025(ra)001:13403: h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum h+aum 'phro 'du las zhi
NK025(ra)001:13404: khro'i phyag mtshan rnam pa drug gi gzugs brnyan thogs
NK025(ra)001:13405: te dbul zhing / lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku la phyag mtshan drug phul bas //
NK025(ra)001:13406: ye shes drug gi 'gro don yongs rdzogs nas //
NK025(ra)001:13407: phrin las chen pos bsam pa mthar phyin shog /
NK025(ra)001:13409: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs pa la phyag mtshan drug gis mnga' gsol bas /
NK025(ra)001:13410: ye shes su drug rdzogs te phrin las mthar phyin
NK025(ra)001:13411: pa bdag dang bcu po gzugs brnyan gyi bye brag
NK025(ra)001:13412: go // gnyis pa mdzes pa rgyan la /
NK025(ra)001:13414: h+aum s+w+aam +aamhh+aa'i 'phro 'du la rin po che las
NK025(ra)001:13415: grub pa'i rigs lnga'i dbu rgyan gyi rnam par gyur
NK025(ra)001:13417: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku la dbu rgyan mnga' gsol bas //
NK025(ra)001:13418: sems rgyud rnam shes tshogs brgyad gnas dag nas //
NK025(ra)001:13419: ye shes lnga yi 'gro don mthar phyin shog /
NK025(ra)001:13421: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs
NK025(ra)001:13422: pa la rin po che'i dbu rgyan gyis mnga' gsol
NK025(ra)001:13423: bas / rnam shes tshogs brgyad gnas su dag nas ye shes lnga bdag dang cod pan la /
NK025(ra)001:13424: h+aum hri'i 'phro 'dus la gong bzhin bsam la cod pan thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13425: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku la
NK025(ra)001:13426: cod pan mnga' khams gsum gdug pa ma lus kun
NK025(ra)001:13427: 'dus zhing // srid gsum chos kyi rgyal po byed par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13429: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs pa la cod pan gyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK025(ra)001:13430: khams gsum gyi gdug pa ma lus pa 'dren zhing
NK025(ra)001:13431: srid gsum chos kyi rgyal po bdag dang snyan cha
NK025(ra)001:13432: mgur chu la / ho'i 'phro 'dus las snyan cha dang mgur chu thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13433: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku la rin chen snyan cha dang //
NK025(ra)001:13434: mgur chu la sogs rgyan gyis mnga' rdzu 'phrul snyan gyi ma g.yos gsan par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13436: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i bde bar gshegs pa
NK025(ra)001:13437: la rin chen snyan cha mgur chus mnga' gsol bas
NK025(ra)001:13438: / rdzu 'phrul gyi snyan gyis rang rig pa las ma g.yos pa bdag dang do shal la /
NK025(ra)001:13439: tram gi 'phro 'du las do shal thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13440: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku la
NK025(ra)001:13441: do shal zhal mnga' don rnams thams cad rig par
NK025(ra)001:13442: rtogs nas ni // mi brjed gzungs dang rtag tu ldan par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13444: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs
NK025(ra)001:13445: pa la rin po che'i do shal gyis mnga' don
NK025(ra)001:13446: thams cad ma lus par rig cing mi brjed pa'i
NK025(ra)001:13447: gzungs bdag dang se mo do la /
NK025(ra)001:13448: tram gi 'phro 'du las se mo do ste do shal phyed pa thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13449: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku la se mo do yis ni //
NK025(ra)001:13450: mnga' gsol phul bas mi brjed gzungs kyi sgo //
NK025(ra)001:13451: 'bum phrag rdzogs nas brgya phrag 'phrad gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:13453: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs pa la se mo do yis mnga' gsol bas /
NK025(ra)001:13454: gzungs kyi sgo 'bum phrag rdzogs shing brgya phrag 'phrad pa bdag dang dpung rgyan la /
NK025(ra)001:13455: sa'i 'phro 'du las dpung rgyan thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13456: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku la
NK025(ra)001:13457: dpung rgyan mnga' mi 'jigs bzhi yi ting 'dzin thob
NK025(ra)001:13458: nas ni // re dogs kun gyi mtha' dang bral gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:13460: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs pa la dpung rgyan gyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK025(ra)001:13461: mi 'jigs pa bzhi'i ting nge 'dzin gyi re dogs
NK025(ra)001:13462: thams cad kyi mtha' dang bral ba bdag dang phyag
NK025(ra)001:13464: sa'i 'phro 'du las phyag zhabs kyi gdu bu thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13465: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku la
NK025(ra)001:13466: gdu bus mnga' tshul khrims rnam dag stobs bcu lhun
NK025(ra)001:13467: grub nas // mtshan ma thams cad lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13469: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs
NK025(ra)001:13470: pa la rin po che'i gdu bus mnga' gsol bas
NK025(ra)001:13471: / tshul khrims rnam par dag pa'i stobs bcu lhun gyis grub nas /
NK025(ra)001:13472: mtshan ma thams cad zil gyi gnon pa bdag dang gdan khri la /
NK025(ra)001:13473: sems can chen po lnga'i gdan khri /
NK025(ra)001:13474: su'i spro bsdu las zhi ba la seng ge glang chen rta mchog rma bya shang shang gi /
NK025(ra)001:13475: khro bo la khyu mchog ma he gzig stag dom lnga'i gdan thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13476: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku la sems can lnga yi ni //
NK025(ra)001:13477: gdan khri brjid bag ldan pas mnga' che ba'i yon tan lnga po lhun grub nas //
NK025(ra)001:13478: kun gyis bkur nas sangs rgyas sar 'god shog /
NK025(ra)001:13480: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs
NK025(ra)001:13481: pa la sems can chen po lnga'i gdan khris mnga'
NK025(ra)001:13482: gsol bas che ba'i yon tan lnga lhun gyis grub
NK025(ra)001:13483: nas sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang bdag dang nyi zla
NK025(ra)001:13484: pad+ma'i gdan la / a ma pa'i 'phro 'du las nyi zla'i pad+ma'i gdan thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13485: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku la nyi zla pad+ma yi //
NK025(ra)001:13486: gdan khris mnga' gsol mdzad pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK025(ra)001:13487: thugs rje chen pos kun la khyab par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13489: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs
NK025(ra)001:13490: pa la nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan gyis mnga' gsol bas
NK025(ra)001:13491: / thugs rjee chen pos kun la khyab cing shes
NK025(ra)001:13492: rab chen pos lta ngan sel bas gang la'ang spyod
NK025(ra)001:13493: cing ma chags pa bdag dang rin po che'i khri
NK025(ra)001:13494: / rkang la / tram gi 'phro 'du las rin po che'i khri thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13495: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku la rin chen khri rkang gi //
NK025(ra)001:13496: gdan khris mnga' gsol byas pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
