NK025(ra)001:13497: 'gro ba'i re 'dod yid bzhin skong gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:13499: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs
NK025(ra)001:13500: pa la rin po che'i khri rkang gis mnga' gsol
NK025(ra)001:13501: bas / 'gro ba ma lus pa'i re ba yid bzhin du skong ba bdag dang 'od zer la /
NK025(ra)001:13502: ra'i 'phro 'du las 'od zer sna lnga'i rnam par thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13503: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku la
NK025(ra)001:13504: 'od zer mnga' bsam mi khyab kyi ye shes rang
NK025(ra)001:13505: gsal nas // spros pa'i mtha' rnams yongs su gsal gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:13508: 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs pa la 'od zer gyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK025(ra)001:13509: chos thams cad bsam mi khyab kyi ye shes rang
NK025(ra)001:13510: gsal zhing spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral pa
NK025(ra)001:13511: rtogs pa bdag dang stod g.yogs la /
NK025(ra)001:13512: sa'i 'phro 'du las dar gyi stod g.yogs thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13513: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku la na bza' stod g.yogs kyis //
NK025(ra)001:13514: mnga' gsol byas pas gdul bya'i 'gro ba kun //
NK025(ra)001:13515: yongs su smin nas thams cad skyob par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13517: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs
NK025(ra)001:13518: pa la stod g.yogs kyi mnga' gsol bas gdul bya
NK025(ra)001:13519: yongs su skyob pa bdag dang sham thabs la /
NK025(ra)001:13520: sa'i 'phro 'du las dar gyi smad dkris thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13521: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku la sham thabs mnga' gsol bas //
NK025(ra)001:13522: spyod lam rnam par dag pa'i sgo rdzogs nas //
NK025(ra)001:13523: mdzad pa mthar mi 'gag pa thob par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13525: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs pa la sham thabs kyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK025(ra)001:13526: gdul bya yongs su rdzogs pa bdag dang gsang phod la /
NK025(ra)001:13527: sa'i 'phro 'du las gsang phod thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13528: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku la
NK025(ra)001:13529: gsang phod mnga' gdul bya'i re ba yid bzhin skong
NK025(ra)001:13530: nas ni // yon tan mdzad pa ci yang 'char bar shog /
NK025(ra)001:13532: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs pa la gsang phod kyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK025(ra)001:13533: gdul bya ma lus pa'i re ba yid bzhin du
NK025(ra)001:13534: skong zhing yon tan mdzad pa cir yang 'char ba
NK025(ra)001:13536: sa'i 'phro 'du las stod g.yogs zi ldir gyi rdo rje'i gong ba thogs te dabulazhing /
NK025(ra)001:13537: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku la
NK025(ra)001:13538: zi ldir mnga' sangs rgyas dgongs pa ma lus thugs
NK025(ra)001:13539: chud nas // thugs kyi mdzad pa mthar mi 'gog par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13541: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs pa la zi ldir gyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK025(ra)001:13542: sangs rgyas ma lus pa'i dgongs pa thugs su chud
NK025(ra)001:13543: nas thugs kyi mdzad pa la longs spyod pa bdag
NK025(ra)001:13544: dang phyag rgya gar gyi phu dung la /
NK025(ra)001:13545: sa'i 'phro 'du las zhi ba'i gar gos thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13546: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor bde gshegs sku la phyag rgya gar phul bas //
NK025(ra)001:13547: sna tshogs lhun gyis grub pa'i phrin las kyis //
NK025(ra)001:13548: phrin las thogs med kun la spyod par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13550: phyogs bcu 'dus pa chen po'i lha bde bar gshegs pa la phyag rgya gar gyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK025(ra)001:13551: sna tshogs phrin las lhun gyis grub pa bdag dang
NK025(ra)001:13552: mtha' gsum pa che ba'i longs spyod phun tshogs kyi
NK025(ra)001:13554: sa'i 'phro 'du las rin po che'i gdugs su gyur par bsam la gdugs thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13556: gzi brjid shin tu khyad par 'phags pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:13557: bde gshegs sku la rin chen gdugs phul bas //
NK025(ra)001:13558: log par lta ba mtha' dag yongs spangs nas //
NK025(ra)001:13559: 'bar ba'i rgyal po thub med 'grub par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13561: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK025(ra)001:13562: rnal 'byor pa bdag gi rgyal ba zhi khro'i lhag
NK025(ra)001:13563: pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs la
NK025(ra)001:13564: rin po che'i gdugs kyis mnga' gsol bas /
NK025(ra)001:13565: thugs rje chen pos gdul bya yongs su skyob cing
NK025(ra)001:13566: tsha ba'i gdung ba sel ba bdag dang mtha' yas
NK025(ra)001:13567: pa'i sems can thams cad kyis thob par gyur cig
NK025(ra)001:13569: h+aum gi spro bsdu las rgyal mtshan thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13571: gzi brjid shin tu khyad par bde gshegs sku la rgyal mtshan 'di phul bas //
NK025(ra)001:13572: log par lta ba mtha' dag yongs 'bar ba'i rgyal po thub med 'grub na mo /
NK025(ra)001:13573: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK025(ra)001:13574: rnal 'byor pa bdag gis rgyal ba zhi khro'i lhag
NK025(ra)001:13575: pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la rgyal mtshan gyis
NK025(ra)001:13576: mnga' gsol bas / phas kyi rgol ba thams cad tshar gcod cing /
NK025(ra)001:13577: mtshan mar lta ba zil gyis gnon pa bdag dang bla bre la /
NK025(ra)001:13578: sa'i 'phro 'du las bla bre thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13580: gzi brjid shin tu khyad par bde gshegs sku la
NK025(ra)001:13581: bla bre 'di log par lta ba mtha' dag yongs
NK025(ra)001:13582: 'bar ba'i rgyal po thub med 'grub na mo /
NK025(ra)001:13583: phyogs bcu rnal 'byor pa bdag gis rgyal ba zhi
NK025(ra)001:13584: khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la bla
NK025(ra)001:13586: chos nyid brdal ba chen po bdag dang yol ba la /
NK025(ra)001:13587: h+aum gi spro bsdus las yol ba thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13589: gzi brjid shin tu khyad par bde gshegs sku la
NK025(ra)001:13590: yol ba 'di log par lta ba mtha' dag yongs
NK025(ra)001:13591: 'bar ba'i rgyal po thub med 'grub na mo /
NK025(ra)001:13592: phyogs bcu rnal 'byor pa bdag gis rgyal ba zhi
NK025(ra)001:13593: khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyis dkyil 'khor la yol
NK025(ra)001:13595: sems nyid yongs su nga rgyal dang bral nas thams
NK025(ra)001:13596: cad bdag nyid chen por skyob pa bdag dang 'phan
NK025(ra)001:13597: la / tam gyi spro bsdu las 'phan thogs te 'bul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13599: gzi brjid shin tu khyad par bde gshegs sku la
NK025(ra)001:13600: 'phan chen 'di log par lta ba mtha' dag yongs
NK025(ra)001:13601: 'bar ba'i rgyal po thub med 'grub par na mo
NK025(ra)001:13602: / phyogs bcu rnal 'byor pa bdag gis rgyal ba
NK025(ra)001:13603: zhi khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la
NK025(ra)001:13605: thams cad bdag nyid chen por rtogs pas thogs pa med pa'i shes rab bdag dang man+dala la /
NK025(ra)001:13606: sa'i spro bsdu las gling bzhi ri rab kyi man+dala thogs shing dbul te /
NK025(ra)001:13608: 'bras bu mtha' yas kun la mnga' brnyes pas //
NK025(ra)001:13609: bde gshegs sku la man+dala 'di 'phags pa'i nor gyi dbul ba kun bral nas //
NK025(ra)001:13610: ting 'dzin 'bum phrag yongs su rdzogs pa shog /
NK025(ra)001:13612: phyogs bcu rnal 'byor pa bdag gis rgyal ba zhi
NK025(ra)001:13613: khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la gling
NK025(ra)001:13614: bzhi'i man+dala rin po ches spras pa phul bas 'phags
NK025(ra)001:13615: pa'i nor bdun dang ting nge 'dzin gyi sgo 'bum
NK025(ra)001:13616: phrag la mnga' brnyes pa bdag dang yul mkhar la
NK025(ra)001:13617: / sa'i spro bsdu las yul mkhar gyi rnam pa thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13619: 'bras bu mtha' yas kun la mnga' brnyes pa //
NK025(ra)001:13620: bde gshegs sku la yul mkhar 'di yul snang 'dzin pa'i 'ching ba kun bral nas //
NK025(ra)001:13621: 'phags pa'i zhing khams rnam dag thob par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13623: phyogs bcu rgyal ba zhi khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la yul mkhar phul bas /
NK025(ra)001:13624: gzhal yas khang chen po la dbang sgyur ba bdag dang bran pho mo la /
NK025(ra)001:13625: h+r+aih'i 'phro 'du las bran pho dang bran mo'i gzugs brnyan thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13627: gzi brjid shin tu khyad par 'phags pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:13628: bde gshegs sku la pho mo'i bran phul bas //
NK025(ra)001:13629: log par lta ba mtha' dag yongs spangs nas /
NK025(ra)001:13630: 'khor rnams yongs smin tshogs la dbang byed shog /
NK025(ra)001:13632: phyogs bcu rgyal ba zhi khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la bran pho mo phul bas /
NK025(ra)001:13633: 'khor yongs su smin pa phun sum tshogs pa la dbang sgyur ba bdag dang bu pho mo la /
NK025(ra)001:13634: h+r+aih'i 'phro 'du las bu pho dang bu mo'i gzugs brnyan thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13636: gzi brjid shin tu khyad par bde gshegs sku la
NK025(ra)001:13637: lcam sring 'di log par lta ba mtha' dag yongs
NK025(ra)001:13638: sprul pa'i gdul bya don la dbang byed shog /
NK025(ra)001:13640: phyogs bcu rgyal ba zhi khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan
NK025(ra)001:13641: gyi dkyil 'khor la bu dang bu mo phul bas
NK025(ra)001:13642: / thabs la mkhas pa'i sprul pa mang pos gdul
NK025(ra)001:13643: bya kha lo bsgyur ba bdag dang gzungs ma la
NK025(ra)001:13644: / / h+r+aih'i 'phro 'du las gzungs ma'i snang brnyan thogs te dbul zhing /
NK025(ra)001:13646: gzi brjid shin tu khyad par bde gshegs sku la
NK025(ra)001:13647: gzungs ma 'di log par lta ba mtha' dag yongs
NK025(ra)001:13648: gsang spyod yongs su dag pa thob par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13650: phyogs bcu rgyal ba zhi khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan
NK025(ra)001:13651: gyi dkyil 'khor la rig ma phul bas gang spyod
NK025(ra)001:13652: yongs su dag pa snyoms pa ra 'jug pa bdag
NK025(ra)001:13653: dang bzhi pa mnyes mchod phul bar mnga' gsol ba
NK025(ra)001:13654: la gsum las / ma skyes rdo rje dang /
NK025(ra)001:13655: bdag med phyogs bral kyis nang gi phyag 'tshal /
NK025(ra)001:13656: zhes gsungs pa'i zhi phyag rin chen d+r+wa ba las byung ba 'di ltar /
NK025(ra)001:13658: ma skyes rdo rje thabs kyi ye shes ni //
NK025(ra)001:13659: dmigs med shes rab yum gyi ngang du rtogs //
NK025(ra)001:13660: thugs rje bye brag sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK025(ra)001:13661: rdo rje sems dpa' che la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:13662: chos sku nam mkha' bzhin du dbyer med kyang //
NK025(ra)001:13663: gzugs sku 'ja' tshon bzhin du so sor gsal //
NK025(ra)001:13664: thabs dang shes rab mchog la mnga' brnyes pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:13665: rigs lnga bde bar gshegs la dmigs med chos kyi
NK025(ra)001:13666: sku la longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la cir yang
NK025(ra)001:13667: sprul pa'i sku la khams gsum zhing du sbyor la
NK025(ra)001:13668: mdzes pa'i sku mchog sems can sgrol la mkhas //
NK025(ra)001:13669: ngo mtshar pho brang bde bar gshegs pa'i yum //
NK025(ra)001:13670: shes rab thabs kyi gtso la mnyes mdzad ma //
NK025(ra)001:13671: rigs kyi yum chen lnga la thabs mkhas thugs rje ye shes sprul pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:13672: rang rgyud rnal 'byor dag pas grub pa brnyes //
NK025(ra)001:13673: thugs rje chen pos 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:13674: sems dpa' sems ma rnams la chos rnams rnam dag ye nas lhun grub pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:13675: rtogs par bya ba'i yul ni chos bzang mo //
NK025(ra)001:13676: de nyid don rig byed pa rdo rje yid //
NK025(ra)001:13677: kun bzang yab yum gnyis la rdzogs pa chen po'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK025(ra)001:13678: rtog pas rgyud drug so sor 'khor ba las //
NK025(ra)001:13679: thabs mkhas thugs rje cis 'dul der ston pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:13680: thub pa chen po drug la byams dang snying rje dga' dang btang snyoms kyis //
NK025(ra)001:13681: nyon mongs log par lta ba'i dgra rnams 'joms //
NK025(ra)001:13682: gshin rje gshed po la sogs khro rgyal bzhi //
NK025(ra)001:13683: sgo ba yab yum rnams la a ti pu hoh
NK025(ra)001:13684: pra t+aits+tsha hoh khro phyag dam pa rgyan las 'byung
NK025(ra)001:13685: ba 'di ltar / bdag med phyogs bral don dam thugs chud cing //
NK025(ra)001:13686: byams dang snying rjes dgra zin mi mnga' yang //
NK025(ra)001:13687: gdug pa 'dul phyir dus las mi 'da' ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:13688: 'jigs byed he ru ka phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:13689: srid gsum 'joms pa'i lha la mnyam nyid ngang gis
NK025(ra)001:13690: khro la khro bo longs spyod mdzad la rdo rje
NK025(ra)001:13691: 'du 'phro khro la mi gnas mi dmigs chos skur
NK025(ra)001:13692: dag pa la // bdud 'dul khro bo mchog gi skur ston pa //
NK025(ra)001:13693: thugs rje gzi ldan gdug pa thabs kyis 'dul //
NK025(ra)001:13694: bcom ldan khro rgyal sku la thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK025(ra)001:13695: khro mo dbang phyug sku la 'khril mdzad cing //
NK025(ra)001:13696: mkha' 'gro mi bzad 'bar ba'i sprin 'phro ma //
NK025(ra)001:13697: gdug pa 'dul mdzad yum la nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing //
NK025(ra)001:13698: 'dod rgur bsgyur ba'i gzugs can 'phrul po che //
NK025(ra)001:13699: ma sring byams pa'i tshul gyis grogs mdzad ma //
NK025(ra)001:13700: phyi nang mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la a ti pu hoh
NK025(ra)001:13701: pra t+aits+tsa hoh bye brag gi phyag 'tshal ba ni
NK025(ra)001:13703: chos sku mu mtha' dpag med rigs //
NK025(ra)001:13704: thabs mkhas phyag rgya rgyu 'bras rdzogs //
NK025(ra)001:13705: rang byung rol pa rang snang ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:13706: rang bzhin sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:13708: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK025(ra)001:13709: bde gshegs sku la phyag gi mchod 'bul bas //
NK025(ra)001:13710: lha dang bdag nyid gnyis su med pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:13711: don la 'byams pa'i 'bras bu thob par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13713: phyogs bcu rnal 'byor pa bdag gis rgyal ba zhi
NK025(ra)001:13714: khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK025(ra)001:13715: tshogs rnams la gus pa'i phyag phul bas /
NK025(ra)001:13716: dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang gnyis med du mjal ba bdag dang phyag rgya la /
NK025(ra)001:13721: bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha dz+ny+aa na d+h+aa tu a /
NK025(ra)001:13724: h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK025(ra)001:13725: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:13728: 'di ni rgyal ba thams cad kyi //
NK025(ra)001:13729: dgyes pa chen po bskyed pa'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:13730: phyag rgya'i mchod pa dam pa yin //
NK025(ra)001:13731: a la la ste mchod par 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:13732: a la la ste dgyes par mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:13734: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK025(ra)001:13735: bde gshegs sku la phyag rgya'i gar phul bas //
NK025(ra)001:13736: mi 'da' dam tshig phrin las rol pa yis //
NK025(ra)001:13737: phyag rgya bzhi don yongs su mi 'da' shog /
NK025(ra)001:13739: phyogs bcu rnal 'byor pa bdag gis rgyal ba zhi
NK025(ra)001:13740: khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor lha tshogs
NK025(ra)001:13741: la phyag rgya'i mchod pa phul bas /
NK025(ra)001:13742: mi 'da' ba'i dam tshig gi sgo nas phyag rgya
NK025(ra)001:13743: bdag dang snang srid kun bzang dang zhes gsungs pa
NK025(ra)001:13745: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK025(ra)001:13746: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i ye shes kyis //
NK025(ra)001:13747: srid pa rgya ma tsho mtha' yas kun //
NK025(ra)001:13748: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK025(ra)001:13751: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi shwa mu
NK025(ra)001:13752: khe b+h+yahsarba tat+kham ung+ga te s+pha ra na hi mam
NK025(ra)001:13753: ga ga na kham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:13756: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK025(ra)001:13757: rgyal la snang srid mchod par phul ba yis //
NK025(ra)001:13758: spyod yul yongs dag lha dang dbyer med pa //
NK025(ra)001:13759: don rtogs kun nas kun bzang thob par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13761: phyogs bcu rnal 'byor pa bdag gis rgyal ba zhi
NK025(ra)001:13762: khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la spyod
NK025(ra)001:13763: yul yongs su dag pa snang srid kyi mchod pa
NK025(ra)001:13764: phul bas / dkyil 'khor kun tu dbyer med kun
NK025(ra)001:13765: tu bzang po bdag dang yang dag don du dang
NK025(ra)001:13768: yang dag don du dag mod kyang //
NK025(ra)001:13769: 'gro ba yongs kyi don slad du //
NK025(ra)001:13770: phyag dang zhabs gnyis bsil nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:13771: rdo rje'i gdan la bzugs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:13772: +aa ha ra +aa ha ra sarba bi d+y+aa d+h+aa
NK025(ra)001:13773: ra p+au dzi te na mahs man+ta bud+d+ha n+aam ga
NK025(ra)001:13774: ga na kham sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:13776: lhag pa gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK025(ra)001:13777: rang bzhin spros bral chos su rnam dag kyang //
NK025(ra)001:13778: sri zhu gus pas ar+g+ha 'di phul bas //
NK025(ra)001:13779: phyi nang byang chub sems su rnam dag cing //
NK025(ra)001:13780: bsod nams mi zad gter gyi phul gyur shog /
NK025(ra)001:13782: phyogs bcu rnal 'byor pa bdag gis rgyal ba zhi
NK025(ra)001:13783: khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor lha la
NK025(ra)001:13785: spyod lam gyi sgo yongs su dag nas bsod nams
NK025(ra)001:13786: mi zad pa'i gter bdag dang dkyil 'khor shar gyi
NK025(ra)001:13787: rab gnas kyi mchod pa'i yo byad spos dang mar
NK025(ra)001:13791: ti pu pa ra muh sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid d+hoo /
NK025(ra)001:13792: sa ma yo ta muh sarba ma h+aa su kha sid d+hoo /
NK025(ra)001:13793: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+au pe d+h+au /
NK025(ra)001:13795: mchog tu rnam par dag pa'i sku mnga' ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:13796: bde gshegs sku la bdug spos 'di dam tshig sdom pa'i nyes pa kun bral nas //
NK025(ra)001:13797: ye shes thugs rjes ma lus 'dzin par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13799: phyogs bcu rnal 'byor pa bdag gis rgyal ba zhi
NK025(ra)001:13800: khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK025(ra)001:13802: theg pa so so'i dam tshig sdom pa'i nyes ltung
NK025(ra)001:13803: las grol te thugs rje ngang gis phyogs bcur 'gro
NK025(ra)001:13804: ba la 'dzin pa bdag dang pa na pem sh+r+ai
NK025(ra)001:13807: yon tan lhun rdzogs sangs rgyas sku gzugs la //
NK025(ra)001:13808: rin chen mdzes pa'i me tog 'di log lta'i nyon mongs tha ba kun bral nas //
NK025(ra)001:13809: lta bas mi ngom mchog gi sku thob shog /
NK025(ra)001:13811: phyogs bcu rnal 'byor pa bdag gis rgyal ba zhi
NK025(ra)001:13812: khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK025(ra)001:13813: tshogs la me tog phul bas /
NK025(ra)001:13814: log lta nyon mongs kyi thabs bral te /
NK025(ra)001:13815: bsod nams ye shes kyi sku bdag dang pa na
NK025(ra)001:13816: pem sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga +aa lo ge h+r+aih rtsa
NK025(ra)001:13817: bar / thams cad mkhyen pa'i sku gzugs sangs rgyas la //
NK025(ra)001:13818: mun pa sel byed mar me 'di ma rig 'thibs po'i mun pa kun bral nas //
NK025(ra)001:13819: spyan lnga yongs su dag pa thob par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13821: phyogs bcu rnal 'byor pa bdag gis rgyal ba zhi
NK025(ra)001:13822: khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK025(ra)001:13823: tshogs la mar me phul bas /
NK025(ra)001:13824: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa'i mun pa rab tu bsal te /
NK025(ra)001:13825: sangs rgyas kyi spyan lnga bdag dang pa na pem sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga gan+d+he gan /
NK025(ra)001:13827: snyigs ma lnga nyid 'bras bu yongs rdzogs pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:13828: bde gshegs sku la dri chab 'di nyon mongs gdung ba'i zug rngu kun bral te //
NK025(ra)001:13829: 'od zer mtha' yas 'gyed pa'i sku thob shog /
NK025(ra)001:13831: phyogs bcu rnal 'byor pa bdag gis rgyal ba zhi
NK025(ra)001:13832: khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK025(ra)001:13833: tshogs la dri chab phul bas /
NK025(ra)001:13834: nyon mongs pa'i zug rngu zhi nas 'od zer mtha' yas 'gyed pa'i sku bdag dang rtsa bar /
NK025(ra)001:13835: nang gi zhi khro'i sngags tshang ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:13838: a a a badz+r+ai b+ha dra sa man+ta ah h+aum badz+ra d+h+rika /
NK025(ra)001:13849: h+aum l+aa s+ya sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:13851: tram m+aa l+ye sa ma ya hoh h+r+aihha h+aum pad+ma pa da ma /
NK025(ra)001:13853: dz+rim ku ru pan+na h+r+aih a n+air+t+ya r+aa ga ya mi /
NK025(ra)001:13854: mee d+ha ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:13856: th+l+him nis+sa ram ba ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:13858: h+aum sa r+aa dza ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:13859: bam d+ai pa su khi n+ai /
NK025(ra)001:13860: mum sh+r+ai a ram ga ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:13863: mu ne h+aum trum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:13869: ma h+aa badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:13871: ma h+aa rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:13873: ma h+aa pad+ma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:13875: ma h+aa karma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dz+wa la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:13876: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:13877: a kra ma h+aa kro d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:13878: ka ta ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:13879: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sh+r+ai he ru ka sarba ta th+aa ga ta kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:13880: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:13881: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:13882: rat+na sh+r+ai he kur ka rat+na kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:13883: pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:13884: karma sh+r+ai he ru ka karma kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:13885: rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum rak+sha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:13886: sa nu sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum sa nu kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:13887: gu h+ya sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum gu h+ya kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:13888: yak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum yak+sha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:13898: badz+ra b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kh+aa he /
NK025(ra)001:13899: badz+ra sring+ga la mu kh+aa he /
NK025(ra)001:13900: badz+ra shwa na mu kh+aa he /
NK025(ra)001:13903: badz+ra k+aa ka mu kh+aa he /
NK025(ra)001:13904: badz+ra u lu ka mu kh+aa he /
NK025(ra)001:13905: badz+ra ar+ya te dzahte nga dzah badz+ra a mu kh+aa h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:13907: badz+ra b+hasmi ba la ya ba to hoh badz+ra a
NK025(ra)001:13908: pra ti ha +aar+ya ni tsa tu ra ta ra
NK025(ra)001:13910: sh+r+ai badz+ra mud+ga ra mu kha shwa ra ya na
NK025(ra)001:13911: mah a sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga ma shwa ra ya
NK025(ra)001:13912: y+aa na mah sh+r+ai badz+ra kha t+wam ga pra dz+wa
NK025(ra)001:13913: la ya y+aa na mah sh+r+ai badz+ra g+han+de pra dz+wa
NK025(ra)001:13914: la ya y+aa na mah ma nu rak+sha s+ai b+h+yo
NK025(ra)001:13917: besh+na be b+h+yoh ku m+aa r+ai b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:13926: badz+ra ru d+hi ra mat+t+aa b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:13927: badz+ra e ka tsa ra ma b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:13931: badz+ra ma h+aa m+aa ra na b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:13939: badz+ra bum pa ka la ma b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:13940: badz+ra lam bo d+ha ra b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:13943: ging+ga ra ha ha ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:13945: b+ha na b+ha na ang+ku sha dzah ha la ha la p+aa sha h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:13947: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+de hoh ma ma shwa ra h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:13948: bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha dz+ny+aa na d+h+aa tu +aah ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:13949: ma h+aa gu ru sh+aa ri ram g+ai li h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:13950: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:13952: ye shes sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:13953: rgyal ba'i sku la bdud rtsi lnga phul bas //
NK025(ra)001:13954: dug lnga gdod nas ye shes lnga dag pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:13955: sku dang ye shes lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13957: phyoogs bcu rnal 'byor pa bdag gis rgyal ba zhi
NK025(ra)001:13958: khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK025(ra)001:13959: tshogs rnams la bdud rtsi sman gyi mchod pa phul
NK025(ra)001:13960: bas / dug lnga ma spangs ye shes lngar dag
NK025(ra)001:13961: nas sku lnga bdag dang +aahh+aum gi 'phro 'du las
NK025(ra)001:13962: gtor ma bdud rtsi'i rgya mtshor bsam la /
NK025(ra)001:13965: u pa b+h+yoh ka ma la m+aa la badz+ra a
NK025(ra)001:13966: mri ta ha ra na pra t+aits+tsha b+ha ga wan
NK025(ra)001:13967: dzahh+aum bam hoh a la la hoh pa na pem
NK025(ra)001:13969: ti pu pa ra muh sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid d+hoo /
NK025(ra)001:13970: sa ma yo ta muh sarba ma h+aa su kha sid d+hoo /
NK025(ra)001:13971: bar 'dir sngar bzhin zhi khro'i mtshan sngags mthar /
NK025(ra)001:13972: ma h+aa ba lin+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:13976: chos rnams longs spyod yongs su dag pa yis //
NK025(ra)001:13977: bde gshegs sku la gtor ma 'di phul bas //
NK025(ra)001:13978: rdzas su spyod pa'i gdung ba kun bral nas //
NK025(ra)001:13979: gsang ba'i longs spyod yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK025(ra)001:13981: phyogs bcu rnal 'byor pa bdag gis rgyal ba zhi
NK025(ra)001:13982: khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor lha tshogs
NK025(ra)001:13984: dngos po rdzas kyi gdung ba ye shes su grol nas /
NK025(ra)001:13985: dam rdzas gsang ba'i longs spyod phun sum tshogs pa bdag dang nang gi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK025(ra)001:13987: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po ni //
NK025(ra)001:13988: sems kyi yid bzhin sprin tshogs kyis //
NK025(ra)001:13989: phyogs bcu thams cad sangs rgyas zhing //
NK025(ra)001:13990: mnyen 'jam reg na bde ba yi //
NK025(ra)001:13991: sna tshogs rin po che yi gzhi //
NK025(ra)001:13992: mdzes par bres shing spras pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:13994: dbyibs legs rdzing bu bro mchog bsil //
NK025(ra)001:13995: rin chen khang pa sna tshogs dang //
NK025(ra)001:13996: rgyan dang dpag bsam ljon pa'i tshal //
NK025(ra)001:13997: glu dbyangs tshigs su bcad pa'i sgra //
NK025(ra)001:13998: bla bre rgyal mtshan na bza' gdugs //
NK025(ra)001:13999: do shal dpung rgyan se mo do //
NK025(ra)001:14000: bza' dang btung ba'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK025(ra)001:14001: rang la mdzes par brgyan pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:14002: lha dang lha mo rdul snyed kyis //
NK025(ra)001:14003: bro gar la sogs bsam yas kyis //
NK025(ra)001:14004: phyogs bcu nam mkha'i khams bkang nas //
NK025(ra)001:14005: dkyil 'khor kun la rgyas par dbul //
NK025(ra)001:14006: skal ldan gsal ba'i khyad par gyis //
NK025(ra)001:14007: rim gyis yang na cig car du //
NK025(ra)001:14008: chos kyi dbyings dang mnyam sbyor zhing //
NK025(ra)001:14009: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen por bsgom //
NK025(ra)001:14010: a la la ste mchod par 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:14012: bde gshegs sku la ting 'dzin mchod phul bas //
NK025(ra)001:14013: phyi nang gsang don ma lus kun rdzogs te //
NK025(ra)001:14014: rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud mnyes nas //
NK025(ra)001:14015: 'bras bu mtha' yas kun la longs spyod shog /
NK025(ra)001:14017: phyogs bcu rnal 'byor pa bdag gis rgyal ba zhi
NK025(ra)001:14018: khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK025(ra)001:14019: tshogs la lhag pa ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa
NK025(ra)001:14020: phul bas / rgyal ba'i sku gsung thugs mnyes pa bdag dang bsgral mchod ni //
NK025(ra)001:14021: ri rab chen po'i gling bzhi la //
NK025(ra)001:14022: gnas pa'i sems can ma lus kun //
NK025(ra)001:14023: ye shes me chen bsgom bya ste //
NK025(ra)001:14024: thams cad ma lus bsreg par bya //
NK025(ra)001:14025: srid gsum sreg pa'i me yin te //
NK025(ra)001:14026: yid kyi ye shes me ru 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:14027: thog mar bdag nyid rtogs goms bsgral //
NK025(ra)001:14028: de nas gnyis med blo yis ni //
NK025(ra)001:14029: blo ngan 'jig rten snying re rje //
NK025(ra)001:14030: gnyis su med par bsgral bar bya //
NK025(ra)001:14032: ye shes spyod yul yongs su dag pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:14033: bde gshegs sku la ta na 'di phul bas //
NK025(ra)001:14034: khams gsum dug gsum rtsad nas bcad gyur te //
NK025(ra)001:14035: sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa thob par shog /
NK025(ra)001:14037: phyogs bcu rnal 'byor pa bdag gis rgyal ba zhi
NK025(ra)001:14038: khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK025(ra)001:14039: tshogs la sgrol ba'i mchod pa phul bas /
NK025(ra)001:14040: dug gsum rtsad nas chod cing sku gsum lhun grub bdag dang sbyor mchod ni /
NK025(ra)001:14041: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med par //
NK025(ra)001:14042: pad+mo la ni rdo rje zhugs //
NK025(ra)001:14043: 'khril ba'i mchod chen mnyam sbyor bas //
NK025(ra)001:14044: bdag nyid mnyes pas mnyes par bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:14045: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:14046: a nu r+aa ga ya mi /
NK025(ra)001:14047: a nu r+aa ga ya ham /
NK025(ra)001:14048: dzahh+aum bam hoh h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:14049: bo d+hi tsit+ta s+pha ra na phata /
NK025(ra)001:14051: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa p+au dza badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:14053: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:14054: bde gshegs sku la ga na 'di phul bas //
NK025(ra)001:14055: snod bcud byang chub sems su rnam dag ste //
NK025(ra)001:14056: mtha' yas snyoms par 'jug pa thob par shog /
NK025(ra)001:14058: phyogs bcu rnal 'byor pa bdag gis rgyal ba zhi
NK025(ra)001:14059: khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK025(ra)001:14060: la sbyor ba'i mchod pa phul bas /
NK025(ra)001:14061: thabs shes kyi spyod pas snod bcud theg pa chen po'i dbyings su dag ste /
NK025(ra)001:14062: bsam yas lhun gyis grub ting nge 'dzin bdag dang
NK025(ra)001:14063: dkyiil 'khor gyi lhor rgyas pa'i sbyin sreg gi dod
NK025(ra)001:14064: du bza' btung sna tshogs bsham pa rnams la dmigs
NK025(ra)001:14065: te / bza' dang btung dang bca' dang bgo //
NK025(ra)001:14066: longs spyod lnga ldan thams cad ni //
NK025(ra)001:14068: chos nyid la ni chos nyid rol //
NK025(ra)001:14069: a la la hoh rtsa bar /
NK025(ra)001:14070: bdag dang mtha' yas 'bral ba med pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:14071: rgyal ba'i sku la 'dod yon lnga phul bas //
NK025(ra)001:14072: mtha' la zhen pa'i gdung ba kun bral nas //
NK025(ra)001:14073: bde ba chen po'i don rnams rdzoogs pa shog /
NK025(ra)001:14075: phyogs bcu rnal 'byor pa bdag gis rgyal ba zhi
NK025(ra)001:14076: khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK025(ra)001:14077: tshogs la 'dod yon gyi mchod pa phul bas /
NK025(ra)001:14078: mthar 'dzin gyi zhen pa thams cad bral nas bde ba chen po bdag dang rak+ta dbul ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:14079: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK025(ra)001:14080: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK025(ra)001:14081: dpal chen 'khor bcas spyan drangs te //
NK025(ra)001:14082: dur khrod mchog gi gnas 'di ru //
NK025(ra)001:14083: zhing chen gsar rnying ti rar bcas //
NK025(ra)001:14084: dmar gyi ar+g+ham rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK025(ra)001:14086: ma lus par ni bsnams su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:14087: nga ni za byed chen po ste //
NK025(ra)001:14088: khams gsum ma lus bsgral ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:14089: gdul dka' ba dang 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:14090: sha rus la sogs za bar bya //
NK025(ra)001:14091: nga ni khrag 'thung chen po ste //
NK025(ra)001:14092: 'khor ba'i d+r+wa bar chags pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:14093: dmar chen po yi ar+g+ham la //
NK025(ra)001:14094: dmar gyi de ni rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK025(ra)001:14096: dzahh+aum bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya /
NK025(ra)001:14100: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta /
NK025(ra)001:14101: ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha hoh kha kha kha /
NK025(ra)001:14103: h+aum b+h+yo h+aum b+h+yo h+aum b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:14106: 'khor ba'i rtsa ba 'dod chags zhe sdang dang //
NK025(ra)001:14107: gti mug ma spangs rang sar grol ba yi //
NK025(ra)001:14108: khams gsum bag chags gting nas zad gyur te //
NK025(ra)001:14109: sprul pa'i sku yis 'gro ba sgrol bar shog /
NK025(ra)001:14111: phyogs bcu rnal 'byor pa bdag gis rgyal ba zhi
NK025(ra)001:14112: khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la rak+ta
NK025(ra)001:14114: rgyal ba'i thugs rjes khams gsum gyi dug thams cad
NK025(ra)001:14115: ma spangs par rang sar grol ba bdag dang zhi
NK025(ra)001:14117: khro bo'i sgeg pa dpa' ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:14119: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:14121: sgeg pa dpa' ba 'jigs su rung ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:14124: rang bzhin rnam dag bde gshegs sku gzugs la //
NK025(ra)001:14125: glu dbyangs snyan pa'i mchod pa 'di phul bas //
NK025(ra)001:14126: chos rnams skye 'gag med pa'i ngo bo la //
NK025(ra)001:14127: 'gro ba kun gyi spyod yul thob par shog /
NK025(ra)001:14129: phyogs bcu rnal 'byor ba bdag gis rgyal ba zhi
NK025(ra)001:14130: khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK025(ra)001:14131: tshogs la glu'i mchod pa phul bas /
NK025(ra)001:14132: yon tan gyis mngon par mtho bas kun gyis bkur
NK025(ra)001:14133: ba'i gnas su gyur pa bdag dang sku mchog phyag
NK025(ra)001:14134: rgya chen por gsal ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:14135: gsung mchog sngags kyi rang sgrar gsal ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:14136: thugs mchog chos nyid ngang du gsal ba yi //
NK025(ra)001:14137: yon tan rin chen bdag gzhan re 'dod skong //
NK025(ra)001:14138: phrin las rnam lngas dug lnga rang sar grol //
NK025(ra)001:14139: lhag pa'i 'bras bu lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK025(ra)001:14141: phyogs bcu rnal 'byor pa bdag gis zhi ba dang
NK025(ra)001:14142: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor la bstod pa'i mchod pa phul
NK025(ra)001:14143: bas / che ba'i yon tan mtha' dag thob nas
NK025(ra)001:14144: 'gro ba'i bkur gnas bdag dang phyag rgya gar mchod
NK025(ra)001:14146: khrag 'thung rgyal po gar la dgyes //
NK025(ra)001:14147: sku mdog zhal ni rnam par bsgyur //
NK025(ra)001:14148: sku yi gar stabs glog 'gyu ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:14149: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa bzhes //
NK025(ra)001:14152: rang bzhin rnam dag rgyal ba'i sku gzugs la //
NK025(ra)001:14153: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa 'di phul bas //
NK025(ra)001:14154: bsgul bskyod rol pa chen po'i phrin las kyis //
NK025(ra)001:14155: rdzu 'phrul thabs kyis 'gro ba'i don byed shog /
NK025(ra)001:14157: phyogs bcu rnal 'byor pa bdag gis rgyal ba zhi
NK025(ra)001:14158: khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor lha tshogs
NK025(ra)001:14159: la gar ye shes kyi mchod pa phul bas /
NK025(ra)001:14160: thabs mkhas rdzu 'phrul gyi rdzas thams cad lhun gyis
NK025(ra)001:14161: grub pa bdag dang rol mo'i mchod pa 'bul ba
NK025(ra)001:14162: ni / rnam dag sgrib spangs srid gsum skyon bral zhing //
NK025(ra)001:14163: ston ka'i zla gsal dri med zhal mnga' ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:14164: bcom ldan bde gshegs ye shes dkyil 'khor dbyings //
NK025(ra)001:14165: khro bo'i tshogs chen ma lus thams cad dang //
NK025(ra)001:14166: dus gsum bde bar gshegs pa bskyed pa'i yab //
NK025(ra)001:14167: shes rab lha mo rigs kyi yum dang bcas //
NK025(ra)001:14168: phyag brnyan gtum chen rngam pa'i tshogs la sogs //
NK025(ra)001:14169: bsod nams ye shes tshogs kyi zhing rab rdzogs //
NK025(ra)001:14170: rnal 'byor dam tshig bdag cag rnams kyis 'tshal //
NK025(ra)001:14171: dgyes pa'i dus kyi mchod par sbyar ba'i 'di //
NK025(ra)001:14172: bzhes te a la la ste dgyes par mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:14176: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:14177: dzahh+aum bam hoh badz+ra pra t+aits+tsha hoh rtsa bar /
NK025(ra)001:14179: ye shes spyod yul yongs su dag pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:14180: bde gshegs sku la rol mo'i sgra phul bas //
NK025(ra)001:14181: bdag dang 'gro ba sems can ma lus kun //
NK025(ra)001:14182: skye 'gag med pa'i don dang 'phrad par shog /
NK025(ra)001:14184: phyogs bcu rnal 'byor pa bdag gis rgyal ba zhi
NK025(ra)001:14185: khro'i lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor lha tshogs
NK025(ra)001:14186: la rol mo ye shes kyi mchod pa phul bas
NK025(ra)001:14187: / sgra'i bye brag sna tshogs don mthun du brda
NK025(ra)001:14188: 'phrod cing skye 'gag med par bdag dang zhi khro
NK025(ra)001:14189: la tshogs mchod so sor dbul /
NK025(ra)001:14191: dkyil 'khor gyi byang du bshams pa'i tshogs kyi 'khor
NK025(ra)001:14192: lo rnams cha gnyis su phye ste thog mar zhi
NK025(ra)001:14193: ba'i tshogs kyi 'khor lo bsang sbyang byin gyis rlob
NK025(ra)001:14194: pa nas / tshogs thog mtha' bar gsum tshang bar
NK025(ra)001:14195: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor la dmigs te bya
NK025(ra)001:14196: pa nas / / de rjes khro bo'i tshogs 'khor bsang sbyang byin gyis brlab pa nas bzung /
NK025(ra)001:14197: thog mtha' bar gsum tshogs la rol pa'i bar byas la /
NK025(ra)001:14200: yongs su smin pa phun sum tshogs pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:14201: bde gshegs sku la tshogs mchod 'di phul bas //
NK025(ra)001:14202: rdzas su spyod pa'i gdung ba kun bral nas //
NK025(ra)001:14203: gsang ba'i longs spyod yongs su rdzogs par shog /
NK025(ra)001:14205: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa chen po'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK025(ra)001:14206: rnal 'byor pa bdag gis rgyal ba zhi khro'i lhag
NK025(ra)001:14207: pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams la
NK025(ra)001:14208: longs spyod tshogs kyi mchod pa phul bas tshogs rnam
NK025(ra)001:14209: pa gnyis yongs su rdzogs pa'i don bdag dang de
NK025(ra)001:14211: e ma hoh mi 'jigs khri la mthing kha rdo rje bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14212: zhe sdang rnam dag rgyal ba badz+ra d+h+rika /
NK025(ra)001:14213: stong nyid ye shes mthar phyin chos kyi sku //
NK025(ra)001:14214: mngon spyod thugs rje'i dpal la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK025(ra)001:14215: stobs ldan khri la dung mdog 'khor lo bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14216: gti mug rnam dag rgyal ba dz+ai na dzika /
NK025(ra)001:14217: chos dbyings ye shes longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK025(ra)001:14218: thugs rje zhi ba'i dpal la rdzu 'phrul khri la gser mdog nor bu bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14219: nga rgyal rnam dag rgyal ba rat+na d+h+rika /
NK025(ra)001:14220: mnyam nyid ye shes mthar phyin rdo rje'i sku //
NK025(ra)001:14221: yon tan rgyas pa'i dpal la mdangs ldan khri la le brgan pad+ma bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14222: 'dod chags rnam dag rgyal ba +aa ro lika /
NK025(ra)001:14223: sor rtog ye shes mthar phyin byang chub sku //
NK025(ra)001:14224: dbang sgyur thugs rje'i dpal la thogs med khri la ljang gu rgya gram bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14225: phrag dog rnam dag rgyal ba pradz+ny+aa d+h+rika /
NK025(ra)001:14226: nan tan ye shes mthar phyin sprul pa'i sku //
NK025(ra)001:14227: las rab grub pa'i dpal la de nas kun gyi
NK025(ra)001:14228: phyag tu me tog thogs te bskor ba byed cing
NK025(ra)001:14229: / dus kyi 'khrug pa zhi bar gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:14230: mtshon gyi bskal pa zhi bar mi nad phyugs nad
NK025(ra)001:14231: rgyun chad par char chu dus su 'bab par lo
NK025(ra)001:14232: phyugs rtag tu legs par sems can thams cad bde
NK025(ra)001:14233: skyid phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan par bla na
NK025(ra)001:14234: med pa'i byang chub rin po che thob par gyur
NK025(ra)001:14235: cig bya'o // de dag ni rab gnas kyi cho
NK025(ra)001:14236: ga bsnyen sgrub bzhi las nye bsnyen zhag drug pa
NK025(ra)001:14238: zhes gsungs kyang zhag grangs skabs dang bstun pas chog go //
NK025(ra)001:14240: spyi don gsum pa dkyil 'khor sgrub zhag gi cho ga la /
NK025(ra)001:14246: zhal zas rol mo rtsa ba dang yan lag gi mchod pa so ma bsham /
NK025(ra)001:14250: srid pa phyi nang snod bcud ces srung ba'i 'khor los mtshams bcad /
NK025(ra)001:14251: steng 'og phyogs mtshams kyis gsal gdab /
NK025(ra)001:14253: sgrib pa rnam gnyis kyis gsal btab /
NK025(ra)001:14257: mthu dang bral ces pas gsal gdab /
NK025(ra)001:14258: ma tram mnan zhing gsang mtshams bcad /
NK025(ra)001:14259: khro bo bcu'i stangs stabs kyis dam sri brdung /
NK025(ra)001:14264: phyogs mtshams steng 'og gi mtshams srung khro bo rnams dang /
NK025(ra)001:14265: rang lus kyi steng 'og phyogs mtshams su khro bo
NK025(ra)001:14266: bcu rnams phyogs skyong bcu'i gdan la gsal btab ste
NK025(ra)001:14269: gdod nas ma skyes rnam dag chos kyi sku //
NK025(ra)001:14270: chos nyid byang chub sems su dbyer med kyang //
NK025(ra)001:14271: srid pa srog gis bsdus pa'i 'jig rten pa //
NK025(ra)001:14272: log rtog dngos po gsal ba'i dbang gis na //
NK025(ra)001:14273: sdug bsngal brgyad khri bzhi stong rang las byung //
NK025(ra)001:14274: sdug bsngal brgyad dang gsum gyi 'gro ba rnams //
NK025(ra)001:14275: rgyu 'bras theg pa gzhan gyis mi 'dul te //
NK025(ra)001:14276: gsang sngags gsang chen nges pa'i dus la bab //
NK025(ra)001:14278: srid gsum phyi nang snod bcud thams cad nas //
NK025(ra)001:14279: snyigs ma lnga dang skye 'gro ma lus kun //
NK025(ra)001:14280: thams cad sangs rgyas nyid kyi rang bzhin la //
NK025(ra)001:14281: thabs la mkhas pas 'di ltar brtag shing bsgom //
NK025(ra)001:14282: zhes brjod la bar 'dir gong du bshad pa ltar /
NK025(ra)001:14283: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:14284: bdag nyid skad cig gis rdo rje he ru ka
NK025(ra)001:14285: sku mdog mthing nag mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum
NK025(ra)001:14286: phyag drug gi zhes sogs nas /
NK025(ra)001:14287: ra ba gsum rim nam mkha'i mtha' klas pas gang bas mtshams bcad par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:14289: yang lung gi phrin las kyis /
NK025(ra)001:14291: steng 'og phyogs mtshams dngos po cir khro bcu yab
NK025(ra)001:14292: yum bsgoms pa'i byin phyogs bcur gnas pa'i bgegs rnams
NK025(ra)001:14293: kun bsal nas // bar gcod med cing dngos grub thob par shog /
NK025(ra)001:14294: ces pa don gsal gdab bo //
NK025(ra)001:14297: ye nas mnyam nyid chos skur dag pa la //
NK025(ra)001:14298: ma rig dbang gis sgro dang skur btab te //
NK025(ra)001:14299: bde dang sdug bsngal sna tshogs ngo bor smin //
NK025(ra)001:14300: de zlog don du rgyal ba'i dam nos te //
NK025(ra)001:14301: bdag cag ma rig lus dang ngag sems kyis //
NK025(ra)001:14302: bag med tshul gyi dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK025(ra)001:14303: rgyal ba 'khor bcas thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK025(ra)001:14304: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK025(ra)001:14305: don gsal gdab pa ni lung gi phrin las ltar /
NK025(ra)001:14307: sgrib pa rnam gnyis dngos po cir yid kyis sngon
NK025(ra)001:14308: du bshags pa'i byin sgrib pa ye nas dag pa'i
NK025(ra)001:14309: don rtogs nas // sems nyid rang bzhin med pa'i don rtogs shog /
NK025(ra)001:14312: rnal 'byor dbang po ye shes mthar phyin pa //
NK025(ra)001:14315: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:14316: byang chub mchog tu bdag gis sems bskyed de //
NK025(ra)001:14317: don dam dang ni sku rdzob byang chub sems //
NK025(ra)001:14318: deng nas tshul bzhin yongs su bzung bar bgyi //
NK025(ra)001:14321: spos dang rol mor bcas te /
NK025(ra)001:14323: a la la hoh b+ha ga wan /
NK025(ra)001:14324: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:14325: 'phags mchog thugs rje'i dus la bab //
NK025(ra)001:14326: khyad par bstan pa'i dus mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus
NK025(ra)001:14327: byin gyis brlab pa'i dus dbang mchog skur ba'i dus
NK025(ra)001:14328: dngos grub stsol ba'i dus mthu chen bdud 'dul bcom
NK025(ra)001:14329: ldan 'das // byin chen byin phob bcom dbang chen
NK025(ra)001:14330: dbang bskur bcom dngos grub mchog stsol bcom bdag cag
NK025(ra)001:14336: mthu dang bral ba'i sdug bsngal cir bde gshegs byin rlabs gsal bar rdzogs pa'i mthus //
NK025(ra)001:14337: rgyal ba'i sku ru lhun gyis grub nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:14338: thams cad byin rlabs mthu nyid lhun grub shog /
NK025(ra)001:14341: ma tram mnan zhing gsang mtshams bcad /
NK025(ra)001:14342: khro bo bcu'i stangs stabs kyis dam sri brdung /
NK025(ra)001:14344: de dag sngon 'gro'i skabs su rgyas par grub pas 'dir mi dgos shing /
NK025(ra)001:14346: sgrub chen gyi dus 'dir gong du rgyu mtshan smos
NK025(ra)001:14347: pa ltar bka' gter thams cad la nang re bzhin
NK025(ra)001:14351: rak+ta'i thig le rnams kyi rtags sgrub mched dpon slob kun 'debs shing gdab tshig ni /
NK025(ra)001:14354: chos rnams ye nas gnyis su med pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:14355: byang chub sems su gcig pa'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:14356: zhag gi zo ris mtshan pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:14357: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK025(ra)001:14358: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad dang //
NK025(ra)001:14359: sangs rgyas kun dang gcig pa'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:14360: 'di yang sngon gyi dam tshig lags //
NK025(ra)001:14362: ma h+aa smri ti man+da la h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:14363: chos rnams ye nas gnyis su byang chub sems su
NK025(ra)001:14364: thal chen tshom bus he ru ka yi dur khrod
NK025(ra)001:14365: chen po'i ging chen kun dang 'di yang sngon gyi
NK025(ra)001:14366: 'di yang rtags kyi ma h+aa kem ni ri ti
NK025(ra)001:14368: chos rnams ye nas gnyis byang chub sems su rak+ta'i
NK025(ra)001:14369: thig les he ru ka yi dur khrod chen po'i
NK025(ra)001:14370: mkha' 'gro kun dang 'di yang sngon gyi 'di yang
NK025(ra)001:14371: rtags ma h+aa rak+ta ti la ka man+da la h+aum
NK025(ra)001:14373: mchod pa byin gyis brlab la /
NK025(ra)001:14374: thun mong rdzas kyis zhes pas gsal btab /
NK025(ra)001:14375: ces gsungs pas gong du bshad pa ltar /
NK025(ra)001:14376: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi mchod pa byin gyis brlab pa las /
NK025(ra)001:14377: bdud rtsi byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:14378: amri ta kun+da li badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:14383: phyi mchod rnams byin gyis brlabs te /
NK025(ra)001:14384: nyer spyod dwangs shing thogs pa med pa nam mkha' dang mnyam par bsam mo //
NK025(ra)001:14388: thun mong rdzas kyi dngos po cir mchod pa byin gyis brlabs pa'i nus mthu yis //
NK025(ra)001:14389: 'dod pa'i yon tan mngon du rdzogs gyur nas //
NK025(ra)001:14390: dus gsum bde gshegs ma lus mchod par shog /
NK025(ra)001:14393: las mkhan gyis zhi khro rgyud ltar bskyed la lung gi gsal gdab gzhung gi skabs su /
NK025(ra)001:14394: lha kun bzang yab yum gyis gtso byas la 'dod don gsol gdab yan bya /
NK025(ra)001:14396: rab gnas kyi sngon 'gro'i gzhung srong skabs su lung
NK025(ra)001:14397: gi phrin las dang zhi ba'i las byang spel ba'i
NK025(ra)001:14399: zhi ba'i las byang gi thog mar kun rdzob sems bskyed ni /
NK025(ra)001:14400: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK025(ra)001:14403: gnas sa ri brag dngos po cir snang yang //
NK025(ra)001:14404: zhes sogs kyis gsal 'debs bya bas mtshon te /
NK025(ra)001:14405: 'dod don gsol 'debs kyi gsal 'dab lung gi phrin las kyi /
NK025(ra)001:14406: yid la bsam pa'i dngos po cir snang yang //
NK025(ra)001:14408: 'gro don ma lus lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK025(ra)001:14409: ces pa'i bar gong bzhin rgyud ma h+aa ltar bskyed cing /
NK025(ra)001:14410: don gsal 'debs lung a nu ltar bya /
NK025(ra)001:14411: bdag mdun gnyis snga ma ltar me long gi gzugs brnyan bzhin gsal 'debs pa'am /
NK025(ra)001:14412: yang na mdun bskyed ni dkyil 'khor la dmigs pa gzhir bcas /
NK025(ra)001:14413: bdag bskyed lus dkyil gong du smos pa bzhin bsgoms kyang chog pa gang bde bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:14415: de nas 'dzab khang phye la lha'i gtso bo kun bzang la /
NK025(ra)001:14416: rig pa gsung gi byin rlabs sogs kyi 'dzab bya /
NK025(ra)001:14417: chos sku nam mkha'i bstod pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:14418: sems dpa' dang sgo ba thub pa yan chad kyi bstod pa bya /
NK025(ra)001:14420: gong gi 'dzab khang dbye ba'i cho ga yang 'dir blangs te /
NK025(ra)001:14423: rtog pa'i gnas gsal gdab cing 'dzab bya ba /
NK025(ra)001:14425: zhes sogs sa bcad dang dmigs pa'i 'phro 'du bya tshul /
NK025(ra)001:14427: rig pa gsung gi byin rlabs kyis //
NK025(ra)001:14428: ljags kyi rtse la bkram nas ni //
NK025(ra)001:14429: du ma nyid du so sor go //
NK025(ra)001:14430: zhes sogs kun bzang yab yum nas bzung /
NK025(ra)001:14431: rdo rje dril bu ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:14432: zhes sgo ma dril bu ma'i bstod pa'i bar du sgra ji bzhin par bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:14433: de ltar zhi ba'i sgrub mchod grub nas khro bo'i cho ga bya ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:14434: chog khrigs chung zad mi 'dra bar bshad 'dug pas /
NK025(ra)001:14437: de nas che mchog gi zhal byang bya ste /
NK025(ra)001:14439: rang byung khro bo chen po bcu //
NK025(ra)001:14440: bgegs rnams thams cad gzir ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:14441: phyogs mtshams phur pas btab nas ni //
NK025(ra)001:14442: srung dang mtshams kyi las mdzod cig /
NK025(ra)001:14443: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum k+aa ra h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:14445: badz+ra kro d+ha bi dz+aa ya h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:14446: ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:14447: badz+ra kro d+ha n+ai la dan+da h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:14448: da ha da ha h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:14449: badz+ra kro d+ha ya man+ta ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:14450: pa tsa pa tsa h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:14451: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:14453: badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai wa h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:14454: hu lu hu lu h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:14455: badz+ra kro d+ha a p+aa ra dz+ai ta h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:14457: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:14459: badz+ra kro d+ha tree lo kya bi dz+aa ya h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:14461: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa b+aa la h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:14462: s+pho ta ya s+pho ta ya h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:14463: ces mtshams kyi khrod bcu gsal btab la /
NK025(ra)001:14466: dang po byang chub mchog dang zhes gsungs pa'i don
NK025(ra)001:14467: dri med bshags rgyud kyi le'u bcu drug pa las
NK025(ra)001:14469: dus gsum bde gshegs rgyal ba 'khor dang bcas //
NK025(ra)001:14470: rdo rje dam can ma lus dgongs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:14471: dang po byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed de //
NK025(ra)001:14472: sgrub pa'i rig 'dzin byang chub go 'phang du //
NK025(ra)001:14473: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:14474: yi dam lha dang rdo rje slob dpon dang //
NK025(ra)001:14475: gsang ba'i dam tshig grangs su mnos pa las //
NK025(ra)001:14476: dam bcas bka' las 'da' bar mi bgyid de //
NK025(ra)001:14477: las dang skal bas dmyal par skye bar 'gyur //
NK025(ra)001:14478: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug nga rgyal dang //
NK025(ra)001:14479: phrag dog la sogs shor nas nongs bgyis pa //
NK025(ra)001:14480: rdo rje slob dpon ston pa 'i sgron me la //
NK025(ra)001:14481: snying nas smad cing dam tshig nyams pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:14482: dam tshig gcig pa'i rdo rje spun rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:14483: ngan sems log par lta ba la sogs pa //
NK025(ra)001:14484: sku yi dam tshig nyams pa mthol lo bshags //
NK025(ra)001:14485: yi dam lha yi phyag rgya ma gsal zhing //
NK025(ra)001:14486: sngags kyi bsnyen pa grangs las chad pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:14487: dus drug las kyi mchod pa khyad pa du //
NK025(ra)001:14488: bsnyen sgrub skong ba'i cho ga ma bgyis te //
NK025(ra)001:14489: bka' ltar ma lcogs gzhung bzhin rngo ma thogs //
NK025(ra)001:14490: gsung gi dam tshi nyams pa rdo rje slob dpon byams pa'i bka' drin gyis //
NK025(ra)001:14491: snyan khung brgyud nas sems kyi dkyil du bzhag /
NK025(ra)001:14492: thugs kyi man ngag byin pas dam tshig 'dres //
NK025(ra)001:14493: gsang mtshams 'das nas 'chol bar smras la sogs //
NK025(ra)001:14494: thugs kyi dam tshig nyams pa chos rnams mnyam pa nyid du ma rtogs te //
NK025(ra)001:14495: yan lag dam tshig nyams pa le lo snyoms las gnyid kyi dbang gyur te //
NK025(ra)001:14496: bsnyen sgrub dam tshig nyams pa lung ngag yid kyi bsrung bya 'das pa yis //
NK025(ra)001:14497: sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig rtsa bar /
NK025(ra)001:14498: dang po skye ba thog ma med pa nas //
NK025(ra)001:14499: rnam par smin pa'i lus 'di yan chad du //
NK025(ra)001:14500: mi dge las kyis 'gro ba'i rgyu bsags pa //
NK025(ra)001:14501: byang zhing dag par byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK025(ra)001:14504: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:14505: byang chub mchog tu bdag gis sems bskyed de //
NK025(ra)001:14506: don dam dang ni kun rdzob byang chub sems //
NK025(ra)001:14507: deng nas tshul bzhin yongs su bzung bar bgyi //
NK025(ra)001:14510: spos dang rol mor bcas te /
NK025(ra)001:14512: dus gsum sangs rgyas 'khor dang bcas //
NK025(ra)001:14513: rang bzhin gnas nas sku bskyod de //
NK025(ra)001:14514: mkhyen pa'i gnas mchog 'dir gshegs la //
NK025(ra)001:14515: brtse bas byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK025(ra)001:14520: zhes pa skabs 'dir bdud rtsi byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:14522: a mri ta kun+da li badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha h+aum phata kyis bsang ba nas bzung /
NK025(ra)001:14523: byin gyis brlabs pa snga ma ltar byas te mthar /
NK025(ra)001:14524: sku gsung thugs sra zhing mkhregs pa'i dbang dang dngos grub dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:14526: a ho su kha d+har+m+aa k+aa ya +aahh+aum /
NK025(ra)001:14527: sid+d+hi h+r+aih zhes cung zad myang /
NK025(ra)001:14529: tshig dang bstun te gtor zhing /
NK025(ra)001:14532: bdud rtsi rang byung chen po 'dis //
NK025(ra)001:14533: ye shes lha la gtor byas pas //
NK025(ra)001:14534: bdag dang gnyis su med par 'grub //
NK025(ra)001:14535: dam can mched la gtor byas pas //
NK025(ra)001:14536: thugs dam gnyan po skong bar gyur //
NK025(ra)001:14537: rnal 'byor pa la gtor byas pas //
NK025(ra)001:14538: rtog sgrib bag chags byang bar 'gyur //
NK025(ra)001:14539: mi mthun phyogs la gtor byas pas //
NK025(ra)001:14540: drag po gtum po tshim par 'gyur //
NK025(ra)001:14541: b+ha gar ji bzhin bzhag pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14542: byang chub de nyid ltung gnas med //
NK025(ra)001:14543: byang chub sems ni kun tu drag /
NK025(ra)001:14544: thig le chos sku khyab pa'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:14545: ye nas dbyer med bya mi dgos //
NK025(ra)001:14546: dkyil du gyur nas mnyam gnas pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:14548: khams lugs su skabs 'dir gtor ma dang rak+ta la
NK025(ra)001:14549: de byin rlabs bya bar gsungs pa 'brel chags su
NK025(ra)001:14550: snang bas gong gi bdud rtsi byin rlabs kyi 'phros
NK025(ra)001:14551: ltar bya'o // khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:14554: e yam ra bam kem ram rnams chad de /
NK025(ra)001:14556: ces byung rim nas gzhal yas khang dang lha tshogs rnams tshang bar bskyed de /
NK025(ra)001:14557: mthar dkyil 'khor bcu gcig pa'i khyams kyi lha bskyed
NK025(ra)001:14558: pa rig 'dzin bla ma'i tshogs thams cad kyang zhal
NK025(ra)001:14559: lam mer mngon sum du bzhugs par gyur gyi bar
NK025(ra)001:14560: tshang bar brjod / bsdu na gzhung 'di bzhin brjod
NK025(ra)001:14561: pa'i rkyen gyis sngar yod gsal 'debs kyi tshul du
NK025(ra)001:14562: mdun bskyed kyi dkyil 'khor rten dang brten par bcas
NK025(ra)001:14563: pa rnams lam gyis gsal zhing /
NK025(ra)001:14564: bdag bskyed kyang me long dang gzugs brnyan bzhin du cig car gsal 'debs pa'am /
NK025(ra)001:14565: a nu ltar lus dkyil sgom pa gang bde bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:14566: rgyas bsdus gang byed kyang rtsa tshig 'di med du mi rung bas /
NK025(ra)001:14569: de nyid byang chub sems su gyur //
NK025(ra)001:14571: byang chub sems dpa' rim bzhin bskyed //
NK025(ra)001:14573: kun tu bzang mo nam mkha'i mkha' klong du //
NK025(ra)001:14574: dam tshig sgrol ma rlung gi rgya gram gtams //
NK025(ra)001:14575: m+aa ma k+ai ni rak+ta'i rgya mtshor 'khrug /
NK025(ra)001:14576: sangs rgyas spyan ma kem rus ri rab steng //
NK025(ra)001:14577: na bza' dkar mo kun tu drod 'bebs ma //
NK025(ra)001:14578: 'byung lnga yum lnga mtha' yas lhun gyis brtan //
NK025(ra)001:14579: b+h+r+aum las bskyed pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK025(ra)001:14580: nam mkha'i dbyings dang mnyam pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:14581: tshul bzhin byin gyis brlabs nas su //
NK025(ra)001:14582: gzhal yas khang pas gyur par bsgom //
NK025(ra)001:14583: zhes rten gzhal yas khang dang /
NK025(ra)001:14584: h+aum h+aum h+aum bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la
NK025(ra)001:14585: man+da la phata phata ha la ha la h+aum phata
NK025(ra)001:14587: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:14591: a kra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:14592: ma s+aur+ya man+da la ka ta ma h+aa kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:14594: gzhan yang khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi sngags rnams tshang bar brjod pas brten pa lha gsal gdab bo //
NK025(ra)001:14595: dbang bskur dang sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlab pa yang spro na gong ltar rgyas par bya /
NK025(ra)001:14598: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa +aa dar+sha sa ma t+aa
NK025(ra)001:14599: pra t+ya bek+sha na kri t+y+aa nush+tha na dz+ny+aa na
NK025(ra)001:14600: badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:14601: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya w+aa
NK025(ra)001:14602: ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham
NK025(ra)001:14603: / zhes pa tsam gyis don dran par byas te byin gyis brlab bo //
NK025(ra)001:14604: rtsa bar gsal bar ma byung yang med du mi rung ba'i phyir /
NK025(ra)001:14605: gong gi khro bo'i mdun bskyed kyi skabs ltar /
NK025(ra)001:14606: bdag mdun bum gsum gyi lha tshogs rnams kyi thugs
NK025(ra)001:14607: kar rang 'dra ba'i ye shes sems dpa'i thugs kar
NK025(ra)001:14608: dwangs ma'i srog h+aum mthing kha ye shes lnga'i rang
NK025(ra)001:14609: bzhin can las 'od zer gyi phreng ba phyogs bcur
NK025(ra)001:14610: 'bar zhing 'phros pas phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i rgyal ba
NK025(ra)001:14611: sras dang bcas pa rang bzhin sgyu 'phrul khro bo'i
NK025(ra)001:14612: dkyil 'khor 'khor lo'i bdag nyid can du gyur te
NK025(ra)001:14613: 'gro ba'i don la chas par gyur /
NK025(ra)001:14614: sa la sogs las phyag rgya byas //
NK025(ra)001:14615: zhes pa nas bzung snyan gsan spyan drangs bstim brtan pa /
NK025(ra)001:14616: b+h+au ta k+she tri pra tri t+aam pa ka la h+aum phata kyi bar du bya /
NK025(ra)001:14617: de nas bzhugs su gsol zhing phyag 'tshal ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:14618: rtags bstod kyi lha gsal gdab pa sogs thun mong ni /
NK025(ra)001:14620: e ma ho che mchog he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:14621: nyi shu rtsa gcig dbu ni rnam pa lhun gyis grub //
NK025(ra)001:14622: sgrib sbyong ye shes dbu ni khro chen stobs po che //
NK025(ra)001:14623: dang po rab tu dga' ba'i sa mnan pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:14624: skyon med ye shes dbu ni khams gsum rgyal //
NK025(ra)001:14625: gnyis pa dri ma med pa'i sa bdud 'joms ye shes dbu ni bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK025(ra)001:14626: gsum pa 'od 'phro ba yi sa rtog 'joms ye shes dbu ni 'dod pa'i rgyal //
NK025(ra)001:14627: bzhi pa 'od byed pa yi sa gzir mnan ye shes dbu ni rta mchog dpal //
NK025(ra)001:14628: lnga pa sbyang dka' ba yi sa rnam dag ye shes dbu ni mi g.yo mgon //
NK025(ra)001:14629: drug pa mngon du gyur pa'i sa thabs mkhas ye shes dbu ni gshin rje gshed //
NK025(ra)001:14630: bdun pa ring du song ba'i sa stobs ldan ye shes dbu ni dbyug sngon can //
NK025(ra)001:14631: brgyad pa mi g.yo ba yi sa mkhyen ldan ye shes dbu ni rnam par rgyal //
NK025(ra)001:14632: dgu pa legs pa'i blo gros sa brjid gnon ye shes dbu ni h+aum k+aa ra //
NK025(ra)001:14633: bcu pa chos kyi sprin gyi sa mngon shes ye shes dbu ni yak+sha he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:14634: bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa kun mkhyen ye shes dbu ni gu h+ya he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:14635: bcu gnyis rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa byams mgon ye shes dbu ni sa nu he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:14636: bcu gsum rdo rje 'chang gi sa rngam brjid ye shes dbu ni rak+sha he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:14637: bcu bzhi stug po bkod pa'i sa sprul pa'i ye shes dbu ni karma he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:14638: bco lnga pad+ma can gyi sa chags med ye shes dbu ni pad+ma he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:14639: bcu drug 'khor lo tshogs chen sa yid bzhin ye shes dbu ni rat+na he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:14640: bcu bdun de ba ko sha'i sa 'bar 'phro ye shes dbu ni bud+d+ha he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:14641: bco brgyad kun bzang dbye ba med pa'i sa stobs ldan ye shes dbu ni badz+ra he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:14642: bcu dgu rdzogs pa bla ma'i sa khyab gdal dbu ni che mchog nyid kyi dbu //
NK025(ra)001:14643: nyi shu srid gsum ngang rdzogs sa byang chub ye shes dbu ni rta skad nam mkhar sgrog /
NK025(ra)001:14644: rtsa gcig ye shes bla ma'i sa g.yas kyi dbu bdun zhal gdangs mche gtsigs pas //
NK025(ra)001:14645: 'khor ba'i skye shi rtsad nas gcod par mdzad //
NK025(ra)001:14646: g.yon gyi dbu bdun zhal gdangs mche gtsigs pas //
NK025(ra)001:14647: 'khor ba'i nyon mongs sdug bsngal zad par byed //
NK025(ra)001:14648: dbus kyi dbu bdun zhal gdangs mche gtsigs pas //
NK025(ra)001:14649: chos nyid klong du thams cad rngub par byed //
NK025(ra)001:14650: g.yas kyi spyan zlog nyi shu rtsa gcig gis //
NK025(ra)001:14651: bdud dang bgegs rigs thams cad thal bar zlog /
NK025(ra)001:14652: g.yon gyi spyan zlog nyi shu rtsa gcig gis //
NK025(ra)001:14653: ngan song 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal phyags mas 'debs //
NK025(ra)001:14654: dbus kyi spyan zlog nyi shu rtsa gcig gis //
NK025(ra)001:14655: mi 'gyur chos kyi dbyings su ce re gzigs //
NK025(ra)001:14656: mche ba dkar po zangs yag gtsigs pa yis //
NK025(ra)001:14657: 'khor ba'i bag chags skye shi rtsad nas gcod //
NK025(ra)001:14658: ral pa dmar po gyen du bardzesa pa yis //
NK025(ra)001:14659: chos dbyings ye shes mthar thug 'gran zla med //
NK025(ra)001:14660: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis phyag ni mngon sangs rgyas //
NK025(ra)001:14661: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi dang po na //
NK025(ra)001:14662: kun tu bzang po mnyam pa'i phyag rgya bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14663: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi dang po na //
NK025(ra)001:14664: kun tu bzang mo thal mo mnyam sbyor bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14665: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi gnyis pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14666: rnam par snang mdzad gser gyi 'khor lo bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14667: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi gnyis pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14668: sangs rgyas spyan ma gser gyi dril bu bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14669: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi gsum pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14670: rdo rje sems dpa' rdo rje rtse lnga bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14671: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi gsum pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14672: rdo rje dbyings phyug shel gyi dril bu bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14673: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bzhi pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14674: rin chen 'byung ldan rin chen zur brgyad bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14675: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bzhi pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14676: m+aa ma k+ai na g.yu yi dril bu bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14677: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi lnga pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14678: snang ba mtha' yas pad+ma 'dab brgyad bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14679: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi lnga pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14680: na bza' dkar po byu ru'i dril bu bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14681: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi drug pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14682: don yod grub pa rdo rje rgya gram bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14683: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi drug pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14684: dam tshig sgrol ma mthing gi dril bu bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14685: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bdun pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14686: sa yi snying po rin chen myu gu bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14687: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bdun pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14688: l+aa s+ye dkar mo me long rgya gram bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14689: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi dgu pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14690: nam mkha'i snying po gcod byed ral gri bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14691: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi brgyad pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14692: m+aa le sngon mo rin chen phreng ba bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14693: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi dgu pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14694: spyan ras gzigs dbang pad+ma dkar po bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14695: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi dgu pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14696: g+ai rti dmar po lcags sgrog pi wang bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14697: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14698: phyag na rdo rje rdo rje rtse lnga bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14699: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bcu pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14700: n+ai rti ljang gu dar gyi cod pan bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14701: zhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu gcig pas //
NK025(ra)001:14702: mgon po byams pa klu shing g+hun+d+he bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14703: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bcu gcig pas //
NK025(ra)001:14704: lha mo d+h+au be ma ni bdug spos bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14705: zhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu gnyis pas //
NK025(ra)001:14706: sgrib pa rnam sel gsung rab po ti bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14707: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bcu gnyis pas //
NK025(ra)001:14708: lha mo push+pe ma ni me tog bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14709: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu gsum na //
NK025(ra)001:14710: kun tu bzang po rin chen snye ma bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14711: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bcu gsum na //
NK025(ra)001:14712: lha mo +aa lo ke ni mar me bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14713: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu bzhi pas //
NK025(ra)001:14714: 'jam dpal gzhon nu me tog ut+pala bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14715: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bcu bzhi pas //
NK025(ra)001:14716: lha mo gan+d+he ma ni dri chab bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14717: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bco lnga pas //
NK025(ra)001:14718: gshin rje gshed po thod dbyugs gdengs pa bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14719: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bco lnga pas //
NK025(ra)001:14720: 'gugs byed rta gdong ma ni lcags kyu bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14721: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu drug pas //
NK025(ra)001:14722: bgegs rnams mthar byed rdo rje rtse lnga bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14723: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bcu drug pas //
NK025(ra)001:14724: chings byed gzhags pa ma ni zhags pa bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14725: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu bdun na //
NK025(ra)001:14726: pad+ma mthar byed thod pa sbrul dkris bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14727: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bcu bdun pas //
NK025(ra)001:14728: sdom byed nyi zla ma ni lcags sgrog bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14729: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bco brgyad pas //
NK025(ra)001:14730: shes rab mthar byed rdo rje rtse lnga bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14731: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bco brgyad pas //
NK025(ra)001:14732: thal byed dril bu ma ni dril bu bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14733: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu dgu pas //
NK025(ra)001:14734: lha dbang brgya byin sgra snyan pi wang bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14735: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bcu dgu pas //
NK025(ra)001:14736: lha min thag bzang ris ni go cha bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14737: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi nyi shu pas //
NK025(ra)001:14738: sh+aakya thub pa bseg shang par bu bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14739: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi nyi shu pas //
NK025(ra)001:14740: par+na sha ba ri ni po ti bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14741: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyii nyer gcig pas //
NK025(ra)001:14742: kha 'bar ma ni rin chen sgrom bu bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14743: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi tha ma na //
NK025(ra)001:14744: a wa glang mgo me chu grang dro bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14745: zhabs brgyad bgrad pas khro mo'i dbu brgyad bardzisa //
NK025(ra)001:14746: zhabs brgyad g.yas kyi dang po bgrad pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:14747: thig le chen po ting 'dzin chen po dang //
NK025(ra)001:14748: yangs pa med par chos kyi dbyings su sbyor //
NK025(ra)001:14749: zhabs brgyad g.yas kyi gnyis pa bde ba chen po'i ting 'dzin chen po dang //
NK025(ra)001:14750: klong du gyur pa'i chos kyi zhabs brgyad g.yas kyi
NK025(ra)001:14751: gsum pa rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin chen po
NK025(ra)001:14752: dang // skye shi med pa chos kyi zhabs brgyad
NK025(ra)001:14753: g.yas kyi tha ma thams cad 'byung gnas ting 'dzin
NK025(ra)001:14754: dang // chen po dang // zag pa med pa'i
NK025(ra)001:14755: chos kyi zhabs brgyad g.yon gyi dang po chags pa
NK025(ra)001:14756: med pa'i ting 'dzin chen po dang //
NK025(ra)001:14757: ye nas dag pa'i chos kyi zhabs brgyad g.yon gyi
NK025(ra)001:14758: gnyis pa 'da' bar dka' ba'i ting 'dzin chen po
NK025(ra)001:14759: dang // mthong ba med pa'i chos kyi zhabs brgyad
NK025(ra)001:14760: g.yon gyii gsum pa dmigs su med pa'i ting 'dzin
NK025(ra)001:14761: dang // chen po dang // rang bzhin med pa'i
NK025(ra)001:14762: chos kyi zhabs brgyad g.yon gyi tha ma skye shi
NK025(ra)001:14763: med pa'i ting 'dzin chen po dang //
NK025(ra)001:14764: 'du 'bral med pa'i chos kyi dbu skra kham nag gyen du 'khyil ba ni //
NK025(ra)001:14765: srid pa gsum las rnam par rgyal ba'i rtags //
NK025(ra)001:14766: rta mgo ljang nag rta skad sgrog pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:14767: snang srid thams cad dbang du sdud pa'i rtags //
NK025(ra)001:14768: smin ma khro gnyer glog ltar 'gyu ba ni //
NK025(ra)001:14769: ma rig rmongs pa'i mun pa sel ba'i rtags //
NK025(ra)001:14770: tshangs pa'i g.yang gzhi na bza' gsol ba ni //
NK025(ra)001:14771: longs spyod rdzogs sku mngon du bstan pa'i rtags //
NK025(ra)001:14772: sku mdog mthing nag 'jigs par bstan pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:14773: chos kyi sku la 'gyur ba med pa'i rtags //
NK025(ra)001:14774: sku smad stag gi sham thabs bsnams pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:14775: sprul pa'i sku yis cir yang don mdzad rtags //
NK025(ra)001:14776: sku stod glang chen ko rlon gsol ba ni //
NK025(ra)001:14777: theg pa rim dgus 'gro don mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK025(ra)001:14778: zhing chen g.yang gzhi sku la gsol ba ni //
NK025(ra)001:14779: thugs rje tshad med bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags //
NK025(ra)001:14780: thod pa skam pos dbu la brgyan pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:14781: dus gsum rgyal bas bsnyen bkur mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK025(ra)001:14782: sbrul nag stong gi gdengs kas brgyan pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:14783: klu rgyal rigs bzhi dbang du sdud pa'i rtags //
NK025(ra)001:14784: khrag dang zhag gi thig les brgyan pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:14785: ma mo mkha' 'gro dbang du 'dus pa'i rtags //
NK025(ra)001:14786: bskal pa'i me dpung klong na bzhugs pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:14787: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer 'phro ba'i rgyan //
NK025(ra)001:14788: rdo rje gshog pa mkha' ltar gdengs pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:14789: stong gsum 'jig rten zil gyis gnon pa'i rtags //
NK025(ra)001:14790: 'bar ba chen po'i gar dgus 'gying ba ni //
NK025(ra)001:14791: che btsan dpe byad kun las rgyal ba'i rtags //
NK025(ra)001:14792: khro rgyal che mchog 'bar ba'i zhabs 'og nas //
NK025(ra)001:14793: shin tu rngam pa'i khro mo gnam zhal ma //
NK025(ra)001:14794: sku mdog dud kha sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK025(ra)001:14795: dbu dgu phyag ni bco brgyad zhabs bzhi bgrad //
NK025(ra)001:14796: rnam thar dbu brgyad gyen du byung ba ni //
NK025(ra)001:14797: gsang ba'i thugs rje thabs dang shes rab ldan //
NK025(ra)001:14798: byang chub sems ni bdud rtsi ga 'ur bskyil //
NK025(ra)001:14799: 'jam dpal gzhon nu bdud rtsi'i pho brang bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14800: rta mgrin yab yum bdud rtsi'i pho brang bskyil //
NK025(ra)001:14801: stong pa bco brgyad phyag ni mya ngan 'das //
NK025(ra)001:14802: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis //
NK025(ra)001:14803: ban+d+ha rak+tasa bkang ba rdo rjes dkrug /
NK025(ra)001:14804: bco brgyad phyag ni g.yas kyi gnyis pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14805: goo r+ai b+han dmar zhing gi dbyung to 'phyar //
NK025(ra)001:14806: bco brgyad phyag ni g.yon gyi gnyis pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14807: sid+ha kha ro seng ge'i mgo bo can //
NK025(ra)001:14808: bco brgyad phyag ni g.yas kyi gsum pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14809: tsoo r+ai ser mo mda' gzhu 'gengs pa bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14810: bco brgyad phyag ni g.yon gyi gsum pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14811: b+y+aa g+h+ri gnan ltag stag gi mgo bo can //
NK025(ra)001:14812: bco brgyad phyag ni g.yas kyi bzhi pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14813: pra mo dmar mo chu srin rgyal mtshan 'phyar //
NK025(ra)001:14814: bco brgyad phyag ni g.yon gyi bzhi pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14815: sri la byis ldag wa yi mgo bo can //
NK025(ra)001:14816: bco brgyad phyag ni g.yas kyi lnga pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14817: beet+ta byis za rdo rje rtse dgu 'phyar //
NK025(ra)001:14818: bco brgyad phyag ni g.yon gyi lnga pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14819: shwa na 'dral lta spyang ki'i mgo bo can //
NK025(ra)001:14820: bco brgyad phyag ni g.yas kyi drug pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14821: puk+ka dmar ser byis rgyu 'dren byed ma //
NK025(ra)001:14822: bco brgyad phyag ni g.yon gyi drug pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14823: gri d+ha mgrin dmar bya rgod mgo bo can //
NK025(ra)001:14824: bco brgyad phyag ni g.yas kyi bdun pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14825: g+ha sma dung dmar rdo rje dung khrag 'thung //
NK025(ra)001:14826: bco brgyad phyag ni g.yon gyi bdun pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14827: kang+ka rkang phrag dur bya'i mgo bo can //
NK025(ra)001:14828: bco brgyad phyag ni g.yas kyi brgyad pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14829: sme sha mthing nag byis snying za ba mo //
NK025(ra)001:14830: bco brgyad phyag ni g.yon gyi brgyad pa na //
NK025(ra)001:14831: k+aa ka kha rog bya rog mgo bo can //
NK025(ra)001:14832: bco brgyad phyag ni g.yas kyi tha ma na //
NK025(ra)001:14833: tsan+da ser skya mchog lus 'dral ba rnams //
NK025(ra)001:14834: bco brgyad phyag ni g.yon gyi tha ma na //
NK025(ra)001:14835: hu lu lcags kyu 'ug pa'i mgo can bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14836: zhabs bzhi bgrad pas rigs bzhi'i dbu rnams bardzisa //
NK025(ra)001:14837: zhabs bzhi g.yas kyi dang po bgrad pa yis //
NK025(ra)001:14838: klong du gyur pa'i gsang ba'i b+ha ga dang //
NK025(ra)001:14839: bde ba chen po byang chub sems su sbyor //
NK025(ra)001:14840: zhabs bzhi g.yon gyi dang po zag stong med pa
NK025(ra)001:14841: gsang ba'i thams cad 'byung ba'i byang chub zhabs bzhi
NK025(ra)001:14842: g.yas kyi gnyis pa 'du 'bral med ba gsang ba'i
NK025(ra)001:14843: skye shi med pa'i byang chub zhabs bzhi g.yon gyi
NK025(ra)001:14844: gnyis pa gdod nas dag pa gsang ba'i rdo rje
NK025(ra)001:14845: lta bu'i byang chub khro mo gnam zhal 'bar ba'i
NK025(ra)001:14846: zhabs 'og na // sku gdung 'bar ba'i dpal chen yab yum bcu //
NK025(ra)001:14847: sngo nag smug nag ser nag dmar nag dang //
NK025(ra)001:14848: ljang nag zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi bgrad //
NK025(ra)001:14849: rdo rje 'khor yug dung chen gang ba dang //
NK025(ra)001:14850: ral gri thong gshol dgra s+t+wa sna tshogs bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:14851: sbrul dang thod rlon glang chen ko rlon dang //
NK025(ra)001:14852: zhing chen g.yang gzhi stag gi sham thabs dang //
NK025(ra)001:14853: khrag dang zhag dang rak+ta'i thig les brgyan //
NK025(ra)001:14854: bskal pa'i me ri 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs //
NK025(ra)001:14855: gnas yul khro mo bcu drug brjid pas bzhugs //
NK025(ra)001:14856: phyag rgya khro mo bzhi ni sgo bzhi bsrungs //
NK025(ra)001:14857: dbang phyug chen mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad ni //
NK025(ra)001:14858: rang rang stan dang lag cha sna tshogs dang //
NK025(ra)001:14859: ci bgyi zhes gsol nas ni chas te gnas //
NK025(ra)001:14860: de ltar rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal bkod nas //
NK025(ra)001:14861: snang srid thams cad 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal //
NK025(ra)001:14862: phyogs bcu rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor sangs rgyas nas //
NK025(ra)001:14863: 'jigs byed chen po'i dkyil 'khor bzhugs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:14864: skad cig gcig la bde gshegs skur ston ma //
NK025(ra)001:14865: byin rlabs mchog dang ldan par mdzad du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:14866: chos nyid mnyam pa'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang //
NK025(ra)001:14867: sku dang ye shes dkyil 'khor rang snang ba //
NK025(ra)001:14868: snang srid thams cad yab yum sku la rdzogs //
NK025(ra)001:14869: che mchog yab yum rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:14870: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus pa'i sku //
NK025(ra)001:14871: khams gsum sems can thams cad 'dren pa'i dpal //
NK025(ra)001:14872: 'gro drug sems can kun gyi sgrib sbyong ba //
NK025(ra)001:14873: bdud rtsi rgyal po khyed la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:14874: dug lnga 'bar ba'i sku lngar sbyor //
NK025(ra)001:14875: len pa med cing gtong ba med //
NK025(ra)001:14876: rig lnga dpal chen yab yum bcu //
NK025(ra)001:14878: chu zla lta bur rnyog bral zhing //
NK025(ra)001:14879: thams cad rtog pa yongs kyis spangs //
NK025(ra)001:14880: koo r+ai sing+ha sgo ma'i tshogs //
NK025(ra)001:14881: bdud rtsi sbyor la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:14882: bdag tu 'dzin med rnam par dag /
NK025(ra)001:14883: bdud dang ngan song gsum las thar //
NK025(ra)001:14884: dbang phyug ma dang ging gi tshogs //
NK025(ra)001:14885: bdud kyi bdud la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:14886: a ti pu hoh ma h+aa pu ru sha ya hoh bde bar gshegs pas dam bca' /
NK025(ra)001:14887: kun bzang gis mchod pa phul /
NK025(ra)001:14888: p+au tsa lnga gzhung ltar dbul /
NK025(ra)001:14890: khro bo'i cho ga'i skabs ltar /
NK025(ra)001:14891: bde bar gshegs pa khyed ci 'dra //
NK025(ra)001:14893: bdag cag bsam pa 'grub gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:14895: kun tu bzang po'i mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:14896: bde bar gshegs so khro rgyal gtso //
NK025(ra)001:14898: chu gnyis dang lha mo bzhi bsnol gyi mchod pa yang dkyus bzhin la /
NK025(ra)001:14899: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mchod pa chen po thams cad
NK025(ra)001:14900: dag cing lhun gyis grub par mdzad du gsol gyi
NK025(ra)001:14901: bar ro // bdud rtsi 'bul ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:14903: rang byung gdod nas rnam par dag /
NK025(ra)001:14904: rtsa brgyad stong las sbyar ba'i sman //
NK025(ra)001:14905: gnyis med bde chen las byung ba //
NK025(ra)001:14906: zas mchog tshe yi dri chen po //
NK025(ra)001:14907: sha chen mchod pa rin po che //
NK025(ra)001:14908: me tog pad+ma yang dag ldan //
NK025(ra)001:14909: rdo rje chu ste bdud rtsi mchog /
NK025(ra)001:14910: ga bur shel gyi pog phor dri //
NK025(ra)001:14911: rin chen me ltar 'bar ba'i tshogs //
NK025(ra)001:14912: yon tan 'bum phrag yangs pa'i bcud //
NK025(ra)001:14913: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK025(ra)001:14914: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK025(ra)001:14915: rgyud lnga sems can kun sgrol ba //
NK025(ra)001:14916: dug lnga sel ba'i thabs mchog ste //
NK025(ra)001:14917: thams cad bdud rtsi rnal 'byor che //
NK025(ra)001:14918: ma lus 'dus pa'i thig le che //
NK025(ra)001:14919: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyor ba //
NK025(ra)001:14920: gcig tu dpa' bo'i ro rnams dang //
NK025(ra)001:14921: gnyis su med par mnyam sbyar nas //
NK025(ra)001:14922: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK025(ra)001:14923: rgyal ba rgya mtsho thams cad la //
NK025(ra)001:14924: rnam dag bdud rtsi'i dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:14925: thugs rje che dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK025(ra)001:14926: ye sangs rgyas pa'i che mchog he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:14927: sku dang ye shes dkyil 'khor nyid la rdzogs //
NK025(ra)001:14928: rnam dag thugs rje sgyu 'phrul dkyil 'khor ye shes rang snang ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:14929: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis sangs rgyas rang snang la //
NK025(ra)001:14930: rnam dag thugs rje 'jam dpal gzhon nu rta mgrin yab yum dang //
NK025(ra)001:14931: bdud rtsi srid 'dzin yab yum mnga' bdag lha tshogs la //
NK025(ra)001:14932: rnam dag thugs rje khro mo gnam zhal koo seng bcu drug dang //
NK025(ra)001:14933: yum chen mkha' mnyam klong gi dkyil 'khor la //
NK025(ra)001:14934: rnam dag thugs rje tshogs rje tshogs bdag dpal chen he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:14935: sku gdung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor lha tshogs la //
NK025(ra)001:14936: rnam dag thugs rje sgo ma dbang phyug dam can ging gi tshogs //
NK025(ra)001:14937: dbang chen dkyil 'khor kun 'dus 'khor bcas la //
NK025(ra)001:14938: rnam dag thugs rje bsrung dang bskrad dang gsad kyi las mdzad pa //
NK025(ra)001:14939: rang byung bdud 'dul khro bo bcu rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:14940: rnam dag thugs rje dam tshig dbang dang shes rgyud gab sbas pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:14941: nges pa'i lung ston rdo rje slob dpon la //
NK025(ra)001:14942: rnam dag thugs rje kha skong sgyu 'phrul las 'di ltar /
NK025(ra)001:14943: shes pa'i khyad par rim pas dbang bskur ba'i //
NK025(ra)001:14944: rgyal thebs la sogs karma ging rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:14945: rnam dag thugs rje 'jig rten 'di dang phyi ma thams cad du //
NK025(ra)001:14946: dam tshig zung gis 'brel ba'i mched lcam la //
NK025(ra)001:14947: rnam dag thugs rje dam la gnas shing rig 'dzin sgrub pa po //
NK025(ra)001:14948: lha dang lha min phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor la //
NK025(ra)001:14949: rnam dag thugs rje tshe rabs sngon nas da lta yan chad du //
NK025(ra)001:14950: lus srog bskyed pa'i dus gsum pha ma la //
NK025(ra)001:14951: rnam dag thugs rje bdud rtsi'i dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:14953: thugs kyi dngos grub dam pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:14954: dngos po med pas dngos grub blang //
NK025(ra)001:14955: byang chub sems kyi sprin chen las //
NK025(ra)001:14956: ci ltar dmigs pa bzhin du 'grub //
NK025(ra)001:14957: a ho su ka d+har+m+aa k+aa ya +aahh+aum sid+d+hi h+r+aih zhes lan gsum gyis myang ngo //
NK025(ra)001:14959: u pa b+h+yoh ka ma la m+aa la badz+ra a
NK025(ra)001:14960: mri ta ha ra na pra t+aits+tsha b+ha ga wan
NK025(ra)001:14961: dzahh+aum bam hoh a la la hoh pa na pem
NK025(ra)001:14963: ti pu pa ra muh sarba ta th+aa ga ta sid d+hoo /
NK025(ra)001:14964: sa ma yo ta muh sarba ma h+aa su kha sid d+hoo /
NK025(ra)001:14965: ma h+aa ba lin+ta kh+aa his gtor ma phul /
NK025(ra)001:14967: bla med mchog gi mchod pa dam pa sbyar ba ni //
NK025(ra)001:14968: ye shes lnga yi 'dod pa'i dam tshig gsang ba'i mchod par bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:14969: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:14970: zhes bdud rtsi phul la bsgral mchod ni /
NK025(ra)001:14972: ye nas rgyu nyid dag pa la //
NK025(ra)001:14973: nga dang bdag tu rtog pa yis //
NK025(ra)001:14975: khams gsum thams cad bsgral ba'i zhing //
NK025(ra)001:14976: a tsa la sa ma ya d+har+m+aa d+h+aa tu swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:14979: lus kun yongs su 'khyud pa yis //
NK025(ra)001:14980: rdo rje pad+mara ldan byas pas //
NK025(ra)001:14981: rang byung rnams kyi bde mchog sems //
NK025(ra)001:14982: phul bas myur du 'grub pa yin //
NK025(ra)001:14983: r+aa ga p+au dza hoh rak+ta tshar gsum 'bul ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:14985: rgyud drug 'khor ba stongs par bsgral slad du //
NK025(ra)001:14986: dug gsum rtsad bcad sha khrag rus pa'i tshogs //
