NK025(ra)001:14987: gzung 'dzin rnam rtog kun dang bral ba yi //
NK025(ra)001:14988: mnyam pa chen po'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:14989: ma h+aa m+aam sa kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:14991: ma h+aa kem ni ri ti dz+wa la kh+aa hi /
NK025(ra)001:14992: gar dang rol mo glu ye shes kyi mchod pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:14994: lha mo rol mo bro gar glu yi tshig /
NK025(ra)001:14995: mdzes ldan sgyu ma'i gar dang tshangs pa'i dbyangs //
NK025(ra)001:14996: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor rnams la 'bul lags na //
NK025(ra)001:14997: kun tu bzang po'i mchod par bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:14998: ma h+aa p+au dza hoh 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:15000: hoh spros pa med pa'i dbyings rnam par dag pa'i
NK025(ra)001:15001: ngang ye nas lhun gyis grub pa'i rang byung rang
NK025(ra)001:15002: snang gi dkyil 'khor chen po bcom ldan 'das khro
NK025(ra)001:15003: bo thams cad kyi che ba'i mchog che mchog he
NK025(ra)001:15004: ru ka dang / khro mo gnam zhal ma dang /
NK025(ra)001:15005: sku gdung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor la sogs pa rnams mkhyen pas byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol /
NK025(ra)001:15006: yab yum thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa
NK025(ra)001:15007: las sprul pa'i sku phyag na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK025(ra)001:15009: dkyil 'khor gyi lha mo nyi shu dang bcas pa mkhyen pa'i byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol /
NK025(ra)001:15010: dbang mo ging dang bcas pa ye shes dang las
NK025(ra)001:15011: las grub pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa rnams mkhyen
NK025(ra)001:15012: pas byin rlabs dam pa mdzad du gsol /
NK025(ra)001:15013: hoh rnal 'byor gyi mchod pa longs spyod rdzogs pa'i
NK025(ra)001:15014: tshul du sbyar ba'i chos nyid las chos nyid 'byung
NK025(ra)001:15015: ba 'phags pa kun tu bzang po'i mchod pa'i sprin
NK025(ra)001:15016: bsam gyis mi khyab par sprul nas bdag nyid chen
NK025(ra)001:15017: po 'khor dang bcas pa la phud dang gtsang ma
NK025(ra)001:15019: ye shes la ye shes rol /
NK025(ra)001:15020: chos nyid la chos nyid rol pa'i tshul gyis bzhes shing longs spyad du gsol /
NK025(ra)001:15022: zhes gsungs pas ye shes sku mchog gi bshags pa bya /
NK025(ra)001:15025: rdzogs pa'i ye shes rmad po che //
NK025(ra)001:15026: zla gam dkyil 'khor rin chen dbang //
NK025(ra)001:15027: shar gyi phyogs su kha bltas nas //
NK025(ra)001:15029: mchod khang yid bzhin rin po che //
NK025(ra)001:15031: phar 'phros pas ni thugs dam bskul //
NK025(ra)001:15032: slar 'dus pas ni dngos grub stsol //
NK025(ra)001:15033: 'di yang bsnyen pa'i mchog yin te //
NK025(ra)001:15034: nam yang nyams pa'i dus mtha' med //
NK025(ra)001:15035: dug gsum dbyings su sbyong bar mdzad //
NK025(ra)001:15037: dkyil 'khor gang byed kyi 'dzab bzlas zhes gsungs pas /
NK025(ra)001:15038: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha h+aum h+aum h+aum zhes dang /
NK025(ra)001:15039: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:15040: zhes pa ci mang bzlas so //
NK025(ra)001:15041: bar 'dir legs ldan dang dam can sogs chos srung rnams kyi bskang gso bya /
NK025(ra)001:15043: de nas tshogs byin gyis brlab /
NK025(ra)001:15044: dmigs med kyis spyan drangs la /
NK025(ra)001:15045: zhes gsungs pa'i don tshogs kyi 'khor lo rgya cher bshams la /
NK025(ra)001:15047: h+r+ai bi shud+d+he a mri ta h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:15048: d+harma a mri te h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:15049: badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:15050: ram yam kham gis bsreg gtor bkrus sbyangs nas /
NK025(ra)001:15051: pad+ma ba lin+ta bi shwa tsakra b+h+r+aum /
NK025(ra)001:15052: ma s+aur+ya man+da la s+pha ra na phata /
NK025(ra)001:15054: pam pad+ma man+da la s+pha ra sam ha a tsan+d+ra
NK025(ra)001:15055: man+da la s+pha ra sam ha tshogs kyi snod pad+ma
NK025(ra)001:15056: nyi zla'i gdan gyi steng du tshogs kyi yo byad
NK025(ra)001:15057: sha lnga bdud rtsi ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin 'dod
NK025(ra)001:15058: pa'i yon tan lnga'i rnam pa ma tshang ba med
NK025(ra)001:15059: pa bdud rtsi'i rol pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK025(ra)001:15060: bza' btung gi dngos por gyur /
NK025(ra)001:15062: ba lin+ta te dz+wa ba lin+ta gu h+ya sa ma ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK025(ra)001:15063: lan gsum gyis byin gyis brlabs te /
NK025(ra)001:15064: tshogs zhing spyan drang ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:15066: dmigs med mkha' ltar dag pas khyab pa'i sku //
NK025(ra)001:15067: spyan 'dren gshegs su gsol bar mi dmigs kyang //
NK025(ra)001:15068: thugs rje'i ngang nyid chos skur dag pa las //
NK025(ra)001:15069: ye shes sgyu mar rol cing gshegs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:15070: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:15071: e h+yi hi a na ya hoh dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes spyan drangs te /
NK025(ra)001:15072: tshogs kyi mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:15073: tshogs mchod 'dod yon gyi lha mo nam mkha' gang
NK025(ra)001:15074: ba dkyil 'khor lha tshogs rnams kyi dbang po'i lnga'i
NK025(ra)001:15075: spyod yul du thim par bsam la /
NK025(ra)001:15077: gzugs ni lag gnyis me long bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:15078: gzugs mdzes kun nas phyogs bcur spros //
NK025(ra)001:15079: shin tu sgeg bas gzi brjid bar //
NK025(ra)001:15080: gzugs kyi lha mo spyan la thim //
NK025(ra)001:15081: sgra ni lag gnyis pi wang bsnams //
NK025(ra)001:15082: sgra snyan yid du 'ong ba'i sgra //
NK025(ra)001:15083: sems can sdug bsngal sim byed pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:15084: sgra yi lha mo snyan la thim //
NK025(ra)001:15085: dri ni lag gnyis spos bsnams te //
NK025(ra)001:15086: spos kyi sprin lding bdug pa 'phro //
NK025(ra)001:15087: kun tu tshim byed dri bsung 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:15088: dri yi lha mo shangs la thim //
NK025(ra)001:15089: ro ni lag gnyis rin cen gzhong //
NK025(ra)001:15090: ro mchog brgyad ldan sna tshogs rol //
NK025(ra)001:15091: kun 'dus lus sems brtas byed pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:15092: ro yi lha mo ljags la thim //
NK025(ra)001:15093: reg nyid lag nas g.yon 'khyud la //
NK025(ra)001:15094: thugs ka dag tu yongs su sbyor //
NK025(ra)001:15095: kun tu sbyor bas bde ba che //
NK025(ra)001:15096: reg gi lha mo sku la thim //
NK025(ra)001:15097: de nas tshogs gsum du bcad de spros la /
NK025(ra)001:15098: dang po mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:15100: rdo rje tshogs dang mo k+sha'i tshogs la sogs //
NK025(ra)001:15101: smin ma a 'bras rgun 'brum pa na pem //
NK025(ra)001:15102: na ri ge sar a ti ka la sogs //
NK025(ra)001:15103: de yi tshim byed sna tshogs rnams dang ni //
NK025(ra)001:15104: zla rdzogs la sogs yang dag ldan pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:15105: dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i mchog tu sbyar ba 'di //
NK025(ra)001:15106: bsnams shing rol te dgyes par dgongs nas kyang //
NK025(ra)001:15107: dbang dang dngos grub bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:15108: bar ba bshags pa 'bul ba ni /
NK025(ra)001:15110: ma rig 'khrul pas gnong zhing 'gyod pa ni //
NK025(ra)001:15111: snyoms las dbang gis yi dam lha spangs shing //
NK025(ra)001:15112: slu byed rkyen gyis slob dpon snying nas dmad //
NK025(ra)001:15113: nga rgyal dregs pas mched dang lcam dral dkrugs //
NK025(ra)001:15114: lcam la phyar bas gsang tshig gzhan la spel //
NK025(ra)001:15115: ser snas bcings pas mchod pa lo zlar 'gyangs //
NK025(ra)001:15116: khrel 'dzem spags pas che ba'i yon tan dmad //
NK025(ra)001:15117: drag shul chung bas log 'dren tshar ma chod //
NK025(ra)001:15118: dpa' brtan chung bas phrin las zab mor dngangs //
NK025(ra)001:15119: mtshan ngan dri mas gsang ba'i p+au dza chag /
NK025(ra)001:15120: rngams pas thug thub phud dang lhag ma nyams //
NK025(ra)001:15121: mthong bsen rngan chags blang dor gnyis su gyur //
NK025(ra)001:15122: bka' chad rnam grangs gyur pa ci mchis pa //
NK025(ra)001:15123: byang zhing dag par byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK025(ra)001:15124: bdag cag mchod pa chags dang dam tshigs nyams //
NK025(ra)001:15125: mchod pa chag pa longs spyod tshogs kyis bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15126: rtsa ba yan lag nyams 'khrul ci mchis pa //
NK025(ra)001:15127: thams cad tshogs 'dis nyams chag skongs gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:15129: khro bo'i tshogs tha ma ltar ling ga bshams te /
NK025(ra)001:15130: rang dpal chen po'i nga rgyal gsal te /
NK025(ra)001:15134: bee d+aur sngon po'i rin chen ri rab la //
NK025(ra)001:15135: zhes sogs kyis khro bo la bstod cing /
NK025(ra)001:15136: sngags kyis 'bul ba'i bar rnams snga ma ltar ro //
NK025(ra)001:15137: slar yang tshogs la brten nas bshags pa dang gsol ba gdab pa'i slad du /
NK025(ra)001:15140: rdo rje dam can ma lus dgongs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:15141: rgyal ba zhi khro'i rjes 'brangs mkha' 'gro'i tshogs //
NK025(ra)001:15142: mchod sprin bla med nam mkha'i mtha' klas pa //
NK025(ra)001:15143: phul ba 'di bzhes bdag la skyabs mdzod cig /
NK025(ra)001:15144: dus ngan tha mar skyes pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK025(ra)001:15145: rang rig mngon shes mthu dang mi ldan pas //
NK025(ra)001:15146: snod dang skal par mi ldan slob ma btsud //
NK025(ra)001:15147: mi 'tshams pa la dbang bskur gsang ba bshad //
NK025(ra)001:15148: gsang sngags bcos gyin ngan pa'i rgyu bsags pa //
NK025(ra)001:15149: rjes su 'brangs pa khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK025(ra)001:15150: khyed ni rang rig mngon shes mthu dang ldan //
NK025(ra)001:15151: 'gro ba'i skyabs mchog ci phyir bskul ba bzhin //
NK025(ra)001:15152: thugs rje byams mgon ldan pa'i grogs mdzod cig /
NK025(ra)001:15153: dad pas rang nyid 'phags mchog khyed la mos //
NK025(ra)001:15154: rnal 'byor sku gsum ma thob bar du ni //
NK025(ra)001:15155: lus dang grib ma bzhin du 'grogs bya zhing //
NK025(ra)001:15156: rnam lnga mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK025(ra)001:15157: bdag gi bcol ba'i las rnams sgrub par mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:15158: de nas brtan ma bskyang ngo //
NK025(ra)001:15159: zhes gsungs pa gzhung 'di ga nas 'byung ba ltar ram /
NK025(ra)001:15160: yang na snga 'gyur spyi ltar ro //
NK025(ra)001:15162: de nas khro bo'i 'dzab khang phye la /
NK025(ra)001:15163: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha h+aum h+aum h+aum dang /
NK025(ra)001:15164: rdo rje sems dpa' gnas 'gyur ba sogs kyi rigs lnga'i 'dzab bya /
NK025(ra)001:15165: de nas dbang mchog gi bya /
NK025(ra)001:15166: de nas lung gi he ru ka bzhi'i bya /
NK025(ra)001:15169: zhes gsungs pa'i don gong du khro bo'i 'dzab khang dbye ba ltar /
NK025(ra)001:15170: a kra ma h+aa kro d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:15171: ka ta ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai h+aum phata dzah ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:15173: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dbang gi dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK025(ra)001:15174: 'khor lo 'bar ba dbus kyi lte ba la //
NK025(ra)001:15175: bcom ldan che mchog dpal chen he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:15178: che mchog la gong du song ba'i dbang du byas te /
NK025(ra)001:15179: badz+ra he ru ka nas bzung byed par gsungs kyang /
NK025(ra)001:15180: lhag pa'i skyon med pas 'di bzhin bya ba legs pas /
NK025(ra)001:15182: bcom ldan dbang mchog he ru ka /
NK025(ra)001:15186: dbang gis dkyil 'khor chen po yi //
NK025(ra)001:15188: dregs pa bsnol ba'i gdan steng du //
NK025(ra)001:15189: rdo rje mi bskyod gnas gyur pa //
NK025(ra)001:15190: zhes sogs badz+ra he ru ka nas bzung /
NK025(ra)001:15191: ma h+aa gu ru sh+aa ri ram g+ai li h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:15192: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:15194: zhes rig 'dzin bla ma'i 'dzab kyi bar du dkyus bzhin bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:15196: de nas gsal btab la phyoogs bcu dus bzhi dang /
NK025(ra)001:15198: ces gsungs pa zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor gsal btab ste //
NK025(ra)001:15199: phyogs bcu dus bzhi rdzogs pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:15201: sku gsung thugs kyi thig le che ho'i bar gyis zhi ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:15203: gtum chen dus mtha'i me chen 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:15205: rdo rje rlung ste 'thor rlung che ho'i bar gyis khro bo la bstod do //
NK025(ra)001:15209: lung gsal gdab ste nub mo'i cho ga bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:15210: zhes gsungs pa tshogs song ma thag yin pas bya mi dgos /
NK025(ra)001:15211: lung gi phrin las gsal gdab ste mi nyal bar 'dzab bya ba'i don yin no //
NK025(ra)001:15213: nam langs ma thag lung gi lhag ma btang /
NK025(ra)001:15214: zhes gsungs pa lhag ma'i rgyu mtshan gong du song ba ltar ma byas kyang khyab la /
NK025(ra)001:15216: glan ston bsod nams mgon pos /
NK025(ra)001:15217: lhag ma btang la gtor ma ke tshang du bsag go //
NK025(ra)001:15218: ces gsungs pa'i phyir tshogs lhag gi cho ga bya
NK025(ra)001:15219: zhing lhag ga tor phyir mi bskyal bar nang du
NK025(ra)001:15220: bsag pa la dgongs pa yin pas shin tu 'thad
NK025(ra)001:15221: par snang bas de bzhin bya zhing cho ga 'og
NK025(ra)001:15224: de nas snga dro cho ga 'bring po byas la phyag 'tshal /
NK025(ra)001:15237: khro bo la ru lu bzlas /
NK025(ra)001:15238: yang na khams gsum lhar gsal gdab la /
NK025(ra)001:15239: gsang ba thugs kyi snying po nus tshad bzlas /
NK025(ra)001:15240: bla ma gzungs thag bzung la gu h+ya dang ru lu bzlas /
NK025(ra)001:15244: zhes gsungs pa'i don nyin mo'i cho ga bshad pas /
NK025(ra)001:15245: sngar bzhin rtsa ba dang yan lag gi mchod pa
NK025(ra)001:15246: tshogs kyi 'khor lo dang bcas pa zhal zas dang
NK025(ra)001:15247: mar me brgya phreng sogs bsham /
NK025(ra)001:15248: phyag 'bring po'am bsdus pa gang rigs bya /
NK025(ra)001:15249: mtshams gcod las gzhung ltar bya zhing /
NK025(ra)001:15250: lung gi phrin las kyis gsal gdab /
NK025(ra)001:15252: ye nas mnyam nyid kyis bshags //
NK025(ra)001:15253: rnal 'byor dbang po ye shes mthar phyin pa //
NK025(ra)001:15255: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:15257: byin 'bebs 'phags mchog thugs rje'am gong du bshad pa bzhin /
NK025(ra)001:15259: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i 'jig rten 'dir //
NK025(ra)001:15261: khrag zhag thal ba'i mtshan ma gsum gyis rtags gdab /
NK025(ra)001:15262: mchod pa byin brlab kyang las gzhung ji bzhin par bya /
NK025(ra)001:15263: zhi khro'i las byang dang lung gi phrin las spel ba yang snga ma ltar rgyas par bya zhing /
NK025(ra)001:15264: zhi ba'i tshogs kyi sngon du zhi ba'i 'dzab khang dbye ba dkyus bzhin bya /
NK025(ra)001:15265: khro bo'i tshogs kyi sngon du khro ba'i 'dzab khang dbye ba yang dkyus bzhin bya /
NK025(ra)001:15266: dril 'dzab dpon slob thams cad kyis gu h+ya dz+nya na dang /
NK025(ra)001:15268: 'dzab dbyangs 'dzab bskor dang bcas te bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:15270: rdul bral rtsol ba'i sdug bsngal cir snang yang //
NK025(ra)001:15271: bsnyen grub rnam bzhi'i 'dzab bsnyen byas pa'i mthus //
NK025(ra)001:15273: spro na zhi khro gnyis ka'i tshogs bya dgos kyang /
NK025(ra)001:15274: spros pas dub na snga dro'i cho ga 'dir zhi ba'i tshogs phul na legs sam snyam zhing /
NK025(ra)001:15276: ru lu'i 'dzab la brtson par bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:15279: gung dang dgong mo khro bo bcus mtshams bcad /
NK025(ra)001:15280: ye nas mnyam nyid kyis bshags /
NK025(ra)001:15284: zhi khro'i lha sngags kyis gsal gdab /
NK025(ra)001:15285: kun bzang nas mchod pa lnga dbul /
NK025(ra)001:15286: sngags tshan bsdus pas zhi khro la bdud rtsi /
NK025(ra)001:15290: khro bo la sngags kyis rang rak+ta dbul /
NK025(ra)001:15291: badz+ra e sa h+aum dang rgya mtsho lnga bya /
NK025(ra)001:15293: bo d+hi tsit+ta dang ru lu'i 'dzab bya /
NK025(ra)001:15295: de dag dkyil 'khor zhag gi cho ga te /
NK025(ra)001:15296: sgrub pa zhag grangs su byed kyang de ltar bya'o //
NK025(ra)001:15297: zhes gsungs pa'i don rtsa ba dang yan lag gi
NK025(ra)001:15298: mchod pa tshogs kyi 'khor lo rnams lngar ltar bsham
NK025(ra)001:15299: / rab gnas kyi rang bzhin dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'i skabs ltar /
NK025(ra)001:15301: dbang mchog sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK025(ra)001:15302: zhes pa nas khro bo bcu'i sngags kyi bar brjod la khro mtshams gsal gdab /
NK025(ra)001:15304: ye nas mnyam nyid chos skur dag pa la //
NK025(ra)001:15306: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yi //
NK025(ra)001:15309: sman gtor rak+ta nyer spyod rnams las gzhung ltar byin gyis brlab /
NK025(ra)001:15310: zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor gnyis sngags kyis gsal gdab pa ni thog mar zhi ba la /
NK025(ra)001:15311: e yam bam sum lam ram b+h+r+aum /
NK025(ra)001:15312: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra rat+na pad+ma man+da la b+h+r+aum /
NK025(ra)001:15315: ma h+aa karma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai dza la n+ai h+aum phata /
NK025(ra)001:15316: zhes pa'i bar gyis zhi ba rnams dang /
NK025(ra)001:15317: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor la dmigs te /
NK025(ra)001:15318: e yam ram bam kem ram b+h+r+aum /
NK025(ra)001:15319: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he b+han+d+ha dz+ny+aa na tsakra s+aur+ya
NK025(ra)001:15320: tsan+d+ra pad+ma e ka man+da la de wa ti ra
NK025(ra)001:15322: ru tra kro d+hi ti ra bam /
NK025(ra)001:15323: a kra ma h+aa zhes sogs nas /
NK025(ra)001:15324: ma h+aa gu ru sh+aa ri ram g+ai li h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:15325: zhes pa'i bar gyis sngags rnams kyis gsal btab /
NK025(ra)001:15326: 'di ni sngags kyi phrin las lta bu'i don yin pas /
NK025(ra)001:15328: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra s+w+aa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:15333: zhes sogs sbyar bas dbang bskur /
NK025(ra)001:15334: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra /
NK025(ra)001:15335: de bzhin du w+aa ka badz+ra /
NK025(ra)001:15336: tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:15337: zhes sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab /
NK025(ra)001:15338: badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum dzah zhes snyan gsan dbab /
NK025(ra)001:15339: e h+ye hi b+ha ga wan ma h+aa k+aa ru
NK025(ra)001:15340: ni ka d+r+ai sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh sa
NK025(ra)001:15341: ma ya s+t+wam / e h+ye hi a na ya hoh dzahh+aum bam hohs spyan drangs /
NK025(ra)001:15342: badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah badz+ra p+aa sha h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:15345: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra gyis brtan par bya /
NK025(ra)001:15346: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK025(ra)001:15348: chu gnyis bzhi bsnol gyis thun mong du mchod /
NK025(ra)001:15349: sngar ltar rang sngags sam bsdu na zhi ba la bo d+hi tsit+ta dang /
NK025(ra)001:15350: khro bo la ru lu'i mthar /
NK025(ra)001:15351: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa his bdud rtsi phul /
NK025(ra)001:15352: de bzhin du sngags rgyas bsdus gang rung gi mthar /
NK025(ra)001:15353: ma h+aa ba lin+ta kh+aa his gtor ma 'bul /
NK025(ra)001:15354: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:15355: a nu r+aa ga ya mi /
NK025(ra)001:15356: a nu r+aa ga ya hoh dzahh+aum bam hoh h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:15357: bo d+hi tsit+ta s+pha ra na phata /
NK025(ra)001:15359: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa p+au dza badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK025(ra)001:15361: mchod pa'i phyag rgya chen po zhes sogs nas /
NK025(ra)001:15362: a la la ste mchod par 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:15363: zhes pa yan gyi ting nge 'dzin gyi mchod pa 'bul /
NK025(ra)001:15364: dzahh+aum bam hohsh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra sa ma ya /
NK025(ra)001:15368: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta /
NK025(ra)001:15369: ma h+aa ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha hoh kha kha kha /
NK025(ra)001:15371: h+aum b+h+yo h+aum b+h+yo h+aum b+h+yo /
NK025(ra)001:15376: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:15377: dzahh+aum bam hoh badz+ra pra t+aits+tsha hoh hohrgyala ba rgya mtsho dgongs su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:15378: mchod pa rgya mtsho bzhes su gsol //
NK025(ra)001:15379: nyams chag rgya ma tsho bskang du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:15380: dngos grub rgya mtsho stsal du gsol //
NK025(ra)001:15381: phrin las rgya mtsho bsgrub tu gsol //
NK025(ra)001:15383: rgyas bsdus gang 'os gong du bshad pa rnams las rig pas dpags te bya /
NK025(ra)001:15385: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha h+aum h+aum h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:15388: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:15391: zhi khro gnyis kar ram khro bo'i tshogs 'khor byin rlabs nas rol pa'i bar du bya /
NK025(ra)001:15393: bzhi pa sgrub pa chen po ni /
NK025(ra)001:15394: zhag bcu gcig gi dbang du byas na /
NK025(ra)001:15395: bcur 'gro ba'i dgong mo phrin las thung ba dang sbrel ba dbang gi sbyin sreg bya /
NK025(ra)001:15396: zhes gsungs pa'i don 'di lta bu ni chog khrigs
NK025(ra)001:15397: ltar sgrub zhag bdun lnga gsum gcig sogs ci 'grub
NK025(ra)001:15398: byas pa'i tha ma'i nub sngags kyi phrin las 'di
NK025(ra)001:15399: bzhin nam / zhi thung khro thung gzhung bsrang ste dbang gi sbyin sreg bya bar gsungs kyang /
NK025(ra)001:15400: zur lugs 'dir sbyin sreg bya gsungs pa tsam las
NK025(ra)001:15401: cho ga mi snang bas spro na rab gnas dus
NK025(ra)001:15402: kyi rgyas pa'i sbyin sreg skabs dang /
NK025(ra)001:15403: 'di'i dbang gi sbyin sreg sogs khams lugs lta bu'i cho ga zur nas blang ngo //
NK025(ra)001:15405: tshar ba dang dkyil 'khor gyi tha mar phyes rdo rje rgya gram bris /
NK025(ra)001:15406: dngos grub kyi zhal zas dang sha mar khur ba
NK025(ra)001:15407: sogs mched lcam du yod kyi grangs las lnga 'gyur
NK025(ra)001:15408: gyis lhag pa byas la mtha' mar dgod /
NK025(ra)001:15409: ces gsungs pa dngos grub blang ba'i rdzas yin pas da lta bsham mi dgos /
NK025(ra)001:15410: rtsa bar shar du dpal bshos /
NK025(ra)001:15413: zla gam la bkra shis kyi bya kha sprod /
NK025(ra)001:15414: gsol byang bdud rtsi rlon sbyor dza gad kyi gang ba khur bas bkab pa bsham mo //
NK025(ra)001:15415: zhes gsungs pa'i don ni dpal bshos dang rdo rje'i
NK025(ra)001:15416: tshe che mchog glang po'i dkyil 'khor rnams gong du
NK025(ra)001:15417: bshams zin la / gsol byang bdud rtsi'i snod kyi
NK025(ra)001:15418: gdan ni 'og tu gsang dbang gi dus su bshad
NK025(ra)001:15419: pa dang bdud rtsi'i dkyil 'khor bsgrub tshul gyi skabs
NK025(ra)001:15420: su bshad pa ltar sman lnga /
NK025(ra)001:15425: bdud rtsi lnga'i lde gu snyoms par byugs pa'i steng
NK025(ra)001:15426: rdul tshon nam chu tshon gyis 'khor lo ser po
NK025(ra)001:15427: rtsibs bzhi mu khyud can lte ba mthing kha pad+ma
NK025(ra)001:15428: 'dab brgyad kyi lte bar rdo rjes mtshan pa bris
NK025(ra)001:15429: pa la zhi ba zhe gnyis kyi mtshan ma byang
NK025(ra)001:15431: de'i steng thod pa mtshan ldan du byang sems 'o
NK025(ra)001:15432: ma bu ram sbyar ba dza gad bzang po dang
NK025(ra)001:15433: bsres te bkang ba khur bas kha bcad par gsungs
NK025(ra)001:15434: kyang / dar mthing dmar ram me long gis kha
NK025(ra)001:15435: bcad pa lding khri'i steng shar ram gang bder bzhag
NK025(ra)001:15437: de'i nub mo sngon 'gro sgrub pa'i phrin las rgyas par bya //
NK025(ra)001:15438: zhes gsungs pa sang nyin nas tshogs chen 'dus pa'i
NK025(ra)001:15439: dbang gi phrin las la 'jug pa'i dbang du byas
NK025(ra)001:15440: pa yin pas / gzhung bzhin nub mo'am yang na
NK025(ra)001:15441: nangs par tho rengs kyi cha la sngar bzhin rtsa
NK025(ra)001:15442: ba dang yan lag gi mchod gtor tshogs kyi 'khor
NK025(ra)001:15443: lo lha bshos dang mar me brgya phreng sogs kyang
NK025(ra)001:15444: spro na bsham ste sngon 'gro tshul phyag dang gral
NK025(ra)001:15446: mtshams gcod kyi bar shin tu rgyas pa dang /
NK025(ra)001:15447: bshags pa dam bca' byin dbab /
NK025(ra)001:15449: sman gtor rak+ta mchod pa byin brlab sogs kyang rgyas par rgyud lung bsdebs te byas /
NK025(ra)001:15450: mchod pa byin brlab kyi mjug tu bye brag gi dbang rdzas rnams byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK025(ra)001:15452: mchod pa byin brlab dus kyi dpal bshos la bdag
NK025(ra)001:15453: gi thugs ka nas h+aum dkar po 'phro 'dus 'od
NK025(ra)001:15454: du zhu ba las dpal bshos byang chub kyi sems
NK025(ra)001:15455: dkar dmar gyi ngo bo longs spyod sna tshogs 'byung
NK025(ra)001:15456: bar bsam mo // dbang bshos thugs ka'i tram 'phro
NK025(ra)001:15457: 'du las tram rat+na tree lo kya s+pha ra na
NK025(ra)001:15458: bar bsam mo // phata / sam ha ra na
NK025(ra)001:15459: h+aum gis rin po che'i mchod sdong phyi nang gsang
NK025(ra)001:15460: ba'i mchod pa thams cad 'byung bar bsam mo //
NK025(ra)001:15463: 'brang rgyas dang tshe lcam lugs ltar byin gyis brlab bo //
NK025(ra)001:15464: zhes gsungs pa 'og tu tshe dbang rgyas par yod pas de'i dus su bsgrub pas 'thus so //
NK025(ra)001:15466: gsol byang la thugs ka'i h+aum 'phro 'du las /
NK025(ra)001:15467: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra rat+na pad+ma man+da la /
NK025(ra)001:15468: zhes pa 'khor lo rtsibs gzhi mu khyud can du dpal chen po che mchog dbu nyer gcig /
NK025(ra)001:15469: phyag zhe gnyis pa gnam zhal ma dang khro mkhar
NK025(ra)001:15470: gyi tshul du bzhugs pa la koo r+ai brgyad kyis
NK025(ra)001:15471: bskor ba lam gyis bskyed la /
NK025(ra)001:15472: +aahh+aum las dkyil 'khor lha'i 'od zer thams cad 'dus
NK025(ra)001:15473: pas sku gsung thugs kyi ngo bo 'bru gsum du
NK025(ra)001:15474: bsam mo // de ni che mchog glang po'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK025(ra)001:15478: zhes gsungs pa thog mar zhi ba'i las byang rgyud lung gnyis bsdebs te bya /
NK025(ra)001:15481: de nas khro bo'i las gzhung yang rgyud lung gnyis bsdebs te bsrang /
NK025(ra)001:15483: spyi 'dzab tu gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na dang /
NK025(ra)001:15487: zhi khro gnyis thun mong gi skongs bshags ni stod smad kun dang /
NK025(ra)001:15488: gzhan la yang mkho che bas kho bo'i yongs 'dzin
NK025(ra)001:15489: sman lung pa chen po'i phyag bzhes las 'byung ba
NK025(ra)001:15490: bzhin 'di ltar / dpal he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK025(ra)001:15491: bskal pa dus kyi tha ma la /
NK025(ra)001:15492: nyams chag mang bas bskang ba ste tshogs bsham /
NK025(ra)001:15496: mched lcam kun byin brlab bya /
NK025(ra)001:15501: bskang ngo bskal pa'i thugs dam bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15502: dngos po stong nyid klong du bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15503: snang ba ye shes gsal ba shes rab sdug bsngal chos nyid kun gzhi klong yangs b+hany+dza ru //
NK025(ra)001:15504: byang chub sems kyi bdud rtsis bkang //
NK025(ra)001:15505: chos kyi sku yi lha tshogs thugs dam bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15506: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro'i thugs dam bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15507: nyams chag thams cad skong gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:15509: ye shes dri med bdud rtsis bkang //
NK025(ra)001:15510: longs spyod rdzogs sku'i lha tshogs bla ma yi dam
NK025(ra)001:15511: mkha' 'gro'i nyams chag thams cad mchog gi 'od gsal
NK025(ra)001:15512: b+hany+dza ru // thig le 'bar ba'i bdud rtsis bkang //
NK025(ra)001:15513: sprul pa sku yi lha tshogs bla ma yi dam
NK025(ra)001:15514: mkha' 'gro'i nyams chag thams cad ye shes rtsa lnga'i
NK025(ra)001:15515: b+hany+dza ru // skye med a dkar bdud rtsis bkang //
NK025(ra)001:15516: bde gshegs zhi ba'i lha tshogs bla ma yid dam
NK025(ra)001:15517: mkha' 'gro'i nyams chag thams cad ye shes 'bru lnga'i
NK025(ra)001:15518: b+hany+dza ru // shes rab rang gsal bdud rtsis bkang //
NK025(ra)001:15519: bde gshegs khro bo'i lha tshogs bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro'i //
NK025(ra)001:15520: nyams chag thams cad a wa d+hu ti'i b+hany+dza ru //
NK025(ra)001:15521: thig le 'bar ba'i bdud rtsis bkang //
NK025(ra)001:15522: 'jam dpal sku yi lha tshogs bla ma yi dam
NK025(ra)001:15523: mkha' 'gro'i nyams chag thams cad ro ma rkyang ma'i
NK025(ra)001:15524: chos nyid brlan gyi pad+ma gsung gi lha tshogs //
NK025(ra)001:15525: bla ma yi dam nyams chag thams cad mi shigs
NK025(ra)001:15526: thig le'i brdal ba chos nyid yang dag thugs kyi
NK025(ra)001:15527: lha tshogs bla ma yi dam nyams chag thams cad
NK025(ra)001:15528: dwangs ma lnga yi chos nyid 'od gsal bdud rtsi
NK025(ra)001:15529: yon tan lha tshogs bla ma yi dam nyams chag
NK025(ra)001:15530: thams cad rlung rtsa stong gi chos nyid stong gsal
NK025(ra)001:15531: phrin las phur ba'i lha tshogs bla ma yi dam
NK025(ra)001:15532: nyams chag thams cad lus rnams gsang ba dbang po'i
NK025(ra)001:15533: bde ba thig le dkar dmar rbod gtong ma mo'i
NK025(ra)001:15534: lha tshogs bla ma yi dam nyams chag thams cad
NK025(ra)001:15535: lto rgyab nyi zla ga'u'i 'chi med a yu dmar
NK025(ra)001:15536: po'i rig 'dzin slob dpon lha tshogs bla ma yi
NK025(ra)001:15537: dam nyams chag thams cad bdag med snying rjee chen
NK025(ra)001:15538: po'i ru tra zhing bcu bsgral ba'i 'jig rten mchod
NK025(ra)001:15539: bstod lha tshogs bla ma yi dam nyams chag thams
NK025(ra)001:15540: cad dam gtsang ting 'dzin gsal ba'i bsnyen sgrub gtor
NK025(ra)001:15541: tshogs chen po'i dmod pa drag sngags lha tshogs bla
NK025(ra)001:15542: ma yi dam nyams chag thams cad h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:15543: ma bcos rang byung chen po'i rdzas //
NK025(ra)001:15544: gdod nas dag pa gtsang rme bral //
NK025(ra)001:15545: rtsa ba brgyad la yan lag stong //
NK025(ra)001:15546: rigs lnga rgyal ba sgrub pa'i rdzas //
NK025(ra)001:15547: dam tshig skong ba'i sman chen 'di //
NK025(ra)001:15548: 'og min brdal khyab chen po na //
NK025(ra)001:15549: rang bzhin bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK025(ra)001:15550: ye shes lnga yi 'od kyi mdangs //
NK025(ra)001:15551: kun bzang mchod pa'i sprin gyis bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15552: thugs kyi dgongs pa rdzogs pa dang //
NK025(ra)001:15553: thugs rje'i sprul pas rigs drug sgrol //
NK025(ra)001:15555: kun tu bzang po'i thugs dam bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15556: rang la ye shes shar ba'i sku //
NK025(ra)001:15557: zhi khro rab 'byams 'gro ba 'dren pa thams cad kyi //
NK025(ra)001:15558: sku dang zhing khams mchod pas bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15559: thugs kyi dgongs pa rdzogs gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:15560: dam tshig nyams chag byang gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:15561: bdud rtsi sman gyi mchod pa la brten nas bla ma yi dam rgyal ba zhi khro rab 'byams /
NK025(ra)001:15562: dgyes ma mkha' 'gro bka' srung dang bcas pa /
NK025(ra)001:15563: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyi
NK025(ra)001:15564: thugs dam gyi rgyun ma bskang ba thams cad skong
NK025(ra)001:15565: bar gyur cig / de ltar thugs dam bskang pa la brten nas bdag sogs /
NK025(ra)001:15566: gshin don yin na dmigs yul gyis gtso byas zhes dang /
NK025(ra)001:15567: gal te sbyin bdag yin na sbyin pa'i bdag pos gtso byas zhes 'don pa bsgyur /
NK025(ra)001:15568: sems can thams cad kyi dam tshig nyams chag sdig
NK025(ra)001:15569: sgrib nyes ltung dri ma'i tshogs thams cad rtsa ba
NK025(ra)001:15570: nas byang zhing dag par byin gyis brlab tu gsol
NK025(ra)001:15573: shangs kyi rlung sgrom dpal bshos btsugs //
NK025(ra)001:15575: sgron ma mig gi dza gad gsal //
NK025(ra)001:15576: dbang po lnga yi rak+tasa brgyan //
NK025(ra)001:15577: 'di yang rang byung gtor ma yin //
NK025(ra)001:15578: bla ma yi dam mkha' 'gro'i thugs dam bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15579: nyams chag thams cad nyi zla ga'u'i gtor tsit+ta 'bar
NK025(ra)001:15580: ba'i dpal pad+ma 'dab brgyad mtheb rnam shes tshogs brgyad
NK025(ra)001:15581: dza rtsa chen bzhi yi rak+tasa 'di yang rang byung
NK025(ra)001:15582: gtor bla ma yi dam nyams chag thams cad brdal
NK025(ra)001:15583: khyab pags pa'i gtor rus pa rang gsal dpal rang
NK025(ra)001:15584: sha lnga yi mtheb bkrag dang mdangs kyi dza khrag
NK025(ra)001:15585: dang chu ser rak+tasa 'di yang rang byung gtor bla
NK025(ra)001:15586: ma yi dam nyams chag thams cad khog pa stong
NK025(ra)001:15587: yangs gtor mchin pa rang gsal dpal glo mtsher mkhal
NK025(ra)001:15588: ma'i mtheb gu h+ya nang rol dza rang snang mkhris
NK025(ra)001:15589: pa'i rak+tasa 'di yang rang byung gtor bla ma yi
NK025(ra)001:15590: dam nyams chag thams cad h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:15591: khams gsum gso ba zas kyi rgyu //
NK025(ra)001:15592: 'bru dang shing tog ro drug zas //
NK025(ra)001:15593: zhing bcu bsgral ba phung po'i sha /
NK025(ra)001:15594: dza gad dpa' bo 'bru yi bcud //
NK025(ra)001:15595: zhal zas 'dod yon sna tshogs su //
NK025(ra)001:15596: mos pas bsam ste mchod pa 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:15597: chos kyi dbyings su mos pas 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:15598: zhi ba'i lha la mdzes par 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:15599: khro bo'i lha la brjid par 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:15600: bla ma rnams la mnyes par 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:15602: bka' srung rnams la tshim par 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:15603: dam tshig bskang ba'i rten du 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:15604: dam tshig skongs la dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK025(ra)001:15605: ba lin gtor ma'i mchod pa la brten nas /
NK025(ra)001:15606: bla ma yi dam zhi khro rab 'byams /
NK025(ra)001:15609: spyi bo bde chen 'khor lo'i b+hany+dza ru //
NK025(ra)001:15610: sna tshogs rtsa yi rak+tasa bkang //
NK025(ra)001:15612: bla ma yi dam nyams chag thams cad mgrin pa
NK025(ra)001:15613: longs spyod 'khor lo'i sna tshogs yid kyi rak+tasa bkang
NK025(ra)001:15614: // 'di yang rang byung bla ma yi dam nyams
NK025(ra)001:15615: chag thams cad snying kha chos kyi 'khor lo'i bsam
NK025(ra)001:15617: 'di yang rang byung bla ma yi dam nyams chag
NK025(ra)001:15618: thams cad lte ba sprul ba 'khor lo'i nyon mongs
NK025(ra)001:15620: 'di yang rang byung bla ma yi dam nyams chag
NK025(ra)001:15621: thams cad gsang ba dbang po'i bde ba thig le'i
NK025(ra)001:15622: rak+tasa bkang // 'di yang rang byung bla ma yi dam nyams chag thams cad h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:15623: chos nyid brlan gyi ye shes chu //
NK025(ra)001:15624: thugs rje chags pa kha dog dmar //
NK025(ra)001:15625: srid pa bskyed pa rgyu yi khrag /
NK025(ra)001:15627: zhing bcu bsgral ba srog gi khrag /
NK025(ra)001:15628: rtsi shing dmar po 'byung ba'i khrag /
NK025(ra)001:15629: thams cad dag pa dbang gi rdzas //
NK025(ra)001:15630: ma dag khams gsum 'khor ba'i rgyu //
NK025(ra)001:15631: he ru ka yi dgongs pa yis //
NK025(ra)001:15632: srid gsum 'khor ba'i bag chags rnams //
NK025(ra)001:15633: mchod pa'i rdzas su byin brlabs te //
NK025(ra)001:15634: yum chen kun tu bzang mo la //
NK025(ra)001:15636: khrag 'thung khro bo'i tshogs rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:15637: thugs rje bskul ba'i mchod par 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:15638: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs rnams la //
NK025(ra)001:15639: dam tshig gso ba'i rdzas su 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:15640: dam tshig skongs la dngos grub stsol //
NK025(ra)001:15641: hoh rak+ta dmar gyi mchod pa la brten nas //
NK025(ra)001:15642: bla ma yi dam rgyal ba zhi khro rab 'byams /
NK025(ra)001:15645: brdal khyab pags pa'i kong bu ru //
NK025(ra)001:15646: khrag dang chu ser mar khus gtams //
NK025(ra)001:15647: sha khrag rus pa'i sdong bu la //
NK025(ra)001:15648: rang gsal bkra mdangs zhun me 'bar //
NK025(ra)001:15649: 'di yang rang byung sgron me yin //
NK025(ra)001:15650: bla ma yi dam nyams chag thams cad b+hany+dza 'bar
NK025(ra)001:15651: ba'i kong go ro tsa na'i mar gsal byed rtsa
NK025(ra)001:15652: yi sdong dbang po lnga yi zhun 'di yang rang
NK025(ra)001:15653: byung sgron bla ma yi dam nyams chag thams cad
NK025(ra)001:15654: tsit+ta 'bar ba'i kong snying tshil dkar dmar mar pad+ma
NK025(ra)001:15655: 'dab brgyad sdong rnam shes tshogs brgyad zhun 'di yang
NK025(ra)001:15656: rang byung sgron bla ma yi dam nyams chag thams
NK025(ra)001:15657: cad dwangs ma lnga yi kong sgrib med 'od lnga'i
NK025(ra)001:15658: mar don snying lnga yi sdong 'gyu byed rtsal gyi
NK025(ra)001:15659: zhun 'di yang rang byung sgron bla ma yi dam
NK025(ra)001:15660: nyams chag thams cad a wa d+h+au ti'i kong rang
NK025(ra)001:15661: gsal 'od kyi mar 'khor lo bdun brtsegs sdong byang
NK025(ra)001:15662: chub sems kyi zhun 'di yang rang byung sgron bla
NK025(ra)001:15663: ma yi dam nyams chag thams cad mi shigs thig
NK025(ra)001:15664: le'i kong skye med ye shes mar rtsa phran bcu
NK025(ra)001:15665: yi sdong rig pa rang byung zhun 'di yang rang
NK025(ra)001:15666: byung sgron bla ma yi dam nyams chag thams cad
NK025(ra)001:15667: ye shes rtsa lnga'i kong a dkar rtsa yi mar
NK025(ra)001:15668: ye shes 'od zer sdong shes rab 'bru lnga'i zhun
NK025(ra)001:15669: 'di yang rang byung sgron bla ma yi dam nyams
NK025(ra)001:15670: chag thams cad mchog gi 'od gsal kong mdangs gsal
NK025(ra)001:15671: 'od kyi mar thig le 'bar ba'i sdong ye shes
NK025(ra)001:15672: lnga yi zhun 'di yang rang byung sgron bla ma
NK025(ra)001:15673: yi dam nyams chag thams cad kun gzhi klong yangs
NK025(ra)001:15674: kong chos kyi dbyings kyi mar byang chub sems kyi
NK025(ra)001:15675: sdong dang sku lnga lhun grub zhun 'di yang rang
NK025(ra)001:15676: byung sgron bla ma yi dam nyams chag thams cad
NK025(ra)001:15677: h+aum / rdzas kyi kong bu brgya rtsa ru //
NK025(ra)001:15678: gtsang ma'i sdong bu brgya rtsa btsugs //
NK025(ra)001:15679: 'byung ba'i bcud mar zhun gyis bkang //
NK025(ra)001:15680: gsal ba'i mar me brgya spar nas //
NK025(ra)001:15681: dam tshig nyams chag bskang ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:15682: mos pas rgyal ba rnams la 'bul //
NK025(ra)001:15683: 'og min chos dbyings pho brang nas //
NK025(ra)001:15684: ye shes 'od lnga bkrag dang ldan //
NK025(ra)001:15685: zhi khro rab 'byams thugs dam bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15686: snying kha chos kyi pho brang nas //
NK025(ra)001:15687: ye shes sa bon thig ler gsal //
NK025(ra)001:15688: rang byung zhi ba'i thugs klad pa dung khang gzhal yas nas //
NK025(ra)001:15690: rang byung khro bo'i thugs mos gus dad pa'i snang ba la //
NK025(ra)001:15691: rig pa rang byung 'gag med gsal //
NK025(ra)001:15692: rdo rje slob dpon thugs rtsa rlung thig le'i dwangs ma la //
NK025(ra)001:15693: shes pa rang byung sa ler gnas //
NK025(ra)001:15694: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i thugs 'jig rten srid pa yangs pa la //
NK025(ra)001:15695: gza' skar 'od kyi thig ler gsal //
NK025(ra)001:15696: phyi yi dam can thugs dam tshig nyams chag thams cad kun //
NK025(ra)001:15697: thugs dam dbang gis dag par mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:15703: e yam bam lam ram shud+d+he shud+d+he /
NK025(ra)001:15705: zhes zhi byed khrus bdun gyi rig pa lan bdun bzlas /
NK025(ra)001:15706: skabs 'dir khyab bdag sman lung pa chen pos /
NK025(ra)001:15707: 'di ni sgyu 'phrul gyi chos skor du gtogs kyang /
NK025(ra)001:15709: snang ba ye shes sogs nas nye bar brtsams te mchog gi 'od gsal mi shigs pa'i thig le /
NK025(ra)001:15710: rig pa rang byung sogs rdzogs chen lhun grub chen
NK025(ra)001:15711: po'i nges pa gsal por ston phyir rnal 'byor pas
NK025(ra)001:15712: mnyam gzhag gi ngang nas ma yengs par brjod na
NK025(ra)001:15713: phan yon bsam gyis mi khyab cing /
NK025(ra)001:15714: tshig 'bru re la brtags kyang chos gzhan thams cad phyi shun nam /
NK025(ra)001:15715: sbun pa lta bur 'gro ba tsam yin pas mos
NK025(ra)001:15716: gus dang spro ba bskyed de brtson par bya rigs
NK025(ra)001:15719: sku yi dam tshig gso ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:15720: rdo rje slob dpon brgyud par bcas //
NK025(ra)001:15721: rdo rje mched lcam thugs dam bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15722: gsung gi dam tshig gso ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:15723: yi dam lha tshogs thugs thugs kyi dam tshig gso ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:15725: mi spang ba yi dam tshig rnams //
NK025(ra)001:15726: nyams pa gso bar bya ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:15727: gnyis su med pas thugs dang du blang ba'i dam tshig rnams //
NK025(ra)001:15728: nyams pa gso bar bya ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:15729: dam rdzas lnga yis thugs spyad par bya ba'i dam tshig rnams //
NK025(ra)001:15730: nyams pa gso bar sbyor dang sgrol bas shes par bya ba'i dam tshig rnams //
NK025(ra)001:15731: nyams pa gso bar phung po zhi khror grol 'dis bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15732: bsgrub par bya ba'i dam tshig rnams //
NK025(ra)001:15733: nyams pa gso bar rigs lngas dag pas gnas dang gnas gyur bskang ba ni //
NK025(ra)001:15735: rnam shes phung po gnas dag pa //
NK025(ra)001:15736: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs dam bskang ba //
NK025(ra)001:15737: gzugs kyi phung po gnas rnam par snang mdzad thugs
NK025(ra)001:15738: tshor ba'i phung po gnas rin chen 'byung ldan thugs
NK025(ra)001:15739: 'du shes phung po gnas snang ba mtha' yas thugs
NK025(ra)001:15740: 'du byed phung po gnas don yod grub pa'i thugs
NK025(ra)001:15741: nam mkha'i ngo bo gnas kun tu bzang mo'i thugs
NK025(ra)001:15742: sa yi ngo bo gnas sangs rgyas spyan ma'i thugs
NK025(ra)001:15743: chu yi ngo bo gnas m+aa ma k+ai yi thugs
NK025(ra)001:15744: me yi ngo bo gnas na bza' dkar mo'i thugs
NK025(ra)001:15745: rlung gi ngo bo gnas dam tshig sgrol ma'i thugs
NK025(ra)001:15746: mig gi rnam shes gnas sa yi snying po'i thugs
NK025(ra)001:15747: rna ba'i rnam shes gnas nam mkha'i snying po'i thugs
NK025(ra)001:15748: sna yi rnam shes gnas spyan ras gzigs kyi thugs
NK025(ra)001:15749: lce yi rnam shes gnas phyag na rdo rje'i thugs
NK025(ra)001:15750: mig gi dbang po gnas byams pa mgon po'i thugs
NK025(ra)001:15751: rna ba'i dbang po gnas sgrib pa rnam sel thugs
NK025(ra)001:15752: sna yi dbang po gnas kun tu bzang po'i thugs
NK025(ra)001:15753: lce yi dbang po gnas 'jam dpal gzhon nu'i gzugs
NK025(ra)001:15754: su snang ba gnas rdo rje sgeg mo'i sgra ru
NK025(ra)001:15755: grags pa gnas rdo rje phreng ba ma yi dri
NK025(ra)001:15756: ru snom pa gnas rdo rje glu dbyangs ma yi
NK025(ra)001:15757: ro ru bro ba gnas rdo rje gar bsgyur ma
NK025(ra)001:15758: yi 'das dus rtog pa gnas lha mo d+h+au pe
NK025(ra)001:15759: ma yi da ltar rtog pa gnas lha mo push+pe
NK025(ra)001:15760: ma yi ma 'ongs rtog pa gnas lha mo +aa
NK025(ra)001:15761: lo ke ma'i 'byung bar ma nges gnas lha mo
NK025(ra)001:15762: gan+d+he ma'i lus kyi rnam shes gnas gshin rje gshed
NK025(ra)001:15763: po'i lus kyi dbang po gnas stobs po che yi
NK025(ra)001:15764: lus kyi reg yul gnas rta mgrin rgyal po'i lus
NK025(ra)001:15765: kyi reg shes gnas bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i rtag par
NK025(ra)001:15766: lta ba gnas lcags kyu ma yi chad par lta
NK025(ra)001:15767: ba gnas zhags pa ma yi bdag tu lta ba
NK025(ra)001:15768: gnas lcags sgrog ma yi mtshan mar lta ba gnas
NK025(ra)001:15769: dril bu ma yi yid kyi rnam shes gnas rgyas
NK025(ra)001:15770: ba kun bzang chos khams sna tshogs gnas kun tu
NK025(ra)001:15771: bzang mo'i nyon mongs nga rgyal gnas lha yi thub
NK025(ra)001:15772: pa'i nyon mongs phrag dog gnas lha min thub pa'i
NK025(ra)001:15773: nyon mongs 'dod chags gnas mi yi thub pa'i nyon
NK025(ra)001:15774: mongs gti mug gnas byol song thub pa'i nyon mongs
NK025(ra)001:15775: ser sna gnas yi dwags thub pa'i nyon mongs zhe
NK025(ra)001:15776: sdang gnas dmyal ba'i thub pa'i bskang ngo bskal pa'i
NK025(ra)001:15777: thugs dam bskang // skongs gyur dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK025(ra)001:15779: rnam shes zhe sdang gnas gyur pa'i //
NK025(ra)001:15780: badz+ra he ru ka'i thugs dam bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15781: gzugs phung gti mug gnas bud+d+h+aa he ru ka'i tshor
NK025(ra)001:15782: ba nga rgyal gnas rat+na he ru ka'i 'du shes
NK025(ra)001:15783: 'dod chags gnas pad+ma he ru ka'i 'du byed phrag
NK025(ra)001:15784: dog gnas karma he ru ka'i nam mkha'i bkrag mdangs
NK025(ra)001:15785: gnas badz+ra kro d+hi'i sa khams sha rus gnas bud+d+ha
NK025(ra)001:15786: kro d+hi'i chu khams khrag chen gnas rat+na kro d+hi'i
NK025(ra)001:15787: me khams drod chen gnas pad+ma kro d+hi'i rlung khams
NK025(ra)001:15788: dbugs chen gnas karma kro d+hi'i kun gzhi'i rnam shes
NK025(ra)001:15789: gnas koo r+ai ma yi yid kyi rnam shes gnas
NK025(ra)001:15790: tsoo r+ai ma yi nyon yid rnam shes gnas pra
NK025(ra)001:15791: mo h+aa yi lus kyi rnam shes gnas bet+ta l+ai
NK025(ra)001:15792: yi mig gi rnam gnas puk+ka s+ai yi rna ba'i
NK025(ra)001:15793: rnam shes g+hasma r+ai yi sna yi rnam shes gnas
NK025(ra)001:15794: sme sha ni yi lce yi rnam shes gnas tsan+da
NK025(ra)001:15795: l+ai yi don dam sems nyid gnas sing ha ma
NK025(ra)001:15796: yi chos kyi khams chen b+y+aa gri ma yi bag
NK025(ra)001:15797: chags 'thug po sri la ma yi reg bya'i ngo
NK025(ra)001:15798: bo gnas shwa na ma yi gzugs kyi ngo bo
NK025(ra)001:15799: gnas gri d+ha ma yi sgra grags ngo bo gnas
NK025(ra)001:15800: kam ka ma yi dri snom ngo bo k+aa ka
NK025(ra)001:15801: ma yi ro yi ngo bo gnas u lu ma
NK025(ra)001:15802: yi rtag par 'dzin pa gnas rta gdong lcags kyi
NK025(ra)001:15803: ma yi chad par 'dzin pa gnas phag gdong zhags
NK025(ra)001:15804: pa ma yi bdag tu 'dzin pa gnas seng gdong
NK025(ra)001:15805: lcags sgrogs yi mtshan mar 'dzin pa gnas spyang gdong
NK025(ra)001:15806: dril bu ma yi sgal tshigs nyi shu rtsa brgyad
NK025(ra)001:15807: gnas dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad rtsa nyon yid
NK025(ra)001:15808: chos gnas spor ma brgyad kyi mi dge bcu po
NK025(ra)001:15809: gnas khro bo bcu yi pha rol phyin bcu gnas
NK025(ra)001:15810: khro mo bcu yi rtog tshogs chos dbyings gnas mkha'
NK025(ra)001:15812: dam can rgya mtsho'i bskang ngo bskal pa'i thugs dam bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15814: khro bo kun gyi rje btsan mchog che mchog lha tshogs thugs dam bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15815: mnyam nyid dbyings las ma g.yos kyang //
NK025(ra)001:15816: khrag 'thung lha tshogs drag pos gdug pa tshar bcad phyir //
NK025(ra)001:15817: gshin rje'i lha tshogs khams gsum dbang du sdud pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK025(ra)001:15818: dregs pa ma lus dbang du bsdus pa'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:15819: rta mgrin dbang gi lha tshogs dam sri gdug pa 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:15820: phur pa'i lha tshogs dus min 'chi ba bzlog pa'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:15821: ma mo'i lha tshogs rdo rje slob dpon mchod pa'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:15822: rig 'dzin gnyan gyi lha tshogs 'gro ba'i lha rnams mchod pa'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:15823: 'jig rten dregs pa'i zhing bcu gdug pa bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK025(ra)001:15824: drag sngags lha tshogs phyi rim lcags ri nag po la //
NK025(ra)001:15825: dpal gyi bka' sdod ci bgyi'i tshogs //
NK025(ra)001:15826: bskang ngo mchod do thugs dam bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15828: bskang ba med de khams gsum ye nas bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15829: sgrol ba med de dug gsum ye nas sgrol //
NK025(ra)001:15830: sbyor ba med de srid gsum ye nas sbyor //
NK025(ra)001:15831: ye sgrol ye sbyor chen po'i thugs dam bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15832: thugs dam bskang ba'i dam rdzas ni //
NK025(ra)001:15833: rgyu mchog chen po rnam lnga dang //
NK025(ra)001:15834: mchog chen mchog phran mtshan ldan dang //
NK025(ra)001:15835: rang byung dam rdzas bdud rtsi dang //
NK025(ra)001:15836: rmad du byung ba'i gtor ma dang //
NK025(ra)001:15837: rak+ta dmar gyi dgyes mchod dang //
NK025(ra)001:15838: sha chen spos kyi dud sprin dang //
NK025(ra)001:15839: rnal 'byor tshogs kyi longs spyod dang //
NK025(ra)001:15840: snang gsal 'di yi mdangs kyis bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15841: tsa ra 'di yi mdangs kyis bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15842: mkha' lding 'di yi mdangs kyis bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15843: shel gong 'di yi mdangs kyis bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15844: 'dir ltar bskang bskang gsos gsos pas //
NK025(ra)001:15845: thugs dam gnyan po des skongs la //
NK025(ra)001:15846: cho ga lhag chad rdzogs gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:15847: bdag gi g.yar dam gsos gyur cig /
NK025(ra)001:15848: g.yar dam skongs la rkyen dbang bzlog /
NK025(ra)001:15850: mchod du med de gnyis med rol pas mchod //
NK025(ra)001:15851: bskang du med de skye med ngang du bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15852: sbyar du med de zung 'jug chen por sbyar //
NK025(ra)001:15853: bsgral du med du mnyam nyid dbyings su bsgral //
NK025(ra)001:15854: ye sgrol ye sbyor chen pos thugs dam bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15855: gzhan yang thugs dam bskang ba'i dam rdzas ni //
NK025(ra)001:15856: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i bdud rtsi dang //
NK025(ra)001:15857: khyad par rmad du byung ba'i gtor ma dang //
NK025(ra)001:15858: pad+ma m+aam sar sbyar ba'i rak+ta dang //
NK025(ra)001:15859: 'bru bcud stong la sbyar ba'i dza gad dang //
NK025(ra)001:15860: rnam rtog rgyu bsgral bam chen rdzas mchog dang //
NK025(ra)001:15861: tshogs kyi zhal zas longs spyod sna tshogs dang //
NK025(ra)001:15862: spyan gzigs dkor cha mthun pa'i dam rdzas bcas //
NK025(ra)001:15863: mchod pa'i bye brag bsam yas dpag med kyis //
NK025(ra)001:15865: chos sku kun tu bzang po'i thugs dam bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15867: drin can rtsa ba'i bla ma'i thugs dam bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15868: zhes sogs kyi bar rig pas dpyad la bya /
NK025(ra)001:15870: snga rabs gshegs pa'i rdo rje slob dpon dang //
NK025(ra)001:15871: da lta bzhugs pa'i rdo rje slob dpon dang //
NK025(ra)001:15872: slad nas 'byon pa'i rdo rje slob dpon dang //
NK025(ra)001:15873: dus gsum rdo rje slob dpon thugs dam bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15874: snga rabs gshegs pa'i rdo rje mched lcam dang //
NK025(ra)001:15875: da lta bzhugs pa'i rdo rje mched lcam dang //
NK025(ra)001:15876: slad nas 'byon pa'i rdo rje mched lcam dang //
NK025(ra)001:15877: dus gsum rdo rje mched lcam thugs dam bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15878: bskang ngo bskal ba'i thugs dam bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15879: skongs gyur dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK025(ra)001:15880: mchod du med de gnyis med rol pas mchod //
NK025(ra)001:15882: mchod pa'i bye brag bsam yas dpag med kyis //
NK025(ra)001:15883: rgyal ba zhi khro rab 'byams thugs dam bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15884: sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis thugs dam bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15885: khrag 'thung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad 'chi med tshe yi
NK025(ra)001:15886: lha tshogs dngos grub bam gyi lha tshogs 'dus pa
NK025(ra)001:15887: mdo yi lha tshogs lnga brgya brgyad cu rtsa bzhi'i
NK025(ra)001:15888: 'jam dpal sku yi lha tshogs pad+ma gsung gi lha
NK025(ra)001:15889: tshogs yang dag thugs kyi lha tshogs bdud rtsi yon
NK025(ra)001:15890: tan lha tshogs phur pa phrin las lha tshogs ma
NK025(ra)001:15891: mo rbood gtong lha tshogs rig 'dzin slob dpon lha
NK025(ra)001:15892: tshogs 'jig rten mchod bstod lha tshogs dmod pa drag
NK025(ra)001:15893: sngags lha tshogs bka' brgyad sgrub pa'i lha tshogs bdun
NK025(ra)001:15894: brgya nyi shu rtsa lnga'i bka' brgyad sgrub pa'i dam
NK025(ra)001:15895: can theg pa dgu yi lha tshogs rgyud sde bzhi
NK025(ra)001:15896: yi lha tshogs bcom ldan bde dgyes gsang gsum dpal
NK025(ra)001:15897: chen dus kyi 'khor lo'i yi dam rdo rje phag
NK025(ra)001:15898: mo'i ye shes mkha' 'gro sde lnga'i dur khrod mkha'
NK025(ra)001:15899: 'gro sde brgyad bskang ngo bskal pa'i thugs dam bskang
NK025(ra)001:15900: // skongs gyur dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK025(ra)001:15902: mchod du med de gnyis med rol pas mchod //
NK025(ra)001:15903: bskang du med de sogs gong bzhin //
NK025(ra)001:15904: dbyings kyi yum chen drug gi thugs dam bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15905: ye shes rje mo bcu bzhi'i dman mo lnga bcu
NK025(ra)001:15906: rtsa brgyad bdag nyid chen mo bzhi yi shwa na
NK025(ra)001:15907: mu kha bzhi yi bse yi lha mo bzhi yi
NK025(ra)001:15908: rgyal mo chen mo bzhi yi blon mo chen mo
NK025(ra)001:15909: bzhi yi bdud mo chen mo bzhi yi dge bsnyen
NK025(ra)001:15910: nyi shu rtsa gcig chos skyong srung ma rnams kyi
NK025(ra)001:15911: ye shes mgon po 'bar ma'i lha chen ma h+aa
NK025(ra)001:15912: k+aa la'i dpal ldan mdo yi mgon po'i gter bdag
NK025(ra)001:15913: ma ning nag po'i dpal ldan lha mo dpon g.yog
NK025(ra)001:15914: sngags srung e ka dz+aa ti'i smug nag khros ma
NK025(ra)001:15915: rgyal mo'i nyi zla rlung gshog can gyi dur khrood
NK025(ra)001:15916: ma mo gsum gyi skyes bu zhwa yi mgon po'i
NK025(ra)001:15917: gnod sbyin rdo rje bdud 'dul rgyal chen rnam thos
NK025(ra)001:15918: sras kyi dregs pa'i sde dpon sum cu'i bskang ngo
NK025(ra)001:15920: skong gyur dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK025(ra)001:15922: mchod du med de gnyis med rol pas mchod //
NK025(ra)001:15923: bskang du med de sogs gong bzhin //
NK025(ra)001:15924: dam can rgya mtsho rnams kyi dam can dkar mo
NK025(ra)001:15925: 'bum gyi dam can ser mo 'bum gyi dam can
NK025(ra)001:15926: smug mo 'bum gyi dam can nag mo 'bum gyi
NK025(ra)001:15927: dam can sngon mo 'bum gyi bka' bdag bka' srung
NK025(ra)001:15928: rnams kyi gter bdag gter srung rnams kyi pha mes
NK025(ra)001:15929: rgyud kyi srung ma'i slob dpon rgyud kyi srung ma'i
NK025(ra)001:15930: dam chos rgyud kyi srung ma'i dben gnas gnyan gyi
NK025(ra)001:15931: srung ma'i gnas mchog 'di yi srung ma'i sngags 'chang
NK025(ra)001:15932: bdag gi srung ma'i thugs dam bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15933: bskang ngo bskal pa'i thugs dam bskang //
NK025(ra)001:15934: skongs gyur dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK025(ra)001:15935: nad gdon sdig sgrib thams cad zhi bar mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:15936: tshe dang longs spyod thams cad rgyas par mdzod //
NK025(ra)001:15937: khams gsum srid gsum thams cad dbang du sdus //
NK025(ra)001:15938: dgra bgegs gdug pa'i tshogs rnams tshar chod la //
NK025(ra)001:15939: mi mthun gnod pa'i rkyen dbang bzlog tu gsol //
NK025(ra)001:15940: sgyu 'phrul skong bshags kyi rim pa'o //
NK025(ra)001:15941: de nas tshogs la rol zhing lhag ma'i cho ga byas te lhag gtor bsag /
NK025(ra)001:15943: rol nas slob ma phyir khrus bya /
NK025(ra)001:15945: ces gsungs pa slob ma'i khrus ni 'og tu 'byung /
NK025(ra)001:15946: khri ni bshams bzhin pa yin no //
NK025(ra)001:15948: slob dpon rang nyid dkyil 'khor du 'jug pa'i phyir /
NK025(ra)001:15950: gos gsar pa gyon la shar sgor 'dug ste /
NK025(ra)001:15952: ye shes rgyal pos gsol ba btab la me tog dor /
NK025(ra)001:15953: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya /
NK025(ra)001:15955: zhes gsungs pa'i don bla mas khrus bya /
NK025(ra)001:15956: gos gsar pa gyon te dkyil 'khor gyi shar sgo
NK025(ra)001:15957: nas rdo rje'i phyag rgyas me tog bzung la dkyil
NK025(ra)001:15960: +aahbadz+ra sa ma ya +aah h+aum badz+ra sa ma ya h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:15961: s+w+aa badz+ra sa ma ya s+w+aa /
NK025(ra)001:15962: h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya h+aa //
NK025(ra)001:15963: ye shes rgyal po'i sku gsung thugs //
NK025(ra)001:15964: yon tan phrin las rmad po che //
NK025(ra)001:15965: de nyid du ni mnyam sbyor bas //
NK025(ra)001:15966: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK025(ra)001:15967: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK025(ra)001:15968: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya h+aum /
NK025(ra)001:15969: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya hoh dzahh+aum bam hoh
NK025(ra)001:15970: zhes me tog dor zhing dngos grub bskul la dmigs
NK025(ra)001:15972: de nas rang gi sgo gsum nas 'od zer dkar dmar mthing gsum 'phros /
NK025(ra)001:15973: dkyil 'khor lha'i sku gsung thugs la phog /
NK025(ra)001:15974: thams cad mchod pa chen pos mnyes /
NK025(ra)001:15975: dkyil 'khor gyi steng na gang mos kyi bla ma
NK025(ra)001:15976: bzhugs pa de lhag par mnyes par bsam nas thal
NK025(ra)001:15977: mo sbyar te / zhes gsungs pas dkyil 'khor gyi
NK025(ra)001:15978: steng na rang la mdo sgyu sems gsum gyi dkyil
NK025(ra)001:15979: 'khor chen por smin par mdzad pa po kho bo'i
NK025(ra)001:15980: dper mtshon na rigs brgya'i khyab bdag sman lung pa
NK025(ra)001:15981: chen po blo gros mchog gi rdo rje kun bzang
NK025(ra)001:15982: rdo rje 'chang chen po de nyid dkyil 'khor gyi
NK025(ra)001:15983: 'khor lo spro bsdu'i byed po rigs kyi bdag por
NK025(ra)001:15984: gsal btab pa de nyid bdag la lhag par mnyes
NK025(ra)001:15985: par bsam la gus pa chen pos gsol ba gdab
NK025(ra)001:15986: mo sbyar te / pa ni / rtsa bar /
NK025(ra)001:15987: bla ma rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po dang /
NK025(ra)001:15988: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams dang /
NK025(ra)001:15989: lha mkha' 'gro rig pa 'dzin pa thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol /
NK025(ra)001:15990: bdag gis sems can thams cad kyi don bya ba dang /
NK025(ra)001:15991: slob ma 'di rnams 'khor ba las yongs su bsgral
NK025(ra)001:15992: pa'i slad du 'dus pa chen po'i dbang bskur bar
NK025(ra)001:15993: 'tshal gyis bdag ngag nus pa dang ldan par byin
NK025(ra)001:15995: zhes lan gsum byas pa bla ma dang dkyil 'khor
NK025(ra)001:15996: lha tshogs kyi sku gsung thugs las 'od zer dkar
NK025(ra)001:15997: dmar mthing gsum byung nas bdag gi lus ngag yid
NK025(ra)001:15998: gsum la thim pas sgo gsum gyi rtog pa rang
NK025(ra)001:15999: rgyud pa dag / lha rnams dang rang bzhin gnyis su med par bsam /
NK025(ra)001:16000: de nas lha rnams kyis zhal 'dzum pa dang bcas pa /
NK025(ra)001:16001: rigs kyi bu phrin las ci dga' bar spyod cig /
NK025(ra)001:16002: ces gnang ba thob par bsam /
NK025(ra)001:16003: de nas lha la dbang rnams rang gis blangs te
NK025(ra)001:16004: zhus pas rang sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las
NK025(ra)001:16005: kyi gzi brjid dang ldan par bsam la dbang khri'i
NK025(ra)001:16007: de ni slob dpon gyi bdag 'jug go //
NK025(ra)001:16008: zhes gsungs pas spro na de bzhin kyi rjes su
NK025(ra)001:16009: slob ma la ji ltar bskur ba bzhin bdag 'jug
NK025(ra)001:16012: de nas lha la dbang rnams rang gi blangs te zhus pas /
NK025(ra)001:16014: mnga' ris pan chen sku mched kyang nan tan du mdzad pa'i phyir ro //
NK025(ra)001:16015: bsdu na rig pa'i me tog dor pa tsam gyis
NK025(ra)001:16016: kyang 'grub ces yongs 'dzin blo mchog rdo rje gsungs
NK025(ra)001:16017: pa bzhin don la gnas so //
NK025(ra)001:16018: de dag gis tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dngos gzhi sgrub
